訪了老墓地，向我們的祖先致敬。"}},"02e8220ca0965c2fef477fe4f6136d5d":{"createdAt":1781856328293,"data":{"sentence":"The doctor noticed abnormal test results and decided to conduct further investigations.","translation":"醫生注意到異常的檢查結果，並決定進行進一步的調查。"}},"02eb4f8409afb8837ad873ac83bd05ce":{"createdAt":1781856684693,"data":{"sentence":"The school administrator is responsible for managing the budget and hiring staff.","translation":"學校行政人員負責管理預算和招聘員工。"}},"0304dcbb67260b4ee10b0cd85e7e4205":{"createdAt":1781802267358,"data":{"sentence":"The designer's new collection was criticized for being a cheap imitation of high-end fashion brands.","translation":"該設計師的新系列因為是高端時尚品牌的廉價仿製品而受到批評。"}},"0326fdfdbd5e14e20c85bf94048ddcdd":{"createdAt":1781893800433,"data":{"sentence":"The students interact with each other during group discussions to share different perspectives.","translation":"學生在小組討論中互動，以分享不同的觀點。"}},"0328b27fd3949b2e634ce035443769be":{"createdAt":1781665682404,"data":{"sentence":"The volcano erupted violently, sending ash and lava across the surrounding villages.","translation":"火山劇烈噴發，將火山灰和熔岩四散到周圍的村莊。"}},"036e0c272815a250c70b15198dcfccf9":{"createdAt":1781881229728,"data":{"sentence":"Her teacher's encouragement helped her gain confidence in public speaking.","translation":"她的老師的鼓勵幫助她在公開演講中獲得了信心。"}},"03939b259aa1e94dc7328e7a2019cee7":{"createdAt":1781535728145,"data":{"sentence":"The protagonist in the novel is a fictional character who never actually existed in real life.","translation":"小說中的主角是一個虛構的人物，在現實生活中從未真實存在過。"}},"0394579d42b06cebd9c1417edb3b31fe":{"createdAt":1781400777234,"data":{"sentence":"The definition of success varies from person to person depending on their individual goals and values.","translation":"成功的定義因人而異，取決於每個人的個人目標和價值觀。"}},"039e890e0f080b76fc372801ce1efe90":{"createdAt":1781400632580,"data":{"sentence":"The teacher asked the students to define the term 'photosynthesis' in their own words.","translation":"老師要求學生用自己的話來定義「光合作用」這個術語。"}},"03b731d7cf02c667678b0a71c3fb035d":{"createdAt":1781805700289,"data":{"sentence":"The manager treated his inferiors with respect and fairness, never looking down on those in lower positions.","translation":"這位經理尊重並公平對待他的下級員工，從不輕視那些職位較低的人。"}},"03db19410238f952eb1d15445a77540c":{"createdAt":1781621612581,"data":{"sentence":"The company plans to develop new software features to improve user experience.","translation":"該公司計畫開發新的軟體功能來改善使用者體驗。"}},"03ed9e7d517f873e42c1a539bcce2f2c":{"createdAt":1781564218200,"data":{"sentence":"I am writing this letter on behalf of our entire team to express our gratitude for your support.","translation":"我代表我們整個團隊寫這封信，以表達我們對您支持的感謝。"}},"049f9054244bb8480cb44d7a0100b98b":{"createdAt":1781526693031,"data":{"sentence":"My grandfather is still alive at the age of ninety-five.","translation":"我的祖父現在還活著，已經九十五歲了。"}},"04be5ee478c8d5c40406e6ccce332abe":{"createdAt":1781737568312,"data":{"sentence":"Coffee is commonly consumed in the morning by millions of people around the world.","translation":"全世界數百萬人通常在早晨喝咖啡。"}},"04bf8ed01183b0d1979e616923694f84":{"createdAt":1781278612392,"data":{"sentence":"She gave him a distant look, making it clear she wasn't interested in continuing their conversation.","translation":"她用冷淡的眼神看著他，清楚地表明她不想繼續他們的談話。"}},"04eabc366bc37081763da6f5451fb18c":{"createdAt":1781278653232,"data":{"sentence":"She always dressed with decency and maintained proper etiquette in formal settings.","translation":"她在正式場合中總是穿著得體，舉止端莊。"}},"0500447965ee8e2a3c9799da8b940d82":{"createdAt":1781856381767,"data":{"sentence":"The doctor explained the different medical options available to the patient considering abortion.","translation":"醫生向考慮墮胎的患者解釋了可用的不同醫療選擇。"}},"0516bda7d9eeea79d03e6ac1d1211ac1":{"createdAt":1781368019404,"data":{"sentence":"She couldn't hide her envy when her colleague got promoted before her.","translation":"當她的同事在她之前升職時，她無法隱藏自己的忌妒。"}},"0557a777ebd73f46c2a818a03a5ccd11":{"createdAt":1781536169181,"data":{"sentence":"A flash of lightning illuminated the dark sky for just a moment.","translation":"一道閃光的閃電只是瞬間照亮了黑暗的天空。"}},"05fb40f31d6d960f24439b1a5afa0a92":{"createdAt":1781430824375,"data":{"sentence":"The company has a well-defined strategy for expanding into new markets over the next five years.","translation":"該公司對於未來五年開拓新市場有一個明確界定的策略。"}},"06133db8eb54a1cd3f3f683ed40b82d0":{"createdAt":1781802282832,"data":{"sentence":"When the fire alarm went off, everyone evacuated the building immediately.","translation":"火警警報響起時，每個人立刻撤離了建築物。"}},"062191a3286c1a57b2f0ccc0ac01d988":{"createdAt":1781535778310,"data":{"sentence":"The financial report includes a detailed figure showing the company's revenue growth over the past five years.","translation":"財務報告中包含一份詳細的圖表，顯示公司過去五年的收入增長情況。"}},"0683067e412f6aabbddccf926a180af4":{"createdAt":1781769936143,"data":{"sentence":"Many of my fondest memories come from playing in the park during my childhood.","translation":"我許多最美好的回憶都來自於童年時期在公園裡玩耍。"}},"06bc17fdeeb86e777b546f47ed715d32":{"createdAt":1781278343158,"data":{"sentence":"Many restaurants have switched to using eco-friendly disposables instead of plastic bags and containers.","translation":"許多餐廳已經改用環保一次性用品，而不是塑膠袋和容器。"}},"075db77f731dcf11a5ec76c7cec46cdd":{"createdAt":1781769461680,"data":{"sentence":"Early detection of cancer can significantly improve a patient's chances of survival.","translation":"及早發現癌症可以大幅提高患者的存活機率。"}},"078cd30023b12e51c8c4cc6042a67daf":{"createdAt":1781450631365,"data":{"sentence":"The idiom 'break the ice' means to relieve tension in a social situation.","translation":"習語「break the ice」是指在社交場合中緩解緊張氣氛。"}},"07c3fa3368ce8201de478a5b5e6bbda8":{"createdAt":1781366159873,"data":{"sentence":"The construction workers used a crane to elevate the heavy steel beam to the top floor of the building.","translation":"建築工人用起重機把沉重的鋼梁舉起到建築物的頂樓。"}},"07e0fa7e9a53d902068f013d529fbc3f":{"createdAt":1781881163461,"data":{"sentence":"The new marketing strategy proved to be very effective in increasing sales.","translation":"這個新的行銷策略在增加銷售方面證明非常有效