olvement in the crime despite the evidence against him.","translation":"儘管有證據指控他，那名嫌疑人仍然持續否認自己參與了這起犯罪。"}},"8ac72970fc047d7e73a4af890ae087ab":{"createdAt":1781737885054,"data":{"sentence":"Before traveling abroad, I decided to insure my luggage against loss or damage.","translation":"在出國旅行前，我決定為我的行李投保以防止遺失或損壞。"}},"8af0ac9652b83271a19473a078d0a9d5":{"createdAt":1781450325424,"data":{"sentence":"The new policy will exclude employees who have not completed the mandatory training program.","translation":"新政策將開除那些未完成強制培訓計畫的員工。"}},"8b2edb8babcb80283f2c38aa10ceef41":{"createdAt":1781768331191,"data":{"sentence":"The addition of fresh vegetables to the salad made it much more nutritious.","translation":"沙拉中新鮮蔬菜的添加使其營養價值大大提高。"}},"8b44ff84ca3c34045d266e7d12365443":{"createdAt":1781737574234,"data":{"sentence":"The cost of living in major cities has increased significantly over the past decade.","translation":"過去十年來，大城市的生活費用已經大幅上升。"}},"8bba0bf1562c48a5cd2bbe768a49f25d":{"createdAt":1781894664706,"data":{"sentence":"The manager struggled to justify the company's decision to lay off experienced employees during the profitable quarter.","translation":"經理努力為公司在獲利季度裡裁減資深員工的決定辯護。"}},"8bc559602c15e27dbf44489cdff14847":{"createdAt":1781777328691,"data":{"sentence":"She felt confident about her presentation after weeks of thorough preparation.","translation":"經過數週的充分準備後，她對自己的演講感到很有信心。"}},"8bf2b06a72ce2dd538876764c8864811":{"createdAt":1781504091243,"data":{"sentence":"He carefully groomed his mustache every morning with a special wax.","translation":"他每天早上都用特殊的蠟小心翼翼地修剪他的八字鬚。"}},"8c0942b12f382e2e65d0f6e1a3ee232b":{"createdAt":1781711728022,"data":{"sentence":"After work, I usually go to the gymnasium to lift weights and use the treadmill.","translation":"下班後，我通常去健身房舉重和使用跑步機。"}},"8c736e7afb2182cb0dde0ff7de8ea324":{"createdAt":1781881343152,"data":{"sentence":"The existence of life on other planets remains one of science's greatest mysteries.","translation":"其他星球上生命的存在仍然是科學最大的謎團之一。"}},"8c9