iety.","translation":"許多古代文明在今天已不復存在，但它們的遺產繼續影響現代社會。"}},"8e40e1870d2dffc5b79070a1dbcd9e2c":{"createdAt":1781838557457,"data":{"sentence":"After going through the ordeal of losing his job and home, he finally found stability and hope again.","translation":"在經歷了失業和失家的磨難之後，他終於重新找到了穩定和希望。"}},"8e44a0fe6ee9523f88c6f795a67f1624":{"createdAt":1781738227657,"data":{"sentence":"The squirrels chattered loudly in the oak tree as we walked past.","translation":"當我們走過時，松鼠在橡樹上吱吱喳喳地大聲叫著。"}},"8e4fcd631c761efa923c19d69ffd8a32":{"createdAt":1781577797882,"data":{"sentence":"The sleek design of the sports car caught everyone's attention as it glided smoothly down the street.","translation":"那輛跑車流線型的設計吸引了所有人的目光，當它光滑地沿著街道滑行時。"}},"8e6544fb66cf4a635e4d39354fa6ce67":{"createdAt":1781477616948,"data":{"sentence":"Her grandmother was diagnosed with dementia last year and now struggles to remember her own children's names.","translation":"她的祖母去年被診斷出患有老年癡呆症,現在甚至記不住自己孩子們的名字了。"}},"8e9fab8e901f8b755eafd66d2618f2cf":{"createdAt":1781367611869,"data":{"sentence":"The hotel provides excellent entertainment options including live music, comedy shows, and dancing every evening.","translation":"這家飯店提供優質的娛樂選項，包括每晚的現場音樂、喜劇表演和舞蹈。"}},"8ec0fd6a9c37ccff6e1affcbf58dfbe8":{"createdAt":1781893796757,"data":{"sentence":"His intentional silence during the meeting was a deliberate choice to avoid conflict.","translation":"他在會議中的故意沉默是一個刻意的選擇，用來避免衝突。"}},"8ed8f8a5d1460c8e1fa71a10133694cb":{"createdAt":1781770279809,"data":{"sentence":"She founded her own technology company five years ago and now employs over fifty people.","translation":"她五年前創辦了自己的科技公司，現在已經僱用了五十多名員工。"}},"8f62b63607f53113870e1ba12342c7f3":{"createdAt":1781650758724,"data":{"sentence":"Despite the heavy rain, she decided to go for a walk in the park.","translation":"儘管下著大雨，她還是決定去公園散步。"}},"8f679fd53d1e79a83e05e0add46f81fb":{"createdAt":1781623419038,"data":{"sentence":"I prepared all the materials beforehand so that the meeting would run smoothly.","tran