441,"data":{"sentence":"There is a small gap between the two wooden boards where you can see daylight.","translation":"在兩塊木板之間有一個小裂口，你可以看到陽光透過來。"}},"fd44e92d3760549401e214513dd5531c":{"createdAt":1781894220375,"data":{"sentence":"She decided to invest her savings in a tech startup because she believed in the company's potential for growth.","translation":"她決定將積蓄投資於一家科技新創公司，因為她相信該公司具有成長潛力。"}},"fdbacb704381a8ee43fe917a714b74f9":{"createdAt":1781325915034,"data":{"sentence":"After losing her passport at the airport, she made frantic calls to the airline trying to catch her flight.","translation":"在機場遺失護照後，她瘋狂地撥打航空公司的電話，試圖趕上她的班機。"}},"fe0eaf7eab74953140cd7203081fa2dd":{"createdAt":1781511011065,"data":{"sentence":"The sponge quickly absorbed the spilled water from the kitchen counter.","translation":"海綿迅速吸收了廚房檯面上灑出的水。"}},"fe16d50706edec5697d0db1cf1e44847":{"createdAt":1781961948584,"data":{"sentence":"The aviation industry has made tremendous advances in safety and fuel efficiency over the past decade.","translation":"過去十年間，航空工業在安全性和燃油效率方面取得了巨大進步。"}},"fe23bab160127fc2f7c035a80b43aea2":{"createdAt":1781519605295,"data":{"sentence":"After graduating from college, she moved to her own apartment to pursue her independence.","translation":"大學畢業後，她搬到自己的公寓去追求獨立。"}},"fe2d21414102707dc45d30a65a453cee":{"createdAt":1781971635837,"data":{"sentence":"Every challenge you face is actually an opportunity to grow stronger and discover your true potential.","translation":"你面臨的每一個挑戰實際上都是一個機會，讓你變得更堅強並發現自己真正的潛力。"}},"fe3c82884879fd5f7c59548af0ff0206":{"createdAt":1781665314995,"data":{"sentence":"The company offered a bonus as an incentive for employees to increase their productivity.","translation":"公司提供獎金作為激勵員工提高生產力的誘因。"}},"fe5d7c24d93849be6389a015603245f4":{"createdAt":1781738083511,"data":{"sentence":"It is in the nature of children to be curious about the world around them.","translation":"孩童對周圍世界充滿好奇是他們的天性。"}},"fe60d778a0f96e6a53e101725e519e54":{"createdAt":1781447594518,"data":{"sentence":"I ran into an old acquaintance at the grocery store yesterday.","translation":"我昨天在雜貨店遇到了一位老相識。"}},"fe944772e273d2d12ca11ed554d77408":{"createdAt":1781894269993,"data":{"sentence":"When the doctor tapped his knee, his leg jerked up in an involuntary reflex.","translation":"當醫生敲擊他的膝蓋時，他的腿因為不由自主的反射作用而抖動。"}},"fec8424956f20910c355b9bbb8055b74":{"createdAt":1781665520423,"data":{"sentence":"The ancient king's burial took place in a grand tomb deep beneath the pyramid.","translation":"這位古代國王的埋葬儀式在金字塔深處的宏偉墓穴中舉行。"}},"fedb366c24e13be0138d9ff6b168b184":{"createdAt":1781689307296,"data":{"sentence":"During the pandemic, many people began to hoard toilet paper and hand sanitizer in their homes.","translation":"在疫情期間，許多人開始在家中囤積衛生紙和手部消毒液。"}},"fef33805092ede59502387c880d45382":{"createdAt":1781505931314,"data":{"sentence":"The conspiracy to assassinate the president was discovered by the secret service before it could be carried out.","translation":"暗殺總統的陰謀在特勤局執行前被發現了。"}},"ff0576fedd6123cc16f0c57a7d59e6cc":{"createdAt":1781529065728,"data":{"sentence":"The severe winter weather caused the school to close for several days.","translation":"嚴重的冬季天氣導致學校停課了好幾天。"}},"ff312bb0b13a12319821bf824c8de667":{"createdAt":1781278839687,"data":{"sentence":"The constant notifications on her phone became a major distraction while she was trying to study for her exam.","translation":"她手機上不斷的通知成為了她準備考試時的一大心煩意亂。"}},"ffc492020ad521a73e96e1c6d239998c":{"createdAt":1781737730988,"data":{"sentence":"I expect the package to arrive tomorrow based on the tracking information.","translation":"根據追蹤資訊，我預料包裹明天會送達。"}},"ffd6216592025e7a709556f6c3f390e8":{"createdAt":1781793023777,"data":{"sentence":"The hungry lion devoured the antelope in just a few minutes.","translation":"飢餓的獅子在短短幾分鐘內就狼吞虎嚥地吃掉了那隻羚羊。"}},"ffdf75ef8a1dae7b0589c5f313c235af":{"createdAt":1781487089354,"data":{"sentence":"The dense fog rolled across the highway, reducing visibility to just a few meters.","translation":"濃厚的霧氣籠罩著高速公路，能見度降低到只有幾米。"}}},"file-search-intents":{"Ucc2288bf1bdfa7b6c2414622c0df2ba4":{"expireAt":1776952398298}},"onedrive-auth":{"folders":{"admin":{"driveId":"ED0685DFF9D8666E","itemId":"ED0685DFF9D8666E!44098","name":"Wisdom English 唯思英文","path":"/drives/ED0685DFF9D8666E/root:/Wisdom English 唯思英文","url":"https://1drv.ms/f/c/ed0685dff9d8666e/IgBuZtj534UGIIDtQqwAAAAAAV2J_orqMl9nG5riCaVAVIo?e=JE0eNi"},"shared":{"driveId":"ED0685DFF9D8666E","itemId":"ED0685DFF9D8666E!44100","name":"#團隊事項","path":"/drives/ED0685DFF9D8666E/root:/Wisdom English 唯思英文/#團隊事項","url":"https://1drv.ms/f/c/ed0685dff9d8666e/IgBuZtj534UGIIDtRKwAAAAAAUoMQOQ4c1iafODy-Wz-ISc?e=VLgQDG"}},"refreshToken":"M.C547_BL2.0.U.-Clv0SUBbj5DLJX!57r2*cOod*nmmEuAKV9Fqa0NLVdOGpA82rTiyQx84YcQ8mSdvEM8ynRYbCHDYs24Uwsje92M!olEMHcm0hPNSLo56vNePrAcqA9AW06kr4wr4bSDS94pjgGZa2HNFbJEXFjmV2RHf*9wV4lMh!ZVmWI8s7z1wjV2sAC8dhPVnL*01sJAAKLJgLoeHZMBsmGoakjTAd!K3wceGrn7BavFeea9EgFlnWIkTFF9DKs7cZMLRFfesnmCPyfrMj2UEMS3CCNj0Xzld6jumyk23oBmq5R2ZteHxgUwCfe*0EKDU2pb6Qvz*DvFIKYjOFAIzsWh!vI9mZftUeiRX4S4N73vn9n6A6vvESqqjs25TbLdZxVPkdUPU4Q$$","savedAt":1776994065013},"published":{"article":"The High-Stakes Confrontation: Trump and Iran\nThe geopolitical tension between Donald Trump and Iran remains one of the most volatile issues in modern international relations. To understand the origins of this conflict, we must examine the 2015 Iran Nuclear Deal (JCPOA). While the Obama administration viewed the deal as a diplomatic breakthrough to prevent Iran from developing nuclear weapons, Trump campaigned against it, calling it \"the worst deal ever negotiated.\" He argued that the agreement was fundamentally flawed because it failed to address Iran’s ballistic missile program and its support for various proxy groups across the Middle East.\n\nIn May 2018, the situation reached a critical turning point when Trump officially withdrew the United States from the nuclear deal. This move initiated a strategy known as the \"Maximum Pressure\" campaign. The primary objective was to cripple Iran’s economy through heavy sanctions, specifically targeting their oil exports—the nation's economic lifeline. By cutting off Iran's primary source of revenue, Trump aimed to force the Iranian leadership back to the negotiating table to sign a much stricter, more comprehensive \"grand bargain.\"\n\nThe process of escalation moved rapidly from economic warfare to direct military confrontation. In 2019, tensions spiked after several oil tankers were attacked in the Strait of Hormuz, and Iran shot down a high-tech U.S. surveillance drone. However, the most significant moment occurred in January 2020, when Trump authorized a drone strike that killed the powerful Iranian General Qasem Soleimani in Baghdad. This targeted killing brought both nations to the very brink of a full-scale war. Iran responded by launching ballistic missiles at U.S. bases in Iraq, though both sides eventually stepped back to avoid a total catastrophe.\n\nCurrently, with Trump’s return to office in 2026, the strategy remains focused on strategic containment. While the military threat is always present, Trump’s approach often involves a unique blend of extreme rhetoric and the possibility of high-level diplomacy. He frequently oscillates between threatening \"obliteration\" and expressing a desire to meet with Iranian leaders to resolve the dispute. As the international community watches closely, the world remains uncertain whether this pressure will lead to a new diplomatic breakthrough or an accidental escalation into a regional conflict. The line between deterrence and open war remains incredibly thin.","articleTitle":"The High-Stakes Confrontation: Trump and Iran","data":{"discussion":[{"q":"Do you think economic sanctions are more effective than military action in resolving international conflicts? Why or why not?","zh":"中文提示：比較經濟制裁與軍事行動的效果和後果"},{"q":"How should world leaders balance between showing strength and pursuing diplomatic solutions when dealing with adversaries?","zh":"中文提示：探討領導人在展現強硬與外交之間的平衡"}],"fill":[{"blanks":["Maximum Pressure","oil"],"sentence":"Trump withdrew from the nuclear deal to initiate a strategy called ___ which targeted Iran's ___ exports.","zh_hint":"中文提示：川普的經濟制裁策略"},{"blanks":["Qasem Soleimani","full-scale war"],"sentence":"The killing of General ___ in January 2020 brought both nations to the brink of ___.","zh_hint":"中文提示：2020年的軍事衝突事件"}],"mcq":[{"ans":1,"explain":"中文解題說明：文中指出川普認為協議未處理飛彈計畫和代理人組織問題","opts":["A. Iran violated the agreement's terms","B. The deal didn't address missiles and proxy groups","C. Obama requested the withdrawal","D. Iran refused to negotiate further"],"q":"Why did Trump withdraw from the Iran Nuclear Deal?"},{"ans":1,"explain":"中文解題說明：目標是透過經濟制裁迫使伊朗重回談判桌並簽署更嚴格協議","opts":["A. To start a military war immediately","B. To force Iran to negotiate a stricter deal","C. To support Iran's economy","D. To help Iran export more oil"],"q":"What was the primary goal of the 'Maximum Pressure' campaign?"},{"ans":2,"explain":"中文解題說明：文中描述川普的策略是極端言論與高層外交可能性的結合","opts":["A. Pure military aggression only","B. Complete diplomatic cooperation","C. A mix of threats and diplomatic possibilities","D. Total withdrawal from the region"],"q":"What characterizes Trump's current approach to Iran?"}],"vocab":[{"pos":"adj.","word":"volatile","zh":"不穩定的；易變的"},{"pos":"n.","word":"diplomatic breakthrough","zh":"外交突破"},{"pos":"adj.","word":"fundamentally flawed","zh":"根本上有缺陷的"},{"pos":"v.","word":"cripple","zh":"削弱；使癱瘓"},{"pos":"n.","word":"escalation","zh":"升級；惡化"},{"pos":"n.","word":"brink","zh":"邊緣"},{"pos":"v.","word":"oscillates","zh":"搖擺；振盪"},{"pos":"n.","word":"deterrence","zh":"威懾；遏制"}]},"fillCount":2,"level":"B2","publishedAt":"2026-03-26T18:31:40.453Z"},"quiz-cache":{"abbreviate":{"createdAt":1781268630478,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"abbreviate表示縮寫或簡短，使某事變得更簡潔或更短。","options":["extend","abbreviate","reschedule","postpone"],"sentence":"We decided to ______ the meeting because time was running short. We removed all unnecessary discussions and covered only the essential points.","translation":"因為時間不夠，我們決定縮短會議時間。我們刪除了所有不必要的討論，只涵蓋了要點。","word":"abbreviate"}},"abbreviated":{"createdAt":1781351849565,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"abbreviated 表示「縮寫的、簡稱的」，與「節省時間和空間」的描述完全相符。","options":["extended","expanded","shortened","lengthened"],"sentence":"The ______ form of 'United States of America' is commonly written as 'USA' in official documents. This shorter version saves time and space while maintaining clarity.","translation":"「美利堅合眾國」的縮寫形式在官方文件中通常寫成「美國」。這個較短的版本節省時間和空間，同時保持清晰。","word":"abbreviated"}},"abbreviation":{"createdAt":1781581336195,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"abbreviation指的是用縮短形式表示的單詞或短語。","options":["definition","abbreviation","translation","description"],"sentence":"The ______ 'USA' stands for United States of America and is widely recognized worldwide. Using such shortened forms helps save time in writing and speaking.","translation":"'美國'的縮寫代表美利堅合眾國，在世界各地廣為人知。使用這樣的簡稱有助於節省寫作和演講的時間。","word":"abbreviation"}},"abide":{"createdAt":1781481124702,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"abide 表示遵守或服從某些規則、法律或協議。","options":["ignore","violate","comply with","challenge"],"sentence":"All employees must ______ by the company's strict code of conduct and ethics. Those who violate these rules will face serious disciplinary measures.","translation":"所有員工必須遵守公司嚴格的行為規範和倫理準則。違反這些規則的人將面臨嚴肅的紀律處分。","word":"abide"}},"ability":{"createdAt":1781331945987,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ability 指某人擁有的技能或才能，能夠做好某件事情。","options":["weakness","talent","age","costume"],"sentence":"The young pianist demonstrated remarkable ______ during the concert last night. Her technical skill and emotional control impressed even the most experienced music critics in the audience.","translation":"那位年輕鋼琴家在昨晚的音樂會上展現了非凡的才能。她的技術技巧和情感控制給觀眾中最資深的音樂評論家留下了深刻印象。","word":"ability"}},"able":{"createdAt":1781351849564,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"able 表示「有能力的」，與「獲得評委讚賞」的背景相符，說明她具備了必要的能力。","options":["unable","willing","nervous","competent"],"sentence":"After years of training, the young pianist was finally ______ to perform at the international competition. The judges were impressed by her technical skill and musical interpretation.","translation":"經過多年的訓練，年輕鋼琴家終於能夠在國際比賽中表演。評委對她的技術技巧和音樂詮釋印象深刻。","word":"able"}},"abnormal":{"createdAt":1781527602363,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"abnormal 表示偏離常規、不正常或異於尋常的；在醫學檢查中特指超出正常範圍的結果。","options":["typical","expected","abnormal","regular"],"sentence":"The doctor noticed ______ test results when reviewing the patient's blood work. The values were so far outside the standard range that immediate investigation was required.","translation":"醫生在檢查患者的血液檢查結果時發現了異常的數值。這些數值遠在標準範圍之外，需要立即進行調查。","word":"abnormal"}},"aboard":{"createdAt":1781351849566,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aboard 表示「在船、飛機、車上」或「搭上」，與「起飛前的最後安全檢查」相符，說明乘客已經上飛機。","options":["outside","inside","away from","near"],"sentence":"All passengers must be ______ the aircraft at least thirty minutes before departure. The flight attendants will then conduct a final safety check before takeoff.","translation":"所有乘客必須在起飛前至少三十分鐘登上飛機。隨後空服員會在起飛前進行最後的安全檢查。","word":"aboard"}},"abolish":{"createdAt":1781227315831,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"abolish 的意思是「廢除、廢止」，指完全消除或終止某項法律、制度或習慣，通常用於正式的政治或法律行為。","options":["strengthen","abolish","amend","enforce"],"sentence":"The government voted to ______ the outdated law that had been in effect for over fifty years. After the new policy took effect, citizens no longer had to follow those old regulations.","translation":"政府投票廢除了已實施超過五十年的過時法律。新政策生效後，市民不再需要遵守那些舊規定。","word":"abolish"}},"abolition":{"createdAt":1781598671071,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"abolition 作名詞表示廢止或廢除，特別指正式終止某項制度或法律","options":["expansion","abolition","continuation","regulation"],"sentence":"The ______ of slavery was a major turning point in American history. The Emancipation Proclamation and the 13th Amendment formally ended this institution in the United States.","translation":"廢除奴隸制是美國歷史上的重要轉折點。《解放宣言》和第13條憲法修正案正式結束了美國的這一制度。","word":"abolition"}},"aboriginal":{"createdAt":1781360906188,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aboriginal 意思是原住民的或原始的，指最早的本土居民及其文化。","options":["modern","aboriginal","imported","contemporary"],"sentence":"The museum exhibits ______ artifacts and artwork from the native peoples of Australia. These pieces date back thousands of years to the earliest inhabitants.","translation":"博物館展示了澳洲土著民族的原住民文物和藝術作品。這些作品可以追溯到最早居民的數千年前。","word":"aboriginal"}},"aborigine":{"createdAt":1781362281647,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aborigine指的是某地的原始居民，特別是澳大利亞的土著人民。","options":["immigrant","aborigine","settler","visitor"],"sentence":"The ______ of Australia have lived on the continent for thousands of years. Their ancient cultures and traditions date back to the earliest inhabitants of the land.","translation":"澳大利亞的原住民已經在這個大陸上生活了數千年。他們古老的文化和傳統可以追溯到這片土地最早的居民。","word":"aborigine"}},"abortion":{"createdAt":1781351849567,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"abortion 表示「墮胎」，與「宗教和倫理信仰」的政治辯論背景相符，這是一個具有爭議性的話題。","options":["education","healthcare","pregnancy","reproduction"],"sentence":"The government's new legislation regarding ______ has sparked heated debate among politicians and citizens. Different groups hold strong views based on their religious and ethical beliefs.","translation":"政府關於墮胎的新立法在政治人物和公民之間引發了激烈的辯論。不同的團體根據他們的宗教和倫理信仰持有強烈的觀點。","word":"abortion"}},"abound":{"createdAt":1781351849565,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"abound 表示「大量存在、充滿」，與「公司積極招聘」的線索相符，說明機會非常豐富。","options":["disappear","decrease","flourish","diminish"],"sentence":"Excellent job opportunities ______ in the technology sector these days. Companies are actively hiring and competing to attract talented professionals.","translation":"現今科技行業充滿了優質的工作機會。公司正在積極招聘並競爭以吸引有才華的專業人士。","word":"abound"}},"abroad":{"createdAt":1781275226791,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"此處abroad作副詞表示「在國外；到國外」，指離開本國到其他國家","options":["abroad","controversial","breast","feast"],"sentence":"She decided to study ______ in France for a full year to improve her language skills. Living in Paris would give her immersion in the French culture and environment.","translation":"她決定在法國國外生活一整年以提高她的語言技能。住在巴黎將使她沉浸在法國文化和環境中。","word":"abroad"}},"abrupt":{"createdAt":1781360906188,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"abrupt 意思是突然的或陡峭的，指沒有預警或漸進過程就立即發生的事情。","options":["gradual","abrupt","smooth","expected"],"sentence":"The train made an ______ stop when the brakes were applied suddenly. Passengers were thrown forward without warning.","translation":"當緊急剎車被啟動時，火車突然停止了。乘客在沒有警告的情況下向前衝去。","word":"abrupt"}},"absence":{"createdAt":1781598671085,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"absence 作名詞表示缺席或缺少，指某物或某人不在場或不存在的狀態","options":["presence","absence","abundance","storage"],"sentence":"The ______ of fresh water made it difficult for the village to survive the drought. Residents had to travel miles to find any source of drinking water.","translation":"缺乏淡水使村莊很難在乾旱中生存。居民必須走幾英里才能找到任何飲用水源。","word":"absence"}},"absent":{"createdAt":1781351849563,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"absent 在此表示「不注意的、心不在焉的」，與「沒有注意演講」的線索相符。","options":["present","distracted","bored","quiet"],"sentence":"During the important meeting, Tom appeared to be ______ even though he was sitting at the table. His supervisor noticed he wasn't paying attention to any of the presentations or discussions.","translation":"在重要會議期間，湯姆看起來不在場，儘管他坐在桌子旁。他的主管注意到他沒有注意任何演講或討論。","word":"absent"}},"absolute":{"createdAt":1781351849561,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"absolute 表示「完全的、絕對的」，與「需要更多研究」的對比相符，因為絕對陳述會排除進一步研究的需要。","options":["tentative","definitive","temporary","preliminary"],"sentence":"The scientist refused to make an ______ statement about the new discovery without more evidence. She explained that further research would be necessary before confirming anything with certainty.","translation":"科學家拒絕在沒有更多證據的情況下對新發現做出絕對的陳述。她解釋說在以確定性確認任何事情之前需要進一步的研究。","word":"absolute"}},"absorb":{"createdAt":1781360906182,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"absorb 意思是吸收或理解，這裡用來描述海綿吸收水分的能力。","options":["release","absorb","pour","spill"],"sentence":"The sponge can ______ large amounts of water. When you squeeze it, all the liquid comes back out.","translation":"海綿可以吸收大量的水。當你擠它時，所有的液體都會流出來。","word":"absorb"}},"absorbed":{"createdAt":1781581336210,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"absorbed表示完全沉浸於某事物中，給予全部的注意力。","options":["distracted","absorbed","bored","confused"],"sentence":"The student was completely ______ in the fascinating novel during class and didn't notice the teacher calling his name. His full concentration on the story made him oblivious to his surroundings.","translation":"這個學生在課堂上完全沉浸在迷人的小說中，沒有注意到老師叫他的名字。他對故事的全神貫注使他對周圍環境視而不見。","word":"absorbed"}},"absorption":{"createdAt":1781360885490,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"absorption在商業中指一個公司被另一個公司吞併或合併，成為更大企業的一部分。","options":["rejection","absorption","separation","division"],"sentence":"The ______ of the smaller company by the larger corporation was completed last year. The two businesses are now operating as a single unified entity.","translation":"較小公司被較大公司的並購去年完成。這兩家業務現在作為一個統一的實體運營。","word":"absorption"}},"abstract":{"createdAt":1781336858156,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"abstract 形容詞表示不具體、不以真實物體為基礎，而是基於概念或想象的事物，尤其在藝術中常見。","options":["realistic","concrete","abstract","literal"],"sentence":"The ______ painting confused many visitors at the modern art museum. Without recognizable objects or clear representations, viewers had to use their imagination to interpret its meaning.","translation":"這幅抽象畫在現代藝術博物館中令許多訪客感到困惑。沒有可識別的物體或清晰的表現形式，觀眾必須使用想像力來解釋其意義。","word":"abstract"}},"absurd":{"createdAt":1781351849562,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"absurd 表示「荒唐的、不合理的」，與愚人節玩笑的背景完全相符。","options":["reasonable","ridiculous","practical","sensible"],"sentence":"The proposal to ban all bicycles from the city seemed ______ to most citizens. However, the mayor explained it was a joke made during the April Fools' Day announcement.","translation":"禁止所有自行車進入城市的提議對大多數市民來說似乎是荒唐的。不過，市長解釋說這是在愚人節公告期間開的玩笑。","word":"absurd"}},"abundance":{"createdAt":1781532967157,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"abundance 表示豐富、充足，與句中「從未見過這麼多」的描述相符。","options":["scarcity","abundance","shortage","deficit"],"sentence":"The farmer was pleased to see an ______ of fresh vegetables in the market this season. He had never seen so many crops available at once.","translation":"農民很高興看到這個季節市場上有______(豐富)的新鮮蔬菜。他以前從未見過這麼多的農產品一次性上市。","word":"abundance"}},"abundant":{"createdAt":1781843473807,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"abundant 用來形容大量且充足的事物，在這裡指降雨量豐富，導致水庫充滿，農民不再需要人工灌溉。","options":["scarce","abundant","moderate","unpredictable"],"sentence":"The ______ rainfall this season has filled all the reservoirs to capacity. The farmers are celebrating because they won't need to irrigate their crops for months.","translation":"這個季節充足的降雨量已經將所有水庫填滿至容量。農民們在慶祝，因為他們在未來幾個月內不需要灌溉他們的莊稼。","word":"abundant"}},"abuse":{"createdAt":1781351849557,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"abuse 作為動詞表示「虐待、濫用、辱罵」，與造成傷害和創傷的背景相符。","options":["praise","mistreat","train","encourage"],"sentence":"The coach was fired for his decision to ______ young athletes during training sessions. The investigation revealed physical harm and emotional trauma inflicted on the team members.","translation":"那位教練因在訓練期間對年輕運動員的虐待而被解僱。調查揭露了對隊員造成的身體傷害和情感創傷。","word":"abuse"}},"academic":{"createdAt":1781493458242,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"academic 形容詞指與學院、學術或教育有關的，這裡指大學研究和學術工作","options":["athletic","commercial","academic","musical"],"sentence":"She pursued an ______ career studying ancient history at the university. Her research papers were published in peer-reviewed journals and presented at scholarly conferences.","translation":"她追求了在大學研究古代歷史的學術生涯。她的研究論文發表在同行評審期刊上，並在學術會議上發表。","word":"academic"}},"accelerate":{"createdAt":1781484539654,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"accelerate 的意思是加快速度或增加移動的快度，與減速或停止的行為相對。","options":["brake","decelerate","accelerate","reverse"],"sentence":"The driver decided to ______ the car when he saw the green traffic light. His vehicle quickly moved faster down the highway.","translation":"當司機看到綠燈時，他決定加速汽車。他的車輛在高速公路上快速加快速度。","word":"accelerate"}},"accelerated":{"createdAt":1781360906190,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accelerated 意思是加速的或促進的，指速度或進度增加的過程。","options":["standard","accelerated","delayed","normal"],"sentence":"The ______ program allows gifted students to complete their studies faster than usual. These students advance through the curriculum at twice the normal pace.","translation":"加速課程允許天才學生比平常更快地完成他們的學習。這些學生以兩倍的正常速度推進課程。","word":"accelerated"}},"access":{"createdAt":1781581336205,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"access作為名詞指進入某個地方或使用某個東西的權利或途徑。","options":["knowledge","access","permission","approval"],"sentence":"Employees need a special card to gain ______ to the restricted areas of the office building. Without this security credential, entry is strictly prohibited.","translation":"員工需要特殊卡才能進入辦公樓的受限制區域。沒有此安全憑證，進入受到嚴格禁止。","word":"access"}},"accessible":{"createdAt":1781360906189,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accessible 意思是易接近的或易取得的，指可以方便地到達或使用。","options":["isolated","accessible","restricted","remote"],"sentence":"The new library is very ______ to students with disabilities. The building has ramps, elevators, and specialized facilities for everyone.","translation":"新圖書館對有殘疾的學生非常容易接近。該建築為每個人配備了斜坡、電梯和專業設施。","word":"accessible"}},"accessory":{"createdAt":1781256485494,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accessory指的是附件或配件，用來完善或裝飾主要物品","options":["weapon","accessory","vehicle","ingredient"],"sentence":"The leather belt was the perfect ______ to complete her outfit. It matched well with her jacket and shoes.","translation":"這條皮帶是完成她服裝搭配的完美配件。它與她的夾克和鞋子搭配得很好。","word":"accessory"}},"accident":{"createdAt":1781532967166,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accident 表示事故、意外，與「兩車相撞、司機失控」的描述相符。","options":["meeting","accident","event","incident"],"sentence":"The traffic ______ on the highway caused a three-hour delay for all commuters. Two cars had collided when one driver lost control.","translation":"高速公路上的______(事故)造成所有通勤者延誤三小時。兩輛車在一名司機失控時相撞。","word":"accident"}},"accidental":{"createdAt":1781527758986,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accidental 表示意外發生的、非故意的事情，與 intentional、deliberate 或 planned 相反。","options":["intentional","unintentional","deliberate","planned"],"sentence":"The fire was completely ______, caused by a dropped cigarette that the homeowner didn't realize had ignited. The investigation confirmed there was no evidence of intentional arson or deliberate negligence.","translation":"這場火災完全是偶然的，由屋主沒有意識到已經點燃的掉落香菸引起的。調查證實沒有故意放火或故意過失的證據。","word":"accidental"}},"acclaim":{"createdAt":1781360906190,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acclaim 意思是讚揚或公開的稱譽，指公眾對某人成就的認可和歡迎。","options":["criticism","acclaim","rejection","complaint"],"sentence":"The actor received ______ from critics and audiences for his powerful performance. Newspapers praised his outstanding talent and dedication.","translation":"該演員因其強大的表演而獲得了評論家和觀眾的讚揚。報紙讚揚了他傑出的才華和奉獻精神。","word":"acclaim"}},"accommodate":{"createdAt":1781869467053,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accommodate 在此表示「容納、提供住宿」，指飯店有能力接待和安排大量客人的食宿。","options":["reject","house","ignore","charge"],"sentence":"The hotel can ______ up to 500 guests during the peak season. The staff has prepared extra rooms, meals, and facilities to ensure everyone is comfortable and properly hosted.","translation":"這家飯店在旺季時可以容納多達500位客人。員工已經準備了額外的房間、餐食和設施，以確保每個人都舒適且得到妥善接待。","word":"accommodate"}},"accommodation":{"createdAt":1781581336202,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accommodation指的是提供給人們居住或停留的住所或房間。","options":["transportation","accommodation","meals","entertainment"],"sentence":"The hotel provided comfortable ______ for all the conference attendees during their week-long stay. Rooms were spacious and located in a convenient downtown area.","translation":"酒店為所有會議與會者在一週長的逗留期間提供舒適的住所。房間寬敞，位於方便的市中心區域。","word":"accommodation"}},"accomplish":{"createdAt":1781360906183,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accomplish 意思是完成或達成，強調成功地實現了目標。","options":["attempt","accomplish","ignore","abandon"],"sentence":"She worked hard to ______ her goal of finishing the marathon. By crossing the finish line, she proved her determination.","translation":"她努力工作以完成馬拉松的目標。通過衝過終點線，她證明了她的決心。","word":"accomplish"}},"accomplishment":{"createdAt":1781360885487,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accomplishment指成功完成的事情，通常需要努力和技能，令人感到自豪。","options":["failure","accomplishment","setback","delay"],"sentence":"Graduating from university was a major ______ for her family. It represented years of hard work and dedication to education.","translation":"從大學畢業是她家族的重大成就。這代表了多年來對教育的努力和奉獻。","word":"accomplishment"}},"according":{"createdAt":1781849622416,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"根據是介詞，用於表示基於某項規則、聲明或來源，引入信息的根據或依據。","options":["Despite","According","Contrary","Opposed"],"sentence":"______ to the new company policy, all employees must complete training by next month. The human resources department issued this requirement in writing last week.","translation":"根據新的公司政策，所有員工必須在下個月前完成培訓。人力資源部上週以書面形式發出了這項要求。","word":"according"}},"accordingly":{"createdAt":1781581336209,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accordingly是副詞，表示根據特定的情況或條件而採取相應的行動。","options":["hastily","accordingly","reluctantly","abruptly"],"sentence":"The weather forecast predicted heavy rain for tomorrow morning, so we adjusted our plans ______. We decided to move the outdoor picnic to the following weekend.","translation":"天氣預報預測明天上午會下大雨，所以我們相應地調整了計劃。我們決定將戶外野餐改到下週末。","word":"accordingly"}},"accountable":{"createdAt":1781360885486,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accountable表示必須對自己的行為或決定承擔責任，並可以被要求解釋或說明。","options":["irresponsible","accountable","unaware","innocent"],"sentence":"The manager is ______ for all the mistakes made by his team members. He must explain to the director why the project failed.","translation":"經理對他的團隊成員所犯的所有錯誤負責。他必須向主管解釋該項目為什麼失敗。","word":"accountable"}},"accountant":{"createdAt":1781360885497,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accountant是指專門從事會計工作的專業人士，負責管理和審計財務記錄。","options":["lawyer","accountant","engineer","designer"],"sentence":"The company hired an experienced ______ to manage their financial records and taxes. She will prepare financial statements and ensure all accounts are balanced correctly.","translation":"公司聘請了一位經驗豐富的會計師來管理他們的財務記錄和稅務。她將準備財務報表並確保所有帳戶平衡正確。","word":"accountant"}},"accounting":{"createdAt":1781424157175,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"accounting 是一門學科和專業領域，涉及記錄和管理財務交易。","options":["marketing","law","accounting","engineering"],"sentence":"Maria studied ______ in university to prepare for a career managing financial records and budgets. Her courses included auditing, tax preparation, and financial statement analysis.","translation":"瑪麗亞在大學學習會計，為從事財務記錄和預算管理的職業做準備。她的課程包括審計、稅務準備和財務報表分析。","word":"accounting"}},"accumulate":{"createdAt":1781840667146,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"accumulate意思是逐漸聚集或堆積，表示數量或量度隨時間增加。","options":["disappear","scatter","accumulate","settle"],"sentence":"Over the years, dust and dirt began to ______ in the attic. By the time they cleaned it out, there were piles of forgotten items stacked everywhere.","translation":"多年來，灰塵和污垢開始在閣樓堆積。到他們清理時，到處都是堆積的遺忘物品。","word":"accumulate"}},"accurate":{"createdAt":1781360885491,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accurate指信息、測量或預測非常準確，沒有或很少有誤差。","options":["vague","accurate","misleading","approximate"],"sentence":"The weather forecast was ______ and predicted the storm within an hour. The meteorologists had correctly identified the exact time and location of the rainfall.","translation":"天氣預報是準確的，並在一小時內預測了風暴。氣象學家準確地確定了降雨的確切時間和地點。","word":"accurate"}},"accusation":{"createdAt":1781360885493,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accusation指指控某人犯罪或做錯事，通常需要有證據來支持。","options":["praise","accusation","compliment","support"],"sentence":"The ______ against the politician was made by several witnesses who claimed to have evidence. However, the charges were later proven false.","translation":"對政治家的控訴是由幾位聲稱擁有證據的證人提出的。但是，這些指控後來被證明是虛假的。","word":"accusation"}},"accuse":{"createdAt":1781337343696,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"accuse意為指控或控告某人犯了某種過錯或罪行。","options":["praise","accuse","invite","assist"],"sentence":"The detective decided to ______ the suspect of stealing the priceless painting from the museum. However, security footage later proved the suspect's innocence.","translation":"偵探決定指控嫌疑人從博物館竊取了無價的畫作。然而，監控錄影後來證明了嫌疑人的清白。","word":"accuse"}},"ache":{"createdAt":1781452425259,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"ache表示疼痛或酸痛，是一種持續性的身體不適感。","options":["strengthen","improve","hurt","relax"],"sentence":"Her back began to ______ after sitting at her desk for eight hours straight. By evening, she could barely move without experiencing sharp pain.","translation":"連續坐了八小時的辦公桌後，她的背開始疼痛。到晚上，她稍微動一下都會感到劇烈疼痛。","word":"ache"}},"achieve":{"createdAt":1781672973707,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"achieve表示「完成；達成」，指通過努力最終實現目標或願望。","options":["abandon","achieve","avoid","accuse"],"sentence":"After years of hard work and dedication, she finally managed to ______ her dream of becoming a doctor. The medical license hanging on her wall was proof of her success.","translation":"經過多年的辛苦工作和奉獻，她終於設法完成了成為醫生的夢想。掛在她牆上的醫學執照是她成功的證明。","word":"achieve"}},"acid":{"createdAt":1781849511875,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"酸是一種化學物質，具有腐蝕性，pH值低於7，能夠溶解某些物質。","options":["base","acid","salt","alkali"],"sentence":"The chemistry teacher warned students to handle the ______ carefully because it could burn through metal and skin. We all wore protective gloves and goggles when working with this corrosive substance in the lab.","translation":"化學老師警告學生要小心處理酸，因為它可能會腐蝕金屬和皮膚。我們在實驗室處理這種腐蝕性物質時都穿著保護手套和護目鏡。","word":"acid"}},"acidity":{"createdAt":1781417610416,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"acidity是指物質所含的酸性或酸度，在飲食中特別指酸味的強度。","options":["sweetness","texture","acidity","aroma"],"sentence":"The ______ of the vinegar made it unsuitable for use in the delicate recipe. The chef needed to dilute it significantly because the sourness would overpower all other flavors.","translation":"醋的酸性使其不適合用於這個精緻的食譜。廚師需要大量稀釋它，因為這種酸味會蓋過所有其他的味道。","word":"acidity"}},"acknowledge":{"createdAt":1781693304923,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acknowledge 表示承認或感謝他人的貢獻，與忽視或輕視相反。","options":["ignore","acknowledge","overlook","dismiss"],"sentence":"The author failed to ______ the contributions of her research team in the book's introduction. This oversight angered the colleagues who had spent months assisting her.","translation":"作者在書籍序言中未能承認她的研究團隊的貢獻。這個疏忽激怒了那些花了數個月協助她的同事。","word":"acknowledge"}},"acknowledgement":{"createdAt":1781860901467,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acknowledgement表示承認或感謝，常指對他人貢獻的正式認可和表達感謝","options":["introduction","acknowledgement","conclusion","preface"],"sentence":"The author included an ______ in her book thanking all the people who helped her. She named her family, colleagues, and mentors who supported her throughout the writing process.","translation":"作者在她的書中包含了一份致謝，感謝所有幫助她的人。她列舉了在整個寫作過程中支持她的家人、同事和導師。","word":"acknowledgement"}},"acknowledgment":{"createdAt":1781449095511,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acknowledgment意為承認或感謝，用來表示對某人的貢獻或幫助的認可。","options":["criticism","acknowledgment","complaint","disagreement"],"sentence":"In the book's introduction, the author gave special ______ to her mentor. She expressed deep gratitude for all the guidance and support he had provided.","translation":"在書的序言中，作者特別感謝了她的導師。她表達了對他所提供的所有指導和支持的深深感激。","word":"acknowledgment"}},"acne":{"createdAt":1781395428239,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acne 是一種皮膚疾病，特徵是出現粉刺、丘疹和黑頭，通常在青春期出現。","options":["eczema","acne","psoriasis","melanoma"],"sentence":"Many teenagers struggle with ______ during puberty due to hormonal changes. This skin condition causes inflamed pimples and blemishes primarily on the face and chest.","translation":"許多青少年在青春期因激素變化而與粉刺作鬥爭。這種皮膚狀況主要在臉部和胸部引起發炎的粉刺和瑕疵。","word":"acne"}},"acoustic":{"createdAt":1781738105695,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acoustic 指的是與聲音相關的，或指樂器能夠不通過電子放大而產生自然聲音。","options":["electric","acoustic","synthesized","digital"],"sentence":"The musician preferred playing an ______ guitar rather than an electric one for his intimate concert. The natural sound of the wooden instrument resonated beautifully in the small venue.","translation":"這位音樂家更喜歡在親密音樂會上演奏原聲吉他而不是電吉他。這件木製樂器的自然聲音在小場地中美妙地迴蕩。","word":"acoustic"}},"acquaint":{"createdAt":1781484539652,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acquaint 的意思是使某人變得熟悉或了解某事物，常用於 acquaint oneself with（使自己熟悉）的結構。","options":["distance","acquaint","separate","isolate"],"sentence":"The new employee needs time to ______ herself with the company's policies and procedures. By next month, she should be completely familiar with all the systems.","translation":"新員工需要時間使自己熟悉公司的政策和程序。到下個月，她應該會完全熟悉所有的系統。","word":"acquaint"}},"acquaintance":{"createdAt":1781484415232,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acquaintance是指認識但不是親密朋友的人，表示較為淡薄的人際關係。","options":["stranger","acquaintance","relative","enemy"],"sentence":"She ran into an old ______ at the grocery store and they chatted for a few minutes. They weren't close friends, just people who had met a couple of times before.","translation":"她在雜貨店遇到了一位老相識，他們聊了幾分鐘。他們不是親密的朋友，只是之前見過幾次面的人。","word":"acquaintance"}},"acquainted":{"createdAt":1781360906184,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acquainted 意思是相識的或熟悉的，表示對某人或某事有基本的了解。","options":["separated","acquainted","confused","estranged"],"sentence":"Before the project started, the team members became ______ with each other. They attended a meeting where they introduced themselves and shared their backgrounds.","translation":"在項目開始前，團隊成員彼此熟悉了。他們參加了一次會議，在會議上相互介紹並分享了他們的背景。","word":"acquainted"}},"acquire":{"createdAt":1781672973746,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acquire是動詞，表示「取得；獲得；學會」，指通過購買、學習或其他方式獲得某物。","options":["lose","acquire","destroy","donate"],"sentence":"Over the past five years, she has ______ a comprehensive collection of rare art pieces from around the world. Her museum now houses one of the most valuable private collections in the country.","translation":"在過去五年中，她從世界各地獲得了一套全面的罕見藝術品收藏。她的博物館現在擁有該國最有價值的私人收藏品之一。","word":"acquire"}},"acquisition":{"createdAt":1781434900600,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acquisition指獲得或購買某物，特別是在正式或官方的背景下。","options":["loss","acquisition","removal","donation"],"sentence":"The museum's recent ______ of a rare painting from the Renaissance period attracted thousands of visitors. The purchase significantly enhanced the collection's historical value.","translation":"博物館最近獲得了一幅罕見的文藝復興時期繪畫，吸引了數千名遊客。這次購買大大提高了藏品的歷史價值。","word":"acquisition"}},"acre":{"createdAt":1781256547736,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Acre是一個面積測量單位，常用於測量土地面積，特別是在英美地區。","options":["meter","acre","pound","minute"],"sentence":"The farmer owns 50 ______ of fertile land in the countryside. This vast property provides enough space for growing crops, raising cattle, and maintaining various farm buildings.","translation":"這位農民在鄉間擁有50英畝的肥沃土地。這片廣大的地產提供了足夠的空間來種植作物、飼養牲畜和維護各種農舍。","word":"acre"}},"active":{"createdAt":1781965320890,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"active 表示積極參與和忙於某項活動，與被動或不參與的狀態相反。","options":["passive","retired","active","isolated"],"sentence":"She is very ______ in her community, volunteering at the local food bank every weekend. Her constant involvement has earned her several awards from the city.","translation":"她在社區中非常積極，每個週末都在當地食物銀行做志願服務。她持續的參與為她贏得了城市的幾個獎項。","word":"active"}},"actively":{"createdAt":1781672973739,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"actively是副詞，表示「積極地」，修飾動詞表示以主動和積極的方式進行某項活動。","options":["passively","actively","reluctantly","occasionally"],"sentence":"She ______ participated in community service projects throughout the year. Her volunteer hours exceeded everyone else's because of her constant involvement and dedication.","translation":"她全年積極參與社區服務項目。由於她的持續參與和奉獻，她的志願服務時數超過了其他所有人。","word":"actively"}},"activist":{"createdAt":1781395428237,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"activist 指積極推動社會或政治變革的人，強調主動採取行動。","options":["observer","activist","politician","journalist"],"sentence":"Sarah is a passionate environmental ______ who organizes protests against pollution. She dedicates her time to taking direct action and promoting change in her community.","translation":"莎拉是一位熱情的環境積極分子，她組織抗議污染的遊行活動。她致力於採取直接行動並推動社區的改變。","word":"activist"}},"actual":{"createdAt":1781360906183,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"actual 意思是實際的或真實的，指的是真正發生或存在的情況。","options":["projected","actual","assumed","theoretical"],"sentence":"The ______ cost of the project was higher than the estimate. The accountant showed us the real expenses in the final report.","translation":"該項目的實際成本高於估計。會計師在最終報告中向我們展示了真實費用。","word":"actual"}},"acute":{"createdAt":1781429945502,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"acute 表示急性的或劇烈的，通常用來描述突然發生且症狀嚴重的疾病。","options":["chronic","acute","mild","imaginary"],"sentence":"The patient suffered from an ______ case of pneumonia that required immediate hospitalization. The severe infection developed suddenly and needed urgent medical treatment within days.","translation":"這位患者患有急性肺炎，需要立即住院治療。嚴重的感染突然發展，需要在數天內進行緊急醫療。","word":"acute"}},"adapt":{"createdAt":1781360885490,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"adapt指改變或調整某物以適應新的條件或用途，通常涉及修改而非完全改變。","options":["ignored","adapted","rejected","abandoned"],"sentence":"The novel was ______ into a successful film that won several awards. The screenplay captured the essence of the original story while making changes for cinema.","translation":"這部小說被改編成了一部獲得多個獎項的成功電影。劇本抓住了原始故事的精髓，同時為電影做出了改變。","word":"adapt"}},"addict":{"createdAt":1781484415234,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"addict是指對某事物成癮或依賴的人，無法控制地沉迷其中。","options":["trainer","teacher","addict","player"],"sentence":"He became a video game ______ and spent twelve hours every day playing online. His family grew worried about his excessive gaming and neglect of school and social life.","translation":"他成為了一個電玩遊戲成癮者，每天花費十二小時在線上遊戲。他的家人對他過度遊戲以及忽視學業和社交生活感到擔心。","word":"addict"}},"addicted":{"createdAt":1781664082511,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"addicted 表示對某事物有癮，沉迷於某事物，通常帶有負面含義。","options":["immune","addicted","resistant","opposed"],"sentence":"Many teenagers are ______ to social media and spend hours scrolling through their phones. Their parents have noticed they cannot go a single day without checking their accounts.","translation":"許多青少年對社交媒體上癮，花數小時滾動瀏覽手機。他們的父母注意到他們一天都無法不檢查自己的帳戶。","word":"addicted"}},"addition":{"createdAt":1781961517452,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"addition 在短語 \"in addition to\" 中表示「除…之外還有」，表示增加或補充。","options":["contrast","addition","relation","comparison"],"sentence":"In ______ to the main courses, the restaurant offered several delicious desserts on the menu. These sweet treats were available as optional extras that customers could order separately.","translation":"除了主菜外，餐廳菜單上還提供了幾種美味的甜點。這些甜點可以作為顧客可以單獨訂購的可選附加項。","word":"addition"}},"additional":{"createdAt":1781598671077,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"additional 作形容詞表示附加的或額外的，指除了原有的以外還有的東西","options":["main","additional","basic","standard"],"sentence":"The restaurant offered ______ toppings at no extra charge during the promotion. Customers could choose pizza, pasta, or salad as complimentary accompaniments to their main courses.","translation":"該餐廳在促銷期間免費提供額外的配菜。客戶可以選擇披薩、義大利麵或沙拉作為主菜的免費配菜。","word":"additional"}},"additionally":{"createdAt":1782022372248,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"additionally 意為「此外、另外」，用於在陳述事實後添加額外的相關信息或論點。","options":["unfortunately","additionally","previously","rarely"],"sentence":"The restaurant offers excellent food at reasonable prices, and ______, the service staff are incredibly friendly and attentive. These extra positive qualities make it the most popular dining establishment in town.","translation":"這家餐廳提供優質的食物和合理的價格，此外，服務員非常友善和周到。這些額外的優點使其成為城鎮中最受歡迎的用餐場所。","word":"additionally"}},"adjust":{"createdAt":1781693538702,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"adjust 表示調整、改變或修改某物使其處於更好的狀態或位置。","options":["break","adjust","ignore","destroy"],"sentence":"I need to ______ the microscope to see the cells more clearly. After turning the focus knob slightly, the image became perfectly sharp.","translation":"我需要調整顯微鏡以更清楚地看到細胞。轉動對焦旋鈕後，影像變得完全清晰。","word":"adjust"}},"adjustment":{"createdAt":1781360885490,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"adjustment指為了適應新環境或情況而進行的改變或調整，通常需要一段時間。","options":["rejection","adjustment","resistance","refusal"],"sentence":"After moving to a new country, she needed time for ______ to the different culture and lifestyle. Within six months, she had made significant changes to her daily routines.","translation":"搬到新國家後，她需要時間來適應不同的文化和生活方式。在六個月內，她對日常生活做出了重大改變。","word":"adjustment"}},"administer":{"createdAt":1781360885497,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"administer指提供或施放藥物、測試或管理某項服務，通常由授權人員進行。","options":["refuse","administer","deny","withhold"],"sentence":"The nurse will ______ the vaccine to all the children at the health center this morning. The medical staff has prepared everything needed for the immunization program.","translation":"護士今早將在衛生中心向所有兒童施打疫苗。醫療人員已為免疫接種計劃準備好了一切所需物品。","word":"administer"}},"administration":{"createdAt":1781437435166,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"administration 指經營、管理或行政機關，特別是組織的管理部門或經營機構。","options":["decoration","administration","conclusion","celebration"],"sentence":"The ______ of the hospital hired new staff to improve patient care services. The management team implemented new policies across all departments.","translation":"醫院的行政管理部門聘請了新員工以改進患者護理服務。管理團隊在所有部門實施了新政策。","word":"administration"}},"administrative":{"createdAt":1781360885488,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"administrative與管理和組織相關，特別是涉及辦公室工作和官方程序的工作。","options":["creative","administrative","technical","marketing"],"sentence":"The ______ staff handles all the paperwork and scheduling for the company. They manage office operations, files, and coordinate meetings.","translation":"行政人員處理公司的所有文書工作和日程安排。他們管理辦公室運營、文件並協調會議。","word":"administrative"}},"admiration":{"createdAt":1781360906186,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"admiration 意思是欽佩或讚賞，表示對某人的成就或品質的高度評價。","options":["criticism","admiration","jealousy","indifference"],"sentence":"The young athlete earned the ______ of millions of fans worldwide. People respected his dedication and outstanding performance in the sport.","translation":"這位年輕運動員贏得了全球數百萬粉絲的欽佩。人們尊敬他在運動中的奉獻精神和傑出表現。","word":"admiration"}},"admire":{"createdAt":1781360885492,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"admire指對某人的品質、成就或行為表達敬佩和讚美之情。","options":["despise","admire","ignore","criticize"],"sentence":"I ______ my grandmother for her courage and wisdom throughout her life. She faced many challenges with grace and dignity.","translation":"我欽佩我祖母在整個人生中的勇氣和智慧。她以優雅和尊嚴面對了許多挑戰。","word":"admire"}},"admission":{"createdAt":1781484539654,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"admission 在這裡表示被接納或錄取進入某個機構或組織，與被拒絕或被排除的意思完全相反。","options":["rejection","dismissal","admission","exclusion"],"sentence":"His ______ to Harvard University was a dream come true after years of hard work. The acceptance letter confirmed that he had been approved as a new student.","translation":"經過多年的努力，他被哈佛大學錄取是夢想成真。錄取通知書確認了他被批准為新生。","word":"admission"}},"admit":{"createdAt":1781598671162,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"admit 作動詞表示允許入場或承認，在這裡指允許某人進入學校或組織","options":["reject","admit","defer","waitlist"],"sentence":"The university will ______ only 200 students from the 5,000 applications received this year. The acceptance rate is expected to be highly competitive.","translation":"大學將在今年收到的5,000份申請中只錄取200名學生。錄取率預計將非常具競爭力。","word":"admit"}},"admonition":{"createdAt":1781582278976,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"admonition是指針對某人的不當行為而進行的嚴肅警告或責備，通常帶有威脅性的後果。","options":["admonition","celebration","promotion","suggestion"],"sentence":"The coach's harsh ______ about poor sportsmanship echoed through the locker room after the game. He sternly told the players they would face serious consequences if they continued behaving disrespectfully toward opponents.","translation":"教練在比賽後在更衣室裡發出了關於運動精神不佳的嚴厲告誡。他嚴肅地告訴球員們，如果他們繼續對對手表現不尊重，將面臨嚴重後果。","word":"admonition"}},"adopt":{"createdAt":1781704395606,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"adopt作為動詞表示「採取」或「採納」，指官方或正式地接受並實施某項計畫或政策","options":["reject","threaten","adopt","tension"],"sentence":"The government decided to ______ a new environmental policy to reduce carbon emissions. Scientists provided evidence showing this strategy would be most effective at lowering pollution levels.","translation":"政府決定採取新的環保政策來減少碳排放。科學家提供證據表明這項策略在降低污染水準方面最為有效。","word":"adopt"}},"adoption":{"createdAt":1781360906185,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"adoption 意思是採用或接納，表示接受並開始使用或實施某事。","options":["rejection","adoption","avoidance","criticism"],"sentence":"The ______ of new technology improved the company's efficiency. The management team decided to implement the latest software system.","translation":"新技術的採用提高了公司的效率。管理團隊決定實施最新的軟體系統。","word":"adoption"}},"adore":{"createdAt":1781360906186,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"adore 意思是熱愛或崇拜，表示非常喜歡和珍視某人或某物。","options":["avoid","adore","ignore","hate"],"sentence":"The children absolutely ______ the theme park and visit it every summer. They cannot wait to ride the roller coasters and enjoy the attractions.","translation":"孩子們非常熱愛主題公園，每年夏天都去參觀。他們迫不及待地想乘坐過山車並享受各種景點。","word":"adore"}},"advantage":{"createdAt":1781360885493,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"advantage指比他人更有利的條件或優勢，有助於達成目標。","options":["disadvantage","advantage","liability","burden"],"sentence":"Speaking multiple languages gives her a significant ______ in her career. She can communicate with clients from different countries and access more job opportunities.","translation":"說多種語言在她的職業生涯中給了她顯著的優勢。她可以與來自不同國家的客戶溝通，並獲得更多工作機會。","word":"advantage"}},"adverse":{"createdAt":1781256485491,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"adverse表示不利的、有害的或相反的影響","options":["positive","adverse","neutral","minor"],"sentence":"The storm had ______ effects on the harvest. Farmers lost most of their crops due to the heavy rain and strong winds.","translation":"這場暴風雨對收穫產生了不利影響。由於大雨和強風，農民損失了大部分莊稼。","word":"adverse"}},"advertisement":{"createdAt":1781836375368,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"advertisement是廣告，指用來宣傳商品、服務或想法的公開宣傳。","options":["campaign","advertisement","announcement","broadcast"],"sentence":"The company spent millions on a television ______ to promote their new product. The commercial aired during prime time to reach the largest audience.","translation":"公司花費數百萬在電視廣告上推廣他們的新產品。該商業廣告在黃金時間播放以吸引最多觀眾。","word":"advertisement"}},"adviser":{"createdAt":1781360906187,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"adviser 意思是顧問，指提供專業意見和指導的人。","options":["student","adviser","customer","employee"],"sentence":"The financial ______ helped the family plan their investments wisely. His expert recommendations saved them thousands of dollars.","translation":"財務顧問幫助家庭明智地規劃他們的投資。他的專家建議為他們節省了數千美元。","word":"adviser"}},"advisory":{"createdAt":1781360906185,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"advisory 意思是給予建議的或諮詢性的，用來描述提供指導和意見的角色。","options":["mandatory","advisory","executive","administrative"],"sentence":"The company hired an ______ board to provide guidance on business strategy. These experts met monthly to offer recommendations and feedback.","translation":"公司聘請了一個諮詢委員會來提供商業策略指導。這些專家每月開會提供建議和反饋。","word":"advisory"}},"advocate":{"createdAt":1781581336189,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"advocate是指主張或擁護某項事業的人，表示積極的推動者。","options":["politician","advocate","scientist","journalist"],"sentence":"As a passionate ______ for climate action, she spent years promoting renewable energy. Her tireless efforts convinced thousands of people to support environmental policies.","translation":"作為氣候行動的熱情倡導者，她花了多年時間推廣可再生能源。她不懈的努力說服了數千人支持環保政策。","word":"advocate"}},"aerial":{"createdAt":1781580511761,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"aerial 是指來自空中或與飛行相關的事物，常用於形容航空攝影","options":["underground","surface","aerial","microscopic"],"sentence":"The ______ photography captured stunning views of the entire city from above. The drone flying high in the sky provided perspectives impossible to get from the ground.","translation":"航空攝影從上方捕捉了整個城市的壯麗景色。在高空飛行的無人機提供了從地面無法獲得的視角。","word":"aerial"}},"aesthetic":{"createdAt":1781362281666,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aesthetic與美感、藝術價值相關，強調事物的視覺美感和藝術性。","options":["practical","aesthetic","structural","functional"],"sentence":"The ______ design of the building combines beauty with functionality. The architect paid careful attention to visual appeal and artistic elements.","translation":"這棟建築的美感設計結合了美感和功能性。建築師仔細注意視覺吸引力和藝術元素。","word":"aesthetic"}},"affair":{"createdAt":1781256485493,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"affair指的是重要的或引起公眾注意的事件或事情","options":["hobby","affair","game","sport"],"sentence":"The scandal became a major international ______ when the government's corruption was exposed. News outlets worldwide reported on the shocking revelations for months.","translation":"當政府的腐敗行為被揭露時，這個醜聞成為了一樁重大的國際事件。世界各地的新聞媒體數月來都在報導這些令人震驚的揭露。","word":"affair"}},"affected":{"createdAt":1781775363749,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"affected 表示受到影響或罹患，用來描述那些遭受地震災害的地區和居民。","options":["protected","affected","warned","prepared"],"sentence":"The communities ______ by the earthquake received emergency aid from the government. Thousands of residents had lost their homes and needed immediate assistance.","translation":"受到地震______的社區獲得了政府的緊急援助。數千名居民失去了家園，需要立即援助。","word":"affected"}},"affection":{"createdAt":1781693270387,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"affection指「感情、親情、喜愛」，通常用來表達對他人溫暖、關心和愛護的感受。","options":["indifference","hostility","affection","resentment"],"sentence":"She showed deep ______ toward her elderly parents by visiting them every weekend. Her consistent care and warm hugs demonstrated how much she loved them.","translation":"她通過每週末拜訪年邁的父母來表達對他們的深厚感情。她一致的照顧和溫暖的擁抱表明了她有多愛他們。","word":"affection"}},"affiliate":{"createdAt":1781360906192,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"affiliate 意思是附屬機構或分支機構，指與更大組織相關聯的較小業務單位。","options":["competitor","affiliate","subsidiary","partner"],"sentence":"The small bookstore is an ______ of the larger national chain. It operates under the same brand name and follows the company's policies.","translation":"這家小書店是更大的全國連鎖店的分支機構。它在相同的品牌名稱下運營並遵循公司的政策。","word":"affiliate"}},"affirm":{"createdAt":1781746685502,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"affirm指的是證實、斷言、肯定某事為真，表示以有力的方式確認某個事實或觀點。","options":["affirm","cooperate","entertain","terminate"],"sentence":"The witness came to court to ______ the defendant's guilt. His testimony provided clear evidence that matched the facts presented by the prosecution.","translation":"證人來法庭證實被告的有罪。他的證詞提供了與檢察機關提出的事實相符的明確證據。","word":"affirm"}},"agency":{"createdAt":1781429945501,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"agency 表示代理機構或仲介，特別是指幫助人們尋找服務或工作的組織。","options":["rival","agency","competition","restaurant"],"sentence":"My sister found her dream job through an employment ______ that specializes in matching candidates with companies. The recruiter spent weeks reviewing her skills before connecting her with the perfect position.","translation":"我的姐姐通過一家專門將求職者與公司配對的人力資源代理機構找到了她夢想中的工作。招聘人員花了數周時間審查她的技能，然後將她與完美的職位聯繫在一起。","word":"agency"}},"agenda":{"createdAt":1781437013478,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"agenda 指會議的議事日程，是會議中將要討論的各項事項的清單。","options":["budget","agenda","resolution","minutes"],"sentence":"The chairman reviewed the ______ before the board meeting to ensure all important topics would be discussed. The list included quarterly financial reports, new product launches, and strategic planning items.","translation":"主席在董事會會議前審查了議程，以確保所有重要議題都將被討論。該清單包括季度財務報告、新產品發布和戰略規劃項目。","word":"agenda"}},"agent":{"createdAt":1781360906189,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"agent 意思是代理人或經紀人，指代表他人進行交易或談判的人。","options":["architect","agent","tenant","inspector"],"sentence":"The real estate ______ showed us several houses in the neighborhood. She had years of experience helping buyers find their perfect homes.","translation":"房地產經紀人向我們展示了附近的幾所房屋。她有多年幫助買家找到完美家園的經驗。","word":"agent"}},"aggression":{"createdAt":1781360885489,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aggression指主動的敵對行為或攻擊，通常帶有暴力或對抗的意圖。","options":["cooperation","aggression","friendship","alliance"],"sentence":"The country's ______ toward its neighbor led to military conflict. Troops were sent across the border without warning or declaration of war.","translation":"該國對鄰國的侵略導致了軍事衝突。部隊未經警告或宣戰就被派過邊境。","word":"aggression"}},"aggressive":{"createdAt":1781613113024,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"aggressive 形容好鬥、積極進攻或充滿攻擊性的","options":["passive","defensive","aggressive","cautious"],"sentence":"The team's ______ playing style intimidated their opponents from the start. They attacked relentlessly and never backed down.","translation":"球隊從一開始就採取了好鬥的比賽風格嚇唬對手。他們無情地進攻，從不退縮。","word":"aggressive"}},"agony":{"createdAt":1781613179429,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"agony 意為極度痛苦，可以指肉體痛楚或精神上的極度折磨。","options":["comfort","joy","suffering","pleasure"],"sentence":"The patient endured great ______ during the recovery period, experiencing severe pain and emotional distress. Pain management therapy and counseling helped him gradually overcome this difficult phase.","translation":"患者在恢復期間經歷了極大的痛苦，遭受了嚴重的身體和精神痛楚。疼痛管理療法和諮詢幫助他逐漸克服了這個困難階段。","word":"agony"}},"agreeable":{"createdAt":1781336858148,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"agreeable 形容某事令人愉悅、宜人或令人滿意，通常指天氣、情況或他人的舉止。","options":["terrible","harsh","agreeable","stormy"],"sentence":"The weather was ______ and perfect for the outdoor wedding ceremony. Everyone enjoyed the mild temperature and clear blue sky throughout the entire event.","translation":"天氣令人愉悅且完美適合戶外婚禮儀式。在整個活動中，每個人都享受了溫和的溫度和晴朗的藍天。","word":"agreeable"}},"agreement":{"createdAt":1781360906196,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"agreement 意思是同意或協議，表示兩個或更多當事人對某事達成共識。","options":["disagreement","agreement","conflict","dispute"],"sentence":"After hours of negotiation, both parties reached an ______ on the contract terms. They signed the document, confirming their mutual consent.","translation":"經過數小時的談判後，雙方在合同條款上達成了一致。他們簽署了文件，確認了相互同意。","word":"agreement"}},"agricultural":{"createdAt":1781613179429,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"agricultural 意為農業的，指與農業生產、耕種和相關活動相關的事物。","options":["industrial","manufacturing","farming","technological"],"sentence":"The ______ sector is vital to the country's economy, producing crops and livestock for domestic consumption. The government has invested heavily in modernizing farming techniques and equipment.","translation":"農業部門對國家經濟至關重要，為國內消費生產農作物和牲畜。政府投入巨資來現代化農業技術和設備。","word":"agricultural"}},"agriculture":{"createdAt":1781360885496,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"agriculture是指農業及相關的耕作和種植活動，是許多國家的主要經濟產業。","options":["manufacturing","agriculture","technology","tourism"],"sentence":"The country's economy heavily depends on ______ as most of the population works in farming. They grow crops like rice, wheat, and corn for both domestic use and export.","translation":"該國經濟主要依靠農業，因為大部分人口從事農業工作。他們種植水稻、小麥和玉米供國內使用和出口。","word":"agriculture"}},"aground":{"createdAt":1781478568767,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aground 表示船隻被困在淺灘或岩石上，無法航行。","options":["smoothly","aground","safely","swiftly"],"sentence":"The cargo ship ran ______ on the shallow rocks near the coastline. It took several days for rescue vessels to refloat it.","translation":"貨輪在海岸附近的淺灘岩石上擱淺。花了幾天時間才讓救援船隻將其重新浮起。","word":"aground"}},"aim":{"createdAt":1781531595652,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aim 作動詞表示瞄準、對準某目標，特別是在射擊時的準備動作。","options":["guess","aim","shoot","throw"],"sentence":"The archer carefully raised his bow to ______ at the distant target. After taking a deep breath, he released the arrow with perfect precision and hit the bullseye.","translation":"弓箭手小心地抬起弓對準遠處的靶子。深吸一口氣後，他以完美的精準度放出箭，擊中了靶心。","word":"aim"}},"air_conditioned":{"createdAt":1781360906192,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"air-conditioned 意思是安裝了空調設備的，指通過人工製冷系統控制室內溫度。","options":["heated","air-conditioned","ventilated","decorated"],"sentence":"The office building is fully ______, making it comfortable during hot summers. Employees can work in a cool environment regardless of the weather outside.","translation":"辦公樓配有完整的空調設備，在炎熱的夏天使其舒適。無論外面天氣如何，員工都可以在涼爽的環境中工作。","word":"air-conditioned"}},"aircraft":{"createdAt":1781360885498,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aircraft是指所有能夠飛行的運輸工具，包括飛機、直升機等，用於運輸人員和貨物。","options":["boat","aircraft","train","car"],"sentence":"The ______ took off from the runway at exactly 8 AM and headed toward its destination. Hundreds of passengers were on board the commercial flight.","translation":"飛機在上午8點整從跑道起飛，前往目的地。商業航班上有數百名乘客。","word":"aircraft"}},"aisle":{"createdAt":1781837419090,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Aisle指的是飛機、電影院或教堂等場所中座位之間的走道。","options":["cabin","aisle","cockpit","wing"],"sentence":"The flight attendant walked down the ______ of the airplane to distribute beverages and snacks. Passengers could easily access this narrow pathway between the rows of seats.","translation":"空服員沿著飛機的走道走動，分發飲料和零食。乘客可以輕鬆進入這條座位行之間的狹窄通路。","word":"aisle"}},"alcohol":{"createdAt":1781581336189,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"alcohol指的是酒精飲料中的成分，會對身體健康造成影響。","options":["beverage","alcohol","medicine","liquid"],"sentence":"The doctor warned that consuming too much ______ can damage your liver. He specifically mentioned beer, wine, and spirits as common examples.","translation":"醫生警告說過量飲用酒精會傷害你的肝臟。他特別提到啤酒、葡萄酒和烈酒是常見的例子。","word":"alcohol"}},"alcoholic":{"createdAt":1781613113029,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"alcoholic 形容含酒精的或與酒精相關的","options":["soft","carbonated","alcoholic","herbal"],"sentence":"The ______ beverages were kept in a separate section of the store away from children. The drinks contained significant amounts of ethanol.","translation":"含酒精飲料被放在商店的一個單獨區域，遠離兒童。這些飲料含有大量的乙醇。","word":"alcoholic"}},"alert":{"createdAt":1781395428238,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"alert 作為動詞表示提醒或警告某人注意潛在的危險或重要信息。","options":["ignore","alert","confuse","discourage"],"sentence":"The security system will ______ the guards immediately if any suspicious activity is detected. They must stay vigilant and ready to respond within seconds.","translation":"如果偵測到任何可疑活動，安全系統將立即警告警衛。他們必須保持警覺，準備在幾秒內做出反應。","word":"alert"}},"alien":{"createdAt":1781581336196,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"alien作為名詞指來自外國的人或外國人。","options":["resident","alien","citizen","worker"],"sentence":"The customs officer questioned the ______ about his reason for entering the country. His unusual accent and unfamiliar documents required additional verification.","translation":"海關官員詢問了這名外僑進入該國的原因。他不尋常的口音和陌生的文件需要額外驗證。","word":"alien"}},"alienate":{"createdAt":1781395428240,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"alienate 表示使某人感到被孤立、不被接納或與他人產生距離和敵對感。","options":["attract","alienate","motivate","reward"],"sentence":"The company's unpopular decision to raise prices will likely ______ many loyal customers. Those long-time supporters now feel unvalued and may switch to competitors.","translation":"公司提高價格的不受歡迎決定可能會使許多忠實客戶疏遠。那些長期支持者現在感到被低估，可能會轉向競爭對手。","word":"alienate"}},"alienated":{"createdAt":1781360885486,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"alienated表示被隔絕或與他人產生隔閡，導致關係破裂或感到被排斥。","options":["connected","alienated","devoted","attached"],"sentence":"After the argument, John felt ______ from his best friend. They didn't speak for months and grew distant from each other.","translation":"爭執後，約翰感到與他最好的朋友疏遠了。他們好幾個月沒有說話，彼此漸漸變得陌生。","word":"alienated"}},"aliens":{"createdAt":1782006620281,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aliens指的是外星人，特別是來自太空的生物，與第二句中「extraterrestrial invaders from outer space」（來自外太空的地外入侵者）相符。","options":["robots","aliens","soldiers","scientists"],"sentence":"In the science fiction movie, ______ from distant galaxies invaded Earth with advanced technology. The characters in the film had to work together to fight against these extraterrestrial invaders from outer space.","translation":"在這部科幻電影中，來自遠方星系的外星人以先進技術入侵地球。電影中的角色必須團結起來對抗這些來自外太空的地外入侵者。","word":"aliens"}},"align":{"createdAt":1781672973743,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"align是動詞，表示「使成一條直線；對準；校直」，指將事物排列成一直線或正確位置。","options":["damage","align","separate","bend"],"sentence":"The engineer carefully used a laser to ______ the two metal beams perfectly. Even a millimeter of misalignment could compromise the structural integrity of the entire building.","translation":"工程師小心地使用激光器完美地對齊兩根金屬梁。即使只是毫米級的偏差也可能危及整棟建築的結構完整性。","word":"align"}},"allege":{"createdAt":1781425093248,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"allege 表示未經證實地聲稱或指控某事，強調這些說法還未被證明為事實。","options":["prove","allege","demonstrate","verify"],"sentence":"The witness decided to ______ that the defendant had stolen the valuable painting. However, without any concrete evidence or documentation, the court could not confirm whether this claim was actually true.","translation":"證人決定聲稱被告偷了那幅名畫。然而，沒有任何具體證據或文件，法庭無法確認這項指控是否真實。","word":"allege"}},"allergic":{"createdAt":1781824968058,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"allergic 表示對某種物質有過敏反應，通常會導致身體不適或不良症狀。","options":["addicted","allergic","attracted","accustomed"],"sentence":"My brother is ______ to peanuts and must carry an EpiPen everywhere. He breaks out in hives whenever he accidentally consumes any peanut product.","translation":"我的哥哥對花生過敏，必須隨身攜帶腎上腺素自動注射器。每當他不小心吃到任何花生製品時，他就會起蕁麻疹。","word":"allergic"}},"allergy":{"createdAt":1781672973744,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"allergy是名詞，表示「過敏反應；過敏性」，指身體對某些物質的異常免疫反應。","options":["preference","allergy","talent","skill"],"sentence":"He developed a severe ______ to peanuts after a childhood accident involving anaphylactic shock. Now he must carry an EpiPen at all times and avoid all peanut products.","translation":"在童年時期發生過敏性休克事故後，他對花生產生了嚴重的過敏反應。現在他必須隨時攜帶腎上腺素自動注射器，並避免所有花生製品。","word":"allergy"}},"alley":{"createdAt":1781775363748,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"alley 是指小街或小巷，通常是指城市中狹窄的通道或胡同。","options":["hallway","highway","alley","avenue"],"sentence":"The detectives chased the suspect through a narrow ______ behind the old buildings. The passage was only wide enough for one person to walk through at a time.","translation":"偵探們在舊建築物後面的狹窄______追捕嫌疑人。這條通道寬度只能容納一個人同時通過。","word":"alley"}},"alliance":{"createdAt":1781256547735,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Alliance表示兩個或多個國家、組織或人之間的聯盟或合作關係，通常是為了達成共同目標。","options":["competition","alliance","dispute","separation"],"sentence":"The two countries formed a strong ______ to face their common enemies. This partnership allowed them to combine their military forces and resources.","translation":"兩個國家形成了一個強大的聯盟來面對他們的共同敵人。這種夥伴關係使他們能夠合併他們的軍事力量和資源。","word":"alliance"}},"allocate":{"createdAt":1781581336206,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"allocate指的是分配或撥出特定的資源、資金或物品。","options":["investigate","allocate","calculate","regulate"],"sentence":"The government decided to ______ additional funds to improve public transportation in rural areas. This budget increase was announced as part of their new development initiative.","translation":"政府決定撥出額外資金以改善農村地區的公共交通。這個預算增加是他們新發展計劃的一部分公開宣布的。","word":"allocate"}},"allow":{"createdAt":1781672973743,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"allow是動詞，表示「允許；聽任」，指給予他人做某事的許可或機會。","options":["forbid","allow","prevent","restrict"],"sentence":"The manager decided to ______ employees to work from home two days a week. This new policy was implemented to improve their work-life balance and productivity.","translation":"經理決定允許員工每週有兩天在家工作。這項新政策的實施是為了改善他們的工作生活平衡和生產力。","word":"allow"}},"ally":{"createdAt":1781360885494,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ally指在戰爭、政治或商業中與自己站在同一邊的國家或人，提供支持與合作。","options":["enemy","ally","rival","competitor"],"sentence":"During the war, France was Britain's most important ______ in the fight against the enemy. The two nations worked together and supported each other militarily.","translation":"戰爭期間，法國是英國在對抗敵人中最重要的盟友。兩個國家一起工作並在軍事上相互支持。","word":"ally"}},"almond":{"createdAt":1781531595649,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"almond 是一種扁桃樹的果實，具有獨特的堅果風味，常用於烘焙和甜點。","options":["walnut","almond","peanut","cashew"],"sentence":"She added crushed ______ to the dessert for a nutty flavor. The recipe specifically called for this tree nut that grows in warm Mediterranean climates.","translation":"她在甜點中加入了碎杏仁以增添堅果風味。食譜特別要求這種在溫暖的地中海氣候中生長的樹堅果。","word":"almond"}},"altar":{"createdAt":1781484539654,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"altar 是指教堂中的祭壇或聖壇，用於宗教儀式和崇拜活動，特別是婚禮和彌撒。","options":["altar","carpet","podium","stage"],"sentence":"The priest placed flowers on the ______ during the wedding ceremony. The bride and groom stood before this sacred platform to exchange their vows.","translation":"在婚禮中，神父把花放在聖壇上。新郎新娘站在這個神聖的平台前交換誓言。","word":"altar"}},"alter":{"createdAt":1781693304924,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"alter 表示對某物進行改變或調整，通常涉及修改細節而非完全重新製作。","options":["design","alter","create","ruin"],"sentence":"The tailor needed to ______ the wedding dress to fit the bride's measurements perfectly. She carefully adjusted the seams and hemline without changing the overall design.","translation":"裁縫師需要修改婚禮服裝以完美貼合新娘的尺寸。她仔細調整了接縫和褶邊，但沒有改變整體設計。","word":"alter"}},"alternate":{"createdAt":1781311922066,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"alternate 表示兩個或多個事物輪流出現或交替進行。","options":["compete","alternate","rest","sprint"],"sentence":"In the relay race, runners must ______ positions every 400 meters to give each teammate a turn. The coach organized the schedule so that person A runs, then person B, then person A again.","translation":"在接力賽中，跑步者必須每400公尺交替位置以讓每個隊友輪流參賽。教練安排時間表使得甲先跑，然後乙跑，接著甲再跑。","word":"alternate"}},"alternation":{"createdAt":1781613179430,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"alternation 意為輪流或交替，指兩個或多個事物按順序輪流出現的現象。","options":["collision","separation","succession","combination"],"sentence":"The ______ between day and night is a natural phenomenon caused by Earth's rotation. Every 24 hours, the cycle of light and darkness repeats continuously.","translation":"白天和黑夜的交替是由地球自轉引起的自然現象。每24小時，光與黑暗的循環不斷重複。","word":"alternation"}},"alternative":{"createdAt":1781651775059,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"alternative 表示用來取代或代替原有事物的方案或選擇。","options":["frustration","alternative","discussion","childhood"],"sentence":"When the original plan fell through, we needed to find an ______ solution. Since we had no other options left, this new approach became our only choice.","translation":"當原計畫破裂時，我們需要找到一個替代方案。由於我們已經沒有其他選擇，這個新方法成為了我們唯一的出路。","word":"alternative"}},"altitude":{"createdAt":1781360906189,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"altitude 意思是高度或海拔，指物體或地點相對於海平面的垂直距離。","options":["speed","altitude","direction","distance"],"sentence":"As the airplane climbed higher, the ______ increased and the outside temperature dropped. The pilot reported they had reached 35,000 feet.","translation":"當飛機攀升得更高時，高度增加了，外部溫度下降了。飛行員報告他們已經達到了35,000英尺。","word":"altitude"}},"aluminium":{"createdAt":1781360906184,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aluminium 是輕金屬，具有良好的可回收性，廣泛應用於工業。","options":["Iron","Aluminium","Gold","Copper"],"sentence":"This lightweight metal can be recycled many times. ______ is commonly used in beverage cans and aircraft parts.","translation":"這種輕金屬可以多次回收。鋁通常用於飲料罐和飛機零件。","word":"aluminium"}},"amateur":{"createdAt":1781837419092,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Amateur指的是出於愛好而進行某項活動的人，而不是職業人士。","options":["professional","amateur","seasoned","expert"],"sentence":"Though he was just an ______ musician, his talent was undeniable and impressive. He had never received formal training or studied music professionally.","translation":"雖然他只是業餘音樂家，但他的天賦是無可否認和令人印象深刻的。他從未接受過正式培訓或專業學習音樂。","word":"amateur"}},"ambassador":{"createdAt":1781360906185,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ambassador 意思是大使或使節，是由政府派遣的官方代表。","options":["journalist","ambassador","tourist","athlete"],"sentence":"The ______ represented her country at the international conference. She had been appointed by the government to serve as their official delegate.","translation":"大使在國際會議上代表她的國家。她被政府任命為官方代表。","word":"ambassador"}},"ambiguity":{"createdAt":1781672973735,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ambiguity是名詞，表示「模稜兩可；意義含糊」，指某事物可能有多種解釋或不清楚的情況。","options":["clarity","ambiguity","precision","specificity"],"sentence":"The ______ in the contract's wording led to a serious dispute between the two companies. Both parties interpreted the terms completely differently because of the unclear language.","translation":"合同措辭中的模稜兩可導致了兩家公司之間的嚴重紛爭。由於語言不清楚，雙方對條款的解釋完全不同。","word":"ambiguity"}},"ambiguous":{"createdAt":1781360885495,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ambiguous指表達不清楚或可能有多種解釋的，容易造成誤解。","options":["clear","ambiguous","detailed","explicit"],"sentence":"The instructions were ______ and left many team members confused about what they should do. Several different interpretations of the requirements were possible.","translation":"這些指示模糊不清，讓許多團隊成員困惑於他們應該做什麼。對要求有幾種不同的解釋是可能的。","word":"ambiguous"}},"ambitious":{"createdAt":1781360885486,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ambitious指擁有強烈的慾望和決心去達成偉大或困難的目標。","options":["lazy","ambitious","modest","indifferent"],"sentence":"She is an ______ young entrepreneur who wants to build a global business empire. By age thirty, she aims to expand her company to fifty countries.","translation":"她是一位有雄心的年輕企業家，想要建立一個全球商業帝國。到三十歲時，她的目標是將公司擴展到五十個國家。","word":"ambitious"}},"amend":{"createdAt":1781747309099,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"amend 指對文件、法案或計畫進行正式的修改或改進，使其變得更好或更完善。","options":["reject","amend","publish","review"],"sentence":"The committee decided to ______ the original proposal to include better environmental protections. The revised version was significantly different from what was initially submitted.","translation":"委員會決定修訂原始提案以納入更好的環境保護措施。修訂版本與最初提交的版本有很大的不同。","word":"amend"}},"ample":{"createdAt":1781581336208,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ample表示充足的、足夠多的數量。","options":["meager","ample","limited","scarce"],"sentence":"The host prepared ______ food for the party, ensuring no guest would leave hungry. There were multiple courses and abundant servings of every dish.","translation":"主人為派對準備了充足的食物，確保沒有客人會挨餓。有多道菜肴和每道菜的充足份量。","word":"ample"}},"amplify":{"createdAt":1781581336201,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"amplify指的是使聲音或信號變得更大或更強。","options":["translate","amplify","record","repeat"],"sentence":"The speaker used a microphone to ______ his voice so everyone in the large hall could hear clearly. Without this device, the audience in the back would have missed his important message.","translation":"演講者使用麥克風來放大他的聲音，使大廳裡的每個人都能清楚地聽到。沒有這個裝置，後面的觀眾會錯過他的重要信息。","word":"amplify"}},"analogy":{"createdAt":1781360885487,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"analogy是通過比較兩個不同事物之間的相似之處來解釋或理解某個概念的方法。","options":["definition","analogy","fact","summary"],"sentence":"The teacher used an ______ to help students understand the concept. She compared the heart to a pump that moves water through pipes, just as it moves blood through the body.","translation":"老師用類比幫助學生理解這個概念。她將心臟比作一個通過管道泵送水的泵，就像它通過身體泵送血液一樣。","word":"analogy"}},"analytical":{"createdAt":1781360885494,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"analytical指擅長分析和檢查信息，通過邏輯思維來解決問題的能力。","options":["emotional","analytical","impulsive","careless"],"sentence":"As an ______ person, she carefully examines all the data before making a decision. She breaks down complex problems into smaller parts to understand them better.","translation":"作為一個善於分析的人，她在做決定前仔細檢查所有數據。她將複雜的問題分解成更小的部分以更好地理解它們。","word":"analytical"}},"ancestor":{"createdAt":1781360885485,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"祖先指的是過去的世代成員，通常是指父母、祖父母或更早之前的家族成員。","options":["descendant","ancestor","relative","contemporary"],"sentence":"My ______ came to this country over 200 years ago. He was my great-great-grandfather who settled here during the colonial period.","translation":"我的祖先在200多年前來到這個國家。他是我在殖民地時期定居在這裡的曾曾祖父。","word":"ancestor"}},"anchor":{"createdAt":1781581336193,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"anchor作為名詞指用來固定船隻的重金屬裝置。","options":["sail","anchor","rudder","rope"],"sentence":"The ship dropped its ______ to prevent drifting in the strong current. The heavy metal device held the vessel firmly in place throughout the night.","translation":"船隻放下錨以防止在強流中漂流。這個沉重的金屬裝置整晚都將船牢牢地固定在原地。","word":"anchor"}},"ancient":{"createdAt":1781564440922,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ancient 作形容詞表示古代的、古老的，指很久以前的時代或事物。","options":["modern","ancient","contemporary","recent"],"sentence":"The museum displays many artifacts from ______ Egypt. These objects were created thousands of years ago during the time of the pharaohs.","translation":"博物館展示了許多來自古代埃及的文物。這些物品是在法老時代數千年前製造的。","word":"ancient"}},"animate":{"createdAt":1781527602362,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"animate 作為動詞表示使某人或某事變得生氣勃勃、充滿活力和生命力。","options":["depress","animate","freeze","tire"],"sentence":"The talented dancer's passionate performance seemed to ______ the entire audience. By the end, everyone was cheering and clapping with infectious energy.","translation":"這位天才舞者充滿熱情的表演似乎讓整個觀眾席充滿活力。最後，每個人都在歡呼和鼓掌，散發出感染力十足的能量。","word":"animate"}},"animated":{"createdAt":1781360906190,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"animated 意思是有生命的或充滿活力的，在電影中通常指用動畫技術製作的影片。","options":["documentary","animated","live-action","educational"],"sentence":"The children watched the ______ movie with excitement and laughter. The colorful characters and fun story kept them entertained for two hours.","translation":"孩子們興高采烈地觀看了這部動畫電影。彩色角色和有趣的故事使他們娛樂了兩個小時。","word":"animated"}},"anniversary":{"createdAt":1781424574160,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"anniversary 是指重要事件的週年紀念日，通常用於婚姻、公司成立等重要日期。","options":["birthday","anniversary","vacation","promotion"],"sentence":"The couple celebrated their 25th ______ with a special dinner at their favorite restaurant. This milestone marked a quarter-century of marriage and love.","translation":"這對夫婦在他們最喜歡的餐廳享用特別晚宴來慶祝他們的25週年紀念。這個里程碑標誌著他們婚姻和愛情的四分之一世紀。","word":"anniversary"}},"announce":{"createdAt":1781360906186,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"announce 意思是宣佈或公開表達，將信息傳達給大眾。","options":["conceal","announce","whisper","ignore"],"sentence":"The principal will ______ the exam results at the assembly tomorrow. Everyone will hear the official declaration during the school gathering.","translation":"校長將在明天的集會上宣佈考試結果。每個人都將在學校集會期間聽到官方聲明。","word":"announce"}},"announcement":{"createdAt":1781835517795,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"announcement 意為宣布或公開發表某項資訊，通常是向大眾或特定群體傳達重要訊息。","options":["argument","announcement","complaint","question"],"sentence":"The principal made an important ______ at the school assembly this morning. All students gathered in the hall to hear the news about the upcoming holiday schedule.","translation":"校長在今早的學校集會上做了一項重要的宣布。所有學生聚集在大廳裡聽取有關即將到來假期日程的消息。","word":"announcement"}},"annoying":{"createdAt":1781527602360,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"annoying 用來描述令人感到不快、厭煩或困擾的人或事物。","options":["amusing","calming","annoying","helpful"],"sentence":"The constant buzzing sound of the mosquito was ______ to everyone in the room. We finally managed to kill the insect to restore peace and quiet.","translation":"蚊子持續的嗡嗡聲讓房間裡的每個人都感到惱人。我們最終設法殺死了這隻昆蟲以恢復安寧和寧靜。","word":"annoying"}},"annual":{"createdAt":1781581336207,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"annual表示每年發生一次或持續一年的事物。","options":["monthly","annual","weekly","daily"],"sentence":"The company holds an ______ conference every year to bring together employees from all departments. This year's event is scheduled for November and will include workshops and networking opportunities.","translation":"公司每年舉辦一次年度會議，匯聚來自所有部門的員工。今年的活動定於十一月舉行，將包括研討會和社交機會。","word":"annual"}},"anonymous":{"createdAt":1781564440922,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"anonymous 表示匿名的、無名的，指不願透露或沒有署名的身份。","options":["named","anonymous","public","famous"],"sentence":"The ______ donation was received by the charity without a donor's name. The organization had no way to identify or contact the generous benefactor.","translation":"慈善機構收到了一筆匿名捐款，沒有捐贈人的名字。該組織無法識別或聯繫這位慷慨的捐贈者。","word":"anonymous"}},"anthem":{"createdAt":1781841505534,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"anthem 是指國歌或團體組織的讚歌，在正式場合演奏以代表國家或群體的身份。","options":["pollution","anthem","wonder","healthcare"],"sentence":"The ______ of our nation is played at the beginning of every Olympic ceremony. Every athlete stands respectfully as the music representing their country fills the stadium.","translation":"我們國家的國歌在每場奧運會開幕式開始時演奏。每位運動員在代表他們國家的音樂響起時恭敬地站著。","word":"anthem"}},"antibiotic":{"createdAt":1781360885492,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"antibiotic是一種藥物，能夠殺死或阻止細菌的生長，用於治療細菌感染。","options":["vitamin","antibiotic","painkiller","vaccine"],"sentence":"The doctor prescribed an ______ to treat the bacterial infection. The medication killed the harmful bacteria and allowed the patient to recover.","translation":"醫生開了一種抗生素來治療細菌感染。該藥物殺死了有害細菌，使患者得以恢復。","word":"antibiotic"}},"anxiety":{"createdAt":1781837419094,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Anxiety指的是對未來不確定性或潛在危險而感到的焦慮和擔憂。","options":["excitement","anxiety","relief","confidence"],"sentence":"Before her final exam, she felt overwhelming ______ about whether she would pass. The nervous tension kept her awake at night as the test date approached.","translation":"在期末考試前，她對是否能通過感到巨大的焦慮。當考試日期臨近時，緊張感讓她夜不能寐。","word":"anxiety"}},"anxious":{"createdAt":1781331945985,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"anxious 表示對即將發生或未知的事情感到擔心或緊張，常伴隨不安的行為。","options":["excited","bored","anxious","confused"],"sentence":"Sarah felt ______ as she waited for her exam results to be announced. She couldn't sleep the night before and kept checking her phone every few minutes.","translation":"莎拉在等待考試成績宣布時感到焦慮。她前一晚無法入睡，每隔幾分鐘就檢查一次手機。","word":"anxious"}},"anxiously":{"createdAt":1781274836864,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"anxiously是副詞，表示以焦慮、擔心或緊張的態度做某事，通常伴隨著不安的情緒。","options":["calmly","happily","anxiously","excitedly"],"sentence":"She waited ______ by the phone for news about her exam results. Her heart pounded and she couldn't sit still because she was worried about what she would learn.","translation":"她焦慮地在電話旁等待關於考試成績的消息。她的心猛烈地跳動，因為擔心結果而無法靜坐。","word":"anxiously"}},"apart":{"createdAt":1781323901185,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"apart在此表示「相距」或「分開」，用來描述兩人之間的地理距離。","options":["together","close","apart","nearby"],"sentence":"The two friends live ______ and only see each other during summer vacation. They are separated by several hundred miles of distance.","translation":"這兩個朋友相距很遠，只在暑假期間見面。他們被數百英里的距離隔開。","word":"apart"}},"apologize":{"createdAt":1781360906184,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"apologize 意思是道歉，表示為自己的錯誤或冒犯表示遺憾。","options":["explain","apologize","deny","justify"],"sentence":"He had to ______ for arriving late to the meeting. His manager accepted his sincere words of regret.","translation":"他必須為遲到的會議道歉。他的經理接受了他誠摯的遺憾之詞。","word":"apologize"}},"apology":{"createdAt":1781418481461,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"apology作為名詞，指為自己的過錯或不當行為向他人表達歉意和遺憾的言詞或行為。","options":["criticism","apology","compliment","explanation"],"sentence":"He offered a sincere ______ for his hurtful words after realizing the damage he had caused. She accepted his statement and they moved forward with their relationship.","translation":"他在意識到自己造成的傷害後，為傷人的言論提出了真誠的道歉。她接受了他的表示，他們的關係向前發展。","word":"apology"}},"apparent":{"createdAt":1781360885489,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"apparent指明顯可見或容易被注意到的，不需要深入探究就能理解。","options":["hidden","apparent","uncertain","questionable"],"sentence":"It was ______ that the student had not studied for the exam. He could not answer even the most basic questions.","translation":"很明顯該學生沒有為考試準備。他甚至無法回答最基本的問題。","word":"apparent"}},"apparently":{"createdAt":1781360906187,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"apparently 意思是顯然地，表示根據表面跡象或傳聞而看起來是這樣的情況。","options":["Certainly","Apparently","Deliberately","Intentionally"],"sentence":"______, the meeting was cancelled due to the weather, though no official announcement was made. People found out from rumors and social media posts.","translation":"顯然地，會議因天氣原因被取消了，儘管沒有官方公告。人們從謠言和社交媒體帖子中了解到。","word":"apparently"}},"appeal":{"createdAt":1781362281728,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"appeal表示懇求或呼籲，也可指吸引力，在此句中表示懇求他人幫助。","options":["announcement","appeal","complaint","question"],"sentence":"The charity organization made an ______ for donations to help disaster victims. They urged the public to contribute financially to aid relief efforts.","translation":"慈善組織呼籲捐款以幫助災難受害者。他們敦促公眾貢獻資金以支持救災努力。","word":"appeal"}},"appealing":{"createdAt":1781360906187,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"appealing 意思是迷人的或吸引人的，指能引起人們興趣和好感的事物。","options":["boring","appealing","confusing","ugly"],"sentence":"The restaurant's new menu design is very ______, attracting many more customers than before. The colorful presentation of dishes caught everyone's attention.","translation":"餐廳的新菜單設計非常迷人，吸引了比以前多得多的顧客。菜肴的彩色呈現引起了每個人的注意。","word":"appealing"}},"appear":{"createdAt":1781503378956,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"appear 在這裡表示「看起來、似乎」，用來描述事物外在的樣子或印象。","options":["become","appear","turn","seem"],"sentence":"The sky began to ______ darker as the storm approached. The clouds grew thicker and the sun disappeared behind them.","translation":"當暴風雨靠近時，天空開始顯得更暗。烏雲變得更濃密，太陽在它們後面消失了。","word":"appear"}},"appearance":{"createdAt":1781581336204,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"appearance指的是某人的外貌或呈現給他人的樣子。","options":["behavior","appearance","attitude","performance"],"sentence":"Her elegant ______ at the gala impressed everyone in attendance that evening. The stunning dress and refined makeup enhanced her natural beauty.","translation":"她在晚宴上的優雅外貌給所有出席者留下了深刻印象。這套華麗的連衣裙和精緻的妝容提升了她與生俱來的美貌。","word":"appearance"}},"appetite":{"createdAt":1781595752123,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"appetite 指對食物的慾望或食慾，是名詞。","options":["thirst","appetite","energy","strength"],"sentence":"After playing sports for two hours, he had a huge ______ and ate three large plates of food. His stomach was rumbling loudly, demanding substantial nourishment.","translation":"運動兩小時後，他有巨大的食慾，吃了三大盤食物。他的肚子在咕嚕咕嚕叫，需要大量的營養補充。","word":"appetite"}},"applause":{"createdAt":1781836375368,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"applause是指觀眾鼓掌表達讚同或欣賞的掌聲。","options":["silence","applause","music","laughter"],"sentence":"After the pianist finished her stunning performance, the audience erupted in loud ______. Everyone in the concert hall stood up to honour her talent.","translation":"鋼琴家結束她驚人的表演後，觀眾爆發出響亮的掌聲。音樂廳裡的每個人都站起來向她的才華致敬。","word":"applause"}},"appliance":{"createdAt":1781581336190,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"appliance指的是用於家庭或工業用途的電器設備。","options":["utensil","appliance","furniture","decoration"],"sentence":"The new kitchen ______ she purchased can wash dishes automatically in just one hour. It has revolutionized how she manages her daily household chores.","translation":"她購買的新廚房電器只需一小時就能自動洗碗。它徹底改變了她管理日常家務的方式。","word":"appliance"}},"applicant":{"createdAt":1781360906186,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"applicant 意思是申請人，指申請職位或入學機會的人。","options":["employer","applicant","customer","supervisor"],"sentence":"Each ______ submitted a resume and cover letter for the job position. The human resources department reviewed all twenty candidates' materials.","translation":"每位申請人都為該工作職位提交了履歷和求職信。人力資源部審查了所有二十位候選人的材料。","word":"applicant"}},"application":{"createdAt":1781345237582,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"application作名詞表示「申請」，指為了獲得某物或進入某機構而提交的正式請求。","options":["rejection","application","certificate","acceptance"],"sentence":"She submitted her college ______ before the deadline in January. The form included her test scores, personal essay, and letters of recommendation.","translation":"她在1月的截止日期前提交了大學申請。該表格包括她的考試成績、個人文章和推薦信。","word":"application"}},"apply":{"createdAt":1781481124704,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"apply 表示正式提出申請或請求，通常涉及提交文件。","options":["resign","graduate","register","petition"],"sentence":"You need to ______ for the scholarship before the deadline next month. Submit your completed application form along with all required documents to the admissions office.","translation":"你需要在下月截止日期之前申請獎學金。將完整的申請表連同所有所需文件提交給招生辦公室。","word":"apply"}},"appoint":{"createdAt":1781581336202,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"appoint指的是正式任命或指派某人擔任特定職位。","options":["interview","appoint","recruit","promote"],"sentence":"The board of directors decided to ______ a new chief executive officer to lead the company. The announcement was made public during the company's annual shareholders meeting.","translation":"董事會決定任命一位新的首席執行官來領導公司。該任命在公司年度股東大會期間向公眾宣布。","word":"appoint"}},"approach":{"createdAt":1781581336190,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"approach作為名詞表示處理或解決問題的方法和策略。","options":["schedule","approach","classroom","textbook"],"sentence":"The teacher's ______ to teaching mathematics focuses on hands-on problem-solving rather than memorization. Students found this method much more engaging and effective.","translation":"這位老師教授數學的方法側重於動手解決問題，而不是死記硬背。學生們發現這種方法更加有趣且有效。","word":"approach"}},"approve":{"createdAt":1781527602364,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"approve 表示正式同意、認可或批准某個計劃、提案或決定。","options":["reject","ignore","approve","delay"],"sentence":"The school principal had to ______ the new curriculum before it could be implemented in classrooms. After reviewing all the educational standards, she signed the official documentation to move forward.","translation":"學校校長必須認可新課程才能在教室中實施。在審查所有教育標準後，她簽署了正式文件以推進該計劃。","word":"approve"}},"approximate":{"createdAt":1781581336203,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"approximate表示大概的或近似的數字，而不是精確的。","options":["final","approximate","total","actual"],"sentence":"The ______ cost of the renovation project is fifty thousand dollars, though the exact figure may vary. The contractor provided this rough estimate based on initial assessments.","translation":"裝修項目的大約成本是五萬美元，儘管確切數字可能會有所不同。承包商根據初步評估提供了這個粗略估計。","word":"approximate"}},"apron":{"createdAt":1781336858145,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"apron 是穿在身體前面用來保護衣服的服裝，通常在廚房或進行髒亂工作時穿著。","options":["hat","apron","uniform","glove"],"sentence":"The chef wore a white ______ to protect his clothes while cooking. He tied it around his waist before starting to prepare the elaborate meal.","translation":"廚師穿著白色圍裙以在烹飪時保護他的衣服。他在開始準備這頓豐盛的食物之前在腰部繫上了它。","word":"apron"}},"aptitudes":{"createdAt":1781581336197,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aptitudes指的是某人在特定領域的天生才能和適應能力。","options":["hobbies","aptitudes","grades","interests"],"sentence":"The career counselor assessed the student's ______ and recommended fields in mathematics and engineering. Her natural talents in these areas made the decision clear.","translation":"職業顧問評估了學生的天賦才能，並推薦數學和工程領域。她在這些領域的天然才能使決定變得清晰。","word":"aptitudes"}},"aquarium":{"createdAt":1781709854485,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"aquarium（水族館）指展示水生生物的地方，與marine creatures（海洋生物）、fish（魚）和tanks（水箱）的描述完全吻合。","options":["aquarium","library","gallery","museum"],"sentence":"The children pressed their faces against the glass at the local ______ to watch the colorful fish swim. Inside, thousands of marine creatures from around the world were on display in large tanks.","translation":"孩子們在當地水族館的玻璃前貼著臉觀看彩色魚兒游泳。館內的大水箱中展示著來自世界各地的數千種海洋生物。","word":"aquarium"}},"aquatic":{"createdAt":1781434900595,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aquatic指與水有關的或發生在水中的事物。","options":["terrestrial","aquatic","aerial","underground"],"sentence":"The children's ______ activities at the summer camp included swimming, diving, and water polo. All events took place in the Olympic-sized pool.","translation":"夏令營中兒童的水上活動包括游泳、跳水和水球。所有活動都在奧運規模的游泳池進行。","word":"aquatic"}},"archaeology":{"createdAt":1781798927521,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"archaeology 是研究古代人類文明的學科，通過發掘和分析古代遺物來了解過去。","options":["history","archaeology","geology","anthropology"],"sentence":"Dr. Chen devoted her entire career to ______ and made several groundbreaking discoveries. Her team uncovered ancient pottery, stone tools, and human remains from civilizations thousands of years old.","translation":"陳博士把整個職業生涯投入考古學，並取得了多項突破性發現。她的團隊發掘了數千年前文明的古代陶器、石器和人類遺骸。","word":"archaeology"}},"archipelago":{"createdAt":1781581336194,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"archipelago指的是由許多島嶼組成的群島系統。","options":["continent","archipelago","peninsula","island"],"sentence":"The ______ of Indonesia consists of thousands of islands spread across the Indian and Pacific Oceans. This unique geography makes it one of the most biodiverse regions on Earth.","translation":"印度尼西亞群島由分佈在印度洋和太平洋上的數千個島嶼組成。這種獨特的地理特徵使其成為地球上生物多樣性最豐富的地區之一。","word":"archipelago"}},"architecture":{"createdAt":1782007262075,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"architecture 指的是建築物的設計風格和結構特徵，在此語境中強調的是建築物的物理設計方式。","options":["decoration","architecture","location","history"],"sentence":"The ______ of the ancient Roman buildings featured massive stone arches and columns. Engineers studied these structural designs to understand how they distributed weight so effectively.","translation":"古羅馬建築物的建築風格採用了巨大的石拱和圓柱。工程師研究這些結構設計，以了解它們如何有效地分散重量。","word":"architecture"}},"archive":{"createdAt":1781401361945,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"archive作為動詞表示將文件或資料妥善存檔和保存，以便日後查閱和研究。","options":["destroy","display","archive","distribute"],"sentence":"The library decided to ______ all the old newspapers and historical documents in a climate-controlled vault. These materials will be preserved and organized digitally so future researchers can access them safely.","translation":"圖書館決定將所有舊報紙和歷史文件存檔到一個氣候控制的保險庫中。這些材料將被保存和數位化組織，以便未來的研究人員能夠安全地訪問它們。","word":"archive"}},"arena":{"createdAt":1781311983482,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"arena 表示競爭或活動的場所，這裡指政治競爭的場域。","options":["timer","arena","syndrome","offshore"],"sentence":"The political ______ has become increasingly competitive in recent years. Candidates from both parties are actively campaigning in this space where major decisions are made.","translation":"近年來政治舞臺變得越來越競爭激烈。來自兩黨的候選人在這個做出重大決定的場所中積極進行競選活動。","word":"arena"}},"argument":{"createdAt":1781274836865,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"argument表示兩個或多個人之間的爭論或不同意見的交換，通常涉及對立的立場。","options":["agreement","discussion","argument","conversation"],"sentence":"The two neighbors had a heated ______ about whose fence was on whose property. They presented different pieces of evidence to support their conflicting claims.","translation":"兩個鄰居就誰的籬笆在誰的地產上發生了激烈的爭論。他們提出了不同的證據來支持他們相互衝突的主張。","word":"argument"}},"arise":{"createdAt":1782018712113,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「arise」表示問題、困難等突然出現或發生，通常帶有意外的含義。","options":["disappear","arise","continue","improve"],"sentence":"A serious problem began to ______ during the project's final stages. The team had to halt work immediately to address this unexpected situation.","translation":"在專案的最後階段，一個嚴重的問題開始發生。團隊必須立即停止工作來解決這個意外的情況。","word":"arise"}},"armed":{"createdAt":1781581336200,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"armed表示被武裝或配備武器的狀態。","options":["trained","armed","dressed","equipped"],"sentence":"The security guards at the bank were ______ with weapons to protect against potential robberies. Their visible firearms served as a strong deterrent to criminals.","translation":"銀行的保安人員持有武器以防止可能的搶劫。他們明顯的火槍對罪犯起到了強大的威懾作用。","word":"armed"}},"arms":{"createdAt":1781693303267,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"arms 在此指「武器」，通常指用於戰爭或軍事目的的工具，特別是槍支、炸彈等致命武器。","options":["supplies","arms","uniforms","food"],"sentence":"The soldiers carried ______ and ammunition as they prepared for the military operation. Their weapons included rifles, grenades, and tactical gear.","translation":"士兵們攜帶武器和彈藥，準備進行軍事行動。他們的武器包括步槍、手榴彈和戰術裝備。","word":"arms"}},"army":{"createdAt":1781274836865,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"army指國家的陸軍部隊，是由大量士兵組成的軍事組織，負責陸地防禦。","options":["navy","police","army","guard"],"sentence":"The ______ was deployed to the border region to strengthen national security. Thousands of soldiers were stationed there to protect the country's territorial integrity.","translation":"陸軍被派遣到邊境地區以加強國家安全。數千名士兵駐紮在那裡以保護國家的領土完整。","word":"army"}},"arouse":{"createdAt":1781847052512,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"arouse是動詞，意思是喚起或引起某種情感、興趣或反應，通常帶有積極的行動結果。","options":["suppress","arouse","ignore","delay"],"sentence":"The documentary about endangered species managed to ______ strong emotions in the audience members. After watching it, many viewers decided to donate to wildlife conservation organizations.","translation":"這部關於瀕危物種的紀錄片成功地在觀眾中喚起了強烈的情感。看完後，許多觀眾決定向野生動物保護組織捐款。","word":"arouse"}},"arrangement":{"createdAt":1781437220551,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「Arrangement」指事先計畫和組織的各種準備或安排。","options":["ceremony","arrangement","celebration","invitation"],"sentence":"The wedding ______ took three months to complete successfully. Every detail from the flowers to the seating chart was planned by a professional coordinator.","translation":"婚禮的安排花了三個月才順利完成。從鮮花到座位表，每個細節都由專業協調員規劃。","word":"arrangement"}},"array":{"createdAt":1781437013479,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"array 指種類繁多、數量眾多的一系列事物或物品的集合展示。","options":["collection","array","shortage","sample"],"sentence":"The museum displayed a magnificent ______ of ancient artifacts from different civilizations. Visitors could see Egyptian mummies, Greek sculptures, Roman coins, and Persian jewelry all in one exhibition hall.","translation":"博物館展出了來自不同文明的古代文物的宏偉陣列。遊客可以在一個展覽廳裡看到埃及木乃伊、希臘雕像、羅馬硬幣和波斯珠寶。","word":"array"}},"arrogant":{"createdAt":1781835134541,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"arrogant 指一個人過度自信且對他人缺乏尊重，通常表現出自認高人一等的態度。","options":["humble","arrogant","generous","curious"],"sentence":"The ______ CEO refused to listen to any suggestions from his employees. His behavior made it clear that he believed he was superior to everyone else in the company.","translation":"那位傲慢的執行長拒絕聽取員工的任何建議。他的行為清楚表明，他認為自己優於公司裡的每個人。","word":"arrogant"}},"artery":{"createdAt":1781839950962,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"artery 是指從心臟輸送血液到身體各部分的血管。","options":["vein","artery","nerve","organ"],"sentence":"The patient's ______ was blocked, restricting blood flow to his heart. The cardiologist performed emergency surgery to clear the main vessel carrying blood from the heart.","translation":"患者的動脈被堵塞,限制了流向心臟的血流。心臟科醫生進行了緊急手術以清除從心臟輸送血液的主要血管。","word":"artery"}},"article":{"createdAt":1781429945503,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"article 表示報紙或雜誌上的文章或報導，是新聞或評論的書面形式。","options":["cartoon","advertisement","article","recipe"],"sentence":"The journalist wrote an excellent ______ about climate change for the newspaper's Sunday edition. Her in-depth investigation and research were published across five pages of the magazine.","translation":"這名記者為報紙的週日版寫了一篇關於氣候變化的優秀文章。她深入的調查和研究在雜誌的五頁上發表。","word":"article"}},"articulate":{"createdAt":1781437220552,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「Articulate」形容詞表示一個人能夠清楚、有效地表達自己的想法。","options":["quiet","articulate","nervous","confused"],"sentence":"The ______ speaker explained the complex theory so clearly that even children could understand it. His ability to communicate difficult concepts with precision impressed the entire audience.","translation":"這位善於表達的演講者解釋複雜理論的方式如此清晰，甚至連小孩都能理解。他用精確的方式傳達困難概念的能力給全體聽眾留下了深刻印象。","word":"articulate"}},"artificial":{"createdAt":1781613113027,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"artificial 表示人造的、非天然的或用人工方法製造的","options":["natural","artificial","fresh","real"],"sentence":"The ______ flowers looked so realistic that visitors couldn't tell they weren't genuine. However, they would never wilt or need watering.","translation":"人造花看起來非常逼真，遊客無法分辨它們不是真的。然而，它們永遠不會凋謝或需要澆水。","word":"artificial"}},"ascend":{"createdAt":1781424157170,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ascend 表示向上爬或上升，與達到山頂的結果相符。","options":["descend","ascend","traverse","avoid"],"sentence":"The mountaineers decided to ______ the peak early in the morning when the weather was clear. By noon, they had successfully reached the summit at 3,000 meters above sea level.","translation":"登山者決定在天氣晴朗的清晨攀登山峰。到了中午，他們已經成功到達了海拔3,000公尺的山頂。","word":"ascend"}},"aspect":{"createdAt":1781664082524,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aspect 表示事物的方面或觀點，指事物的某一個具體的特徵或部分。","options":["result","aspect","location","date"],"sentence":"One important ______ of the job interview is demonstrating your communication skills. Employers want to see how clearly and confidently you can express your ideas.","translation":"工作面試的一個重要方面是展示你的溝通技能。僱主想看你如何清楚而自信地表達你的想法。","word":"aspect"}},"aspire":{"createdAt":1781672973739,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"aspire是動詞，表示「追求；渴望；有志於」，指對遠大目標的強烈渴望和追求。","options":["refuse","aspire","fear","forget"],"sentence":"Since childhood, he has ______ to become a professional musician and perform on world stages. His passion for music has never wavered despite the many challenges he faced.","translation":"從童年起，他就渴望成為專業音樂家並在世界舞台上表演。儘管面臨許多挑戰，他對音樂的熱情從未動搖。","word":"aspire"}},"assassinate":{"createdAt":1781850287959,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"assassinate 指秘密地或突然地殺害重要人物，通常是出於政治目的。","options":["arrest","betray","assassinate","exile"],"sentence":"The dictator feared that his enemies would ______ him while he slept. Security forces doubled the number of guards around his bedroom each night because of these persistent threats.","translation":"獨裁者擔心他的敵人會在他睡眠中暗殺他。由於這些持續的威脅，安全部隊每晚都將他臥室周圍的警衛數量加倍。","word":"assassinate"}},"assassination":{"createdAt":1781613113021,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"assassination 是暗殺或有預謀地殺害重要人物的行為","options":["election","inauguration","assassination","resignation"],"sentence":"The ______ of the president shocked the entire nation. The sudden violent death of the leader created chaos and uncertainty.","translation":"總統遇刺震驚了整個國家。領導人的突然暴力死亡造成了混亂和不確定。","word":"assassination"}},"assault":{"createdAt":1781779647059,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"assault表示對他人進行暴力攻擊或襲擊","options":["assistance","assault","assembly","assessment"],"sentence":"The police arrested a man for ______ on Main Street. According to witnesses, he attacked another person without any provocation.","translation":"警方逮捕了一名在主街發起攻擊的男子。根據目擊者所說，他無故攻擊了另一個人。","word":"assault"}},"assemble":{"createdAt":1781613113029,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"assemble 表示集合、組裝或把分散的部分聚集在一起","options":["disassemble","assemble","inspect","separate"],"sentence":"The workers needed to ______ all the furniture parts together carefully. Following the instruction manual, they put each piece in the correct position.","translation":"工人們需要小心地將所有家具零件組裝在一起。按照說明書，他們把每一件放在正確的位置。","word":"assemble"}},"assembly":{"createdAt":1781672973737,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"assembly是名詞，表示「大會；議會；集合」，指人們聚集在一起的正式活動或集會。","options":["dismissal","assembly","recess","detention"],"sentence":"The school held a special ______ in the gymnasium to announce the scholarship winners. All students and teachers gathered together to celebrate the achievements of their peers.","translation":"學校在體育館舉辦了特別集會，宣布獎學金獲得者。所有學生和教師聚集在一起慶祝他們同學的成就。","word":"assembly"}},"assert":{"createdAt":1781417610419,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"assert是指堅定地聲稱或斷言某事為真，通常帶有信心和把握。","options":["doubt","deny","assert","question"],"sentence":"The witness chose to ______ that she had seen the suspect leaving the building at midnight. Multiple security cameras confirmed her account with video evidence.","translation":"證人聲稱她看到嫌疑人在午夜時離開大樓。多台監控攝像機用視頻證據確認了她的說法。","word":"assert"}},"assertion":{"createdAt":1781613113012,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"assertion 是主張或聲明，通常是對某事的堅定陳述","options":["question","assertion","invitation","suggestion"],"sentence":"The politician made a bold ______ that he would solve the economic crisis within one year. However, he provided no concrete evidence or detailed plan to support his claim.","translation":"這位政治家大膽聲稱他將在一年內解決經濟危機。然而，他沒有提供具體證據或詳細計劃來支持他的主張。","word":"assertion"}},"assess":{"createdAt":1781613179430,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"assess 意為評價或評定，指對某人或某事進行系統的判斷和評估。","options":["ignore","praise","evaluate","overlook"],"sentence":"The teacher will ______ the students' performance through a combination of tests, projects, and class participation. This comprehensive evaluation will determine their final grades for the semester.","translation":"教師將通過測試、項目和課堂參與的組合來評估學生的表現。這個全面的評估將決定他們本學期的最終成績。","word":"assess"}},"assist":{"createdAt":1781672973738,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"assist是動詞，表示「協助；幫助」，指為他人的工作或活動提供支持或幫助。","options":["ignore","assist","distract","obstruct"],"sentence":"The nurse will ______ the surgeon during the complicated operation tomorrow. Her expertise and quick hands will be essential to ensure the procedure goes smoothly.","translation":"護士明天將在複雜的手術中協助外科醫生。她的專業知識和靈巧的雙手對於確保手術順利進行至關重要。","word":"assist"}},"assistance":{"createdAt":1781581336211,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"assistance指的是提供給他人的幫助或支持。","options":["directions","assistance","information","advice"],"sentence":"The elderly woman asked for ______ in carrying her heavy shopping bags to the parking lot. A kind stranger immediately offered to help her with the difficult task.","translation":"這位老婦人請求幫助將她沉重的購物袋提到停車場。一位善良的陌生人立即主動幫助她完成這項困難的任務。","word":"assistance"}},"association":{"createdAt":1781779647127,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"association表示由志同道合的人組成的組織或協會","options":["company","association","family","school"],"sentence":"She joined a professional ______ to network with others in her field. The organization held monthly meetings and provided valuable resources.","translation":"她加入了一個專業協會與同行交流。該組織每月舉辦會議並提供寶貴資源。","word":"association"}},"assume":{"createdAt":1781613113016,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"assume 表示假定或假設，不經過驗證就認為某事是真實的","options":["know","assume","ask","ignore"],"sentence":"Don't ______ that everyone likes the same kind of music as you do. People have different tastes and preferences that are valid.","translation":"不要假定每個人都喜歡和你一樣的音樂類型。人們有不同的有效口味和偏好。","word":"assume"}},"assumption":{"createdAt":1781613113013,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"assumption 是假定或臆測，指未經驗證而接受的想法","options":["fact","assumption","observation","knowledge"],"sentence":"He made an incorrect ______ about her intentions without asking for clarification first. Later he discovered his guess was completely wrong.","translation":"他在沒有先尋求澄清的情況下對她的意圖做出了不正確的假定。後來他發現他的猜測完全錯了。","word":"assumption"}},"assurance":{"createdAt":1781613113031,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"assurance 是保證、確認或向某人保證某事的言語","options":["question","assurance","doubt","denial"],"sentence":"She gave him her ______ that she would keep his secret safe. His trust in her promise helped him feel more confident.","translation":"她向他保證她會保護他的秘密。他對她承諾的信任幫助他更有信心。","word":"assurance"}},"assure":{"createdAt":1781613113024,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"assure 表示向某人保證或確認某事是真實的","options":["frighten","assure","confuse","deceive"],"sentence":"The doctor tried to ______ his worried patient that the surgery would be successful. His confident words and experience helped calm her fears.","translation":"醫生試圖向他擔心的患者保證手術會成功。他自信的言語和經驗幫助平復了她的恐懼。","word":"assure"}},"assured":{"createdAt":1781527602353,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"assured 表示對某事充滿信心和把握，通常用來描述一個人感到安心和確定的心理狀態。","options":["nervous","assured","confused","annoyed"],"sentence":"The captain felt ______ that the ship would safely reach its destination despite the storm. His confidence came from decades of experience navigating treacherous waters.","translation":"儘管暴風雨來襲，船長感到有把握船隻會安全抵達目的地。他的信心源自於數十年駕馭危險水域的經驗。","word":"assured"}},"asthma":{"createdAt":1781613113012,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"asthma 是一種慢性呼吸道疾病，會導致呼吸困難","options":["allergy","asthma","injury","fatigue"],"sentence":"His ______ made it difficult for him to participate in sports activities. The respiratory condition required him to use an inhaler during exercise.","translation":"他的氣喘使他難以參加體育活動。這種呼吸系統疾病要求他在運動時使用吸入器。","word":"asthma"}},"astonished":{"createdAt":1781429945499,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"astonished 表示非常驚訝或震驚，通常是面對出乎意料的事情時的強烈反應。","options":["bored","astonished","disappointed","confused"],"sentence":"We were ______ when our quiet neighbor suddenly announced she was a professional rock climber. Her incredible feats and achievements left us completely stunned and speechless.","translation":"當我們安靜的鄰居突然宣布她是專業攀岩者時，我們驚訝不已。她不可思議的壯舉和成就讓我們完全震驚，說不出話來。","word":"astonished"}},"astronaut":{"createdAt":1781581336202,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"astronaut指的是經過訓練進行太空飛行和探索的人。","options":["pilot","astronaut","engineer","scientist"],"sentence":"The ______ underwent years of rigorous training before being selected for the space mission. His dedication and scientific expertise made him an ideal candidate to explore the moon.","translation":"這位太空人在被選中執行太空任務之前接受了多年嚴格的訓練。他的奉獻精神和科學專業知識使他成為探索月球的理想人選。","word":"astronaut"}},"astronomy":{"createdAt":1781499075057,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"天文學是研究宇宙中天體的科學，包括恆星、行星和星系。","options":["geology","botany","astronomy","meteorology"],"sentence":"Dr. Patel spent her career studying ______ and discovering new planets and stars. Her telescope revealed distant galaxies that had never been observed by humans before.","translation":"帕特爾博士用她的職業生涯研究天文學，發現了新的行星和恆星。她的望遠鏡揭示了人類以前從未觀測過的遙遠星系。","word":"astronomy"}},"athlete":{"createdAt":1781566460884,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"athlete是指經過訓練、參加體育競賽的人，與每日訓練和優秀表現相符。","options":["coach","athlete","spectator","judge"],"sentence":"The Olympic ______ trained six hours daily to prepare for the competition. His dedication to practice and fitness made him one of the country's top performers.","translation":"奧運運動員每天訓練六小時以準備比賽。他對練習和健身的投入使他成為國家頂級表現者之一。","word":"athlete"}},"athletic":{"createdAt":1781566460882,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"athletic形容與運動相關或具有運動員特質的身體和能力。","options":["artistic","academic","athletic","artistic"],"sentence":"Sarah has an ______ build with strong muscles developed from years of training. She excels in competitive sports due to her physical conditioning.","translation":"莎拉擁有一身運動員的體格，肌肉在多年訓練中得到發展。由於她的體能狀況，她在競技運動中表現卓越。","word":"athletic"}},"athletics":{"createdAt":1782007196630,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「田徑運動；體育競技」指各種體育活動和運動項目的總稱，包括競速、跳躍和投擲等。","options":["academics","arts","athletics","music"],"sentence":"The school invested heavily in ______ by building new tracks, gyms, and sports facilities. The track team, basketball team, and volleyball team all benefited from these improvements.","translation":"學校通過建造新跑道、體育館和運動設施，投入大量資金支持田徑運動和體育競技。田徑隊、籃球隊和排球隊都從這些改善中受益。","word":"athletics"}},"atmosphere":{"createdAt":1781484415214,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"atmosphere意指一個地方或情境的整體氛圍和感覺，由多種元素組成。","options":["menu","price","atmosphere","noise"],"sentence":"The restaurant had such a romantic ______ that every couple felt in love. The soft lighting, gentle music, and intimate seating created the perfect mood.","translation":"餐廳有著如此浪漫的氣氛，使每一對情侶都感到相愛。柔和的燈光、溫柔的音樂和親密的座位安排營造了完美的氛圍。","word":"atmosphere"}},"attachment":{"createdAt":1781395428240,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"attachment 在電子郵件中指附加的文件或文檔，需要單獨下載或打開。","options":["signature","attachment","header","footer"],"sentence":"The email included an important ______ that contained the contract details. You need to download this file to review all the terms and conditions.","translation":"這封電子郵件包含了一個重要的附件，其中包含合約詳情。您需要下載此文件以查看所有條款和條件。","word":"attachment"}},"attack":{"createdAt":1781871338559,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"attack表示對敵人或目標進行軍事攻擊或進攻。","options":["defend","join","assault","retreat"],"sentence":"The general ordered his troops to ______ the enemy's fortress at dawn. The soldiers charged forward with weapons ready for the planned assault.","translation":"將軍命令他的部隊在黎明時發動對敵人堡壘的進攻。士兵們衝向前進，準備好武器進行計劃中的攻擊。","word":"attack"}},"attain":{"createdAt":1781272410989,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"attain表示通過努力達到、獲得或實現某個目標或位置。","options":["abandon","forget","attain","ignore"],"sentence":"She worked hard for ten years to ______ her dream of becoming a doctor. Her determination and perseverance finally paid off when she completed her medical degree.","translation":"她努力了十年才達成了成為醫生的夢想。當她完成醫學學位時，她的決心和毅力終於得到了回報。","word":"attain"}},"attempt":{"createdAt":1781336858154,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"attempt 作為動詞或名詞，表示試圖做某事或進行某項嘗試，即使可能不會成功。","options":["completion","escape","attempt","decision"],"sentence":"The mountaineers made a final ______ to reach the peak before winter storms arrived. Despite their efforts, severe weather forced them to turn back just 200 meters from the summit.","translation":"登山者在冬季風暴到來之前做了最後一次試圖到達山峰的嘗試。儘管他們做出了努力，嚴酷的天氣迫使他們在距離頂峰僅200米的地方折返。","word":"attempt"}},"attentive":{"createdAt":1781414438954,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"attentive表示留心、注意周圍事物或對他人體貼關懷的態度","options":["careless","rude","attentive","sleepy"],"sentence":"The nurse was ______ to her patient's needs throughout the night. She responded immediately whenever he called for help or showed discomfort.","translation":"護士整夜都注意著她患者的需求。每當他呼救或表現出不適時，她立即做出反應。","word":"attentive"}},"attract":{"createdAt":1781850287960,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"attract 意指使某人或某物被吸引或對其產生興趣。","options":["repel","confuse","attract","disturb"],"sentence":"The bright neon lights and loud music will ______ many young people to the new nightclub downtown. The grand opening party is expected to draw hundreds of visitors on its first night.","translation":"明亮的霓虹燈和響亮的音樂將吸引許多年輕人前往市中心的新夜店。盛大的開幕派對預計在首晚會吸引數百名訪客。","word":"attract"}},"attraction":{"createdAt":1781613179425,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"attraction 意為吸引力或景點，指能吸引人們前來參觀或體驗的地方或事物。","options":["problem","issue","destination","burden"],"sentence":"The new museum has become the main ______ in the city, drawing hundreds of visitors every day. Tourists from around the world come to experience the impressive exhibits and interactive displays.","translation":"新博物館已成為該城市的主要景點，每天吸引數百名訪客。來自世界各地的遊客前來體驗令人印象深刻的展品和互動展示。","word":"attraction"}},"attractive":{"createdAt":1781779647062,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"attractive表示有吸引力的、引人注意的或令人愉悅的","options":["repulsive","attractive","confusing","boring"],"sentence":"The new advertising campaign was very ______. The company saw a significant increase in customer interest after launching it.","translation":"新廣告活動非常有吸引力。推出後，公司看到顧客興趣大幅增加。","word":"attractive"}},"auction":{"createdAt":1781499075055,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"拍賣是一種銷售方式，透過競價決定商品的最終買家和價格。","options":["exhibition","auction","appraisal","collection"],"sentence":"The art gallery held an ______ where wealthy collectors bid on rare paintings. The highest bidder won each item, paying thousands of dollars for their acquisitions.","translation":"藝術館舉辦了一場拍賣會，富有的收藏家競標稀有繪畫。出價最高的買家贏得了每件物品，為他們的收購支付了數千美元。","word":"auction"}},"audience":{"createdAt":1781581336197,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"audience指的是來看表演或聽演講的觀眾或聽眾。","options":["troupe","audience","orchestra","cast"],"sentence":"The comedian performed for a large ______ of over five hundred people at the theatre. Their enthusiastic laughter and applause showed their appreciation for his humor.","translation":"這位喜劇演員在劇院為超過五百人的大觀眾表演。他們熱情的笑聲和掌聲表明了他們對他幽默的欣賞。","word":"audience"}},"audio":{"createdAt":1781613179419,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"audio 作形容詞時意為聲音的或音訊的，指與聲音或錄音相關的設備和技術。","options":["visual","mechanical","sound","lighting"],"sentence":"The ______ equipment in the concert hall was state-of-the-art and provided crystal-clear sound. The microphones, speakers, and amplifiers were all brand new and professionally calibrated.","translation":"音樂廳的音訊設備是最先進的，提供了清晰的聲音。麥克風、揚聲器和擴音器都是全新的並經過專業校準。","word":"audio"}},"audit":{"createdAt":1781860901468,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"audit表示審計或查帳，是對財務記錄的正式檢查和驗證","options":["presentation","audit","advertisement","celebration"],"sentence":"The company hired a professional firm to conduct a financial ______ of their accounts. The auditors examined all transactions and records from the past three years.","translation":"公司聘請了一家專業公司對其帳目進行財務審計。審計員檢查了過去三年的所有交易和記錄。","word":"audit"}},"authentic":{"createdAt":1781274836867,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"authentic形容詞表示真實的、可信的、非假冒的，特別是指已被證實或經過驗證的真品。","options":["fake","damaged","authentic","modern"],"sentence":"The museum displayed an ______ painting that was created by the famous artist in the 18th century. Experts had verified its genuineness through detailed analysis and historical documentation.","translation":"博物館展示了一幅由18世紀著名藝術家創作的真跡。專家透過詳細分析和歷史文獻驗證了其真實性。","word":"authentic"}},"authority":{"createdAt":1781613179430,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"authority 意為權力或當局，指某人被授予的正式權力或進行某些行動的官方機構。","options":["weakness","doubt","power","confusion"],"sentence":"The police officer exercised her ______ to issue a traffic citation to the speeding driver. She had the official power and legal right to enforce traffic laws in that jurisdiction.","translation":"警察以她的權力向超速駕駛者開出交通罰單。她擁有在該司法管轄區執行交通法律的官方權力和法律權利。","word":"authority"}},"authorize":{"createdAt":1781779647066,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"authorize表示給予官方許可或權限進行某項行動","options":["deny","authorize","investigate","delay"],"sentence":"The manager must ______ any purchase over $5,000. Without her signature of approval, the transaction cannot proceed.","translation":"經理必須批准任何超過5000美元的採購。沒有她的簽名批准，交易無法進行。","word":"authorize"}},"autobiography":{"createdAt":1781581336207,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"autobiography指的是由某人自己撰寫的關於其生活的敘述。","options":["biography","autobiography","memoir","journal"],"sentence":"The famous actor published his ______ last year, sharing personal stories from his childhood and career. Readers were fascinated by his intimate account of becoming a Hollywood star.","translation":"這位著名演員去年出版了他的自傳，分享了他童年和職業生涯的個人故事。讀者對他成為好萊塢明星的親身描述著迷。","word":"autobiography"}},"automatic":{"createdAt":1781581336200,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"automatic表示無需人工干預而自行運作的機器或系統。","options":["sliding","automatic","glass","heavy"],"sentence":"The ______ doors at the mall entrance open and close without any manual effort. Customers simply walk toward the sensor and the system responds instantly.","translation":"購物中心入口的自動門無需任何人工操作就能打開和關閉。顧客只需朝感應器走去，系統就會立即做出反應。","word":"automatic"}},"automatically":{"createdAt":1781581336214,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"automatically是副詞，表示機器或系統自行運作而無需人工干預。","options":["manually","automatically","gradually","eventually"],"sentence":"When you enter the supermarket, the lights turn on ______ without anyone flipping a switch. This motion-sensor technology activates whenever a customer approaches the doors.","translation":"當你進入超市時，燈會自動打開，無需任何人打開開關。每當顧客靠近門時，這種動作傳感器技術就會啟動。","word":"automatically"}},"automobile":{"createdAt":1781613179426,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"automobile 意為汽車或機動車，指由內燃機或電動機驅動的四輪車輛。","options":["bicycle","motorcycle","car","train"],"sentence":"The new ______ model features advanced safety technology and excellent fuel efficiency. It has received outstanding reviews from both critics and consumers who appreciate its performance.","translation":"新汽車型號具有先進的安全技術和卓越的燃油效率。它獲得了評論家和欣賞其性能的消費者的優異評價。","word":"automobile"}},"autonomy":{"createdAt":1781665727110,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"autonomy 指自治權或自我管理的能力，強調獨立決定自身事務的權力。","options":["wealth","autonomy","technology","education"],"sentence":"The newly independent nation fought hard to achieve political ______ from foreign powers. They established their own government, laws, and military without external interference.","translation":"這個新獨立的國家為了從外國勢力中獲得政治自治而奮力抗爭。他們建立了自己的政府、法律和軍隊，不受外部干涉。","word":"autonomy"}},"availability":{"createdAt":1781257238302,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"availability指某物是否可得、可獲取或能被使用的狀況。","options":["price","availability","quality","location"],"sentence":"The ______ of concert tickets determined whether fans could attend the show. Since only 100 seats remained and 500 people wanted to buy them, most disappointed fans went home empty-handed.","translation":"演唱會門票的可得性決定了粉絲是否能參加演出。由於只有100個座位剩餘，而500人想購票，大多數失望的粉絲空手而歸。","word":"availability"}},"available":{"createdAt":1781774456605,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"available 表示某物可以被取得或使用，在此指門票仍有存貨。","options":["expensive","popular","purchasable","desirable"],"sentence":"The concert tickets were no longer ______ after the first hour of sales. All seats had been purchased by eager fans.","translation":"演唱會門票在銷售開始後的第一小時內就不再可得。所有座位都被熱情的粉絲購買了。","word":"available"}},"avenue":{"createdAt":1781485266374,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"avenue除了指街道外，還可以比喻為達成目標的途徑或方法。","options":["dead end","obstacle","avenue","barrier"],"sentence":"The company explored a new ______ to expand their market reach and increase profits. This strategic direction proved successful and brought them valuable new business opportunities.","translation":"公司探索了一條新的途徑來擴大他們的市場覆蓋範圍並增加利潤。這個戰略方向證明是成功的，為他們帶來了寶貴的新商機。","word":"avenue"}},"average":{"createdAt":1781311983487,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"average 表示多個數值的平均值或典型的、中等的水平。","options":["presidential","evolution","average","expressive"],"sentence":"The ______ temperature for this region in July is around 28 degrees Celsius. This figure represents the typical weather conditions most people experience during that summer month.","translation":"這個地區七月的平均溫度約為攝氏28度。這個數字代表了大多數人在那個夏月經歷的典型天氣狀況。","word":"average"}},"avert":{"createdAt":1781595752125,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"avert 作為動詞，表示防止或避免某件不好的事情發生。","options":["cause","create","avert","encourage"],"sentence":"She tried to ______ the accident by slamming on the brakes quickly. Her quick reaction prevented the collision that could have been tragic.","translation":"她通過快速踩剎車試圖防止事故發生。她的快速反應阻止了可能是悲劇性的碰撞。","word":"avert"}},"aviation":{"createdAt":1781272410995,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"aviation指的是航空學、航空工業或飛行術，涉及飛機、飛行和空中運輸的各個方面。","options":["agriculture","architecture","aviation","archaeology"],"sentence":"My brother studied ______ in college and now works as a pilot for an international airline. His degree included courses in aircraft design, aerodynamics, and flight operations.","translation":"我的哥哥在大學裡學習航空學，現在在一家國際航空公司當飛行員。他的學位包括飛機設計、空氣動力學和飛行操作的課程。","word":"aviation"}},"awake":{"createdAt":1781595752119,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"awake 是形容詞，表示清醒的、沒有睡著的狀態。","options":["sleeping","tired","awake","restless"],"sentence":"Even though it was very early in the morning, the baby was fully ______ and alert. The infant had already opened his eyes and was looking around the room.","translation":"儘管天很早，嬰兒已經完全清醒並警覺。嬰兒已經睜開眼睛，四處張望房間。","word":"awake"}},"award":{"createdAt":1781256547739,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Award作為動詞表示正式授予或頒發獎品、獎金或榮譽給某人。","options":["withdraw","award","deny","delay"],"sentence":"The university will ______ scholarships to the top ten students based on their academic achievements. The recipients will be announced at the graduation ceremony next month.","translation":"大學將根據學生的學術成就將獎學金頒發給前十名學生。獲獎者將在下個月的畢業典禮上宣佈。","word":"award"}},"aware":{"createdAt":1781256547738,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Aware表示知道、意識到或認識到某事物的存在或事實。","options":["ignorant","aware","uncertain","careless"],"sentence":"She was ______ of the dangers associated with traveling alone in unfamiliar places. Therefore, she always informed her family of her location and carried safety devices with her.","translation":"她知道獨自在陌生地方旅行的危險。因此，她總是將她的位置告知家人，並隨身攜帶安全裝置。","word":"aware"}},"awareness":{"createdAt":1781499075060,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"意識指人們對某個問題或現象的認識和理解程度。","options":["ignorance","denial","awareness","indifference"],"sentence":"The environmental ______ campaign educated people about the dangers of plastic pollution. After seeing the documentary, viewers became concerned about protecting marine ecosystems.","translation":"環保意識運動教育人們了解塑膠污染的危害。看完紀錄片後，觀眾開始關注保護海洋生態系統。","word":"awareness"}},"awe":{"createdAt":1781672973717,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"awe是名詞，表示「敬畏；畏怯」，指對宏偉或令人印象深刻事物的深刻敬畏感。","options":["anger","awe","anxiety","annoyance"],"sentence":"The tourists stood in ______ as they gazed at the ancient pyramid for the first time. The massive stone structure inspired respect and wonder in everyone who saw it.","translation":"遊客們第一次凝視古老金字塔時站著充滿敬畏。巨大的石頭結構激發了每個看到它的人的尊重和驚歎。","word":"awe"}},"awesome":{"createdAt":1781256485495,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"awesome表示令人驚嘆的、非常棒的或令人印象深刻的","options":["boring","terrible","awesome","confusing"],"sentence":"The concert was absolutely ______ and the crowd was amazed by the stunning performance. Everyone left the venue feeling impressed and energized.","translation":"這場音樂會棒極了，觀眾對這場精彩的表演嘆為觀止。每個人都帶著欽佩和充滿活力的感覺離開了場地。","word":"awesome"}},"awful":{"createdAt":1781256485492,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"awful表示非常糟糕的、令人不快的或令人厭惡的","options":["delicious","fresh","awful","creative"],"sentence":"The food at the restaurant was absolutely ______ and we could barely eat it. Our entire dining experience was a complete disappointment.","translation":"餐廳的食物糟透了，我們幾乎吃不下去。我們整個用餐體驗都非常令人失望。","word":"awful"}},"babysit":{"createdAt":1781664419995,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"babysit是指臨時照顧別人的孩子，包括日常護理和監督。","options":["visit","babysit","teach","coach"],"sentence":"My older sister agreed to ______ my two younger brothers this weekend. She'll prepare their meals, help with homework, and put them to bed.","translation":"我的姐姐同意這個週末照顧我的兩個弟弟。她會為他們準備飯菜、幫助他們做功課，並讓他們上床睡覺。","word":"babysit"}},"babysitter":{"createdAt":1781664419993,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"babysitter是指臨時受僱照顧別人孩子的人，通常在父母外出時工作。","options":["teacher","babysitter","nurse","coach"],"sentence":"We hired a ______ to watch our children while we went out for dinner. She arrived at 6 PM and stayed until midnight.","translation":"我們雇了一位保母在我們外出吃飯時照看我們的孩子。她在下午6點到達，一直待到午夜。","word":"babysitter"}},"backyard":{"createdAt":1781792910177,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"backyard是指房屋後面的私人戶外空間，通常用於休閒和娛樂活動。","options":["park","backyard","playground","garden"],"sentence":"The children played soccer in the ______ behind their house. It was surrounded by a fence and had grass and a swing set.","translation":"孩子們在他們家後面的後院裡踢足球。它被柵欄包圍，有草地和秋千。","word":"backyard"}},"bacteria":{"createdAt":1781935654227,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bacteria 是名詞，表示「細菌」，指肉眼看不見的微小單細胞生物，有些對人體有害。","options":["viruses","bacteria","cells","nutrients"],"sentence":"The laboratory technician examined the sample under a microscope to identify the ______ that caused the infection. The results showed harmful microorganisms present in the patient's blood.","translation":"實驗室技術員在顯微鏡下檢查樣本以識別導致感染的細菌。結果顯示患者血液中存在有害的微生物。","word":"bacteria"}},"bait":{"createdAt":1781836375365,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bait是指放在釣鉤或陷阱上用來吸引魚或動物的餌食。","options":["lure","bait","trap","net"],"sentence":"The fisherman used worms as ______ to catch trout in the river. He placed them on the hook before casting his line into the water.","translation":"漁夫用蟲子作為餌來捕捉河裡的鱒魚。他在投竿前把它們放在鉤子上。","word":"bait"}},"baiting":{"createdAt":1781598671083,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"baiting 作名詞表示誘餌或用餌誘捕的行為，指在釣鉤上放置食物以吸引魚或其他動物","options":["decoration","baiting","shelter","camouflage"],"sentence":"The fisherman used live worms as ______ to catch more fish in the river. He cast his line repeatedly with fresh bait to attract the largest species.","translation":"漁夫用活蟲作誘餌在河裡捕更多魚。他反覆用新鮮的餌料投線以吸引最大的物種。","word":"baiting"}},"ballot":{"createdAt":1781499075058,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"不記名投票是選民表達其政治選擇的方式，通常以秘密方式進行。","options":["petition","proposal","ballot","contract"],"sentence":"Citizens cast their ______ to elect the next president of the country. Each voter received a paper form where they marked their choice in complete secrecy.","translation":"公民投票以選舉該國的下一任總統。每位選民都收到了一份紙質表格，在完全保密的情況下標記他們的選擇。","word":"ballot"}},"ban":{"createdAt":1781613179424,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"ban 作名詞時意為禁止或禁令，指官方或權威性的禁令或限制。","options":["permission","requirement","prohibition","recommendation"],"sentence":"The government issued a ______ on smoking in all public spaces starting next month. Violating this new regulation would result in substantial fines for offenders.","translation":"政府發布了從下個月開始在所有公共場所禁止吸煙的禁令。違反這項新規定將對違反者處以巨額罰款。","word":"ban"}},"band":{"createdAt":1781792910172,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"band是指一群演奏音樂的人組成的樂隊或樂團，通常規模比管弦樂團小。","options":["solo","band","orchestra","conductor"],"sentence":"The music students formed a ______ to perform at the school concert. They played guitars, drums, and keyboards together as a group.","translation":"音樂學生組成一個樂隊在學校音樂會上表演。他們一起演奏吉他、鼓和鍵盤。","word":"band"}},"bandage":{"createdAt":1781598671068,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bandage 作名詞表示繃帶，是用於覆蓋和保護傷口的醫療用品","options":["cast","bandage","injection","prescription"],"sentence":"After the nurse applied a clean ______ to the wound, she instructed the patient to keep it dry for three days. The patient followed her advice carefully to ensure proper healing.","translation":"護士在傷口上貼了乾淨的繃帶後，指示患者三天內保持乾燥。患者仔細遵循她的建議以確保適當癒合。","word":"bandage"}},"bandwagon":{"createdAt":1781883441462,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bandwagon 指某種流行的潮流或時尚，人們盲目跟風參與其中","options":["crisis","movement","bandwagon","debate"],"sentence":"Many companies jumped on the sustainability ______ to attract environmentally conscious consumers. Their sudden interest in eco-friendly practices seemed driven more by profit than genuine commitment.","translation":"許多公司跟風做可持續發展的潮流來吸引有環保意識的消費者。他們對環保做法的突然興趣似乎更多是出於利潤而非真正的承諾。","word":"bandwagon"}},"bankrupt":{"createdAt":1781664420007,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bankrupt形容詞表示破產或完全沒有金錢的，通常指無法償還債務。","options":["profitable","bankrupt","successful","expanding"],"sentence":"After years of poor business decisions, the company declared itself ______ and shut down operations. Creditors would receive only a small fraction of what they were owed.","translation":"在多年的糟糕商業決策後，該公司宣布破產並停止運營。債權人只會收到他們應得金額的一小部分。","word":"bankrupt"}},"banner":{"createdAt":1781598671080,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"banner 作名詞表示橫幅或橫布條，是掛起來進行宣傳或示威的大型布料","options":["sign","banner","poster","flag"],"sentence":"The activist group displayed a large ______ across the city hall building to protest government policies. The bold lettering was visible from several blocks away.","translation":"激進分子團體在市政廳大樓上展示了一條大橫幅以抗議政府政策。粗體字可以從幾個街區外看到。","word":"banner"}},"banquet":{"createdAt":1781336858151,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"banquet 是指一場正式的、豪華的宴會，通常為特殊場合舉辦，有多道菜餚和許多賓客。","options":["fight","breakfast","banquet","interview"],"sentence":"The ______ lasted for three hours with multiple courses and fine wines. The president's speech at the end congratulated all the distinguished guests for their contributions.","translation":"這場宴會持續了三個小時，包括多道菜餚和美酒。總統在結束時的演講祝賀了所有尊貴賓客的貢獻。","word":"banquet"}},"barely":{"createdAt":1781860901466,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"barely是副詞，表示幾乎不、勉強地，強調剛好達到標準或幾近失敗","options":["clearly","barely","comfortably","easily"],"sentence":"The student ______ passed the exam with a score of 51 out of 100. He needed at least 50 points to graduate, so he made it by the smallest margin.","translation":"這名學生勉強以100分中的51分通過考試。他需要至少50分才能畢業，所以他以最小的差距成功了。","word":"barely"}},"bargain":{"createdAt":1781664420003,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bargain表示便宜的交易或划算的購買，以低於正常價格獲得商品。","options":["loss","bargain","expense","waste"],"sentence":"She found a great ______ at the thrift store—a designer handbag for only five dollars. It was in perfect condition and normally would have cost hundreds.","translation":"她在舊貨店找到了一個很好的便宜貨—一個名牌手提包只要五塊錢。它的狀況完美，通常要花費數百元。","word":"bargain"}},"bark":{"createdAt":1781784029102,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"howl是狗發出的吠叫聲，符合「吠叫」的定義，特別是指動物發出的高亢叫聲。","options":["trunk","noise","howl","branch"],"sentence":"The dog's loud ______ woke up the entire neighborhood at midnight. When the mailman approached the gate, the animal made that piercing sound again.","translation":"狗的大聲吠叫在午夜時吵醒了整個鄰居。當郵差走近大門時，那隻動物又發出了那刺耳的聲音。","word":"bark"}},"barn":{"createdAt":1781664419992,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"barn是指用來儲存農作物和農具的建築物，通常位於農場上。","options":["house","barn","market","garage"],"sentence":"The farmer stored hay and grain in the old ______ on his property. The structure had large wooden doors and was painted red.","translation":"農民在他的田產上的舊穀倉裡儲存乾草和穀物。這座建築有大木門，被漆成紅色。","word":"barn"}},"barrel":{"createdAt":1781425024015,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"barrel是指大型木製或金屬容器，用來儲存液體或其他物品，通常比瓶子大得多。","options":["bottle","barrel","tank","cask"],"sentence":"The old wooden ______ in the cellar contained vintage wine that had been aging for decades. We carefully rolled it across the stone floor without spilling a single drop of its precious liquid.","translation":"地窖裡的舊木桶裡裝著已陳年數十年的葡萄酒。我們小心地在石地板上滾動它，沒有灑出一滴珍貴的液體。","word":"barrel"}},"barren":{"createdAt":1781664419997,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"barren形容詞表示不毛之地或無法生長植物的地方，引申為貧瘠的。","options":["fertile","barren","green","lush"],"sentence":"The ______ desert stretched for hundreds of miles with no vegetation visible anywhere. Explorers struggled to find water or any signs of life.","translation":"貧瘠的沙漠綿延數百英里，看不到任何植物。探險家們努力尋找水或任何生命的跡象。","word":"barren"}},"barrier":{"createdAt":1781704395610,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"barrier表示「障礙」或「阻礙」，指阻止進展或溝通的事物或情況","options":["adoption","tension","barrier","threshold"],"sentence":"Language differences created a significant ______ between the two international teams trying to collaborate. They eventually hired a professional translator to bridge the communication gap.","translation":"語言差異在試圖合作的兩個國際團隊之間造成了顯著的障礙。他們最終聘請了專業翻譯來橋接溝通差距。","word":"barrier"}},"base":{"createdAt":1781664419998,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"base可指軍事基地或根據地，是進行活動的中心地點。","options":["camp","base","tent","fort"],"sentence":"The team built their military ______ in the valley for strategic advantage. From this location, soldiers could easily defend against enemy attacks from all directions.","translation":"該隊在山谷裡建立了軍事基地以獲得戰略優勢。從這個位置，士兵們可以輕易地防禦來自各個方向的敵人攻擊。","word":"base"}},"basic":{"createdAt":1781613179419,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"basic 意為基礎的或基本的，指必須先學習的最初級和最重要的內容。","options":["advanced","fundamental","complex","specialized"],"sentence":"Learning ______ mathematics skills is essential before students attempt advanced calculus. Without mastery of addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division, higher mathematics becomes impossible.","translation":"在學生嘗試高等微積分之前，學習基本的數學技能是必不可少的。沒有掌握加、減、乘、除，高等數學就變得不可能。","word":"basic"}},"basically":{"createdAt":1781664420006,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"basically是副詞，表示根本上或基本上，用於簡化復雜的信息。","options":["Confusingly","Basically","Mysteriously","Ironically"],"sentence":"______, the project requires three main steps: planning, execution, and review. The other details can be worked out as we progress.","translation":"基本上，這個項目需要三個主要步驟：規劃、執行和審查。其他細節可以在進展過程中逐步解決。","word":"basically"}},"basin":{"createdAt":1781595752118,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"basin 是指用來盛水的盆或碗，通常用於洗漱等日常活動。","options":["bucket","basin","cup","pitcher"],"sentence":"She filled the ______ with water to wash her hands. The ceramic bowl held about two liters of liquid and had a wide opening.","translation":"她用水填滿水盆來洗手。陶製的碗可以容納約兩升液體，開口很寬。","word":"basin"}},"basis":{"createdAt":1781860901467,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"basis表示基礎或基準，指某事物賴以建立或存在的根本","options":["destruction","basis","weakness","conflict"],"sentence":"The ______ of their friendship was built on mutual trust and shared interests. They bonded over their love of reading and hiking.","translation":"他們友誼的基礎建立在相互信任和共同興趣之上。他們因對閱讀和登山的熱愛而結合。","word":"basis"}},"batter":{"createdAt":1781835517797,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"batter 意為接連猛打或反覆擊打，通常用於描述暴力或激烈的打擊行為。","options":["encourage","batter","welcome","support"],"sentence":"The boxer continued to ______ his opponent with powerful punches throughout the match. Each strike was delivered with tremendous force and intensity.","translation":"這位拳擊手在整場比賽中繼續用強大的拳擊猛打對手。每一次打擊都充滿了巨大的力量和強度。","word":"batter"}},"battered":{"createdAt":1781664420001,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"battered形容詞表示被打傷或飽受摧殘，看起來受到了長期的損壞。","options":["new","battered","clean","modern"],"sentence":"The old ______ suitcase had been through dozens of trips around the world. Its corners were dented, its handle was worn, and the locks barely functioned.","translation":"那只舊的飽受摧殘的手提箱經歷過數十次世界各地的旅行。它的角被撞凹了，把手磨損了，鎖幾乎無法正常工作。","word":"battered"}},"battle":{"createdAt":1781664420000,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"battle是戰役或戰鬥，指武裝衝突或爭鬥。","options":["discussion","battle","meeting","celebration"],"sentence":"The two armies fought in a fierce ______ that lasted from dawn until dusk. Hundreds of soldiers were wounded or killed in the conflict.","translation":"兩支軍隊在一場從黎明到黃昏的激烈戰役中交戰。數百名士兵在衝突中受傷或陣亡。","word":"battle"}},"bay":{"createdAt":1781883441462,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bay 是指被陸地部分包圍的大片水域，通常是海岸邊的開放區域","options":["ocean","river","bay","strait"],"sentence":"The pirates hid their ship in a sheltered ______ surrounded by tall cliffs. The protected inlet kept their vessel safe from storms and enemy detection.","translation":"海盜把船隻藏在被高聳懸崖包圍的海灣裡。受保護的海灣入口使他們的船隻免受風暴和敵人偵測的危害。","word":"bay"}},"bead":{"createdAt":1781664420006,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bead是珠子，通常用於製作珠寶或裝飾品。","options":["stone","bead","coin","button"],"sentence":"She threaded tiny ______ onto a string to create a beautiful necklace. Each ______ was a different color, arranged in a perfect pattern.","translation":"她把小珠子穿在繩子上製作漂亮的項鍊。每顆珠子都是不同的顏色，排列成完美的圖案。","word":"bead"}},"beam":{"createdAt":1781359980248,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"beam作為名詞指光線、光束或光柱；特指一條直線的、集中的光線或粒子流。","options":["shadow","beam","reflection","filter"],"sentence":"A ______ of sunlight streamed through the window and illuminated the entire room. The golden light created a beautiful pattern on the wooden floor.","translation":"一束陽光透過窗戶射進來，照亮了整個房間。金色的光線在木地板上創造了美麗的圖案。","word":"beam"}},"bear":{"createdAt":1781582619550,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bear 在此意為承受或忍受（困難、責任或負擔），表示承載和承受的能力。","options":["avoid","ignore","bear","refuse"],"sentence":"The mother had to ______ the heavy responsibility of raising her children alone after her husband passed away. She worked multiple jobs to provide food, shelter, and education for her family.","translation":"母親在丈夫去世後必須獨自承受撫養孩子的沉重責任。她做多份工作以為家人提供食物、住所和教育。","word":"bear"}},"bearing":{"createdAt":1781257238305,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bearing指人的舉止、風度或姿態，反映了一個人的行為表現和氣質。","options":["weight","bearing","costume","voice"],"sentence":"The elderly gentleman's dignified ______ impressed everyone in the room. His posture was straight, his movements were graceful, and he spoke with confidence and respect.","translation":"這位年邁紳士的高尚舉止給房間裡的每個人都留下了深刻印象。他的姿態筆直，動作優雅，說話時充滿信心和尊重。","word":"bearing"}},"beetle":{"createdAt":1781664419997,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"beetle是甲蟲，一種有硬殼翅膀的昆蟲。","options":["butterfly","beetle","bee","ant"],"sentence":"A large black ______ crawled across the garden path near the flowers. The insect had a hard shell and six legs like all members of its species.","translation":"一隻大黑甲蟲爬過花園小徑旁邊。這種昆蟲有硬殼和六條腿，就像它同類的所有成員一樣。","word":"beetle"}},"beggar":{"createdAt":1781664420004,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"beggar是乞丐，指向他人乞討或要求施捨的人。","options":["merchant","beggar","musician","vendor"],"sentence":"A poor ______ sat on the street corner asking passersby for spare change. He had been homeless for several years.","translation":"一個窮乞丐坐在街角向行人乞討零錢。他已經無家可歸好幾年了。","word":"beggar"}},"behalf":{"createdAt":1781601735989,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"「behalf」表示代表某人或為了某人的利益，通常與「on behalf of」搭配使用，表示代表他人採取行動。","options":["behalf","authority","behalf","expense"],"sentence":"The lawyer spoke on ______ of his client during the court hearing. He presented arguments and evidence to defend the defendant's interests.","translation":"律師在法庭聽證會上代表他的委託人發言。他提出了論點和證據來為被告的利益辯護。","word":"behalf"}},"behavior":{"createdAt":1781792910185,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"behavior是指一個人的行為舉止和所有外顯的動作表現，包括言語和身體行為。","options":["appearance","behavior","schedule","homework"],"sentence":"The teacher was concerned about the student's ______ in class. He was constantly disrupting lessons, talking back to authority, and not following rules.","translation":"老師對這名學生在課堂上的行為感到擔憂。他不斷打擾上課、頂嘴和不遵守規則。","word":"behavior"}},"behavioral":{"createdAt":1781664420003,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"behavioral形容詞指與行為或舉止相關的，通常用於心理學或教育領域。","options":["physical","behavioral","nutritional","financial"],"sentence":"The psychologist studied ______ patterns in children to understand how they learn and develop. She observed their interactions during play sessions.","translation":"心理學家研究兒童的行為模式以了解他們如何學習和發展。她在遊戲過程中觀察了他們的互動。","word":"behavioral"}},"belong":{"createdAt":1781664420003,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"belong動詞表示歸屬於或屬於某人，表達所有權或歸屬關係。","options":["fit","belong","matter","appear"],"sentence":"This book doesn't ______ to me; it must ______ to someone else in the library. I'll return it to the lost and found.","translation":"這本書不屬於我；它一定屬於圖書館裡的其他人。我會把它交給失物招領處。","word":"belong"}},"belongings":{"createdAt":1781664420002,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"belongings是名詞複數，指某人擁有的個人物品或財產。","options":["furniture","belongings","decorations","equipment"],"sentence":"When she moved to a new apartment, she packed all her ______ into cardboard boxes. Her clothes, books, and personal items filled the entire truck.","translation":"當她搬到新公寓時，她把所有的物品裝進紙箱。她的衣服、書籍和個人物品裝滿了整輛卡車。","word":"belongings"}},"beloved":{"createdAt":1781664420005,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"beloved形容詞表示深受喜愛的或心愛的，通常用於形容受人尊敬的人。","options":["disliked","beloved","new","absent"],"sentence":"The ______ teacher retired after forty years of service to the school. Students gathered to celebrate her career and express their gratitude.","translation":"這位深受喜愛的教師在為學校服務四十年後退休。學生們聚在一起慶祝她的事業並表達感謝。","word":"beloved"}},"bend":{"createdAt":1781841148118,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bend 動詞意思是使彎曲、彎腰，指改變直線形狀或向下傾身的動作。","options":["straighten","bend","lift","stretch"],"sentence":"The acrobat had to ______ her body into impossible positions during the circus performance. She twisted and contorted herself so extremely that her head nearly touched her knees.","translation":"雜技演員必須在馬戲團表演中將身體彎曲成不可能的姿勢。她扭轉自己的身體到極端，使得她的頭幾乎接觸到膝蓋。","word":"bend"}},"beneath":{"createdAt":1781336858149,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"beneath 是介詞，表示在某物的下方或下面，通常帶有被覆蓋或隱藏的含義。","options":["above","beside","beneath","within"],"sentence":"The ancient ruins lay ______ the surface of the desert sand. Archaeologists used special equipment to excavate the buried structures from deep underground.","translation":"古代遺跡位於沙漠沙子表面的下方。考古學家使用特殊設備從地下深處挖掘埋藏的結構。","word":"beneath"}},"benefit":{"createdAt":1781437435166,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"benefit 作為動詞表示有益於或對某人有好處；作為名詞表示利益或優勢。","options":["harm","benefit","confuse","ignore"],"sentence":"Regular exercise can greatly ______ your physical and mental health over time. Studies show that people who exercise consistently enjoy lower stress levels and better energy.","translation":"定期運動可以大大有益於你隨著時間推移的身體和心理健康。研究表明，經常運動的人享受更低的壓力水平和更好的能量。","word":"benefit"}},"beside":{"createdAt":1781672973721,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"beside作為前置詞表示「在…旁邊；在…附近」，指兩人或兩物相鄰的空間位置。","options":["beyond","beside","between","below"],"sentence":"She sat ______ her grandmother on the park bench, holding her hand gently. They enjoyed the peaceful moment together, listening to the birds sing.","translation":"她坐在她祖母身邊的公園長凳上，輕輕握著她的手。他們一起享受寧靜的時刻，聆聽鳥兒唱歌。","word":"beside"}},"besides":{"createdAt":1781672973719,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"besides作為前置詞表示「除…之外；再加上」，用來列舉額外的事項。","options":["Despite","Besides","Between","Behind"],"sentence":"______ studying mathematics, she also excels in literature and history. Her well-rounded education made her one of the most accomplished students in her class.","translation":"除了學習數學，她在文學和歷史方面也表現出色。她全面的教育使她成為班級中最優秀的學生之一。","word":"besides"}},"besiege":{"createdAt":1781417610416,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"besiege可以指用大量的事物圍困或騷擾某人，使其受到困擾。","options":["praise","ignore","besiege","motivate"],"sentence":"Complaints from customers continued to ______ the company's management every single day. The overwhelming volume of grievances made it impossible for executives to focus on other business matters.","translation":"顧客的投訴每天都在不斷地煩擾公司的管理層。大量的抱怨使主管們無法專注於其他業務事項。","word":"besiege"}},"betray":{"createdAt":1781709854486,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"betray（背叛）指對國家或他人不忠，與selling secrets to the enemy（向敵人出售秘密）和treacherous actions（叛國行為）的語境直接相關。","options":["betray","protect","defend","support"],"sentence":"The spy agreed to ______ his country by selling classified military secrets to the enemy. His treacherous actions resulted in the capture of innocent soldiers and the loss of strategic advantage.","translation":"間諜通過向敵人出售機密軍事情報同意背叛他的國家。他的叛國行為導致無辜士兵被俘虜，戰略優勢喪失。","word":"betray"}},"betrayal":{"createdAt":1781613113009,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"betrayal 表示背叛、違背信任或出賣某人的行為","options":["loyalty","betrayal","support","honesty"],"sentence":"His ______ of his best friend was the most painful decision he ever made. Finding out that he had revealed confidential secrets to their enemies broke the friendship forever.","translation":"他對最好朋友的背叛是他做過最痛苦的決定。發現他向敵人透露了機密秘密永遠破壞了這段友誼。","word":"betrayal"}},"beware":{"createdAt":1781792910182,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"beware是動詞，意思是「當心」或「提防」，用來警告他人注意危險。","options":["welcome","beware","enjoy","admire"],"sentence":"The sign read \"______ of the dog\" at the entrance to the property. The owner wanted visitors to know that a dangerous animal lived there.","translation":"入口處的標誌寫著「當心狗」。房主想讓訪客知道這裡住著一隻危險的動物。","word":"beware"}},"beyond":{"createdAt":1781362281656,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"beyond表示在...更遠處或超越某個限度。","options":["within","beyond","beside","along"],"sentence":"The mountain range extends far ______ what we can see from this valley. The peaks continue for hundreds of kilometers into the distance.","translation":"山脈延伸到我們從這個山谷看不到的地方。這些山峰繼續向遠處延伸數百公里。","word":"beyond"}},"bias":{"createdAt":1781672973733,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bias是名詞，表示「成見；偏見」，指對人或事物的不公正或不理性的傾向。","options":["fairness","bias","kindness","patience"],"sentence":"The judge's ______ towards the wealthy defendant was evident in his lenient verdict. Critics argued that justice should be fair to everyone regardless of their economic status.","translation":"法官對富有被告的偏見在他寬恕的判決中顯而易見。評論者辯稱司法應該對每個人都公平，無論其經濟地位如何。","word":"bias"}},"biased":{"createdAt":1781613113016,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"biased 形容有成見、偏見或不公正的態度","options":["fair","biased","careful","reasonable"],"sentence":"The judge was criticized for making a ______ decision that favored the wealthy defendant. His prejudice against poor people clearly influenced his verdict.","translation":"法官因做出有利於富有被告的成見決定而受到批評。他對窮人的偏見明顯影響了他的判決。","word":"biased"}},"bilateral":{"createdAt":1781484539655,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bilateral 表示涉及或由兩方面組成，強調雙方的平等合作和相互同意，常用於國際協議和關係。","options":["unilateral","trilateral","bilateral","multilateral"],"sentence":"The two countries signed a ______ trade agreement to benefit both nations equally. Neither country had power over the other in this mutual arrangement.","translation":"兩個國家簽署了一項雙邊貿易協議，使兩個國家都受益平等。在這個互利的安排中，任何一個國家都沒有優勢。","word":"bilateral"}},"bin":{"createdAt":1781613113025,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bin 是垃圾桶或容器，用於存放廢棄物品","options":["drawer","shelf","bin","cup"],"sentence":"He threw the empty soda can into the ______ after finishing his drink. The recycling receptacle was conveniently located near the park bench.","translation":"他喝完飲料後將空罐扔進了垃圾桶。回收容器方便地位於公園長椅附近。","word":"bin"}},"bind":{"createdAt":1781779647043,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bind表示用繩子或其他物品捆綁或束縛某物","options":["separate","bind","open","paint"],"sentence":"We need to ______ these boxes together with rope. The delivery company requires all packages to be secured for transport.","translation":"我們需要用繩子將這些盒子綁在一起。快遞公司要求所有包裹在運輸時必須固定好。","word":"bind"}},"biodegradable":{"createdAt":1781437528473,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"biodegradable 表示能被微生物分解並回歸自然環境，通常用來描述環保的材料。","options":["durable","biodegradable","flexible","waterproof"],"sentence":"These ______ plastic bags will break down naturally within a few months. Unlike regular plastics that take hundreds of years to decompose, this material was specifically designed to return to the earth quickly.","translation":"這些可生物分解的塑膠袋將在幾個月內自然分解。與需要數百年才能分解的普通塑膠不同，這種材料是專門設計來快速回歸自然的。","word":"biodegradable"}},"biography":{"createdAt":1781613113008,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"biography 是傳記，記述某人真實的人生故事和經歷","options":["novel","article","biography","diary"],"sentence":"The author spent five years writing a detailed ______ of the famous musician. The book covered every major event in his life from childhood until his death.","translation":"作者花了五年時間寫一部關於著名音樂家的詳細傳記。這本書涵蓋了他從童年到去世的每一個重要事件。","word":"biography"}},"biology":{"createdAt":1781664419994,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"biology是研究生命和生物體的科學學科。","options":["chemistry","biology","physics","geology"],"sentence":"Sarah chose to study ______ in university because she was fascinated by living organisms. She spent hours in the laboratory examining cells under microscopes.","translation":"莎拉選擇在大學裡研究生物學，因為她對生物體很著迷。她花了數小時在實驗室裡用顯微鏡檢查細胞。","word":"biology"}},"biscuit":{"createdAt":1781257238303,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"biscuit指一種烘焙的、通常是酥脆的麵粉製食品，可以甜也可以鹹。","options":["sandwich","biscuit","soup","salad"],"sentence":"For breakfast, Tom enjoyed a warm ______ with butter and jam. He ate the crispy, golden-brown pastry in just two bites.","translation":"早餐時，湯姆享用了一塊塗有黃油和果醬的溫暖餅乾。他兩口就吃完了這個酥脆的金黃色烘焙食品。","word":"biscuit"}},"bitter":{"createdAt":1781792910184,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bitter在這裡表示因失望或不公平待遇而產生的持久怨恨和極為不滿的情感。","options":["happy","bitter","neutral","indifferent"],"sentence":"She felt ______ about losing the promotion to her colleague. She couldn't forget the disappointment and harbored negative feelings for months.","translation":"她對失去升職機會給了同事而感到怨恨。她無法忘記失望，並在幾個月內心懷不滿。","word":"bitter"}},"blackout":{"createdAt":1781664420004,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blackout是指大範圍停電或電力中斷的情況。","options":["sunrise","blackout","celebration","parade"],"sentence":"The entire city experienced a ______ when the power plant malfunctioned. All the streets went dark and traffic lights stopped working.","translation":"當發電廠故障時，整個城市經歷了停電。所有街道都陷入黑暗，紅綠燈停止工作。","word":"blackout"}},"blade":{"createdAt":1781484415207,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blade是指刀具或工具的切割部分，通常是鋒利的扁平部分。","options":["handle","blade","blade","tip"],"sentence":"He carefully sharpened the ______ of his knife before cutting the vegetables. The razor-sharp edge made slicing through the tomatoes effortless.","translation":"他在切蔬菜前仔細磨尖了他的刀片。鋒利的邊緣使切番茄變得毫不費力。","word":"blade"}},"blame":{"createdAt":1781613179412,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"blame 意為歸咎於或責怪，通常與對某人的不滿或指責相關聯。","options":["criticize","praise","accuse","punish"],"sentence":"The coach refused to ______ the team for the loss, saying it was his responsibility. He took full accountability for the poor strategy he had implemented.","translation":"教練拒絕指責球隊的失敗，說這是他的責任。他為自己實施的糟糕策略承擔了全部責任。","word":"blame"}},"blank":{"createdAt":1781613179418,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blank 作形容詞時意為空白的或無內容的，描述一個沒有任何文字或內容的表面。","options":["written","empty","filled","printed"],"sentence":"The student stared at the ______ page for several minutes, unable to write anything. She had completely forgotten what she studied the night before.","translation":"學生盯著空白的頁面看了幾分鐘，無法寫下任何東西。她完全忘記了前一晚學習的內容。","word":"blank"}},"blanket":{"createdAt":1781613113010,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blanket 作為名詞指毛毯或毯子，用來保暖","options":["pillow","blanket","curtain","rug"],"sentence":"She wrapped herself in a warm ______ to stay cozy on the cold winter night. The thick woolen cover was perfect for keeping her comfortable while she slept.","translation":"她用溫暖的毛毯包裹自己，在寒冷的冬夜保持舒適。厚重的羊毛覆蓋物非常適合讓她睡覺時舒服。","word":"blanket"}},"blare":{"createdAt":1781425024016,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blare是指發出刺耳、刺鼻、令人不快的大聲音，通常用來描述喇叭或警報等聲音。","options":["whisper","blare","hum","beep"],"sentence":"The car horns began to ______ loudly as traffic backed up on the highway during rush hour. The deafening noise was so piercing and harsh that everyone covered their ears in discomfort.","translation":"車子喇叭在尖峰時段高速公路交通堵塞時開始發出刺耳的聲音。這震耳欲聾的噪音如此刺耳刺鼻，以至於每個人都摀住耳朵感到不舒服。","word":"blare"}},"blast":{"createdAt":1781613179424,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"blast 作動詞時意為炸毀或爆破，通常指使用炸藥或強大的力量摧毀某物。","options":["drill","excavate","demolish","smooth"],"sentence":"The construction crew used explosives to ______ the rock formation so they could build the new highway. The controlled demolition was carefully planned to ensure no nearby buildings were damaged.","translation":"建築隊使用炸藥爆破岩石地層，以便能夠建設新的高速公路。受控爆破經過精心規劃，以確保附近建築物不會受到損害。","word":"blast"}},"blaze":{"createdAt":1781746848181,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blaze 表示「烈火」或「熊熊燃燒」，描述強烈而明亮的火焰現象。","options":["breeze","blaze","drizzle","shadow"],"sentence":"The forest fire created a massive ______ that could be seen from miles away. The intense heat and bright flames illuminated the entire night sky.","translation":"森林火災造成了一場大火，從幾英里外都能看到。強烈的熱度和明亮的火焰照亮了整個夜空。","word":"blaze"}},"blazing":{"createdAt":1781840667143,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blazing用來形容極其炎熱、明亮或強烈的事物，特別是光線或火焰的強度。","options":["cold","blazing","distant","pale"],"sentence":"The ______ sun beat down on the desert, making it almost impossible to see. The temperature reached 50 degrees Celsius that day.","translation":"烈日驕陽照射在沙漠上，使得幾乎無法看清。那天氣溫達到攝氏50度。","word":"blazing"}},"bleach":{"createdAt":1781429945500,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bleach 作為動詞表示使褪色或使色彩變淡，通常由於陽光或化學物質的作用。","options":["strengthen","bleach","protect","darken"],"sentence":"The strong sunlight will ______ the colors of your curtains if you leave them in the window for too long. After just a few months, the vibrant red fabric had faded to a pale pink.","translation":"如果你長時間把窗簾放在窗邊，強烈的陽光會使它褪色。僅僅幾個月後，鮮豔的紅色布料就褪成了淡粉紅色。","word":"bleach"}},"bleached":{"createdAt":1781613179413,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bleached 意為漂白的或褪色的，描述經過漂白或日曬而失去原有顏色的物體。","options":["painted","strengthened","lightened","reinforced"],"sentence":"The old wooden fence had a ______ appearance after years of exposure to the sun. The wood had lost all its original dark color and turned pale.","translation":"經過多年日曬後，老舊的木製圍欄呈現褪色的外觀。木頭失去了所有原有的深色，變成了蒼白色。","word":"bleached"}},"bleed":{"createdAt":1781672973729,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bleed是動詞，表示「流血；出血」，指血液從身體傷口流出。","options":["heal","bleed","itch","fade"],"sentence":"After the accident, the wound began to ______ heavily and wouldn't stop. He rushed to the hospital to get medical attention immediately.","translation":"事故發生後，傷口開始大量流血，停不下來。他立即衝往醫院尋求醫療救助。","word":"bleed"}},"blend":{"createdAt":1781272410984,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blend是指將不同的物質或成分混合在一起，使其成為一個整體。","options":["separate","blend","bake","measure"],"sentence":"The chef will ______ the flour, eggs, and milk to create the cake batter. After stirring for several minutes, all ingredients become a smooth, uniform mixture.","translation":"廚師將麵粉、雞蛋和牛奶混合在一起製作蛋糕麵糊。攪拌幾分鐘後，所有材料變成光滑均勻的混合物。","word":"blend"}},"blended":{"createdAt":1781664419999,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blended是blend的過去式或形容詞，表示混合或混在一起。","options":["sliced","blended","heated","froze"],"sentence":"She ______ the fruit smoothie until it was completely smooth and creamy. The mixture of strawberries, bananas, and yogurt combined perfectly.","translation":"她混合果汁冰沙，直到它完全光滑和奶油狀。草莓、香蕉和酸奶的混合物完美結合。","word":"blended"}},"bless":{"createdAt":1781274836867,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bless作為動詞表示祝福或祈求神聖力量保佑某人或某物，通常在宗教或正式場合使用。","options":["curse","name","bless","baptize"],"sentence":"The priest came to ______ the newborn baby during the religious ceremony. He made the sign of the cross and spoke sacred words to invoke divine protection.","translation":"牧師在宗教儀式中來祝福新生兒。他畫了十字聖號並說出神聖的話語來祈求神聖的保護。","word":"bless"}},"blessed":{"createdAt":1781613113005,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blessed 表示感到被祝福、蒙受幸運和恩惠的狀態","options":["cursed","blessed","tired","confused"],"sentence":"She felt truly ______ when she held her newborn baby for the first time. The joy and gratitude she experienced made her realize how fortunate her life had become.","translation":"當她第一次抱著新生嬰兒時，她感到真正的蒙福。她所經歷的喜悅和感恩讓她意識到她的人生變得多麼幸運。","word":"blessed"}},"blessing":{"createdAt":1781613113014,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blessing 是祝福或天賜的福氣，表示值得感恩的好事","options":["curse","blessing","burden","problem"],"sentence":"She considered her good health to be a true ______ in her life. She thanked God every day for this precious gift.","translation":"她認為自己的健康是人生中真正的祝福。她每天都為這份寶貴的禮物感謝上帝。","word":"blessing"}},"blink":{"createdAt":1781779647050,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blink在此表示漠視或逃避困難，引申自眨眼的習慣動作","options":["laugh","blink","smile","wave"],"sentence":"She refused to ______ at the difficult challenge ahead. Her determination showed that she was ready to face anything.","translation":"她對前面的困難挑戰毫不退縮。她的決心表明她已準備好面對任何事情。","word":"blink"}},"bloody":{"createdAt":1781664419996,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bloody形容詞表示涉及流血或暴力的，通常用來描述殘忍或激烈的事件。","options":["peaceful","bloody","brief","distant"],"sentence":"The ______ battle lasted three days and resulted in heavy casualties on both sides. Soldiers had to retreat and regroup after the intense fighting.","translation":"血腥的戰役持續了三天，雙方都遭受了重大傷亡。士兵們在激烈的戰鬥後不得不撤退並重新集結。","word":"bloody"}},"bloom":{"createdAt":1781792910183,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bloom是指花卉開放和綻放，表示植物生長期間的一個自然過程。","options":["wilt","bloom","fall","rot"],"sentence":"The cherry tree will ______ in early spring with beautiful pink flowers. The flowers will appear on all the branches within a few weeks.","translation":"櫻花樹將在早春開花，綻放美麗的粉紅色花朵。花朵將在幾週內出現在所有樹枝上。","word":"bloom"}},"blooming":{"createdAt":1781613113011,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blooming 形容繁盛、興旺、充滿活力的狀態","options":["dead","blooming","withered","empty"],"sentence":"The ______ garden was filled with colorful flowers and thriving plants everywhere. Every corner showed signs of vibrant growth and prosperity.","translation":"興旺的花園到處都是五顏六色的花朵和生長茂盛的植物。每個角落都顯示出生機勃勃的增長和繁榮。","word":"blooming"}},"blossom":{"createdAt":1781613179415,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blossom 作動詞時意為開花或繁榮，常用來描述花朵綻放或事物發展良好。","options":["grow","bloom","fade","wilt"],"sentence":"The cherry trees in the park began to ______ in early spring, creating a beautiful pink landscape. Thousands of visitors came to enjoy the spectacular floral display.","translation":"公園裡的櫻花樹在早春時開始開花，創造了一個美麗的粉紅色景觀。數千名遊客前來欣賞這壯觀的花卉展示。","word":"blossom"}},"blow":{"createdAt":1781613179425,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"blow 作名詞時意為猛擊或打擊，通常指身體上的重擊或精神上的打擊。","options":["breeze","kiss","punch","whistle"],"sentence":"The fighter received a ______ to the head during the match, causing him to stumble backward. The impact was so powerful that it knocked him down to the canvas.","translation":"拳擊手在比賽中頭部受到了猛擊，導致他向後跌倒。這一擊的力量非常大，把他打倒在畫布上。","word":"blow"}},"blunt":{"createdAt":1781672973728,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blunt是形容詞，表示「鈍的，不鋒利的」，指工具或物體的邊緣不尖銳。","options":["sharp","blunt","serrated","pointed"],"sentence":"The knife had become ______ after years of use without sharpening. I couldn't cut the bread properly no matter how hard I pressed down.","translation":"這把刀經過多年使用而沒有磨利後已經變鈍了。無論我多用力按下，我都無法正確地切麵包。","word":"blunt"}},"blurred":{"createdAt":1781564440927,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blurred 作形容詞表示模糊的、不清楚的，指邊界或細節不分明。","options":["sharp","blurred","bright","focused"],"sentence":"The photograph came out ______ because the camera moved during the shot. The image was so unclear that we couldn't identify the subject properly.","translation":"照片出來時模糊不清，因為拍攝時相機移動了。影像非常不清楚，我們無法正確識別主體。","word":"blurred"}},"blush":{"createdAt":1781864339054,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"blush表示因羞愧、害羞或尷尬而臉部發紅。","options":["smile","blush","frown","nod"],"sentence":"When the teacher asked her a difficult question in front of the whole class, she began to ______. Her face turned bright red because she was embarrassed about not knowing the answer.","translation":"當老師在全班面前問她一個困難的問題時，她開始臉紅。她的臉變得通紅，因為她對不知道答案感到尷尬。","word":"blush"}},"board":{"createdAt":1781256485490,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"board在此指的是公司的董事會，由董事組成的管理機構","options":["schedule","board","office","meeting"],"sentence":"The company's ______ met to discuss the quarterly financial results. The directors and executives reviewed all major decisions made during the past three months.","translation":"公司的董事會召開會議討論季度財務成果。董事和高管們審查了過去三個月做出的所有重大決定。","word":"board"}},"boil":{"createdAt":1781779647054,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"boil表示液體加熱達到沸點，產生氣泡並蒸發","options":["freeze","boil","cool","evaporate"],"sentence":"The water will ______ in about five minutes. Once it reaches 100 degrees Celsius, you can add the pasta.","translation":"水將在約五分鐘後煮沸。一旦達到攝氏100度，你就可以加入意粉。","word":"boil"}},"bold":{"createdAt":1781414884514,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bold在排版中指字體粗的、粗體的，透過增加字體粗細來使文字更加醒目。","options":["itchy","bright","bold","soft"],"sentence":"The designer made the title ______ so it would stand out on the page. She increased the font weight to make sure readers would notice it immediately.","translation":"設計師把標題設成粗體，這樣它就會在頁面上突出來。她增加了字體的粗細，確保讀者會立即注意到它。","word":"bold"}},"bomb":{"createdAt":1781672973731,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bomb是名詞，表示「炸彈」，也可作動詞表示「轟炸；砲轟」。","options":["gift","bomb","letter","package"],"sentence":"The military launched a ______ at the enemy's ammunition depot to destroy their supplies. The explosion was so powerful that it was heard from miles away.","translation":"軍隊向敵人的彈藥庫投擲炸彈，以摧毀他們的補給品。爆炸威力之大，距離幾英里外都能聽到。","word":"bomb"}},"bond":{"createdAt":1781613113026,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bond 表示連結、聯繫或人之間的深厚關係","options":["distance","conflict","bond","competition"],"sentence":"The strong ______ between the two sisters was evident in how they supported each other. They shared everything and were always there for one another.","translation":"兩個姐妹之間的強大紐帶從她們互相支持的方式中顯而易見。她們分享一切，總是彼此幫助。","word":"bond"}},"bonds":{"createdAt":1781664419994,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bonds在金融語境中指債券，是政府或公司發行的借貸工具。","options":["stocks","bonds","coins","medals"],"sentence":"The government issued ______ as a way to raise money from investors. These financial instruments promised to pay interest over a fixed period.","translation":"政府發行債券作為從投資者籌集資金的方式。這些金融工具承諾在固定期限內支付利息。","word":"bonds"}},"bonus":{"createdAt":1781443653208,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bonus指的是除了基本薪資之外的額外獎勵金或紅利，通常是作為表現優異的獎勵。","options":["penalty","bonus","deduction","fine"],"sentence":"The company gave each employee a generous ______ for exceeding sales targets this quarter. The extra payment was distributed in addition to their regular monthly salaries.","translation":"公司因員工這季超額完成銷售目標而給予每位員工慷慨的獎金。這筆額外款項是在他們定期月薪之外另行發放的。","word":"bonus"}},"bony":{"createdAt":1781672973723,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bony是形容詞，表示「瘦削的；皮包骨頭的」，形容身體消瘦或身上骨頭明顯。","options":["robust","bony","muscular","plump"],"sentence":"The old man had a ______ frame, as if he hadn't eaten well in years. His thin, angular appearance showed the effects of poverty and malnutrition.","translation":"這位老人體型瘦削，好像多年沒吃過好東西。他瘦弱而棱角分明的外表顯示了貧困和營養不良的影響。","word":"bony"}},"booklet":{"createdAt":1781598671172,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"booklet 作名詞表示小冊子，是一份較小的印刷出版物，通常包含關於特定主題的信息","options":["newspaper","booklet","poster","billboard"],"sentence":"The museum distributed a ______ to visitors containing information about the historical exhibits. The small publication included maps, descriptions, and interesting facts about each gallery.","translation":"博物館向遊客分發了一本小冊子，其中包含有關歷史展覽的信息。這份小出版物包括地圖、描述和有關每個畫廊的有趣事實。","word":"booklet"}},"boom":{"createdAt":1781613113014,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"boom 作為名詞表示經濟繁榮或快速發展時期","options":["recession","boom","depression","decline"],"sentence":"The economy experienced a rapid ______ during the late 1990s. Businesses expanded, unemployment fell, and consumer spending reached record levels.","translation":"經濟在1990年代後期經歷了快速繁榮。企業擴張，失業率下降，消費者支出達到創紀錄水平。","word":"boom"}},"boost":{"createdAt":1781883441463,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"boost 意指提升、增加或促進某事物的增長或改善","options":["reduce","maintain","boost","predict"],"sentence":"The new advertising campaign helped ______ the company's sales by thirty percent. The increased brand visibility significantly improved their quarterly revenue.","translation":"新的廣告活動幫助該公司的銷售額提升了百分之三十。增加的品牌知名度顯著改善了他們的季度收入。","word":"boost"}},"border":{"createdAt":1781613113028,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"border 是邊界或國家之間的分界線","options":["ocean","border","river","road"],"sentence":"The two countries share a long ______ that has been disputed for centuries. Soldiers guard the line that separates their territories.","translation":"這兩個國家共享一條長期有爭議的邊界。士兵守衛著將其領土分開的邊界線。","word":"border"}},"bore":{"createdAt":1781613179414,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bore 作動詞時意為忍受或使厭倦，通常用來表達不能再接受某種負面情況。","options":["enjoy","tolerate","appreciate","remember"],"sentence":"She could no longer ______ the endless complaints from her colleagues every day. She finally decided to look for a new job where the environment would be more positive.","translation":"她再也無法忍受同事每天無休止的抱怨。她最終決定尋找一份新工作，在那裡環境會更加積極。","word":"bore"}},"bosom":{"createdAt":1781613113027,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bosom 指前胸、乳房或胸懷，常用於表示親密或溫暖的懷抱","options":["shoulder","lap","bosom","side"],"sentence":"She hugged her child close to her ______ and whispered reassuring words. The intimate embrace conveyed her deep maternal love.","translation":"她把孩子緊緊抱在胸懷，低聲說著安慰的話。這個親密的擁抱傳達了她深深的母愛。","word":"bosom"}},"bother":{"createdAt":1781746848178,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bother 表示「打擾」或「煩惱」，在此句中表示不要干擾或騷擾某人的工作。","options":["help","bother","encourage","assist"],"sentence":"Don't ______ me while I'm working on this important project. I need complete silence and concentration to finish it on time.","translation":"當我在做這個重要專案時，不要打擾我。我需要完全的安靜和專注來按時完成。","word":"bother"}},"boulevard":{"createdAt":1781613179423,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"boulevard 意為大道或大街，通常指寬闊、優美且常有樹木或商店的城市街道。","options":["alley","avenue","parking lot","tunnel"],"sentence":"The wide ______ was lined with trees and outdoor cafés, making it a perfect place for an evening stroll. Many locals gathered there on weekends to enjoy the street performers and fresh air.","translation":"寬闊的大街兩旁排滿了樹木和露天咖啡館，是晚間散步的完美地點。許多當地人在週末聚集在那裡欣賞街頭表演和新鮮空氣。","word":"boulevard"}},"bounce":{"createdAt":1781564440915,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bounce 作名詞表示彈力、彈性，指物體反彈的能力或動作。","options":["softness","bounce","weight","color"],"sentence":"The basketball had a good ______ when it hit the floor. We could hear it spring back up repeatedly with energy.","translation":"籃球掉到地上時有很好的彈跳。我們可以聽到它反覆有力地彈起來。","word":"bounce"}},"bound":{"createdAt":1781613113015,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bound 形容即將前往某地或肯定會發生的狀態","options":["staying","bound","thinking","worried"],"sentence":"With her suitcase packed and tickets in hand, she was ______ for Paris tomorrow morning. The excitement of her upcoming trip kept her awake all night.","translation":"她的行李已收拾好，機票已在手，她明早即將前往巴黎。即將到來的旅行的興奮使她整夜未眠。","word":"bound"}},"boundary":{"createdAt":1781779647057,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"boundary表示分界線或範圍的邊界，用於劃分不同的區域","options":["bridge","boundary","connection","wall"],"sentence":"The ______ between the two countries was established by the treaty. It runs through the river and is marked with official border posts.","translation":"兩國之間的分界線是由條約確立的。它穿過河流並標有官方邊界哨所。","word":"boundary"}},"bow":{"createdAt":1781767999773,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bow 在這裡指的是弓樂器（如小提琴弓），用來在弦樂器上拉奏音樂。","options":["arrow","gesture","bow","knot"],"sentence":"The musician picked up her ______ and prepared to play the violin concerto. She drew it smoothly across the strings to create beautiful melodies.","translation":"音樂家拿起她的弓，準備演奏小提琴協奏曲。她光滑地用它在琴弦上拉動，創造出美妙的旋律。","word":"bow"}},"boxing":{"createdAt":1781613050059,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"boxing是指拳擊運動，通常涉及兩個人戴著手套在拳擊台上互相對打，或者個人在訓練時練習打拳技巧。","options":["swimming","boxing","dancing","cooking"],"sentence":"My brother trains in ______ three times a week at the local gym. He wears protective gloves and a headgear while practicing punching combinations with his coach.","translation":"我的哥哥每週在當地健身房訓練拳擊三次。他在與教練練習打拳組合時穿著保護手套和頭盔。","word":"boxing"}},"boycott":{"createdAt":1781883441457,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"boycott 意指拒絕購買或參與某事物，作為抗議或反對的方式","options":["promote","boycott","advertise","merge"],"sentence":"Environmental activists decided to ______ companies that use excessive plastic packaging. They organized a campaign encouraging consumers to stop purchasing their products entirely.","translation":"環保運動人士決定抵制使用過量塑膠包裝的公司。他們組織了一項運動，鼓勵消費者完全停止購買這些產品。","word":"boycott"}},"brag":{"createdAt":1781672973725,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"brag是動詞，表示「吹牛」，指自誇或誇大自己的成就和擁有物。","options":["hide","brag","whisper","complain"],"sentence":"He couldn't help but ______ about his new sports car to all his friends. Everyone at the party grew tired of hearing him boast about its expensive features.","translation":"他忍不住向所有朋友吹牛他的新跑車。派對上的每個人都厭倦了聽他吹噓它昂貴的功能。","word":"brag"}},"braid":{"createdAt":1781363994347,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"braid作為動詞表示將線、髮絲等編織在一起，形成交叉的裝飾圖案或辮子。","options":["tear","weave","cut","stitch"],"sentence":"She used colorful thread to ______ a decorative border around the edge of the quilt. The intricate woven pattern added elegance to the handmade blanket.","translation":"她用彩色線條在棉被邊緣編織裝飾邊框。這複雜的編織圖案為手工製作的毛毯增添了優雅氣質。","word":"braid"}},"braided":{"createdAt":1781709890953,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"braided是形容詞，表示用編織或辮的技術將多股物質交叉組合在一起的樣式。","options":["hazard","braided","engagement","hesitation"],"sentence":"The woman wore her long hair in a ______ style for the formal wedding ceremony. The intricate pattern of interwoven strands created an elegant and sophisticated look.","translation":"那位女性在正式的婚禮典禮上用編織的風格梳理她的長髮。交織絞合的複雜圖案呈現出優雅而精緻的外觀。","word":"braided"}},"brake":{"createdAt":1781664420002,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"brake是煞車系統，用於減速或停止車輛。","options":["engine","brake","wheel","seat"],"sentence":"The car's ______ failed while driving down the steep mountain road. The driver had to shift into a lower gear to slow down safely.","translation":"汽車在陡峭的山路上行駛時煞車失效。駕駛員不得不降擋來安全減速。","word":"brake"}},"branch":{"createdAt":1781779647124,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"branch在此指分公司或分支機構，而非樹的分枝","options":["leaf","root","branch","fruit"],"sentence":"The new ______ of our company will open in Tokyo next month. It will serve as our regional headquarters for Asia.","translation":"我們公司的新分店將於下個月在東京開業。它將成為我們在亞洲的區域總部。","word":"branch"}},"brand":{"createdAt":1781449095514,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"brand作為動詞意為打烙印或標記，用來在物品上留下特定的標識以區分品牌。","options":["hide","brand","erase","lose"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ all their products with a new logo. This mark would help customers immediately recognize their goods in stores.","translation":"該公司決定用新標誌為他們所有的產品打上烙印。這個標記會幫助顧客在商店裡立即辨別他們的商品。","word":"brand"}},"brand_new":{"createdAt":1781613113018,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"brand-new 形容全新的、未使用過的東西","options":["old","used","brand-new","damaged"],"sentence":"He proudly showed off his ______ car that he had just purchased from the dealership. The vehicle still had that fresh smell and hadn't a single scratch on it.","translation":"他驕傲地展示了他剛從經銷商那裡購買的嶄新汽車。這輛車仍然有新車的氣味，沒有任何劃痕。","word":"brand-new"}},"breadth":{"createdAt":1781484539655,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"breadth 表示橫向的寬度或距離，指事物從左到右的測量，而非上下或前後的距離。","options":["height","depth","breadth","length"],"sentence":"The ______ of the river is impressive, stretching nearly half a mile from one bank to the other. This wide expanse makes it difficult to cross.","translation":"河流的寬度令人印象深刻，從一岸延伸到另一岸幾乎有半英里。這種寬闊的範圍使其難以穿越。","word":"breadth"}},"break":{"createdAt":1781613113015,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"break 作為名詞表示中場休息或工作中間的休息時間","options":["lesson","break","assembly","dismissal"],"sentence":"During the morning ______, students left the classroom to rest and eat snacks. The twenty-minute interval gave everyone time to relax before the next lesson.","translation":"在上午的休息時間，學生離開教室去休息和吃零食。二十分鐘的間隔給了每個人在下一堂課前放鬆的時間。","word":"break"}},"breakdown":{"createdAt":1781871338562,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"breakdown表示機械故障或停止運作，與需要拖車和修理相關。","options":["departure","progress","accident","malfunction"],"sentence":"The car's ______ on the highway forced us to call a tow truck for assistance. We waited for three hours before help arrived to repair the engine.","translation":"車輛在高速公路上的故障迫使我們撥打拖車公司請求幫助。在幫助到達修理引擎之前，我們等待了三個小時。","word":"breakdown"}},"breakthrough":{"createdAt":1781452425260,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"breakthrough表示重大的進展或突破，通常指科學或技術領域的重要發現。","options":["setback","failure","discovery","delay"],"sentence":"The research team announced a major ______ in cancer treatment after years of intensive study. The new therapy has shown a 60% improvement rate in clinical trials.","translation":"經過多年的密集研究，研究團隊宣佈了癌症治療的重大突破。新療法在臨床試驗中顯示了60%的改善率。","word":"breakthrough"}},"breast":{"createdAt":1781275226787,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"此處breast作動詞表示「挺胸面對；勇敢地迎向」","options":["breast","dump","fume","include"],"sentence":"The soldier decided to ______ the enemy and charge forward despite the danger. His courage inspired all those fighting beside him.","translation":"那位士兵決定挺胸面對敵人並向前衝鋒，儘管危險重重。他的勇氣激勵了所有與他並肩作戰的人。","word":"breast"}},"breasts":{"createdAt":1781693275431,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"乳房在烹飪語境中指禽類（如雞或鴨）胸部的肉，是常見的食材。","options":["wings","breasts","legs","thighs"],"sentence":"The roasted chicken's ______ were tender and juicy, making them the most popular part of the dish. The chef seasoned them perfectly with herbs and garlic butter.","translation":"烤雞的乳房肉嫩多汁，是這道菜中最受歡迎的部分。廚師用香草和大蒜黃油完美地調味。","word":"breasts"}},"breath":{"createdAt":1781672973740,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"breath是名詞，表示「呼吸」，指吸入和呼出空氣的過程或吸入的空氣。","options":["water","breath","food","rest"],"sentence":"After running the marathon, he gasped for ______ and sat down to recover. His lungs burned as he tried to slow down his rapid breathing.","translation":"馬拉松比賽後，他喘著氣坐下來恢復。當他試圖放慢呼吸速度時，他的肺部燃燒著疼痛。","word":"breath"}},"breathe":{"createdAt":1781832549168,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"breathe 是指吸入和呼出空氣的生理動作，在冥想和放鬆練習中特別重要。","options":["think","breathe","move","speak"],"sentence":"The yoga instructor reminded everyone to ______ slowly and deeply during the meditation session. By focusing on each inhale and exhale, the participants felt more relaxed and centered.","translation":"瑜伽教練提醒每個人在冥想課程中要緩慢而深深地呼吸。通過關注每次吸氣和呼氣，參與者感到更加放鬆和平靜。","word":"breathe"}},"breathless":{"createdAt":1781566460883,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"breathless表示屏息的、因驚奇或興奮而屏住呼吸的狀態，與觀眾期待精彩時刻的心理狀態相符。","options":["noisy","breathless","chatty","loud"],"sentence":"The ______ audience sat in complete silence as the magician revealed his final illusion. Everyone had been holding their breath in anticipation of the stunning finale.","translation":"屏息的觀眾在完全寂靜中坐著，當魔術師揭示他的最後幻象時。每個人都屏住呼吸期待著這個驚人的結局。","word":"breathless"}},"breathtaking":{"createdAt":1781850287962,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"breathtaking 形容某事物極其壯觀或美麗，令人驚嘆、屏息。","options":["ordinary","distant","breathtaking","familiar"],"sentence":"The view from the top of the mountain was absolutely ______, leaving all the hikers speechless. They stood in stunned silence for several minutes, overwhelmed by the beauty of the landscape stretching for miles below them.","translation":"從山頂看到的景色絕對令人屏息，讓所有登山者都無言以對。他們以驚嘆的沉默站立了幾分鐘，被延伸到他們下方數英里的風景之美所打動。","word":"breathtaking"}},"breed":{"createdAt":1781566460882,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"breed作為名詞表示特定的品種或類型，通常用於描述經過人工培育的動物或植物。","options":["harvest","breed","crop","farm"],"sentence":"The laboratory was studying a new ______ of disease-resistant corn plants. Scientists had spent years developing this specific variety through selective cultivation.","translation":"實驗室正在研究一種新的抗病玉米品種。科學家花費多年時間通過選擇性培育開發這個特定品種。","word":"breed"}},"bribe":{"createdAt":1781883441461,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bribe 是指為了獲得不正當利益或特殊待遇而提供的非法金錢或禮物","options":["donation","payment","bribe","fee"],"sentence":"The corrupt official was arrested for accepting a ______ from a wealthy businessman. He had agreed to approve an illegal construction project in exchange for cash.","translation":"這名貪污官員因接受一位富有商人的賄賂而被逮捕。他曾同意批准一個非法建築項目以換取現金。","word":"bribe"}},"bridge":{"createdAt":1781672973746,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bridge作為名詞表示「橋；橋樑」，作為動詞表示「把…連結起來；使渡過」，指連接分離的事物或跨越障礙。","options":["divides","bridge","blocks","closes"],"sentence":"The new highway ______ connects the two separated communities that were isolated from each other for decades. Residents can now travel between the towns in just ten minutes.","translation":"新高速公路大橋連接了兩個被隔離了數十年的分離社區。居民現在可以在十分鐘內在兩個城鎮之間旅行。","word":"bridge"}},"brief":{"createdAt":1781613113017,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"brief 形容簡短、簡潔或短暫的","options":["lengthy","brief","complicated","confusing"],"sentence":"The speaker gave a ______ presentation that lasted only ten minutes. Despite its short duration, it covered all the essential points effectively.","translation":"演講者進行了簡短的演講，只持續了十分鐘。儘管時間很短，但它有效地涵蓋了所有要點。","word":"brief"}},"briefcase":{"createdAt":1781481124705,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"briefcase 是一種專為攜帶文件和商業物品而設計的公事包或手提箱。","options":["backpack","portfolio","suitcase","attaché bag"],"sentence":"The business executive carried his leather ______ to the important meeting downtown. Inside were contracts, presentations, and other confidential documents he needed to discuss.","translation":"商業主管攜帶著他的皮革公事包去市中心開重要會議。裡面裝著他需要討論的合約、演示文稿和其他機密文件。","word":"briefcase"}},"briefly":{"createdAt":1781779647028,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"briefly表示簡短地、簡潔地說話或行動，與詳細解釋相反","options":["in detail","briefly","repeatedly","loudly"],"sentence":"The manager explained the project ______ during the meeting. She spoke for only three minutes and covered just the main points.","translation":"經理在會議中簡短地解釋了這個項目。她只講了三分鐘，只涵蓋了要點。","word":"briefly"}},"brilliant":{"createdAt":1781672973727,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"brilliant是形容詞，表示「光輝的；相當聰明的」，形容非常聰慧或才華橫溢的人。","options":["confused","brilliant","ordinary","slow"],"sentence":"Her ______ mind allowed her to solve complex mathematical problems in seconds. The professors were amazed by her exceptional intellectual ability and quick thinking.","translation":"她聰慧的頭腦使她能在幾秒鐘內解決複雜的數學問題。教授們對她傑出的智力能力和敏捷思維感到驚歎。","word":"brilliant"}},"brink":{"createdAt":1781664420007,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"brink表示邊緣或即將發生某事的臨界點，通常帶有危險或緊急的含義。","options":["center","brink","peak","foundation"],"sentence":"The company stood on the ______ of bankruptcy after losing major clients. Management needed to make drastic changes to survive.","translation":"在失去主要客戶後，該公司瀕臨破產邊緣。管理層需要做出激烈改變才能生存。","word":"brink"}},"broad":{"createdAt":1781595752121,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"broad 形容範圍或視野寬廣，可以涵蓋大的區域。","options":["narrow","limited","broad","blocked"],"sentence":"The ______ view from the mountain top allowed us to see for miles in every direction. We could observe the entire valley, distant forests, and the coastline all at once.","translation":"從山頂的寬廣景色使我們能夠朝各個方向看到數英里遠的地方。我們可以一次看到整個山谷、遙遠的森林和海岸線。","word":"broad"}},"broaden":{"createdAt":1781613113022,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"broaden 表示使變寬或擴展視野和知識","options":["narrow","broaden","ignore","forget"],"sentence":"Traveling to different countries helped ______ her perspective on life. Experiencing diverse cultures taught her to appreciate people's differences.","translation":"到不同國家旅遊幫助她拓寬了對生活的觀點。經歷多元文化教會她欣賞人們的差異。","word":"broaden"}},"broadly":{"createdAt":1781664419996,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"broadly是副詞，表示大體上或籠統地談論某事，不涉及細節。","options":["specifically","broadly","quietly","angrily"],"sentence":"When asked about his political views, he spoke ______ without getting into specific details. He preferred to discuss the general principles rather than individual policies.","translation":"當被問及他的政治觀點時，他泛泛地談論，沒有涉及具體細節。他更願意討論一般原則而不是具體政策。","word":"broadly"}},"brochure":{"createdAt":1781792910154,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"brochure是指印刷的宣傳小冊子，通常用來介紹產品、服務或旅遊景點的資訊。","options":["ticket","brochure","map","passport"],"sentence":"The travel agency handed me a colorful ______ about vacation packages. It contained detailed information about hotels, flights, and activities printed on folded paper.","translation":"旅行社遞給我一份關於度假套餐的彩色小冊子。它包含印在折疊紙張上關於飯店、航班和活動的詳細信息。","word":"brochure"}},"broil":{"createdAt":1781883441461,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"broil 意指用直接的上方熱源進行烹飪，通常是在烤箱中","options":["steam","boil","broil","poach"],"sentence":"The chef decided to ______ the salmon instead of frying it in a pan. The intense direct heat from above would give the fish a perfect golden crust.","translation":"廚師決定烤制鮭魚，而不是用平底鍋煎炒。來自上方的強烈直接熱量會給魚一個完美的金黃色外殼。","word":"broil"}},"broke":{"createdAt":1781664419995,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"broke是break的過去式，表示破裂或損壞某物。","options":["fixed","broke","cleaned","moved"],"sentence":"He ______ the vase when he knocked it off the table by accident. Now he's afraid to tell his mother what happened.","translation":"當他不小心把花瓶從桌子上碰掉時，他把它打破了。現在他害怕告訴媽媽發生了什麼事。","word":"broke"}},"bronze":{"createdAt":1781429945500,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bronze 作為名詞表示銅或青銅，在奧運會中特指代表第三名的銅牌。","options":["gold","silver","bronze","platinum"],"sentence":"The athlete won a ______ medal at the Olympic Games for her outstanding performance in the swimming competition. Coming in third place was still a remarkable achievement after four years of training.","translation":"這位運動員在奧運會上獲得了銅牌，以表彰她在游泳比賽中的出色表現。在四年的訓練後，獲得第三名仍然是一項非凡的成就。","word":"bronze"}},"brook":{"createdAt":1781425096277,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"brook 是名詞，指小溪或小河，通常指流量不大、流速較緩的天然水流，常見於鄉村或山區。","options":["path","brook","cliff","cave"],"sentence":"The hikers followed a narrow ______ through the forest to find fresh water during their journey. The gentle sound of flowing water and the cool air surrounding the small watercourse guided them to a perfect resting spot.","translation":"登山者沿著穿過森林的狹窄小溪前進，以便在旅程中找到淡水。流動的溫和水聲和圍繞著小水道的清涼空氣引導他們找到了完美的休息地點。","word":"brook"}},"browse":{"createdAt":1781664420000,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"browse表示隨意翻閱或瀏覽，不一定有明確的尋找目標。","options":["search","browse","rush","skip"],"sentence":"She spent an hour at the bookstore to ______ through the new releases section. She picked up several titles that caught her attention and seemed promising.","translation":"她在書店裡花了一小時瀏覽新發行的書籍。她拿起了幾本引起她注意和看起來很有希望的書。","word":"browse"}},"bruise":{"createdAt":1781613113023,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bruise 是碰傷或瘀傷，皮膚受鈍力撞擊後的損傷","options":["scar","wound","bruise","fracture"],"sentence":"The ______ on her arm was a dark purple color from where she had fallen. The mark would probably fade within a week.","translation":"她手臂上的瘀傷呈深紫色，是她跌倒時留下的。這個印記可能會在一周內消褪。","word":"bruise"}},"brush":{"createdAt":1781613113007,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"brush 作為名詞指的是刷子，用於清潔或繪畫的工具","options":["cloth","broom","brush","sponge"],"sentence":"He used a ______ to clean the paint off the wooden floor. The stiff bristles were perfect for scrubbing away the dried paint spots.","translation":"他用一把刷子清潔木地板上的油漆。堅硬的毛髮非常適合擦掉乾燥的油漆點。","word":"brush"}},"brutal":{"createdAt":1781850287960,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"brutal 形容某事物極其殘忍、兇狠或缺乏人情，通常引起道德譴責。","options":["strategic","clever","brutal","effective"],"sentence":"The enemy soldiers displayed ______ tactics during the occupation, showing no mercy to civilians. International observers documented countless war crimes and atrocities committed against innocent populations.","translation":"敵軍在佔領期間採取殘忍的戰術，對平民毫不留情。國際觀察員記錄了對無辜民眾實施的無數戰爭罪行和暴行。","word":"brutal"}},"bucket":{"createdAt":1781515270345,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bucket 作名詞，指有把手的桶子，用來盛裝或運輸液體或物品。","options":["prospect","curious","bucket","investment"],"sentence":"The farmer carried a heavy ______ of fresh water from the well to his garden. He poured the contents slowly over the thirsty vegetables to help them grow.","translation":"農民從水井裡提著一桶新鮮水來到他的花園。他慢慢地將水倒在口渴的蔬菜上，幫助它們生長。","word":"bucket"}},"buckle":{"createdAt":1781272410990,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"buckle作為動詞表示用扣環或搭扣將某物固定或扣上，特別是在安全帶、皮帶等情況下。","options":["unbuckle","break","buckle","unfasten"],"sentence":"Please ______ your seatbelt before the airplane takes off for safety. The flight attendant reminds all passengers to fasten their restraints properly.","translation":"飛機起飛前，請扣好你的安全帶以保証安全。空服員提醒所有乘客正確地繫好他們的約束帶。","word":"buckle"}},"buddha":{"createdAt":1781503378959,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Buddha 是佛教的創始人和中心人物，被認為是悟道的聖人。","options":["Jesus","Buddha","Muhammad","Krishna"],"sentence":"______ taught his followers the path to enlightenment and inner peace. The religious figure founded Buddhism and is revered by millions of people worldwide.","translation":"佛陀教導他的追隨者通往開悟和內心平和的道路。這位宗教人物創立了佛教，受到全世界數百萬人的尊敬。","word":"buddha"}},"buddhism":{"createdAt":1781664420005,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"buddhism是佛教，一種源於亞洲的宗教和哲學體系。","options":["Islam","buddhism","Christianity","Judaism"],"sentence":"She converted to ______ after spending a year studying in Thailand. The teachings about suffering and enlightenment resonated deeply with her.","translation":"在泰國學習一年後，她改信了佛教。關於苦難和開悟的教義與她產生了深刻共鳴。","word":"buddhism"}},"bulge":{"createdAt":1781256547739,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Bulge表示膨脹、凸起或向外推起，通常是因為內部裝有太多東西。","options":["shrink","bulge","flatten","divide"],"sentence":"The backpack began to ______ as the student packed more and more books inside. By the time she zipped it closed, the fabric was stretched to its limits.","translation":"當學生在背包裡裝入越來越多的書籍時，背包開始膨脹。當她拉上拉鍊時，布料已經延伸到極限。","word":"bulge"}},"bulging":{"createdAt":1781883441463,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"bulging 形容物體鼓起、膨脹或突出，因為內部充滿了東西","options":["light","empty","organized","bulging"],"sentence":"The student's backpack was so ______ with books that the zippers could barely close. It appeared ready to burst open at any moment.","translation":"學生的背包裡裝了太多書籍，鼓得拉鍊都幾乎關不上。看起來隨時都準備裂開。","word":"bulging"}},"bulletin":{"createdAt":1781256547738,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Bulletin是指電視或電臺突然插播的新聞快報或機構發佈的簡報和公告。","options":["advertisement","bulletin","documentary","commercial"],"sentence":"The emergency ______ interrupted the regular television program to announce the severe weather warning. Viewers learned that a powerful storm was approaching their region within the next few hours.","translation":"緊急新聞快報中斷了常規電視節目，宣布了嚴重天氣警告。觀眾得知一場強大的風暴將在接下來的幾小時內逼近他們的地區。","word":"bulletin"}},"bully":{"createdAt":1781664420001,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bully是名詞，指欺凌弱小的人或經常欺負他人的人。","options":["teacher","bully","friend","helper"],"sentence":"The school's biggest ______ constantly picked on smaller students and demanded their lunch money. Teachers finally intervened after many complaints from parents.","translation":"學校裡最大的欺凌者經常欺負較小的學生，並要求他們的午餐錢。在家長多次投訴後，教師終於進行了干預。","word":"bully"}},"bump":{"createdAt":1781362281667,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bump表示碰撞或撞擊，通常帶有一定的力度並可能導致疼痛。","options":["touch","bump","pass","lean"],"sentence":"She ______ her head on the low doorway as she entered the room. A painful impact left a small bruise on her forehead.","translation":"當她進入房間時，她的頭碰到了低門框。一次痛苦的碰撞在她的額頭上留下了一個小瘀傷。","word":"bump"}},"bumpy":{"createdAt":1781424137075,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"bumpy 形容詞意為「顛簸的」，用來描述不平穩或充滿顛簸的旅程或表面。","options":["smooth","pleasant","bumpy","peaceful"],"sentence":"The flight was very ______ and made many passengers feel uncomfortable. The airplane encountered severe turbulence while crossing over the mountain range.","translation":"這班飛機非常顛簸，使許多乘客感到不適。飛機在越過山脈時遭遇了嚴重的亂流。","word":"bumpy"}},"bundle":{"createdAt":1781933311795,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bundle（束；捆）指多個物品打包在一起銷售，而individual（個別的）、fragment（碎片）和sector（部門）都無法描述多個物品的組合套裝。","options":["individual","bundle","fragment","sector"],"sentence":"The store offered a special ______ deal that included a laptop, keyboard, mouse, and monitor all packaged together. Customers who bought the set saved forty percent compared to purchasing items separately.","translation":"商店提供了一個特殊的捆綁優惠，包括筆記型電腦、鍵盤、滑鼠和顯示器全部打包在一起。購買該套裝的消費者與單獨購買物品相比節省了百分之四十。","word":"bundle"}},"bureau":{"createdAt":1781362281654,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bureau是指政府部門或辦公機構，如局、處、署等。","options":["office","bureau","store","factory"],"sentence":"She works at the environmental protection ______ handling pollution cases. The government agency is responsible for enforcing environmental regulations across the region.","translation":"她在環保局工作，處理污染案件。這個政府機構負責在該地區執行環境法規。","word":"bureau"}},"bureaucracy":{"createdAt":1781515329267,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"bureaucracy 名詞，意思是官僚主義，指繁瑣的行政程序和過度的層級管理。","options":["efficiency","bureaucracy","progress","innovation"],"sentence":"The excessive ______ slowed down the approval process for new business licenses. Applicants had to submit documents to multiple departments and wait for weeks before receiving a decision.","translation":"過度的官僚主義減緩了新營業執照的審批過程。申請人必須向多個部門提交文件，並在獲得決定前等待數週。","word":"bureaucracy"}},"burial":{"createdAt":1781665727109,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"burial 指埋葬死者的儀式或行為，通常是文化和宗教習俗的一部分。","options":["celebration","burial","exhibition","documentation"],"sentence":"The ancient civilization practiced ______ of their kings in underground tombs filled with treasures. Archaeologists discovered the tomb intact after 3,000 years.","translation":"這個古老的文明將他們的國王埋葬在充滿珍寶的地下墓室中。考古學家在3000年後發現了完整無損的墓室。","word":"burial"}},"butcher":{"createdAt":1781417610418,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"butcher是指屠夫或肉商，販賣肉類食品的商人。","options":["tailor","butcher","gardener","carpenter"],"sentence":"The local ______ offered the finest quality meat in the neighborhood for over forty years. His shop was known for its fresh cuts and expert knowledge of different animal parts.","translation":"這位當地肉商在鄰近地區提供最優質的肉類已超過四十年。他的店以新鮮的肉品切割和對不同動物部位的專業知識而聞名。","word":"butcher"}},"by":{"createdAt":1781595752116,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"by 在此表示被動語態中的施事者，表示由誰製作或創作。","options":["against","by","for","from"],"sentence":"The famous painting was created ______ a renowned artist in the 17th century. The masterpiece was produced through the skillful hands of Leonardo da Vinci.","translation":"這幅著名繪畫是由一位十七世紀的著名藝術家創作的。這件傑作是通過李奧納多‧達文西的巧妙手藝創作的。","word":"by"}},"cabinet":{"createdAt":1781343050499,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"cabinet 在此指政府內閣，由內閣部長組成，負責政策制定和領導各部門。","options":["furniture","kitchen","cabinet","room"],"sentence":"The President's ______ consists of important ministers who advise on major policy decisions. These officials head various government departments.","translation":"總統的內閣由重要的部長組成，他們就重大政策決定提供建議。這些官員領導著各個政府部門。","word":"cabinet"}},"cafeteria":{"createdAt":1781871338561,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"cafeteria是自助餐館或食堂，學生可以自選食物，通常在學校或辦公場所。","options":["kitchen","dining","refectory","hall"],"sentence":"The school ______ serves lunch to over two thousand students every day at affordable prices. Students can choose from various meal options displayed on the serving line.","translation":"學校食堂每天為兩千多名學生提供價格低廉的午餐。學生可以從自助餐線上展示的各種餐點中選擇。","word":"cafeteria"}},"calcium":{"createdAt":1781799990466,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"calcium是化學元素鈣，是人體骨骼和牙齒的主要成分，通常存在於乳製品和綠葉蔬菜中。","options":["iron","calcium","zinc","sodium"],"sentence":"The doctor recommended that the elderly patient increase her intake of ______ through dairy products. This mineral is essential for maintaining strong bones and preventing fractures.","translation":"醫生建議年長患者透過乳製品增加她的鈣攝入量。這種礦物質對維持骨骼強度和預防骨折至關重要。","word":"calcium"}},"calculate":{"createdAt":1781624534711,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"calculate 意為「計算、估算」，表示通過數學運算確定數量或結果。","options":["guess","calculate","ignore","assume"],"sentence":"The engineer needed to ______ the exact amount of materials required for the construction project before ordering supplies. Any mistake in the numbers would result in cost overruns.","translation":"工程師在訂購物資前需要計算施工項目所需的確切材料數量。數字上的任何錯誤都會導致成本超支。","word":"calculate"}},"calculated":{"createdAt":1781479123533,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"calculated 表示經過深思熟慮、有意圖地策劃的，不是即興的。","options":["spontaneous","calculated","confused","nervous"],"sentence":"Her ______ response to the criticism showed that she had carefully considered every word before speaking. She deliberately chose phrases that would minimize conflict while addressing the concerns raised.","translation":"她對批評的精心策劃的回應顯示她在說話前已經仔細考慮了每一個詞。她刻意選擇能夠最小化衝突同時解決所提出問題的措辭。","word":"calculated"}},"calculator":{"createdAt":1781598671107,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"calculator 作名詞表示計算機或計算器，是用來執行數學運算的電子或機械設備","options":["compass","calculator","ruler","pencil"],"sentence":"The student used a ______ to solve the complex mathematical equations quickly. Without this device, the calculations would have taken much longer to complete.","translation":"學生用計算機快速解決複雜的數學方程。沒有這個設備，計算需要花費更長的時間才能完成。","word":"calculator"}},"campus":{"createdAt":1781709984195,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"campus 特指大學或學校的全部校地和設施，包括建築物、宿舍和活動區域。","options":["building","campus","grounds","area"],"sentence":"The university's ______ is located in the heart of the city with beautiful gardens and modern buildings. Students can walk from their dormitories to the library in just ten minutes.","translation":"這所大學的校園位於城市中心，擁有美麗的花園和現代建築。學生可以在十分鐘內從宿舍走到圖書館。","word":"campus"}},"cancel":{"createdAt":1781824444629,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"cancel 動詞表示取消或廢除已計劃的事件、預約或計畫。","options":["delay","confirm","cancel","accelerate"],"sentence":"Due to severe weather warnings, the airline had to ______ all flights scheduled for tomorrow. Passengers were offered full refunds or the option to rebook on future dates.","translation":"由於嚴重的天氣警告，航空公司必須取消所有計劃在明天進行的航班。乘客被提供全額退款或在未來日期改簽的選項。","word":"cancel"}},"cancer":{"createdAt":1781926371000,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"cancer 在這裡引申意思是迅速蔓延的弊病或惡習，比喻社會中不斷擴散的不良現象。","options":["strength","tradition","cancer","benefit"],"sentence":"Corruption has become a ______ in the local government, spreading through various departments. Officials have been arrested and convicted for accepting bribes and embezzling public funds.","translation":"腐敗已成為地方政府的惡習，蔓延到各個部門。官員因接受賄賂和挪用公款而被逮捕和定罪。","word":"cancer"}},"canyon":{"createdAt":1781343050501,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"canyon 是指由河流侵蝕而成的深谷或峽谷，具有陡峭的岩壁。","options":["mountain","forest","canyon","desert"],"sentence":"Tourists flock to the famous ______ in Arizona to hike along its steep walls and river. The massive geological formation took millions of years to form.","translation":"遊客蜂擁到亞利桑那州著名的峽谷，沿著陡峭的岩壁和河流徒步旅行。這個龐大的地質構造花了數百萬年才形成。","word":"canyon"}},"capability":{"createdAt":1781850347301,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"能力是指某人或某物完成任務、執行功能或達到目標的力量或潛能。","options":["weakness","capability","limitation","cost"],"sentence":"The new software demonstrated impressive ______ by processing thousands of data points in just seconds. The company's engineers were amazed at how efficiently it could handle complex calculations.","translation":"新軟體通過在短短幾秒內處理數千個資料點來展示令人印象深刻的能力。公司的工程師對它處理複雜計算的效率感到驚訝。","word":"capability"}},"capable":{"createdAt":1781693304924,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"capable 表示有能力、有資格或足以勝任某項任務或職位。","options":["incapable","unworthy","capable","hesitant"],"sentence":"Maria proved herself ______ of leading the entire department after successfully completing three major projects. Her manager decided to promote her to director.","translation":"瑪麗亞通過成功完成三個重大項目後，證明了自己有能力領導整個部門。她的經理決定將她晉升為主任。","word":"capable"}},"capacity":{"createdAt":1781798927523,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"capacity 在此語境中表示容納能力或容量，即某物體或場所能容納的最大數量。","options":["design","capacity","quality","style"],"sentence":"The concert hall has a seating ______ of 5,000 people. When the venue reached full occupancy last night, no additional tickets could be sold.","translation":"音樂廳的座位容量為5,000人。當場地昨晚滿座時，無法再銷售任何額外的票券。","word":"capacity"}},"capital":{"createdAt":1781835517794,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"capital 在此作名詞使用，意為一個國家或地區的首都，是政治和經濟中心。","options":["province","capital","village","border"],"sentence":"The ______ of France is Paris, a beautiful city known for its museums and monuments. It is the most important city in the country where the government is located.","translation":"法國的首都是巴黎，一座以博物館和紀念碑聞名的美麗城市。它是國家中政府所在的最重要的城市。","word":"capital"}},"capitalism":{"createdAt":1781256485491,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"capitalism是一種經濟制度，強調私有財產權和市場競爭","options":["socialism","feudalism","capitalism","monarchy"],"sentence":"The country's economy is based on ______, where private individuals and businesses own the means of production. Citizens are free to buy, sell, and compete in the marketplace without heavy government control.","translation":"這個國家的經濟以資本主義為基礎，由私人和企業擁有生產資料。公民可以自由地在市場上買賣和競爭，不受政府過度控制。","word":"capitalism"}},"capitalist":{"createdAt":1781484415140,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"資本家是指相信資本主義經濟制度、進行商業投資以獲取利潤的人。","options":["socialist","capitalist","artist","scientist"],"sentence":"The wealthy ______ invested heavily in new factories and technologies. He believed that private ownership and profit-seeking were the best ways to grow the economy.","translation":"這位富有的資本家在新工廠和技術上投入了大量資金。他相信私人所有制和追求利潤是發展經濟的最佳方式。","word":"capitalist"}},"captain":{"createdAt":1781787229332,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"captain 作為名詞指的是球隊、船舶或飛機的領導者，具有決策權和權威。","options":["referee","captain","coach","spectator"],"sentence":"The team's ______ made the final decision about which players would start the match. He had earned the respect of all his teammates through years of dedication.","translation":"隊長做出了關於哪些球員將首發出場的最終決定。他通過多年的奉獻獲得了所有隊友的尊重。","word":"captain"}},"caption":{"createdAt":1781580511754,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"caption 是圖片下方的說明文字，用來補充圖像內容","options":["border","caption","headline","layout"],"sentence":"The newspaper printed a ______ beneath the photograph to explain what was happening. Without this text, readers wouldn't understand the context of the image.","translation":"報紙在照片下方印了一個說明文字來解釋發生了什麼。沒有這個文本，讀者就不會理解圖像的背景。","word":"caption"}},"captioned":{"createdAt":1781799990462,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"captioned是指帶有字幕或標題的，特別用於描述視頻、照片或文件附加了文字說明的狀態。","options":["translated","captioned","dubbed","animated"],"sentence":"The ______ video included text overlays at the bottom of the screen. This feature was especially helpful for viewers watching in noisy environments.","translation":"那支附字幕的影片在螢幕底部包含了文字覆蓋層。這個功能對在嘈雜環境中觀看的觀眾特別有幫助。","word":"captioned"}},"captivate":{"createdAt":1781256547737,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Captivate表示強烈吸引某人的注意力和興趣，使其深深著迷。","options":["bore","captivate","educate","frighten"],"sentence":"The magician's extraordinary performance managed to ______ the entire audience for two hours. From the opening trick to the final illusion, every moment held their complete attention and wonder.","translation":"魔術師的非凡表演設法使整個觀眾著迷了兩個小時。從開場戲法到最後的幻象，每一刻都吸引了他們的完全注意力和驚嘆。","word":"captivate"}},"captivated":{"createdAt":1781933311795,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"captivated（著迷的）表示被某物吸引並無法移開注意力，與bored（無聊的）、confused（困惑的）和exhausted（筋疲力盡的）的含義都相反。","options":["bored","captivated","confused","exhausted"],"sentence":"The young audience was completely ______ by the magician's incredible illusions and tricks throughout the entire performance. The children sat in amazement, unable to look away from the stage.","translation":"年輕的觀眾在整個表演過程中被魔術師令人難以置信的幻覺和技巧完全迷住了。孩子們驚歎地坐著，無法把目光從舞台上移開。","word":"captivated"}},"captivity":{"createdAt":1781429945496,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"captivity 表示被監禁或囚禁的狀態，通常用來描述動物或人被關起來失去自由的情況。","options":["freedom","captivity","training","migration"],"sentence":"The lion spent twenty years in ______ before finally being released to a wildlife sanctuary. After decades of confinement in a cage, the animal could barely remember how to hunt in the wild.","translation":"這隻獅子在被釋放到野生動物保護區之前，花了二十年被關在籠子裡。經過數十年的囚禁，這隻動物幾乎記不得如何在野外捕獵了。","word":"captivity"}},"capture":{"createdAt":1781709984194,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"capture 在攝影語境中表示拍攝或記錄影像，捕捉某個特定時刻。","options":["record","capture","draw","catch"],"sentence":"The photographer managed to ______ a stunning image of the eagle in flight. The award-winning shot was printed on the cover of National Geographic magazine.","translation":"攝影師成功拍攝到一張老鷹飛行中的絕美影像。這張獲獎照片被印在《國家地理》雜誌的封面上。","word":"capture"}},"carbon":{"createdAt":1781850347303,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"碳是一種化學元素，是有機物的基礎，存在於所有生命體中。","options":["nitrogen","oxygen","hydrogen","carbon"],"sentence":"The scientist measured the amount of ______ dioxide in the atmosphere to track climate change. This chemical compound consists of one carbon atom and two oxygen atoms.","translation":"科學家測量了大氣中的二氧化碳含量以追蹤氣候變化。這種化合物由一個碳原子和兩個氧原子組成。","word":"carbon"}},"careless":{"createdAt":1781850347302,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"粗心是形容詞，指缺乏注意力、不謹慎或沒有仔細考慮。","options":["intentional","clever","careless","strategic"],"sentence":"His ______ mistake on the exam cost him ten points that he could have easily avoided. He simply did not review his answers before submitting the paper.","translation":"他在考試上的粗心錯誤讓他失去了十分，這是他本來可以輕易避免的。他根本沒有在提交試卷前檢查他的答案。","word":"careless"}},"carnival":{"createdAt":1781485266374,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"carnival指的是充滿歡樂、娛樂和狂歡氣氛的節日或嘉年華會。","options":["funeral","conference","carnival","meeting"],"sentence":"The city hosted a week-long ______ with colorful parades, live music, and festive celebrations. Thousands of visitors came to enjoy the vibrant atmosphere and traditional festivities.","translation":"這座城市舉辦了為期一週的嘉年華，有彩色遊行、現場音樂和節日慶祝活動。數千名遊客來享受充滿活力的氛圍和傳統慶祝活動。","word":"carnival"}},"carpenter":{"createdAt":1781362281665,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"carpenter指的是從事木工工作的工人，製造或修理木製結構和物品。","options":["plumber","carpenter","electrician","mason"],"sentence":"The ______ carefully measured and cut the wood for the new deck. His skilled hands shaped each piece into the perfect size and fit.","translation":"木匠仔細測量並為新甲板切割木材。他熟練的手將每一塊木料塑造成完美的尺寸和配合。","word":"carpenter"}},"carriage":{"createdAt":1781256485494,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"carriage是指四輪馬車或火車車廂，用於運載乘客","options":["airplane","bicycle","carriage","submarine"],"sentence":"The luxurious ______ was pulled by four white horses through the royal procession. Passengers sat in the decorated wooden compartment as crowds watched the ceremonial parade.","translation":"這輛豪華的四輪馬車由四匹白馬拉著通過皇家遊行隊伍。乘客坐在裝飾華麗的木製車廂內，眾人觀看了這場儀式性遊行。","word":"carriage"}},"carry":{"createdAt":1781850347301,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"運送或攜帶是指用手、肩膀或其他方式將某物從一個地方移動到另一個地方。","options":["drag","throw","carry","drop"],"sentence":"The strong porter could ______ four heavy suitcases up the stairs without any help. His muscular arms made lifting the luggage look effortless.","translation":"這位強壯的行李員能夠毫無幫助地將四個沉重的行李箱運上樓梯。他結實的手臂使提著行李看起來毫不費力。","word":"carry"}},"cashier":{"createdAt":1781850347302,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"收銀員是在商店、銀行或餐館等地負責收錢、計算費用和處理付款的人員。","options":["manager","customer","cashier","clerk"],"sentence":"The ______ at the supermarket scanned all the groceries and told me the total came to forty-five dollars. I handed over my credit card to complete the transaction.","translation":"超市的收銀員掃描了所有雜貨並告訴我總額是四十五美元。我遞上我的信用卡來完成交易。","word":"cashier"}},"casino":{"createdAt":1781693265624,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"賭場是一個提供賭博遊戲和娛樂的商業場所。","options":["museum","casino","library","hospital"],"sentence":"Many tourists visit the ______ to try their luck at games of chance. The establishment is famous for its slot machines, poker tables, and roulette wheels.","translation":"許多遊客到賭場碰碰運氣玩機率遊戲。該場所以老虎機、撲克牌桌和輪盤遊戲而聞名。","word":"casino"}},"cassette":{"createdAt":1781256485493,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cassette是指盒式錄音帶或錄影帶，通常用於儲存音樂或視頻","options":["mirror","cassette","book","lamp"],"sentence":"She found an old ______ in her mother's attic from the 1980s. The magnetic tape inside contained recordings of family conversations from decades ago.","translation":"她在母親的閣樓裡發現了一個來自1980年代的舊盒式錄音帶。裡面的磁帶包含了幾十年前的家庭對話錄音。","word":"cassette"}},"cast":{"createdAt":1781776694538,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cast 作為名詞，意思是電影、戲劇或節目中的所有演員。","options":["script","cast","budget","location"],"sentence":"The ______ of the new film includes several award-winning actors. The director carefully selected each performer to bring the story to life on screen.","translation":"這部新電影的演員陣容包括多位獲獎的演員。導演仔細挑選了每位演員來在銀幕上呈現這個故事。","word":"cast"}},"castle":{"createdAt":1781951900951,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"castle特指貴族或王室居住的帶有防禦功能的大型建築，通常有護城河和塔樓。","options":["mansion","castle","fortress","tower"],"sentence":"The medieval ______ stood majestically on the hilltop with its tall stone walls and multiple towers. Visitors could see the defensive moat surrounding the entire structure.","translation":"中世紀的城堡以其高聳的石牆和多座塔樓雄偉地矗立在山頂。遊客可以看到環繞整個建築的防禦性護城河。","word":"castle"}},"category":{"createdAt":1781566185161,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"category指將事物按共同特徵分組的方式，用來分類和組織不同的項目。","options":["color","price","category","author"],"sentence":"The books in the library are organized by ______ to help readers find what they need. Fiction, non-fiction, biography, and science are examples of how the collection is arranged.","translation":"圖書館裡的書籍按種類組織，以幫助讀者找到他們需要的書。小說、非虛構、傳記和科學是收藏如何分類的例子。","word":"category"}},"cathedral":{"createdAt":1781598671066,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cathedral 作名詞表示大教堂或總教堂，通常是一座重要的宗教建築","options":["mansion","cathedral","warehouse","restaurant"],"sentence":"The magnificent ______ in the city center attracts thousands of tourists every year. Its Gothic architecture and stained glass windows are masterpieces from the medieval period.","translation":"市中心宏偉的大教堂每年吸引數千名遊客。其哥德式建築和彩色玻璃窗是中世紀的傑作。","word":"cathedral"}},"caught":{"createdAt":1781345746906,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"caught 是 catch 的過去式，在此指「染上」疾病，表示受感染。","options":["threw","caught","threw away","dropped"],"sentence":"The child ______ a terrible cold while playing outside in the rain. Within two days, he developed a fever and had to stay home from school.","translation":"孩子在雨中外面玩耍時染上了嚴重的感冒。兩天內，他發燒了，不得不待在家裡不去上學。","word":"caught"}},"causal":{"createdAt":1781842254311,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"causal 指涉及因果關係的，表示一件事物直接導致另一件事物發生的關係。","options":["random","causal","theoretical","emotional"],"sentence":"The researcher studied the ______ relationship between smoking and lung disease in her medical paper. She carefully examined how smoking directly caused changes in patients' lung tissue over time.","translation":"研究者在她的醫學論文中研究了吸菸和肺病之間的因果關係。她仔細檢查了吸菸如何隨著時間推移直接導致患者肺組織變化。","word":"causal"}},"cave":{"createdAt":1781749177489,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"cave 指自然形成的地下洞穴，會有鐘乳石等自然地質特徵。","options":["temple","tunnel","cavern","bunker"],"sentence":"The explorers discovered ancient paintings deep inside the ______. The stalactites hanging from the ceiling suggested the site had been undisturbed for thousands of years.","translation":"探險家們在山洞深處發現了古代繪畫。天花板上懸掛的鐘乳石表明該遺址已有數千年未被人打擾。","word":"cave"}},"ceiling":{"createdAt":1781274836863,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ceiling在此context表示上限或最高限制，特別是指款項或價格不能超越的界限。","options":["foundation","ceiling","floor","wall"],"sentence":"The government announced a price ______ to prevent inflation from getting worse. No business was allowed to charge more than the maximum amount established by law.","translation":"政府宣布了價格上限以防止通貨膨脹惡化。法律規定沒有企業被允許收取超過最高金額。","word":"ceiling"}},"celebrated":{"createdAt":1781693295125,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"celebrated 是形容詞，表示著名的或備受尊敬的，用來描述有成就的人物。","options":["unknown","celebrated","fictional","ordinary"],"sentence":"The ______ author gave a lecture at our school last week, and hundreds of students attended. Her bestselling novels have been translated into 40 languages and won multiple international awards.","translation":"這位著名作家上周在我們學校舉辦了一場講座，數百名學生參加了。她的暢銷小說已被翻譯成40種語言，並贏得了多項國際獎項。","word":"celebrated"}},"cemetery":{"createdAt":1781425093251,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cemetery 是名詞，指公墓或墓地，是埋葬死者的地方。","options":["museum","cemetery","hospital","library"],"sentence":"The old ______ on the hill is surrounded by tall oak trees and contains graves dating back two centuries. Every November, families visit this sacred burial ground to remember their deceased relatives.","translation":"山上的老墓地被高大的橡樹包圍，裡面有可追溯到兩百年前的墓穴。每年11月，家庭都會到這個神聖的埋葬地悼念他們已故的親人。","word":"cemetery"}},"census":{"createdAt":1781481311493,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"census指的是官方進行的人口普查或人口統計調查。","options":["lawsuit","census","election","forecast"],"sentence":"The government conducted a comprehensive ______ to count the population and gather demographic information. Every household received an official questionnaire asking about age, occupation, and family size.","translation":"政府進行了一次全面的人口普查，以統計人口並收集人口統計信息。每個家庭都收到了一份官方問卷，詢問年齡、職業和家庭人數。","word":"census"}},"ceremony":{"createdAt":1781696018690,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ceremony 意為典禮、禮儀，指正式、莊重的公開活動，通常遵循特定的傳統或規則。","options":["party","ceremony","celebration","feast"],"sentence":"The wedding ______ took place in a beautiful cathedral with hundreds of guests in attendance. The couple exchanged vows and rings according to traditional religious practices.","translation":"婚禮典禮在一座美麗的大教堂舉行，有數百位賓客出席。新人根據傳統宗教習俗交換了誓言和戒指。","word":"ceremony"}},"certain":{"createdAt":1782007262076,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"certain 表示確定、肯定的狀態，由於老師親自驗證了，所以她對此事很確定。","options":["uncertain","hopeful","certain","curious"],"sentence":"The teacher was ______ that all students had completed their homework before the exam. She had checked the submission list herself to verify this.","translation":"老師確定所有學生在考試前都完成了他們的功課。她親自檢查了提交名單來驗證這一點。","word":"certain"}},"certainly":{"createdAt":1782016805982,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"certainly 是副詞，表示無疑地、肯定地或確信地的態度。","options":["doubtfully","certainly","possibly","vaguely"],"sentence":"The professor ______ knows the answer to your question about quantum physics. He has published over fifty peer-reviewed papers on the subject.","translation":"教授無疑地知道你關於量子物理的問題的答案。他已經在這個主題上發表了五十多篇同行評審的論文。","word":"certainly"}},"certification":{"createdAt":1781336858147,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"certification 是正式的證明文件，表示某人已達到特定的標準或完成了特定的要求。","options":["complaint","certification","rejection","rumor"],"sentence":"She earned a ______ from the university after completing the professional development program. The document proved that she had successfully passed all required examinations and met every standard.","translation":"她在完成專業發展課程後從大學獲得了證明書。這份文件證明她已成功通過所有必修考試並達到了每項標準。","word":"certification"}},"challenge":{"createdAt":1781837419092,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Challenge作為動詞表示向某人發起挑戰，邀請他們參加競賽或對抗。","options":["ignore","challenge","congratulate","assist"],"sentence":"The young athlete ______ the world record holder to a competition. She was confident she could defeat him in the upcoming championship match.","translation":"年輕運動員向世界紀錄保持者發起挑戰。她相信自己能在即將舉行的錦標賽中擊敗他。","word":"challenge"}},"chamber":{"createdAt":1781566185160,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"chamber在官方場合中指用於特定官方用途的房間，例如議會廳或法院。","options":["chamber","garden","kitchen","stable"],"sentence":"The parliament members gathered in the ______ for their weekly meeting. The ornate hall featured marble columns and a high ceiling where important legislation was debated and voted upon.","translation":"國會議員們在那間議院集合進行每週的會議。這個裝飾華麗的大廳有大理石柱和高高的天花板，重要的立法在這裡被辯論和表決。","word":"chamber"}},"champion":{"createdAt":1781580511761,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"champion 指在比賽或競爭中獲勝的人，即冠軍","options":["spectator","referee","champion","participant"],"sentence":"The ______ of the tennis tournament raised the trophy above her head in celebration. She had defeated every opponent throughout the entire competition.","translation":"網球賽事的冠軍將獎杯舉過頭頂慶祝。她在整個比賽中擊敗了每一個對手。","word":"champion"}},"championship":{"createdAt":1781425737125,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"championship 指冠軍賽或冠軍頭銜，指最高等級的競賽或獲得的最高榮譽。","options":["playoff","championship","friendly","practice"],"sentence":"The basketball team won the ______ title after defeating every opponent in the tournament. They are now recognized as the best team in the entire league this season.","translation":"籃球隊在擊敗錦標賽中的每個對手後贏得了冠軍頭銜。他們現在被認為是本賽季整個聯賽中最好的隊伍。","word":"championship"}},"chant":{"createdAt":1781256547738,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Chant表示以節奏或重複的方式大聲說出或吟唱某些詞語或短語。","options":["whisper","chant","write","forget"],"sentence":"The crowd began to ______ the team's name repeatedly during the championship game. The rhythmic repetition of \"Go Tigers!\" echoed throughout the entire stadium.","translation":"在冠軍賽期間，群眾開始反覆吟唱球隊的名字。「加油老虎隊！」的有節奏重複聲音迴盪在整個體育場。","word":"chant"}},"chaos":{"createdAt":1781837419088,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Chaos指的是完全的混亂和無序狀態，系統無法正常運作。","options":["peace","chaos","calm","order"],"sentence":"After the earthquake, the city descended into complete ______ with no electricity or clean water. The destruction and disorder made it nearly impossible for emergency services to operate effectively.","translation":"地震後，城市陷入完全混亂，沒有電力或清潔水。破壞和無序使緊急服務幾乎無法有效運作。","word":"chaos"}},"chaotic":{"createdAt":1781839703142,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"chaotic形容完全混亂無序的狀態，與找不到檔案、會議取消、不知道任務的情況完全相符。","options":["organized","peaceful","chaotic","productive"],"sentence":"The office became ______ during the system migration. Staff members couldn't find files, meetings were cancelled, and nobody knew their assignments.","translation":"在系統遷移期間，辦公室變得一片混亂。員工找不到檔案，會議被取消，沒有人知道自己的任務。","word":"chaotic"}},"chapel":{"createdAt":1781424574162,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"chapel 是指一個小型的禮拜堂或祈禱場所，通常規模較教堂小。","options":["stadium","chapel","warehouse","museum"],"sentence":"The bride and groom exchanged vows in a small ______ on the hillside. The intimate stone building had room for only fifty guests and beautiful stained-glass windows.","translation":"新娘和新郎在山坡上的一個小禮拜堂交換誓言。這座親密的石製建築只能容納五十位賓客，並有美麗的彩色玻璃窗。","word":"chapel"}},"character":{"createdAt":1781784910910,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"character 在文學中指人物的性格特徵或品質；第二句明確提到「誠實和善良這些特徵」，與第一句中性格的演變相對應。","options":["plot","character","setting","dialogue"],"sentence":"The protagonist's ______ evolved throughout the story as he learned from his mistakes. By the end of the novel, his honesty and kindness had become his defining traits.","translation":"主角的性格在整個故事中不斷演變，因為他從錯誤中學習。到小說結尾，他的誠實和善良成為了他的決定性特徵。","word":"character"}},"characteristic":{"createdAt":1781749177493,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"characteristic 表示一個人或事物所特有的、獨特的特徵或品質。","options":["uncommon","defining","occasional","recent"],"sentence":"One ______ trait of successful entrepreneurs is their ability to adapt to market changes. This quality allows them to thrive in challenging business environments.","translation":"成功企業家的一個特徵特性是他們適應市場變化的能力。這種素質使他們能夠在具有挑戰性的商業環境中繁榮發展。","word":"characteristic"}},"characterize":{"createdAt":1781481124704,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"characterize 表示描述或描繪某人或某物的特性、特徵或性質。","options":["ignore","describe","dismiss","simplify"],"sentence":"The biography carefully ______ the historical figure as a complex man of contradictions. The author presented evidence of his ambitions, flaws, and lasting impact on society.","translation":"這本傳記詳細描繪了這位歷史人物是一個複雜且自相矛盾的人。作者呈現了他的野心、缺陷以及對社會的持久影響的證據。","word":"characterize"}},"charitable":{"createdAt":1781693254766,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"charitable形容出於善心或慈悲的行為，特別是涉及對他人的幫助和捐贈。","options":["competitive","charitable","commercial","criminal"],"sentence":"His ______ donations to homeless shelters and food banks made a real difference in the community. Every year, he contributed thousands of dollars to help those in need.","translation":"他對無家者收容所和食物銀行的慈善捐款對社區產生了真實的影響。他每年都貢獻數千美元來幫助需要幫助的人。","word":"charitable"}},"charm":{"createdAt":1781256547737,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Charm作為動詞表示以某種吸引人的方式使某人感到愉悅或著迷。","options":["repel","charm","confuse","annoy"],"sentence":"Her warm smile and genuine kindness seemed to ______ everyone she met. People found themselves drawn to her presence and eager to spend time with her.","translation":"她溫暖的微笑和真摯的善良似乎使她遇見的每個人都著迷。人們發現自己被她的存在所吸引，渴望與她相處。","word":"charm"}},"charmed":{"createdAt":1781738105690,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"charmed 意為被迷住或深深吸引，通常表示對某事物的積極和愉快的反應。","options":["bored","charmed","confused","exhausted"],"sentence":"The children were completely ______ by the magician's incredible illusions during the performance. They sat in wonder, watching him make coins disappear and reappear from thin air.","translation":"孩子們在表演中完全被魔術師不可思議的幻覺所吸引。他們坐在那裡驚歎，看著他讓硬幣憑空消失又重新出現。","word":"charmed"}},"chatter":{"createdAt":1781564440926,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"chatter 作動詞表示喋喋不休、嘮叨，指說話多、談話不停。","options":["listen","chatter","whisper","sing"],"sentence":"The students began to ______ loudly during the break period. Their constant talking and conversation filled the entire classroom.","translation":"學生們在休息時間開始喋喋不休地談話。他們不斷的談話和交談充滿了整個教室。","word":"chatter"}},"checkup":{"createdAt":1781783820686,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"checkup是指定期的健康檢查或體檢，用來評估身體的整體狀況，通常包括各種檢查和測試。","options":["operation","checkup","prescription","treatment"],"sentence":"I have a doctor's ______ scheduled for next Tuesday morning. The appointment includes blood tests, a physical examination, and a discussion about my overall health status.","translation":"我預約了下週二上午的醫生體檢。此次預約包括驗血、身體檢查和關於我整體健康狀況的討論。","word":"checkup"}},"chef":{"createdAt":1781343050502,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"chef 指專業廚師或廚師長，負責菜肴的設計、準備和烹飪。","options":["waiter","accountant","chef","manager"],"sentence":"The renowned ______ at the five-star restaurant creates innovative dishes every night. His culinary training and creativity have earned him multiple awards.","translation":"這家五星級餐廳著名的廚師每晚都創作創新菜肴。他的烹飪培訓和創意為他贏得了多個獎項。","word":"chef"}},"chemical":{"createdAt":1781499075056,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"化學反應涉及物質分子或原子的重新排列，產生新的物質。","options":["physical","biological","chemical","electrical"],"sentence":"The ______ reaction between the two liquids produced heat and changed their color. Scientists used beakers and safety goggles to conduct this transformation in the laboratory.","translation":"兩種液體之間的化學反應產生了熱量並改變了它們的顏色。科學家在實驗室使用燒杯和安全護目鏡進行了這種轉化。","word":"chemical"}},"chemicals":{"createdAt":1781425737125,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"chemicals 指化學物質或化學品，與工廠排放的有毒物質和製造過程相關。","options":["chemicals","plants","fish","rocks"],"sentence":"The factory released toxic ______ into the river, causing environmental damage downstream. Scientists tested the water and identified dangerous substances used in manufacturing processes.","translation":"工廠向河中排放有毒化學物質，造成下游環保損害。科學家測試了水質並識別出製造過程中使用的危險物質。","word":"chemicals"}},"chemist":{"createdAt":1781842000007,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"化學家是研究物質成分、性質和化學反應的科學家。","options":["physicist","chemist","biologist","geologist"],"sentence":"The ______ worked in the laboratory conducting experiments on chemical reactions. She had spent years studying the composition and properties of matter to understand how substances interact.","translation":"這位______在實驗室工作，進行化學反應實驗。她花了多年時間研究物質的成分和性質，以了解物質如何相互作用。","word":"chemist"}},"chemistry":{"createdAt":1781850287961,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"chemistry 指研究物質的組成、結構和變化的自然科學。","options":["history","physics","chemistry","biology"],"sentence":"She excelled in ______ class and scored the highest marks in all her exams. Her passion for understanding the properties of elements and compounds led her to pursue a degree in pharmaceutical research.","translation":"她在化學課上表現出色，在所有考試中都獲得最高分。她對了解元素和化合物性質的熱情促使她追求藥學研究的學位。","word":"chemistry"}},"chief":{"createdAt":1781515372606,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"chief用來表示最高層級或最主要的職位和人物","options":["launch","domestic","chief","fulfillment"],"sentence":"The ______ executive officer announced a new strategic direction for the company. As the highest-ranking official in the organization, he had the final authority on all major decisions.","translation":"首席執行官宣佈了公司的新戰略方向。作為組織中最高級別的官員，他對所有重大決策擁有最終的權威。","word":"chief"}},"childhood":{"createdAt":1781651775063,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"childhood 指人生中從出生到青少年期的早期階段。","options":["discussion","frustrate","justify","childhood"],"sentence":"My grandfather often reminisced about his ______ spent in a small village. He described playing in the fields and attending school with fond memories from his early years.","translation":"我的祖父經常回憶起他在小村莊度過的童年時期。他描述了在田野裡玩耍和上學的美好回憶，這些都來自他的早年。","word":"childhood"}},"childish":{"createdAt":1781565657685,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"childish 意指像小孩子一樣不成熟或幼稚的行為，通常用來批評成年人不理性的舉動。","options":["mature","childish","professional","responsible"],"sentence":"His ______ behavior of throwing tantrums when he didn't get his way annoyed everyone at the meeting. The forty-year-old executive needed to learn how to handle disappointment with maturity.","translation":"他在沒有得到他想要的東西時發脾氣的幼稚行為令會議上的每個人都感到厭煩。這位四十歲的執行官需要學會以成熟的方式處理失望。","word":"childish"}},"chill":{"createdAt":1781323901188,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"chill意為「使變冷」或「使冷卻」，在此指降低飲料的溫度。","options":["heat","warm","chill","ferment"],"sentence":"Please ______ the champagne in the freezer before the guests arrive. We need the bottles to be ice-cold for the celebration tonight.","translation":"請在客人到達前在冰箱裡冷卻香檳。我們需要這些瓶子冰冷以供今晚的慶祝活動。","word":"chill"}},"chip":{"createdAt":1781837419096,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Chip作為名詞指的是從物體上脫落的小碎片或缺口，通常是由於碰撞造成的。","options":["stain","chip","crack","dent"],"sentence":"When he dropped the ceramic plate, a small ______ broke off the edge. The damaged dish was no longer perfect but still usable for everyday meals.","translation":"當他掉落陶瓷盤子時，邊緣的一小片碎屑脫落。受損的盤子不再完美，但仍然可以用於日常用餐。","word":"chip"}},"chipped":{"createdAt":1781779647047,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"chipped表示邊緣或角落破損或有小缺口","options":["perfect","shiny","chipped","smooth"],"sentence":"The antique vase had a ______ rim. Despite the damage from years of use, it was still valuable.","translation":"古董花瓶的邊緣有缺口。儘管經過多年使用而受損，它仍然很有價值。","word":"chipped"}},"chirp":{"createdAt":1781414884519,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"chirp指小鳥或昆蟲發出的尖聲尖氣的叫聲，通常是短促而重複的。","options":["roar","chirp","whisper","thunder"],"sentence":"Every morning, the small birds would ______ outside my window to greet the sunrise. Their high-pitched sounds created a cheerful melody that woke me up naturally.","translation":"每個早晨，小鳥都會在我的窗外嘰嘰喳喳地叫來迎接日出。他們尖銳的聲音創造了一首歡樂的旋律，自然地喚醒了我。","word":"chirp"}},"choir":{"createdAt":1781429945498,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"choir 是指一群唱歌的人組成的合唱團或唱詩班，通常在教堂或音樂會中表演。","options":["audience","orchestra","choir","band"],"sentence":"The ______ sang beautifully at the Christmas concert last night. Over fifty singers, dressed in matching robes, harmonized together on stage.","translation":"合唱團昨晚在聖誕節音樂會上唱得很美。五十多名歌手穿著相配的長袍，在舞台上齊聲和諧唱歌。","word":"choir"}},"choke":{"createdAt":1781428458259,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"choke表示呼吸困難或因為疲勞而無法正常呼吸。","options":["contain","confidence","choke","normal"],"sentence":"The runner began to ______ during the final lap of the marathon. He struggled to breathe heavily while gasping for air as exhaustion overtook him.","translation":"跑步者在馬拉松的最後一圈開始窒息。當疲勞襲來時，他掙扎著沉重地呼吸，喘著氣。","word":"choke"}},"cholesterol":{"createdAt":1781425737124,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cholesterol 是一種血液中的脂肪物質，高膽固醇會對健康造成危害，需要通過飲食控制。","options":["iron","cholesterol","sodium","protein"],"sentence":"The doctor warned him that his ______ level was dangerously high after reviewing his recent blood test results. He must change his diet immediately to reduce the fatty substance in his bloodstream.","translation":"醫生在審查他最近的血液檢查結果後警告他膽固醇水平危險地高。他必須立即改變飲食以減少血液中的脂肪物質。","word":"cholesterol"}},"chord":{"createdAt":1781837419086,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"和弦是指多個音符同時發音而形成的音樂元素，與單獨的旋律不同。","options":["melody","chord","rhythm","tempo"],"sentence":"The pianist played a beautiful ______ that resonated through the concert hall. The harmony of multiple notes played simultaneously created a rich, musical sound.","translation":"鋼琴家彈奏了一個在音樂廳裡產生共鳴的美妙和弦。多個音符同時演奏的協調創造了豐富的音樂聲音。","word":"chord"}},"chorus":{"createdAt":1781839703143,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"chorus作動詞表示許多人同時說出相同的話，與thousands of voices united in unison（數千個聲音一致）完美對應。","options":["whisper","silence","chorus","ignore"],"sentence":"The audience began to ______ the main character's name as the finale approached. Thousands of voices united in unison, creating a powerful moment.","translation":"當終幕臨近時，觀眾開始齊聲喊著主角的名字。數千個聲音一致發出，創造了一個強大的時刻。","word":"chorus"}},"chronological":{"createdAt":1781257238299,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"chronological指按照時間先後順序排列的，適合用來描述事件的時間順序。","options":["random","chronological","alphabetical","thematic"],"sentence":"The history textbook presents events in ______ order. Students can easily understand how one event led to the next by following the timeline from 1900 to 2020.","translation":"歷史教科書按時間順序呈現事件。學生可以通過遵循從1900年到2020年的時間線，輕鬆理解一個事件如何導致下一個事件。","word":"chronological"}},"chubby":{"createdAt":1781927792736,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"chubby用來形容人體態豐滿圓潤，通常帶有溫暖親切的含義，特別常用於描述嬰幼兒。","options":["thin","muscular","chubby","tall"],"sentence":"The ______ toddler had rosy cheeks and dimpled hands that made everyone want to pinch them. His round face and soft features were signs of good health and proper nutrition.","translation":"圓胖的幼兒有著紅潤的臉頰和酒窩小手，讓每個人都想捏一下。他圓圓的臉和柔軟的五官是健康和營養良好的象徵。","word":"chubby"}},"chunk":{"createdAt":1782018712119,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「chunk」指粗厚或不規則的大塊固體物質，通常用於描述食物或其他物品被分成的大部分。","options":["grain","chunk","slice","crumb"],"sentence":"He took a large ______ of bread from the table and ate it quickly. The piece was so big that it barely fit in his mouth.","translation":"他從桌子上拿了一大塊麵包並迅速吃掉。這塊麵包大到幾乎放不進他的嘴裡。","word":"chunk"}},"cigarette":{"createdAt":1781343050492,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cigarette 是指紙煙，通常指香煙製品，醫生警告的就是吸煙對肺部的傷害。","options":["alcohol","cigarette","coffee","candy"],"sentence":"He quit smoking ______ last year because of health concerns. His doctor warned him that each stick he smoked was damaging his lungs.","translation":"他去年戒掉了香煙，因為擔心健康。他的醫生警告他說，他抽的每一根都在傷害他的肺。","word":"cigarette"}},"circular":{"createdAt":1781708461103,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"circular在這裡作為名詞，意指公司發送的印刷通知或傳單。","options":["linear","circular","rectangular","triangular"],"sentence":"The company sent out a ______ announcing the new office hours to all employees. Everyone received the printed notice in their mailbox yesterday.","translation":"公司發出一份通知，向所有員工宣佈新的辦公時間。昨天每個人的郵箱裡都收到了印刷的通知。","word":"circular"}},"circulars":{"createdAt":1781850287960,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"circulars 指大量印製並廣泛分發的廣告傳單或通函。","options":["posters","circulars","invoices","certificates"],"sentence":"The marketing department printed thousands of ______ to advertise the upcoming sale. These promotional materials were delivered to every mailbox in the neighborhood within one week.","translation":"行銷部門印製了數千份廣告傳單來宣傳即將舉行的促銷活動。這些宣傳材料在一週內被送到整個社區的每個信箱。","word":"circulars"}},"circumstance":{"createdAt":1781950727564,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"circumstance 指情況或環境因素，通常影響事件的發生或決定。","options":["weather","circumstance","season","color"],"sentence":"Under normal ______, I would never miss a family gathering. However, due to an emergency at work, I had to cancel my attendance.","translation":"在正常情況下，我永遠不會錯過家庭聚會。然而，由於工作上的緊急情況，我不得不取消參加。","word":"circumstance"}},"citation":{"createdAt":1781428458258,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"citation在此指正式的獎狀或榮譽證書，用來表彰個人的成就。","options":["choke","citation","crisis","lecture"],"sentence":"The student received a ______ from the university for her outstanding academic achievements. This award was presented during the graduation ceremony in front of all the faculty and graduates.","translation":"該學生因其傑出的學業成就獲得了大學的獎狀。這個獎項在畢業典禮上在全體教職員和畢業生面前頒發。","word":"citation"}},"citizen":{"createdAt":1781709984196,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"citizen 特指具有國籍和合法身分的人，享有特定國家的公民權利和義務。","options":["resident","citizen","person","inhabitant"],"sentence":"Every ______ of the country has the right to vote in national elections. Those who were born here or completed the naturalization process can participate in the democratic process.","translation":"這個國家的每位公民都有權在國家選舉中投票。那些在這裡出生或完成歸化程序的人可以參與民主進程。","word":"citizen"}},"citizenship":{"createdAt":1781424137077,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"citizenship 名詞意為「公民身分」，指一個人在某個國家的法律地位和權利。","options":["employment","citizenship","education","housing"],"sentence":"He finally obtained ______ after living in the country for ten years. The government approved his application and issued him an official passport.","translation":"他在該國居住十年後終於獲得了公民身分。政府核准了他的申請並頒發給他正式護照。","word":"citizenship"}},"civic":{"createdAt":1781481124690,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"civic 指與城市、市民或社區有關的事務，強調公共利益和社區參與。","options":["private","commercial","community","international"],"sentence":"The mayor launched a new ______ project to improve public parks and community centers. The initiative aimed to strengthen bonds between residents and enhance their quality of life.","translation":"市長啟動了一項新的市民項目，以改善公園和社區中心。該倡議旨在加強居民之間的聯繫並提升他們的生活品質。","word":"civic"}},"civil":{"createdAt":1781272410990,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"civil作為形容詞指的是民事的、市民的，特別是在法律方面指不涉及刑事犯罪的民間糾紛。","options":["military","criminal","civil","martial"],"sentence":"The ______ court handles disputes between two private citizens about property rights. This type of case is different from criminal cases, which involve breaking the law.","translation":"民事法庭處理兩個私人公民之間關於財產權的爭議。這類案件與涉及違反法律的刑事案件不同。","word":"civil"}},"civilization":{"createdAt":1781332009067,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"civilization 指的是具有特定文化、制度和社會結構的人類社會","options":["animals","civilization","weather","mountains"],"sentence":"Ancient Egypt was one of the most advanced ______ in human history. This society developed writing, architecture, and complex government systems thousands of years ago.","translation":"古埃及是人類歷史上最先進的文明之一。這個社會在幾千年前就發展出了文字、建築和複雜的政府體系。","word":"civilization"}},"civilize":{"createdAt":1781850287958,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"civilize 意指透過文化、教育和社會制度的改進來提升一個社會的文明程度。","options":["educate","civilize","explore","colonize"],"sentence":"The missionaries worked to ______ the indigenous people by introducing education and modern institutions. Over centuries, this process transformed their society from nomadic tribes into settled communities with written language and formal government.","translation":"傳教士透過引進教育和現代機構的方式努力使土著人民開化。經過幾個世紀，這個過程將他們的社會從遊牧部落轉變為擁有書寫語言和正式政府的定居社區。","word":"civilize"}},"civilized":{"createdAt":1781332009080,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"civilized 是形容詞，表示文明的、開化的，用於形容有教養和禮貌的行為","options":["barbaric","civilized","chaotic","hostile"],"sentence":"The discussion remained calm and ______ despite the disagreement between the parties. Both sides presented their arguments respectfully without resorting to insults or aggression.","translation":"儘管雙方之間有分歧，討論仍然保持冷靜和文明。雙方都尊重地陳述了他們的論點，沒有訴諸辱罵或侵略。","word":"civilized"}},"claim":{"createdAt":1781838276305,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"claim作為名詞表示根據權利提出的要求或索賠。","options":["proponent","ordeal","claim","volume"],"sentence":"The insurance company rejected his ______ for damages after the car accident. He had submitted all the necessary documentation, but they denied his request for compensation.","translation":"保險公司拒絕了他在車禍後提出的損害賠償要求。他已提交了所有必要文件，但他們拒絕了他的索賠要求。","word":"claim"}},"clap":{"createdAt":1781323901186,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"clap意為「鼓掌」或「拍手」，用來表達對表演者的欣賞和認可。","options":["boo","clap","whistle","shout"],"sentence":"When the performance ended, the entire audience stood up to ______ enthusiastically. The thunderous applause lasted for several minutes as a sign of appreciation.","translation":"當表演結束時，整個觀眾都站起來熱烈鼓掌。雷鳴般的掌聲持續了幾分鐘，表示讚賞。","word":"clap"}},"clarify":{"createdAt":1781337343697,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"clarify意為澄清、闡明或使事情變得清楚明白。","options":["obscure","clarify","ignore","complicate"],"sentence":"The spokesperson held a press conference to ______ the confusing statements made by the government earlier. The journalist's persistent questions forced him to provide specific and detailed explanations.","translation":"發言人舉行新聞發布會澄清政府早前做出的令人困惑的聲明。記者持續的提問迫使他提供具體和詳細的解釋。","word":"clarify"}},"clarity":{"createdAt":1781951900950,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"clarity指清楚明瞭的品質，使人能夠容易理解，與「每個人都明白」的結果相符。","options":["confusion","complexity","clarity","intelligence"],"sentence":"The teacher appreciated the student's ______ when she explained her ideas in simple, direct language. Everyone in the class immediately understood what she meant.","translation":"老師讚賞學生用簡潔直接的語言解釋她的想法時的清晰易懂。班上的每個人都立即明白了她的意思。","word":"clarity"}},"clash":{"createdAt":1781425737122,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"clash 作動詞時指發生衝突、碰撞或對抗，與軍隊之間的戰鬥相符。","options":["dance","clash","negotiate","rest"],"sentence":"The two opposing armies will ______ at dawn tomorrow on the battlefield. The collision between their forces will determine the outcome of the entire war.","translation":"兩支對立的軍隊明天黎明時將在戰場上發生衝突。他們軍隊之間的碰撞將決定整場戰爭的結果。","word":"clash"}},"clasp":{"createdAt":1781799990470,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"clasp是指用手臂或手緊緊握住或抱住某人或某物，表示緊密而用力的握住或擁抱。","options":["release","clasp","wave","guide"],"sentence":"The frightened child began to ______ her mother's hand tightly as they walked through the dark hallway. Her grip was so strong that it took considerable effort to gently loosen her fingers.","translation":"當這個受驚的孩子走過黑暗的走廊時，開始緊緊抓住媽媽的手。她的握力如此之強，需要相當的力氣才能溫和地鬆開她的手指。","word":"clasp"}},"classical":{"createdAt":1781832549169,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"classical 用來形容符合古典風格的音樂、藝術或文學作品，通常指歐洲傳統的古典時期。","options":["modern","classical","experimental","pop"],"sentence":"The orchestra performed several ______ pieces at the concert, including symphonies by Beethoven and Mozart. The audience appreciated the elegance and complexity of these timeless compositions from the 18th and 19th centuries.","translation":"交響樂團在音樂會上演奏了幾首古典樂曲，包括貝多芬和莫札特的交響曲。觀眾欣賞了這些來自18和19世紀的永恆作品的優雅和複雜性。","word":"classical"}},"classification":{"createdAt":1781478568768,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"classification 指將事物按照特定標準進行分類或分級的過程。","options":["decoration","classification","description","illustration"],"sentence":"The library's ______ system organizes books by subject, author, and genre. Students found it much easier to locate materials using this organized method.","translation":"圖書館的分類系統按主題、作者和類型組織書籍。學生們發現使用這種有組織的方法更容易找到資料。","word":"classification"}},"clause":{"createdAt":1781799990468,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"clause是指法律文件或合約中的特定條款或條文，用來規定特定的權利或義務。","options":["chapter","clause","section","agreement"],"sentence":"The employment contract contained a non-compete ______ that prevented employees from working for rival companies. This specific provision was designed to protect the company's trade secrets for five years.","translation":"這份就業合約包含了一項禁業競爭條款，禁止員工為競爭公司工作。這項具體條款旨在保護該公司的商業機密五年。","word":"clause"}},"client":{"createdAt":1781343050500,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"client 指律師、顧問等服務提供者的客戶或委託人，他們需要專業服務。","options":["employees","competitors","client","strangers"],"sentence":"The law firm has many satisfied ______ who return for legal advice year after year. These individuals and companies trust the firm with their most sensitive matters.","translation":"這家律師事務所有許多滿意的客戶，他們多年來一直回來尋求法律建議。這些個人和公司信任該公司處理他們最敏感的事務。","word":"client"}},"cling":{"createdAt":1781425737126,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cling 表示黏著、依附或緊緊抓住，與孩子緊握母親的手和尋求安全感相符。","options":["release","cling","push","ignore"],"sentence":"The frightened child will ______ to her mother's hand tightly as they walk through the crowded market. She refuses to let go because she feels safe and protected only when holding onto her.","translation":"驚嚇的孩子走過擁擠的市場時會緊緊抓住她母親的手。她拒絕放開，因為只有緊握著母親時才感到安全和受保護。","word":"cling"}},"clinic":{"createdAt":1781837048333,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"clinic是指提供基本醫療服務的診所或小型醫療設施，通常不如醫院規模大。","options":["gymnasium","clinic","library","restaurant"],"sentence":"My grandmother visits the ______ every week to get her blood pressure checked. The facility is located right next to the hospital, making it convenient for basic medical consultations and routine check-ups.","translation":"我的祖母每週都去診所檢查血壓。這個設施位於醫院旁邊，方便進行基本的醫療諮詢和定期檢查。","word":"clinic"}},"clinical":{"createdAt":1781667024991,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"clinical指與患者直接相關的醫療實踐，而非單純的理論或實驗室研究。","options":["theoretical","laboratory","clinical","experimental"],"sentence":"The ______ trial tested the new drug on human patients rather than in a laboratory. Researchers observed real-world effects and side effects to ensure safety and efficacy.","translation":"臨床試驗在人類患者身上而不是在實驗室測試了新藥。研究人員觀察了真實世界的效果和副作用，以確保安全性和有效性。","word":"clinical"}},"clockwise":{"createdAt":1781693271587,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"clockwise指的是順時針方向，與鐘錶指針運動方向相同，counterclockwise則是相反方向。","options":["counterclockwise","clockwise","leftward","backward"],"sentence":"The instructor told everyone to rotate their bodies in a ______ direction during the exercise class. The students spun from left to right, moving in the same direction as watch hands.","translation":"教練在運動課上告訴所有人按順時針方向旋轉他們的身體。學生們從左向右旋轉，按照手錶指針相同的方向移動。","word":"clockwise"}},"clone":{"createdAt":1781311685832,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"clone是指通過複製遺傳物質而製造出來的完全相同的個體或物品，強調了遺傳學上的相同性。","options":["mutation","replica","species","hybrid"],"sentence":"The scientist created a ______ of the original sheep by copying its DNA. This genetic duplicate was identical to the animal it came from.","translation":"科學家通過複製其DNA為原始綿羊製造了一個複製品。這個遺傳學上的相同個體與它來自的動物完全一致。","word":"clone"}},"closure":{"createdAt":1781274482554,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"closure在心理上指達到解脫或寬慰的狀態，通常涉及接納和放下過去。","options":["excitement","anger","closure","confusion"],"sentence":"After years of therapy, she finally found ______ regarding her painful childhood memories. The peace and acceptance she gained allowed her to move forward with her life.","translation":"經過多年的治療，她終於對痛苦的童年記憶獲得了寬慰。她獲得的平靜和接納使她能夠繼續前進。","word":"closure"}},"clue":{"createdAt":1781362281667,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"clue表示線索或提示，幫助找到答案或解決問題。","options":["witness","clue","suspect","weapon"],"sentence":"The detective found an important ______ at the crime scene. This piece of evidence helped solve the mysterious case.","translation":"偵探在犯罪現場發現了重要的線索。這條證據幫助破解了神秘案件。","word":"clue"}},"cluster":{"createdAt":1781257238301,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cluster指緊密聚集在一起的一群或一簇東西，特別是指物理上相連的物體。","options":["single","cluster","line","row"],"sentence":"A ______ of grapes hung from the vineyard vine. The farmer carefully harvested the tightly-grouped bunches together because they were all attached at the same point.","translation":"一串葡萄從葡萄園的藤蔓上掛下來。農民小心地將這些緊密分組的葡萄束一起收穫，因為它們都附著在同一個地方。","word":"cluster"}},"clutter":{"createdAt":1781274482560,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"clutter指亂堆或塞滿東西，導致空間變得雜亂無序。","options":["organize","clutter","clean","decorate"],"sentence":"She decided to ______ her living room with too many decorations and furniture. The space became so cramped and disorganized that guests could barely move around.","translation":"她決定用太多裝飾品和家具堆滿客廳。這個空間變得如此擁擠和混亂，以至於客人幾乎無法走動。","word":"clutter"}},"coach":{"createdAt":1781272410986,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"coach指的是教練，專門指導和訓練運動員或學生提高他們的技能和表現。","options":["referee","coach","athlete","spectator"],"sentence":"The basketball ______ teaches his players new strategies and techniques every week. Without his guidance and training sessions, the team would not have won the championship.","translation":"籃球教練每週教導他的球員新的戰術和技巧。沒有他的指導和訓練課程，這支隊伍就不會贏得冠軍。","word":"coach"}},"coalition":{"createdAt":1781927792734,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"coalition指的是為了達成共同目標而由多個團體或政治力量所組成的臨時聯合體。","options":["coalition","competition","rebellion","faction"],"sentence":"The opposition parties formed a ______ to challenge the ruling government in the election. Three separate organizations united their resources and political strategies to compete against the incumbent party.","translation":"反對黨組成一個聯盟來在選舉中挑戰執政政府。三個獨立的組織聯合他們的資源和政治戰略來與現任政黨競爭。","word":"coalition"}},"coarse":{"createdAt":1781449095508,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"coarse意為粗糙的、不光滑的，用來描述物體表面或材質的質感。","options":["smooth","coarse","soft","silky"],"sentence":"The sandpaper's ______ texture made it ideal for removing paint. Its rough surface was much harsher than fine-grit paper.","translation":"砂紙的粗糙紋理使其適合用於去除油漆。它的表面比細顆粒紙粗糙得多。","word":"coarse"}},"coast":{"createdAt":1781443653218,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"coast指的是陸地與海洋相接的邊界，即海岸線或濱海地帶。","options":["mountain","coast","desert","forest"],"sentence":"The small fishing village was located on a rocky ______ where waves crashed against ancient stone cliffs. Tourists visited every summer to enjoy the scenic beauty of the shoreline.","translation":"這個小漁村位於海岸上，那裡海浪拍打著古老的石崖。遊客每年夏天都來享受海岸線的優美景色。","word":"coast"}},"coastal":{"createdAt":1781274482553,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"coastal指靠近海岸或與海岸相關的地方，通常有沙灘和海洋活動。","options":["mountain","coastal","desert","forest"],"sentence":"The ______ town attracted thousands of tourists every summer. Visitors enjoyed swimming in the ocean and walking along sandy beaches.","translation":"那個海邊小鎮每年夏天吸引數千名遊客。遊客享受在海洋中游泳和沿著沙灘散步。","word":"coastal"}},"cognition":{"createdAt":1781837419087,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"認知是指人類的思維、記憶、理解等心智過程。","options":["emotion","cognition","behavior","growth"],"sentence":"The study examined how ______ develops in young children over time. Researchers measured their ability to think, remember, and understand the world around them.","translation":"這項研究檢視了幼兒認知能力如何隨時間發展。研究人員衡量了他們思考、記憶和理解周圍世界的能力。","word":"cognition"}},"cognitive":{"createdAt":1781664082521,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cognitive 指與認知、思考和感知有關的，涉及心理過程和精神活動。","options":["physical","cognitive","emotional","social"],"sentence":"Children develop ______ abilities as they grow, improving their memory and problem-solving skills. These mental processes help them understand and process information better.","translation":"兒童隨著成長發展認知能力，改善他們的記憶力和解決問題的能力。這些心理過程幫助他們更好地理解和處理信息。","word":"cognitive"}},"coherent":{"createdAt":1781965320892,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"coherent 表示論述或想法的連貫性和邏輯性，各部分有機地連接在一起。","options":["confusing","scattered","coherent","contradictory"],"sentence":"The professor's explanation was so ______ that students could easily follow the logical flow from beginning to end. Each point connected naturally to the next one.","translation":"教授的解釋非常連貫，學生可以輕鬆從開始到結束跟隨邏輯流程。每個要點都自然地連接到下一個。","word":"coherent"}},"collaboration":{"createdAt":1781417610415,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"collaboration是指多個人或團體為了共同目標而一起合作、協力工作。","options":["competition","collaboration","isolation","conflict"],"sentence":"The successful project was the result of ______ between the three departments. Without teamwork and shared goals, the departments would have failed to achieve their objectives.","translation":"這個成功的專案是三個部門之間協作的結果。沒有團隊合作和共同目標，這些部門將無法實現他們的目標。","word":"collaboration"}},"collapse":{"createdAt":1781843396460,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"collapse作為名詞，表示結構或系統的突然失敗或倒塌，在此指建築物物理性的倒下。","options":["construction","collapse","expansion","development"],"sentence":"The building's sudden ______ shocked the entire neighborhood. Rescue teams rushed to the site after the structure fell to the ground.","translation":"該建築物的突然倒塌震驚了整個社區。結構倒地後，救援隊立即趕往現場。","word":"collapse"}},"colleague":{"createdAt":1781783820679,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"colleague指的是在同一家公司或機構中與你一起工作的人，通常是平級的工作夥伴。","options":["friend","colleague","manager","client"],"sentence":"I need to discuss this project with my ______ before the meeting. We both work in the same department and have collaborated on several tasks together.","translation":"我需要在會議前與我的同事討論這個項目。我們都在同一部門工作，並且一起合作過幾項任務。","word":"colleague"}},"collect":{"createdAt":1781274836866,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"collect作為動詞表示把分散的東西聚集在一起或收集，通常指有系統地聚集多個物品。","options":["distribute","lose","collect","grade"],"sentence":"The teacher asked all students to ______ their homework assignments before the end of class. She walked around the room and gathered papers from each desk one by one.","translation":"老師要求所有學生在下課前交出他們的作業。她在教室裡走動，逐張地從每張課桌上收集論文。","word":"collect"}},"collection":{"createdAt":1781871338557,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"collection表示經過長期精心收集和保存的物品集合。","options":["waste","group","compilation","hobby"],"sentence":"My grandfather spent fifty years building his ______ of rare stamps from around the world. Each stamp in his display case is carefully preserved and valued.","translation":"我祖父花費五十年時間收集來自世界各地的稀有郵票。他展示櫃中的每枚郵票都被仔細保存和珍視。","word":"collection"}},"collide":{"createdAt":1781799990469,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"collide是指兩個物體以強力相撞或互相碰撞，也可引申為觀點、意見等相牴觸。","options":["approach","collide","pass","follow"],"sentence":"The two vehicles began to ______ at the intersection when neither driver noticed the red traffic light. The impact was severe enough to trigger both airbag systems.","translation":"當兩名駕駛都沒有注意到紅燈時，這兩輛車在十字路口開始相撞。撞擊劇烈到足以觸發兩個安全氣囊系統。","word":"collide"}},"collision":{"createdAt":1782006648202,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"collision 指的是兩個物體或車輛之間的碰撞事件，通常造成損害。","options":["journey","collision","adventure","competition"],"sentence":"The two cars were involved in a serious ______ on the highway. The impact was so severe that both vehicles were completely destroyed.","translation":"兩輛汽車在高速公路上發生了一場嚴重的碰撞。撞擊是如此猛烈，以至於兩輛車都完全毀壞了。","word":"collision"}},"colloquial":{"createdAt":1781799990468,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"colloquial是指非正式的、日常的、口語的語言風格，通常用於日常交流而不是正式場合。","options":["poetic","colloquial","technical","archaic"],"sentence":"The author's writing style became increasingly ______ as the novel progressed. Rather than using formal academic language, the characters spoke in everyday phrases and slang that readers could easily understand.","translation":"隨著小說的進展，作者的寫作風格變得越來越口語化。她沒有使用正式的學術語言，而是讓角色用讀者容易理解的日常短語和俚語交談。","word":"colloquial"}},"colonial":{"createdAt":1781836375370,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"colonial形容詞表示與殖民地有關的，特別是指歐洲殖民統治時期。","options":["modern","colonial","revolutionary","contemporary"],"sentence":"The museum displayed artifacts from the ______ period of American history. These items included furniture and tools used when the country was under British rule.","translation":"博物館展出了美國歷史上殖民地時期的工藝品。這些物品包括該國受英國統治時期使用的家具和工具。","word":"colonial"}},"colonist":{"createdAt":1781363994345,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"colonist指的是前往他人土地上建立殖民地的人，他們在新領土上定居並建立社區。","options":["explorer","settler","merchant","king"],"sentence":"The early ______ established settlements in the New World during the 17th century. These pioneers built homes, farms, and communities far from their native countries.","translation":"早期的殖民者在17世紀在新大陸建立了定居點。這些先驅在遠離祖國的地方建造了家園、農場和社區。","word":"colonist"}},"colony":{"createdAt":1781345237580,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"colony指受主權國家統治的領土或殖民地，特別是在海外建立的定居點。","options":["empire","colony","nation","kingdom"],"sentence":"The British ______ in North America included Virginia, Massachusetts, and Georgia. These settlements were established along the eastern coast during the 17th and 18th centuries.","translation":"北美的英國殖民地包括維吉尼亞州、麻薩諸塞州和喬治亞州。這些定居點是在17和18世紀沿著東海岸建立的。","word":"colony"}},"column":{"createdAt":1781424157175,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"column 在報紙或雜誌中指定期發表的專欄或評論文章。","options":["headline","column","article","advertisement"],"sentence":"The newspaper's advice ______ was written by a psychologist who answered readers' personal questions every week. Thousands of people followed this section closely to get professional guidance.","translation":"報紙的建議專欄由一位心理學家撰寫，每週回答讀者的個人問題。成千上萬的人密切關注這個欄目以獲取專業指導。","word":"column"}},"columnist":{"createdAt":1781257238300,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"columnist是指定期為報紙或雜誌撰寫專欄文章的人。","options":["editor","columnist","printer","photographer"],"sentence":"Sarah works as a ______ for the newspaper, writing articles about current events. Every Monday, her opinion piece appears on page five of the publication.","translation":"莎拉在報紙上擔任專欄作家，撰寫關於時事的文章。每週一，她的評論文章都會出現在該出版物的第五頁。","word":"columnist"}},"combination":{"createdAt":1781402539337,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"combination 指多個元素或數字的特定排列方式，合在一起產生特定的結果。","options":["lock","combination","password","key"],"sentence":"The safe requires a ______ of numbers to open. You must enter them in the correct sequence, starting with 7-15-23.","translation":"這個保險箱需要一個號碼組合才能打開。你必須按正確的順序輸入它們，從7-15-23開始。","word":"combination"}},"combine":{"createdAt":1781776694540,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"combine 是動詞，意思是將兩個或多個事物混合或聯合在一起。","options":["separate","combine","freeze","measure"],"sentence":"The recipe asks you to ______ the flour and sugar in a large bowl. Mix these two dry ingredients together thoroughly before adding the wet ingredients.","translation":"食譜要求你在大碗裡把麵粉和糖混合在一起。在加入濕性材料之前，徹底混合這兩種乾性材料。","word":"combine"}},"combined":{"createdAt":1781871338560,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"combined表示多個事物或力量結合在一起，與pooled resources和together的概念相符。","options":["individual","separate","joint","competitive"],"sentence":"The ______ efforts of the two research teams led to a breakthrough in cancer treatment. Together, they pooled their expertise and resources to achieve success.","translation":"兩個研究小組的聯合努力導致了癌症治療的突破。他們匯集專業知識和資源，一起取得了成功。","word":"combined"}},"comedian":{"createdAt":1781485266373,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"comedian指的是以表演幽默、講笑話和逗樂觀眾為職業的演員。","options":["musician","dancer","comedian","singer"],"sentence":"The ______ took the stage and immediately made the audience roar with laughter. His timing and witty jokes kept everyone entertained for the entire hour-long performance.","translation":"這位喜劇演員走上舞台，立即讓觀眾爆笑。他的時機把握和機智的笑話讓每個人在整個一小時的表演中都開懷大笑。","word":"comedian"}},"comfort":{"createdAt":1781428458250,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"comfort在這裡表示安慰或支持，用來幫助某人度過難過的情緒。","options":["lecture","comfort","citation","crisis"],"sentence":"After losing the competition, Sarah needed some ______ from her parents. They hugged her and told her that she had done her best, which made her feel much better.","translation":"在輸掉比賽後，莎拉需要父母的安慰。他們擁抱她，並告訴她她已經盡力了，這讓她感到好多了。","word":"comfort"}},"comforting":{"createdAt":1781832549167,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"comforting 用來形容能夠給予安慰、消除憂慮或不安的事物或言語。","options":["harsh","comforting","confusing","insulting"],"sentence":"After losing the competition, Sarah found the coach's words very ______, which helped ease her disappointment. She realized that his emphasis on her improvement rather than the loss was exactly what she needed to hear.","translation":"在輸掉比賽後，莎拉發現教練的話非常令人欣慰，這幫助她緩解了失望的心情。她意識到他強調的是她的進步而不是失敗，這正是她需要聽到的。","word":"comforting"}},"comic":{"createdAt":1781582251995,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"comic 是形容詞，表示有趣的、好笑的、能引人發笑的特質。","options":["tragic","serious","comic","dramatic"],"sentence":"The ______ performance made the entire audience burst into laughter throughout the show. The comedian's timing and physical humor were absolutely perfect.","translation":"那場滑稽的表演讓整個觀眾在演出期間始終笑聲不斷。那位喜劇演員的時機和肢體幽默表現得完美無瑕。","word":"comic"}},"comics":{"createdAt":1781837601402,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"comics 是漫畫的統稱，指以連續圖畫和對白框組成的視覺敘事作品，通常包含故事情節和人物對話。","options":["novels","comics","magazines","newspapers"],"sentence":"My brother spent his pocket money on action-packed ______ from the bookstore last weekend. The colorful illustrated stories with speech bubbles were his favorite type of reading material.","translation":"我哥哥上週末用零花錢在書店裡買了充滿動作的漫畫。帶有對白框和彩色插圖的故事是他最喜歡的閱讀材料。","word":"comics"}},"commence":{"createdAt":1781425093249,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"commence 是正式的動詞，表示某事物的開始或著手進行。","options":["finish","commence","postpone","conclude"],"sentence":"The new semester will ______ on Monday morning with a special assembly for all students. The principal has already scheduled the opening speech to begin at 8:30 AM sharp.","translation":"新學期將於週一早上開始，並為所有學生舉辦特別集會。校長已經安排開幕致詞在上午8:30準時開始。","word":"commence"}},"comment":{"createdAt":1781667024997,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"comment是指對某事的看法或評論，通常提供建設性的意見或觀察。","options":["grade","comment","score","mark"],"sentence":"The teacher made a helpful ______ on Maria's essay about her writing style and grammar. Maria used the feedback to revise and improve her work for the final draft.","translation":"老師在瑪麗亞的關於寫作風格和語法的論文上做了一條有幫助的評論。瑪麗亞利用這些反饋來修改和改進她的最終稿。","word":"comment"}},"commentary":{"createdAt":1781485266372,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"commentary指的是對事件或表演的評論和評述，通常由專家或評論員提供。","options":["silence","quiet","commentary","voice"],"sentence":"The sports ______ provided insightful analysis throughout the entire basketball game. His remarks explained the team's strategy and predicted their next moves with remarkable accuracy.","translation":"這位運動評論員在整場籃球比賽中提供了深刻的分析。他的評論解釋了球隊的策略並以驚人的準確性預測了他們的下一步行動。","word":"commentary"}},"commentator":{"createdAt":1781274482558,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"commentator指在廣播或電視上進行實況評論和分析的人，通常提供專業見解。","options":["player","coach","commentator","fan"],"sentence":"The sports ______ provided live analysis of the football match. His expert insights and real-time observations helped viewers understand the strategy and tactics being used.","translation":"體育評論員對足球比賽進行現場分析。他的專業見解和實時評論幫助觀眾理解所使用的戰略和戰術。","word":"commentator"}},"commerce":{"createdAt":1781343050502,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"commerce 指商業貿易和商業活動，涉及商品的買賣和交換。","options":["agriculture","art","commerce","sports"],"sentence":"International ______ between countries has grown significantly due to improved transportation. Businesses now export and import goods across continents daily.","translation":"由於運輸改善，國家間的貿易顯著增長。企業現在每天都在跨洲出口和進口商品。","word":"commerce"}},"commercialize":{"createdAt":1782006648203,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"commercialize 指的是將產品或服務轉變為商業性的活動，以賺取利潤。","options":["publicize","donate","commercialize","simplify"],"sentence":"The startup decided to ______ their popular social media app by introducing premium features and advertisements. Within months, they generated millions of dollars in revenue from these business strategies.","translation":"這家新創公司決定通過引入高級功能和廣告來將其受歡迎的社交媒體應用商業化。幾個月內，他們從這些商業策略中產生了數百萬美元的收入。","word":"commercialize"}},"commercially":{"createdAt":1781493458243,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"commercially 副詞表示以商業目的或商業方式進行，指產品進入市場進行銷售","options":["privately","secretly","commercially","slowly"],"sentence":"The small startup decided to produce and sell its new invention ______ to reach a wider market. Within months, their products were available in stores across the country.","translation":"這家小型新創公司決定以商業方式生產和銷售其新發明，以達到更廣泛的市場。數個月內，他們的產品在全國各地的商店都可購買。","word":"commercially"}},"commit":{"createdAt":1781401803895,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"commit在這裡表示「犯（罪）」，指實施或進行一個不法行為。","options":["dedicate","perpetrate","promise","invest"],"sentence":"The criminal decided to ______ a serious robbery at the bank. Police found evidence that he had planned this illegal act for several months in advance.","translation":"那個罪犯決定在銀行犯下一樁嚴重的搶劫罪。警察發現他提前幾個月就計畫好了這個非法行為。","word":"commit"}},"commitment":{"createdAt":1781664082528,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"commitment 表示承諾、保證或致力於某事，指決心去做某事並為之負責。","options":["doubt","commitment","hesitation","confusion"],"sentence":"Her strong ______ to environmental protection led her to dedicate her career to conservation work. She volunteers regularly and advocates for sustainable practices in her community.","translation":"她對環境保護的堅定承諾使她將職業奉獻給了保護工作。她定期志願服務並在社區中倡導可持續實踐。","word":"commitment"}},"committed":{"createdAt":1781871338567,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"committed表示對某事有堅定的承諾和奉獻，與投入時間和精力相符。","options":["opposed","indifferent","dedicated","resistant"],"sentence":"The volunteer is deeply ______ to helping underprivileged children access quality education. She dedicates at least twenty hours every week to this noble cause.","translation":"這位志願者致力於幫助貧困兒童獲得優質教育。她每週至少花費二十個小時投入這項崇高事業。","word":"committed"}},"committee":{"createdAt":1781840659327,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"committee 是指為特定目的組成的正式組織機構，成員共同工作以做出決策。","options":["student","committee","audience","crowd"],"sentence":"The ______ met for three hours to discuss the new policy proposals. The fifteen members reviewed documents and voted on the recommendations together.","translation":"委員會開會三小時討論新的政策提案。這十五位成員一起審查文件並對建議進行投票。","word":"committee"}},"common":{"createdAt":1781794866339,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"common表示普通的、常見的，用來形容廣為人知的事物或現象。","options":["rare","common","secret","disputed"],"sentence":"It is ______ knowledge that water boils at 100 degrees Celsius. Most people learn this basic scientific fact in elementary school.","translation":"水在攝氏100度沸騰是______ 知識。大多數人在小學時就學習了這個基本科學事實。","word":"common"}},"commonwealth":{"createdAt":1781343050503,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"commonwealth 指由多個國家或地區組成的政治聯合體，成員國之間有共同的政治和經濟聯繫。","options":["kingdom","empire","commonwealth","republic"],"sentence":"Australia is a ______ with a parliamentary system that includes Britain's monarch as head of state. Its member nations cooperate on various political and economic issues.","translation":"澳大利亞是一個國家聯合體，採用議會制，英國君主為國家元首。其成員國在各種政治和經濟問題上合作。","word":"commonwealth"}},"communicate":{"createdAt":1781429945498,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"communicate 是指進行溝通或傳達信息，強調雙向的交流和理解。","options":["argue","communicate","ignore","punish"],"sentence":"Parents should ______ regularly with their children about their feelings and concerns. Without open dialogue, misunderstandings between family members often grow worse.","translation":"父母應該定期與孩子溝通他們的感受和顧慮。如果沒有開放的對話，家庭成員之間的誤會往往會惡化。","word":"communicate"}},"communication":{"createdAt":1781693484715,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"communication 是指人與人之間的資訊交換和訊息傳遞，是相互理解的過程。","options":["cooperation","communication","competition","compensation"],"sentence":"Effective ______ between parents and teachers helps students succeed in school. Without regular conversations and updates, misunderstandings can easily occur.","translation":"父母和老師之間有效的溝通有助於學生在學校取得成功。沒有定期的對話和訊息更新，很容易產生誤解。","word":"communication"}},"communicative":{"createdAt":1781343050498,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"communicative 指樂於交流、健談的，與經常發言和分享想法的行為相符。","options":["shy","quiet","communicative","reserved"],"sentence":"Sarah is very ______ in meetings and always shares her ideas freely. She speaks up constantly and encourages others to participate in discussions.","translation":"莎拉在會議中很健談，總是自由地分享她的想法。她經常發言，並鼓勵他人參與討論。","word":"communicative"}},"communism":{"createdAt":1781343050497,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"communism 是一種政治和經濟制度，馬克思和列寧都是共產主義的倡導者。","options":["democracy","capitalism","communism","monarchy"],"sentence":"The Soviet Union was founded on the principles of ______ and collective ownership. Marx and Lenin were key figures in promoting this ideology.","translation":"蘇聯是建立在共產主義和集體所有制的原則基礎上的。馬克思和列寧是推行這一意識形態的關鍵人物。","word":"communism"}},"communist":{"createdAt":1781395428236,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"communist 作為形容詞或名詞，指與共產主義或共產黨相關的人或思想體系。","options":["democratic","communist","capitalist","monarchist"],"sentence":"During the Cold War, many countries feared the spread of ______ ideology from the Soviet Union. The government implemented policies specifically to prevent this political system from gaining influence.","translation":"冷戰期間，許多國家害怕蘇聯共產主義意識形態的傳播。政府實施了具體政策來阻止這一政治制度的影響力增長。","word":"communist"}},"commuter":{"createdAt":1781332009082,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"commuter 是名詞，指的是定期往返於家庭和工作場所之間的人","options":["tourist","commuter","driver","pedestrian"],"sentence":"The ______ took the same train every morning to get to work in the city. He had been following this routine for over five years.","translation":"這位通勤者每天早上都乘坐同一列火車去城市工作。他已經遵循這一慣例超過五年。","word":"commuter"}},"compact":{"createdAt":1781583174627,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"compact意指體積小、結構緊密，設計得能節省空間但功能完整","options":["spacious","sturdy","compact","elegant"],"sentence":"This ______ car is perfect for city driving since it fits easily into small parking spaces. Its small size allows drivers to navigate through narrow streets without difficulty.","translation":"這輛____汽車非常適合城市駕駛，因為它可以輕鬆停進小停車位。它的小尺寸使駕駛員能夠輕鬆地在狹窄的街道上行駛。","word":"compact"}},"companion":{"createdAt":1781667024995,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"companion是指一起進行活動並分享經歷的同伴或夥伴，強調陪伴和友誼的關係。","options":["guide","companion","stranger","tourist"],"sentence":"During her solo journey across Europe, Sarah found a travel ______ who shared her interests and made the experience more enjoyable. They explored cities together and became lifelong friends.","translation":"在獨自橫跨歐洲的旅程中，莎拉找到了一位分享她興趣的旅遊同伴，使經歷更加愉快。他們一起探索了城市，成為了終身朋友。","word":"companion"}},"company":{"createdAt":1781359980249,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"company作為名詞有陪伴、同伴的意思；指與他人在一起的伴隨或相處的狀態。","options":["absence","rivalry","company","service"],"sentence":"She enjoyed the ______ of her grandmother during the long winter evenings. They spent hours together playing cards and sharing stories from the past.","translation":"她喜歡在漫長的冬夜陪伴祖母。他們花了好幾個小時一起打牌和分享過去的故事。","word":"company"}},"comparable":{"createdAt":1781481072319,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"comparable 表示「可比的、類似的、相當的」，用於比較兩個事物時具有相似的特點或價值。","options":["superior","inferior","comparable","complex"],"sentence":"The performance of the new smartphone is ______ to the leading brand on the market. Both devices offer similar processing speeds, camera quality, and battery life at nearly identical price points.","translation":"這部新智慧手機的性能與市場上的領先品牌相當。兩部設備提供相似的處理速度、攝影品質和電池壽命，價格幾乎相同。","word":"comparable"}},"comparative":{"createdAt":1781849622417,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"比較的是指涉及將兩個或多個事物進行對比以找出相似或差異的，它強調相對關係而非絕對事實。","options":["absolute","comparative","theoretical","historical"],"sentence":"The ______ study examined how different countries handle healthcare systems. By analyzing multiple nations side by side, researchers could identify strengths and weaknesses in each approach.","translation":"這項比較研究檢查了不同國家如何處理醫療保健系統。通過並排分析多個國家，研究人員可以確定每種方法的優缺點。","word":"comparative"}},"compassionate":{"createdAt":1781332009072,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"compassionate 意為有同情心的、富有同情的，表示對他人的痛苦和困難有深刻的同情","options":["cruel","compassionate","impatient","rude"],"sentence":"The ______ doctor spent extra time with each patient, listening to their concerns. She genuinely cared about their well-being and treated everyone with kindness and respect.","translation":"有同情心的醫生為每位患者花費了額外的時間，聆聽他們的關切。她真心關心他們的福祉，用善良和尊重對待每個人。","word":"compassionate"}},"compatible":{"createdAt":1781665727104,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"compatible 表示兩人或兩事物協調一致、投緣，適合一起共處或配合。","options":["anxious","compatible","hostile","uncertain"],"sentence":"Sarah and Mike have a ______ relationship because they share similar values and enjoy spending time together. Their families were thrilled when they announced their engagement last month.","translation":"莎拉和麥克的關係是相容的，因為他們有相似的價值觀，喜歡花時間在一起。當他們上月宣布訂婚時，他們的家人都欣喜若狂。","word":"compatible"}},"compel":{"createdAt":1781402154554,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"compel表示強迫或迫使某人做某事，在這裡指法律強制公司採取特定行動。","options":["compel","suspect","lottery","hijack"],"sentence":"The new law will ______ all companies to reduce their plastic waste by 30%. Failure to comply with this regulation will result in substantial fines and penalties.","translation":"新法律將強迫所有公司將塑料廢物減少30%。不遵守此規定將導致巨額罰款和處罰。","word":"compel"}},"compensate":{"createdAt":1781427134897,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"compensate表示給予金錢或其他報酬來補償或償還某人。","options":["promote","compensate","terminate","schedule"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ employees for the overtime work they completed last month. Management approved a special bonus payment to reward their extra effort.","translation":"公司決定為員工上個月完成的加班工作進行補償。管理層批准了一筆特別獎金來獎勵他們的額外努力。","word":"compensate"}},"compete":{"createdAt":1781884659834,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"compete 意指在比賽或競爭中參與，與奧運會和獎牌競逐的語境相符。","options":["train","compete","celebrate","prepare"],"sentence":"Many athletes ______ in the Olympic Games every four years to earn medals and recognition. Only the most dedicated and skilled performers make it to the international stage.","translation":"許多運動員每四年在奧運會上競爭以獲得獎牌和認可。只有最敬業和最有技能的表演者才能進入國際舞台。","word":"compete"}},"competence":{"createdAt":1781332009079,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"competence 是名詞，表示能力或勝任能力，指做好某事所需的技能","options":["incompetence","competence","weakness","inexperience"],"sentence":"The manager demonstrated her ______ by successfully leading the complex project to completion. Her team members trusted her judgment and relied on her expertise.","translation":"經理通過成功領導複雜項目完成來展示她的能力。她的團隊成員信任她的判斷並依賴她的專業知識。","word":"competence"}},"competent":{"createdAt":1781272410987,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"competent表示具有能力、勝任的、能幹的，用來形容一個人在某方面具有足夠的技能和知識。","options":["lazy","incompetent","competent","dishonest"],"sentence":"The software developer proved to be ______ at solving complex programming problems. His manager decided to promote him because of his excellent skills and reliability.","translation":"這位軟體開發人員證明了他在解決複雜程式設計問題方面很能幹。他的經理因為他的優秀技能和可靠性而決定提拔他。","word":"competent"}},"competition":{"createdAt":1781425093251,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"competition 是名詞，表示比賽或競賽，通常涉及參與者之間的對抗或比較。","options":["cooperation","celebration","competition","cooperation"],"sentence":"The regional singing ______ attracted over 500 talented performers from different schools. Winners were announced after three days of intense judging and elimination rounds.","translation":"地區歌唱比賽吸引了來自不同學校的500多位才華橫溢的表演者。經過三天激烈的評判和淘汰賽後，宣佈了獲勝者。","word":"competition"}},"complementary":{"createdAt":1781274482564,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"complementary指能夠補充、完善或相互配合的事物，共同創造更完整的整體。","options":["opposite","identical","complementary","competing"],"sentence":"The two artists created ______ pieces that worked beautifully together in the exhibition. When displayed side by side, they enhanced and completed each other's visual narrative.","translation":"這兩位藝術家創作了在展覽中配合得很好的互補作品。當它們並排展示時，它們互相強化並完成彼此的視覺敘事。","word":"complementary"}},"complete":{"createdAt":1781532967170,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"complete 表示完整的、完成的，與「所有部分都已完成」的描述相符。","options":["partial","complete","ongoing","delayed"],"sentence":"The construction project is now ______ and ready for the grand opening ceremony. All the walls, floors, and decorations have been finished.","translation":"建築項目現在______(完整)，準備舉行盛大的開幕式。所有的牆壁、地板和裝飾都已完成。","word":"complete"}},"completion":{"createdAt":1781696018691,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"completion 意為完成，指事物達到終點、全部完成或達到預定目標的狀態。","options":["commencement","initiation","completion","halt"],"sentence":"The construction project was finally near ______ after two years of hard work and planning. The grand opening ceremony was scheduled for next month.","translation":"經過兩年的辛苦工作和規劃，這個建築項目終於接近完成。盛大開幕典禮定於下個月舉行。","word":"completion"}},"complexion":{"createdAt":1781323901186,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"complexion意為「膚色」，在此指人皮膚的顏色和質地。","options":["personality","complexion","attitude","expression"],"sentence":"She has a naturally beautiful ______ that glows even without makeup. The healthy pink and tan tones in her skin are inherited from her Mediterranean ancestry.","translation":"她天生擁有美麗的膚色，即使不化妝也閃閃發光。她皮膚上健康的粉紅色和棕褐色調是從她的地中海血統遺傳而來的。","word":"complexion"}},"compliance":{"createdAt":1781274482560,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"compliance指遵守規則、法律或要求的行為，表示順從和配合。","options":["violation","resistance","compliance","defiance"],"sentence":"The company's strict ______ with environmental regulations impressed the government inspectors. They followed every rule and submitted all required documentation on time.","translation":"公司嚴格遵守環境法規給政府檢查員留下深刻印象。他們遵循每項規則並按時提交所有必需的文件。","word":"compliance"}},"complicated":{"createdAt":1781850287961,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"complicated 指某事物結構複雜、難以理解或難以處理。","options":["detailed","lengthy","complicated","boring"],"sentence":"The assembly instructions for the furniture were far too ______ for most people to follow without assistance. Even the engineers at the company admitted that simplifying the steps would require a complete redesign.","translation":"傢俱的組裝說明對大多數人來說太過複雜，沒有幫助根本無法遵循。公司的工程師甚至承認簡化步驟需要完全重新設計。","word":"complicated"}},"complication":{"createdAt":1781836375375,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"complication是複雜情況或併發症，指使情況變得更困難的意外問題。","options":["difficulty","complication","issue","problem"],"sentence":"The surgery went smoothly without any ______ or unexpected problems. The patient recovered quickly and was discharged within two weeks.","translation":"手術進行順利，沒有任何併發症或意外問題。患者恢復快速，兩週內出院。","word":"complication"}},"compliment":{"createdAt":1781425093250,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"compliment 是名詞，表示對他人的讚美、恭維或褒獎。","options":["criticism","complaint","compliment","insult"],"sentence":"Sarah received a lovely ______ from her teacher about her excellent artwork in class. The teacher told her that her painting demonstrated remarkable creativity and skillful technique.","translation":"莎拉因她在課堂上的優秀藝術作品收到老師的讚美。老師告訴她，她的畫作展示了傑出的創意和高超的技巧。","word":"compliment"}},"comply":{"createdAt":1781332009078,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"comply 意為順從或遵守，表示按照規則或要求行動","options":["ignore","comply","break","violate"],"sentence":"All employees must ______ with the company's safety regulations without exception. The workplace has strict rules that everyone is required to follow.","translation":"所有員工都必須順從公司的安全規定，毫無例外。工作場所有所有人都必須遵守的嚴格規則。","word":"comply"}},"compose":{"createdAt":1781625891344,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"compose表示創作音樂、文章等藝術作品","options":["performed","composed","recorded","discovered"],"sentence":"The symphony was ______ by a famous Austrian musician in the 18th century. It consists of four distinct movements that showcase his musical genius.","translation":"這部交響曲是由一位著名的奧地利音樂家在18世紀創作的。它由四個不同的樂章組成，展示了他的音樂天才。","word":"compose"}},"composed":{"createdAt":1781437220557,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「Composed」形容詞表示一個人保持冷靜、鎮定，不受情緒干擾。","options":["panicked","anxious","composed","distressed"],"sentence":"Even during the chaotic emergency, the doctor remained ______ and made decisions with a steady hand. His calm demeanor helped reassure frightened patients in the waiting room.","translation":"即使在混亂的緊急情況下，醫生仍保持鎮定並以穩定的手做出決定。他的平靜表現幫助安撫了候診室裡受驚的患者。","word":"composed"}},"compound":{"createdAt":1781515329270,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"compound 名詞，意思是化合物、複合物，指由兩種或多種物質結合而成的物質。","options":["tool","compound","method","theory"],"sentence":"The pharmaceutical company developed a new ______ to treat the disease more effectively. Scientists combined multiple chemical elements to create this innovative medication with fewer side effects.","translation":"製藥公司開發了一種新的化合物，可以更有效地治療該疾病。科學家結合多種化學元素創造了這種副作用更少的創新藥物。","word":"compound"}},"comprehension":{"createdAt":1781842419967,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"comprehension指對某事物的理解或領悟能力；在這裡強調學生能夠掌握和應用所學知識。","options":["participation","comprehension","presentation","appreciation"],"sentence":"The student's ______ of the complex physics concept was impressive after just one lesson. She could explain every detail and solve problems without any confusion.","translation":"這位學生在一堂課後對複雜物理概念的理解令人印象深刻。她能夠解釋每一個細節，並毫無困惑地解決問題。","word":"comprehension"}},"compress":{"createdAt":1781838276304,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"compress作為動詞表示將某物壓縮或減小體積，以便傳輸或儲存。","options":["ordeal","compress","toll","claim"],"sentence":"You need to ______ the data files before sending them over email. The attachment size is currently too large to fit within the system's upload limit.","translation":"在通過電子郵件發送前，你需要壓縮數據文件。附件大小目前太大，超過了系統的上傳限制。","word":"compress"}},"comprise":{"createdAt":1781698273263,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"comprise 是動詞，表示「由...組成」或「包含」，指整體是由哪些部分或成員構成的。","options":["excludes","comprises","dismisses","questions"],"sentence":"The committee ______ representatives from five different departments within the company. Marketing, sales, operations, finance, and human resources all sent their delegates to the meeting.","translation":"該委員會由公司五個不同部門的代表組成。行銷、銷售、營運、財務和人力資源都派代表參加了會議。","word":"comprise"}},"compromise":{"createdAt":1781343050504,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"compromise 指雙方各退一步、互相讓步達成的協議，通常各方都需要放棄部分要求。","options":["victory","defeat","compromise","agreement"],"sentence":"After hours of negotiation, both parties reached a ______ that satisfied neither side completely. Each side had to give up some of their original demands to reach an agreement.","translation":"經過數小時的談判，雙方達成了妥協，都不完全滿意。雙方都不得不放棄他們最初的一些要求才能達成協議。","word":"compromise"}},"compulsory":{"createdAt":1781935654219,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"compulsory 意為強制性的、義務性的，表示必須執行的要求。","options":["optional","compulsory","temporary","beneficial"],"sentence":"Attendance at the safety training session is ______ for all new employees. Those who fail to attend will face disciplinary action.","translation":"所有新員工必須參加安全培訓課程。不參加的人將面臨紀律處分。","word":"compulsory"}},"compute":{"createdAt":1781332009078,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"compute 意為用機器或計算方法來計算或算出","options":["estimate","compute","guess","ignore"],"sentence":"The accountant used specialized software to ______ the company's annual financial statements. The calculations were complex and required precision to ensure accuracy.","translation":"會計師使用專門的軟件計算公司的年度財務報表。這些計算很複雜，需要精確確保準確性。","word":"compute"}},"conceal":{"createdAt":1781311685838,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"conceal意為隱藏或掩蓋，通常指故意將某物藏起來以避免被發現。","options":["display","hide","analyze","transport"],"sentence":"The criminal tried to ______ the evidence by burying it in the forest. However, the investigators discovered it buried under the old oak tree.","translation":"犯人試圖通過將證據埋在森林裡來隱藏它。然而，調查人員發現它被埋在老橡樹下。","word":"conceal"}},"concede":{"createdAt":1781860901465,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"concede表示讓步、認輸或承認，通常用於承認對方的勝利或正確性","options":["deny","concede","celebrate","ignore"],"sentence":"After losing the chess tournament, the champion had to ______ that his opponent played better. He acknowledged his defeat with grace and respect.","translation":"在輸掉國際象棋錦標賽後，冠軍不得不承認他的對手表現更好。他優雅而尊重地認可了自己的失敗。","word":"concede"}},"conceive":{"createdAt":1781323901178,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"conceive意為「構思」或「想像」，在此指科學家想出並發展了一個新的治療方案。","options":["abandon","conceive","dismiss","reject"],"sentence":"The scientist was able to ______ a revolutionary new treatment for the disease. After years of research and collaboration, her team finally brought this groundbreaking idea to life.","translation":"科學家能夠構思一種革命性的疾病新療法。經過多年的研究和合作，她的團隊終於將這個突破性的想法付諸實現。","word":"conceive"}},"concentrate":{"createdAt":1781332009077,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"concentrate 意為集中或集結，通常用於指集中注意力或將心力聚集在一件事上","options":["relax","concentrate","quit","sleep"],"sentence":"The student needed to ______ on her studies to improve her grades. With fewer distractions and dedicated study time, her academic performance improved significantly.","translation":"學生需要集中精力學習以提高成績。減少干擾和投入專門的學習時間後，她的學習成績明顯改善。","word":"concentrate"}},"concept":{"createdAt":1781965320889,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"concept 是指一個抽象的想法或觀念，常指理論上的概念而非具體事物。","options":["democracy","concept","government","principle"],"sentence":"The ______ of democracy is based on the idea that people should have a say in government. This abstract principle has been discussed by philosophers for thousands of years.","translation":"民主的概念是基於人民應該在政府事務中有發言權的想法。這個抽象的原則已經被哲學家討論了數千年。","word":"concept"}},"concern":{"createdAt":1781481311489,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"concern作動詞表示涉及、關係到某事或對某事表示關切和擔憂。","options":["celebrate","ignore","concern","document"],"sentence":"The environmental report will ______ the effects of climate change on coastal cities. Scientists are particularly worried about rising sea levels threatening millions of residents worldwide.","translation":"這份環境報告將涉及氣候變化對沿海城市的影響。科學家們特別擔心海平面上升會威脅全球數百萬居民。","word":"concern"}},"conclude":{"createdAt":1781837419090,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Conclude表示根據證據或討論的基礎上做出最終的結論或判斷。","options":["begin","conclude","ignore","dispute"],"sentence":"After analyzing all the evidence, the detective ______ that the butler was responsible for the crime. His investigation revealed a clear pattern of guilt and motive.","translation":"在分析了所有證據後，偵探得出結論，女僕應該對犯罪負責。他的調查揭示了明確的內疚和動機模式。","word":"conclude"}},"conclusion":{"createdAt":1781842000007,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"結論是根據證據或事實得出的最終判斷或決定。","options":["beginning","question","conclusion","mystery"],"sentence":"After reviewing all the evidence, the detective reached a ______ about the case. The final summary showed that the suspect was innocent, which brought the investigation to an end.","translation":"在檢查了所有證據後，偵探得出了關於該案件的______。最終總結表明嫌疑人是無辜的，這結束了調查。","word":"conclusion"}},"conditional":{"createdAt":1781836375374,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"conditional形容詞表示有條件的，取決於某些事情是否發生或被滿足。","options":["dependent","conditional","flexible","uncertain"],"sentence":"His offer to help was ______ on receiving payment for his services. He would only assist if the agreed-upon fee was provided first.","translation":"他提供幫助的提議是有條件的，需要獲得服務報酬。他只有在首先提供協定費用的情況下才會協助。","word":"conditional"}},"conduct":{"createdAt":1781437528475,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"conduct 在音樂中表示指揮樂隊或管弦樂團，指揮者用手勢控制樂隊的演奏。","options":["attend","conduct","arrange","compose"],"sentence":"The orchestra leader will ______ the symphony with great passion and precision. Using careful hand gestures, he will guide all the musicians to play in perfect harmony.","translation":"樂隊指揮將以極大的熱情和精確度指揮交響樂。他將用仔細的手勢引導所有音樂家完美地協調演奏。","word":"conduct"}},"conductor":{"createdAt":1782016805984,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"conductor 是名詞，在音樂語境中表示指揮樂隊或交響樂團的人。","options":["soloist","conductor","composer","audience"],"sentence":"The ______ stood on the podium and raised his baton to begin the symphony. The orchestra members watched his movements carefully to stay synchronized.","translation":"樂隊指揮站在指揮台上舉起指揮棒開始演奏交響曲。樂團成員仔細觀察他的動作以保持同步。","word":"conductor"}},"confess":{"createdAt":1781274482556,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"confess指坦白承認錯誤或犯罪，通常涉及詳細說明事實。","options":["deny","confess","ignore","question"],"sentence":"The suspect decided to ______ his guilt to the police officer. He admitted to committing the crime and provided a detailed account of what happened.","translation":"嫌疑人決定向警官承認他的罪行。他承認犯了罪並提供了發生情況的詳細說明。","word":"confess"}},"confession":{"createdAt":1781272410988,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"confession指的是主動坦白或供認自己的錯誤、罪行等，通常是向當局或他人承認自己做了什麼。","options":["denial","promise","confession","complaint"],"sentence":"The suspect made a ______ to the police, admitting that he had stolen the diamond. His testimony was the key evidence that solved the case.","translation":"嫌疑人向警察坦白承認了他偷了鑽石。他的證詞是破案的關鍵證據。","word":"confession"}},"confidence":{"createdAt":1781428458260,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"confidence指對自己能力和成功的信心和相信。","options":["crisis","confidence","citation","superstitious"],"sentence":"The young athlete walked onto the stage with great ______ to perform her gymnastics routine. Her coach had trained her well, and she believed in her abilities completely.","translation":"年輕的運動員以極大的自信走上舞台表演她的體操項目。她的教練訓練得很好，她完全相信自己的能力。","word":"confidence"}},"confident":{"createdAt":1781565657698,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"confident 形容詞表示有信心和自信，相信自己能夠成功完成某事。","options":["nervous","confident","confused","exhausted"],"sentence":"The athlete felt ______ before the championship game because of her rigorous training and consistent victories. She had prepared thoroughly and knew her abilities matched the competition.","translation":"運動員在錦標賽前感到自信，因為她的嚴格訓練和持續的勝利。她已經充分準備，知道她的能力與競爭相匹配。","word":"confident"}},"confidential":{"createdAt":1781337343695,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"confidential意為機密的、秘密的，用於形容需要保護的敏感資訊。","options":["public","famous","confidential","broken"],"sentence":"The company kept the new product design ______ to prevent competitors from stealing the idea. Only the executive team had access to the blueprints and specifications.","translation":"公司將新產品設計保密，以防止競爭對手竊取想法。只有執行團隊能夠獲得藍圖和規格說明書。","word":"confidential"}},"confine":{"createdAt":1781481124698,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"confine 指將某人或某物限制在特定的區域或範圍內。","options":["released","welcomed","restricted","escorted"],"sentence":"The prisoner was ______ to his cell for twenty-three hours a day as punishment. He was allowed only one hour of exercise in the yard under strict supervision.","translation":"作為懲罰，囚犯每天被限制在牢房內二十三小時。他每天只被允許在監督下在院子裡運動一小時。","word":"confine"}},"confirm":{"createdAt":1781850347300,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"確認是指驗證或證實某事是否真實、準確或有效，通常需要進一步的證據或行動。","options":["cancel","confirm","deny","change"],"sentence":"The airline sent an email to ______ my flight reservation for next Tuesday. I needed to click the link to verify that I would indeed be traveling on that date.","translation":"航空公司發送電子郵件來確認我下週二的航班預訂。我需要點擊鏈接來驗證我確實會在那個日期出行。","word":"confirm"}},"conflict":{"createdAt":1781926371000,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"conflict 作為動詞意思是衝突、爭執，指不同的觀點或利益發生激烈的對立。","options":["cooperate","negotiate","conflict","unite"],"sentence":"The two nations began to ______ over territory disputes along their shared border. Diplomatic negotiations failed, and military tensions escalated to the point of armed confrontation.","translation":"兩個國家開始因為共享邊界沿線的領土爭端而發生衝突。外交談判失敗，軍事緊張局勢升級到武裝對抗的程度。","word":"conflict"}},"confused":{"createdAt":1781871338562,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"confused表示感到困惑或不理解，與提出澄清要求的行為相符。","options":["attentive","interested","bewildered","focused"],"sentence":"The student looked ______ when the professor suddenly switched to a completely different topic. He raised his hand to ask for clarification about the abrupt change.","translation":"當教授突然轉向完全不同的話題時，學生看起來困惑不解。他舉手要求對這個突然的轉變進行澄清。","word":"confused"}},"confusing":{"createdAt":1781332009081,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"confusing 是形容詞，表示使人困惑的、令人感到不明白的","options":["clear","confusing","simple","helpful"],"sentence":"The instruction manual was quite ______ with unclear diagrams and poorly written explanations. Customers had difficulty assembling the product and complained about the lack of clarity.","translation":"說明書非常令人困惑，圖表不清楚，解釋寫得很差。客戶在組裝產品時遇到困難，並抱怨缺乏清晰性。","word":"confusing"}},"confusion":{"createdAt":1781661288519,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"confusion 是指無序、混亂或困惑的狀態，常用來形容混亂的環境或思想上的困惑","options":["clarity","confusion","silence","attention"],"sentence":"The ______ in the classroom was so bad that the teacher had to stop the lesson. Students were talking over each other, papers were scattered everywhere, and nobody knew what was happening.","translation":"教室裡的混亂非常嚴重，老師不得不停止上課。學生們互相說話，紙張散落一地，沒有人知道發生了什麼。","word":"confusion"}},"congratulate":{"createdAt":1781484415233,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"congratulate是指向某人表示祝賀和讚美，因為他們取得了成就或好運。","options":["criticize","congratulate","challenge","ignore"],"sentence":"Everyone came to ______ her on winning the scholarship to Harvard University. They gave her flowers, hugs, and warm wishes for her future success.","translation":"每個人都來祝賀她獲得了哈佛大學的獎學金。他們給了她鮮花、擁抱和對她未來成功的美好祝願。","word":"congratulate"}},"congressman":{"createdAt":1781848330184,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"congressman是指在國家立法機構或議會中任職的成員或代表。","options":["judge","congressman","teacher","mayor"],"sentence":"The ______ voted in favor of the new education bill during the parliamentary session. His position in the legislative body allowed him to influence important national policies.","translation":"這位國會議員在議會會議中投票贊成新的教育法案。他在立法機構中的職位使他能夠影響重要的國家政策。","word":"congressman"}},"connect":{"createdAt":1781710289365,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"connect 作動詞表示「聯繫；連接」，指將兩個或多個事物或地點接合在一起。","options":["separated","connected","divided","isolated"],"sentence":"The two cities are ______ by a high-speed railway that takes only two hours to travel between them. This transportation link allows thousands of commuters to move easily from one city to the other every day.","translation":"這兩個城市由一條只需兩小時車程的高速鐵路相連。這條運輸線路使數千名通勤者每天都能輕鬆地在兩個城市之間往來。","word":"connect"}},"connection":{"createdAt":1781582619550,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"connection 指兩個或更多事物之間的關係或聯繫，顯示它們如何相關或相互影響。","options":["separation","barrier","connection","conflict"],"sentence":"There is a strong ______ between regular exercise and good health. Scientific studies have consistently shown that people who exercise frequently have fewer health problems.","translation":"規律運動和良好健康之間有著密切的聯繫。科學研究一致表明經常運動的人健康問題較少。","word":"connection"}},"consecutive":{"createdAt":1781842000007,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"連續的意思是一個接一個地發生，沒有間斷或中斷。","options":["different","consecutive","recent","important"],"sentence":"The team won ______ games without losing a single match. Their winning streak lasted exactly five weeks with no breaks or interruptions.","translation":"該隊贏了______場比賽，沒有輸過一場。他們的連勝紀錄持續了整整五週，沒有任何中斷。","word":"consecutive"}},"consensus":{"createdAt":1781746848184,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"consensus 表示「共識」或「一致同意」，指所有相關人士達成的普遍協議。","options":["conflict","consensus","postponement","confusion"],"sentence":"After three hours of debate, the board finally reached a ______ on the new budget proposal. All twelve members voted in favor of the decision.","translation":"經過三小時的辯論，董事會最終就新的預算提案達成了共識。全部十二名成員都投票贊成該決定。","word":"consensus"}},"consent":{"createdAt":1781965320891,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"consent 是指同意或許可，通常用於正式或法律情況中需要獲得同意。","options":["consent","payment","insurance","diagnosis"],"sentence":"The doctor cannot perform surgery without the patient's ______ in writing. This legal requirement protects patients' rights and ensures they understand the procedure.","translation":"醫生未經患者的書面同意不能進行手術。這項法律要求保護患者的權利並確保他們理解該程序。","word":"consent"}},"consequence":{"createdAt":1781746685513,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"consequence指的是結果、後果，表示某個行為或事件引起的結果或影響。","options":["consequence","tolerance","stadium","miracle"],"sentence":"Driving recklessly can have serious ______ for your safety and the safety of others. You may face accidents, injuries, or legal penalties as a result of your actions.","translation":"魯莽駕駛可能對你和他人的安全造成嚴重的後果。你的行為可能導致事故、傷害或法律處罰。","word":"consequence"}},"consequent":{"createdAt":1781758494837,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"consequent 形容作為結果而產生的、隨後發生的事物，與第二句中列舉的洪水造成的損害相符。","options":["preceding","consequent","unrelated","accidental"],"sentence":"The heavy rainfall caused flooding, and the ______ damage to the town's infrastructure was severe. Because of the flood, roads, bridges, and buildings all suffered major destruction.","translation":"大雨導致洪水，隨之而來的對城鎮基礎設施的破壞非常嚴重。由於洪水，道路、橋樑和建築物都遭受了重大破壞。","word":"consequent"}},"consequently":{"createdAt":1781332009074,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"consequently 是副詞，表示結果或因此，用於說明某事是另一事件的結果","options":["however","consequently","although","meanwhile"],"sentence":"The storm caused severe damage to the power lines; ______, thousands of people lost electricity. The outage lasted for three days until repairs were completed.","translation":"暴風雨對電力線造成了嚴重損壞；因而，數千人失去了電力。停電持續了三天，直到維修完成。","word":"consequently"}},"considerably":{"createdAt":1781824444628,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"considerably 是副詞，表示很大程度上、相當多地或值得注意地改變了某事物。","options":["slightly","considerably","potentially","eventually"],"sentence":"The new highway route has ______ reduced commute times for daily travelers. Traffic that once took forty-five minutes now only requires thirty minutes to navigate.","translation":"新的高速公路路線大幅縮短了日常通勤者的通勤時間。曾經需要四十五分鐘的交通現在只需三十分鐘即可通行。","word":"considerably"}},"considerate":{"createdAt":1781337343698,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"considerate意為體貼的、周到的或關心他人感受的。","options":["rude","selfish","considerate","lazy"],"sentence":"James is a very ______ friend who always remembers everyone's birthdays and asks about their problems. He shows genuine concern for others' feelings and well-being in every interaction.","translation":"詹姆斯是一位非常體貼的朋友，他總是記得每個人的生日並關心他們的問題。他在每次互動中都表現出對他人感受和福祉的真誠關心。","word":"considerate"}},"consistent":{"createdAt":1781749177490,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"consistent 表示始終如一、穩定不變的特性，與變化不定相反。","options":["variable","uniform","unpredictable","fluctuating"],"sentence":"Her grades have been ______ throughout the semester, always ranging between A and B. Teachers appreciate her reliable performance and steady commitment to her studies.","translation":"整個學期她的成績一直保持一致，始終在A和B之間。老師們欣賞她可靠的表現和對學習的穩定承諾。","word":"consistent"}},"console":{"createdAt":1781775363749,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"console 作為動詞表示慰問或慰藉某人，當某人遭遇不幸時提供心理上的支持。","options":["scold","console","advise","ignore"],"sentence":"She tried to ______ her friend who had just lost her job. She listened carefully to his worries and offered kind words to ease his pain.","translation":"她試圖______剛剛失業的朋友。她仔細傾聽他的擔憂，並提供親切的話語來緩解他的痛苦。","word":"console"}},"consonant":{"createdAt":1781965320885,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"consonant 指的是需要氣流受阻才能發音的字母，與母音(vowel)相對。","options":["vowel","consonant","syllable","phoneme"],"sentence":"The letter 'b' is a ______ that requires you to close your lips to pronounce it. In English, there are twenty-one of these letters, as opposed to only five vowels.","translation":"字母'b'是一個子音，發音時需要閉上嘴唇。在英文中，有二十一個這樣的字母，相對於只有五個母音。","word":"consonant"}},"conspiracy":{"createdAt":1781799990470,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"conspiracy是指多個人秘密策劃做某件非法或有害的事情，通常涉及背叛或欺騙。","options":["rumor","conspiracy","scandal","investigation"],"sentence":"The detective uncovered a ______ involving high-ranking government officials who had secretly planned to manipulate the election results. Evidence showed they had been meeting in private for months to coordinate their illegal activities.","translation":"這名偵探揭露了一項由高階政府官員參與的陰謀，他們曾秘密計劃操縱選舉結果。證據顯示他們已經私下開會好幾個月來協調他們的非法活動。","word":"conspiracy"}},"conspire":{"createdAt":1781837419087,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Conspire表示為了達到不正當目的而進行秘密的同謀或策劃。","options":["cooperate","conspire","communicate","collaborate"],"sentence":"The two executives ______ to steal company secrets and sell them to competitors. They secretly planned their scheme without anyone noticing their communications.","translation":"這兩位主管密謀竊取公司機密並將其出售給競爭對手。他們秘密策劃了他們的計畫，沒有人注意到他們的溝通。","word":"conspire"}},"constitute":{"createdAt":1781779647125,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"constitute表示組成或構成某個整體的成分或部分","options":["destroy","constitute","separate","undermine"],"sentence":"These five elements ______ the foundation of a successful business. Together, they form the essential framework that all operations depend upon.","translation":"這五個要素構成了一個成功企業的基礎。它們共同形成了所有業務所依賴的基本框架。","word":"constitute"}},"constitution":{"createdAt":1781424356419,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"constitution指的是一個國家或組織的根本法律文件，規定了其政治體系和基本原則。","options":["budget","constitution","treaty","regulation"],"sentence":"The country's ______ serves as the supreme law that outlines the structure of government and protects individual rights. All legislation must comply with the principles established in this foundational document.","translation":"該國的憲法是闡述政府結構和保護個人權利的最高法律。所有立法都必須符合這份基礎文件中所確立的原則。","word":"constitution"}},"constitutional":{"createdAt":1781779647127,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"constitutional表示符合或遵守憲法規定的","options":["modern","constitutional","popular","fair"],"sentence":"The court ruled that the new law was not ______ . The judges determined it violated several provisions in the founding document.","translation":"法院裁定這項新法律不符合憲法。法官判定它違反了憲法文件中的幾項條款。","word":"constitutional"}},"constraint":{"createdAt":1782006215683,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「constraint」是名詞，表示「限制」或「束縛」，指阻止或減少某事物可能性的因素。","options":["opportunity","advantage","constraint","resource"],"sentence":"The project faced a serious budget ______ that limited what could be accomplished. Without additional funding, the team could only complete half of the originally planned features.","translation":"該項目面臨嚴重的預算限制，限制了可以完成的工作。沒有額外資金，團隊只能完成原計劃功能的一半。","word":"constraint"}},"constructive":{"createdAt":1781779647130,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"constructive表示有益的、建設性的或旨在改進的","options":["destructive","constructive","negative","harsh"],"sentence":"The manager provided ______ feedback to help the team improve. She pointed out specific areas for growth and offered practical suggestions.","translation":"經理提供了建設性反饋來幫助團隊改進。她指出了特定的改進領域並提供了實用建議。","word":"constructive"}},"consult":{"createdAt":1781961466404,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"consult 表示向某人請教或與某人商議，通常是為了獲得專業意見或建議。","options":["ignore","consult","announce","delay"],"sentence":"Before making a decision about the business merger, the CEO decided to ______ with the company's legal team. The lawyers provided expert advice that directly influenced the final contract terms.","translation":"在決定公司合併之前，首席執行官決定與公司的法律團隊商議。律師提供的專業建議直接影響了最終的合同條款。","word":"consult"}},"consultant":{"createdAt":1781779647128,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"consultant表示被聘請提供專業建議和指導的人","options":["employee","consultant","intern","competitor"],"sentence":"The company hired a marketing ______ to improve their brand strategy. This expert spent two weeks analyzing their current approach and proposing solutions.","translation":"公司聘請了營銷顧問來改進品牌戰略。這位專家花了兩週時間分析他們目前的方法並提出解決方案。","word":"consultant"}},"consume":{"createdAt":1781478568769,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"consume 表示使用、消耗或吃掉某樣東西。","options":["produce","consume","store","recycle"],"sentence":"The factory ______ thousands of tons of raw materials each month to produce textiles. The production demands required constant supply chain management.","translation":"工廠每月消耗數千噸原材料來生產紡織品。生產需求需要持續的供應鏈管理。","word":"consume"}},"consumption":{"createdAt":1781926371000,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"consumption 意思是消費、消耗，指人們使用或食用商品和資源的數量。","options":["conservation","production","consumption","rationing"],"sentence":"The world's ______ of fossil fuels has increased dramatically over the past century. This growing demand has led to climate change and environmental degradation that affects the entire planet.","translation":"世界在過去一個世紀裡對化石燃料的消費大幅增加。這種不斷增長的需求導致了影響整個星球的氣候變化和環境退化。","word":"consumption"}},"contain":{"createdAt":1781428458256,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"contain表示包含或包括某些內容或元素。","options":["contain","choke","lecture","superstitious"],"sentence":"The contract ______ several important clauses that protect both parties involved. Each section was carefully reviewed by lawyers before signing.","translation":"合約包含了幾項保護雙方的重要條款。簽署前每一部分都由律師仔細審查。","word":"contain"}},"contaminated":{"createdAt":1781566460883,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"contaminated表示被有害物質或細菌汙染的狀態，與水中有害細菌和政府警告措施相符。","options":["pure","clean","contaminated","treated"],"sentence":"The water supply was declared ______ after tests revealed harmful bacteria. The government issued a boil-water advisory to protect residents from illness.","translation":"經測試發現有害細菌後，供水被宣佈受汙染。政府發佈了煮沸飲用水警告以保護居民免受疾病。","word":"contaminated"}},"contamination":{"createdAt":1781531595650,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"contamination 是指使物質受到有害物質或污染的過程，特別是指危害健康的物質混入。","options":["shortage","contamination","treatment","distribution"],"sentence":"The water ______ made the entire supply unsafe for drinking. Scientists found harmful bacteria and chemicals that had seeped into the reservoir.","translation":"水的汙染使整個供水都不安全飲用。科學家們發現有害細菌和化學物質滲入了水庫。","word":"contamination"}},"contemplation":{"createdAt":1781362281660,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"contemplation表示深思或沉思，指認真思考某事的過程。","options":["action","contemplation","movement","celebration"],"sentence":"After hours of ______, she finally made a decision about her career change. She had carefully thought through all the options and consequences.","translation":"經過數小時的沉思，她終於做出了關於職業改變的決定。她已經仔細考慮了所有的選項和後果。","word":"contemplation"}},"contempt":{"createdAt":1781917052439,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"contempt表示強烈的蔑視或鄙視，通常針對被認為不值得尊重或道德低劣的人或行為。","options":["sympathy","respect","contempt","interest"],"sentence":"The judge showed ______ for the defendant's repeated lies and refusal to tell the truth. She sentenced him harshly and refused to make eye contact during the entire proceeding.","translation":"法官對被告人的反覆謊言和拒絕說出真相表示輕蔑。她判處他嚴厲的刑罰，並在整個訴訟過程中拒絕與他有眼神接觸。","word":"contempt"}},"contend":{"createdAt":1781779647129,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"contend表示競爭或爭奪某物","options":["watch","contend","ignore","abandon"],"sentence":"Three teams will ______ for the championship trophy. Only the strongest and most skilled team will emerge as the winner.","translation":"三支隊伍將為冠軍獎杯而競爭。只有最強大和最有技能的隊伍才能成為贏家。","word":"contend"}},"contentment":{"createdAt":1781698273261,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"contentment 是名詞，表示「滿足感」或「知足」的狀態，指對現況感到滿意和心滿意足。","options":["frustration","ambition","contentment","anxiety"],"sentence":"After retiring from her successful career, Sarah found ______ in spending time with her grandchildren. She no longer felt the need to chase promotions or earn more money.","translation":"從成功的職業生涯退休後，莎拉在花時間與孫子孫女相處中找到了滿足感。她不再感到需要追求升職或賺取更多金錢。","word":"contentment"}},"contents":{"createdAt":1781425024017,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"contents是指容器或出版物裡面所裝的東西或所包含的內容，是複數名詞。","options":["container","contents","structure","label"],"sentence":"The ______ of the antique chest revealed letters, photographs, and jewelry from the 1920s. We consulted the museum's catalog to understand the historical significance of each item inside.","translation":"古董箱子裡面的東西揭示了1920年代的信件、照片和珠寶。我們查閱了博物館的目錄來瞭解裡面每件物品的歷史意義。","word":"contents"}},"contest":{"createdAt":1781836375370,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"contest是競賽或競爭，指參加者為了贏得獎勵或證明能力而進行的正式比賽。","options":["match","contest","game","challenge"],"sentence":"The students eagerly participated in the spelling ______ held at their school. The winner would receive a trophy and advance to the regional competition.","translation":"學生們熱情參加在他們學校舉辦的拼字比賽。獲勝者將獲得獎杯並晉級地區競賽。","word":"contest"}},"contestant":{"createdAt":1781667024998,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"contestant是指參加比賽或競爭的人，強調在特定競技活動中的參與身份。","options":["judge","chef","contestant","winner"],"sentence":"The final ______ on the cooking show prepared a three-course meal in just thirty minutes. Only the top three chefs made it to this stage of the competition.","translation":"烹飪節目的最後參賽選手在三十分鐘內準備了三道菜。只有排名前三的廚師才能進入競賽的這個階段。","word":"contestant"}},"continuity":{"createdAt":1781507137210,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"continuity 指的是故事或敘述的連貫性和持續性，當出現不一致時，就表示連貫性被破壞了。","options":["dialogue","continuity","budget","location"],"sentence":"The film's ______ was broken when the director changed halfway through production. The audience noticed jarring inconsistencies in the plot and character development because of this abrupt transition.","translation":"這部電影的連貫性在製作中途導演更換時被打破了。由於這個突然的轉變，觀眾注意到劇情和角色發展中令人不適的不一致之處。","word":"continuity"}},"continuous":{"createdAt":1781775276768,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"continuous表示不間斷、連續進行，符合全年無休24小時運作的描述。","options":["occasional","continuous","weekly","monthly"],"sentence":"The factory operates on a ______ basis without any breaks. The production line runs 24 hours a day, seven days a week throughout the year.","translation":"該工廠以連續的方式運營，沒有任何停工。生產線一年四季每天運行24小時，每週運行7天。","word":"continuous"}},"continuously":{"createdAt":1781452134701,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"continuously副詞表示不間斷地、持續不斷地進行某個動作或狀態。","options":["intermittently","sporadically","continuously","occasionally"],"sentence":"The factory machines ran ______ for three days without stopping. Production managers monitored them constantly to ensure there were no breaks in the manufacturing process.","translation":"工廠機器連續運轉了三天而沒有停止。生產經理不斷監控它們，以確保製造過程中沒有中斷。","word":"continuously"}},"contradict":{"createdAt":1781336858152,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"contradict 動詞表示說出相反或相衝突的陳述，使某事變得不可信或互相衝突。","options":["supports","validates","contradicts","confirms"],"sentence":"His statement ______ what he had said the previous day. When confronted with the evidence, he could not explain the inconsistency in his accounts.","translation":"他的陳述與他前一天說過的話相矛盾。當面對證據時，他無法解釋他敘述中的不一致之處。","word":"contradict"}},"contrast":{"createdAt":1781746848184,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"contrast 表示「對比」或「對照」，指兩個事物之間的明顯差異。","options":["harmony","similarity","contrast","connection"],"sentence":"The ______ between the wealthy downtown area and the poor suburbs is striking and obvious. The difference in infrastructure, buildings, and resources is immediately noticeable.","translation":"繁華市中心和貧困郊區之間的對比非常鮮明。基礎設施、建築物和資源的差異一目了然。","word":"contrast"}},"contribute":{"createdAt":1781693295123,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"contribute 表示提供或貢獻，在此指員工在會議中提出建議。","options":["contribute","ignore","steal","delay"],"sentence":"All employees are expected to ______ their ideas during team meetings. The manager values input from every staff member and uses their suggestions to improve company processes.","translation":"所有員工都應在團隊會議中貢獻他們的想法。經理重視每位員工的意見，並利用他們的建議來改進公司流程。","word":"contribute"}},"contribution":{"createdAt":1781479123530,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"contribution 指的是對某事物的貢獻或捐獻，通常指物質或金錢上的幫助。","options":["complaint","contribution","permission","instruction"],"sentence":"The charity appreciated every ______ made by donors during the fundraising campaign. Without the generous donations from local businesses, the organization would not have been able to build the new community center.","translation":"慈善機構感謝在募款活動中捐獻者的每一筆捐獻。如果沒有當地企業的慷慨捐贈，該組織就不會能夠建造新的社區中心。","word":"contribution"}},"controversial":{"createdAt":1781275226789,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"此處controversial作形容詞表示「有爭議的；引起爭議的」","options":["controversial","breast","digestion","abroad"],"sentence":"The politician's ______ speech sparked heated debates in newspapers and social media. People on both sides couldn't agree on whether his statements were right or wrong.","translation":"這位政治家的有爭議的演講在報紙和社群媒體上引發了激烈辯論。雙方的人都對他的言論是否正確無法達成共識。","word":"controversial"}},"convention":{"createdAt":1781414884518,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"convention在這裡指大型會議或集會，是業界人士聚集交流的正式活動。","options":["convention","schedule","performance","dream"],"sentence":"The annual film ______ attracted thousands of directors and producers from around the world. Attendees gathered to discuss new trends and network with industry professionals.","translation":"年度電影大會吸引了來自世界各地的數千名導演和製作人。與會者聚集在一起討論新趨勢並與行業專業人士建立聯繫。","word":"convention"}},"conventional":{"createdAt":1781484415208,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"conventional意指遵循傳統習俗和標準方法，不追求創新或特別的做法。","options":["revolutionary","unconventional","conventional","progressive"],"sentence":"Her ______ approach to teaching followed the traditional textbook methods used for decades. She rarely experimented with new or innovative techniques in her classroom.","translation":"她教學的傳統方法遵循了幾十年來使用的傳統教科書方法。她很少在課堂上嘗試新穎或創新的技巧。","word":"conventional"}},"conversion":{"createdAt":1781274482562,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"conversion指將某物從一種形式或用途轉變為另一種形式或用途。","options":["destruction","construction","conversion","collection"],"sentence":"The old warehouse underwent a dramatic ______ into a modern art gallery. The transformation took two years to complete and created a stunning cultural venue for the community.","translation":"舊倉庫經歷了戲劇性的轉變，變成了現代美術館。這次改造花了兩年才完成，為社區創造了一個令人驚嘆的文化場所。","word":"conversion"}},"convey":{"createdAt":1781779647126,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"convey表示傳達、表達或傳輸信息、感受或意思","options":["hide","convey","ignore","change"],"sentence":"The artist tried to ______ emotion through her paintings. Viewers could feel the sadness and hope expressed in every brushstroke.","translation":"藝術家試圖通過她的繪畫傳達情感。觀眾可以感受到每筆筆觸中表達的悲傷和希望。","word":"convey"}},"conviction":{"createdAt":1781693281410,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"conviction（定罪）是法律術語，指法院宣判某人有罪或對其的正式判決。","options":["friendship","conviction","conversation","confusion"],"sentence":"After years of investigating the cold case, the detective finally secured a ______ against the suspect. The jury deliberated for only three hours before returning a guilty verdict.","translation":"經過多年調查這起陳年舊案後，偵探終於對嫌疑人獲得了定罪。陪審團只經過三小時的審議就回報了有罪判決。","word":"conviction"}},"convince":{"createdAt":1781850347304,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"說服或使相信是指通過提供證據或論點使某人相信某事或採取某項行動。","options":["confuse","trick","convince","remind"],"sentence":"The detective presented compelling evidence to ______ the jury that the defendant was guilty. The eyewitness testimony and physical proof left no doubt in their minds.","translation":"偵探提供了令人信服的證據來說服陪審團被告有罪。證人的證詞和物理證據讓他們心中沒有疑問。","word":"convince"}},"cooperate":{"createdAt":1781746685503,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"cooperate指的是合作、協作，表示兩個或多個人或組織為了共同的目的一起工作。","options":["terminate","sober","cooperate","rubbish"],"sentence":"The two companies decided to ______ on the new research project. They combined their resources and expertise to achieve a common goal.","translation":"這兩家公司決定在新研究項目上合作。他們結合資源和專業知識來達成共同目標。","word":"cooperate"}},"coral":{"createdAt":1781837419094,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"Coral是海洋中由微小生物構成的生物礁石，色彩豐富，為海洋生物提供棲息地。","options":["seaweed","sand","coral","rocks"],"sentence":"The scuba diver marveled at the vibrant ______ formations beneath the ocean surface. These colorful structures were home to thousands of fish and marine creatures.","translation":"潛水員對海洋表面下充滿活力的珊瑚構造感到驚嘆。這些色彩繽紛的結構是數千條魚和海洋生物的家園。","word":"coral"}},"core":{"createdAt":1781696018693,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"core 意為核心、最重要的，指組織或系統最基本、最關鍵的價值和原則。","options":["temporary","surface","core","optional"],"sentence":"The ______ values of our organization include honesty, integrity, and respect for all people. These principles guide every decision we make.","translation":"我們組織的核心價值包括誠實、正直和尊重所有人。這些原則指導我們做出的每一個決定。","word":"core"}},"coronation":{"createdAt":1782007262076,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"coronation 是指國王或王后的正式加冕儀式，通常包含莊嚴的傳統禮儀和官方宣布。","options":["celebration","coronation","parade","meeting"],"sentence":"The ______ of the new queen lasted for three hours and included traditional ceremonies passed down through generations. Millions of people watched the live broadcast as she was officially crowned as the nation's monarch.","translation":"新王后的加冕典禮持續了三個小時，包括了世代相傳的傳統儀式。數百萬人觀看了直播，見證她被正式加冕為國家的君主。","word":"coronation"}},"corporate":{"createdAt":1781311685837,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"corporate指的是整個公司或組織層面的決策與規則，適用於所有成員，而非個人或特定地區的。","options":["individual","regional","official","personal"],"sentence":"The ______ policy was decided by the board of directors at the company meeting. All employees across every department must follow these rules without exception.","translation":"公司政策由董事會在公司會議上決定。所有部門的每個員工都必須遵守這些規則，沒有例外。","word":"corporate"}},"corpse":{"createdAt":1781775598766,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"corpse是名詞，指死亡的人體，特別是在法醫或正式的語境中使用，強調已經失去生命的身體。","options":["witness","victim","corpse","suspect"],"sentence":"The detective examined the ______ at the crime scene to determine the time of death. The body had been lying there for several hours before being discovered by the neighbors.","translation":"偵探在犯罪現場檢查屍體以確定死亡時間。屍體在被鄰居發現之前已經躺在那裡好幾個小時了。","word":"corpse"}},"correlate":{"createdAt":1781843207977,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"此字表示找出兩個事物之間的關係或聯繫，通常用於統計或科學分析中。","options":["separate","correlate","ignore","dispute"],"sentence":"Scientists attempt to ______ the rise in global temperatures with increased carbon emissions. Their research clearly demonstrates that these two factors move together in a measurable and predictable way.","translation":"科學家試圖將全球溫度上升與碳排放增加相互聯繫。他們的研究清楚地證明了這兩個因素以可測量和可預測的方式一起變化。","word":"correlate"}},"correlated":{"createdAt":1782006620282,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"correlated表示「相互關聯的」，指兩個變數之間存在統計關係，與第二句中患者吸菸與患病率之間的明顯關聯相符。","options":["independent","correlated","documented","theoretical"],"sentence":"The study found that smoking and lung disease were ______ variables in the patient population. When researchers analyzed the data, they discovered that patients who smoked had significantly higher rates of developing this condition.","translation":"該研究發現吸菸和肺病在患者群體中是相關聯的變數。當研究人員分析數據時，他們發現吸菸的患者患上這種疾病的比率明顯更高。","word":"correlated"}},"correlation":{"createdAt":1781843207979,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"此名詞表示兩個變數或事物之間的相互關係或依存關係。","options":["contradiction","separation","correlation","confusion"],"sentence":"There is a strong ______ between regular exercise and improved mental health. When people exercise more frequently, they consistently report feeling happier and less stressed.","translation":"定期運動與改善心理健康之間存在很強的相互關係。當人們更頻繁地運動時，他們一致報告感到更快樂和壓力減少。","word":"correlation"}},"correspond":{"createdAt":1781693538702,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"correspond 表示相符合、相一致或相當於，也可以指通過寫信進行交流。","options":["contradict","correspond","differ","oppose"],"sentence":"The two letters ______ with each other perfectly in terms of content and date. Both were written on the same day by the same author.","translation":"這兩封信在內容和日期方面完全相符。兩封信都是由同一位作者在同一天寫的。","word":"correspond"}},"correspondence":{"createdAt":1781693304924,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"correspondence 表示兩件事物之間的相符或相似，強調它們在本質上或細節上的一致性。","options":["contradiction","difference","correspondence","confusion"],"sentence":"The detective noticed a striking ______ between the suspect's alibi and the witness statement. Both accounts matched perfectly in every detail.","translation":"偵探發現嫌疑人的不在場證明和證人陳述之間存在令人驚訝的相似之處。兩份陳述在每個細節上都完全相符。","word":"correspondence"}},"correspondent":{"createdAt":1782007196630,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「通訊記者」是指被派駐到特定地點報導新聞的記者，負責現場採集和傳送新聞。","options":["editor","correspondent","photographer","broadcaster"],"sentence":"The news organization sent a ______ to cover the international summit and report directly from the conference. She filed daily updates from the press room, interviewing world leaders and analyzing negotiations.","translation":"新聞機構派遣一名通訊記者去報導國際峰會並直接從會議現場報導。她在新聞室提交每日更新，採訪世界領導人並分析談判情況。","word":"correspondent"}},"corridor":{"createdAt":1781503378964,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"corridor 指的是在建築物內連接不同房間或區域的長走廊或通道。","options":["staircase","room","corridor","window"],"sentence":"The students walked through the long ______ to reach their next classroom. The hallway was lined with lockers and bulletin boards on both sides.","translation":"學生們走過長長的走廊到達他們的下一個教室。走廊兩側排列著儲物櫃和公告板。","word":"corridor"}},"corrupt":{"createdAt":1782007196631,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「貪汙；腐敗」作為動詞表示通過非法手段如接受賄賂而損害廉正，或作為形容詞指已經喪失誠正品質的人或制度。","options":["influenced","motivated","corrupt","inspired"],"sentence":"The scandal revealed that several government officials had been ______ by accepting bribes from wealthy developers. Investigators discovered secret bank accounts and illegal payments that exposed their wrongdoing.","translation":"醜聞揭露了幾名政府官員通過接受富有開發商的賄賂而進行貪汙。調查人員發現了秘密銀行帳戶和非法付款，暴露了他們的不當行為。","word":"corrupt"}},"corruption":{"createdAt":1781619188929,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"corruption 指貪汙和不誠實行為，特別是官員的違法牟利行為。","options":["efficiency","corruption","organization","transparency"],"sentence":"The government launched an investigation into widespread ______ within the customs department. Several officials were arrested for accepting bribes and embezzling public funds.","translation":"政府對海關部門內的廣泛貪汙進行了調查。幾位官員因收受賄賂和挪用公款而被逮捕。","word":"corruption"}},"cost":{"createdAt":1781774456599,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cost 在這裡表示建造醫院所需支付的金錢，與 expense 同義，指成本或開支。","options":["price","expense","advantage","benefit"],"sentence":"The ______ of building a new hospital was extremely high, requiring millions of dollars. The city council had to carefully budget for this major expense.","translation":"建造新醫院的費用極其高昂，需要數百萬美元。市議會必須為這筆重大開支仔細編列預算。","word":"cost"}},"cost_effective":{"createdAt":1781667024994,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"cost-effective指在花費最少金錢的情況下達到最佳結果，是提高經濟效益的做法。","options":["expensive","wasteful","inefficient","cost-effective"],"sentence":"The company switched to a ______ manufacturing method that produced the same quality at half the price. Investors were impressed by the ability to maintain profit margins while reducing expenses.","translation":"公司改用了一種物有所值的製造方法，以一半的價格生產出相同品質的產品。投資者對在保持利潤率的同時降低成本的能力印象深刻。","word":"cost-effective"}},"costly":{"createdAt":1781582424691,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"costly表示昂貴的或代價高的，與hundreds of thousands of dollars相符，quick、simple和temporary都無法與金錢花費相關聯。","options":["quick","simple","costly","temporary"],"sentence":"The repairs to the old mansion turned out to be quite ______ for the owners. They had to spend hundreds of thousands of dollars to restore it.","translation":"對這座老宅的修繕對業主來說成本相當高昂。他們必須花費數十萬美元來修復它。","word":"costly"}},"costume":{"createdAt":1781332009070,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"costume 指的是為舞台表演或角色扮演設計的戲服或服裝","options":["weapon","costume","script","microphone"],"sentence":"The actress wore an elaborate ______ for the historical drama production. The wardrobe department spent weeks creating the period-appropriate clothing and accessories.","translation":"女演員為這部歷史劇製作穿著了精美的戲服。服裝部門花了數周時間創作符合時代的衣服和配飾。","word":"costume"}},"cottage":{"createdAt":1781484415209,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"cottage是指鄉村或鄉間的小房子，通常很小、簡樸但溫馨舒適。","options":["mansion","skyscraper","cottage","apartment"],"sentence":"They bought a small ______ in the countryside where they could enjoy peace and quiet. The humble dwelling had only three rooms and was surrounded by beautiful gardens.","translation":"他們在鄉村買了一所小房子，可以享受寧靜和安詳。這所簡樸的住宅只有三個房間，被美麗的花園包圍。","word":"cottage"}},"counsel":{"createdAt":1781256444516,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"counsel作動詞表示提供建議或勸告，通常由有經驗的人對他人提出專業意見。","options":["inspect","counsel","criticize","assign"],"sentence":"The career advisor will ______ students on which university programs best match their interests. She has helped hundreds of graduates find fulfilling career paths over her twenty years of experience.","translation":"職業顧問將就哪些大學課程最符合學生的興趣向他們提出建議。在她二十年的職業生涯中，她已幫助數百名畢業生找到了令人滿意的職業道路。","word":"counsel"}},"counselor":{"createdAt":1781837419089,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Counselor是提供專業建議和指導的人，特別是在教育和個人發展領域。","options":["teacher","counselor","administrator","principal"],"sentence":"The school ______ helped students make better decisions about their academic future. Her expertise in guidance and career planning made her invaluable to the student body.","translation":"學校輔導員幫助學生對他們的學術未來做出更好的決定。她在指導和職業規劃方面的專業知識使她對學生群體無價。","word":"counselor"}},"count":{"createdAt":1781677018333,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"count在此作動詞，表示「重要」或「有價值」，常用於「count toward」短語中，意思是對某事有貢獻或影響。","options":["matter","count","install","stem"],"sentence":"The CEO said that employee satisfaction will ______ toward the company's success. She emphasized that this metric is crucial for evaluating overall performance.","translation":"執行長說員工滿意度將計算/重要於公司的成功。她強調這個指標對評估整體績效至關重要。","word":"count"}},"countable":{"createdAt":1781839703146,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"countable指可以被數的、可用數字修飾的，與can be pluralized and take numbers（可以複數化和用數字修飾）直接相符。","options":["invisible","countable","abstract","invisible"],"sentence":"In grammar, nouns are divided into ______ and uncountable categories. Words like 'apple' and 'chair' can be pluralized and take numbers before them.","translation":"在語法中，名詞分為可數名詞和不可數名詞兩類。像'apple'和'chair'這樣的詞可以複數化，並且可以在其前面加上數字。","word":"countable"}},"counter":{"createdAt":1781485266371,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"在餐飲環境中，counter指的是料理檯或服務檯，用來放置食物和與顧客互動。","options":["argument","objection","counter","dispute"],"sentence":"The customer placed her order at the ______ while the chef prepared the meal behind it. She watched through the glass display case as they assembled her sandwich on the stainless steel surface.","translation":"顧客在櫃台下單，廚師在後面準備餐點。她透過玻璃展示櫃看著他們在不鏽鋼操作檯上組合她的三明治。","word":"counter"}},"countless":{"createdAt":1781738105696,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"countless 意為無法計數的、數量極其龐大的，表示某物的數量非常多。","options":["several","countless","few","minimal"],"sentence":"The astronomer discovered ______ stars in the night sky using her telescope. So many celestial bodies were visible that it became impossible to count them all individually.","translation":"這位天文學家用她的望遠鏡在夜空中發現了無數的星星。如此多的天體是可見的，以至於不可能單獨數清楚它們。","word":"countless"}},"courage":{"createdAt":1781582251994,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"courage 是名詞，表示在面對危險或困難時的勇氣和無所畏懼的精神。","options":["fear","courage","confusion","hesitation"],"sentence":"The firefighter showed great ______ when running into the burning building to save the family. His bravery was recognized by the entire community the next day.","translation":"那位消防員衝進燃燒的建築物救家人時展現了極大的勇氣。他的英勇行為在隔天被整個社區認可。","word":"courage"}},"courageous":{"createdAt":1782009797688,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"courageous 形容詞，表示具有勇氣、敢於面對困難或危險的品質；在這句話中強調消防員不畏危險的英勇精神。","options":["timid","courageous","lazy","confused"],"sentence":"The firefighter made a ______ decision to run into the burning building to save the trapped family. His bravery in the face of extreme danger earned him a medal of honor from the city.","translation":"消防員做出了一個勇敢的決定，衝進燃燒的建築物中救出被困的家人。他在面對極端危險時的英勇行為為他贏得了城市的榮譽勳章。","word":"courageous"}},"course":{"createdAt":1781424356416,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"course在此指的是在教育機構中系統地教授的一系列課程或科目。","options":["meal","direction","course","river"],"sentence":"She enrolled in a biology ______ at the university to fulfill her science requirement. The semester-long program covered topics such as cellular structure, genetics, and evolution.","translation":"她在大學註冊了一門生物課程以滿足她的理科要求。這個為期一學期的課程涵蓋了細胞結構、遺傳學和進化等主題。","word":"course"}},"court":{"createdAt":1781837419095,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Court在體育中指的是專門用於特定運動（如籃球、網球）的場地。","options":["field","court","stadium","gym"],"sentence":"The basketball players practiced on the ______ every afternoon before the big game. The wooden floor and hoops were professionally maintained for competition.","translation":"籃球運動員在大賽前每天下午在籃球場練習。木質地板和籃圈經過專業維護以備比賽。","word":"court"}},"coverage":{"createdAt":1781693271586,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"coverage在新聞語境中指的是對事件的報導範圍和深度，包括採訪、分析和現場報告。","options":["ignorance","coverage","silence","absence"],"sentence":"The news station provided extensive ______ of the presidential election with multiple reporters at different locations. They interviewed candidates, showed live voting footage, and analyzed poll results throughout the day.","translation":"新聞電台對總統選舉進行了廣泛的報導，多名記者駐守在不同地點。他們採訪了候選人，播放了投票的現場畫面，並全天分析了民調結果。","word":"coverage"}},"coward":{"createdAt":1781693304926,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"coward 指缺乏勇氣、容易害怕且不敢面對困難或危險的人。","options":["hero","leader","coward","defender"],"sentence":"The soldier was branded a ______ after he abandoned his comrades during the battle. His refusal to fight demonstrated a complete lack of courage.","translation":"這位士兵在戰鬥中拋棄同志後被烙上了懦夫的標籤。他拒絕作戰表明他完全缺乏勇氣。","word":"coward"}},"crack":{"createdAt":1781625891346,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"crack可表示身心因壓力過大而疲憊或崩潰","options":["laugh","crack","relax","improve"],"sentence":"After working on the project for three weeks without rest, she began to ______. Her friends noticed she was irritable and emotionally exhausted.","translation":"連續三週不休息地進行這個項目後，她開始身心疲憊。她的朋友注意到她易怒且情緒上很疲憊。","word":"crack"}},"cracked":{"createdAt":1781619188927,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cracked 指表面出現裂紋或破裂，表示結構受損。","options":["solid","cracked","reinforced","stable"],"sentence":"After the earthquake, the ______ foundation posed a serious safety hazard to the building. Engineers recommended immediate reinforcement before further damage occurred.","translation":"地震後，破裂的地基對建築物造成了嚴重的安全隱患。工程師建議在進一步損壞前立即加固。","word":"cracked"}},"cracker":{"createdAt":1781532967167,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cracker 指爆竹、鞭炮，與「巨大噪音、閃光和響聲」的描述相符。","options":["candy","cracker","toy","balloon"],"sentence":"The children lit a ______ outside on New Year's Eve and enjoyed the loud noise and sparkles. It made a tremendous bang that startled the neighbors.","translation":"在除夕夜，孩子們在外面點燃了______(爆竹)，享受著巨大的噪音和閃光。它發出了一聲震天動地的巨響，嚇到了鄰居。","word":"cracker"}},"cradle":{"createdAt":1781831347630,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cradle 作名詞表示搖籃或發源地，引申指某事物的起源或誕生地。","options":["graveyard","cradle","monument","barrier"],"sentence":"Ancient Mesopotamia is often called the ______ of Western civilization where the earliest cities and writing systems emerged. Historians trace the origins of modern society back to this fertile region between the Tigris and Euphrates rivers.","translation":"古美索不達米亞經常被稱為西方文明的搖籃，最早的城市和文字系統在這裡出現。歷史學家將現代社會的起源追溯到這個位於底格里斯河和幼發拉底河之間的肥沃地帶。","word":"cradle"}},"creation":{"createdAt":1781268630487,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"creation指的是創造或創作，是指某人製作或創作的東西。","options":["destruction","creation","collection","exhibition"],"sentence":"The artist was very proud of her latest ______ which took her six months to complete. The sculpture was a masterpiece of modern art.","translation":"藝術家為她耗時六個月完成的最新作品感到非常自豪。這件雕塑是現代藝術的傑作。","word":"creation"}},"creative":{"createdAt":1781268630476,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"creative指的是具有創造力或創意的，能夠想出新的、原創的想法或解決方案。","options":["logical","practical","creative","analytical"],"sentence":"Sarah has a very ______ mind that allows her to solve problems in unique ways. She often finds novel solutions that others would never think of.","translation":"莎拉有一個非常有創造力的頭腦，使她能夠以獨特的方式解決問題。她經常找到其他人永遠不會想到的新穎解決方案。","word":"creative"}},"credit":{"createdAt":1781837419089,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Credit作為名詞表示延期支付的購買方式，允許買家稍後付款。","options":["cash","credit","debit","check"],"sentence":"The store allowed customers to purchase items on ______ if they had an established account. Consumers could pay for their purchases at a later date.","translation":"如果客戶有既定帳戶，商店允許他們以賒帳方式購買商品。消費者可以在日後支付他們的購買費用。","word":"credit"}},"creep":{"createdAt":1781427134902,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"creep指為了避免被發現而緩慢、悄悄地移動。","options":["dash","creep","sprint","stroll"],"sentence":"The burglar began to ______ through the dark hallway of the museum at midnight. He moved silently and carefully to avoid triggering any security alarms.","translation":"竊賊開始在午夜時悄悄潛行穿過博物館的黑暗走廊。他靜靜地小心移動以避免觸發任何安全警報。","word":"creep"}},"crew":{"createdAt":1781667024996,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"crew指執行特定任務的全體工作人員，特別是在船、飛機或製片等領域。","options":["cast","audience","crew","management"],"sentence":"The film production ______ included directors, cameramen, and sound technicians working together on set. Each member played a crucial role in creating the movie.","translation":"電影製作全體人員包括導演、攝影師和音效技師在片場一起工作。每個成員在電影製作中都發揮了關鍵作用。","word":"crew"}},"crippled":{"createdAt":1781417610421,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"crippled是指身體殘廢或受傷，導致行動困難或喪失某些功能。","options":["wealthy","intelligent","crippled","tall"],"sentence":"The ______ knight struggled to walk up the stone staircase despite his determination. His leg injury from the battle prevented him from moving quickly or without pain.","translation":"這位殘廢的騎士儘管決心十足，仍然難以上石階。他在戰鬥中的腿部傷害阻止了他快速移動或無痛移動。","word":"crippled"}},"crippling":{"createdAt":1781951900952,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"crippling形容嚴重損害身體功能或使人喪失能力的傷害，帶有極其負面的後果。","options":["minor","crippling","temporary","concerning"],"sentence":"The athlete suffered a ______ injury that prevented him from competing in the championship. His leg was so badly damaged that he couldn't walk without assistance.","translation":"運動員遭受了一個嚴重損害身體的傷害，使他無法在錦標賽中競賽。他的腿傷得太重，沒有幫助就無法行走。","word":"crippling"}},"crisis":{"createdAt":1781428458256,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"crisis指突然發生的困難或危險局面，需要迅速採取行動解決。","options":["confidence","normal","crisis","comfort"],"sentence":"The company faced a serious ______ when their main product was discovered to be defective. Management had to act immediately to recall all units and restore customer trust.","translation":"當該公司的主要產品被發現有缺陷時，公司面臨了嚴重的危機。管理層必須立即採取行動召回所有產品並恢復客戶信任。","word":"crisis"}},"criteria":{"createdAt":1781738105695,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"criteria 是用來評判或衡量事物的標準或準則，通常以複數形式出現。","options":["opinions","criteria","rumors","guesses"],"sentence":"The hiring committee established clear ______ for evaluating all job applicants fairly and objectively. They would assess candidates based on education, experience, and communication skills.","translation":"招聘委員會制定了明確的標準，以便公平和客觀地評估所有求職者。他們將根據教育背景、工作經驗和溝通技能來評估候選人。","word":"criteria"}},"criticism":{"createdAt":1781738105681,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"criticism 指的是對某人或某事物的負面評論或評判，通常涉及指出缺點或問題。","options":["praise","criticism","promotion","admiration"],"sentence":"The artist received harsh ______ about her new painting from several art reviewers. Despite their negative comments, she felt the feedback was constructive and helped her improve her technique.","translation":"這位藝術家因為她的新畫作從幾位藝術評論家那裡收到了嚴厲的批評。儘管他們的評論是負面的，但她認為這些反饋是建設性的，幫助她改進了技巧。","word":"criticism"}},"criticize":{"createdAt":1781283344040,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"criticize意為指出缺點或不足之處；當與「指出具體錯誤」和「提供改進建議」搭配時，表示進行建設性的評論。","options":["praise","criticize","ignore","summarize"],"sentence":"The teacher decided to ______ the student's essay for its numerous grammatical errors. She pointed out specific mistakes and offered constructive suggestions for improvement.","translation":"老師決定批評學生的論文因為它有許多文法錯誤。她指出具體的錯誤並提供改進建議。","word":"criticize"}},"crop":{"createdAt":1781831848725,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"crop 作為名詞表示「作物」或「收成」，指的是農業種植並收穫的產物。","options":["harvest","crop","season","weather"],"sentence":"The farmers harvested their ______ of wheat this autumn. They sold the entire yield at the market for a good price.","translation":"農民在今年秋天收穫了他們的作物。他們以優好的價格在市場上銷售了整個產量。","word":"crop"}},"crowd":{"createdAt":1781274836864,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"crowd作為名詞表示聚集在一起的大量人群，通常表現出擁擠和混亂的狀態。","options":["crowd","line","team","parade"],"sentence":"A large ______ gathered outside the concert venue before the gates opened. Thousands of excited fans pushed and shoved to get the best positions for the show.","translation":"在演唱會場地大門打開前，一大群人聚集在外面。數千名興奮的粉絲互相推擠以獲得最佳位置看演出。","word":"crowd"}},"cruel":{"createdAt":1781961506840,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cruel表示殘酷、無情，用於描述令人痛苦或傷害他人的行為和態度。","options":["kind","cruel","forgiving","gentle"],"sentence":"The villain in the movie was ______ to the innocent villagers, showing no mercy whatsoever. He tortured them and enjoyed their suffering, demonstrating the darkest aspects of human nature.","translation":"電影中的反派對無辜村民很______，毫無憐憫之心。他折磨他們並享受他們的痛苦，展現了人性最黑暗的一面。","word":"cruel"}},"cruise":{"createdAt":1781268630483,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cruise指的是乘船遊覽，通常是一次休閒的海上旅行，船會停靠多個港口。","options":["flight","cruise","safari","expedition"],"sentence":"They booked a Caribbean ______ for their honeymoon. The ship would stop at five different tropical islands over two weeks.","translation":"他們為蜜月預訂了一次加勒比海遊輪之旅。這艘船將在兩周內停靠五個不同的熱帶島嶼。","word":"cruise"}},"crunchy":{"createdAt":1781484415225,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"crunchy意指食物發出嘎吱嘎吱聲且質地脆硬，通常表示食物新鮮美味。","options":["soft","smooth","crunchy","sticky"],"sentence":"The ______ texture of the fresh apple made a satisfying sound when she bit into it. Each chew produced a pleasant crackling noise that indicated its freshness and crispness.","translation":"新鮮蘋果的脆爽質地在她咬下去時發出令人滿足的聲音。每次咀嚼都產生令人愉快的嘎吱聲，表明它的新鮮和脆爽。","word":"crunchy"}},"crush":{"createdAt":1781693293269,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"crush 作名詞表示「迷戀的人」或「暗戀」，指對某人的浪漫感情。","options":["plant","philosopher","crush","executive"],"sentence":"Sarah has had a ______ on her classmate for months. She blushes whenever she sees him in the hallway.","translation":"莎拉暗戀她的同學已經好幾個月了。每當她在走廊裡看到他時，她就會臉紅。","word":"crush"}},"crushing":{"createdAt":1781693269016,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"crushing 作為形容詞表示非常嚴重的、毀滅性的、難以承受的，通常用於描述負面的影響或結果。","options":["minor","negligible","crushing","slight"],"sentence":"The company faced ______ losses after the market crash last month. The financial impact was so severe that hundreds of employees had to be laid off within weeks.","translation":"上個月市場崩潰後，該公司遭受了極其嚴重的損失。財務影響非常嚴重，以至於數百名員工必須在幾週內被裁員。","word":"crushing"}},"crystal":{"createdAt":1781256444507,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"crystal在此指手錶或鐘錶的玻璃蓋，既透明又具有保護作用。","options":["leather","crystal","metal","fabric"],"sentence":"The antique pocket watch had a protective ______ covering its face. Without this transparent shield, the delicate hands inside would be exposed to dust and damage.","translation":"古董懷錶的錶面有一層保護性的水晶玻璃。沒有這層透明的保護罩，裡面的精緻指針會暴露在灰塵和損害中。","word":"crystal"}},"cub":{"createdAt":1781951900951,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cub特指獅子、熊等野生動物的幼仔，是對小型肉食動物的專門術語。","options":["offspring","cub","pup","infant"],"sentence":"The mother bear protected her ______ fiercely from any danger that approached their den. The young animal stayed close to its parent during their first months of life.","translation":"母熊兇悍地保護她的幼崽免受任何接近洞穴的危險。這隻年輕的動物在生命的前幾個月都緊跟在父母身邊。","word":"cub"}},"cuisine":{"createdAt":1781362281726,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cuisine指的是烹飪或烹調風格，特別是某個地區或國家的特色菜餚。","options":["music","cuisine","art","fashion"],"sentence":"The restaurant specializes in Thai ______ with authentic recipes. The chefs use traditional cooking methods and genuine ingredients from Thailand.","translation":"這家餐廳專門提供泰國烹飪，採用正宗食譜。廚師使用傳統的烹飪方法和來自泰國的真正食材。","word":"cuisine"}},"culinary":{"createdAt":1781850347302,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"烹飪是形容詞，用來描述與烹飪、食品準備或廚房相關的事物。","options":["musical","artistic","culinary","athletic"],"sentence":"Her ______ skills were so exceptional that she won three Michelin stars for her restaurant. Food critics praised her innovative techniques and exquisite flavor combinations.","translation":"她的烹飪技能非常出色，她的餐廳獲得了三顆米其林星。美食評論家稱讚她的創新技巧和精緻的味道組合。","word":"culinary"}},"cultivated":{"createdAt":1781479123533,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"cultivated 指的是有教養、精緻優雅的，通過學習和經驗培養出來的品質。","options":["rude","wild","cultivated","lazy"],"sentence":"The ______ gentleman displayed excellent manners and refined taste in art and literature. His years of travel and education had shaped him into a person of sophistication and cultural appreciation.","translation":"這位有教養的紳士展現了在藝術和文學方面的優雅品味和精良舉止。他多年的旅行和教育經歷使他成為一個老練而具有文化修養的人。","word":"cultivated"}},"cumulate":{"createdAt":1781532967169,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cumulate 表示積聚、收集，與「每年增長」的描述相符。","options":["discard","cumulate","donate","trade"],"sentence":"Over the years, the collector continued to ______ rare stamps from around the world. His dedication meant his collection grew larger every single year.","translation":"多年來，收藏家繼續______(積聚)來自世界各地的稀有郵票。他的執著意味著他的收藏每年都在增長。","word":"cumulate"}},"curative":{"createdAt":1782022372243,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"curative 意為「有療效的、能治療的」，用來形容能夠治癒或緩解疾病的方法或物質。","options":["harmful","curative","experimental","expensive"],"sentence":"The doctor prescribed a ______ treatment that would help heal the patient's chronic illness. After three months of following the regimen, the patient's symptoms disappeared completely.","translation":"醫生開了一種具有療效的治療方法來幫助患者治癒慢性病。經過三個月的治療後，患者的症狀完全消失了。","word":"curative"}},"curfew":{"createdAt":1781364476360,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Curfew是指政府為了維持秩序或安全而規定的在特定時間後禁止人們外出的法令。","options":["holiday","curfew","festival","meeting"],"sentence":"During the emergency, the government imposed a strict ______ that required all residents to stay indoors after 8 PM. Police patrolled the streets to ensure compliance with this mandatory time restriction.","translation":"在緊急狀況期間，政府實施了嚴格的宵禁，要求所有居民必須在晚上8點後待在室內。警察在街上巡邏，以確保遵守這項強制性的時間限制。","word":"curfew"}},"curious":{"createdAt":1781515270344,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"curious 作形容詞，表示對某事物充滿好奇心或渴望瞭解的態度。","options":["bucket","investment","curious","prospect"],"sentence":"The young child was ______ about how the old clock worked on the mantelpiece. She asked her grandmother endless questions and wanted to take it apart to see the gears inside.","translation":"年幼的孩子對壁爐上的舊鐘如何運作感到好奇。她不斷地問祖母問題，想拆開它來看裡面的齒輪。","word":"curious"}},"currency":{"createdAt":1781860901465,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"currency指一個國家或地區使用的貨幣，是經濟交易的媒介","options":["language","culture","currency","custom"],"sentence":"When traveling to Japan, you need to exchange your dollars for the local ______. The yen is the official monetary unit used throughout the country.","translation":"前往日本旅遊時，你需要將美元兌換成當地貨幣。日圓是該國官方使用的貨幣單位。","word":"currency"}},"curve":{"createdAt":1781871338558,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"curve表示道路上的彎曲或弧形，與需要減速和小心轉彎相關。","options":["straight","section","bend","path"],"sentence":"The mountain road had a dangerous ______ ahead that required drivers to slow down significantly. We took the turn carefully to avoid skidding on the wet pavement.","translation":"前面的山路有一個危險的轉彎，需要駕駛員大幅減速。我們小心地轉過彎角以避免在濕潤的路面上打滑。","word":"curve"}},"cushion":{"createdAt":1781653278522,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"cushion是名詞，表示墊子、座墊或靠墊，用於提供舒適和支撐，常放在家具上以增加舒適度。","options":["bracket","cushion","frame","shelf"],"sentence":"She placed a soft ______ on the hard wooden chair to make sitting more comfortable. After adding this padding, she could sit for hours without experiencing back pain.","translation":"她在堅硬的木製椅子上放了一個柔軟的______，使坐著更舒服。加上這個墊子後，她可以坐幾個小時而不會感到背部疼痛。","word":"cushion"}},"custody":{"createdAt":1781709854484,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"custody（監護）指法律上對兒童的照管和監護權，與court award（法院判決）和responsible for daily care（負責日常照顧）的語境相符。","options":["custody","dismissal","liberty","estate"],"sentence":"After the divorce, the mother was awarded ______ of both children by the court. She became responsible for their daily care, education, and well-being.","translation":"離婚後，母親被法院判予兩個孩子的監護權。她成為負責他們日常照顧、教育和福祉的人。","word":"custody"}},"custom":{"createdAt":1781336858149,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"custom 指的是在特定文化或社會中代代相傳的習慣或傳統做法。","options":["law","accident","custom","mistake"],"sentence":"In Japan, it is a ______ to remove your shoes before entering someone's home. This tradition has been practiced for centuries and is still widely respected today.","translation":"在日本，進入他人家中前脫掉鞋子是一個習俗。這個傳統已經被實踐了幾個世紀，今天仍然得到廣泛尊重。","word":"custom"}},"customer":{"createdAt":1781848934153,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"customer指購買商品或服務的人","options":["employee","customer","competitor","supplier"],"sentence":"The store manager apologized sincerely to the upset ______ about the billing error. She promised to refund the overcharge immediately.","translation":"商店經理為計費錯誤向不滿的顧客真摯地道歉。她承諾立即退款。","word":"customer"}},"customs":{"createdAt":1781848934150,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"customs指邊境檢查站，也指一個國家的關稅部門","options":["hotels","customs","restaurants","hospitals"],"sentence":"When traveling internationally, you must pass through ______ to declare any goods you're bringing into the country. The officers will inspect your luggage carefully.","translation":"在國際旅行時，你必須通過海關申報任何你帶入該國的物品。海關官員將仔細檢查你的行李。","word":"customs"}},"daily":{"createdAt":1781837419087,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"Daily指的是每天發生或進行的事物，日報就是每天出版一次的報紙。","options":["weekly","monthly","daily","annual"],"sentence":"I read the ______ newspaper every morning before going to work. The publication is released fresh each new day with updated news.","translation":"我每天早上上班前都會閱讀日報。這份出版物每天新鮮發行，提供最新新聞。","word":"daily"}},"dampen":{"createdAt":1781696018693,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dampen 意為使潮濕或減弱、抑制，指降低或削弱某種情感、熱情或動力。","options":["enhance","dampen","increase","inspire"],"sentence":"The unexpected criticism did not ______ his enthusiasm for the project at all. He remained fully committed to completing his vision.","translation":"這意外的批評絲毫沒有削弱他對這個項目的熱情。他仍然完全致力於完成他的願景。","word":"dampen"}},"dazzle":{"createdAt":1781275226789,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"此處dazzle作動詞表示「使感到刺眼；使目眩」","options":["dump","breast","dazzle","stroke"],"sentence":"The fireworks display continued to ______ the audience with brilliant colors and unexpected explosions. Their eyes were overwhelmed by the stunning brightness of each burst.","translation":"煙火表演繼續以炫目的色彩和意想不到的爆炸使觀眾眼花繚亂。每一次爆發的驚人亮度都讓他們的眼睛感到刺眼。","word":"dazzle"}},"deal":{"createdAt":1781395310166,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"deal 作為動詞表示應付、處理某種情況或問題。","options":["ignore","avoid","deal","celebrate"],"sentence":"The manager had to ______ with three customer complaints before lunch. She handled each issue professionally and resolved them all within an hour.","translation":"經理必須在午餐前應付三個客戶投訴。她專業地處理了每個問題並在一小時內全部解決。","word":"deal"}},"debris":{"createdAt":1781598671164,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"debris 作名詞表示碎片或殘骸，指破壞或損毀後留下的廢棄物質","options":["furniture","debris","belongings","supplies"],"sentence":"The tornado left scattered ______ across the entire neighborhood after its destructive path. Residents spent weeks cleaning up the remains of destroyed buildings.","translation":"龍捲風在其破壞路徑後在整個社區留下散落的碎片。居民花了數週時間清理被摧毀建築物的殘骸。","word":"debris"}},"debt":{"createdAt":1781598671104,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"debt 作名詞表示債務，指某人或某個組織必須償還的金錢","options":["assets","debt","income","revenue"],"sentence":"After the loan was fully repaid, the company was finally free from financial ______. Management celebrated the achievement of becoming a debt-free organization.","translation":"貸款全額償還後，該公司終於擺脫了財務債務。管理層慶祝了成為無債務組織的成就。","word":"debt"}},"debut":{"createdAt":1781850347304,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"首演是指一個人或作品首次公開出現或展示，通常指演員或藝術家的第一次正式表演。","options":["retirement","performance","debut","appearance"],"sentence":"The young actress made her ______ in a small independent film last year. She has since appeared in three major Hollywood productions and received critical acclaim.","translation":"這位年輕女演員去年在一部小型獨立電影中首演。她此後出現在三部好萊塢主要影片中，並獲得了評論家的讚譽。","word":"debut"}},"decay":{"createdAt":1781848934148,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"decay指事物逐漸腐爛、腐朽或衰敗的過程","options":["strengthen","decay","whiten","grow"],"sentence":"If you don't brush your teeth regularly, they will begin to ______. Poor dental hygiene leads to cavities and serious infections.","translation":"如果你不定期刷牙，牙齒就會開始腐爛。糟糕的牙齒衛生會導致蛀牙和嚴重感染。","word":"decay"}},"deceit":{"createdAt":1781283344055,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deceit意為欺騙、詐欺；與「虛假宣傳」和「調查揭露真相」搭配，表示故意誤導他人的行為。","options":["honesty","deceit","compliance","transparency"],"sentence":"The company was involved in ______ when it falsely advertised that its products were environmentally friendly. Investigations revealed that the manufacturing process actually produced significant pollution.","translation":"該公司因虛假宣傳其產品環保而涉及欺騙。調查顯示製造過程實際上產生了大量污染。","word":"deceit"}},"deceive":{"createdAt":1781849847400,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deceive表示欺騙或哄騙，與「說謊」和「失去信譽」的線索相符。","options":["inform","deceive","educate","encourage"],"sentence":"The salesman tried to ______ his customers about the product's quality. He was caught lying and lost all credibility.","translation":"銷售員試圖欺騙顧客關於產品的品質。他被發現說謊並失去了所有信譽。","word":"deceive"}},"decency":{"createdAt":1781850347301,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"得體或端莊是指符合社會道德規範、表現得當、行為高尚的品質。","options":["intelligence","strength","decency","humor"],"sentence":"The politician showed a lack of ______ when he publicly mocked his opponent's personal struggles. Such behavior violated basic standards of respect and dignity in public discourse.","translation":"當政治家公開嘲笑他對手的個人困難時，他展現出缺乏得體。這種行為違反了公開辯論中基本的尊重和尊嚴標準。","word":"decency"}},"decent":{"createdAt":1781959842986,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"decent 表示令人滿意、像樣的，用來形容達到可接受標準的事物，不一定是奢華或最好的。","options":["luxurious","decent","spacious","modern"],"sentence":"Although the hotel room was small, it was ______ and comfortable for our stay. We were satisfied with the clean sheets, working air conditioning, and friendly staff.","translation":"雖然飯店房間很小，但它很體面舒適，適合我們住宿。我們對乾淨的床單、正常運作的冷氣和友善的員工感到滿意。","word":"decent"}},"declaration":{"createdAt":1781959842990,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"declaration 指正式的、公開的宣佈或聲明，通常來自權威人士或政府機構，具有重要的法律或政治意義。","options":["suggestion","declaration","rumor","question"],"sentence":"The president made an official ______ announcing the new environmental policy to the nation. All major news outlets broadcast the formal announcement on television and radio.","translation":"總統發表了一份正式聲明，向全國宣佈新的環境政策。所有主要新聞媒體都在電視和廣播上播放了這項正式公告。","word":"declaration"}},"declare":{"createdAt":1781624534655,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"declare 意為「宣稱、宣佈、聲明」，表示正式公開地說出或宣告某事。","options":["hide","declare","delay","question"],"sentence":"The president will ______ the results of the election during a live television broadcast tomorrow. Citizens are waiting to hear the official announcement from the government.","translation":"總統將在明天的電視直播中宣佈選舉結果。公民們正在等待聽政府的正式宣告。","word":"declare"}},"decline":{"createdAt":1781598671099,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"decline 作名詞表示衰退或下降，指某事物數量或質量的減少","options":["growth","decline","stability","boom"],"sentence":"The company experienced a sharp ______ in sales after losing its largest client. Revenue dropped by 40% within just six months.","translation":"失去最大客戶後，該公司的銷售額經歷了急劇下降。收入在短短六個月內下降了40%。","word":"decline"}},"decorate":{"createdAt":1781395310168,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"decorate 表示為空間或物品進行美化或點綴以使其更加吸引人。","options":["demolish","decorate","abandon","damage"],"sentence":"The team decided to ______ the office for the holiday party with colorful balloons and lights. By evening, the plain gray walls had been transformed into a festive wonderland.","translation":"團隊決定用彩色氣球和燈光為假日派對裝飾辦公室。到了晚上，樸素的灰色牆壁已經變成了一個節日樂園。","word":"decorate"}},"decorative":{"createdAt":1781832478020,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"decorative 意為「裝飾性的」，用來形容主要目的是為了美觀和裝飾而非實用的東西。","options":["functional","decorative","expensive","ancient"],"sentence":"The vase serves a ______ purpose in the living room rather than a practical one. It's purely for beauty and has no function other than to enhance the appearance of the space.","translation":"這個花瓶在客廳裡的作用是裝飾性的，而不是實用的。它純粹是為了美觀，除了增強空間外觀外，沒有其他功能。","word":"decorative"}},"decrease":{"createdAt":1781362281654,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"decrease表示減少或降低，通常用於數量、程度或強度的下降。","options":["increase","decrease","stabilize","fluctuate"],"sentence":"The company's profits will ______ if they don't reduce operational costs. The financial reports show fewer sales this quarter compared to last year.","translation":"如果公司不降低運營成本，利潤將會減少。財務報告顯示本季度的銷售額少於去年。","word":"decrease"}},"deduct":{"createdAt":1781848934154,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deduct指從總數中減去或扣除某個部分","options":["add","deduct","multiply","divide"],"sentence":"The accountant will ______ all business expenses from your gross income before calculating taxes. This reduces the amount of taxes you owe.","translation":"會計將在計算稅款前從你的總收入中扣除所有業務開支。這減少了你所欠的稅款金額。","word":"deduct"}},"deem":{"createdAt":1781832761716,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deem 表示認為、以為、視作，指做出某種判斷或評估。","options":["reject","consider","ignore","criticize"],"sentence":"The judges ______ the student's essay to be the best among all submissions for the competition. It demonstrated exceptional writing skills and original thinking that surpassed all others.","translation":"評委們認為該學生的論文是競賽中所有投稿中最優秀的。它展現了超越所有其他作品的卓越寫作技巧和原創思維。","word":"deem"}},"defeat":{"createdAt":1781425122880,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"defeat 意為失敗或被擊敗，與失分多和排名最後的資訊相符。","options":["victory","defeat","discount","exhibition"],"sentence":"The team suffered a terrible ______ in the championship game. They lost by thirty points and finished in last place.","translation":"球隊在錦標賽中遭受了慘敗。他們被領先三十分，最終排名墊底。","word":"defeat"}},"defect":{"createdAt":1781395310155,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"defect 指物品或系統中的問題或不完美之處，這裡用於描述需要修復的故障。","options":["strength","defect","feature","benefit"],"sentence":"The manufacturer discovered a ______ in the product that could affect safety. Engineers immediately recalled all units to fix this flaw before it reached consumers.","translation":"製造商發現產品中的缺陷可能會影響安全。工程師立即召回所有單位，在缺陷到達消費者之前進行修復。","word":"defect"}},"defendant":{"createdAt":1781693254767,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"defendant是法律術語，指被指控或起訴的人，在訴訟中被告方。","options":["plaintiff","witness","defendant","judge"],"sentence":"The ______ stood in court to hear the jury's verdict after months of trial. The person accused of the crime listened carefully as the judge announced the decision.","translation":"經過數月的審判後，被告站在法庭上聽取陪審團的判決。被控犯罪的人認真地聆聽法官宣布的決定。","word":"defendant"}},"defensive":{"createdAt":1781449588283,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"defensive作為形容詞表示「防禦的、防守的」，用於描述保護或阻止攻擊的行為和策略。","options":["improve","signify","defensive","regulate"],"sentence":"The soccer team adopted a ______ strategy to protect their goal from the opponent's attacks. The coach instructed the players to focus on blocking shots and preventing dangerous advances into their penalty area.","translation":"足球隊採取了防禦性策略來保護他們的球門免受對手的攻擊。教練指示球員專注於擋球和防止對手危險地推進到他們的禁區。","word":"defensive"}},"deficient":{"createdAt":1781693270386,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deficient表示「不足的、缺乏的」，用來描述某物數量或質量不夠或有缺陷的情況。","options":["abundant","deficient","excessive","balanced"],"sentence":"The patient's diet was ______ in vitamin C, which led to serious health complications. Blood tests confirmed that his nutrient levels were critically low.","translation":"患者的飲食缺乏維生素C，導致了嚴重的健康問題。血液檢查證實他的營養水平嚴重不足。","word":"deficient"}},"deficit":{"createdAt":1782016805984,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deficit 是名詞，表示支出大於收入的差額，即赤字或虧損。","options":["surplus","deficit","balance","profit"],"sentence":"The country faced a massive budget ______ as government spending far exceeded tax revenues. Without significant policy changes, the national debt would continue to grow rapidly.","translation":"由於政府支出遠超稅收收入，該國面臨巨大的預算赤字。如果沒有重大政策改變，國債將繼續迅速增長。","word":"deficit"}},"define":{"createdAt":1781395310172,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"define 表示給予清晰的定義或詳細說明某個詞語、概念或事物的確切含義。","options":["erase","define","illustrate","memorize"],"sentence":"The teacher asked students to ______ the term 'photosynthesis' in their own words during the exam. Each student had to provide a clear explanation of what the process means and how it works.","translation":"老師要求學生在考試中用自己的話定義「光合作用」這一術語。每個學生都必須清楚地解釋該過程的含義及其工作方式。","word":"define"}},"definite":{"createdAt":1781871338568,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"definite表示絕對確定、明確和不會改變，與沒有變化或驚喜的預期相符。","options":["uncertain","ambiguous","vague","firm"],"sentence":"The coach gave a ______ answer about which player would start in the championship game. There would be no changes or surprises on game day.","translation":"教練對誰將在錦標賽中先發給出了明確的答案。比賽當天不會有任何變化或驚喜。","word":"definite"}},"definitely":{"createdAt":1781283344047,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"definitely意為確實地、肯定地；與「已經註冊和預訂」的事實搭配，表示非常確定的態度。","options":["might","definitely","probably","possibly"],"sentence":"I will ______ attend the conference next month without any doubt. I have already registered and booked my hotel room.","translation":"我絕對會參加下個月的會議，毫無疑問。我已經註冊並預訂了酒店房間。","word":"definitely"}},"definition":{"createdAt":1781871338563,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"definition表示對詞語的精確含義的解釋，用於詞典或教學中。","options":["pronunciation","meaning","origin","example"],"sentence":"The ______ of the word 'artificial' in the dictionary states that it means 'made or produced by humans rather than occurring naturally.' Students should memorize this explanation for the vocabulary test.","translation":"字典中'人工'一詞的定義指出它的意思是'由人類製造或生產而不是自然發生的'。學生應該為詞彙測試記住這個解釋。","word":"definition"}},"degree":{"createdAt":1781395310169,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"degree 表示溫度、程度或強度的度量單位，這裡指溫度的測量值。","options":["color","sound","degree","texture"],"sentence":"The heat in the desert reached an extreme ______ of 50 degrees Celsius during the afternoon. Residents stayed indoors to avoid the dangerous temperature.","translation":"沙漠中的高溫在下午達到了極端的50攝氏度。居民們呆在室內以避免危險的溫度。","word":"degree"}},"deliberate":{"createdAt":1781401803898,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deliberate作形容詞表示「經過深思熟慮的」，強調在做出決定或回答前經過充分考慮。","options":["hasty","thoughtful","automatic","confused"],"sentence":"The student gave a ______ answer to the difficult question during the exam. She paused for a moment, thought carefully, and then spoke with confidence and precision.","translation":"那個學生在考試中對難題給出了經過深思熟慮的答案。她停頓了一下，仔細思考，然後自信而準確地說話。","word":"deliberate"}},"deliberately":{"createdAt":1781507137218,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"deliberately 表示故意地、刻意地做某件事，強調行為是有計劃和意識的，而不是無意的。","options":["accidentally","reluctantly","deliberately","gradually"],"sentence":"She ______ knocked over the vase to test if her brother was telling the truth about the accident. Her actions proved that he had lied about how the original vase broke.","translation":"她故意打翻花瓶來測試她的哥哥是否在說關於意外的真話。她的行為證明他對原來的花瓶如何打破撒了謊。","word":"deliberately"}},"delicate":{"createdAt":1781425024018,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"delicate表示易碎的、脆弱的、精美的，需要謹慎對待，稍不注意就會受損。","options":["sturdy","delicate","heavy","modern"],"sentence":"The antique porcelain vase was extremely ______ and required special handling to prevent damage. One small drop or careless movement could cause it to shatter into a thousand pieces.","translation":"這個古董瓷花瓶極其脆弱，需要特殊處理以防止損壞。一次輕微的跌落或粗心的動作可能會使它破成一千片。","word":"delicate"}},"deliver":{"createdAt":1781598671087,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deliver 作動詞表示發表或遞送，在這裡指正式地發表演講或講話","options":["write","deliver","publish","record"],"sentence":"The president will ______ the inaugural address at the ceremony tomorrow morning. The speech is expected to outline his vision for the nation over the next four years.","translation":"總統明天上午將在儀式上發表就職演說。該演講預計將闡述他對未來四年國家的願景。","word":"deliver"}},"delivery":{"createdAt":1782002325570,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"delivery 在醫療語境中指的是分娩的過程，即嬰兒從子宮出生的過程。","options":["delivery","distribution","presentation","transmission"],"sentence":"The ______ of the newborn baby was successful, and both mother and child were in excellent health. The doctor completed the procedure in the hospital's maternity ward without any complications.","translation":"嬰兒的分娩很順利，母親和孩子都健康狀況良好。醫生在醫院的產科病房順利完成了手術，沒有任何併發症。","word":"delivery"}},"demanding":{"createdAt":1781598671169,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"demanding 作形容詞表示苛求的或過分要求的，指對他人有很高期望且難以滿足","options":["lenient","demanding","flexible","understanding"],"sentence":"The manager had a reputation for being very ______ with his team members. He expected perfection in every project and rarely accepted work that didn't meet his extremely high standards.","translation":"這位經理以對團隊成員過分要求而聞名。他期望每個項目都完美無缺，很少接受不符合他極高標準的工作。","word":"demanding"}},"dementia":{"createdAt":1781624534654,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dementia 意為「老年癡呆、癡呆症」，是一種影響記憶、思考和行為能力的神經系統疾病。","options":["arthritis","dementia","insomnia","allergy"],"sentence":"The elderly man was diagnosed with ______ after forgetting his family members' names and losing the ability to care for himself. His doctor explained that the disease affects memory and cognitive function.","translation":"這位老人在忘記家人的名字並喪失自理能力後被診斷患有老年癡呆。他的醫生解釋該疾病會影響記憶和認知功能。","word":"dementia"}},"democracy":{"createdAt":1781624534705,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"democracy 意為「民主政治、民主制度」，是指由人民統治的政治制度。","options":["tyranny","monarchy","democracy","dictatorship"],"sentence":"The citizens celebrated the establishment of ______ in their nation after years of living under military rule. They could finally vote freely and express their opinions without fear.","translation":"在多年生活在軍事統治下後，公民們慶祝了國家民主制度的建立。他們終於可以自由投票和表達意見而不用擔心。","word":"democracy"}},"democrat":{"createdAt":1781624534705,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"democrat 意為「民主主義者、民主派」，指擁護民主制度並為其效力的人。","options":["authoritarian","oligarch","democrat","monarch"],"sentence":"As a committed ______, he has spent his entire career fighting for equal rights and freedom of speech. His speeches always emphasize the importance of citizen participation in government.","translation":"作為一名致力於民主主義的人士，他花費了整個職業生涯爭取平等權利和言論自由。他的演講總是強調公民參與政府的重要性。","word":"democrat"}},"democratic":{"createdAt":1781624534657,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"democratic 意為「民主的」，指以人民主權和多數統治為基礎的政治制度。","options":["authoritarian","dictatorial","democratic","totalitarian"],"sentence":"The country adopted a ______ system where all citizens have the right to vote and participate in government. Every person's voice matters equally in the decision-making process.","translation":"該國採用了民主制度，所有公民都有權投票和參與政府事務。每個人在決策過程中的聲音都同等重要。","word":"democratic"}},"demonstrate":{"createdAt":1781283344054,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"demonstrate意為示範、展示；與「培訓會」和「員工看到實際操作」搭配，表示向他人展示如何使用或操作某物。","options":["criticize","demonstrate","estimate","document"],"sentence":"The engineer will ______ how the new software system works during the company training session tomorrow. All employees will have the opportunity to see the features in action and ask questions.","translation":"工程師將在明天的公司培訓會上示範新軟體系統的工作方式。所有員工將有機會看到實際操作並提出問題。","word":"demonstrate"}},"denial":{"createdAt":1781624534707,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"denial 意為「否認、否定」，指拒絕承認或接受某事實。","options":["admission","denial","agreement","confession"],"sentence":"The suspect's ______ of the crime became less convincing as more evidence was presented in court. The eyewitness testimony contradicted his claims completely.","translation":"隨著法庭上提出更多證據，被告對犯罪的否認變得越來越不可信。目擊者的證詞與他的說法完全相反。","word":"denial"}},"dense":{"createdAt":1781624534653,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dense 意為「密集的、稠密的」，用來形容物質或事物緊密排列或高度濃縮。","options":["sparse","dense","colorful","ancient"],"sentence":"The ______ forest was so thick that sunlight barely reached the ground. The hikers had to use flashlights during the middle of the day.","translation":"這片密集的森林非常濃厚，陽光幾乎無法到達地面。登山者不得不在白天中午使用手電筒。","word":"dense"}},"density":{"createdAt":1781624534711,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"density 意為「密度」，指單位面積或體積內物質或人口的濃度。","options":["scarcity","rarity","density","emptiness"],"sentence":"The ______ of the population in the city center is much higher than in the suburban areas. Over ten thousand people live in just one square kilometer downtown.","translation":"市中心的人口密度遠高於郊區。市中心每平方公里就住著超過一萬人。","word":"density"}},"deny":{"createdAt":1781332009068,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deny 意為否認或拒絕承認某事，尤其是在面對指控時","options":["admit","deny","ignore","celebrate"],"sentence":"The suspect continued to ______ all accusations of theft during the interrogation. However, security cameras had recorded him taking the items from the store.","translation":"嫌疑人在審訊中繼續否認所有的盜竊指控。然而，安全攝像頭錄下了他從商店拿走這些物品的過程。","word":"deny"}},"depart":{"createdAt":1781832761718,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"depart 表示離開、出發，指開始旅程或從某地離開。","options":["arrive","leave","stop","return"],"sentence":"The train will ______ from the station at 3 PM sharp, so all passengers must be onboard by then. Latecomers will not be allowed to board after the scheduled time.","translation":"列車將在下午3點整離開車站，所以所有乘客必須在那時上車。在預定時間之後，遲到的人將不被允許上車。","word":"depart"}},"depend":{"createdAt":1781624534654,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"depend 意為「依靠、依賴」，表示需要他人或其他事物的幫助或支持才能完成某事。","options":["ignore","depend","refuse","prevent"],"sentence":"Small businesses often ______ on loans from the bank to start their operations. Without financial support, most entrepreneurs cannot afford to open their stores.","translation":"小型企業通常依靠銀行貸款來啟動業務。沒有財務支持，大多數企業家無法負擔開設商店的費用。","word":"depend"}},"dependable":{"createdAt":1781624534641,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dependable 意為「可信賴的、可依靠的」，用來形容值得信任、行為可預測的人或事物。","options":["lazy","dependable","confused","arrogant"],"sentence":"You can trust John because he is a ______ employee who always completes his work on time. When the company faced a crisis last month, he was the first person management called.","translation":"你可以相信約翰，因為他是一位可信任的員工，總是按時完成工作。上個月公司面臨危機時，他是管理層首先召喚的人。","word":"dependable"}},"dependence":{"createdAt":1781624534707,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"dependence 意為「依靠、依賴」，指對某物或某人的需要或信賴的狀態。","options":["independence","freedom","dependence","health"],"sentence":"The patient's ______ on medication became so severe that he could not function without taking multiple pills every day. The doctor warned him about the dangers of prolonged reliance.","translation":"患者對藥物的依賴變得如此嚴重，他每天不吃多種藥片就無法正常生活。醫生警告他長期依賴的危害。","word":"dependence"}},"dependent":{"createdAt":1781624534706,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dependent 意為「依賴的、依靠的」，形容某人需要他人的支持或幫助才能生存或生活。","options":["independent","dependent","responsible","capable"],"sentence":"Young children are naturally ______ on their parents for food, shelter, and emotional support. As they grow older, they gradually learn to become more independent.","translation":"幼小的孩子自然上依賴父母提供食物、住所和情感支持。隨著年齡增長，他們逐漸學會變得更加獨立。","word":"dependent"}},"depict":{"createdAt":1781451343289,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"描繪是指通過藝術、文字或其他方式生動地表現或展示某物，使其清晰可見。","options":["ignore","depict","conceal","erase"],"sentence":"The artist used bold colors and dramatic brushstrokes to ______ the emotions of grief and loss in her painting. Viewers immediately recognized the sadness and despair expressed through the artwork.","translation":"藝術家用大膽的色彩和戲劇性的筆觸在她的畫作中描繪悲傷和失去的情感。觀眾立即認出通過藝術品表達的悲傷和絕望。","word":"depict"}},"deplete":{"createdAt":1781395310167,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"deplete 表示大量減少或耗盡資源，使其變得稀少。","options":["increase","replenish","deplete","multiply"],"sentence":"Excessive fishing has begun to ______ the ocean's fish populations at an alarming rate. Scientists warn that if this continues, many species may disappear entirely within decades.","translation":"過度捕撈已開始以驚人的速度耗盡海洋的魚類資源。科學家警告，如果這種情況繼續下去，許多物種可能在幾十年內完全消失。","word":"deplete"}},"deploy":{"createdAt":1781624534656,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deploy 意為「部署、展開、有效運用」，表示策略性地安排或利用某事物達到特定目標。","options":["abandon","deploy","criticize","ignore"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ its new marketing strategy across all social media platforms. This comprehensive approach helped them reach more customers than ever before.","translation":"該公司決定在所有社交媒體平台上部署其新的行銷策略。這種全面的方法幫助他們達到了前所未有的客戶數量。","word":"deploy"}},"deposit":{"createdAt":1781395310163,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deposit 作為名詞表示存入銀行的錢款或作為動詞表示將錢存入銀行。","options":["withdrawal","deposit","loan","mortgage"],"sentence":"She made a ______ at the bank to save money for her future. The teller accepted her $500 payment and credited it to her savings account.","translation":"她在銀行進行存款以為未來儲蓄。出納員接受了她的500美元付款並將其計入她的儲蓄賬戶。","word":"deposit"}},"depress":{"createdAt":1782009504013,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"使沮喪或壓低是指使某人的情緒、士氣或經濟狀況變差，造成消極或負面的心理或經濟影響。","options":["excite","energize","depress","inspire"],"sentence":"The gloomy weather and endless rain began to ______ everyone's mood in the office. By Friday, the entire team seemed lethargic and unmotivated to complete their projects.","translation":"陰沉的天氣和持續的雨開始______辦公室裡每個人的情緒。到了星期五，整個團隊似乎都沒有精力，也沒有動力完成他們的項目。","word":"depress"}},"depressed":{"createdAt":1782001211011,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"depressed 是形容詞，表示感到沮喪、悲傷或情緒低落的狀態。","options":["excited","depressed","motivated","confident"],"sentence":"After failing the exam, he felt ______ and didn't want to socialize with his friends. His mood improved only when he started preparing a study plan with his parents.","translation":"考試不及格後，他感到沮喪，不想和朋友交往。只有當他開始和父母制定學習計畫時，他的情緒才改善。","word":"depressed"}},"depressing":{"createdAt":1781967668681,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"depressing 指壓抑的或令人沮喪的，用來描述使人心情低落的事物或情況。","options":["bad","depressing","cold","wet"],"sentence":"The ______ weather made everyone feel gloomy and unmotivated throughout the day. The gray skies and constant drizzle seemed to drain all energy from the city.","translation":"整天壓抑的天氣使每個人都感到沮喪和沒有動力。灰色的天空和持續的細雨似乎耗盡了這座城市的所有活力。","word":"depressing"}},"depression":{"createdAt":1781283344048,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"depression意為心理沮喪或精神疾病（憂鬱症）；與「處方藥物」和「心理治療」搭配，表示需要醫療介入的精神狀況。","options":["anxiety","depression","stress","tiredness"],"sentence":"Sarah has been suffering from ______ for over a year and finds it difficult to enjoy activities she once loved. Her therapist has prescribed medication and recommended regular counseling sessions.","translation":"莎拉一年多來一直遭受抑鬱症的困擾，發現很難享受她曾經喜愛的活動。她的治療師開了藥物處方並建議定期諮詢。","word":"depression"}},"deprive":{"createdAt":1781425094902,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deprive 指不公正地或強行奪取某人擁有或應該得到的東西。","options":["provide","rob","supply","give"],"sentence":"The strict diet would ______ him of the nutrients his body needed to stay healthy. Without proper vitamins and minerals, his immune system would eventually weaken and become vulnerable to illness.","translation":"這種嚴格的飲食會剝奪他身體保持健康所需的營養。沒有適當的維生素和礦物質，他的免疫系統最終會虛弱並容易患病。","word":"deprive"}},"deprived":{"createdAt":1781624534647,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"deprived 意為「被剝奪的、缺乏的」，表示某人或某地區缺少基本的或必要的東西。","options":["proud","deprived","surprised","concerned"],"sentence":"Many children in that region are ______ of proper education and nutrition. The government's failure to invest in schools has left them far behind their peers in developed areas.","translation":"該地區的許多兒童缺乏適當的教育和營養。政府未能投資學校，導致他們遠遠落後於發達地區的同齡人。","word":"deprived"}},"derive":{"createdAt":1781362281655,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"derive表示源自或得自某處，指事物的起源或來源。","options":["create","derive","invent","form"],"sentence":"The word 'democracy' is ______ from Greek words meaning 'people' and 'rule'. Scholars trace its origins back to ancient Greece.","translation":"'民主'這個詞源自希臘語，意思是'人民'和'統治'。學者將其起源追溯到古希臘。","word":"derive"}},"descent":{"createdAt":1781698273256,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"descent 是名詞，表示「下降」或「下落」的動作，特別是指高度或位置的降低。","options":["ascent","descent","turbulence","takeoff"],"sentence":"The plane's ______ toward the runway was smooth and controlled. The pilots gradually lowered the altitude over several minutes until we touched down safely.","translation":"飛機向跑道的下降是平穩和受控的。飛行員在幾分鐘內逐漸降低高度，直到我們安全著陸。","word":"descent"}},"describe":{"createdAt":1782001211007,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"describe 意思是用言語或文字詳細說明或描繪某物的特徵。","options":["ignore","describe","identify","forget"],"sentence":"The witness was asked to ______ the appearance of the man who stole her purse. She provided detailed information about his height, clothing, and distinctive tattoo on his arm.","translation":"證人被要求描述偷她錢包的男人的外貌。她提供了關於他的身高、衣著和手臂上明顯刺青的詳細資訊。","word":"describe"}},"description":{"createdAt":1781967668676,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"description 指詳細的描述或刻畫，用來說明事物的特徵和外觀。","options":["identification","report","description","announcement"],"sentence":"The ______ of the missing dog was broadcast on all local news channels. The announcer mentioned its brown spots, white collar, and distinctive bark.","translation":"失蹤狗的描寫在所有當地新聞頻道上播放。播報員提到了它的棕色斑點、白色項圈和獨特的吠聲。","word":"description"}},"descriptive":{"createdAt":1781832761710,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"descriptive 是形容詞，表示描寫的、描述性的，旨在生動地表現某事物。","options":["technical","analytical","detailed","statistical"],"sentence":"The travel writer used ______ language to paint a vivid picture of the mountains. Readers could almost see the snow-capped peaks and feel the cold wind as they read the passage.","translation":"旅遊作家使用描寫性的語言來描繪山脈的生動景象。讀者在閱讀這段文字時，幾乎可以看到積雪的山峰，並感受到寒風。","word":"descriptive"}},"deserve":{"createdAt":1781431278558,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"deserve表示因為某些品質或行為而應該得到某物或應該受到某種待遇。","options":["deserve","require","avoid","expect"],"sentence":"After working so hard on the project for three months, she truly ______ a promotion. Her manager recognized her dedication and effort by giving her the leadership role she earned.","translation":"在這個項目上努力工作三個月後，她真的應該獲得晉升。她的經理通過給予她贏得的領導職位來認可她的奉獻和努力。","word":"deserve"}},"desirable":{"createdAt":1781283344051,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"desirable意為渴望獲得的、令人想要的；與「願意支付更高房租」搭配，表示高度受歡迎和珍視的特性。","options":["rare","desirable","problematic","unavailable"],"sentence":"Living near public transportation is a ______ feature for many urban professionals. Those who commute daily are willing to pay higher rent for this convenience.","translation":"住在公共交通附近對許多都市專業人士來說是一個渴望獲得的特點。每天通勤的人願意為這種便利支付更高的房租。","word":"desirable"}},"desire":{"createdAt":1782001211008,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"desire 可作名詞或動詞，表示強烈的渴望或慾望。","options":["fear","desire","regret","doubt"],"sentence":"She had a strong ______ to travel around the world and experience different cultures. This dream had motivated her to save money and plan her journey for many years.","translation":"她強烈渴望環遊世界並體驗不同的文化。這個夢想促使她多年來一直在存錢和計畫旅程。","word":"desire"}},"desperate":{"createdAt":1781583174626,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"desperate意指極度絕望或急切，通常伴隨著無奈和被迫做出極端決定的情況","options":["curious","desperate","uncertain","thoughtful"],"sentence":"After losing his job, Tom felt ______ about his financial situation. He hadn't slept in days and was considering taking any work available, no matter how unsuitable.","translation":"失去工作後，湯姆對自己的財務狀況感到____。他已經好幾天沒有睡眠，正在考慮接受任何工作，無論多麼不適合。","word":"desperate"}},"desperation":{"createdAt":1781967668677,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"desperation 指絕望和孤注一擲的心態，用於描述被迫採取極端行動的情況。","options":["anger","desperation","determination","exhaustion"],"sentence":"In ______, the trapped miners dug through the rubble with their bare hands. This extreme situation forced them to take dangerous risks they would never normally attempt.","translation":"在拚命之下，被困的礦工用赤手空拳挖掘廢墟。這種極端情況迫使他們冒他們通常不會嘗試的危險。","word":"desperation"}},"despise":{"createdAt":1781967668679,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"despise 指強烈鄙視或看不起，表示極度的不尊重。","options":["distrust","despise","avoid","dislike"],"sentence":"He ______ people who lie and cheat others for personal gain. His strong moral principles made him look down upon such dishonest behavior.","translation":"他鄙視那些為了個人利益而欺騙他人的人。他堅強的道德原則使他看不起這種不誠實的行為。","word":"despise"}},"despite":{"createdAt":1781850347304,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"儘管是前置詞，表示雖然有某種困難或不利條件，但某事仍然發生。","options":["Because of","Unlike","Since","Despite"],"sentence":"______ the heavy rain and strong winds, the outdoor concert continued as scheduled. The audience stayed in their seats with umbrellas and enjoyed the entire performance.","translation":"儘管下著大雨和刮著強風，戶外音樂會仍按計劃繼續進行。觀眾帶著雨傘坐在座位上，享受了整場表演。","word":"despite"}},"destination":{"createdAt":1782001211010,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"destination 意思是旅程的終點或目標地點。","options":["journey","destination","vehicle","route"],"sentence":"After driving for eight hours, we finally arrived at our ______ and checked into the hotel. The mountain resort was even more beautiful than the travel guide had promised.","translation":"開了八小時的車後，我們終於抵達了目的地並入住飯店。這個山區度假村比旅遊指南承諾的還要美麗。","word":"destination"}},"destine":{"createdAt":1781950727562,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"destine 表示命定或注定某人會遭遇特定的命運。","options":["forced","destined","prevented","encouraged"],"sentence":"Some people believe we are ______ to become successful from birth. However, others argue that hard work and determination matter more than fate.","translation":"有些人相信我們從出生開始註定要成功。然而，其他人認為努力和決心比命運更重要。","word":"destine"}},"destined":{"createdAt":1781967668680,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"destined 指特定目的或命中註定，用來說明預定的方向或終點。","options":["headed","destined","sailing","traveling"],"sentence":"The ship was ______ for North America when it suddenly encountered a terrible storm. The voyage had been planned months in advance with a specific arrival date.","translation":"這艘船前往北美時突然遭遇了可怕的風暴。這次航程已經提前幾個月計劃，有具體的到達日期。","word":"destined"}},"destiny":{"createdAt":1781693281408,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"destiny（命運）指的是被認為是預先決定或注定的未來事件，經常與宿命論的概念相關聯。","options":["choice","destiny","accident","reward"],"sentence":"Many people believe that their ______ is predetermined by fate. However, modern psychology suggests that our choices and actions shape our future more than any cosmic force.","translation":"許多人相信他們的命運是由命運預先決定的。然而，現代心理學表明我們的選擇和行動比任何宇宙力量更能塑造我們的未來。","word":"destiny"}},"destroy":{"createdAt":1782001211011,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"destroy 意思是完全破壞或毀壞某物。","options":["build","destroy","repair","renovate"],"sentence":"The hurricane ______ many buildings and roads in the coastal town last month. Reconstruction efforts are still ongoing to restore the damaged infrastructure and homes.","translation":"上月颶風摧毀了沿海城鎮的許多建築物和道路。重建工作仍在進行中，以恢復受損的基礎設施和房屋。","word":"destroy"}},"destruction":{"createdAt":1781345564013,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"destruction 是指大規模的破壞或毀滅，常用來描述戰爭、自然災害或重大災難造成的損害。","options":["creation","destruction","construction","production"],"sentence":"The hurricane caused massive ______ to the coastal city. Buildings were flattened, roads were torn apart, and thousands of people lost their homes.","translation":"颶風對沿海城市造成了大規模的毀滅。建築物被夷為平地，道路被摧毀，數千人失去了家園。","word":"destruction"}},"destructive":{"createdAt":1781774456601,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"destructive 形容造成破壞和傷害的事物，在此指颶風對環境的負面影響。","options":["constructive","positive","damaging","helpful"],"sentence":"The hurricane had a ______ impact on the coastal town, leaving devastation everywhere. Buildings were flattened and homes were destroyed.","translation":"颶風對沿海城鎮造成了毀滅性的影響，到處一片廢墟。建築物被夷為平地，房屋被摧毀。","word":"destructive"}},"detach":{"createdAt":1781967668672,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"detach 意指將某物分離或拆開，通常用於分離連接的物體。","options":["disconnect","detach","remove","extract"],"sentence":"You need to ______ the USB cable from the computer before moving it. The technician carefully separated the connector without damaging the port.","translation":"你需要從電腦上拆掉USB電纜才能移動它。技術人員小心地分離連接器而不損壞接口。","word":"detach"}},"detail":{"createdAt":1781429810250,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"detail是指事物的細微部分或具體的項目，強調精確和全面的信息。","options":["symbol","detail","objection","square"],"sentence":"The artist paid careful attention to every ______ in the painting, from the texture of the fabric to the expression in the eyes. Without these small elements, the work would lack its remarkable realism.","translation":"藝術家對繪畫中的每個細節都仔細關注，從布料的質地到眼睛的表情。沒有這些小元素，這件作品將缺乏其出色的現實感。","word":"detail"}},"detain":{"createdAt":1782001211002,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"detain 意思是暫時拘留或扣留某人，通常是出於調查或程序需要。","options":["release","detain","interview","arrest"],"sentence":"The police had to ______ the suspect for questioning about the robbery. They kept him at the station for several hours before releasing him without charges.","translation":"警察必須將嫌疑人留下來接受關於搶劫案的詢問。他們將他關在警察局幾個小時後才釋放他，沒有提出控罪。","word":"detain"}},"detect":{"createdAt":1781395310165,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"detect 表示發現、察覺到原本未被發現的事物，通常指通過工具或感官識別。","options":["ignore","detect","welcome","announce"],"sentence":"The security system failed to ______ the intruder until he was already inside the building. The alarm should have alerted guards the moment someone attempted to enter.","translation":"安全系統未能在入侵者進入建築物時發現他。警報應該在有人試圖進入的那一刻提醒警衛。","word":"detect"}},"detective":{"createdAt":1781274482547,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"detective指從事調查犯罪案件的執法人員，必須蒐集證據並破案。","options":["actor","detective","reporter","teacher"],"sentence":"The ______ spent months investigating the mysterious disappearance. She gathered evidence, interviewed witnesses, and finally solved the case.","translation":"那位偵探花了數月時間調查神秘失蹤案。她蒐集證據、詢問證人，最終破案了。","word":"detective"}},"detergent":{"createdAt":1782001211009,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"detergent 是一種清潔劑，通常用於洗衣或清潔家居。","options":["soap","detergent","perfume","shampoo"],"sentence":"I need to buy some ______ to wash these dirty clothes stained with mud. The product aisle in the supermarket has many brands available for different types of fabrics.","translation":"我需要買一些洗衣液來洗這些沾有泥土的髒衣服。超市的日用品走廊有很多適合不同布料的品牌。","word":"detergent"}},"determination":{"createdAt":1781626081097,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"determination 表示為了達成目標而堅持不懈的意志力和決心，常用於描述面對困難時不放棄的精神。","options":["confusion","determination","laziness","uncertainty"],"sentence":"She showed great ______ in pursuing her dream despite countless failures. Her unwavering commitment never wavered, even when others doubted her abilities.","translation":"儘管失敗無數次，她在追求夢想時展現了很大的堅定決心。她堅定不移的承諾從未動搖，即使其他人懷疑她的能力。","word":"determination"}},"determine":{"createdAt":1782001211013,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"determine 意思是做出決定或確定某事的結果。","options":["ignore","determine","suggest","wonder"],"sentence":"The jury had to ______ whether the defendant was guilty or innocent based on the evidence presented. Their verdict would significantly impact the future of the accused person.","translation":"陪審團必須根據呈交的證據確定被告是有罪還是無罪。他們的判決將對被告人的未來產生重大影響。","word":"determine"}},"determined":{"createdAt":1782009504013,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"下定決心的意思是有堅強的意志和決心去達成某個目標，不會輕易放棄或改變主意。","options":["hesitant","uncertain","determined","confused"],"sentence":"He was ______ to finish his degree despite working full-time and raising three children. His unwavering commitment to his goal inspired everyone around him to pursue their own dreams.","translation":"儘管要全職工作並撫養三個孩子，他仍下定決心完成學位。他堅定不移的承諾激勵了他周圍的每個人去追求自己的夢想。","word":"determined"}},"devastate":{"createdAt":1781967668681,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"devastate 指造成大規模破壞或蹂躪，表示極其嚴重的損害。","options":["damage","devastate","affect","impact"],"sentence":"The powerful hurricane will ______ the coastal regions if it makes landfall. The destructive winds and storm surge could destroy entire communities and cause massive damage.","translation":"如果強颶風登陸，它將摧毀沿海地區。破壞性的風和風暴潮可能會摧毀整個社區並造成巨大破壞。","word":"devastate"}},"devastated":{"createdAt":1781842419968,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"devastated形容極度悲傷、沮喪或遭受嚴重打擊的狀態；通常表示情感上的深度創傷而非輕微失望。","options":["disappointed","devastated","frustrated","annoyed"],"sentence":"She felt completely ______ when she learned that her beloved pet had passed away. The loss was so profound that she couldn't stop crying for days.","translation":"當她得知她心愛的寵物去世時，她感到完全摧毀。這個損失是如此深刻，以至於她好幾天都停不下來哭泣。","word":"devastated"}},"develop":{"createdAt":1781395310168,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"develop 表示逐步創造、改進或使某事物成長並達到成熟的狀態。","options":["destroy","abandon","develop","ignore"],"sentence":"The startup spent two years to ______ a revolutionary new smartphone application. The finished product received excellent reviews from technology critics and millions of downloads.","translation":"該初創公司花費兩年時間開發了一種革命性的新智慧手機應用程式。完成的產品獲得了科技評論家的好評和數百萬次下載。","word":"develop"}},"developing":{"createdAt":1781967668680,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"developing 指開發中的或發展中的，用於描述正在進步但尚未完全發達的國家或地區。","options":["poor","developing","struggling","emerging"],"sentence":"Many ______ countries are working hard to improve their infrastructure and education systems. These nations are gradually building modern facilities to support economic growth.","translation":"許多開發中的國家正在努力改善他們的基礎設施和教育系統。這些國家正在逐漸建設現代設施以支持經濟增長。","word":"developing"}},"development":{"createdAt":1782001211014,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"development 意思是逐步增進或改進的過程，通常指進步或成長。","options":["decline","development","regression","stagnation"],"sentence":"The ______ of artificial intelligence has changed how we live and work in recent years. Companies are investing billions of dollars into research and new technologies in this rapidly growing field.","translation":"人工智能的發展在近年來改變了我們的生活和工作方式。公司正在向這個快速增長領域的研究和新技術投入數十億美元。","word":"development"}},"devise":{"createdAt":1781424363982,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"devise 表示通過計畫和思考來創造或設計某個方案或方法，強調創意和設計的過程。","options":["execute","discover","devise","demand"],"sentence":"The engineers had to ______ a new plan to solve the bridge construction problem that appeared last week. After brainstorming for hours, they finally created a solution that satisfied all the safety requirements.","translation":"工程師們必須想出一個新計畫來解決上週出現的橋樑建築問題。經過數小時的腦力激盪後，他們終於創造出滿足所有安全要求的解決方案。","word":"devise"}},"devote":{"createdAt":1781484415228,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"devote意指將時間、精力或生命全力投入於某項事業或目標，表示真摯的承諾。","options":["waste","spend","devote","lose"],"sentence":"She decided to ______ her life to helping disadvantaged children in her community. For the next twenty years, she worked tirelessly at the local orphanage without expecting any reward.","translation":"她決定將她的人生奉獻給幫助社區中的弱勢兒童。在接下來的二十年裡，她在當地孤兒院不知疲倦地工作，沒有期待任何回報。","word":"devote"}},"devoted":{"createdAt":1782001211010,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"devoted 是形容詞，意思是全心投入或獻身於某事或某人。","options":["lazy","devoted","careless","hostile"],"sentence":"She was a ______ teacher who stayed late every day to help struggling students with their homework. Her commitment to her students' success never wavered despite the long hours and low salary.","translation":"她是一位獻身教育的老師，每天都待到很晚幫助學習困難的學生做功課。儘管工作時間長且薪酬低，她對學生成功的承諾從未動搖。","word":"devoted"}},"devotion":{"createdAt":1781967668678,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"devotion 指對某事或某人的深愛和奉獻，表示全身心投入。","options":["commitment","devotion","passion","interest"],"sentence":"Her ______ to charitable work has earned her numerous awards and recognition. For over thirty years, she has selflessly dedicated every moment to helping the poor.","translation":"她對慈善工作的奉獻獲得了許多獎項和認可。三十多年來，她一直無私地奉獻每一刻來幫助窮人。","word":"devotion"}},"diabetes":{"createdAt":1781967668682,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"diabetes 指糖尿病，一種影響血糖調節的代謝疾病，需要長期管理和治療。","options":["obesity","diabetes","hypertension","arthritis"],"sentence":"His uncle was diagnosed with ______ last year and has since changed his diet significantly. The doctor prescribed daily insulin injections to manage his blood sugar levels.","translation":"他的叔叔去年被診斷出患有糖尿病，從此改變了他的飲食習慣。醫生開了每日胰島素注射來控制他的血糖水平。","word":"diabetes"}},"diagnose":{"createdAt":1781283344046,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"diagnose意為確定或識別疾病；後面提到「檢查結果後確定」，表示通過檢驗得出診斷結論。","options":["cure","diagnose","prevent","treat"],"sentence":"The doctor ran several tests to ______ the patient's mysterious illness. After examining the blood work and imaging results, she determined it was a thyroid disorder.","translation":"醫生進行了幾項檢查來診斷患者神秘的疾病。檢查血液檢驗和影像檢查結果後，她確定這是甲狀腺疾病。","word":"diagnose"}},"dictate":{"createdAt":1781841742845,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dictate 作動詞表示「命令、規定」，指以權威方式強制執行特定的要求或決定。","options":["suggest","dictate","encourage","permit"],"sentence":"The strict teacher would ______ every detail of how students should complete their assignments. Students had no freedom to choose their own approach.","translation":"這位嚴格的教師會決定學生如何完成作業的每一個細節。學生沒有自由選擇自己方法的權利。","word":"dictate"}},"dictation":{"createdAt":1781967668676,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dictation 指口述或朗讀讓他人筆錄的做法，通常用於語言學習。","options":["lecture","dictation","presentation","speech"],"sentence":"During the English class, the teacher conducted a ______ exercise where students wrote down everything they heard. The students listened carefully and transcribed every word without seeing the text.","translation":"在英文課上，老師進行了一項口述練習，學生們寫下他們聽到的一切。學生們仔細聆聽並抄錄每個字而不看文本。","word":"dictation"}},"dictatorship":{"createdAt":1782001211012,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dictatorship 意思是由獨裁者統治的政體，特點是權力集中和個人自由受限。","options":["democracy","dictatorship","monarchy","republic"],"sentence":"The country lived under a brutal ______ for over thirty years before finally transitioning to democracy. Citizens suffered from severe restrictions on free speech and human rights during this dark period.","translation":"這個國家在獨裁統治下生活了三十多年，最後才過渡到民主制度。在這個黑暗時期，公民遭受了言論自由和人權的嚴重限制。","word":"dictatorship"}},"diesel":{"createdAt":1782009504007,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"柴油是一種石油產品，常用於卡車、公車和發電機等重型機械，燃油效率高且動力強勁。","options":["electric","diesel","hybrid","petrol"],"sentence":"The truck runs on ______ fuel, which is more efficient than gasoline for heavy vehicles. Many long-haul drivers prefer this type of engine because it provides better fuel economy and torque.","translation":"這輛卡車使用______燃料，對於重型車輛來說比汽油更有效率。許多長途司機更喜歡這種引擎，因為它提供更好的燃油經濟性和扭矩。","word":"diesel"}},"difficult":{"createdAt":1782001211014,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"difficult 是形容詞，表示某事很難做或很難理解。","options":["easy","difficult","simple","clear"],"sentence":"The ______ math problem required multiple steps and advanced knowledge to solve correctly. Even the top students in the class spent over an hour working through all the calculations.","translation":"這道困難的數學題需要多個步驟和進階知識才能正確求解。即使是班上的頂尖學生也花了一個多小時來完成所有計算。","word":"difficult"}},"digest":{"createdAt":1781696018689,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"digest 可作動詞表示消化或理解，指對信息進行深入思考和吸收的過程。","options":["memorize","ignore","digest","skim"],"sentence":"It took the student several weeks to ______ all the complex information from the economics textbook. Only after repeated reading and reflection could she truly understand the key concepts.","translation":"這位學生花了幾週時間才消化經濟學教科書中的所有複雜資訊。只有經過反覆閱讀和思考，她才能真正理解關鍵概念。","word":"digest"}},"digestion":{"createdAt":1781275226788,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"此處digestion指「消化」的過程，特別是食物在胃中的處理","options":["feast","stroke","digestion","dazzle"],"sentence":"After eating a large meal, his ______ was slow and uncomfortable. He felt bloated for hours because his stomach needed more time to process the food.","translation":"吃完一頓大餐後，他的消化很慢且不舒服。他感到腹脹持續數小時，因為他的胃需要更多時間來消化食物。","word":"digestion"}},"dignity":{"createdAt":1781886743286,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Dignity 指的是一個人內在的威嚴和尊嚴，代表自尊心和被尊重的應有權利。","options":["attitude","dignity","character","pride"],"sentence":"The elderly man maintained his ______ despite his difficult circumstances and health challenges. He refused to accept pity from others and insisted on living with respect and self-worth.","translation":"這位老人儘管處境困難和健康挑戰，仍保持著尊嚴。他拒絕接受他人的同情，堅持以尊重和自我價值來生活。","word":"dignity"}},"dilemma":{"createdAt":1781515329271,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dilemma 名詞，意思是困境、進退兩難，指必須在兩個或多個不理想的選擇中做出決定的困難處境。","options":["opportunity","dilemma","coincidence","agreement"],"sentence":"She faced a difficult ______ when both job offers required her to relocate to different cities. She had to choose between career advancement and staying close to her family.","translation":"當兩份工作都要求她搬遷到不同城市時，她面臨了一個困難的困境。她必須在職業發展和與家人親近之間做出選擇。","word":"dilemma"}},"diligent":{"createdAt":1781503378962,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"diligent 表示認真、刻苦、細致和持之以恆地從事工作或學習。","options":["lazy","careless","diligent","absent-minded"],"sentence":"The ______ student studied every evening without fail. She completed all her assignments on time and achieved the highest grades in the class.","translation":"這位勤奮的學生每晚都毫不間斷地學習。她按時完成所有作業，並取得班級中最高的成績。","word":"diligent"}},"dim":{"createdAt":1781886743284,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Dim 表示光線暗淡、不夠亮，通常是有意降低照明強度以達到特定效果。","options":["bright","dim","warm","soft"],"sentence":"The ______ light in the restaurant created a romantic atmosphere for couples dining together. The bulbs were deliberately turned down to make the space feel intimate and cozy.","translation":"餐廳裡昏暗的光線為一起用餐的情侶營造了浪漫的氛圍。燈泡被意圖調低亮度，使空間感到親密和舒適。","word":"dim"}},"dimension":{"createdAt":1781794866351,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dimension指尺寸、規模或面積，用來描述物體或空間的測量數據。","options":["colors","dimension","materials","purposes"],"sentence":"The architect had to consider multiple ______ when designing the new building. The length, width, and height all needed to fit within the constraints of the available land.","translation":"建築師在設計新建築時必須考慮多個______。長度、寬度和高度都需要符合可用土地的限制。","word":"dimension"}},"diminish":{"createdAt":1781886743286,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"Diminish 作為動詞，表示逐漸減小或減弱，強調一個漸進的過程而非突然消失。","options":["increase","disappear","diminish","echo"],"sentence":"The sound of the ambulance began to ______ as it drove further away from our location. Within minutes, we could barely hear the siren anymore because it was so far in the distance.","translation":"當救護車駛離我們的位置時，警笛聲開始減弱。幾分鐘內，我們幾乎聽不到警笛了，因為它距離太遠了。","word":"diminish"}},"dimly":{"createdAt":1781758494832,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dimly 用來形容光線微弱或模糊不清，與第二句中「光線非常微弱」相符。","options":["brightly","dimly","loudly","quickly"],"sentence":"The old lamp on the desk shone ______, casting shadows across the room. I could barely read the words on the page because the light was so faint.","translation":"桌子上的舊燈光線昏暗，在房間裡投下陰影。因為光線非常微弱，我幾乎無法讀清頁面上的文字。","word":"dimly"}},"dimple":{"createdAt":1781698273262,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"dimple 是名詞，表示「酒窩」，是皮膚上的小凹陷，通常在笑時變得更明顯。","options":["wrinkle","freckle","dimple","scar"],"sentence":"The baby's sweet smile revealed a tiny ______ on each cheek. These adorable facial features appeared whenever she laughed or grinned.","translation":"嬰兒甜蜜的笑容在每隻臉頰上露出一個小酒窩。每當她笑或咧嘴時，這些可愛的面部特徵就會出現。","word":"dimple"}},"dip":{"createdAt":1781311922070,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dip 表示短暫地將某物浸入液體中，通常是為了檢查或品嚐。","options":["drop","dip","throw","push"],"sentence":"Before eating the hot soup, I decided to ______ my spoon into it to test the temperature. The liquid was too hot, so I waited a few more minutes before starting my meal.","translation":"在吃熱湯之前，我決定把湯匙浸入其中來測試溫度。液體太熱了，所以我等了幾分鐘才開始用餐。","word":"dip"}},"diploma":{"createdAt":1781886743283,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Diploma 是指由教育機構頒發的學位證書，證明學生完成了課程並達到畢業要求。","options":["certificate","diploma","transcript","license"],"sentence":"After four years of studying engineering, Sarah finally received her ______ at graduation. The document certified that she had completed all required coursework and earned her degree.","translation":"在學習工程學四年後，莎拉終於在畢業典禮上獲得了文憑。這份文件證明她已完成所有必修課程並獲得了學位。","word":"diploma"}},"diplomacy":{"createdAt":1781886743285,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Diplomacy 指的是通過談判和協商解決國際事務的藝術和實踐，強調和平和妥協的方式。","options":["strategy","diplomacy","negotiation","protocol"],"sentence":"The two countries resolved their trade dispute through careful ______ rather than military conflict. Government representatives spent months negotiating and making compromises to reach a peaceful agreement.","translation":"兩國通過謹慎的外交而非軍事衝突來解決他們的貿易爭端。政府代表花費數月進行談判和妥協以達成和平協議。","word":"diplomacy"}},"diplomat":{"createdAt":1781774456602,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"diplomat 是指從事外交工作的人，負責代表國家進行談判和協商。","options":["soldier","journalist","ambassador","teacher"],"sentence":"The ______ skillfully negotiated between the two nations to reach a peace agreement. Her ability to communicate effectively resolved the conflict.","translation":"外交官在兩國之間巧妙協商以達成和平協議。她有效溝通的能力解決了衝突。","word":"diplomat"}},"diplomatic":{"createdAt":1781886743285,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Diplomatic 是形容詞，用來形容與外交相關的事物，特別是指外交官員和外交事務。","options":["corporate","diplomatic","political","governmental"],"sentence":"The ______ corps at the United Nations includes ambassadors and officials from nearly every country. These representatives work to maintain international relations and resolve disputes between nations.","translation":"聯合國的外交使團包括來自幾乎每個國家的大使和官員。這些代表致力於維護國際關係和解決國家之間的爭端。","word":"diplomatic"}},"direct":{"createdAt":1781564440933,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"direct 作動詞表示管理、指揮，指領導或控制他人的工作和方向。","options":["follow","direct","ignore","abandon"],"sentence":"The manager will ______ the project team to ensure it meets all deadlines and objectives. She will make important decisions and give clear instructions to all members.","translation":"經理將管理項目團隊以確保它達到所有截止日期和目標。她將做出重要決定並向所有成員發出明確指示。","word":"direct"}},"direction":{"createdAt":1781967668675,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"direction 指方向或指導，用來幫助人們知道往哪裡去或該如何做。","options":["location","distance","direction","route"],"sentence":"The GPS provided clear ______ for navigating through the unfamiliar city. Without these step-by-step instructions, we would have been completely lost.","translation":"GPS為在陌生城市中導航提供了明確的指導。沒有這些逐步指示，我們會完全迷路。","word":"direction"}},"directive":{"createdAt":1781967668681,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"directive 指正式的指令或命令，用於下達必須執行的具體要求。","options":["suggestion","directive","memo","notice"],"sentence":"The CEO issued a ______ requiring all employees to attend the mandatory safety training. The formal order outlined specific procedures that everyone must follow immediately.","translation":"首席執行官發布了一項指令，要求所有員工參加強制安全培訓。這個正式命令列出了每個人必須立即遵循的具體程序。","word":"directive"}},"directory":{"createdAt":1781967668677,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"directory 指名錄或簿冊，用來查找特定人物或機構的信息。","options":["database","directory","catalog","index"],"sentence":"I consulted the phone ______ to find the contact information for the local hospital. The book contained alphabetically organized names and phone numbers for thousands of businesses.","translation":"我查閱了電話簿找到當地醫院的聯絡資訊。這本書包含了數千個企業按字母順序組織的名字和電話號碼。","word":"directory"}},"disability":{"createdAt":1782009504012,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"殘疾或殘障是指身體或心智功能的受損，可能影響日常活動，但不代表一個人的能力或價值。","options":["advantage","disability","talent","skill"],"sentence":"She has a hearing ______ that requires her to use a special microphone during meetings. Despite this physical challenge, she has become one of the most successful engineers in her company.","translation":"她有聽力______，在開會時需要使用特殊麥克風。儘管有這個身體上的挑戰，她已成為公司最成功的工程師之一。","word":"disability"}},"disable":{"createdAt":1781848330183,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disable表示使人喪失能力或行動能力，通常指因傷病或其他原因導致功能受損。","options":["discourage","disable","disappoint","dislike"],"sentence":"The accident was severe enough to ______ him from ever playing professional sports again. The injury left him physically unable to perform at the level he once did.","translation":"這場意外嚴重到使他無法再參加職業體育比賽。這次受傷使他身體上無法以他曾經的水準表現。","word":"disable"}},"disabled":{"createdAt":1781967668679,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disabled 指使某人失去能力或傷殘，通常指身體或功能上的損害。","options":["injured","disabled","weakened","affected"],"sentence":"The accident ______ him permanently, leaving him unable to walk without assistance. Despite his physical limitations, he maintains a positive attitude and continues his studies.","translation":"這場事故使他永久傷殘，使他無法在沒有協助的情況下行走。儘管身體有限制，他保持積極態度並繼續他的學習。","word":"disabled"}},"disagree":{"createdAt":1781967668679,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disagree 指意見或看法不一致，用於描述不同的立場或觀點。","options":["discuss","disagree","debate","differ"],"sentence":"My brother and I often ______ about which movie to watch on weekends. This time, he wanted to see an action film while I preferred a romantic comedy.","translation":"我和我的哥哥經常在週末看哪部電影的問題上意見不合。這次他想看動作片，而我更喜歡浪漫喜劇。","word":"disagree"}},"disagreement":{"createdAt":1781967668678,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disagreement 指意見不合或看法分歧，用於描述兩方持不同立場的情況。","options":["confusion","disagreement","misunderstanding","difficulty"],"sentence":"The board members expressed strong ______ over the new budget proposal. Some wanted to increase spending while others insisted on cutting costs significantly.","translation":"董事會成員對新預算提案表達了強烈的意見不合。有些人想增加支出，而其他人堅持要大幅削減成本。","word":"disagreement"}},"disappear":{"createdAt":1781715397122,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disappear 意為「消失、不見」，強調事物完全不在視野中或不存在的狀態。","options":["reappear","disappear","escape","hide"],"sentence":"The magician made the rabbit ______ from the locked box in front of thousands of amazed spectators. When the audience opened the box after the trick was over, there was nothing inside.","translation":"魔術師在數千名驚訝的觀眾面前讓兔子從上鎖的盒子裡消失。當魔術結束後觀眾打開盒子時，裡面什麼都沒有。","word":"disappear"}},"disappearance":{"createdAt":1781429810254,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disappearance是指某人或某物突然消失或不見蹤影的狀態。","options":["temperature","disappearance","detail","firecracker"],"sentence":"The ______ of the ship in the ocean remains a mystery to this day, with no wreckage or survivors ever found. Investigators have spent decades trying to understand what happened.","translation":"這艘船在海洋中的消失至今仍然是一個謎，沒有發現任何殘骸或倖存者。調查人員已經花費了數十年試圖理解發生了什麼。","word":"disappearance"}},"disappoint":{"createdAt":1782009504014,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"使失望是指未能滿足某人的期望或希望，造成他人感到沮喪或受挫折。","options":["delight","satisfy","disappoint","impress"],"sentence":"The restaurant's poor service and cold food would ______ even the most patient customer. We had looked forward to celebrating our anniversary there for weeks, but we left feeling upset and regretful.","translation":"餐廳的服務不周和冷食物會______甚至最有耐心的顧客。我們期盼了幾周要在那裡慶祝周年紀念，但我們失望和後悔地離開了。","word":"disappoint"}},"disappointed":{"createdAt":1781693538704,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"disappointed 表示感到失望、沮喪或對某事未能如預期而感到難受。","options":["thrilled","relieved","disappointed","excited"],"sentence":"The team was ______ after losing the championship game in the final seconds. They had trained for months and believed they could win.","translation":"球隊在最後幾秒鐘輸掉冠軍賽後感到失望。他們訓練了好幾個月，相信他們能贏。","word":"disappointed"}},"disappointment":{"createdAt":1781967668681,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disappointment 指失望或掃興，用於描述期望未能實現時的負面情緒。","options":["sadness","disappointment","sorrow","regret"],"sentence":"She felt great ______ when her favorite team lost the championship game in overtime. The bitter result after such a hard-fought season left her heartbroken.","translation":"當她最喜歡的隊伍在加時賽中輸掉了冠軍賽時，她感到極大的失望。經過如此艱苦的賽季後，這個苦澀的結果使她心碎。","word":"disappointment"}},"disapprove":{"createdAt":1781835517793,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disapprove 意為反對或不贊成某事，通常表示對他人行為的負面態度。","options":["approve","disapprove","ignore","understand"],"sentence":"The parents strongly ______ of their son's decision to quit university. They expressed their objection at the family dinner last night.","translation":"這對父母強烈反對他們兒子退學的決定。他們在昨晚的家庭晚餐上表達了他們的反對意見。","word":"disapprove"}},"disaster":{"createdAt":1781451343288,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"災難是指突發的不幸事件，通常造成重大破壞、傷害或損失，需要緊急救援。","options":["blessing","disaster","festival","opportunity"],"sentence":"The hurricane was a terrible ______ that destroyed thousands of homes and displaced many families. The government declared a state of emergency and sent relief supplies to the affected region.","translation":"颶風是一場可怕的災難，摧毀了數千棟房屋並使許多家庭流離失所。政府宣布進入緊急狀態，並向受災地區派遣了救援物資。","word":"disaster"}},"disastrous":{"createdAt":1782009504011,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"災難性的意思是非常糟糕、造成嚴重負面後果的，通常用來形容計畫、事件或決定的失敗結果。","options":["successful","disastrous","neutral","profitable"],"sentence":"The company's marketing campaign was ______ and caused significant financial losses. The CEO apologized publicly after the strategy failed to reach any of its intended goals.","translation":"該公司的行銷活動是______性的，造成了重大的財務損失。該執行長在策略未能達成任何既定目標後公開道歉。","word":"disastrous"}},"discard":{"createdAt":1781835517791,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"discard 意為拋棄或丟掉某物，通常是因為它不再有用或不需要了。","options":["collect","discard","organize","display"],"sentence":"After the game ended, the player decided to ______ all the broken cards from his collection. He threw them into the trash bin because they were no longer usable.","translation":"遊戲結束後，這位玩家決定拋棄他收藏中所有破損的卡片。他把它們扔進垃圾桶，因為它們已經無法使用了。","word":"discard"}},"discharge":{"createdAt":1781798927511,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"discharge 在醫療語境中表示允許病人離開醫院或出院。","options":["admit","discharge","transfer","examine"],"sentence":"The hospital decided to ______ the patient after a successful surgery. The doctor signed the paperwork stating he was fully recovered and no longer needed medical care.","translation":"醫院決定在成功手術後將病人出院。醫生簽署了文件，說明他已完全康復，不再需要醫療照護。","word":"discharge"}},"disciple":{"createdAt":1781480360482,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disciple指的是跟隨某位導師或領袖並學習其教義的人，通常用來形容宗教領袖的追隨者。","options":["critics","apostles","enemies","merchants"],"sentence":"Jesus had twelve ______ who followed him and learned his teachings. These devoted followers traveled with him throughout his ministry and became leaders of the early Christian church.","translation":"耶穌有十二位門徒跟隨他並學習他的教導。這些忠誠的追隨者與他一起旅行，並成為早期基督教會的領導者。","word":"disciple"}},"discount":{"createdAt":1781425122880,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"discount 指價格上的減少或優惠，與節省金錢和購物這個脈絡相符。","options":["tournament","exhibition","discount","fiber"],"sentence":"The store is offering a special ______ on all winter clothing this week. Customers can save up to forty percent on their purchases.","translation":"這家店本週對所有冬季服裝提供特別折扣。顧客最多可以節省百分之四十的購物費用。","word":"discount"}},"discouragement":{"createdAt":1781871338567,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"discouragement表示失去信心和希望的沮喪感，與多次失敗和想要放棄相關。","options":["excitement","determination","dejection","curiosity"],"sentence":"After failing the exam three times, the student felt overwhelming ______ and nearly quit school. However, a supportive teacher helped restore his confidence and motivation to continue.","translation":"在三次考試失敗後，這名學生感到了壓倒性的氣餒，幾乎要放棄學業。然而，一位支持他的老師幫助恢復了他的信心和繼續學習的動力。","word":"discouragement"}},"discovery":{"createdAt":1781693295124,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"discovery 表示發現新的東西或知識，在此指科學上的新發現。","options":["loss","mistake","discovery","opinion"],"sentence":"The scientist's groundbreaking ______ of a new element changed the field of chemistry forever. Her research team published their findings in the most prestigious scientific journals worldwide.","translation":"這位科學家對新元素的突破性發現永遠改變了化學領域。她的研究團隊在世界上最著名的科學期刊上發表了他們的發現。","word":"discovery"}},"discreet":{"createdAt":1781425024017,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"discreet表示謹慎的、小心的、周密的，強調一個人能夠保守秘密且行為得當。","options":["loud","discreet","talkative","careless"],"sentence":"Maria was a ______ woman who never gossiped about her colleagues' personal lives. She kept all confidences to herself and carefully avoided spreading rumors around the office.","translation":"瑪麗亞是一個謹慎的女人，從不談論她同事的私人生活。她對所有秘密保密，小心避免在辦公室裡散播謠言。","word":"discreet"}},"discriminate":{"createdAt":1781746848182,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"discriminate 在此意為「辨別」或「區別」，表示分辨不同事物之間的差異。","options":["ignore","discriminate","combine","unite"],"sentence":"It's important to ______ between healthy competition and unfair business practices. The key difference lies in whether all competitors have equal opportunities.","translation":"區分健康競爭和不公平的商業行為是很重要的。關鍵區別在於所有競爭者是否都有平等的機會。","word":"discriminate"}},"discrimination":{"createdAt":1781256444519,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"discrimination在此指辨別力或區分能力，用於做出精明和公正的判斷。","options":["bias","discrimination","preference","favoritism"],"sentence":"The selection committee showed excellent ______ in choosing the scholarship winner by carefully evaluating each applicant's academic achievements and personal qualities. Their thoughtful assessment ensured the most deserving student received the award.","translation":"評選委員會在選擇獎學金得主時表現出卓越的辨別力，仔細評估了每位申請人的學術成就和個人素質。他們深思熟慮的評估確保了最值得的學生獲得了獎項。","word":"discrimination"}},"discussion":{"createdAt":1781651775062,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"discussion 指人們聚在一起交流意見、商談或討論某個主題的過程。","options":["childhood","alternative","discussion","frustrate"],"sentence":"The board held a lengthy ______ about the company's future direction. After hours of exchanging opinions and debating different viewpoints, they finally reached a decision.","translation":"董事會針對公司的未來方向進行了漫長的討論。經過數小時的意見交換和不同觀點的辯論後，他們最終做出了決定。","word":"discussion"}},"disguise":{"createdAt":1781424363981,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disguise 指的是為了隱瞞真實身份而穿著或改變外貌的行為或物品，重點在於欺騙他人。","options":["costume","disguise","uniform","decoration"],"sentence":"The spy wore a clever ______ to hide his true identity at the embassy party. Nobody recognized him because he looked completely different with the fake beard and glasses.","translation":"那位間諜穿著巧妙的偽裝來隱瞞他在大使館派對上的真實身份。沒有人認出他，因為他戴著假鬍子和眼鏡看起來完全不同。","word":"disguise"}},"disgust":{"createdAt":1781961466408,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"disgust 表示對某事物感到嫌惡、厭惡或反感，通常導致負面的反應或行動。","options":["curiosity","concern","disgust","surprise"],"sentence":"The health inspector felt a strong sense of ______ when she discovered the unsanitary conditions in the restaurant's kitchen. She immediately closed the establishment and filed a formal complaint with the health department.","translation":"衛生檢查員在發現餐廳廚房的不衛生狀況時感到強烈的厭惡。她立即關閉了該餐廳並向衛生部門提交了正式投訴。","word":"disgust"}},"dismay":{"createdAt":1781661288531,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dismay 是指感到失望、沮喪或灰心喪志的情感反應，通常是對於不好消息的負面情感","options":["delight","dismay","surprise","confusion"],"sentence":"To her great ______, Sarah discovered that her flight had been cancelled. She felt devastated and helpless as she stared at the airport departure board showing only red cancellation notices.","translation":"令莎拉極其沮喪的是，她發現她的航班被取消了。當她看著機場出發看板上全是紅色的取消通知時，她感到絕望和無助。","word":"dismay"}},"dispensable":{"createdAt":1781784283026,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"dispensable是形容詞，表示可有可無的、非必需的；句子中強調這些項目可以被移除而不會影響工作效率。","options":["irreplaceable","invaluable","dispensable","critical"],"sentence":"The manager decided that several items in the budget were ______ and could be cut without affecting productivity. Only the essential equipment and personnel would be retained in the restructuring.","translation":"經理決定預算中的幾項是______ 的，可以刪除而不會影響生產力。重組中只會保留必要的設備和人員。","word":"dispensable"}},"displacement":{"createdAt":1781452425261,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"displacement表示流離失所或被迫遷移，通常指人們由於戰爭、災難或其他原因被迫離開原居地。","options":["growth","prosperity","relocation","development"],"sentence":"The war caused widespread ______ as thousands of families were forced to flee their homes. International organizations worked to provide shelter and assistance to those affected.","translation":"戰爭造成了廣泛的流離失所，數千個家庭被迫逃離家園。國際組織努力為受影響的人提供庇護和援助。","word":"displacement"}},"display":{"createdAt":1781449095514,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"display意為展示或展覽，用來表示將某物公開展示或呈現給觀眾。","options":["hide","display","store","discard"],"sentence":"The museum will ______ the ancient artifacts in the new exhibition hall. Visitors will be able to see these historical treasures up close.","translation":"博物館將在新的展覽廳展示這些古代文物。遊客將能夠近距離看到這些歷史寶藏。","word":"display"}},"disposable":{"createdAt":1781283344049,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disposable意為可拋棄的、用完即丟的；與「減少洗碗時間」和「環境廢棄物問題」搭配，表示一次性使用的產品。","options":["ceramic","disposable","glass","metal"],"sentence":"The restaurant switched to ______ cups to reduce the time spent washing dishes after service. However, this decision raised concerns about environmental waste.","translation":"餐廳改用用完即丟的杯子來減少服務後洗碗的時間。然而，這個決定引起了對環境廢棄物的擔憂。","word":"disposable"}},"disposables":{"createdAt":1781403377827,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disposables 指的是可以拋棄或一次性使用的物品，通常用於描述餐具、包裝等日常消費品。","options":["permanent dishes","disposables","decorations","supplies"],"sentence":"The restaurant switched to ______ to reduce their environmental impact. They now use paper plates and plastic utensils that can be thrown away after each meal.","translation":"這家餐廳改用一次性用品來減少環境影響。他們現在使用紙盤和塑膠餐具，這些在每頓飯後都可以丟棄。","word":"disposables"}},"disposal":{"createdAt":1781283344053,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disposal意為處置、處理；與「環保法規」和「安全移除」搭配，表示按照規定處理有害物質的過程。","options":["storage","disposal","production","inventory"],"sentence":"The hazardous waste requires proper ______ according to environmental regulations and safety standards. The company hired a specialized firm to handle the removal process safely.","translation":"根據環保法規和安全標準，危險廢棄物需要妥善處理。公司聘請了一家專業公司來安全地處理移除過程。","word":"disposal"}},"disputable":{"createdAt":1781425024016,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disputable表示有爭議的、可以被質疑或辯論的，即不是所有人都同意的觀點。","options":["proven","disputable","obvious","certain"],"sentence":"The claim that climate change is entirely human-caused remains highly ______ among scientists. Some experts agree with it, while others present compelling counterarguments based on their research.","translation":"氣候變化完全由人類造成的說法在科學家中仍然有很大的爭議。有些專家同意，而其他人則根據他們的研究提出了令人信服的反駁。","word":"disputable"}},"dispute":{"createdAt":1781839703152,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"dispute指爭論或爭執，與disagreed over border territories and refused to negotiate（對邊界領土存在分歧並拒絕談判）完全相符。","options":["alliance","friendship","dispute","cooperation"],"sentence":"The ______ between the two neighbouring countries lasted for decades. They disagreed over border territories and refused to negotiate for years.","translation":"這兩個鄰國之間的爭執持續了數十年。他們在邊界領土上存在分歧，多年來拒絕談判。","word":"dispute"}},"dissolve":{"createdAt":1781738724026,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dissolve指的是固體物質在液體中融化並均勻混合，最終消失成為溶液的一部分。","options":["harden","dissolve","evaporate","crystallize"],"sentence":"When I added the sugar cube to my hot tea, it began to ______ instantly. Within seconds, the solid white cube had completely turned into liquid and mixed throughout the beverage.","translation":"當我把方糖加入熱茶時，它立即開始溶解。在幾秒鐘內，白色的固體方糖已經完全變成液體並混入飲料中。","word":"dissolve"}},"distinct":{"createdAt":1781272410979,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"distinct表示清楚可見的、易於辨別的，用來形容事物之間明顯的區別。","options":["similar","distinct","expensive","ancient"],"sentence":"The two paintings have ______ styles that make them easy to tell apart. Even a child can recognize the differences between them immediately.","translation":"這兩幅畫有明顯不同的風格，使人們很容易區分它們。即使是小孩也能立即認出它們之間的差異。","word":"distinct"}},"distinction":{"createdAt":1781871338563,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"distinction表示兩者之間的區別或差異，用於強調不同之處。","options":["similarity","connection","difference","relationship"],"sentence":"There is an important ______ between knowledge and wisdom that philosophers have debated for centuries. Knowledge is the accumulation of information, while wisdom is the proper application of that knowledge.","translation":"知識和智慧之間存在重要的區別，哲學家們已經爭論了幾個世紀。知識是信息的積累，而智慧是對該知識的正確應用。","word":"distinction"}},"distinctive":{"createdAt":1781619188937,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"distinctive 指獨特的、有辨識度的、與眾不同的特徵或特色。","options":["common","distinctive","ordinary","standard"],"sentence":"The brand's ______ logo was instantly recognizable to customers all over the world. No other company used the same design or color combination.","translation":"該品牌的獨特標誌在世界各地的客戶都能立即識別。沒有其他公司使用相同的設計或色彩組合。","word":"distinctive"}},"distinguished":{"createdAt":1781443653221,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"distinguished形容詞指的是傑出、著名或受人尊敬的，通常用來形容在某個領域有重大成就的人。","options":["mediocre","ordinary","distinguished","unknown"],"sentence":"Professor Chen was a ______ scholar who had published over one hundred research papers in prestigious journals. Her groundbreaking work in quantum physics earned her international recognition and numerous awards.","translation":"陳教授是一位卓越的學者，在著名期刊上發表了超過一百篇研究論文。她在量子物理學上的開創性工作為她贏得了國際認可和眾多獎項。","word":"distinguished"}},"distress":{"createdAt":1781849847408,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"distress表示憂慮、痛苦或受難，與「擔憂和沮喪」的線索相符。","options":["joy","distress","delight","excitement"],"sentence":"The news about the accident caused great ______ to the family members. They were extremely worried and upset for weeks afterward.","translation":"關於這場事故的消息給家庭成員造成了極大的痛苦。他們在隨後的幾周內極度擔憂和沮喪。","word":"distress"}},"distressed":{"createdAt":1781499075060,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"焦慮不安表示一個人因為擔心或害怕而感到痛苦和不安。","options":["calm","content","distressed","relieved"],"sentence":"The mother looked ______ when she couldn't find her young son at the amusement park. Security guards immediately helped search the crowd and reunite them within minutes.","translation":"當這位母親在遊樂園找不到她的小兒子時，她看起來焦慮不安。保安人員立即幫助搜尋人群，並在幾分鐘內將他們重新團聚。","word":"distressed"}},"distribution":{"createdAt":1781499075058,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"分發指將物品或物資按照計畫分配給多個人或地點。","options":["collection","distribution","storage","purchase"],"sentence":"The charity organized the ______ of food and blankets to homeless people throughout the city. Volunteers worked for weeks to ensure everyone in need received assistance.","translation":"慈善機構組織了向全市無家可歸者分發食物和毛毯。志願者花了幾週的時間確保每個需要幫助的人都得到協助。","word":"distribution"}},"disturb":{"createdAt":1781283344049,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disturb意為妨礙或打擾；與「保持音量低」和「輕輕移動」搭配，表示避免任何可能影響睡眠的動作。","options":["comfort","disturb","feed","bathe"],"sentence":"Please do not ______ the sleeping baby as she needs rest to recover from her fever. Keep the volume low and move quietly around the house.","translation":"請不要打擾睡著的寶寶，因為她需要休息來從發燒中恢復。保持音量低並在屋子裡輕輕移動。","word":"disturb"}},"disturbance":{"createdAt":1781362281723,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"disturbance表示打擾或干擾，指破壞安寧或正常秩序的行為。","options":["joy","disturbance","pleasure","comfort"],"sentence":"The loud noise from the construction site caused ______ to the neighbors. Residents complained about the constant interruption to their peace.","translation":"建築工地的噪音對鄰居造成了打擾。居民抱怨他們的寧靜受到了持續的干擾。","word":"disturbance"}},"diverse":{"createdAt":1781449095510,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"diverse意為多樣的、多變化的，用來形容具有多種差異或種類的事物。","options":["homogeneous","diverse","uniform","identical"],"sentence":"The city has a ______ population with people from many different countries and cultures. This multicultural environment enriches the community in many ways.","translation":"這座城市擁有來自許多不同國家和文化的多樣化人口。這個多元文化環境在許多方面豐富了社區。","word":"diverse"}},"diversify":{"createdAt":1781417610417,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"diversify是指使事物變得多樣化或涉足多個不同的領域以降低風險。","options":["consolidate","simplify","diversify","reduce"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ its product line by entering new markets. Instead of relying solely on electronics, they began producing clothing, furniture, and household goods.","translation":"公司決定通過進入新市場來使其產品線多樣化。他們不再只依賴電子產品，而是開始生產衣服、家具和家用商品。","word":"diversify"}},"diversion":{"createdAt":1781840030396,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"diversion 是名詞，表示繞行路線；在此句中特指因主路關閉而改變的臨時路線。","options":["shortcut","diversion","highway","intersection"],"sentence":"The main road was closed for construction, so the traffic was redirected on a ______ that took drivers through the countryside. This temporary route added thirty minutes to everyone's commute.","translation":"主要道路因施工而關閉，所以交通被重新定向到一條繞行路線，該路線引導駕駛人穿過鄉村。這條臨時路線為每個人的通勤增加了三十分鐘。","word":"diversion"}},"diversity":{"createdAt":1781479123533,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"diversity 指的是差異、多樣性，強調不同群體和觀點的存在和價值。","options":["uniformity","efficiency","diversity","stability"],"sentence":"The company's commitment to ______ meant hiring people from various ethnic backgrounds, religions, and cultures. The leadership believed that having employees with different perspectives would lead to better innovation and problem-solving.","translation":"公司對多樣性的承諾意味著聘請來自不同種族、宗教和文化背景的員工。領導層相信擁有具有不同觀點的員工會導致更好的創新和解決問題的能力。","word":"diversity"}},"divert":{"createdAt":1781832761713,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"divert 表示使改變方向、使轉向、改變用途，指改變某物原本的路徑或目的。","options":["stop","redirect","accelerate","monitor"],"sentence":"The police had to ______ traffic away from the accident scene to prevent congestion. Vehicles were redirected through alternate routes while emergency responders worked at the site.","translation":"警察不得不將交通改向以遠離事故現場以防止堵塞。在應急救援人員在現場工作時，車輛被改道通過替代路線。","word":"divert"}},"divide":{"createdAt":1781362281729,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"divide表示分開或分裂，指因為不同的意見或利益而導致分離或衝突。","options":["unite","divide","strengthen","develop"],"sentence":"The controversial issue will ______ the community into different groups. Citizens have strong opposing opinions about the proposed development project.","translation":"這個有爭議的問題將使社區分成不同的團體。市民對提議的發展項目有著強烈的相反意見。","word":"divide"}},"divine":{"createdAt":1781437435165,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"divine 可以表示極好的、美妙的、令人驚嘆的，用來形容非常優美或完美的事物。","options":["ordinary","divine","dark","cloudy"],"sentence":"The sunset was absolutely ______, with golden light spreading across the entire sky. Everyone stopped to admire its breathtaking and magnificent beauty.","translation":"日落絕對是美妙的，金色的光線遍佈整個天空。每個人都停下來欣賞它令人驚嘆的華麗美景。","word":"divine"}},"domestic":{"createdAt":1781515372607,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"domestic指國內的或本國的市場和事物","options":["persuasive","launch","domestic","force"],"sentence":"The ______ market in China has experienced significant growth over the past decade. Consumers within the country are increasingly purchasing locally-made products rather than imports.","translation":"過去十年來，中國的國內市場經歷了顯著增長。該國消費者越來越多地購買本地製造的產品，而不是進口商品。","word":"domestic"}},"doom":{"createdAt":1781709984197,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"doom 名詞表示必然的毀滅或死亡，通常暗示無法避免的不幸結局。","options":["danger","doom","risk","peril"],"sentence":"The captain sensed ______ as the ship encountered the massive storm at sea. Dark clouds and towering waves suggested that the vessel might not survive the night.","translation":"當船在海上遇到巨大風暴時，船長感到厄運即將來臨。烏雲和高聳的浪潮表明這艘船可能無法度過這個夜晚。","word":"doom"}},"doubtful":{"createdAt":1781653278520,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"doubtful是形容詞，表示可疑的或靠不住的，用於描述對某人或某事的信任或可靠性產生懷疑的狀態。","options":["confident","certain","doubtful","assured"],"sentence":"The manager felt ______ about hiring the candidate who had never worked in the industry before. The applicant's lack of relevant experience and contradictory references made the decision risky.","translation":"經理對聘用這位從未在該行業工作過的候選人感到______。申請人缺乏相關經驗和相互矛盾的推薦信使這個決定很危險。","word":"doubtful"}},"draft":{"createdAt":1781951900949,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"draft是初步或粗略的版本，通常需要進一步修改，而非最終成品。","options":["manuscript","draft","outline","summary"],"sentence":"The author wrote a rough ______ of her novel before submitting it to the publisher. She made many corrections and revisions before producing the final version.","translation":"作者在將小說提交給出版商之前先寫了一個粗略的草稿。在製作最終版本之前，她進行了許多修正和修改。","word":"draft"}},"drastic":{"createdAt":1781794866352,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"drastic指激烈的、猛烈的，用於形容急劇、極端或影響深遠的變化或行動。","options":["minor","gradual","drastic","theoretical"],"sentence":"The company made ______ changes to its operations after losing most of its customers. They completely restructured their management, eliminated entire departments, and relocated their headquarters overseas.","translation":"公司在失去大部分客戶後對其運營進行了______ 改變。他們完全重組了管理層、裁減了整個部門，並將總部遷往海外。","word":"drastic"}},"draught":{"createdAt":1781581925129,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"draught 作為名詞表示初步的草圖或草稿，通常用於建築、工程或設計領域。","options":["proposal","draught","contract","blueprint"],"sentence":"The architect showed us a ______ of the new building design before construction began. We could see the preliminary sketches with measurements and structural details marked on paper.","translation":"在施工開始前，建築師向我們展示了新建築設計的草圖。我們可以看到紙上標有測量值和結構細節的初步草圖。","word":"draught"}},"dressing":{"createdAt":1781850347304,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"佐料或調料是指添加到食物中以增強風味的液體或半液體混合物。","options":["sauce","dressing","syrup","seasoning"],"sentence":"She poured the creamy ______ over her salad to add flavor and moisture. The vinaigrette combined olive oil, lemon juice, and herbs in the perfect balance.","translation":"她將奶油佐料倒在沙拉上以增加風味和濕潤度。這種油醋汁將橄欖油、檸檬汁和草本植物完美地結合在一起。","word":"dressing"}},"dressy":{"createdAt":1781848330184,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dressy形容穿著得體、講究、正式的，適合在特殊場合或正式場合穿著。","options":["casual","dressy","sporty","plain"],"sentence":"She wore a ______ outfit to the formal evening gala. Her elegant gown and fancy accessories showed she had taken great care with her appearance for this important occasion.","translation":"她穿著精緻講究的服裝出席正式晚宴。她優雅的禮服和華麗的配飾表明她為這個重要場合精心打扮。","word":"dressy"}},"drift":{"createdAt":1781836375377,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"drift表示漂流或漂動，指在水或空氣中被自然力量緩慢移動。","options":["sail","drift","float","move"],"sentence":"The damaged boat began to ______ helplessly across the ocean without power. The currents carried it further away from the shipping lanes.","translation":"受損的船開始在沒有動力的情況下無助地漂過海洋。洋流把它帶得離航道越來越遠。","word":"drift"}},"drown":{"createdAt":1781345564015,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"drown 表示在水中溺水身亡或被水淹沒，通常描述危險或致命的水上事故。","options":["float","drown","swim","paddle"],"sentence":"The man began to ______ in the deep ocean as the waves pulled him under. Lifeguards immediately dove in and rescued him before it was too late.","translation":"當海浪把他拖入水下時，這名男子開始在深海中溺水。救生員立即跳入水中，在為時已晚之前救了他。","word":"drown"}},"drowsy":{"createdAt":1781310338174,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"drowsy 表示困倦、昏昏欲睡的狀態，通常是因為疲勞或缺乏睡眠。","options":["alert","drowsy","energetic","anxious"],"sentence":"After working the night shift, the security guard felt increasingly ______ as morning approached. He struggled to keep his eyes open and had difficulty concentrating on his duties.","translation":"在上完夜班後，隨著早晨的臨近，保安感到越來越昏昏欲睡。他很難睜開眼睛，在執行職務時難以集中注意力。","word":"drowsy"}},"drunk":{"createdAt":1781362281651,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"drunk是drink的過去分詞，表示已經喝下去，也可作形容詞表示醉酒的狀態。","options":["eaten","drunk","spent","bought"],"sentence":"He had ______ too much wine at the party and could barely stand. His stumbling walk and slurred speech made it clear he was intoxicated.","translation":"他在派對上喝了太多葡萄酒，幾乎站不住。他踉蹌的步態和含糊的言語清楚地表明他醉了。","word":"drunk"}},"dual":{"createdAt":1781619188932,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dual 指具有兩個部分或兩重性質的，表示同時具有兩個目的或功能。","options":["single","dual","multiple","triple"],"sentence":"The ______ purpose of the conference was to discuss policy changes and network with industry leaders. Attendees would gain both educational content and valuable professional connections.","translation":"這次會議的雙重目的是討論政策變化並與行業領袖建立聯繫。與會者將獲得教育內容和寶貴的專業人脈。","word":"dual"}},"dubious":{"createdAt":1781359980245,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dubious指令人懷疑、可疑或值得懷疑的；表示對某事的真實性或可信度持懷疑態度。","options":["reliable","dubious","popular","expensive"],"sentence":"The ______ claim that the product could cure all diseases within days raised serious concerns among health officials. Independent testing found no scientific support for these extraordinary promises.","translation":"該產品能在幾天內治癒所有疾病的可疑說法引起了衛生官員的嚴重關注。獨立測試發現這些非凡承諾沒有科學支持。","word":"dubious"}},"dull":{"createdAt":1781595752114,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"dull 形容某事物缺乏趣味或令人感到無聊。","options":["interesting","exciting","dull","educational"],"sentence":"The lecture was so ______ that half the students fell asleep. The professor spoke in a monotone voice without any enthusiasm or engaging examples.","translation":"講座是如此乏味，以至於一半的學生睡著了。教授用單調的聲音講話，沒有任何熱情或引人入勝的例子。","word":"dull"}},"dump":{"createdAt":1781275226790,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"此處dump作動詞表示「傾倒；丟棄」，指將廢棄物放在特定地點","options":["stroke","dazzle","dump","feast"],"sentence":"The construction company had to ______ tons of waste material at the designated site. The environmental regulations required them to dispose of it properly and legally.","translation":"建築公司必須在指定地點傾倒數噸的廢料。環保法規要求他們合法地妥善處理它。","word":"dump"}},"duration":{"createdAt":1781746685498,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"duration指的是持續時間、時間長度，用來表示某事物從開始到結束所花費的時間。","options":["duration","medal","section","entertain"],"sentence":"The film's ______ was two hours and thirty minutes. Audiences had to remain seated throughout the entire showing without interruption.","translation":"這部電影的持續時間是兩小時三十分鐘。觀眾必須始終坐著觀看，不能中途中斷。","word":"duration"}},"dusk":{"createdAt":1781965320893,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"dusk 指的是日落時刻，介於白天和夜間之間的時段。","options":["midnight","noon","dawn","dusk"],"sentence":"The park is closed at ______, just after the sun has set below the horizon. Visitors must leave before darkness falls completely.","translation":"公園在黃昏時關閉，就在太陽落到地平線以下之後。訪客必須在天色完全變黑前離開。","word":"dusk"}},"duty":{"createdAt":1781836375372,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"duty表示責任或義務，通常指由職位或地位要求的重要責任。","options":["job","duty","work","task"],"sentence":"As a police officer, protecting the community is her primary ______. She takes this ______ seriously and works diligently every day.","translation":"作為警察，保護社區是她的主要責任。她認真對待這項責任，每天都勤奮工作。","word":"duty"}},"dynasty":{"createdAt":1781484415235,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"dynasty是指由同一家族統治的政治權力時期，代表某個皇室的統治年代。","options":["country","dynasty","revolution","century"],"sentence":"The Ming ______ ruled China for nearly three hundred years and produced magnificent architecture. This period saw the construction of the Forbidden City and the Great Wall expansions.","translation":"明朝統治中國近三百年，並產生了宏偉的建築。這個時期見證了紫禁城和長城擴建的建造。","word":"dynasty"}},"eager":{"createdAt":1781582939255,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"eager 形容對某事充滿熱情和期待的心理狀態，與積極主動和提前準備的行為相符。","options":["tired","eager","confused","absent"],"sentence":"The ______ students raised their hands immediately when the teacher asked who wanted to volunteer for the science fair. They had been looking forward to this opportunity for weeks and had already started preparing their projects at home.","translation":"當老師問誰想參加科學展覽時，那些熱切的學生立即舉起手。他們已經期待這個機會好幾週，並已在家開始準備他們的項目。","word":"eager"}},"earnest":{"createdAt":1781484415154,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"earnest意指認真、誠摯和熱心，表現出真正的決心和承諾。","options":["lazy","earnest","careless","reluctant"],"sentence":"She made an ______ effort to improve her grades before the final exam. Her determination was so genuine that she studied every single day without missing once.","translation":"她在期末考試前做出了誠摯的努力來改進她的成績。她的決心是如此真誠，以至於她每天都堅持學習，沒有缺過一次。","word":"earnest"}},"ecology":{"createdAt":1781625891345,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"ecology是研究生物與其環境和其他生物之間相互關係的學科","options":["architecture","psychology","ecology","astronomy"],"sentence":"The university offers a specialized degree program in ______. Students study how organisms interact with their environment and each other.","translation":"這所大學提供生態學專業學位課程。學生們研究生物如何與它們的環境和彼此互動。","word":"ecology"}},"economical":{"createdAt":1781425737124,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"economical 形容詞指節儉的、節約的或成本效益高的，與低燃油和維護成本相關。","options":["expensive","economical","luxurious","heavy"],"sentence":"She bought an ______ car model that uses less fuel and costs less to maintain. The vehicle's low operating expenses make it perfect for her tight monthly budget.","translation":"她購買了一輛節能車型，耗油量少，維護成本也較低。這輛車的低運營費用非常適合她緊張的月度預算。","word":"economical"}},"economics":{"createdAt":1781425737125,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"economics 是經濟學，研究市場、商業、供應和需求等經濟現象的學科。","options":["art","biology","economics","literature"],"sentence":"She decided to major in ______ to understand how markets and businesses operate globally. Her university professors teach theories about supply, demand, and international trade systems.","translation":"她決定主修經濟學以理解市場和企業如何在全球運營。她的大學教授教授關於供應、需求和國際貿易系統的理論。","word":"economics"}},"economy":{"createdAt":1781564440925,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"economy 表示經濟，指一個國家或地區的生產、貿易和財政活動的整體系統。","options":["culture","economy","geography","military"],"sentence":"The country's ______ has been growing steadily over the past decade. The increased production and trade have brought prosperity to many citizens.","translation":"該國的經濟在過去十年裡穩步增長。生產和貿易的增加為許多公民帶來了繁榮。","word":"economy"}},"edge":{"createdAt":1781434900585,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"edge在此表示「優勢」，指相對於他人的有利位置或條件。","options":["boundary","edge","corner","margin"],"sentence":"The company gained a competitive ______ over its rivals by developing innovative technology. This advantage allowed them to capture more market share than their competitors.","translation":"該公司通過開發創新技術獲得了相對於競爭對手的競爭優勢。這種優勢使他們能夠比競爭對手獲得更多的市場份額。","word":"edge"}},"editorial":{"createdAt":1781871338556,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"editorial指社論或編輯文章，代表報紙編輯部的正式觀點。","options":["sports","advertisement","opinion","weather"],"sentence":"The newspaper's ______ section features the opinions of the chief editor on current political issues. This column is published every Monday without fail.","translation":"報紙的社論欄目刊登編輯對當前政治問題的看法。這專欄每個星期一都準時發表。","word":"editorial"}},"editorials":{"createdAt":1781746685502,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"editorials指的是社論、編者按語，是報刊雜誌中編輯或評論員發表的評論文章。","options":["medal","editorials","moisture","obedience"],"sentence":"The newspaper published several ______ about the new government policy. The writers expressed their professional opinions and analysis on the controversial legislation.","translation":"報紙發表了幾篇關於新政府政策的社論。撰稿人表達了對這項有爭議立法的專業意見和分析。","word":"editorials"}},"effective":{"createdAt":1781661288528,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"effective 是指能達到預期效果的、有效的，用來形容某件事物是否成功地實現了目標","options":["efficient","popular","effective","expensive"],"sentence":"The new marketing campaign was not ______ at reaching younger audiences. Despite spending months on it, the company saw no increase in sales from that demographic.","translation":"新的行銷活動在接觸年輕觀眾方面並不有效。儘管花了幾個月的時間，該公司在這個年齡段的銷售額沒有增加。","word":"effective"}},"efficiency":{"createdAt":1781841148116,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"efficiency 名詞意思是效率、功效，指以最少的時間、能量或資源完成任務的能力。","options":["cost","efficiency","quality","safety"],"sentence":"The factory improved its production ______ by introducing automated machinery and streamlined workflows. Workers completed the same amount of work in half the time with fewer resources.","translation":"工廠通過引入自動化機械和簡化的工作流程提高了生產效率。工人用更少的資源在一半的時間內完成了相同數量的工作。","word":"efficiency"}},"elastic":{"createdAt":1781427134900,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"elastic在此指具有靈活性和適應性，能夠根據情況進行調整。","options":["strict","elastic","permanent","mandatory"],"sentence":"The company's work schedule is quite ______, allowing employees to adjust their hours based on personal needs. Workers can come in early or stay late depending on their family commitments.","translation":"公司的工作時間表相當靈活，允許員工根據個人需求調整他們的工作時間。員工可以根據家庭承諾提早上班或延遲下班。","word":"elastic"}},"election":{"createdAt":1781481124691,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"election 是指通過投票程序選擇公職人員的正式過程。","options":["debate","census","poll","vote"],"sentence":"The citizens participated in the ______ to choose their new representative. Voting booths were set up across the city, and millions of people cast their ballots.","translation":"公民參與了選舉以選擇他們的新代表。投票站在全市各地設立，數百萬人投了他們的票。","word":"election"}},"electrician":{"createdAt":1781598671096,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"electrician 作名詞表示電工或電氣技師，是專門從事電氣維修和安裝的技術人員","options":["plumber","electrician","carpenter","painter"],"sentence":"The ______ quickly diagnosed the electrical problem in the building and fixed the wiring. The power was restored within two hours of his arrival.","translation":"電工迅速診斷了建築物中的電氣問題並修復了佈線。他到達後兩小時內電力已恢復。","word":"electrician"}},"element":{"createdAt":1781583174626,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"element是指組成某物的基本成分或要素，對整體具有重要作用","options":["enemy","audience","element","problem"],"sentence":"Humor is an essential ______ of a good comedy film. Without it, the movie would fail to entertain audiences or make them laugh.","translation":"幽默是優秀喜劇電影的必要____。沒有它，這部電影將無法娛樂觀眾或使他們發笑。","word":"element"}},"eligible":{"createdAt":1781621431914,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"eligible 表示符合某些要求或條件，有資格參與或獲得某物。在此句中，強調申請人必須滿足特定的學歷要求才能有資格申請。","options":["qualified","eligible","interested","prepared"],"sentence":"To apply for this scholarship, you must be ______ to compete with other university students. Since you haven't finished high school yet, you cannot submit your application this year.","translation":"要申請這項獎學金，你必須有資格與其他大學生競爭。由於你還沒有完成高中學業，你今年無法提交申請。","word":"eligible"}},"eligibly":{"createdAt":1782016805977,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"eligibly 是副詞，表示以符合資格或合適的方式進行某事。","options":["ineligibly","eligibly","reluctantly","temporarily"],"sentence":"She met all the requirements and could ______ apply for the scholarship program. The selection committee confirmed that her academic record and test scores satisfied every criterion.","translation":"她滿足了所有要求，可以合適地申請獎學金計畫。選拔委員會確認她的學術記錄和考試成績滿足了每一項標準。","word":"eligibly"}},"embark":{"createdAt":1781434900596,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"embark指開始一次旅程或冒險，特別是通常涉及上船。","options":["abandon","embark","return","delay"],"sentence":"The explorers prepared to ______ on their dangerous expedition to the Arctic. They boarded their ship with supplies for a two-year journey.","translation":"探險家們準備開始他們危險的北極遠征。他們帶著兩年旅程的物資登上了他們的船。","word":"embark"}},"embrace":{"createdAt":1782016805983,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"embrace 是動詞，表示接受、擁抱或熱情地採納某事物或某種想法。","options":["reject","avoid","embrace","question"],"sentence":"The university decided to ______ the new digital learning platform for all its courses. Faculty members across all departments have integrated the technology into their classrooms.","translation":"該大學決定在所有課程中採納新的數位學習平台。各個部門的教職員工已將該技術整合到他們的課堂中。","word":"embrace"}},"emerge":{"createdAt":1781437013467,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"emerge 意為浮現或出現，通常用於某人或某事物逐漸變得知名或受到關注的情況。","options":["disappear","emerge","decline","retreat"],"sentence":"After years of obscurity, the talented musician finally began to ______ on the international stage. Critics praised her performances at major concert halls across Europe and America.","translation":"經過多年的默默無聞後，這位才華橫溢的音樂家終於開始在國際舞台上浮現。歐洲和美洲主要音樂廳的評論家都稱讚了她的表演。","word":"emerge"}},"emergency":{"createdAt":1781693265625,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"緊急情況指需要迅速處理和應對的意外事件或危機。","options":["birthday","emergency","vacation","training"],"sentence":"During the fire alarm, staff immediately activated the ______ response plan. The procedure included evacuation routes and assembly points for all employees.","translation":"火警警報期間，員工立即啟動緊急應變計畫。該程序包括所有員工的疏散路線和集合點。","word":"emergency"}},"emigration":{"createdAt":1781507137217,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"emigration 指的是人民從自己的國家移出或遷往他國，強調離開祖國的行為。","options":["immigration","emigration","celebration","exploration"],"sentence":"The country experienced massive ______ during the economic crisis of the 1980s. Millions of citizens left their homeland to seek better opportunities abroad.","translation":"這個國家在1980年代的經濟危機期間經歷了大規模的移居。數百萬公民離開他們的祖國去尋求海外的更好機會。","word":"emigration"}},"emission":{"createdAt":1781425094903,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"emission 指物質（特別是氣體、光或熱）被排放或散發出來的行為或結果。","options":["absorption","absorption","discharge","collection"],"sentence":"The factory's toxic gas ______ violated environmental regulations and threatened the health of nearby residents. Local officials demanded immediate action to reduce the release of pollutants into the atmosphere.","translation":"工廠的有毒氣體排放違反了環境法規，威脅了附近居民的健康。地方當局要求立即採取行動減少向大氣中排放的污染物。","word":"emission"}},"emotion":{"createdAt":1781424356418,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"emotion指的是人所經歷的強烈而主觀的感受或心理反應，如喜悅、悲傷或憤怒。","options":["schedule","emotion","decision","expense"],"sentence":"She struggled to control her ______ when she received the news of her promotion. Tears of joy streamed down her face as she felt overwhelming happiness and gratitude.","translation":"當她收到晉升的消息時，她努力控制自己的情感。當她感到莫大的喜悅和感激時，淚水從她的臉上流下。","word":"emotion"}},"emotional":{"createdAt":1781566055841,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"emotional 用來形容受到強烈感受或情感影響的狀態，通常伴隨著對事物的情感反應。","options":["logical","emotional","physical","practical"],"sentence":"After hearing the sad news, she became very ______ and couldn't stop crying. Her reaction showed how deeply the loss had affected her feelings.","translation":"聽到悲傷的消息後，她變得非常情緒化，無法停止哭泣。她的反應表明這個損失對她的感受有多深遠的影響。","word":"emotional"}},"empathy":{"createdAt":1781693538703,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"empathy 指的是能夠理解和感受他人的情感和處境的能力。","options":["ignorance","empathy","criticism","skepticism"],"sentence":"The counselor showed great ______ when listening to the patient's difficult life story. She understood their pain and offered genuine support rather than judgment.","translation":"諮詢師在聽患者困難的人生故事時表現出了極大的同理心。她理解他們的痛苦，並提供真誠的支持而不是批評。","word":"empathy"}},"emperor":{"createdAt":1781566185159,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"emperor指的是一個國家或帝國的最高統治者，擁有絕對的權力和權威。","options":["servant","emperor","merchant","scholar"],"sentence":"The ______ ruled over a vast empire for fifty years. He made all the major political decisions and was considered the supreme leader of the entire nation.","translation":"那位皇帝統治了一個遼闊的帝國五十年。他做出了所有重大的政治決定，被認為是整個國家的最高統治者。","word":"emperor"}},"emphasis":{"createdAt":1781832478022,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"emphasis 意為「強調」或「著重」，用來表示對某事特別重視和突出強調。","options":["doubt","emphasis","criticism","confusion"],"sentence":"The teacher placed strong ______ on the importance of studying for the final exam. She repeated several times that this test would determine our final grade.","translation":"老師強調了期末考試的重要性。她多次重複說這次考試將決定我們的最終成績。","word":"emphasis"}},"empirical":{"createdAt":1781359980239,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"empirical指基於實驗觀察和實際數據而非理論的；強調通過親身經驗或實驗驗證的方式獲得的知識。","options":["theoretical","empirical","hypothetical","abstract"],"sentence":"The scientist's ______ evidence was based on carefully controlled experiments and measurements. She collected data over five years rather than relying on theories or assumptions.","translation":"科學家的經驗證據是基於仔細控制的實驗和測量。她用了五年時間蒐集資料，而不是依賴理論或假設。","word":"empirical"}},"encounter":{"createdAt":1781749177481,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"encounter 表示意外地或突然地面對某人或某事，這裡特別強調了非預期的相遇。","options":["avoid","meet","follow","escape"],"sentence":"During my hike, I unexpectedly ______ a bear on the trail. The animal was blocking my path, so I had to carefully back away.","translation":"在我的登山途中，我在小徑上出乎意料地遇到了一隻熊。那隻動物擋住了我的路，所以我必須小心地往回走。","word":"encounter"}},"endanger":{"createdAt":1781798927527,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"endanger 表示使某人或某物處於危險或風險中，可能造成傷害或損失。","options":["protect","endanger","educate","celebrate"],"sentence":"Reckless driving on the highway can ______ the lives of innocent passengers and pedestrians. Statistics show that speeding and ignoring traffic signals cause thousands of accidents annually.","translation":"在高速公路上魯莽駕駛會危及無辜乘客和行人的生命。統計數據顯示，超速和無視交通信號每年導致數千起事故。","word":"endanger"}},"endangered":{"createdAt":1781961517452,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"endangered 表示物種面臨滅絕的危險，強調物種已經進入危急狀態。","options":["rare","endangered","protected","threatened"],"sentence":"The giant panda was once considered an ______ species on the brink of extinction. Thanks to conservation efforts, its population has gradually increased over the past decade.","translation":"大熊貓曾經被認為是瀕臨滅絕的物種。由於保護措施，其數量在過去十年裡逐漸增加。","word":"endangered"}},"endeavor":{"createdAt":1781884659834,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"endeavor 表示為達成目標而持續努力和嘗試，與二十年的堅持不懈相呼應。","options":["struggle","endeavor","hesitate","retreat"],"sentence":"Despite facing countless obstacles, the scientist continued to ______ toward finding a cure for the disease. Her persistent determination finally led to a breakthrough after twenty years.","translation":"儘管面臨無數障礙，這位科學家繼續努力尋找這種疾病的治療方法。她的堅持決心在二十年後終於取得了突破。","word":"endeavor"}},"endorse":{"createdAt":1781621431920,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"endorse 意為公開支持、贊同或認可某個人、產品或想法，通常涉及將個人信譽借予該對象以增加其可信度。","options":["promote","endorse","produce","purchase"],"sentence":"The famous athlete decided to ______ the new sports drink by appearing in its advertisements. His signature and public approval helped boost sales significantly because many fans trust his opinion.","translation":"這位著名運動員決定透過在廣告中現身來贊同這款新運動飲料。他的簽名和公開認可幫助銷售額大幅增長，因為許多粉絲信任他的意見。","word":"endorse"}},"endorsement":{"createdAt":1782018712117,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「endorsement」指對某人或某事的公開支持、贊同或認可，常用於商業和政治領域。","options":["criticism","ignorance","endorsement","rejection"],"sentence":"The celebrity's ______ of the new product helped boost its sales significantly. Without her public approval and backing, the campaign would have failed.","translation":"名人對這個新產品的贊同幫助大幅提升了銷售量。如果沒有她的公開認可和支持，這個活動就會失敗。","word":"endorsement"}},"engage":{"createdAt":1781709890957,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"engage作為動詞表示參與、從事或投入某項活動，通常暗示積極主動的參與。","options":["engage","hazard","hesitation","obsession"],"sentence":"The two competitors decided to ______ in a friendly debate about the best strategies for sustainable development. After hours of discussing different perspectives, both sides gained valuable insights from each other.","translation":"這兩位競爭者決定參與一場關於永續發展最佳策略的友誼辯論。在經過數小時討論不同觀點後，雙方都從彼此身上獲得了寶貴的見解。","word":"engage"}},"engaged":{"createdAt":1781485266371,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"engaged在此表示「正在從事某事」或「忙於」，表示某人目前正被某項活動佔據。","options":["married","disengaged","engaged","betrothed"],"sentence":"She was ______ in an intense phone conversation when I arrived at her office. She held up one finger to signal she would be free in just a few minutes.","translation":"我到達她辦公室時，她正忙於一通激烈的電話交談。她舉起一根手指示意幾分鐘後就能空出時間。","word":"engaged"}},"engine":{"createdAt":1781749177488,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"engine 是指機器或車輛的動力裝置，會因冷卻系統問題而過熱。","options":["tire","battery","motor","transmission"],"sentence":"The mechanic discovered that the car's ______ was overheating due to a faulty cooling system. He immediately replaced the damaged radiator to prevent permanent damage.","translation":"機械師發現汽車的引擎因冷卻系統故障而過熱。他立即更換了損壞的散熱器以防止永久性損傷。","word":"engine"}},"engineer":{"createdAt":1781598671072,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"engineer 作名詞表示工程師，是設計和建造結構或機械的專業人士","options":["architect","engineer","contractor","inspector"],"sentence":"The senior ______ designed a revolutionary bridge that could withstand earthquakes. Her innovative structural solutions have been adopted by engineering firms worldwide.","translation":"這位資深工程師設計了一座能抵抗地震的革命性橋樑。她的創新結構解決方案已被世界各地的工程公司採用。","word":"engineer"}},"enhance":{"createdAt":1781583174626,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"enhance是指改進或增強某物的品質、價值或效果，使其變得更好","options":["reduce","enhance","maintain","spoil"],"sentence":"Adding fresh herbs will ______ the flavor of your soup significantly. The taste will become more complex and delicious compared to the original recipe.","translation":"添加新鮮香草將大幅____您湯的風味。與原始食譜相比，味道會變得更加複雜和美味。","word":"enhance"}},"enlighten":{"createdAt":1781323901187,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"enlighten意為「啟迪」或「開導」，表示通過提供信息和知識來消除他人的誤解。","options":["confuse","mislead","enlighten","deceive"],"sentence":"The teacher's lecture helped ______ students about the true causes of climate change. By presenting scientific evidence and data, she cleared up many misconceptions they had held.","translation":"老師的講座幫助開導學生了解氣候變化的真正原因。通過呈現科學證據和數據，她消除了他們持有的許多誤解。","word":"enlighten"}},"enormously":{"createdAt":1781564440926,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"enormously 作副詞表示巨大地、極大地，用來修飾動詞或形容詞以強調程度。","options":["slightly","enormously","modestly","gradually"],"sentence":"The technology industry has grown ______ in the last twenty years. The sector now employs millions of people and generates trillions of dollars in revenue worldwide.","translation":"技術產業在過去二十年裡巨幅增長。該部門現在僱用了數百萬人，在全球創造了數万億美元的收入。","word":"enormously"}},"enrollment":{"createdAt":1781427134891,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"enrollment是指註冊入學的人數或過程，與申請新學生直接相關。","options":["graduation","enrollment","tuition","curriculum"],"sentence":"The university's ______ numbers increased by 30% this year. The admissions office had to hire additional staff to process all the new student applications.","translation":"這所大學的登記人數今年增加了30%。招生辦公室不得不雇用額外的工作人員來處理所有新學生的申請。","word":"enrollment"}},"ensure":{"createdAt":1781362281665,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ensure表示擔保或確保某事肯定會發生，強調保證和確定性。","options":["ignore","ensure","question","dispute"],"sentence":"The safety inspectors will ______ that the building meets all building codes. They conduct thorough checks before issuing approval certificates.","translation":"安全檢查員將確保建築物符合所有建築法規。他們在頒發批准證書前進行徹底檢查。","word":"ensure"}},"entertain":{"createdAt":1781746685505,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"entertain指的是招待、款待、使歡樂，表示提供娛樂活動或使他人感到愉快。","options":["obedience","entertain","affirm","terminate"],"sentence":"The host worked hard to ______ the guests throughout the evening. Everyone enjoyed the music, jokes, and delicious food that kept them smiling and laughing.","translation":"主人整晚努力招待客人。每個人都享受音樂、笑話和美食，這些讓他們一直微笑和歡笑。","word":"entertain"}},"enthusiasm":{"createdAt":1781274836862,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"enthusiasm表示對某事的熱心和熱忱，特別是指積極且充滿能量的態度。","options":["laziness","enthusiasm","confusion","criticism"],"sentence":"The team played with great ______ throughout the entire championship match. Their energy and positive attitude inspired everyone in the stadium to cheer loudly.","translation":"這支隊伍在整個錦標賽比賽中以極大的熱心參賽。他們的能量和積極態度激勵了體育館裡的每個人大聲歡呼。","word":"enthusiasm"}},"entitle":{"createdAt":1781841505535,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"entitle 表示給予權利或使某人符合資格，通常與官方許可或資格相關。","options":["wonder","entitle","pollute","legendary"],"sentence":"Having a valid passport should ______ you to enter most countries without requiring additional documentation. The government issues these documents specifically to grant citizens this right.","translation":"擁有有效的護照應該使你有權進入大多數國家而無需額外文件。政府發放這些文件的目的就是為了賦予公民這項權利。","word":"entitle"}},"entity":{"createdAt":1781598671075,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"entity 作名詞表示實體或獨立存在的單位，在法律和商業中指作為一個整體而存在的組織","options":["person","entity","relationship","concept"],"sentence":"The corporation is a legal ______ that can own property and sign contracts independently. It operates as a separate organization distinct from its individual shareholders and owners.","translation":"該公司是一個獨立擁有財產和簽署合同的法律實體。它作為一個獨立組織運營，與其個別股東和所有者不同。","word":"entity"}},"entrance":{"createdAt":1781582619548,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"entrance 在此指建築物或場所的開口或門道，遊客進入時使用的通道。","options":["exit","entrance","corridor","window"],"sentence":"The museum's grand ______ was decorated with marble columns and statues. Visitors had to pass through this ornate doorway to get inside the building.","translation":"博物館宏偉的入口裝飾著大理石柱子和雕像。訪客必須通過這扇華麗的門道才能進入建築物內部。","word":"entrance"}},"entry":{"createdAt":1781693538701,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"entry 指的是進入某個領域、行業或地點的過程，通常表示開始或加入。","options":["exit","entry","departure","rejection"],"sentence":"Her ______ into the music industry came after years of hard work and auditions. She finally signed her first record deal last month.","translation":"她進入音樂產業是在多年的努力和試鏡後才實現的。她終於在上個月簽署了第一份唱片合約。","word":"entry"}},"envy":{"createdAt":1781503378971,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"envy 表示對他人擁有或成就的羨慕和嫉妒，渴望擁有相同的事物。","options":["pride","joy","envy","happiness"],"sentence":"She felt a sense of ______ watching her friend receive the award she had hoped for. The jealous feeling grew stronger as she realized her friend's success surpassed her own achievements.","translation":"看著她的朋友獲得她一直希望的獎項，她感到一種忌妒。當她意識到朋友的成功超過她自己的成就時，這種嫉妒的感覺變得更強烈。","word":"envy"}},"epidemic":{"createdAt":1781256485489,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"epidemic指的是在特定地區或時期內迅速傳播的疾病或流行性疾病","options":["celebration","epidemic","mystery","scandal"],"sentence":"The ______ spread rapidly through the city, affecting thousands of residents. Health officials declared a state of emergency because the infectious disease was out of control.","translation":"這場傳染病迅速蔓延到整個城市，影響了數千名居民。衛生官員宣布進入緊急狀態，因為這種傳染性疾病已失控。","word":"epidemic"}},"episode":{"createdAt":1781860901468,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"episode表示連續劇的一集或插曲，指連續故事中的單個部分","options":["character","episode","location","genre"],"sentence":"The final ______ of the TV series aired last night and left viewers wanting more. Fans were thrilled by the cliffhanger ending and are hoping for a second season.","translation":"這部電視劇的最後一集昨晚播出，令觀眾期待更多內容。粉絲們對懸念結局感到興奮，希望能有第二季。","word":"episode"}},"equalize":{"createdAt":1781493458233,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"equalize 意為使相等或平衡，在這裡指讓兩支隊伍的上場時間相同","options":["increase","equalize","reduce","analyze"],"sentence":"The coach decided to ______ the playing time between the two teams' forwards. This adjustment ensured that both sides had the same number of minutes on the court.","translation":"教練決定平等分配兩隊前鋒的上場時間。這項調整確保雙方在場上有相同的分鐘數。","word":"equalize"}},"equip":{"createdAt":1781709984197,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"equip 動詞表示配備或裝備某物以使其完備，通常用於配備工具或設備。","options":["furnish","equip","provide","supply"],"sentence":"The school decided to ______ all classrooms with new computers and projectors. The principal announced that the upgrade would be completed by the start of the academic year.","translation":"學校決定用新電腦和投影儀裝備所有教室。校長宣佈升級將在學年開始前完成。","word":"equip"}},"equipment":{"createdAt":1782016805983,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"equipment 是名詞，表示執行特定任務所需的物質工具和裝置的集合。","options":["knowledge","equipment","courage","experience"],"sentence":"The mountaineering team spent weeks preparing their ______ before attempting to summit the peak. Ropes, harnesses, oxygen tanks, and specialized clothing were all carefully checked and packed.","translation":"登山隊在嘗試登頂前花了數週時間準備他們的裝備。繩索、安全帶、氧氣罐和專業服裝都被仔細檢查和打包。","word":"equipment"}},"equivalent":{"createdAt":1781402539338,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"equivalent 表示在價值、意義或功能上相等或相當，雖然形式可能不同。","options":["superior","equivalent","inferior","identical"],"sentence":"A passing grade of 60% is ______ to a D mark on the letter scale. Both represent the minimum acceptable performance level.","translation":"60%的及格分數相當於字母等級中的D分。兩者都代表最低可接受的表現水平。","word":"equivalent"}},"errand":{"createdAt":1781434900598,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"errand指需要執行的短途任務或差事，通常是代表他人進行。","options":["party","errand","conversation","class"],"sentence":"She ran several ______ for her elderly mother, including picking up groceries and paying bills. The tasks were essential to help her mother manage daily responsibilities.","translation":"她為年邁的母親跑了幾次差事，包括購買雜貨和支付賬單。這些任務對幫助她母親處理日常事務至關重要。","word":"errand"}},"escape":{"createdAt":1781332009068,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"escape 意為逃跑或逃脫某個地方或情況","options":["enter","escape","sleep","work"],"sentence":"The prisoners planned to ______ from the maximum-security facility by tunneling under the fence. They successfully fled and were not recaptured for several months.","translation":"囚犯計畫通過在圍欄下挖隧道來逃跑。他們成功逃脫，並在幾個月內沒有被重新逮捕。","word":"escape"}},"essential":{"createdAt":1781746685505,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"essential指的是本質的、必要的、不可缺少的，用來形容某樣事物對於達到某個目標是必不可少的。","options":["essential","duration","editorials","sober"],"sentence":"Good nutrition is ______ for children's healthy development. Without proper food intake, their bodies cannot grow strong and their minds cannot develop properly.","translation":"良好的營養對兒童的健康發展是必要的。沒有適當的食物攝入，他們的身體無法強健，心智也無法正常發展。","word":"essential"}},"estate":{"createdAt":1781849847402,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"estate表示大片土地和建築組成的財產或莊園，與「包括豪宅和數百英畝」的線索相符。","options":["apartment","estate","cottage","hotel"],"sentence":"The wealthy family inherited a large ______ that included a mansion and hundreds of acres. The property had been in the family for generations.","translation":"這個富有的家族繼承了一個包括豪宅和數百英畝土地的大莊園。該房產已經在家族中傳了許多代。","word":"estate"}},"esteem":{"createdAt":1781831848728,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"esteem 作為名詞表示「尊敬」或「敬重」，指對某人或某事的高度評價和認可。","options":["criticism","esteem","attention","interest"],"sentence":"The professor earned great ______ among her students for her innovative teaching methods. Everyone respected her dedication to making complex topics easy to understand.","translation":"這位教授因其創新的教學方法在學生中獲得了高度的尊敬。每個人都欽佩她致力於使複雜主題容易理解的精神。","word":"esteem"}},"estimate":{"createdAt":1781331945989,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"estimate 指根據可用信息進行合理的估計或預算，通常涉及計算或評價。","options":["ignore","guess","estimate","remember"],"sentence":"The contractor asked me to ______ how much money I would need for home renovations. Based on the materials, labor costs, and the scope of work described, he predicted the project would cost around thirty thousand dollars.","translation":"承包商要求我估計進行房屋翻新需要多少錢。根據所述的材料、勞動力成本和工作範圍，他預測該項目將花費大約三萬美元。","word":"estimate"}},"estimation":{"createdAt":1781849847409,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"estimation表示估計或評價，與「詳細分析、涵蓋費用」的線索相符。","options":["guess","estimation","whim","mood"],"sentence":"According to the expert's ______, the project will cost approximately fifty thousand dollars. The detailed analysis covered all potential expenses.","translation":"根據專家的評估，這個項目將花費大約五萬美元。詳細的分析涵蓋了所有潛在費用。","word":"estimation"}},"eta":{"createdAt":1781228443753,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"Eta是希臘字母表中的第七個字母，在物理學中常用來代表效率、黏度等物理量。","options":["zeta","theta","eta","iota"],"sentence":"The seventh letter of the Greek alphabet is ______. Students learning about efficiency and viscosity in physics class regularly encounter this symbol in their textbooks.","translation":"希臘字母表中的第七個字母是______。學生在物理課堂上學習效率和黏度時，經常在教科書中遇到這個符號。","word":"eta"}},"eternity":{"createdAt":1781515634901,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「eternity」表示無限長的時間或似乎永遠不會結束的很長一段時間。","options":["a moment","eternity","seconds","minutes"],"sentence":"Waiting for the exam results felt like ______. Time seemed to move incredibly slowly those two weeks.","translation":"等待考試成績的過程感覺像是永恆。那兩週時間似乎過得極其緩慢。","word":"eternity"}},"ethical":{"createdAt":1781256444518,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ethical指符合道德和倫理原則的，強調正直和誠實的行為標準。","options":["strict","ethical","marketing","financial"],"sentence":"The company's ______ standards require all employees to report conflicts of interest immediately. This policy ensures that business decisions are made with integrity and transparency.","translation":"公司的道德標準要求所有員工立即報告利益衝突。該政策確保業務決策以誠信和透明度進行。","word":"ethical"}},"ethics":{"createdAt":1781933311794,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"ethics（倫理；道德）涉及道德原則和公平對待，而logistics（物流）、mechanics（機械）和acoustics（聲學）都與道德標準和公平性無關。","options":["logistics","mechanics","ethics","acoustics"],"sentence":"The company's ______ committee reviewed all business practices to ensure no employees were treated unfairly. The group examined whether decisions followed moral principles and legal standards.","translation":"該公司的倫理委員會審查了所有業務實踐，以確保沒有員工受到不公平對待。該小組檢視了決策是否遵循道德原則和法律標準。","word":"ethics"}},"eventual":{"createdAt":1781849847408,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"eventual表示最終的或最後才發生的，與「經過多年、需要耐心」的線索相符。","options":["immediate","eventual","unexpected","impossible"],"sentence":"The ______ success of the company came after many years of hard work and dedication. It took patience before the business became profitable.","translation":"公司的最終成功是在經過許多年的辛勤工作和奉獻之後才實現的。在業務開始盈利之前需要耐心等待。","word":"eventual"}},"eventually":{"createdAt":1781849847410,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"eventually表示最終或最後，與「經過二十年才發現」的線索相符。","options":["never","eventually","rarely","hardly"],"sentence":"She tried many different careers before she ______ found her true passion in teaching. It took her twenty years to discover what she loved.","translation":"在她最終在教學中找到真正的熱情之前，她嘗試了許多不同的職業。她花了二十年才發現自己喜歡的工作。","word":"eventually"}},"evidence":{"createdAt":1781331945968,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"evidence 指能夠證明事實或支持主張的具體證據或證詞，通常在法律或調查情境中使用。","options":["proof","opinion","rumor","suspicion"],"sentence":"The detective presented ______ in court to prove the suspect was guilty. The photographs, fingerprints, and witness statements she showed the jury were all crucial to building her case.","translation":"偵探在法庭上出示證據以證明嫌疑人有罪。她向陪審團展示的照片、指紋和證人陳述都對建立她的案件至關重要。","word":"evidence"}},"evident":{"createdAt":1781624534708,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"evident 意為「明顯的、顯然的」，指容易看出或理解的事物。","options":["hidden","uncertain","evident","questionable"],"sentence":"It is ______ from her facial expression that she is unhappy with the decision made by the committee. She frowned and left the meeting without speaking to anyone.","translation":"從她的面部表情可以明顯看出，她對委員會做出的決定不滿意。她皺著眉頭離開了會議，沒有和任何人說話。","word":"evident"}},"evidently":{"createdAt":1781624534650,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"evidently 意為「顯然地、明顯地」，用於表達某事很清楚或容易看出。","options":["secretly","evidently","fortunately","theoretically"],"sentence":"The student ______ did not understand the mathematics concept during the lesson. He raised his hand multiple times to ask the same question in different ways.","translation":"該學生顯然在課堂上沒有理解數學概念。他多次舉手用不同方式提出同樣的問題。","word":"evidently"}},"evil":{"createdAt":1781345564015,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"evil 是形容詞，表示道德上邪惡、不道德或傷害他人的，常用來描述令人厭惡的人或行為。","options":["kind","generous","evil","peaceful"],"sentence":"The ______ dictator ruled his country with fear and violence for thirty years. His regime was responsible for torturing and murdering countless innocent citizens.","translation":"這位邪惡的獨裁者用恐懼和暴力統治他的國家三十年。他的政權對無數無辜公民進行了刑求和謀殺。","word":"evil"}},"evoke":{"createdAt":1781598671069,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"evoke 作動詞表示引起或喚起，通常指引起特定的情感、記憶或反應","options":["suppress","evoke","ignore","delay"],"sentence":"The old photograph managed to ______ strong emotions in my heart. Seeing it instantly transported me back to my childhood memories with vivid clarity.","translation":"這張舊照片設法在我心中引起強烈的情感。看到它讓我立刻回到童年回憶中，清晰生動。","word":"evoke"}},"evolution":{"createdAt":1781840030398,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"evolution 是名詞，表示演化、進化；與「化石記錄」、「遺傳證據」和「數百萬年」的科學背景相符。","options":["creation","extinction","evolution","revolution"],"sentence":"Scientists study the ______ of species by examining fossil records and genetic evidence from different time periods. This process of change took millions of years to produce the diverse life forms we see today.","translation":"科學家通過檢查不同時期的化石記錄和遺傳證據來研究物種的進化。這個變化過程花了數百萬年才產生了我們今天看到的多樣生命形式。","word":"evolution"}},"exceed":{"createdAt":1782022372249,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"exceed 意為「超過、超越」，表示某事物的程度或數量比預期或比較對象更大或更多。","options":["decline","match","exceed","approach"],"sentence":"The company's profit this quarter will ______ all previous records and expectations set by investors. The financial analysts had predicted a modest growth, but the actual results surpassed their most optimistic forecasts by a significant margin.","translation":"公司本季度的利潤將超越所有先前的記錄和投資者的預期。財務分析師曾預測增長幅度較為溫和，但實際結果遠超他們最樂觀的預測。","word":"exceed"}},"except":{"createdAt":1781425122880,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"except 是介詞，表示排除或不包括某人或某物，與湯姆因病缺席但其他人都在的脈絡相符。","options":["including","except","during","throughout"],"sentence":"Everyone attended the meeting ______ for Tom, who was sick that day. All other team members were present and participated.","translation":"除了生病的湯姆以外，所有人都參加了會議。所有其他團隊成員都出席並參與了會議。","word":"except"}},"excerpt":{"createdAt":1781332009071,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"excerpt 指的是從書籍、文章或演講中摘取的一部分內容","options":["preface","excerpt","epilogue","outline"],"sentence":"The teacher showed the class an ______ from the novel to illustrate the author's writing style. The passage was only a few pages long but demonstrated the key themes of the book.","translation":"老師向班級展示了小說中的摘錄以說明作者的寫作風格。這段文章只有幾頁，但展示了該書的關鍵主題。","word":"excerpt"}},"excess":{"createdAt":1781598671068,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"excess 作名詞表示過量或超過，指超過必要或合理的數量","options":["essential","excess","required","annual"],"sentence":"The company must reduce its ______ spending to improve profitability this quarter. The accountant identified millions of dollars wasted on unnecessary purchases and luxury expenses.","translation":"公司必須減少過度支出以改善本季度的利潤率。會計師發現數百萬美元浪費在不必要的購買和奢侈開支上。","word":"excess"}},"excessive":{"createdAt":1781798927522,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"excessive 形容某事超過正常或合理的程度，表示過度或極度的。","options":["minimal","excessive","moderate","reasonable"],"sentence":"The teacher complained about the student's ______ use of social media during class. He spent more than five hours per day texting and scrolling instead of paying attention.","translation":"老師抱怨學生在課堂上過度使用社群媒體。他每天花超過五個小時發短信和滑動屏幕，而不是專注聽課。","word":"excessive"}},"exchange":{"createdAt":1781738105693,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"exchange 意為互相交換或調換，指的是兩個或以上的人之間相互給予東西。","options":["ignore","exchange","collect","record"],"sentence":"The two students decided to ______ phone numbers so they could stay in touch after graduation. They wrote down their contact information and handed each other their details.","translation":"兩位學生決定交換電話號碼，以便畢業後能保持聯繫。他們寫下了聯繫信息並互相交給了對方的詳細信息。","word":"exchange"}},"exclusive":{"createdAt":1781362281664,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"exclusive表示排外的或獨家的，只限於特定的人或團體。","options":["public","exclusive","open","general"],"sentence":"This ______ club membership is only available to wealthy individuals. Regular people cannot join regardless of their interest in membership.","translation":"這個排外俱樂部會員只對富人開放。無論普通人多麼有興趣，他們都無法加入。","word":"exclusive"}},"execute":{"createdAt":1781424356416,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"execute指的是按照計劃或指令來完成某個任務或行動。","options":["ignore","execute","modify","cancel"],"sentence":"The architect asked the construction team to ______ the building plans exactly as designed. Every detail from the blueprints needed to be implemented precisely to ensure structural integrity.","translation":"建築師要求建築隊完全按照設計來執行建築計劃。藍圖中的每一個細節都需要精確實施，以確保結構完整性。","word":"execute"}},"executive":{"createdAt":1781693293272,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"executive 是形容詞，意思是「行政上的」或「執行的」，用於形容管理層的決定或權力。","options":["ruthless","executive","crush","priceless"],"sentence":"The company's ______ decision to cut costs affected all departments immediately. The board of directors approved the new budget and operational changes during their monthly meeting.","translation":"公司的行政決定立即影響了所有部門的成本削減。董事會在月度會議期間批准了新預算和運營變化。","word":"executive"}},"exert":{"createdAt":1781323901188,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"exert意為「運用」或「施加」，在此指使用權力或影響力來達成目標。","options":["lose","exert","ignore","abandon"],"sentence":"The manager decided to ______ her influence over the board members to approve the new project. Through her persuasion and political connections, she successfully pushed the proposal forward.","translation":"經理決定運用她對董事會成員的影響力來批准新項目。通過她的勸說和政治關係，她成功推動了該提案。","word":"exert"}},"exhausted":{"createdAt":1781499075056,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"筋疲力盡表示一個人因為用力或工作而完全失去了體力和精力。","options":["excited","refreshed","exhausted","motivated"],"sentence":"After running a marathon, the athlete felt completely ______ and could barely stand. He had used up all his energy reserves during the grueling 26-mile race.","translation":"跑完馬拉松後，運動員感到筋疲力盡，幾乎無法站立。他在這場艱苦的26英里比賽中耗盡了所有的能量。","word":"exhausted"}},"exhibit":{"createdAt":1781775276771,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"exhibit意為展示或展覽，指將作品公開展示給公眾觀看。","options":["hide","steal","exhibit","destroy"],"sentence":"The museum will ______ rare paintings from the Renaissance period next month. Visitors will be able to see masterpieces that have been kept in private collections for centuries.","translation":"博物館下個月將展示文藝復興時期的罕見繪畫。遊客們將能夠看到數百年來一直保存在私人收藏中的傑作。","word":"exhibit"}},"exhibition":{"createdAt":1781425122881,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"exhibition 指展覽會或展覽品，與美術館、藝術作品和展出這個脈絡相符。","options":["tournament","exhibition","discount","defeat"],"sentence":"The museum held a special ______ featuring paintings by famous impressionist artists. Visitors came from around the world to see the masterpieces on display.","translation":"博物館舉辦了一場特別展覽，展出著名印象派畫家的作品。來自世界各地的遊客前來欣賞展出的傑作。","word":"exhibition"}},"exhibitor":{"createdAt":1781738105692,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"exhibitor 指的是展示或展覽商品、作品或物品的人，特別是在展覽會或展示會上。","options":["visitor","exhibitor","curator","artist"],"sentence":"The art gallery hired a professional ______ to arrange all the paintings and sculptures for the upcoming exhibition. This person had years of experience in displaying artwork to attract visitors.","translation":"美術館聘請了一位專業展示者來為即將舉辦的展覽安排所有的繪畫和雕塑。這個人有多年展示藝術作品以吸引遊客的經驗。","word":"exhibitor"}},"exhilarate":{"createdAt":1782009797690,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"exhilarate 動詞，表示使某人感到興高采烈、愉快或充滿活力；第二句的「大笑」和「心臟狂跳」強調了這種高興和興奮的情感狀態。","options":["bore","depress","exhilarate","tire"],"sentence":"The roller coaster ride will ______ everyone on the track with its thrilling twists and turns. Passengers walked off with huge smiles, their hearts pounding from the adrenaline rush.","translation":"雲霄飛車將以其令人刺激的轉彎和翻滾使軌道上的每個人都感到興高采烈。乘客下車時面帶大笑，他們的心臟因腎上腺素激增而狂跳。","word":"exhilarate"}},"exotic":{"createdAt":1781598671101,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"exotic 作形容詞表示異國的或異國情調的，指來自遠方或不同文化的東西","options":["ordinary","exotic","basic","simple"],"sentence":"The restaurant serves ______ dishes from Southeast Asia that attract food enthusiasts. Diners enjoy flavors and spices that are rarely found in typical Western cuisine.","translation":"該餐廳提供來自東南亞的異國菜肴，吸引美食愛好者。食客喜歡在典型西方美食中很少見到的風味和香料。","word":"exotic"}},"expand":{"createdAt":1781664082522,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"expand 表示擴大、擴展或增加某事物的規模和範圍。","options":["contract","expand","collapse","pause"],"sentence":"The company plans to ______ its business into three new markets next year. They will open additional offices and hire more employees to support this growth.","translation":"該公司計畫明年將其業務擴展到三個新市場。他們將開設更多辦公室並聘請更多員工來支持這一增長。","word":"expand"}},"expansion":{"createdAt":1781839703137,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"expansion指事業或範圍的擴大延伸，與opening branches（開設分店）這個具體例子相符。","options":["contraction","expansion","stability","decline"],"sentence":"The company's ______ into new markets has created hundreds of jobs. They opened ten additional branches in Southeast Asia last quarter alone.","translation":"該公司向新市場的擴展創造了數百個工作機會。他們在上個季度僅在東南亞就開設了十家分支機構。","word":"expansion"}},"expectation":{"createdAt":1781619188925,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"expectation 指對未來事件的期望或預期，反映對結果的盼望。","options":["anxiety","expectation","fear","doubt"],"sentence":"Her ______ for the job interview were extremely high after years of preparation. However, she performed poorly and didn't receive an offer.","translation":"經過多年準備，她對這次工作面試的期望極高。然而，她表現不佳，沒有收到錄用通知。","word":"expectation"}},"expedition":{"createdAt":1781619188923,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"expedition 指有目的的遠征或探險活動，通常涉及科研或探索目標。","options":["vacation","expedition","migration","journey"],"sentence":"The research team planned a challenging ______ to the Arctic to study climate change. They spent eighteen months preparing equipment and training before departing.","translation":"研究團隊計劃進行一次艱辛的北極探險，以研究氣候變化。他們在出發前花了十八個月準備設備和培訓。","word":"expedition"}},"expense":{"createdAt":1781961517451,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"expense 特指金錢上的支出或費用，通常用在經濟成本的語境中。","options":["burden","expense","effort","problem"],"sentence":"The family decided to cut down on their vacation ______ by staying at a budget hotel. They needed to reduce their overall spending due to limited financial resources.","translation":"這個家庭決定通過住在經濟旅館來減少他們的度假費用。由於財務資源有限，他們需要減少總體支出。","word":"expense"}},"expensive":{"createdAt":1781424137078,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"expensive 形容詞意為「昂貴的」，用來描述價格很高、花費很大的物品或服務。","options":["cheap","affordable","expensive","reasonable"],"sentence":"This restaurant is quite ______ and only wealthy customers can afford to eat here regularly. A single meal at this establishment costs more than a hundred dollars.","translation":"這家餐廳相當昂貴，只有富有的顧客才能經常在這裡用餐。這家店的一頓飯要花一百多美元。","word":"expensive"}},"expert":{"createdAt":1781715051242,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"expert 作為名詞表示「專家」或「熟練者」，指在某個領域具有深厚知識和高超技能的人。","options":["beginner","expert","student","observer"],"sentence":"Dr. Chen is an ______ in cardiac surgery who has performed thousands of complex operations. She was invited to lead the medical team because of her decades of specialized knowledge and proven skill in this field.","translation":"陳醫生是心臟手術的專家，已經進行過數千次複雜手術。由於她在這個領域擁有數十年的專業知識和經驗豐富的技能，她被邀請領導醫療團隊。","word":"expert"}},"expertise":{"createdAt":1781414438960,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"expertise指在特定領域中獲得的深厚知識、技能和專業能力","options":["luck","expertise","interest","theory"],"sentence":"The company hired a consultant with ______ in digital marketing strategy. His twenty years of experience and proven track record made him the perfect choice for leading the campaign.","translation":"公司聘請了一位擁有數位行銷策略專長的顧問。他二十年的經驗和成熟的業績使他成為領導這項活動的完美人選。","word":"expertise"}},"expire":{"createdAt":1781452425261,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"expire表示期限屆滿或失效，指某份文件或許可證不再有效。","options":["extend","renew","end","strengthen"],"sentence":"Your passport will ______ on December 31st of this year. You should apply for a renewal immediately if you have any international travel plans.","translation":"您的護照將在今年12月31日期滿。如果您有任何國際旅行計劃，應該立即申請續期。","word":"expire"}},"explicit":{"createdAt":1781581925131,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"explicit 表示詳盡的、明確的、毫不含糊的，指信息清楚直接，不需要推測。","options":["implicit","explicit","vague","ambiguous"],"sentence":"The teacher gave ______ instructions on how to complete the assignment. Students did not need to guess; every step was clearly written with specific examples.","translation":"老師給了關於如何完成作業的明確指示。學生不需要猜測；每個步驟都用具體的例子明確寫出。","word":"explicit"}},"explode":{"createdAt":1781693538700,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"explode 表示突然猛烈地爆發或炸開，常伴隨巨大的聲音和光線。","options":["whisper","explode","melt","float"],"sentence":"The fireworks will ______ into the night sky at midnight. We can already hear the loud bangs and see the colorful lights bursting above us.","translation":"煙火將在午夜時分爆炸進入夜空。我們已經能聽到巨大的爆炸聲，看到五顏六色的光線在我們上方炸裂。","word":"explode"}},"exploit":{"createdAt":1781425737122,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"exploit 作名詞時指傑出的功績或英勇的行為，與戰爭中的英雄表現相符。","options":["defeat","exploit","retreat","loss"],"sentence":"The soldier's brave ______ during the battle earned him a medal of honor. His heroic actions saved many lives and inspired his entire regiment.","translation":"這位士兵在戰鬥中的英勇功績為他贏得了榮譽勳章。他的英雄行為拯救了許多生命，激勵了整個團隊。","word":"exploit"}},"explore":{"createdAt":1781332009069,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"explore 意為探測或探險，通常用於對未知地區的調查和研究","options":["avoid","explore","close","ignore"],"sentence":"The research team decided to ______ the newly discovered cave system in the mountains. They spent weeks mapping out all the tunnels and studying the geological formations inside.","translation":"研究小組決定探測山區新發現的洞穴系統。他們花了數周時間繪製所有隧道並研究內部的地質構造。","word":"explore"}},"expose":{"createdAt":1781598671164,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"expose 作動詞表示使暴露或揭露，指揭示隱藏或秘密的事實","options":["conceal","expose","ignore","protect"],"sentence":"Journalists worked to ______ the corruption scandal within the government agency. Their investigation revealed illegal activities hidden from the public for years.","translation":"記者致力於揭露政府機構內的腐敗醜聞。他們的調查揭示了多年來向公眾隱瞞的非法活動。","word":"expose"}},"exposure":{"createdAt":1781839703152,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"exposure指暴露在某物中，與prolonged sun exposure causing skin damage and UV radiation warnings（長時間暴曬導致皮膚損傷和紫外線警告）直接對應。","options":["shelter","protection","exposure","coverage"],"sentence":"Prolonged ______ to the sun without sunscreen can cause severe skin damage. The dermatologist warned her about the risks of UV radiation.","translation":"在沒有防曬霜的情況下長時間暴曬會造成嚴重的皮膚損傷。皮膚科醫生警告她紫外線輻射的危險。","word":"exposure"}},"expressive":{"createdAt":1781311983486,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"expressive 表示能夠表達感情或想法的，富有表現力和感染力的。","options":["average","offshore","expressive","evolution"],"sentence":"The dancer's ______ movements captivated the entire audience during the performance. Her body language conveyed deep emotion and artistic intention without speaking a single word.","translation":"舞者在表演中富有表現力的動作迷住了整個觀眾。她的肢體語言在沒有說一句話的情況下傳達了深層的情感和藝術意圖。","word":"expressive"}},"extension":{"createdAt":1781709984193,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"extension 在這裡指的是延長期限或時間長度，特別是在借用物品時的期限延長。","options":["renewal","extension","delay","postponement"],"sentence":"I need to request an ______ on my library book because I haven't finished reading it yet. The librarian said I can add two more weeks to the due date.","translation":"我需要申請延長我的圖書館借書期限，因為我還沒讀完。圖書館員說我可以在到期日期上再加兩週。","word":"extension"}},"extensive":{"createdAt":1781693591740,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"extensive 是形容詞，表示「廣闊的」、「大面積的」或「覆蓋範圍廣的」，強調規模大且涵蓋範圍廣。","options":["minimal","brief","extensive","focused"],"sentence":"The professor conducted ______ research across multiple countries and collected data from thousands of participants. His study covered urban areas, rural communities, and everything in between over five years.","translation":"教授在多個國家進行了廣泛的研究，並從數千名參與者收集了數據。他的研究涵蓋了城市地區、農村社區以及介於兩者之間的所有地方，歷時五年。","word":"extensive"}},"extinct":{"createdAt":1781598671067,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"extinct 作形容詞表示絕種的或消失的，指物種或現象完全不復存在","options":["endangered","extinct","migrating","thriving"],"sentence":"The dodo bird is now ______ and can only be seen in museums and historical records. This species disappeared forever in the 17th century due to human hunting.","translation":"渡渡鳥現在已經絕種，只能在博物館和歷史記錄中看到。這個物種在17世紀因人類獵殺而永遠消失。","word":"extinct"}},"extraordinary":{"createdAt":1781693269016,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"extraordinary 意思是非凡的、特別的、超出尋常的，形容極其出眾或令人驚嘆的事物。","options":["ordinary","extraordinary","mediocre","average"],"sentence":"The young athlete displayed ______ talent during the championship match, impressing all the coaches in attendance. Her performance was so exceptional that professional teams immediately began scouting her for recruitment.","translation":"這位年輕運動員在錦標賽中展現了非凡的才能，給所有出席的教練留下了深刻印象。她的表現非常傑出，以至於職業隊伍立即開始尋求簽約她。","word":"extraordinary"}},"fable":{"createdAt":1781703691073,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"fable 作為名詞指寓言故事，通常涉及動物角色並傳達道德或教訓。","options":["novel","essay","fable","poem"],"sentence":"Aesop's most famous ______ tells the story of a tortoise and a hare racing to prove that slow and steady progress wins the competition. This timeless tale teaches children the moral lesson that persistence and determination are more valuable than natural talent.","translation":"伊索最著名的寓言講述了烏龜和兔子比賽的故事，用來證明穩定持久的進展能贏得比賽。這個永恆的故事教導孩子們一個道德教訓，即堅持和決心比天賦更有價值。","word":"fable"}},"fabric":{"createdAt":1781485266373,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"fabric指的是通過編織或紡織製成的織物和織品，用於製作衣服和其他物品。","options":["metal","plastic","fabric","leather"],"sentence":"She selected a soft cotton ______ for her summer dress project at the textile shop. The material felt smooth and breathable, perfect for hot weather clothing.","translation":"她在紡織品店為她的夏季連衣裙項目選擇了柔軟的棉織物。這種材料感覺光滑透氣，非常適合炎熱天氣的服裝。","word":"fabric"}},"fabulous":{"createdAt":1781780789949,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fabulous 是形容詞，意為極好的、令人難以置信的，通常用來讚美某事物非常出色或令人印象深刻。","options":["boring","fabulous","confusing","ordinary"],"sentence":"The performance was absolutely ______ and left the entire audience speechless. Everyone gave it a standing ovation and praised it as one of the best shows they had ever seen.","translation":"那場表演絕對是極好的，讓整個觀眾都驚呆了。每個人都起立鼓掌，並稱讚它是他們看過最好的演出之一。","word":"fabulous"}},"facilitate":{"createdAt":1781703691070,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"facilitate 作為動詞表示使某事變得容易或便利，促進事情的進行。","options":["complicate","facilitate","ignore","prevent"],"sentence":"Online learning platforms ______ communication between teachers and students across different time zones. Without these digital tools, remote education would be much more challenging and inefficient.","translation":"線上學習平台促進了不同時區的老師和學生之間的溝通。沒有這些數位工具，遠距教育會變得更加困難和低效。","word":"facilitate"}},"facility":{"createdAt":1781417610422,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"facility是指為特定目的而建造的設備、機構或場所，通常配備必要的工具和資源。","options":["library","dormitory","facility","cafeteria"],"sentence":"The university invested millions of dollars in building a state-of-the-art research ______ for its chemistry department. Scientists now had access to the latest equipment and technology needed for advanced experiments.","translation":"大學投入數百萬美元為化學系建造最先進的研究設施。科學家們現在可以使用進行先進實驗所需的最新設備和技術。","word":"facility"}},"faculty":{"createdAt":1781843487264,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"faculty 指的是學校或大學的全體教職員，包括教師和其他工作人員，是集體名詞。","options":["students","faculty","alumni","trustees"],"sentence":"The ______ at this university includes professors, lecturers, and administrative staff. The dean called a meeting with all 200 members to discuss the new curriculum policy.","translation":"這所大學的教職員包括教授、講師和行政人員。院長召集所有200名成員開會討論新的課程政策。","word":"faculty"}},"fahrenheit":{"createdAt":1781784283025,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"Fahrenheit是名詞，指華氏溫標；美國主要使用華氏溫度來測量和報告天氣溫度，而不是攝氏溫度。","options":["Celsius","Kelvin","Fahrenheit","Rankine"],"sentence":"The weather report showed the temperature was 68 degrees ______. This is the temperature scale commonly used in the United States and a few other countries.","translation":"天氣預報顯示溫度是68度______。這是在美國和少數其他國家常用的溫度計量表。","word":"fahrenheit"}},"faithful":{"createdAt":1781564440928,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"faithful 作形容詞表示忠實的、守信的，指保持忠誠、可靠和真實。","options":["aggressive","faithful","lazy","unfriendly"],"sentence":"The dog was a ______ companion who followed his owner everywhere. Throughout the years, the animal never abandoned or betrayed its owner's trust.","translation":"這隻狗是忠實的伴侶，到處跟著主人。多年來，這隻動物從未拋棄或背叛主人的信任。","word":"faithful"}},"faithfully":{"createdAt":1781696018689,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"faithfully 意為忠實地、忠誠地，形容以忠心、堅定和持久的方式對待某人或某事。","options":["reluctantly","faithfully","occasionally","carelessly"],"sentence":"The old dog ______ followed his master everywhere, never leaving his side for decades. Such unwavering devotion was truly remarkable.","translation":"老狗幾十年來忠實地跟隨主人到處走，從不離開主人身邊。這種堅定不移的忠誠確實令人印象深刻。","word":"faithfully"}},"fake":{"createdAt":1781780789962,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fake 在此作名詞，意為贗品或冒充者，表示非真實的、偽造的物品或假裝者。","options":["treasure","fake","discovery","relic"],"sentence":"The museum discovered that the ancient artifact was actually a ______ created by a clever forger. Testing revealed it was made only fifty years ago, not two thousand years ago.","translation":"博物館發現那件古代藝術品實際上是由一位聰明的偽造者創作的贗品。檢測表明它是五十年前製造的，而不是兩千年前。","word":"fake"}},"fame":{"createdAt":1781499075061,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"名聲指一個人因為成就或才能而廣為人知和受認可。","options":["obscurity","anonymity","fame","poverty"],"sentence":"The young musician achieved ______ after her debut album became a worldwide hit. Record labels wanted to sign her, and millions of fans followed her on social media.","translation":"這位年輕音樂家在她的首張專輯成為全球熱門後獲得了名聲。唱片公司想簽約她，數百萬粉絲在社交媒體上關注她。","word":"fame"}},"familiar":{"createdAt":1781832761711,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"familiar 表示熟悉的、常見的，指對某事物有充分的認識或接觸。","options":["strange","unknown","well-known","foreign"],"sentence":"The old song sounded ______ to Sarah, bringing back memories of her childhood. She had heard that melody many times on her grandmother's radio years ago.","translation":"這首舊歌對莎拉來說很熟悉，喚起了她童年的回憶。多年前她曾在祖母的收音機上多次聽過這首旋律。","word":"familiar"}},"familiarity":{"createdAt":1781499075057,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"熟悉指對某事物或某人有充分的認識或了解。","options":["confusion","unfamiliarity","familiarity","uncertainty"],"sentence":"Her ______ with the local customs made it easy for her to navigate the new city. Having lived there for five years, she knew all the best restaurants and neighborhoods.","translation":"她對當地習俗的熟悉使她很容易在這個新城市導航。在那裡生活了五年後，她知道所有最好的餐廳和社區。","word":"familiarity"}},"fanatic":{"createdAt":1781424574163,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fanatic 指對某事物有過度熱情或狂熱的人，有時帶有盲目追隨的含義。","options":["casual","fanatic","critic","player"],"sentence":"The sports ______ attended every single game, wore team jerseys, and collected memorabilia obsessively. His passion for the team bordered on an unhealthy obsession.","translation":"這位運動狂熱者參加了每一場比賽，穿著球隊球衣，並瘋狂地收集紀念品。他對球隊的熱情幾乎成為了不健康的執著。","word":"fanatic"}},"fantastic":{"createdAt":1781332009065,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fantastic 意為極好的、非常令人滿意的，通常用來表達對某事物的高度讚美","options":["terrible","fantastic","boring","average"],"sentence":"The movie was absolutely ______ and exceeded all my expectations. Critics praised it as one of the best films of the year.","translation":"那部電影絕對是極好的，超越了我所有的期望。評論家稱讚它是今年最好的電影之一。","word":"fantastic"}},"fashion":{"createdAt":1781481124700,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"fashion 作為動詞表示製造、製作或設計某物。","options":["purchased","destroyed","created","displayed"],"sentence":"The designer carefully ______ a stunning evening gown from expensive silk fabric. Each seam was perfectly stitched, and every detail was meticulously crafted.","translation":"設計師從昂貴的絲綢面料中精心製作了一件令人驚艷的晚禮服。每條接縫都完美縫製，每個細節都精心製作。","word":"fashion"}},"fatal":{"createdAt":1781839703145,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"fatal指導致死亡的，與pronounced dead（被宣佈死亡）直接相關。","options":["minor","superficial","recoverable","fatal"],"sentence":"The accident proved to be ______ for the young driver. He was pronounced dead at the scene despite immediate medical intervention.","translation":"這場事故對年輕駕駛員來說是致命的。儘管立即進行了醫療干預，他仍在現場被宣佈死亡。","word":"fatal"}},"fatigued":{"createdAt":1781696018682,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"fatigued 意為疲憊、勞累，形容身體或精神上的極度疲勞狀態。","options":["energized","refreshed","fatigued","motivated"],"sentence":"After working sixteen hours straight, the nurse felt completely ______ and could barely stand. She collapsed onto her bed immediately upon arriving home.","translation":"連續工作十六小時後，護士感到極其疲憊，幾乎站不住。她一到家就立刻倒在床上。","word":"fatigued"}},"faucet":{"createdAt":1781849511875,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"龍頭是一種裝置，用於控制水的流量，通常安裝在水管出口處。","options":["pipe","faucet","sink","drain"],"sentence":"Sarah twisted the ______ in the kitchen sink to get some water for cooking dinner. The handle controlled the flow of water from the pipe directly into her pot.","translation":"莎拉轉動廚房水槽上的龍頭以獲得烹飪晚餐所需的水。把手控制從管道直接流入她的鍋中的水流。","word":"faucet"}},"favor":{"createdAt":1781708652664,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"favor 指幫助或善意行為，通常需要某人花費時間或努力來為另一個人做事。","options":["question","favor","reminder","suggestion"],"sentence":"She asked her friend to do her a ______ by picking up her package at the post office. Her friend agreed without hesitation because they had helped each other many times in the past.","translation":"她請求朋友幫她去郵局取包裹。她的朋友毫不猶豫地同意了，因為他們過去曾多次互相幫助。","word":"favor"}},"favorable":{"createdAt":1781708652665,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"favorable 指贊同的、稱讚的或有利的，用來描述積極正面的評價或態度。","options":["negative","mixed","favorable","harsh"],"sentence":"The movie received ______ reviews from critics who praised its innovative storytelling and outstanding performances. Every major newspaper gave it four or five stars and recommended it highly to their readers.","translation":"這部電影獲得了評論家的好評，他們讚揚了它的創新敘事和傑出表演。每家主要報紙都給了它四顆或五顆星，並強烈推薦給讀者。","word":"favorable"}},"feast":{"createdAt":1781275226788,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"此處feast指「盛宴；筵席」，指隆重而豐盛的聚餐活動","options":["digestion","feast","fume","abroad"],"sentence":"The royal ______ included dozens of dishes, entertainment, and guests from across the kingdom. Everyone celebrated and enjoyed the lavish spread of food and festivities.","translation":"皇家盛宴包括數十道菜餚、娛樂表演和來自整個王國的賓客。每個人都慶祝並享受了這場豐盛的食物和慶典。","word":"feast"}},"feature":{"createdAt":1781703691064,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"feature 作為名詞表示事物的特徵或特點，通常是值得注意或重要的屬性。","options":["defect","feature","price","brand"],"sentence":"The smartphone's most impressive ______ is its advanced camera system. This characteristic has become the main reason why customers choose this particular model over competitors.","translation":"這支智慧型手機最令人印象深刻的特徵是其先進的相機系統。這項優點已成為客戶選擇這款特定型號而不選擇競爭對手產品的主要原因。","word":"feature"}},"fee":{"createdAt":1781850347303,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"費用是指為獲得服務、進入場所或使用設施而必須支付的金錢。","options":["gift","reward","discount","fee"],"sentence":"The bank charged a monthly ______ of fifteen dollars for maintaining the account. Customers who kept a minimum balance could avoid paying this charge.","translation":"銀行為維護該帳戶每月收取十五美元的費用。保持最低餘額的客戶可以避免支付此費用。","word":"fee"}},"feedback":{"createdAt":1781832761709,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"feedback 表示對某人的工作或行為提供的評論、建議或反應。","options":["applause","response","punishment","silence"],"sentence":"After the presentation, the manager gave the team helpful ______ about their performance. The comments included specific suggestions for improvement and praise for what they did well.","translation":"演講結束後，經理對團隊的表現提供了有幫助的回應。評論包括具體的改進建議和對他們做得好的地方的讚揚。","word":"feedback"}},"feminine":{"createdAt":1781841148115,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"feminine 形容詞意思是女性的、女性特質的，用來描述具有女性特點或吸引女性的事物。","options":["masculine","feminine","neutral","bold"],"sentence":"The designer chose soft colors and delicate patterns to create a more ______ aesthetic for the spring collection. The boutique specifically targeted women who appreciated graceful and traditionally womanly design elements.","translation":"設計師選擇了柔和的顏色和精緻的圖案，為春季系列創造更女性化的美學風格。這家精品店特別針對欣賞優雅和傳統女性設計元素的女性。","word":"feminine"}},"fertile":{"createdAt":1781780789959,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"fertile 是形容詞，意為肥沃的、多產的，用於描述適合植物生長的土壤或具有生育能力的生物。","options":["rocky","frozen","fertile","sandy"],"sentence":"The farmer chose to plant his crops in the ______ soil near the river. The land produced an exceptionally abundant harvest year after year.","translation":"農民選擇在河邊肥沃的土壤中種植莊稼。這片土地年復一年地產出異常豐富的收穫。","word":"fertile"}},"fertility":{"createdAt":1781708652661,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fertility 指土壤的肥沃程度，能支持植物生長的能力。","options":["texture","fertility","depth","composition"],"sentence":"The ______ of the soil in this region is exceptional because of the yearly flooding from the river. Farmers here can harvest three crops annually without needing to add any synthetic fertilizers.","translation":"這個地區土壤的生育力是非常出色的，因為每年河流都會泛濫。這裡的農民每年可以收割三次莊稼，而不需要添加任何合成肥料。","word":"fertility"}},"fertilizer":{"createdAt":1781840030397,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fertilizer 是名詞，表示肥料；與「提高產量」和「改善土壤品質」的農業背景相符。","options":["pesticide","fertilizer","water","sunlight"],"sentence":"The farmer applied ______ to his fields to help the crops grow stronger and produce higher yields. The nutrients in this product significantly improved the soil quality.","translation":"農民在田地裡施用肥料以幫助農作物生長得更強壯並提高產量。這個產品中的營養物質大大改善了土壤品質。","word":"fertilizer"}},"fetch":{"createdAt":1781951900950,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fetch指去某個地方拿來某樣東西並帶回來，暗示著一個往返的動作。","options":["chase","fetch","throw","hide"],"sentence":"The dog wagged its tail excitedly when the boy asked it to ______ the ball from across the yard. The animal ran quickly and brought the toy back in its mouth.","translation":"當男孩要求狗去從院子對面拿回球時，狗興奮地搖著尾巴。那隻動物快速奔跑，用嘴叼回了玩具。","word":"fetch"}},"fiber":{"createdAt":1781425122880,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"fiber 指構成物質的細長線狀物，與棉花植物和布料的特性相符。","options":["discount","tournament","fiber","defeat"],"sentence":"The new fabric is made from natural ______ that comes from cotton plants. This material is soft, breathable, and comfortable to wear.","translation":"這種新布料由來自棉花植物的天然纖維製成。這種材料柔軟、透氣，穿著舒適。","word":"fiber"}},"fiction":{"createdAt":1781424574161,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fiction 指虛構的敘述或故事，不是真實發生的事件。","options":["historical","fiction","scientific","political"],"sentence":"She enjoyed reading ______ novels that transported her to imaginary worlds. The stories she loved most were completely made up by the authors' creative minds.","translation":"她喜歡閱讀將她帶入想像世界的小說。她最喜歡的故事完全是由作者的創意想像所創作的。","word":"fiction"}},"fictional":{"createdAt":1781708652663,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fictional 指虛構的、想像出來的、不真實的，常用於描述小說或故事中的角色和情節。","options":["memorable","fictional","popular","mysterious"],"sentence":"Many readers were disappointed to learn that the ______ character they had grown to love would not appear in the author's next book. The author confirmed that this character existed only in her imagination and was never based on a real person.","translation":"許多讀者得知他們喜愛的虛構角色不會出現在這位作者的下一部書中而感到失望。作者確認這個角色只存在於她的想像中，從未以真實人物為基礎。","word":"fictional"}},"fierce":{"createdAt":1781776694537,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"fierce 是形容詞，意思是狂熱的、激烈的，通常用來形容強烈的情感或激烈的衝突。","options":["gentle","quiet","fierce","polite"],"sentence":"The ______ competition between the two companies has resulted in better products and lower prices. Customers benefit greatly from their intense rivalry in the market.","translation":"兩家公司之間的激烈競爭導致了更好的產品和更低的價格。顧客從他們在市場上的激烈競爭中受益匪淺。","word":"fierce"}},"finance":{"createdAt":1781780789960,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"finance 是名詞，意為財務，指與金錢和資金相關的事務和管理。","options":["marketing","production","finance","human resources"],"sentence":"The company hired a new director to manage their ______ department. She was responsible for budgeting, accounting, and investment decisions.","translation":"公司聘請了一位新主任來管理他們的財務部門。她負責預算編製、會計和投資決策。","word":"finance"}},"firecracker":{"createdAt":1781429810251,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"firecracker是指在慶典或節日中點燃的小型爆炸裝置，會發出響亮的聲音。","options":["trustee","firecracker","swift","disappearance"],"sentence":"Children lit a ______ during the New Year celebration, and the sudden explosive sound made everyone jump with excitement. The tradition of setting off these noisemakers dates back centuries.","translation":"孩子們在新年慶祝中點燃了爆竹，突然的爆炸聲讓每個人都興奮地跳了起來。放置這些噪音製造者的傳統可以追溯到幾個世紀前。","word":"firecracker"}},"flake":{"createdAt":1781268630465,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"flake指的是薄片或單個的小片，特別是指雪花或其他細小物質的單個單位。","options":["sheet","flake","layer","blanket"],"sentence":"A ______ of snow fell gently on the windowpane. Each individual crystal was visible before it melted into the glass.","translation":"一片雪花輕輕地落在窗戶玻璃上。每個單獨的冰晶在融化到玻璃中之前都是可見的。","word":"flake"}},"flammable":{"createdAt":1781832478021,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"flammable 意為「易燃的」或「可燃的」，用來描述容易著火的物質或材料。","options":["fragile","flammable","frozen","flexible"],"sentence":"The warehouse manager warned us that we must store all ______ materials in a separate, fireproof room. Gasoline, paint thinner, and other combustible substances require special handling and storage protocols.","translation":"倉庫經理警告我們必須將所有易燃物質存放在單獨的防火室中。汽油、油漆稀釋劑和其他易燃物質需要特殊的處理和儲存程序。","word":"flammable"}},"flat":{"createdAt":1781850347301,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"平坦是形容詞，表示表面光滑無凹凸，沒有高低起伏。","options":["curved","rounded","flat","sloped"],"sentence":"The carpenter carefully sanded the wooden surface until it was completely ______. The table now had no bumps, ridges, or uneven areas at all.","translation":"木匠仔細打磨木製表面，直到它完全平坦。這張桌子現在沒有任何凹凸、隆起或不平整的地方。","word":"flat"}},"flatter":{"createdAt":1781747309099,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"flatter 指用不誠實或過度的恭維來討好某人，目的是獲得利益或好感。","options":["inform","flatter","warn","assist"],"sentence":"He tried to ______ the boss by praising her appearance and complimenting her decisions at every meeting. Though insincere, these hollow words seemed to improve his chances for promotion.","translation":"他試圖通過讚美老闆的外表並在每次會議上恭維她的決定來諂媚她。雖然言不由衷，但這些虛偽的言語似乎改善了他晉升的機會。","word":"flatter"}},"fled":{"createdAt":1781780789956,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"fled 是 flee 的過去式，意為逃跑、逃離，表示某人迅速離開某個地方以躲避危險或追捕。","options":["entered","decorated","fled","repaired"],"sentence":"When the police arrived at the scene, the suspect immediately ______ the building. Officers searched the entire area but could not find him anywhere.","translation":"當警察到達現場時，嫌疑人立即逃離了大樓。警察搜查了整個地區，但找不到他。","word":"fled"}},"flee":{"createdAt":1781481124689,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"flee 意思是緊急地、倉促地離開某個地方，通常是為了躲避危險或不好的情況。","options":["stay","escape","arrive","rebuild"],"sentence":"The refugees had to ______ from the war-torn city before the conflict reached their neighborhood. They packed only essential belongings and left on foot during the night.","translation":"難民必須在衝突到達他們的社區之前從戰爭蹂躪的城市逃離。他們只打包了必要的物品，並在夜間步行離開。","word":"flee"}},"fleeting":{"createdAt":1781884659836,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fleeting 表示持續時間短、轉瞬即逝的，與只有幾週和快速消逝的描述完全吻合。","options":["eternal","fleeting","seasonal","fragrant"],"sentence":"The beauty of cherry blossoms is ______, lasting only a few weeks each spring before they fall to the ground. Tourists rush to see them because this magical season passes so quickly.","translation":"櫻花的美麗是短暫的，每個春天只持續幾週就會掉落到地面。遊客們匆忙前往觀看，因為這個神奇的季節轉瞬即逝。","word":"fleeting"}},"flexible":{"createdAt":1781839703145,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"flexible指有彈性、可調整的，與employees choosing different work options（員工可以選擇不同的工作方式）完全吻合。","options":["rigid","strict","flexible","mandatory"],"sentence":"Our company offers ______ working arrangements to employees. They can choose to work from home, the office, or a combination of both.","translation":"我們公司為員工提供靈活的工作安排。他們可以選擇在家工作、在辦公室工作或兩者結合。","word":"flexible"}},"float":{"createdAt":1781696018687,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"float 意為漂浮，指物體輕輕地浮在液體或空氣中而不下沉。","options":["sink","drift","float","fall"],"sentence":"The balloon began to ______ upward into the sky after the children released it. It gradually disappeared among the clouds within minutes.","translation":"孩子們放開氣球後，它開始向空中漂浮。幾分鐘內它逐漸消失在雲層中。","word":"float"}},"flunk":{"createdAt":1781840030395,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"flunk 是動詞，表示不及格、當掉；與「不及格分數」和「父母失望」的情境相符。","options":["pass","flunk","teach","improve"],"sentence":"Tom studied very little and unfortunately decided to ______ his mathematics exam. His parents were disappointed when he received a failing grade.","translation":"湯姆學習很少，不幸地在數學考試中不及格。當他得到不及格分數時，他的父母很失望。","word":"flunk"}},"following":{"createdAt":1781564440934,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"following 作介詞表示在...之後、接著，指某事發生在另一事件之後。","options":["before","following","during","despite"],"sentence":"The team achieved great success in the competition, and ______ that victory, they received many sponsorship offers. The period right after their achievement brought them numerous opportunities.","translation":"團隊在比賽中取得了巨大成功，在那次勝利之後，他們收到了許多贊助邀請。他們成就之後的時期為他們帶來了許多機會。","word":"following"}},"force":{"createdAt":1781515372606,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"force在這裡指武力或強制力量，用來控制或強迫他人","options":["fulfillment","chief","force","launch"],"sentence":"The government used ______ to disperse the protesters from the street. Police officers arrived with riot gear and physical restraint to control the crowd.","translation":"政府用武力將抗議者從街道上驅散。警察穿著防暴裝備到達現場，用身體約束力來控制人群。","word":"force"}},"forge":{"createdAt":1781843396462,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"forge表示非法偽造或假冒，在此指製造虛假文件以欺騙他人的行為。","options":["create","design","forge","produce"],"sentence":"The criminal was arrested for attempting to ______ government documents. Investigators discovered fake passports and counterfeit certificates in his apartment.","translation":"那名罪犯因試圖偽造政府文件而被逮捕。調查人員在他的公寓裡發現了假護照和偽造證書。","word":"forge"}},"formation":{"createdAt":1781449095515,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"formation意為形成或結構，用來描述事物是如何逐漸發展或組合成最終形態的過程。","options":["destruction","formation","melting","disappearance"],"sentence":"The ______ of the mountain range took millions of years of geological processes. The rocks were slowly shaped by tectonic forces over countless generations.","translation":"山脈的形成花費了數百萬年的地質過程。這些岩石通過數不清的代際中的構造力量慢慢塑造而成。","word":"formation"}},"formerly":{"createdAt":1781780789964,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"formerly 是副詞，意為從前、以前，用於描述過去的狀態或身份，與現在的情況相對比。","options":["currently","formerly","never","recently"],"sentence":"The building ______ served as a prison but was converted into a museum decades ago. Now it attracts thousands of visitors interested in learning about its history.","translation":"這棟建築以前曾用作監獄，但在幾十年前被改建成博物館。現在它吸引了數千名對其歷史感興趣的遊客。","word":"formerly"}},"formula":{"createdAt":1781955529029,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"formula 在這裡指的是製作某物的標準步驟和規則，與科學或商業程序相關。","options":["recipe","formula","strategy","method"],"sentence":"The company uses a secret ______ for making their famous sauce. After years of research, they finally discovered the exact combination of ingredients and steps that creates the perfect taste.","translation":"該公司使用祕密公式來製作他們著名的醬汁。經過多年的研究，他們終於發現了製造完美味道的確切成分和步驟組合。","word":"formula"}},"forth":{"createdAt":1781581925132,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"forth 作為副詞表示向前出發、外出或離開某地，常用於「set forth」表示開始旅程。","options":["back","forth","ahead","away"],"sentence":"The explorer set ______ on a journey into the Amazon rainforest to discover new species. He packed his equipment and left the village at dawn, determined to venture deep into the jungle.","translation":"探險家出發進入亞馬遜雨林，尋求發現新物種。他打好行裝，在黎明時分離開村莊，決心深入叢林探險。","word":"forth"}},"fortify":{"createdAt":1781693295123,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"fortify 意為加強或增強，在此指運動對免疫系統的強化作用。","options":["weaken","confuse","fortify","document"],"sentence":"Regular exercise can ______ your immune system and help you stay healthy. Studies show that people who exercise frequently get sick less often than sedentary individuals.","translation":"定期運動可以增強你的免疫系統並幫助你保持健康。研究顯示經常運動的人比久坐不動的人生病次數更少。","word":"fortify"}},"fortunate":{"createdAt":1781437528476,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fortunate 形容幸運的、僥倖的，指運氣好或經歷了好的結果。","options":["careless","fortunate","unfortunate","careful"],"sentence":"We felt very ______ to survive the car accident with only minor injuries. Many similar crashes result in serious harm, so we consider ourselves incredibly lucky to have walked away.","translation":"我們感到非常幸運在車禍中只受了輕傷。許多類似的撞車事故導致嚴重傷害，所以我們認為自己能夠安全脫離是不可思議的幸運。","word":"fortunate"}},"fossil":{"createdAt":1781311922073,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fossil 是指遠古生物的遺骨或遺跡經過地質作用保存在岩石中形成的。","options":["bone","fossil","skeleton","artifact"],"sentence":"The museum displayed a 200-million-year-old ______ of a prehistoric dinosaur in the main exhibition hall. Scientists carefully studied the preserved remains to learn about ancient life on Earth.","translation":"博物館在主展廳展示了一個2億年前的史前恐龍化石。科學家仔細研究了這些保存下來的遺骸，以了解地球上的古代生命。","word":"fossil"}},"fountain":{"createdAt":1781708652663,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fountain 指噴出水的裝置或建築物，通常在公共場所用來裝飾和娛樂。","options":["statue","fountain","bridge","monument"],"sentence":"The ______ in the town square sprayed water high into the air, creating a beautiful display. Children ran around it laughing and trying to catch the droplets on hot summer days.","translation":"城鎮廣場上的噴泉將水噴向空中，創造出美麗的景象。在炎熱的夏日，孩子們在周圍跑動、歡笑，試圖接住水滴。","word":"fountain"}},"fowl":{"createdAt":1781532967166,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fowl 指家禽（雞、鴨等），與「生產雞蛋和肉類」和「鳥類」的描述相符。","options":["fish","fowl","cattle","sheep"],"sentence":"The farmer kept several ______ in the barnyard to produce eggs and meat. These birds were essential to his rural lifestyle.","translation":"農民在谷倉院子裡飼養了幾隻______(家禽)以生產雞蛋和肉類。這些鳥類對他的鄉村生活至關重要。","word":"fowl"}},"fraction":{"createdAt":1782006648204,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fraction 在這裡指的是極小的部分或比例，強調數量非常少。","options":["portion","fraction","majority","section"],"sentence":"Only a ______ of the student body attended the optional weekend workshop. Specifically, fewer than five percent of the enrolled students showed up.","translation":"只有一小部分學生參加了可選的週末工作坊。具體來說，少於百分之五的註冊學生出席了。","word":"fraction"}},"fragile":{"createdAt":1781478568760,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fragile 用來形容容易破損或脆弱的東西，通常需要特別小心對待。","options":["durable","fragile","ornate","valuable"],"sentence":"The antique vase is extremely ______ and must be handled with great care. The slightest bump could cause it to shatter into pieces.","translation":"這個古董花瓶極其易碎，必須小心輕放。最輕微的碰撞都可能導致它破裂成碎片。","word":"fragile"}},"fragment":{"createdAt":1782006648203,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"fragment 指的是破碎後的小碎片或殘片，通常無法單獨成為完整的物體。","options":["fragment","theory","memory","document"],"sentence":"After the explosion, investigators carefully collected every ______ of evidence from the scene. Each piece of debris was catalogued and analyzed to reconstruct what happened.","translation":"爆炸後，調查人員仔細收集現場的每一個碎片證據。每一塊碎片都被編目和分析以重建發生的情況。","word":"fragment"}},"fragrance":{"createdAt":1781780789966,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fragrance 是名詞，意為香氣、芳香，指令人愉悅的氣味或香味。","options":["noise","fragrance","darkness","weight"],"sentence":"The beautiful rose garden filled the air with a delicate ______ that attracted butterflies and bees. Visitors could smell the sweet scent from across the park.","translation":"美麗的玫瑰園充滿了精緻的香氣，吸引了蝴蝶和蜜蜂。遊客可以從公園的另一端聞到甜蜜的氣味。","word":"fragrance"}},"fragrant":{"createdAt":1781708652660,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fragrant 指散發出宜人香氣的，與甜蜜的香氣相對應。","options":["colorful","fragrant","delicate","wilting"],"sentence":"The ______ flowers in the garden attracted many bees and butterflies. The sweet aroma was so strong that visitors could smell it from across the entire neighborhood.","translation":"花園裡的芬芳花朵吸引了許多蜜蜂和蝴蝶。這種甜蜜的香氣非常濃烈，訪客從整個鄰里的另一邊都能聞到它。","word":"fragrant"}},"frame":{"createdAt":1781708652666,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"frame 指建築物的框架或骨架，是支撐整個結構的主要構件。","options":["decoration","exterior","frame","roof"],"sentence":"The wooden ______ of the old house was damaged by termites and had to be completely replaced. Without the supporting beams and structural components, the walls could not stand properly.","translation":"老房子的木製框架被白蟻破壞，必須完全更換。沒有支撐梁和結構部件，牆壁無法正確站立。","word":"frame"}},"frantic":{"createdAt":1781850347302,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"發狂似的或情緒失控的是形容詞，表示極度焦急、緊張或狂亂的狀態。","options":["leisurely","careful","frantic","organized"],"sentence":"The mother's ______ search for her lost child lasted for hours through the crowded shopping mall. Her hands were shaking and her voice was trembling with panic.","translation":"母親在擁擠的購物中心發狂似地搜索她失散的孩子持續了好幾個小時。她的手在顫抖，她的聲音因恐慌而顫動。","word":"frantic"}},"freeway":{"createdAt":1781787229322,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"freeway 指的是沒有紅綠燈、高速的多車道道路，用於長距離運輸。","options":["bridge","freeway","parking lot","intersection"],"sentence":"During rush hour, traffic on the ______ moved slowly despite the lack of traffic lights. The highway's multiple lanes allowed cars to bypass city streets entirely.","translation":"在尖峰時段，儘管沒有紅綠燈，高速公路上的交通仍然緩慢移動。這條公路的多條車道讓汽車能夠完全繞過城市街道。","word":"freeway"}},"freight":{"createdAt":1781832478024,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"freight 意為「貨物」或「貨運」，通常指通過運輸方式（如卡車、火車、船舶）大量運送的商品。","options":["passengers","freight","equipment","luggage"],"sentence":"The truck was carrying heavy ______ across the country on a long-haul delivery. The cargo included machinery, textiles, and other goods destined for warehouses across the nation.","translation":"這輛卡車在長途運輸中跨越全國運送重貨。貨物包括機械、紡織品和其他運往全國各地倉庫的商品。","word":"freight"}},"fright":{"createdAt":1781783820687,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"fright指的是突然的、令人感到害怕或驚嚇的感覺，通常是由於出乎意料的事件引起的。","options":["fright","joy","surprise","anger"],"sentence":"The sudden loud noise gave me quite a ______ while I was working alone in the office. It took me several minutes to calm down and realize it was just the printer malfunctioning.","translation":"當我獨自在辦公室工作時，突然的巨大噪音嚇了我一跳。我花了幾分鐘才平靜下來，意識到那只是印表機故障。","word":"fright"}},"frontier":{"createdAt":1781481124703,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"frontier 指未被開發或人煙稀少的邊遠地區，通常指國家的邊界地帶。","options":["city","capital","border region","coast"],"sentence":"The pioneers ventured into the ______ to settle new territories and build their communities. They crossed vast wilderness areas that had never been explored before.","translation":"開拓者們冒險進入邊疆以開闢新領土並建立他們的社區。他們穿越了從未被探索過的廣闊荒野地區。","word":"frontier"}},"froze":{"createdAt":1781532967165,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"froze 表示呆住、僵住，與「無法移動或尖叫」的描述相符。","options":["ran","froze","laughed","danced"],"sentence":"When the burglar suddenly appeared in the dark hallway, she ______ in absolute terror. She could not move or scream at that moment.","translation":"當竊賊突然出現在黑暗的走廊裡時，她因絕對恐懼而______(呆住)。她在那一刻無法移動或尖叫。","word":"froze"}},"frugal":{"createdAt":1781531595651,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"frugal 表示節約的、儉樸的，指在花費金錢時精打細算，不浪費。","options":["luxurious","lavish","frugal","extravagant"],"sentence":"Despite earning a high salary, he maintained a ______ lifestyle and avoided unnecessary spending. His modest apartment and secondhand furniture reflected his commitment to saving money.","translation":"儘管收入很高，他卻保持著節約的生活方式，避免不必要的開支。他樸素的公寓和二手傢具反映了他對存錢的承諾。","word":"frugal"}},"frustrate":{"createdAt":1781651775061,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"frustrate 意為讓人感到沮喪、挫折或被阻止達成目標。","options":["justify","discussion","frustrate","childhood"],"sentence":"The repeated delays began to ______ the entire team. Everyone felt angry and disappointed because their hard work seemed to be blocked at every turn.","translation":"反覆的延誤開始挫敗整個團隊。每個人都感到憤怒和失望，因為他們的辛苦工作似乎在每一步都被阻擾。","word":"frustrate"}},"frustration":{"createdAt":1781425024019,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"frustration是指因無法達成目標或反覆失敗而產生的挫敗感、沮喪感和煩悶情緒。","options":["joy","frustration","excitement","confidence"],"sentence":"After failing the exam for the third time, he felt overwhelming ______ and seriously questioned his abilities. His repeated disappointments had left him feeling defeated and uncertain about his future.","translation":"第三次考試不及格後，他感到壓倒性的挫敗感，並認真質疑自己的能力。他一次次的失望讓他感到沮喪和對未來的不確定。","word":"frustration"}},"fuel":{"createdAt":1781837601403,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fuel 作為動詞表示「激起」或「促進」，指提供能量或動力使某事物增長或加強。","options":["dampen","fuel","question","delay"],"sentence":"The environmental activist's passionate speech about climate change continued to ______ the students' determination to take action. Her inspiring words motivated them to organize a recycling campaign at school.","translation":"那位環保活動人士關於氣候變化的熱情演講繼續激起學生採取行動的決心。她鼓舞人心的話語激勵他們在學校組織回收活動。","word":"fuel"}},"fulfill":{"createdAt":1781425737121,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"fulfill 表示實現、完成或履行承諾和義務，與完成所有工作相符。","options":["fulfill","ignore","delay","avoid"],"sentence":"She promised to ______ all her responsibilities before leaving for vacation. Her supervisor confirmed that every project deadline and task requirement will be completed by Friday.","translation":"她承諾在休假前完成所有責任。她的主管確認每個專案截止日期和任務要求都會在星期五前完成。","word":"fulfill"}},"fulfillment":{"createdAt":1781515372607,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"fulfillment指實現自我或完成目標後所獲得的成就感和滿足感","options":["chief","launch","force","fulfillment"],"sentence":"She found great ______ in volunteering at the local shelter every weekend. The sense of purpose and satisfaction from helping others brought her genuine happiness.","translation":"她在每個週末在當地收容所做志工中找到了巨大的成就感。幫助他人帶來的目標感和滿足感給她帶來了真正的幸福。","word":"fulfillment"}},"fume":{"createdAt":1781275226788,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"此處fume作動詞表示「發怒；生悶氣」，通常指內心的不滿","options":["dazzle","include","fume","breast"],"sentence":"She began to ______ when she discovered her coworker had taken credit for her project. Her anger only grew as she realized the unfairness of the situation.","translation":"當她發現同事竊取她的項目成果時，她開始生悶氣。當她意識到這種不公平時，她的憤怒更加增長。","word":"fume"}},"functional":{"createdAt":1781323901183,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"functional意為「正常工作的」或「實用的」，在此指電腦的所有功能都能正常運作。","options":["broken","obsolete","functional","decorative"],"sentence":"Although the old computer looks worn, it remains completely ______. Every program runs smoothly and all hardware components respond normally.","translation":"雖然這台舊電腦看起來磨損了，但它仍然完全正常工作。每個程序運行順暢，所有硬件組件都反應正常。","word":"functional"}},"fund":{"createdAt":1781449095509,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"fund作為動詞意為提供資金或籌集經費，用來支持某個項目或計畫。","options":["close","fund","ignore","demolish"],"sentence":"The non-profit organization needed to ______ their new community center project. They launched a fundraising campaign to collect donations from local businesses.","translation":"非營利組織需要為他們的新社區中心項目提供資金。他們發起了募款活動以從本地企業籌集捐款。","word":"fund"}},"fundamental":{"createdAt":1781832478023,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"fundamental 意為「基礎的」或「根本的」，用來形容最基本、最重要、不可或缺的事物。","options":["advanced","optional","fundamental","temporary"],"sentence":"Learning to read and write is a ______ skill that all students must master. Without these basic abilities, it's nearly impossible to succeed in any other academic subject.","translation":"學習閱讀和寫作是所有學生必須掌握的基礎技能。沒有這些基本能力，在任何其他學術科目中都幾乎不可能成功。","word":"fundamental"}},"furiously":{"createdAt":1781626081101,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"furiously 作為副詞表示以激烈、狂暴或極具力量的方式進行某個動作，通常帶有強烈的情感或急迫感。","options":["lazily","slowly","furiously","calmly"],"sentence":"He worked ______ throughout the night to meet the deadline. His intense energy and rapid pace showed his desperation to finish the project before dawn.","translation":"他整晚狂怒地工作以趕上截止日期。他激烈的精力和快速的步伐顯示了他在天亮前完成項目的迫切性。","word":"furiously"}},"furniture":{"createdAt":1781886743284,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"Furniture 特指可移動的家居用品，如椅子、桌子、床等，用於室內陳設和日常生活。","options":["decorations","fixtures","furniture","appliances"],"sentence":"The living room needed new ______ after the old pieces became worn and broken. The family decided to buy a sofa, armchairs, and a coffee table to fill the space.","translation":"客廳需要新的家具，因為舊的家具已經破舊損壞。家人決定買沙發、扶手椅和咖啡桌來填滿這個空間。","word":"furniture"}},"galaxy":{"createdAt":1781850347302,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"星系是指由數十億顆恆星、行星、氣體和塵埃組成的龐大天體系統。","options":["planet","meteor","galaxy","nebula"],"sentence":"The ______ containing billions of stars stretched across the night sky in a magnificent spiral pattern. Astronomers estimated it was over 100,000 light-years in diameter.","translation":"包含數十億顆恆星的星系以壯麗的螺旋形式跨越夜空。天文學家估計其直徑超過十萬光年。","word":"galaxy"}},"gallery":{"createdAt":1781531595652,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"gallery 是指展示藝術品的場所，特別是展示繪畫、雕塑等視覺藝術的地方。","options":["museum","gallery","theater","library"],"sentence":"The art ______ opened a new exhibition featuring paintings by contemporary artists. Visitors lined up outside to view the masterpieces displayed on the white walls.","translation":"畫廊開設了一場新展覽，展出當代藝術家的繪畫作品。遊客排隊進入以欣賞展示在白色牆壁上的傑作。","word":"gallery"}},"gang":{"createdAt":1781653278519,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"gang是名詞，表示群伙或成群結隊的人，可以指任何聚集在一起的群體，無論是友善的或不友善的。","options":["single","gang","pair","duo"],"sentence":"A ______ of teenagers gathered at the park every evening to play basketball together. Their coach recognized them as a dedicated group of friends who helped each other improve.","translation":"一______青少年每天晚上聚集在公園裡一起打籃球。他們的教練認出他們是一群致力於互相幫助進步的朋友。","word":"gang"}},"garment":{"createdAt":1781693275430,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"服裝是指穿在身上的衣服和衣著物品，包括各種類型的衣服如連衣裙、襯衫或外套等。","options":["accessory","fabric","garment","decoration"],"sentence":"She bought an elegant ______ at the boutique for the wedding ceremony. The silk dress was carefully tailored and cost over a thousand dollars.","translation":"她在精品店為婚禮購買了一件優雅的服裝。這件絲綢連衣裙經過精心裁製，花費超過一千元。","word":"garment"}},"gather":{"createdAt":1781402539338,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"gather 作動詞表示收集、聚集或整合來自不同來源的信息或物品。","options":["ignore","gather","create","lose"],"sentence":"The volunteers will ______ information about the problem from community members. They plan to conduct surveys and interviews over the next month.","translation":"志願者將從社區成員那裡收集關於該問題的信息。他們計畫在下個月進行調查和訪談。","word":"gather"}},"gathering":{"createdAt":1781848934149,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"gathering指多人為了某個目的集合在一起的聚會或集會","options":["complaint","gathering","lawsuit","accident"],"sentence":"The family ______ was held at grandmother's house every summer. Cousins, aunts, and uncles came from all over to celebrate together.","translation":"家庭聚會每個夏天都在奶奶家舉行。表親、阿姨和叔叔從四面八方來慶祝。","word":"gathering"}},"gaze":{"createdAt":1781842254307,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"gaze 表示長時間注視或凝視，通常帶有沉思或欣賞的情感，比 stare 更溫和，比 glance 的持續時間更長。","options":["ignore","gaze","glance","stare"],"sentence":"She couldn't help but ______ at the beautiful sunset over the ocean. Her eyes remained fixed on the horizon for nearly an hour without blinking.","translation":"她忍不住注視著海洋上美麗的日落。她的眼睛在將近一個小時內一直固定在地平線上，沒有眨眼。","word":"gaze"}},"gear":{"createdAt":1781581925133,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"gear 作為名詞表示特定用途的裝備、工具或衣服，尤其是用於某項活動或工作的專門配件。","options":["supplies","gear","luggage","baggage"],"sentence":"The mountain climber packed all the necessary ______ including ropes, harnesses, and carabiners for the expedition. She carefully checked each piece of equipment to ensure safety during the ascent.","translation":"登山者為遠征打包了所有必要的裝備，包括繩索、安全帶和快速掛鉤。她仔細檢查了每件設備以確保登山時的安全。","word":"gear"}},"gender":{"createdAt":1781839950963,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"gender 指的是一個人的性別身份,通常包括男性、女性或其他性別認同。","options":["age","name","gender","education"],"sentence":"The survey asked each participant to indicate their ______ in the demographic section. The results showed that 55% of respondents identified as female and 45% as male.","translation":"調查要求每位參與者在人口統計部分註明他們的性別。結果顯示55%的受訪者認同女性身份,45%認同男性身份。","word":"gender"}},"general":{"createdAt":1781836375375,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"general作名詞表示陸軍最高軍銜之一，擁有指揮大規模軍事單位的權力。","options":["major","general","officer","commander"],"sentence":"The ______ led his troops into battle with great strategic skill and courage. His military rank and experience commanded respect from all his soldiers.","translation":"將軍以高超的戰略技巧和勇氣帶領他的部隊進入戰鬥。他的軍銜和經驗獲得了所有士兵的尊重。","word":"general"}},"generally":{"createdAt":1781515329269,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"generally 副詞，意思是通常、一般地，表示大多數情況或廣泛的趨勢。","options":["Rarely","Generally","Specifically","Occasionally"],"sentence":"______, people prefer to visit the beach during summer vacation rather than winter. Statistics show that beach tourism peaks in the warmest months of the year.","translation":"一般來說，人們在暑假期間更喜歡去海灘而不是冬天。統計數據顯示，海灘旅遊在一年中最溫暖的月份達到高峰。","word":"generally"}},"generation":{"createdAt":1781951900944,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"generation在這裡指的是同時代出生並經歷相似事件的人群，而不是指製造或創作的過程。","options":["production","generation","creation","invention"],"sentence":"The invention of the smartphone created a new ______ of technology users. Young people who grew up with mobile devices think very differently from their parents.","translation":"智慧型手機的發明創造了新一代的科技使用者。從小就接觸行動設備的年輕人的想法與他們的父母截然不同。","word":"generation"}},"generosity":{"createdAt":1781709854482,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"generosity（慷慨）指無私地給予和幫助他人，與donate millions（捐獻數百萬）和willingness to help（幫助他人的意願）相呼應。","options":["stinginess","kindness","generosity","modesty"],"sentence":"The billionaire's ______ was evident when he donated millions to the children's hospital. His action showed genuine compassion and a willingness to help those in need.","translation":"這位億萬富翁的慷慨在他向兒童醫院捐獻數百萬美元時顯而易見。他的行動展現了真誠的同情心和幫助有需要的人的意願。","word":"generosity"}},"genius":{"createdAt":1781484415219,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"genius是指具有卓越才能和異常聰慧的人，在某個領域展現出非凡的成就。","options":["student","conductor","genius","critic"],"sentence":"Mozart was a musical ______ who composed his first symphony at the age of eight. His extraordinary talent and natural ability set him apart from ordinary musicians.","translation":"莫札特是一位音樂天才，在八歲時創作了他的第一部交響樂。他的非凡才能和天生的能力使他與普通音樂家不同。","word":"genius"}},"giggle":{"createdAt":1781331945988,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"giggle 指輕聲或斷斷續續地笑，通常是因為覺得有趣或感到害羞。","options":["giggle","cry","sleep","leave"],"sentence":"The children couldn't help but ______ when the clown made funny faces at them. Their laughter filled the entire room with joy and amusement.","translation":"當小丑對孩子們做鬼臉時，他們忍不住咯咯笑起來。他們的笑聲讓整個房間充滿了歡樂和娛樂。","word":"giggle"}},"glamor":{"createdAt":1781794866351,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"glamor指吸引力、魅力或誘惑力，特別是指華麗迷人但常帶有虛幻成分的外表。","options":["plainness","glamor","simplicity","ordinariness"],"sentence":"Hollywood movies often emphasize the ______ of celebrity life with red carpets and luxury cars. However, the reality behind the scenes is often quite different from what audiences see on screen.","translation":"好萊塢電影經常強調名人生活的______ ，包括紅地毯和豪車。然而，幕後的現實往往與觀眾在螢幕上看到的大不相同。","word":"glamor"}},"glamorous":{"createdAt":1781842254314,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"glamorous 表示迷人的、富有魅力的、光彩照人的，通常用來形容具有吸引力和優雅風度的人或事物。","options":["ordinary","glamorous","plain","timid"],"sentence":"The ______ movie star arrived at the red carpet event wearing a designer gown and sparkling diamonds. Photographers crowded around her, captivated by her stunning appearance and radiant charm.","translation":"這位迷人的電影明星穿著設計師禮服和閃閃發光的鑽石出現在紅毯活動上。攝影師聚集在她周圍，被她的驚人外表和光彩照人的魅力所吸引。","word":"glamorous"}},"glide":{"createdAt":1781417610414,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"glide是指光滑、流暢地滑動，通常帶有輕鬆優雅的感覺。","options":["jump","stumble","glide","sprint"],"sentence":"The ice skater began to ______ gracefully across the frozen pond. Her smooth movements required years of practice to master the technique of sliding without friction.","translation":"這位溜冰者開始在結冰的池塘上優雅地滑行。她流暢的動作需要多年的練習才能掌握無摩擦滑行的技巧。","word":"glide"}},"glimpse":{"createdAt":1781493458243,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"glimpse 名詞指短暫或不完整的看一眼，強調時間短暫和視野受限","options":["conversation","glimpse","interview","meeting"],"sentence":"I caught only a brief ______ of the celebrity as she rushed past the crowd. My view lasted just a few seconds before she disappeared around the corner.","translation":"當名人匆匆走過人群時，我只瞥見了她一眼。我的視線只持續了幾秒鐘，她就消失在街角了。","word":"glimpse"}},"global":{"createdAt":1781784283023,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"global是形容詞，表示涉及世界各地的，與全球性相關的；在這個句子中強調公司在多個大陸的國際業務範圍。","options":["local","global","regional","domestic"],"sentence":"The company has expanded its operations to become a ______ enterprise with offices on every continent. Their influence now extends across North America, Europe, Asia, Africa, and Australia.","translation":"該公司已擴展業務成為一家______ 企業，在每個大陸都設有辦事處。他們的影響力現在延伸到北美、歐洲、亞洲、非洲和澳洲。","word":"global"}},"glorify":{"createdAt":1781449588288,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"glorify作為動詞表示「美化、讚頌、把…理想化」，指以過度正面或不準確的方式描繪某人或某事物。","options":["sensibly","signify","glorify","improve"],"sentence":"The documentary was criticized for attempting to ______ the actions of a controversial historical figure rather than presenting a balanced perspective. The filmmaker's portrayal emphasized heroic qualities while downplaying serious moral failings and harmful consequences.","translation":"這部紀錄片因試圖美化一位有爭議的歷史人物的行為而受到批評，而不是呈現平衡的觀點。電影製作人的描繪強調了英雄品質，同時淡化了嚴重的道德缺陷和有害後果。","word":"glorify"}},"glorious":{"createdAt":1781840030398,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"glorious 是形容詞，表示光榮的、壯麗的；與「令人驚嘆」和「壯麗的自然景觀」相呼應。","options":["dim","glorious","cloudy","ordinary"],"sentence":"The ______ sunset painted the sky in shades of orange, pink, and gold, creating a breathtaking view. Everyone stopped to admire the magnificent natural display that evening.","translation":"光榮燦爛的日落將天空染成橙色、粉紅色和金色，創造了令人驚嘆的景象。那天晚上每個人都停下來欣賞這壯麗的自然景觀。","word":"glorious"}},"goods":{"createdAt":1781693275430,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"商品是指用於買賣或交易的物品和貨物，特別是具有商業價值的物質產品。","options":["people","information","goods","animals"],"sentence":"The merchant transported ______ from China to Europe along the ancient Silk Road. These products included silk, spices, and porcelain that were highly valued in Western markets.","translation":"商人沿著古代絲綢之路將商品從中國運往歐洲。這些產品包括在西方市場中備受推崇的絲綢、香料和瓷器。","word":"goods"}},"gossip":{"createdAt":1781401591590,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"gossip 作為動詞，意思是說別人的閒話或八卦，通常涉及傳播他人的祕密或私人信息。","options":["complain","gossip","whisper","celebrate"],"sentence":"The two friends love to ______ about their coworkers during lunch breaks. They share secrets and personal stories that they've heard from others around the office.","translation":"這兩個朋友喜歡在午餐時間說同事的閒話。他們分享從辦公室裡其他人那裡聽到的祕密和個人故事。","word":"gossip"}},"gown":{"createdAt":1781484415211,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"gown是指正式場合穿著的長禮服，通常用於重要活動如婚禮或宴會。","options":["jeans","gown","jacket","scarf"],"sentence":"The bride looked stunning in her white silk ______ as she walked down the aisle. The formal dress was elegantly designed with intricate lace details throughout.","translation":"新娘穿著白色絲綢禮服走下紅毯時看起來令人驚艷。這件正式的長衣優雅地設計，通篇都有複雜的蕾絲細節。","word":"gown"}},"grace":{"createdAt":1781713470386,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"優美的風度是指行為舉止中所展現的優雅和精緻的品質。","options":["anger","grace","haste","confusion"],"sentence":"The ballet dancer moved across the stage with remarkable ______, captivating the entire audience. Her elegant movements and refined posture demonstrated years of professional training.","translation":"芭蕾舞者以非凡的優美姿態在舞台上移動，迷住了整個觀眾。她優雅的動作和精緻的姿態展現了多年的專業訓練。","word":"grace"}},"grain":{"createdAt":1781950727562,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"grain 指穀物或穀粒，如小麥、玉米、水稻等。","options":["metal","grain","fabric","equipment"],"sentence":"Farmers harvested tons of ______ from the fields this season. The wheat, barley, and corn were stored in silos for future use.","translation":"農民今年從田地中收穫了大量穀物。小麥、大麥和玉米被儲存在筒倉中供日後使用。","word":"grain"}},"grant":{"createdAt":1781345237575,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"grant作動詞表示「給予」或「授予」，通常用於正式或官方的贈與行為。","options":["deny","grant","refuse","withhold"],"sentence":"The government decided to ______ the organization a substantial amount of funding for their research project. The money was officially awarded in a formal ceremony last month.","translation":"政府決定向該組織授予大筆資金用於他們的研究項目。該筆款項在上個月的正式儀式上正式撥款。","word":"grant"}},"graph":{"createdAt":1781566055844,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"graph 是一種視覺化數據的工具，用坐標軸、曲線或其他圖形元素來表示數據之間的關係。","options":["report","graph","theory","conclusion"],"sentence":"The scientist presented a ______ showing the relationship between temperature and plant growth. The data points were plotted on both x and y axes to visualize the trend.","translation":"科學家展示了一張圖表，顯示溫度與植物生長之間的關係。數據點被繪製在 x 軸和 y 軸上以視覺化趨勢。","word":"graph"}},"grasp":{"createdAt":1781926370998,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"grasp 在這裡意思是理解、領悟，指通過努力和思考來掌握知識或概念。","options":["avoid","ignore","grasp","reject"],"sentence":"The student struggled to ______ the complex mathematical concept during the lecture. Only after reviewing the textbook three times did she finally understand it completely.","translation":"這名學生在講座中很難領悟這個複雜的數學概念。直到她複習了三次教科書後，她才最終完全理解了它。","word":"grasp"}},"gratitude":{"createdAt":1781425024019,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"gratitude是指感謝之心、感激之情，通常在受到幫助或善待後表達對他人的感謝。","options":["anger","gratitude","confusion","sorrow"],"sentence":"She expressed her ______ by baking homemade cookies for her neighbor who had helped her move. The thoughtful gesture showed how deeply she appreciated his kindness and support.","translation":"她通過為幫助她搬家的鄰居烘烤自製餅乾來表達她的感謝。這個貼心的舉動表明她對他的善良和支持的深深感激。","word":"gratitude"}},"grave":{"createdAt":1781693265627,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"墳墓是指埋葬死者的地點，通常在墓地中。","options":["school","grave","office","restaurant"],"sentence":"The elderly couple visited their late son's ______ every Sunday with fresh flowers. They spent time reflecting on cherished memories at the cemetery.","translation":"這對老夫婦每個星期天都會帶著鮮花去已故兒子的墳墓。他們在墓地花時間回憶珍貴的回憶。","word":"grave"}},"graze":{"createdAt":1781693271587,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"graze指的是牲畜在草地上邊走邊吃草，是一種典型的放牧行為，與奔跑或衝刺的動作完全不同。","options":["gallop","graze","sprint","charge"],"sentence":"The shepherd watched his sheep ______ peacefully in the meadow all afternoon. The animals slowly moved around eating grass from the field without any herding needed.","translation":"牧羊人整個下午都在觀看他的羊在草地上安靜地吃草。這些動物緩慢地四處走動，從田野裡吃草，不需要任何驅趕。","word":"graze"}},"grease":{"createdAt":1781515329265,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"grease 名詞，意思是油脂、油膩狀物，指機械或食物中的油性物質。","options":["dust","grease","water","rust"],"sentence":"The mechanic wiped away the excess ______ from the engine with an old cloth. The thick, oily substance had accumulated over months of regular use and needed cleaning.","translation":"機修工用一塊舊布擦去引擎上多餘的油脂。這種厚重的油膩物質經過數月的定期使用已經積累，需要清潔。","word":"grease"}},"greasy":{"createdAt":1781566460881,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"greasy形容充滿油脂或油膩的食物質感，與手指上留下殘留物和需要擦拭相符。","options":["dry","fresh","greasy","crispy"],"sentence":"The pizza was covered in a thick layer of ______ cheese that left residue on our fingers. We needed napkins to wipe off the oily coating.","translation":"披薩上覆蓋著一層厚厚的油膩起司，在我們的手指上留下了殘留物。我們需要餐巾紙來擦掉油膩的塗層。","word":"greasy"}},"grieve":{"createdAt":1781418481460,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"grieve作為動詞，表示因失去某人或某事而感到深深的悲傷和哀慟。","options":["celebrate","grieve","organize","appreciate"],"sentence":"The family continued to ______ over the loss of their beloved grandmother. They spent weeks mourning at home and attending memorial services.","translation":"這個家庭因失去親愛的祖母而繼續悲傷。他們花了數週在家中哀悼並參加追思會。","word":"grieve"}},"guarantee":{"createdAt":1781566460881,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"guarantee是一份正式的保證或擔保書，用來保護購買者的權益。","options":["receipt","guarantee","invoice","license"],"sentence":"The car manufacturer offers a five-year ______ on all engine parts. This written promise protects customers if any defects appear.","translation":"汽車製造商對所有引擎零件提供五年的保證。這份書面承諾在出現任何缺陷時保護客戶。","word":"guarantee"}},"habitual":{"createdAt":1781484415234,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"habitual意指習慣性的或通常的，表示經常重複發生的行為或傾向。","options":["occasional","rare","habitual","sudden"],"sentence":"His ______ tardiness had become a serious problem at work, and his boss finally gave him a warning. He arrived late to meetings almost every single day without fail.","translation":"他習慣性的遲到已經成為工作中的一個嚴重問題，他的老闆最終給了他一個警告。他幾乎每天都毫無例外地遲到開會。","word":"habitual"}},"handicap":{"createdAt":1781451343287,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"障礙是指阻止或延遲進展的因素，表示一個人必須克服的困難或缺陷。","options":["advantage","achievement","handicap","skill"],"sentence":"His lack of formal education was a significant ______ in his career advancement. However, through determination and self-study, he managed to overcome this limitation and achieve success.","translation":"他缺乏正規教育是他職業發展中的一個重大障礙。然而，通過決心和自學，他設法克服了這一限制並取得了成功。","word":"handicap"}},"handicraft":{"createdAt":1781920819165,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"handicraft 意為「手工藝；手工藝品」，指用手工製作的藝術品或實用物品，強調手工製作的過程。","options":["machinery","artwork","fabric","jewelry"],"sentence":"She sold her beautiful ______ at the local market every weekend to earn extra income. Each piece was painstakingly created by hand using traditional techniques passed down through generations.","translation":"她每個週末都在當地市集販售她美麗的手工藝品來賺取額外收入。每件作品都是用祖傳的傳統技術精心手工製作而成的。","word":"handicraft"}},"hardship":{"createdAt":1781871338561,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"hardship表示困難、艱辛或痛苦的經歷，與戰爭、飢餓等負面情況相關。","options":["luxury","convenience","prosperity","adversity"],"sentence":"Despite facing considerable ______ during the war, the family never lost hope for a better future. They endured hunger, displacement, and loss with remarkable resilience.","translation":"儘管在戰爭期間面臨相當大的困難，這家人從未失去對美好未來的希望。他們以非凡的韌性承受了飢餓、流離失所和喪失。","word":"hardship"}},"harmful":{"createdAt":1781532967169,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"harmful 表示有害的，與「造成嚴重疾病」和「危險習慣」的描述相符。","options":["beneficial","harmful","neutral","helpful"],"sentence":"Smoking cigarettes is very ______ to your health and can cause serious diseases. Doctors strongly advise people to quit this dangerous habit.","translation":"吸煙對你的健康______(有害)，可能導致嚴重疾病。醫生強烈建議人們戒掉這個危險的習慣。","word":"harmful"}},"harmonious":{"createdAt":1781437013476,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"harmonious 形容事物協調一致、和睦融洽的狀態，特別是指沒有衝突和爭執的關係。","options":["competitive","chaotic","harmonious","isolated"],"sentence":"The community garden created a ______ environment where neighbors from different backgrounds worked together peacefully. Volunteers from various ethnic groups collaborated on planting and harvesting without any conflicts.","translation":"社區花園創造了一個和諧的環境，來自不同背景的鄰居和平地一起工作。來自各個民族的志願者在種植和收穫過程中毫無衝突地合作。","word":"harmonious"}},"harmony":{"createdAt":1781667024984,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"harmony是指各部分協調一致的狀態，在音樂中指不同聲部的和諧配合。","options":["melody","harmony","rhythm","tempo"],"sentence":"The orchestra played in perfect ______ with each instrument blending beautifully. The conductor praised the musicians for their ability to work together without any conflicting sounds.","translation":"樂隊以完美的協調演奏，每件樂器都融合得很好。指揮讚揚了音樂家能夠一起工作而沒有任何不協調聲音的能力。","word":"harmony"}},"harsh":{"createdAt":1781798927525,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"harsh 形容言詞或態度嚴厲、刺耳或令人不快，帶有冷酷的質感。","options":["gentle","harsh","silent","brief"],"sentence":"The teacher's ______ criticism of the student's essay was difficult to accept. She pointed out every spelling error, grammar mistake, and logical flaw in a cold, cutting manner.","translation":"老師對學生論文的尖銳批評很難接受。她以冷酷、尖刻的方式指出每一個拼寫錯誤、語法錯誤和邏輯缺陷。","word":"harsh"}},"harvest":{"createdAt":1781345746903,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"harvest 作名詞，指農作物的收穫或收成，通常是農業活動的成果。","options":["drought","harvest","planting","irrigation"],"sentence":"The farmers celebrated the end of summer with a bountiful ______. The fields yielded more crops than they had expected, ensuring food security for the entire region.","translation":"農民們用豐收來慶祝夏季的結束。田地產出的農作物比預期更多，確保了整個地區的糧食安全。","word":"harvest"}},"haste":{"createdAt":1781332009071,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"haste 意為匆忙或急促，通常導致粗心或錯誤","options":["care","haste","precision","planning"],"sentence":"In their ______, the workers made several mistakes on the construction site. If they had taken their time and worked more carefully, the errors could have been avoided.","translation":"在匆忙中，工人在建築工地上犯了幾個錯誤。如果他們花時間並更加小心地工作，這些錯誤是可以避免的。","word":"haste"}},"hatch":{"createdAt":1781427134899,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"hatch在此指秘密策劃或準備一個計劃或陰謀。","options":["discover","analyze","hatch","report"],"sentence":"The spy agency spent months planning to ______ a secret operation against their rivals. By the time the plot was discovered, the operatives were already in position.","translation":"間諜機構花了數個月時間策劃一項針對敵手的秘密行動。當陰謀被發現時，特務已經就位了。","word":"hatch"}},"hazard":{"createdAt":1781709890955,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"hazard指的是可能導致傷害、損失或危險的人物、情況或物質。","options":["implication","engagement","hazard","braided"],"sentence":"Working with heavy machinery without proper training presents a serious ______ to worker safety. The factory manager implemented strict protocols to minimize the risk of accidents and injuries.","translation":"在沒有適當訓練的情況下操作重型機械對工人的安全造成了嚴重的危害。工廠經理實施了嚴格的協議來最小化事故和傷害的風險。","word":"hazard"}},"healthcare":{"createdAt":1781841505535,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"healthcare 是指醫療保健系統和服務，涵蓋了預防、治療和健康管理的各個方面。","options":["anthem","healthcare","wonder","legendary"],"sentence":"Many developed countries provide free ______ to all their citizens as a basic public service. The government funds hospitals, clinics, and medicines to ensure everyone can access medical treatment.","translation":"許多發達國家為所有公民提供免費的醫療保健作為基本公共服務。政府資助醫院、診所和藥物，以確保每個人都能獲得醫療治療。","word":"healthcare"}},"healthful":{"createdAt":1781693270387,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"healthful表示「有益健康的、促進健康的」，用來描述對身體有好處的飲食、習慣或生活方式。","options":["toxic","harmful","restrictive","healthful"],"sentence":"The nutritionist recommended a ______ diet full of vegetables, fruits, and whole grains. She emphasized that these foods would strengthen his immune system and boost his energy levels.","translation":"營養師推薦一種有益健康的飲食，充滿蔬菜、水果和全穀物。她強調這些食物會增強他的免疫系統並提升他的能量水平。","word":"healthful"}},"herd":{"createdAt":1781836375379,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"herd是畜群，特別是指牛、羊或其他大型家畜的一群。","options":["pack","herd","flock","school"],"sentence":"The cowboys guided a large ______ of cattle across the prairie toward the market. Hundreds of animals moved together in a coordinated group.","translation":"牛仔們引導一大群牛穿過草原前往市場。數百隻動物協調地聚集在一起移動。","word":"herd"}},"heroic":{"createdAt":1781848330188,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"heroic表示表現出英勇、勇敢或非凡勇氣的行為，或需要花費巨大努力的壯舉。","options":["cowardly","heroic","lazy","reckless"],"sentence":"The firefighter's ______ efforts to rescue the child from the burning building earned him widespread praise. Despite the extreme danger and personal risk, he refused to give up until everyone was safe.","translation":"消防員從燃燒的建築物中救出孩子的英勇努力獲得了廣泛讚揚。儘管面臨極端危險和個人風險，他拒絕放棄直到每個人都安全。","word":"heroic"}},"hesitation":{"createdAt":1781709890954,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"hesitation指的是在做決定或採取行動前的遲疑或猶豫，表示缺乏確定性或信心。","options":["obsession","hazard","hesitation","implication"],"sentence":"Without any ______, he immediately accepted the job offer from the international company. His quick decision surprised everyone who expected him to take time to think about such a major career move.","translation":"他毫不猶豫地立即接受了那家國際公司的工作邀約。他的快速決定讓所有人感到驚訝，因為他們預期他會花時間考慮這樣的重大職業轉變。","word":"hesitation"}},"hideaway":{"createdAt":1781709984200,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"hideaway 名詞指隱秘的地方或逃避處，人們可以在那裡躲避世界、獨自享受時光。","options":["resort","hideaway","retreat","shelter"],"sentence":"The old cottage in the mountains served as a perfect ______ for the family seeking peace and solitude. They could escape from the busy city life and enjoy nature for weeks without interruption.","translation":"山裡的這棟老房子是尋求和平與寧靜的家庭的完美隱匿處。他們可以逃離繁忙的城市生活，享受數週的自然，不受打擾。","word":"hideaway"}},"hierarchy":{"createdAt":1781848330186,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"hierarchy是組織系統中按權力、地位或重要性排列的等級結構。","options":["schedule","hierarchy","budget","conflict"],"sentence":"The company has a strict ______ that determines who reports to whom. The CEO sits at the top, followed by department heads, then managers, and finally regular employees at the bottom.","translation":"這家公司有嚴格的等級制度來決定誰向誰報告。首席執行官位居最高層，其次是部門主管、經理，最後是普通員工。","word":"hierarchy"}},"hijack":{"createdAt":1781402154557,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"hijack表示非法奪取和控制交通工具（如飛機、船隻）或貨物，通常涉及暴力或威脅。","options":["compel","hijack","possess","lottery"],"sentence":"Terrorists attempted to ______ the airplane and divert it to an undisclosed location. Fortunately, the pilot managed to alert authorities, and fighter jets intercepted the aircraft before it could change course.","translation":"恐怖分子試圖劫持飛機並將其轉向未公開的地點。幸運的是，飛行員成功警告了當局，戰鬥機在飛機改變路線前攔截了它。","word":"hijack"}},"hoarse":{"createdAt":1781693275429,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"嘶啞用來形容聲音沙啞、粗糙或沙沙的狀態，通常是由於過度使用或喉嚨不適引起的。","options":["loud","hoarse","clear","strong"],"sentence":"After shouting at the concert all night, the singer's voice became ______. She could barely whisper the next morning and had to cancel her interviews.","translation":"在演唱會上整晚尖叫後，歌手的嗓音變得嘶啞。她隔天早上幾乎無法低聲說話，不得不取消她的採訪。","word":"hoarse"}},"hoax":{"createdAt":1781481124691,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"hoax 是指故意製造的虛假信息或事件，目的是欺騙或捉弄他人。","options":["confirmation","notification","scam","reminder"],"sentence":"The email claiming to be from the bank was actually a ______ designed to steal personal information. The sender had fabricated the entire message to deceive unsuspecting victims.","translation":"聲稱來自銀行的電子郵件實際上是一個旨在竊取個人信息的騙局。發送者編造了整個消息來欺騙毫無防備的受害者。","word":"hoax"}},"hold":{"createdAt":1781515634900,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「hold」在這裡表示用手抓握或支撐某物，使其保持在原位。","options":["drop","hold","throw","catch"],"sentence":"Please ______ this box while I open the door. I need you to keep it steady with both hands until I return.","translation":"請你握住這個盒子，我去開門。我需要你用雙手保持它穩定直到我回來。","word":"hold"}},"hose":{"createdAt":1781484415236,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"hose是指軟的管狀物，通常用於運輸流體如水，常見於花園澆水。","options":["ladder","hose","fence","gate"],"sentence":"He grabbed the garden ______ to water the flowers in the backyard. The flexible rubber tube made it easy to reach all the plants and beds.","translation":"他拿起花園水管來澆灌後院的花。這條柔軟的橡膠軟管使他可以輕鬆到達所有的植物和花床。","word":"hose"}},"hospitable":{"createdAt":1781849847404,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"hospitable表示好客的或招待周到的，與「準備美食和舒適住宿」的線索相符。","options":["rude","hospitable","cold","unfriendly"],"sentence":"Our hosts were very ______ and made us feel welcome from the moment we arrived. They prepared delicious food and provided comfortable accommodations.","translation":"我們的主人非常好客，從我們到達的那一刻起就讓我們感到受歡迎。他們準備了美味的食物並提供了舒適的住宿。","word":"hospitable"}},"hospitality":{"createdAt":1781849511876,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"熱情好客是指以友善、慷慨和殷勤的態度對待客人。","options":["efficiency","location","hospitality","cleanliness"],"sentence":"The hotel's ______ made our stay absolutely wonderful and memorable. The staff offered us complimentary snacks, warm greetings, and went out of their way to help with all our requests.","translation":"飯店的熱情好客使我們的住宿絕對精彩而難忘。員工為我們提供免費點心、溫暖的問候，並竭盡全力幫助滿足我們所有的需求。","word":"hospitality"}},"hostage":{"createdAt":1781581925134,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"hostage 指被扣押以作為談判籌碼或保證的人，通常涉及要求賠償或其他條件的情況。","options":["prisoner","hostage","captive","suspect"],"sentence":"The criminal took a ______ to negotiate with the police for safe passage out of the city. The negotiator spoke carefully to ensure the innocent person's safety throughout the standoff.","translation":"犯罪分子抓了一個人質與警察談判，以便安全離開城市。談判代表小心謹慎地說話，以確保無辜者在整個對峙中的安全。","word":"hostage"}},"hostility":{"createdAt":1781965320891,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"hostility 指的是敵意和不友好的態度，通常伴隨著對抗和衝突。","options":["friendship","cooperation","hostility","alliance"],"sentence":"The ______ between the two neighboring countries has escalated into military tensions. Both sides refuse to negotiate and continue making aggressive threats.","translation":"兩個鄰近國家之間的敵意已經升級為軍事緊張局勢。雙方拒絕談判並繼續發出侵略性的威脅。","word":"hostility"}},"housing":{"createdAt":1781332009082,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"housing 是名詞，指的是住房或住宅，通常用於指人們的居住場所","options":["education","housing","healthcare","transportation"],"sentence":"The government launched a new initiative to improve ______ for low-income families. The program provided subsidies and loans to help people purchase affordable homes.","translation":"政府啟動了一項新倡議來改善低收入家庭的住房。該計畫提供補助和貸款幫助人們購買負擔得起的房屋。","word":"housing"}},"humanity":{"createdAt":1781484415236,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"humanity是指人性中的善良、同情和慈悲，代表對人類共同福祉的關心。","options":["selfishness","cruelty","humanity","ignorance"],"sentence":"Despite the tragedy, the rescue workers showed great ______ by risking their lives to save strangers. Their compassion and selflessness demonstrated the best qualities of humankind.","translation":"儘管發生了悲劇，救援工作人員通過冒著生命危險救陌生人來展現了偉大的人道精神。他們的同情心和無私展現了人類最好的品質。","word":"humanity"}},"humble":{"createdAt":1781693538704,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"humble 表示謙虛、謙卑或不自誇的品質，不傲慢也不自大。","options":["arrogant","proud","humble","boastful"],"sentence":"Despite winning three major awards, the actress remained ______ and never bragged about her accomplishments. She always credited her success to her dedicated team.","translation":"儘管贏得三個主要獎項，這位女演員仍然保持謙虛，從不吹噓她的成就。她總是將她的成功歸功於她敬業的團隊。","word":"humble"}},"humiliation":{"createdAt":1781434900590,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"humiliation指因失敗或被貶低而感到的羞辱和恥辱感。","options":["joy","humiliation","excitement","pride"],"sentence":"Losing the championship match in front of thousands of fans caused him great ______. He felt deeply ashamed and embarrassed by his poor performance.","translation":"在數千名球迷面前輸掉冠軍賽給他帶來了巨大的羞辱。他為自己糟糕的表現感到深深的羞愧和尷尬。","word":"humiliation"}},"humor":{"createdAt":1781345237583,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"humor指使人感到愉快或發笑的幽默感或幽默天賦。","options":["silence","humor","sadness","anger"],"sentence":"His natural ______ made him popular at parties and social gatherings. Everyone appreciated his funny jokes and witty observations about everyday life.","translation":"他天生的幽默感使他在派對和社交聚會上很受歡迎。每個人都欣賞他關於日常生活的有趣笑話和詼諧評論。","word":"humor"}},"humorous":{"createdAt":1781424356415,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"humorous用來形容能夠引起笑聲或娛樂的事物，特別是通過聰慧或幽默的方式。","options":["serious","humorous","aggressive","confusing"],"sentence":"The comedian's ______ jokes made the entire audience burst into laughter. His timing and clever wordplay demonstrated why he was considered one of the funniest performers of the year.","translation":"這位喜劇演員幽默有趣的笑話讓整個觀眾席爆發出笑聲。他的時機把握和聰慧的措辭充分說明了為什麼他被認為是該年最有趣的表演者之一。","word":"humorous"}},"hung":{"createdAt":1781849847410,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"hung是hang的過去式，表示懸掛或吊起，與「掛在牆上、花時間調整位置」的線索相符。","options":["dropped","hung","broke","hid"],"sentence":"She ______ the painting carefully on the living room wall. It took her an hour to find the perfect spot and ensure it was level.","translation":"她小心地將這幅畫掛在客廳的牆上。她花了一個小時才找到完美的位置並確保它是水平的。","word":"hung"}},"hydrogen":{"createdAt":1781849847402,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"hydrogen是化學元素，與「最輕、最豐富」及「火箭燃料和製造水」的特性相符。","options":["Oxygen","Hydrogen","Carbon","Nitrogen"],"sentence":"______ is the lightest and most abundant element in the universe. Scientists use it as fuel in rockets and for creating water.","translation":"氫是宇宙中最輕和最豐富的元素。科學家將其用作火箭燃料和製造水。","word":"hydrogen"}},"hygiene":{"createdAt":1781832089958,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"hygiene 指個人或公共衛生，包括清潔和預防疾病的習慣和實踐","options":["nutrition","hygiene","medication","exercise"],"sentence":"Good personal ______ is essential for preventing the spread of diseases. Washing hands regularly and keeping your surroundings clean are basic practices everyone should follow.","translation":"良好的個人衛生對於防止疾病傳播至關重要。定期洗手和保持周圍環境清潔是每個人都應該遵循的基本習慣。","word":"hygiene"}},"ideal":{"createdAt":1781848934149,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"ideal指最完美或最令人滿意的狀態或情況","options":["terrible","rainy","ideal","cold"],"sentence":"The weather was ______ for the outdoor wedding ceremony. The temperature was perfect, and there wasn't a cloud in the sky.","translation":"天氣對於戶外婚禮非常理想。溫度完美，天空中沒有一絲雲彩。","word":"ideal"}},"identical":{"createdAt":1781424574160,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"identical 意為完全相同的，沒有任何區別。","options":["identical","different","expensive","damaged"],"sentence":"The two paintings were ______ in every way. Even the expert art appraiser could not tell them apart, as they had the same colors, brushstrokes, and dimensions.","translation":"這兩幅畫在各方面都完全相同。即使是專業的美術鑑定師也無法區分它們，因為它們有相同的色彩、筆觸和尺寸。","word":"identical"}},"identification":{"createdAt":1781841148118,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"identification 名詞意思是識別、辨認身份，指證明或驗證某人身份的過程或證件。","options":["payment","identification","reservation","luggage"],"sentence":"The airline required ______ from all passengers before allowing them to board the international flight. Each traveler had to present a valid passport or government-issued ID card at the check-in counter.","translation":"航空公司在允許所有乘客登上國際航班之前要求提供身份識別。每位旅客都必須在值機櫃台出示有效護照或政府簽發的身份證。","word":"identification"}},"identify":{"createdAt":1781840030395,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"identify 是動詞，表示辨認、鑑定；通過比較特徵來確認某人的身分正是此動詞的典型用法。","options":["ignore","identify","arrest","question"],"sentence":"The detective was able to ______ the suspect from the security camera footage. By comparing facial features and distinctive marks, she confirmed the criminal's identity.","translation":"偵探能夠從安全攝影機的錄像中辨認嫌疑人。通過比較面部特徵和獨特標記，她確認了罪犯的身分。","word":"identify"}},"idiom":{"createdAt":1781484415206,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"idiom是指一個短語或表達方式，其含義不能從組成詞語的字面意思推導出來。","options":["grammar","idiom","alphabet","accent"],"sentence":"The phrase 'raining cats and dogs' is a common English ______ that doesn't literally mean animals are falling from the sky. It simply means it's raining very heavily.","translation":"短語「下雨貓狗」是常見的英語習語，並不是字面上的意思動物從天上掉下來。它只是表示下雨非常猛烈。","word":"idiom"}},"ignorant":{"createdAt":1781849847405,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ignorant表示不知道的或無知的，與「從未學習過、知識缺陷」的線索相符。","options":["knowledgeable","ignorant","expert","informed"],"sentence":"She was ______ about the historical facts and had never studied the subject. Her lack of knowledge became obvious during the discussion.","translation":"她對歷史事實一無所知，從未學過這個科目。她的知識缺陷在討論中變得很明顯。","word":"ignorant"}},"ignore":{"createdAt":1781873027345,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ignore 表示故意不注意或不理會某人說的話或做的事。","options":["answer","ignore","repeat","hear"],"sentence":"When the teacher called on him, he decided to ______ her question and stare at his desk instead. His deliberate refusal to acknowledge what she said made it clear he was being disrespectful.","translation":"當老師點他回答時，他決定忽視她的問題，而是盯著自己的課桌。他刻意拒絕承認她說的話，清楚表明他在不尊重人。","word":"ignore"}},"illusion":{"createdAt":1781849847409,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"illusion表示幻覺或錯覺，與「魔術、巧妙的把戲」的線索相符。","options":["reality","illusion","fact","truth"],"sentence":"The magician created a convincing ______ that made the audience believe the car had disappeared. Everyone was amazed by the clever trick.","translation":"魔術師創造了一個令人信服的幻覺，讓觀眾相信汽車消失了。每個人都對這個巧妙的把戲感到驚訝。","word":"illusion"}},"illustrator":{"createdAt":1782022372248,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"illustrator 意為「插畫家」，指專門為書籍、雜誌等創作插圖的藝術工作者。","options":["publisher","illustrator","author","printer"],"sentence":"The children's book became a bestseller thanks to the talented ______ who created beautiful, colorful drawings for each page. Without these stunning visual artworks, the young readers would have found the story much less engaging.","translation":"這本兒童書籍成為暢銷書，多虧了才華橫溢的插畫家為每一頁創作了美麗多彩的插圖。如果沒有這些令人驚艷的視覺藝術作品，年輕讀者會發現故事的吸引力大大降低。","word":"illustrator"}},"image":{"createdAt":1782005726784,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"image 在此指某人或機構在公眾心目中的印象和看法，可以通過行動來改變和塑造。","options":["image","schedule","budget","strategy"],"sentence":"The politician worked hard to improve her public ______ before the election. She donated to charities and participated in community service to show voters her commitment to helping others.","translation":"這位政治家在選舉前努力改善她的公眾形象。她向慈善機構捐款並參與社區服務，向選民展示她幫助他人的承諾。","word":"image"}},"imagination":{"createdAt":1781849847411,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"imagination表示想像力，與「創造奇幻世界、魔法生物和冒險」的線索相符。","options":["logic","imagination","memory","reasoning"],"sentence":"The child's ______ was so vivid that he created entire fantasy worlds in his mind. His stories were filled with magical creatures and impossible adventures.","translation":"這個孩子的想像力非常生動，他在腦子裡創造了整個奇幻世界。他的故事充滿了魔法生物和不可能的冒險。","word":"imagination"}},"imitate":{"createdAt":1781848934152,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"imitate指複製或仿效他人的行為、言語或動作","options":["ignore","imitate","avoid","criticize"],"sentence":"Young children tend to ______ the behavior of their parents and older siblings. This is a natural part of learning and development.","translation":"年幼的孩子往往會模仿父母和哥哥姐姐的行為。這是學習和發展的自然部分。","word":"imitate"}},"imitative":{"createdAt":1781434900592,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"imitative指模仿或複製他人的特點，通常暗示缺乏原創性。","options":["elaborate","imitative","minimalist","modern"],"sentence":"The new restaurant's ______ décor copied the style of famous Italian establishments without any original design. Art critics dismissed it as lacking authenticity and creativity.","translation":"這家新餐廳的模仿式裝飾抄襲了著名義大利餐廳的風格，沒有任何原創設計。藝術評論家認為它缺乏真實性和創意。","word":"imitative"}},"immediate":{"createdAt":1781437220556,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「Immediate」形容詞表示直接的或立即發生的，沒有中間過程或延遲。","options":["distant","delayed","immediate","indirect"],"sentence":"The ______ cause of the accident was the driver's failure to brake in time. Within seconds of impact, emergency services arrived at the scene.","translation":"這起事故的直接原因是司機未能及時制動。撞擊後幾秒鐘內，緊急服務人員便趕到現場。","word":"immediate"}},"imminent":{"createdAt":1781431278559,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"imminent指某事即將發生或臨近，通常用於描述快速逼近的事件。","options":["distant","imminent","unlikely","mild"],"sentence":"The weather forecast warns that a severe storm is ______ and residents should seek shelter immediately. Dark clouds are already gathering over the city, and rain is expected within the next hour.","translation":"天氣預報警告嚴重風暴即將來臨，居民應該立即尋求庇護。烏雲已經聚集在城市上空，預計雨水將在下一小時內開始。","word":"imminent"}},"immune":{"createdAt":1781840892410,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"immune表示對某種疾病或有害物質的免疫或抵抗力，無法被感染。","options":["vulnerable","resistant","immune","allergic"],"sentence":"After receiving the vaccine, the body developed antibodies that made her ______ to the virus. She could now be exposed to infected individuals without contracting the disease.","translation":"接種疫苗後，身體產生了使她對該病毒免疫的抗體。她現在可以接觸感染者而不會患病。","word":"immune"}},"impact":{"createdAt":1781345237581,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"impact作動詞表示對某事物產生重要的影響或衝擊效果。","options":["ignore","impact","observe","measure"],"sentence":"The new marketing campaign will ______ our sales figures significantly. We expect to see at least a 30% increase in revenue based on preliminary market analysis.","translation":"新的行銷活動將對我們的銷售數字產生重大影響。根據初步市場分析，我們預計收入至少會增加30%。","word":"impact"}},"implication":{"createdAt":1781709890956,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"implication指的是在沒有明確說明的情況下暗示或表達的意思，是隱含的含義。","options":["braided","implication","obsession","engagement"],"sentence":"The ______ of her statement was that the company had been dishonest with its investors. Although she never directly accused anyone, her carefully chosen words suggested serious misconduct had occurred.","translation":"她聲明的暗示是該公司對投資者不誠實。雖然她從未直接指責任何人，但她精心選擇的措詞表明發生了嚴重的不當行為。","word":"implication"}},"import":{"createdAt":1781841742836,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"import 作動詞表示「進口」，指將外國商品運入本國，與 export 相反。","options":["export","import","produce","consume"],"sentence":"Many countries ______ raw materials from Africa to use in manufacturing. These goods arrive by ship and truck at ports and distribution centers.","translation":"許多國家從非洲進口原材料用於製造業。這些商品通過船隻和卡車運抵港口和配送中心。","word":"import"}},"impose":{"createdAt":1781840659327,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"impose 表示強制實施或徵收，指通過權力強加某些要求或限制。","options":["suggest","impose","discuss","consider"],"sentence":"The government decided to ______ strict new regulations on all manufacturing plants. Companies now must follow these mandatory rules or face significant penalties.","translation":"政府決定在所有製造廠實施嚴格的新規定。公司現在必須遵守這些強制性規則，否則將面臨重罰。","word":"impose"}},"impressive":{"createdAt":1781849511876,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"令人印象深刻是指某事物給人留下深刻而良好的印象，令人欽佩。","options":["boring","loud","impressive","fast"],"sentence":"The young pianist's performance was truly ______ and moved many people to tears. Her technical skill, emotional depth, and perfect execution earned her a standing ovation from the entire audience.","translation":"這位年輕鋼琴家的表演確實令人印象深刻，使許多人感動得流淚。她的技術、情感深度和完美的表現贏得了全體觀眾的起立鼓掌。","word":"impressive"}},"improve":{"createdAt":1781449588285,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"improve作為動詞表示「改善、增進、提高」，指使某事物變得更好或更優秀。","options":["improve","glorify","signify","just"],"sentence":"The student's test scores began to ______ after receiving tutoring and studying more consistently. Her progress was remarkable, jumping from a D grade to a B grade within just two months.","translation":"學生在接受輔導並更加持續地學習後，測試成績開始改善。她的進步是顯著的，在短短兩個月內從D級跳升到B級。","word":"improve"}},"improvement":{"createdAt":1782005726781,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"improvement 意指某事物變得更好或更優良的過程，通常伴隨正面的結果和進展。","options":["decline","improvement","confusion","tension"],"sentence":"The company made significant ______ to its products after listening to customer feedback. This change resulted in better sales and higher customer satisfaction scores.","translation":"該公司在聽取客戶反饋後對其產品進行了重大改善。這一變化導致銷售額更高和客戶滿意度評分提升。","word":"improvement"}},"impulse":{"createdAt":1781839703149,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"impulse指未經理性考慮的衝動，與bought without thinking and regretting（未經思考地購買並後悔）直接對應。","options":["planning","analysis","impulse","preparation"],"sentence":"Acting on ______ without thinking often leads to regrettable decisions. She bought expensive items she didn't need just because they were on sale.","translation":"在沒有思考的衝動下行動常常導致後悔的決定。她只是因為東西在打折就買了一些她不需要的昂貴物品。","word":"impulse"}},"impurity":{"createdAt":1781832761717,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"impurity 表示雜質、不潔，指混入純淨物質中的不需要的物質。","options":["clarity","purity","contamination","cleanliness"],"sentence":"The scientist found traces of ______ in the water sample during the laboratory analysis. The contaminants needed to be removed to make the water safe for consumption.","translation":"科學家在實驗室分析期間在水樣本中發現了微量的雜質。需要去除污染物以使水安全飲用。","word":"impurity"}},"incentive":{"createdAt":1781598671167,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"incentive 作名詞表示激勵或鼓勵，指促使某人採取特定行動的刺激物或獎勵","options":["penalty","incentive","restriction","burden"],"sentence":"The company offered a cash bonus as an ______ to increase employee productivity. Workers became more motivated to exceed their performance targets.","translation":"公司提供現金獎金作為激勵以提高員工生產力。工人變得更有動力超過他們的績效目標。","word":"incentive"}},"include":{"createdAt":1781275226790,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"此處include作動詞表示「包括；涵蓋」，指某物是整體的一部分","options":["fume","include","dazzle","dump"],"sentence":"The package deal will ______ airfare, hotel accommodations, and all meals. The price quote covers everything you need for your complete vacation.","translation":"這個套餐會包括機票、酒店住宿和所有餐飲。報價涵蓋了你完整假期所需的一切。","word":"include"}},"including":{"createdAt":1781362281657,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"including表示包括或包含某些東西作為整體的一部分。","options":["excluding","including","limiting","deducting"],"sentence":"The total cost of the trip is $500, ______ all meals and transportation. Accommodation, activities, and guides are part of this price.","translation":"旅行的總成本是500美元，包括所有的餐飲和交通。住宿、活動和導遊都包含在這個價格中。","word":"including"}},"incoming":{"createdAt":1781935654224,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"incoming 是形容詞，表示「即將來臨的」或「正在到達的」，指飛機、訊息或人員即將抵達。","options":["departing","incoming","delayed","cancelled"],"sentence":"The ______ flight from Tokyo will arrive at Gate 12 in approximately thirty minutes. Please proceed to the arrival hall to greet your passengers.","translation":"從東京來的班機將在大約三十分鐘內抵達12號登機口。請前往到達大廳迎接您的乘客。","word":"incoming"}},"incorporate":{"createdAt":1781746848185,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"incorporate 表示「包含」或「將...包括在內」，指將某物納入或整合到整體中。","options":["remove","incorporate","separate","abandon"],"sentence":"The new software will ______ artificial intelligence features into its existing platform. Users will benefit from these technological advancements starting next month.","translation":"新軟體將人工智能功能集成到其現有平台中。用戶從下個月開始將從這些技術進步中受益。","word":"incorporate"}},"incorporates":{"createdAt":1781564440921,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"incorporates 表示納入、併入，指將某物包含或整合到整體中。","options":["removes","incorporates","ignores","rejects"],"sentence":"The new recipe ______ several traditional ingredients with modern cooking techniques. By mixing old and new methods, it creates a unique fusion dish.","translation":"新食譜將傳統食材與現代烹飪技術結合在一起。通過混合老舊和新的方法，它創造了獨特的融合菜餚。","word":"incorporates"}},"incur":{"createdAt":1781693304925,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"incur 表示因為某項行為或決定而招致或遭受（通常是負面的後果）。","options":["avoid","prevent","incur","deserve"],"sentence":"By arriving late to the meeting, the executive began to ______ the anger of the entire board. His tardiness had serious consequences for his standing in the company.","translation":"因為遲到開會，這位高管開始招致整個董事會的憤怒。他的遲到對他在公司的地位造成了嚴重後果。","word":"incur"}},"independence":{"createdAt":1781624534658,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"independence 意為「獨立、自主」，指不依賴他人而能自立的狀態。","options":["dependence","independence","confusion","anxiety"],"sentence":"After living with her parents for twenty years, she finally achieved ______ by moving into her own apartment and supporting herself financially. She no longer needed their financial assistance.","translation":"在與父母生活了二十年後，她終於通過搬到自己的公寓並自給自足而獲得了獨立。她不再需要他們的經濟援助。","word":"independence"}},"independent":{"createdAt":1781564440934,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"independent 作形容詞表示獨立的，指不依賴他人、能自主做決定的。","options":["dependent","independent","uncertain","indecisive"],"sentence":"The young woman was ______ and made all her own decisions without relying on others. She had moved out of her parents' house and supported herself financially.","translation":"年輕女性是獨立的，自己做所有決定，不依賴他人。她已經搬出父母的房子並自己承擔財務支持。","word":"independent"}},"indicate":{"createdAt":1781257238303,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"indicate指顯示、表明或指出某事，常用於從徵兆推斷結論。","options":["prevent","indicate","delay","cancel"],"sentence":"The dark clouds ______ that a storm was coming soon. Within the next two hours, heavy rain and lightning would arrive in the area.","translation":"烏雲表明暴風雨即將來臨。在接下來的兩小時內，該地區將迎來暴雨和閃電。","word":"indicate"}},"indicator":{"createdAt":1781860901470,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"indicator是名詞，表示指標或標誌，指用來衡量或表示某種情況的事物","options":["obstacle","indicator","weapon","reward"],"sentence":"Rising unemployment is often considered a key ______ of economic recession. Economists use this figure as a measurement to predict future market trends.","translation":"失業率上升通常被認為是經濟衰退的關鍵指標。經濟學家以此數據作為衡量標準來預測未來市場趨勢。","word":"indicator"}},"indifferent":{"createdAt":1781582424691,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"indifferent表示不關心或冷漠，與didn't investigate和didn't take action相符，interested、concerned和sympathetic都表示有關心或同情。","options":["interested","concerned","indifferent","sympathetic"],"sentence":"The manager seemed ______ to the complaints from the employees about working conditions. He didn't investigate or take any action whatsoever.","translation":"經理對員工關於工作條件的投訴似乎漠不關心。他既沒有調查也沒有採取任何行動。","word":"indifferent"}},"indispensable":{"createdAt":1781884659829,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"indispensable 表示絕對必需、不能沒有的，強調某物對生存或功能至關重要。","options":["abundant","indispensable","precious","renewable"],"sentence":"Water is ______ for all living organisms to survive. Without it, no plant, animal, or human could exist on Earth.","translation":"水對所有生物生存是不可或缺的。沒有水，地球上沒有植物、動物或人類能夠存活。","word":"indispensable"}},"individual":{"createdAt":1781838276303,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"individual作為形容詞表示單獨的、個別的，強調每個人都是獨立的。","options":["nutritious","individual","compressed","standing"],"sentence":"Each ______ student must submit their own research project by Friday. The teacher will evaluate the work of every single person in the class separately.","translation":"每個學生必須在週五前提交自己的研究項目。老師將分別評估班級裡每個人的作品。","word":"individual"}},"industrialization":{"createdAt":1781581925128,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"industrialization 指的是工業發展和製造業的擴張，使社會從農業為主轉變為工業為主的過程。","options":["urbanization","industrialization","mechanization","globalization"],"sentence":"The ______ of the country transformed it from an agricultural society into a modern economic powerhouse. Factories replaced farms, and millions of workers moved to cities to operate machinery.","translation":"該國的工業化使其從農業社會轉變為現代經濟強國。工廠取代了農場，數百萬工人遷入城市操作機器。","word":"industrialization"}},"industrialize":{"createdAt":1781955529035,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"industrialize 指的是將一個地區或國家從農業經濟轉變為以工業製造為主的經濟。","options":["modernize","industrialize","urbanize","develop"],"sentence":"During the 19th century, many European countries began to ______ their economies rapidly. Factories replaced farmland, and millions of workers moved from rural villages to growing cities to work in manufacturing plants.","translation":"在19世紀，許多歐洲國家開始迅速使其經濟工業化。工廠取代了農田，數百萬工人從農村遷移到不斷發展的城市，在製造工廠工作。","word":"industrialize"}},"industry":{"createdAt":1781860901468,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"industry作名詞表示勤勉或勤奮，指認真努力地工作的品質","options":["laziness","industry","dishonesty","rudeness"],"sentence":"The ______ of the workers was evident in their dedication to completing the project on time. They worked long hours without complaint to meet the deadline.","translation":"工人的勤勉在他們致力於按時完成項目上顯而易見。他們不怨言地長時間工作以趕上截止日期。","word":"industry"}},"infant":{"createdAt":1781425024018,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"infant是指非常小的嬰幼兒，通常指出生後不久的新生兒，比toddler更小。","options":["child","infant","teenager","toddler"],"sentence":"The newborn ______ cried throughout the night, keeping the exhausted parents awake. The baby was only three days old and still adjusting to life outside the womb.","translation":"新生嬰兒整夜哭鬧，讓疲憊的父母徹夜未眠。這個寶寶才三天大，仍在適應子宮外的生活。","word":"infant"}},"infect":{"createdAt":1781363994346,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"infect表示病原體或疾病傳播到人體內，造成感染或疾病發生。","options":["heal","protect","contaminate","understand"],"sentence":"The virus can ______ multiple people if they don't practice proper hygiene. Scientists are studying how quickly the disease spreads from person to person.","translation":"如果人們不做好衛生措施，病毒可能會感染多人。科學家正在研究這種疾病在人與人之間傳播的速度。","word":"infect"}},"infection":{"createdAt":1781693304923,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"infection 指由病原體引起的傳染病或感染狀態，通常需要用抗生素治療。","options":["injury","infection","inflammation","allergy"],"sentence":"The doctor warned that without proper treatment, the ______ could spread to other parts of the body. She prescribed antibiotics to kill the bacteria causing the illness.","translation":"醫生警告說，如果沒有適當的治療，感染可能會擴散到身體的其他部位。她開了抗生素來殺死引起疾病的細菌。","word":"infection"}},"inferior":{"createdAt":1781515329264,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"inferior 形容詞，意思是次等的、劣於，用來描述質量或價值較低的事物。","options":["superior","inferior","comparable","equivalent"],"sentence":"The ______ quality of the counterfeit product became obvious when we opened the package. The materials felt cheap, and the craftsmanship was noticeably poor compared to the authentic version.","translation":"當我們打開包裝時，假冒產品的次等品質變得顯而易見。材料感覺廉價，與正品相比工藝明顯低劣。","word":"inferior"}},"inferiors":{"createdAt":1781425122878,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"inferiors 指職位較低或地位低於自己的人，與經理尊重所有員工這個脈絡相符。","options":["supervisors","inferiors","colleagues","competitors"],"sentence":"The manager treated his ______ with respect and fairness. He believed that everyone in the company, regardless of rank, deserved to be valued.","translation":"經理尊重和公平對待他的下級。他相信公司裡的每個人，無論職位如何，都應該受到重視。","word":"inferiors"}},"infinite":{"createdAt":1781848330179,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"infinite表示無邊無際、無窮無盡的，沒有限制或邊界的狀態。","options":["finite","infinite","spherical","mysterious"],"sentence":"The universe is so vast and ______ that scientists believe it extends endlessly in all directions. No matter how far our telescopes look, we can never reach its edge or boundary.","translation":"宇宙是如此廣闊無限，科學家相信它向各個方向無盡地延伸。無論我們的望遠鏡看多遠，我們永遠無法到達它的邊緣或邊界。","word":"infinite"}},"inflict":{"createdAt":1781787229334,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"inflict 指造成傷害、痛苦或損失，通常用於不幸或負面的事件。","options":["prevent","inflict","repair","announce"],"sentence":"The natural disaster ______ severe damage on the coastal communities. Thousands of homes were destroyed, and many people lost everything.","translation":"自然災害對沿海社區造成了嚴重的損害。數千戶房屋被摧毀，許多人失去了一切。","word":"inflict"}},"influence":{"createdAt":1781715397126,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"influence 意為「影響、影響力」，指一個人或事物對他人行為、觀點或決定的推動作用。","options":["pressure","influence","authority","control"],"sentence":"The famous celebrity's ______ over her millions of followers was so powerful that her fashion choices instantly became global trends. When she wore a particular style, stores across the world sold out within days.","translation":"這位著名名人對她數百萬粉絲的影響力非常強大，以至於她的時尚選擇瞬間成為全球潮流。當她穿上特定款式時，世界各地的商店在幾天內就會售罄。","word":"influence"}},"inform":{"createdAt":1781693293270,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"inform 是動詞，意思是「通知」或「告知」某人某些資訊。","options":["inform","plant","crush","priceless"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ all employees about the upcoming restructuring. The announcement was made through an official email sent to everyone's inbox.","translation":"公司決定通知所有員工即將進行的重組。公告通過發送給每個人收件箱的正式電子郵件發送。","word":"inform"}},"informed":{"createdAt":1781693538704,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"informed 表示基於充分信息、知識或事實做出的決定或判斷。","options":["random","hasty","informed","reckless"],"sentence":"She made an ______ decision about which university to attend after researching programs and speaking with current students. Her choice was based on solid facts and careful consideration.","translation":"在研究課程和與現有學生交談後，她對選擇哪所大學做出了有根據的決定。她的選擇基於確實的事實和仔細的考慮。","word":"informed"}},"inhabitant":{"createdAt":1781715397125,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"inhabitant 意為「居民」，指長期居住在某個地方的人。","options":["visitor","inhabitant","tourist","refugee"],"sentence":"Every ______ of the small island village had to evacuate when the hurricane warning was issued by meteorological authorities. The entire population of approximately five hundred people sought shelter on the mainland.","translation":"當氣象部門發佈颶風警報時，小島村莊的每位居民都必須撤離。大約五百人的整個人口都前往大陸尋求庇護。","word":"inhabitant"}},"inherent":{"createdAt":1781425104310,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"inherent 表示內在的、固有的、天生就有的特性或品質。","options":["external","temporary","inherent","relative"],"sentence":"Honesty is an ______ quality of his character that he has possessed since childhood. No matter what circumstances he faced, he never compromised his principles.","translation":"誠實是他自幼就具有的性格中固有的品質。無論他面臨什麼情況，他都從未妥協過自己的原則。","word":"inherent"}},"initial":{"createdAt":1781437013481,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"initial 形容事物的開始階段或最初的狀態，之後可能會改變或發展。","options":["final","initial","revised","approved"],"sentence":"The company's ______ proposal outlined a budget of five million dollars for the expansion project. After stakeholder feedback, the plan evolved significantly over the following months.","translation":"公司最初的提案為擴展項目概述了五百萬美元的預算。在利益相關者的反饋後，該計劃在隨後的幾個月內發生了顯著變化。","word":"initial"}},"initially":{"createdAt":1781715397123,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"initially 意為「最初、開頭」，表示事件或行為發生的早期階段，與後來發生的改變形成對比。","options":["eventually","initially","gradually","suddenly"],"sentence":"The company ______ refused to accept the new business proposal from its competitors. However, after reviewing the terms more carefully, the board decided to reconsider their position.","translation":"該公司最初拒絕了來自競爭對手的新商業提案。不過在更仔細地審查條款後，董事會決定重新考慮他們的立場。","word":"initially"}},"injure":{"createdAt":1781566185160,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"injure意思是造成身體上的傷害或損傷，通常指事故或暴力行為導致的傷害。","options":["help","injure","entertain","inspire"],"sentence":"The car accident did not ______ him seriously, thankfully. He was treated at the hospital for minor cuts and bruises, and was released within a few hours.","translation":"幸運的是，那場車禍沒有嚴重傷害他。他在醫院接受了輕微割傷和瘀傷的治療，幾小時內就被釋放了。","word":"injure"}},"injury":{"createdAt":1781798927524,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"injury 表示由於事故或暴力造成的身體傷害或損傷。","options":["victory","injury","experience","achievement"],"sentence":"The soccer player suffered a serious ______ during the match and had to be carried off the field. His leg was broken in two places and required surgery to heal.","translation":"足球運動員在比賽中遭受嚴重傷害，必須被抬出球場。他的腿在兩個地方骨折，需要手術才能癒合。","word":"injury"}},"innovation":{"createdAt":1781933311788,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"innovation（創新）指的是新穎獨特的想法或產品，與tradition（傳統）、repetition（重複）和complication（複雜化）都不符合句意。","options":["tradition","innovation","repetition","complication"],"sentence":"The company's latest ______ in smartphone technology has attracted millions of customers worldwide. This breakthrough design was completely different from anything competitors had released before.","translation":"該公司在智慧型手機技術上的最新創新吸引了全球數百萬消費者。這項突破性的設計與競爭對手之前發佈的任何產品都完全不同。","word":"innovation"}},"insight":{"createdAt":1781927792735,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"insight是指對某件事物的深刻理解或敏銳的洞察力，通常需要思考和分析能力。","options":["luck","guess","insight","accident"],"sentence":"The detective's ______ about the crime scene helped solve the mysterious case within days. Her ability to understand subtle clues and connect seemingly unrelated evidence proved invaluable to the investigation.","translation":"偵探對犯罪現場的洞察力幫助在幾天內破解了神秘案件。她理解細微線索並連接看似無關證據的能力對調查至關重要。","word":"insight"}},"insist":{"createdAt":1781849847405,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"insist表示堅持或強調，與「不接受例外」的嚴格態度線索相符。","options":["suggest","insist","wonder","question"],"sentence":"The teacher continued to ______ that all students submit their assignments on time. She would not accept any late work without a valid excuse.","translation":"老師堅持所有學生必須按時提交作業。她不會接受任何遲交的作業，除非有正當理由。","word":"insist"}},"inspect":{"createdAt":1781774456606,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"inspect 表示仔細檢查或檢驗某物，特別是為了確認其狀況或安全性。","options":["design","renovate","examine","decorate"],"sentence":"The food safety officer came to ______ the restaurant's kitchen for cleanliness. She examined every surface and checked equipment thoroughly.","translation":"食品安全官員來檢查餐廳廚房的清潔度。她檢查了每個表面並徹底檢驗了設備。","word":"inspect"}},"inspection":{"createdAt":1781484415156,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"inspection是指官方或正式的檢查和檢驗過程，通常用於確保符合安全或品質標準。","options":["decoration","inspection","construction","election"],"sentence":"The building failed the safety ______ last week due to several code violations. The inspector documented all the problems that needed immediate repair.","translation":"這棟建築物上週安全檢驗不合格，因為存在多項規範違規。檢驗員記錄了所有需要立即修復的問題。","word":"inspection"}},"inspirational":{"createdAt":1781935654224,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"inspirational 是形容詞，表示「鼓舞人心的」或「激勵人的」，指能夠激發他人勇氣或靈感的內容。","options":["boring","inspirational","controversial","lengthy"],"sentence":"Her ______ speech about overcoming adversity moved the entire audience to tears. Many people said it changed their perspective on life.","translation":"她關於克服逆境的鼓舞人心的演講讓整個觀眾感動得流淚。許多人說這改變了他們對生活的看法。","word":"inspirational"}},"install":{"createdAt":1781677018338,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"install是動詞，表示「安裝」或「設置」，指將軟體、硬體或系統置於可使用的位置或狀態。","options":["remove","create","install","count"],"sentence":"The IT team will ______ the new software on all office computers next week. They have already scheduled the maintenance window to ensure minimal disruption.","translation":"IT團隊將在下週在所有辦公室電腦上安裝新軟體。他們已經安排了維護時間窗口以確保中斷最少。","word":"install"}},"installation":{"createdAt":1781693270388,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"installation指「安裝、設置」，表示將設備、機器或系統放在適當的位置並連接使其能夠使用的過程。","options":["removal","installation","design","inspection"],"sentence":"The ______ of the solar panels took three days to complete from start to finish. Workers carefully mounted each panel on the roof and connected them to the electrical system.","translation":"太陽能電池板的安裝花了三天時間完成。工人們仔細地在屋頂上安裝了每塊面板並將它們連接到電氣系統。","word":"installation"}},"instructor":{"createdAt":1781479123534,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"instructor 指的是教練或講師，負責教授特定技能或知識的人。","options":["student","instructor","competitor","audience"],"sentence":"The fitness ______ demonstrated the proper technique for performing squats before the class began their workout. Students watched carefully as she showed them each step to ensure they exercised safely and effectively.","translation":"健身教練在課程開始前示範了進行深蹲的正確技巧。學生們仔細觀看她展示的每一個步驟，以確保他們能夠安全有效地運動。","word":"instructor"}},"instrument":{"createdAt":1781839950958,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"instrument 在這裡指的是樂器,特別是用於演奏音樂的工具。","options":["microphone","tool","instrument","document"],"sentence":"The musician tuned his ______ before the concert began. He carefully adjusted the strings on his violin to ensure perfect pitch.","translation":"音樂家在音樂會開始前調整了他的樂器。他仔細調整小提琴上的琴弦以確保完美音高。","word":"instrument"}},"insult":{"createdAt":1781849847410,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"insult表示侮辱或羞辱，與「粗魯評論、客人受傷」的線索相符。","options":["compliment","insult","praise","encourage"],"sentence":"His rude comment seemed to ______ the guest during the dinner party. She was visibly hurt and left the table early that evening.","translation":"他在晚宴中的粗魯評論似乎侮辱了這位客人。她顯然感到受傷並提早離開了餐桌。","word":"insult"}},"insured":{"createdAt":1781849847411,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"insured表示已投保的或被保險人，與「可以提出索賠、獲得賠款」的線索相符。","options":["unprotected","insured","vulnerable","exposed"],"sentence":"The ______ homeowner filed a claim after the fire destroyed the house. The insurance company approved the reimbursement within two weeks.","translation":"被保險的房主在火災摧毀房子後提出了索賠。保險公司在兩周內批准了賠款。","word":"insured"}},"intact":{"createdAt":1781715397124,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"intact 意為「完整無缺的、未被破壞的」，指事物保持原本的狀態，沒有受到損傷。","options":["damaged","intact","restored","preserved"],"sentence":"Despite the severe earthquake that shook the entire region, the ancient temple remained ______ and structurally sound. Engineers were amazed that not a single stone was out of place.","translation":"儘管嚴重的地震震撼了整個地區，但古老的寺廟保持完整無缺且結構完善。工程師們驚訝地發現沒有一塊石頭移位。","word":"intact"}},"intake":{"createdAt":1781935654225,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"intake 是名詞，表示「吸入」或「攝入」，指身體吸收或消耗的食物、液體或物質的量。","options":["output","intake","exercise","medication"],"sentence":"The patient's daily salt ______ should not exceed two grams according to his doctor's orders. The physician warned him about the dangers of excessive sodium consumption.","translation":"根據醫生的指示，患者每日的鹽分攝取量不應超過兩克。醫生警告他過量攝入鈉的危害。","word":"intake"}},"intend":{"createdAt":1781849847402,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"intend表示計畫或打算做某事，與「已經採取具體行動」的線索相符。","options":["forgot","intend","dreamed","assumed"],"sentence":"She ______ to finish her project by Friday. She has already scheduled time and gathered all necessary materials.","translation":"她計畫在星期五之前完成她的項目。她已經安排了時間並收集了所有必要的材料。","word":"intend"}},"interact":{"createdAt":1781832761719,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"interact 表示互動、相互作用，指兩個或多個人或事物彼此影響或溝通。","options":["compete","communicate","separate","ignore"],"sentence":"The children ______ with each other during playtime at school, making friends and learning social skills. They shared toys, laughed together, and cooperated in group games.","translation":"孩子們在學校玩耍時間互動，交朋友並學習社交技巧。他們分享玩具、一起笑，並在集體遊戲中合作。","word":"interact"}},"interaction":{"createdAt":1781714871284,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"互動是指兩個或多個個體之間相互溝通、交流和影響的過程。","options":["silence","interaction","distance","confusion"],"sentence":"The ______ between the teacher and students was very positive and engaging during the class discussion. They exchanged ideas, asked questions, and listened to each other actively.","translation":"課堂討論期間，老師和學生之間的互動非常積極且引人入勝。他們交換想法、提問並積極傾聽彼此。","word":"interaction"}},"interfere":{"createdAt":1782018712119,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「interfere」表示某物妨礙或阻礙另一物的正常運作，或兩種事物之間產生不利的相互作用。","options":["enhance","interfere","improve","support"],"sentence":"The radio signal began to ______ with the television reception in the living room. Both devices stopped working properly at the same time.","translation":"無線電信號開始干擾客廳的電視接收。兩台設備同時無法正常工作。","word":"interfere"}},"intermix":{"createdAt":1781564440925,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"intermix 作動詞表示使混合、使混雜，指將不同的物質或元素混合在一起。","options":["separate","intermix","isolate","contrast"],"sentence":"The artist decided to ______ oil paint with watercolor in a single artwork. By blending these two different mediums together, she created a unique texture and effect.","translation":"藝術家決定在一件藝術作品中混合油畫和水彩。通過將這兩種不同的媒介混合在一起，她創造了獨特的質感和效果。","word":"intermix"}},"interpret":{"createdAt":1781835517798,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"interpret 意為口譯或解說，即將一種語言轉換為另一種語言，或解釋某物的含義。","options":["question","interpret","record","memorize"],"sentence":"The translator was hired to ______ the foreign speaker's words for the audience. Without her help, nobody in the room would have understood what was being said.","translation":"翻譯被雇來為觀眾口譯外國演講者的言辭。沒有她的幫助，房間裡的任何人都不會理解所說的話。","word":"interpret"}},"interrupt":{"createdAt":1781832478020,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"interrupt 意為「插嘴」或「打斷」，用來表示在他人說話時突然插入自己的話語。","options":["listen","interrupt","understand","support"],"sentence":"Please don't ______ me while I'm speaking; I need to finish my thought. I was in the middle of explaining my proposal when you asked that question.","translation":"當我說話時，請不要打斷我；我需要把我的想法說完。我正在解釋我的提案時，你問了那個問題。","word":"interrupt"}},"interview":{"createdAt":1781767999779,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"interview 在這裡指的是正式的工作面試，通常由僱主進行以評估求職者的適合度。","options":["appointment","interview","meeting","discussion"],"sentence":"Sarah attended an ______ with the hiring manager at the tech company last Tuesday. The conversation lasted forty minutes and covered her professional experience and technical skills.","translation":"莎拉上週二參加了科技公司招聘經理的面試。談話持續了四十分鐘，涵蓋了她的專業經驗和技術技能。","word":"interview"}},"interviewer":{"createdAt":1781598671065,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"interviewer 作名詞表示面試官或進行面試的人，通常是代表公司進行招聘的人","options":["applicant","interviewer","receptionist","candidate"],"sentence":"The ______ asked me challenging questions about my previous work experience. After the meeting, she told me the hiring committee would contact me within a week.","translation":"面試官問我有關我以前工作經驗的具有挑戰性的問題。會議後，她告訴我招聘委員會將在一週內與我聯繫。","word":"interviewer"}},"intimate":{"createdAt":1781566055843,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"intimate 表示關係親密、個人的，通常指那些涉及深層信任和情感共享的互動。","options":["casual","formal","intimate","distant"],"sentence":"The couple shared an ______ conversation over dinner, discussing their deepest fears and dreams. They had been together for fifteen years and could be completely vulnerable with each other.","translation":"這對情侶在晚餐時進行了一次親密的對話，討論了他們最深層的恐懼和夢想。他們在一起已經十五年了，彼此可以完全敞開心扉。","word":"intimate"}},"intimidating":{"createdAt":1781955529033,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"intimidating 形容人或事物令人感到害怕、畏懼或不自在的特質。","options":["friendly","intimidating","welcoming","approachable"],"sentence":"The new manager's ______ presence made the junior employees nervous during their first meeting. However, once they got to know him better, they realized he was actually quite friendly and supportive.","translation":"新經理令人生畏的氣場在第一次會議上使初級員工感到緊張。然而，一旦他們更好地了解他，他們意識到他實際上相當友好且樂於支持他人。","word":"intimidating"}},"intruder":{"createdAt":1781693271585,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"intruder指的是未經邀請或未經允許闖入的人，強調其非法或不受歡迎的特性。","options":["guest","intruder","visitor","friend"],"sentence":"The police arrested the ______ who had broken into the house while the family was sleeping. The homeowners were terrified to discover an unauthorized person had entered their home.","translation":"警察逮捕了在家人睡覺時闖入房屋的不速之客。屋主們驚恐地發現有未經授權的人進入了他們的家。","word":"intruder"}},"intuition":{"createdAt":1781714871277,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"直覺是指不依賴邏輯推理或證據而產生的內心感受或判斷。","options":["calculation","intuition","memory","theory"],"sentence":"Sarah had a strong ______ that something was wrong, even though there was no obvious evidence. Later, she discovered that her gut feeling had been correct all along.","translation":"莎拉有著強烈的直覺，認為有些事情不對勁，儘管沒有明顯的證據。後來，她發現她的第六感一直都是正確的。","word":"intuition"}},"investment":{"createdAt":1781515270342,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"investment 作名詞，指為了獲利而投入的金錢、時間或資源。","options":["curious","bucket","investment","prospect"],"sentence":"Sarah decided her ______ in the new technology startup was the right decision. After three years, the company's profits tripled and her initial deposit of $10,000 grew to $50,000.","translation":"莎拉認為她對新科技新創公司的投資是正確的決定。三年後，該公司的利潤增加了三倍，她最初投入的一萬美元增長到五萬美元。","word":"investment"}},"involuntary":{"createdAt":1781860901469,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"involuntary是形容詞，表示非自願的或不由自主的，指無法控制的反應","options":["deliberate","planned","involuntary","intentional"],"sentence":"His ______ reaction to the loud noise was to cover his ears immediately. He did not consciously decide to do this; it happened automatically.","translation":"他對巨大噪音的不由自主反應是立即捂住耳朵。他沒有有意識地決定這樣做；這是自動發生的。","word":"involuntary"}},"involve":{"createdAt":1781624534704,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"involve 意為「牽涉、涉及、包含」，表示某事物作為必要部分或結果而包括在內。","options":["prevent","ignore","involve","cancel"],"sentence":"The project will ______ cooperation between different departments and several weeks of hard work. Success depends on everyone contributing their unique skills.","translation":"該項目將涉及不同部門之間的合作和數周的辛苦工作。成功取決於每個人貢獻他們獨特的技能。","word":"involve"}},"involvement":{"createdAt":1781709984197,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"involvement 名詞表示參與、投入或涉及某項活動的程度。","options":["attendance","involvement","presence","performance"],"sentence":"The teacher praised my ______ in the class discussion and group projects. She noted that I participated actively and contributed meaningful ideas every day.","translation":"老師讚揚了我在課堂討論和小組項目中的參與。她指出我每天都積極參與並貢獻有意義的想法。","word":"involvement"}},"irritable":{"createdAt":1781693538703,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"irritable 形容易發脾氣、容易被激怒或心情不好的狀態。","options":["calm","peaceful","irritable","cheerful"],"sentence":"The patient became very ______ after not sleeping for three days. His doctor advised him to rest because fatigue was making him short-tempered and easily annoyed.","translation":"在三天沒有睡眠後，患者變得非常暴躁。他的醫生建議他休息，因為疲勞讓他脾氣暴躁，容易被激怒。","word":"irritable"}},"isolate":{"createdAt":1781860901469,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"isolate是動詞，表示使孤立或隔離，指將某人或某物分開以防止接觸","options":["integrate","isolate","display","celebrate"],"sentence":"The hospital decided to ______ the infected patients from the general population. They were placed in a separate ward to prevent the disease from spreading to others.","translation":"醫院決定將受感染的患者與普通人群隔離。他們被安置在單獨的病房，以防止疾病傳播給他人。","word":"isolate"}},"isolated":{"createdAt":1781452134702,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"isolated形容詞表示某物遠離其他地方、孤立的或與外界隔絕的狀態。","options":["central","populated","isolated","connected"],"sentence":"The remote research station was ______ high in the mountains, far from any nearby towns or cities. Scientists working there could only communicate with the outside world through satellite phones.","translation":"遠程研究站位於高山之上，與任何附近的城鎮相隔離。在那裡工作的科學家只能通過衛星電話與外界溝通。","word":"isolated"}},"isolation":{"createdAt":1781840892403,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"isolation表示與他人分開或被隔開，用於防止疾病傳播的情況下最為合適。","options":["consultation","isolation","celebration","observation"],"sentence":"The patient was placed in ______ to prevent spreading the infectious disease to others. The hospital staff ensured he had no contact with any other patients or visitors.","translation":"患者被隔離以防止將傳染病傳播給他人。醫院工作人員確保他與其他患者或訪客沒有任何接觸。","word":"isolation"}},"issue":{"createdAt":1781515634900,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「issue」作為名詞表示報刊或雜誌的期號，即某一特定的版本或期次。","options":["section","edition","article","column"],"sentence":"The magazine released a special ______ last month featuring celebrity interviews. You can find it in the July collection at the library.","translation":"這本雜誌上個月發行了一期特刊，內容是名人訪談。你可以在圖書館的七月合訂本中找到它。","word":"issue"}},"itch":{"createdAt":1781515634901,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「itch」表示身體某個部位發癢或感到瘙癢的動作和感覺。","options":["burn","itch","swell","tingle"],"sentence":"My arm started to ______ after I got bitten by a mosquito. The sensation was so uncomfortable that I couldn't stop scratching.","translation":"被蚊子叮咬後，我的手臂開始發癢。這種感覺非常不舒服，我忍不住一直在抓。","word":"itch"}},"item":{"createdAt":1781625891347,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"item指列表、清單或議程中的一個單獨的條目或項目","options":["person","item","building","animal"],"sentence":"Please review the third ______ on the agenda before the meeting begins. It concerns the budget allocation for next quarter.","translation":"請在會議開始前查看議程上的第三項。它涉及下一季度的預算分配。","word":"item"}},"ivory":{"createdAt":1781843487265,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"ivory 是名詞，指象牙這種材料，通常來自大象的象牙，也可指象牙白的顏色。","options":["ebony","marble","ivory","pearl"],"sentence":"The piano had ______ keys that had yellowed with age over the decades. Museum experts confirmed these keys were made from elephant tusks harvested in the 1800s.","translation":"這架鋼琴的象牙色琴鍵經過數十年已經泛黃。博物館專家確認這些琴鍵是用19世紀採集的象牙製成的。","word":"ivory"}},"ivy":{"createdAt":1781499075059,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"常春藤是一種攀爬植物，以其能夠沿著牆壁和其他表面生長而聞名。","options":["moss","ivy","grass","vines"],"sentence":"The old brick mansion was covered in wild ______ that had grown over decades. The climbing plant created a picturesque appearance as it wound around the walls and windows.","translation":"古老的磚砌大宅被數十年來生長的野生常春藤覆蓋。這種攀爬植物纏繞在牆壁和窗戶周圍，營造了一種如畫的外觀。","word":"ivy"}},"jasmine":{"createdAt":1781948564907,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"茉莉是一種常見的觀賞花卉，以其濃郁的香氣和白色花瓣聞名，經常被用來製作香水和茶葉。","options":["rose","jasmine","tulip","daisy"],"sentence":"The garden was filled with the sweet fragrance of ______ flowers blooming in the warm evening. Sarah picked a delicate white blossom to wear in her hair, enjoying its distinctive floral perfume.","translation":"花園裡充滿了______花在溫暖的夜晚綻放的甜蜜香氣。莎拉摘了一朵精緻的白色花瓣戴在頭髮上，享受著它獨特的花香。","word":"jasmine"}},"jealous":{"createdAt":1781747309097,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"jealous 用來形容因害怕失去某人或某物的關注而產生的不安全感和猜疑。","options":["grateful","jealous","curious","confused"],"sentence":"She felt ______ when her best friend started spending more time with someone else. Her constant worry that she was being replaced revealed her insecure nature.","translation":"當她最好的朋友開始花更多時間與別人在一起時，她感到嫉妒。她不斷擔心自己被取代，這反映了她缺乏安全感的本性。","word":"jealous"}},"jointly":{"createdAt":1781848934151,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"jointly表示共同地或聯合地進行某項活動","options":["separately","jointly","slowly","privately"],"sentence":"The two companies decided to ______ develop a new technology. By pooling their resources and expertise, they could complete the project faster.","translation":"兩家公司決定聯合開發一項新技術。通過整合資源和專業知識，他們可以更快地完成項目。","word":"jointly"}},"jolly":{"createdAt":1781836375378,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"jolly形容詞表示興高采烈的、快活的或充滿歡樂的。","options":["stern","jolly","grumpy","serious"],"sentence":"Santa Claus is traditionally depicted as a ______ figure with a big smile and round belly. His cheerful demeanor brings joy to children everywhere.","translation":"聖誕老人傳統上被描繪成一個興高采烈的人物，帶著燦爛笑容和圓潤的肚子。他愉快的舉止給世界各地的兒童帶來歡樂。","word":"jolly"}},"journal":{"createdAt":1781950727565,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"journal 指期刊或定期出版的學術雜誌。","options":["novel","journal","newspaper","textbook"],"sentence":"She publishes her research in a prestigious ______ that reaches thousands of scientists worldwide. The academic publication has been in existence for over fifty years.","translation":"她在一份享有聲譽的期刊上發表研究，該期刊觸及全球數千名科學家。這份學術出版物已存在超過五十年。","word":"journal"}},"journalism":{"createdAt":1781713470387,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"新聞工作是指從事新聞採編、報導和傳播信息的行業和專業。","options":["agriculture","mathematics","journalism","medicine"],"sentence":"She studied ______ in university and now works as a reporter for a major newspaper. Her job involves investigating stories, conducting interviews, and writing articles for publication.","translation":"她在大學裡學習新聞工作，現在是一家主要報紙的記者。她的工作涉及調查故事、進行採訪和撰寫文章以供發表。","word":"journalism"}},"journalist":{"createdAt":1781452134700,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"journalist名詞指的是以撰寫和報導新聞為職業的專業人士。","options":["baker","journalist","architect","mechanic"],"sentence":"The ______ spent weeks investigating the corruption scandal and interviewing witnesses. Her research was published as a detailed news report in the morning newspaper.","translation":"這名新聞記者花了數週時間調查腐敗醜聞並採訪證人。她的研究以詳細新聞報導的形式發表在晨報上。","word":"journalist"}},"journey":{"createdAt":1781310338172,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"journey 是指一次旅行或旅程，通常涉及較長的距離和時間。","options":["destination","journey","vehicle","schedule"],"sentence":"Their ______ across three continents took nearly six months to complete. They visited dozens of cities and crossed multiple oceans during this extended expedition.","translation":"他們跨越三大洲的旅程耗時近六個月才完成。在這次漫長的遠征中，他們訪問了許多城市並跨越多個海洋。","word":"journey"}},"judge":{"createdAt":1781437220555,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「Judge」作名詞指在法庭上主持訴訟、解釋法律並做出判決的司法官員。","options":["witness","lawyer","judge","defendant"],"sentence":"The ______ carefully reviewed all the evidence before making a final decision in the trial. His responsibility was to apply the law fairly and determine the verdict.","translation":"法官在審判中做出最終判決之前仔細審查了所有證據。他的責任是公正地適用法律並裁定判決。","word":"judge"}},"junction":{"createdAt":1781836375370,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"junction是聯結點或樞紐，特別是在交通運輸中多條路線匯合的地方。","options":["station","junction","platform","depot"],"sentence":"The train ______ was crowded with passengers transferring between different rail lines. Multiple tracks converged at this central point in the station.","translation":"火車樞紐站擁擠著在不同鐵路線之間轉換的乘客。多條軌道在車站的這個中心點匯合。","word":"junction"}},"junior":{"createdAt":1781481124693,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"junior 指位置、級別或地位較低，或年紀較小的人，通常具有較少的經驗。","options":["experienced","skilled","novice","retired"],"sentence":"The ______ accountant was assigned to assist the senior partner on the important audit. She had just completed her training and was eager to learn more about client management.","translation":"初級會計師被指派協助資深合夥人進行重要的審計。她剛完成培訓，渴望學習更多關於客戶管理的知識。","word":"junior"}},"junk":{"createdAt":1781951900953,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"junk指沒有價值的廢棄物或垃圾，通常是人們想要丟棄的無用物品。","options":["treasures","junk","artifacts","antiques"],"sentence":"The old storage room was filled with ______ that had been accumulated over decades. The owner decided to throw out most of the useless items and start fresh.","translation":"老舊的儲藏室堆滿了數十年來積累的廢棄物。房主決定扔掉大部分無用的東西，重新開始。","word":"junk"}},"just":{"createdAt":1781449588282,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"just作為形容詞時表示「公平的、正當的」，在法律或道德評判的背景下使用。","options":["defensive","just","trillion","sensibly"],"sentence":"The judge made a ______ decision that satisfied both parties in the lawsuit. Everyone agreed the ruling was fair and based on the facts presented in court.","translation":"法官做出了一個公平的判決，使訴訟雙方都感到滿意。每個人都同意這項裁定是公正的，並以法庭上呈現的事實為基礎。","word":"just"}},"justification":{"createdAt":1781832089959,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"justification 指為某件事提供合理的解釋或辯護，用於證明某事的合理性","options":["punishment","justification","promotion","transfer"],"sentence":"The manager demanded a ______ for the employee's sudden absence from work. Without a valid reason, the employee faced disciplinary action.","translation":"經理要求員工對其突然缺勤工作給出理由。沒有充分的原因，該員工將面臨紀律處分。","word":"justification"}},"justify":{"createdAt":1781651775064,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"justify 表示為某事提供理由或證明其正當性和合理性。","options":["alternative","childhood","justify","frustrate"],"sentence":"The manager tried to ______ the controversial decision to all the employees. However, no matter what reasons were provided, most workers still disagreed with the choice.","translation":"經理試圖為這個有爭議的決定向所有員工辯護。然而，無論提供什麼理由，大多數工人仍然不同意這個選擇。","word":"justify"}},"juvenile":{"createdAt":1781950727560,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"juvenile 指青少年的或與年輕人相關的，也可指不成熟的行為。","options":["adult","corporate","juvenile","criminal"],"sentence":"The court handles ______ cases involving people under the age of eighteen. These young offenders receive different legal treatment than adults.","translation":"法院處理涉及十八歲以下的人的少年案件。這些年輕的違法者受到與成年人不同的法律待遇。","word":"juvenile"}},"kidnap":{"createdAt":1781860901467,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"kidnap是動詞，表示非法綁架他人，通常為了勒索金錢或其他利益","options":["rescue","kidnap","interview","hire"],"sentence":"The criminals planned to ______ the wealthy businessman's son for ransom. The police launched an immediate investigation and arrested the suspects before they could execute their plot.","translation":"罪犯計畫綁架這位富有商人的兒子以勒索贖金。警方立即展開調查，並在他們執行計畫之前逮捕了嫌疑人。","word":"kidnap"}},"kidney":{"createdAt":1781362281726,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"kidney指的是腎臟，是人體的重要器官，負責過濾廢物和產生尿液。","options":["liver","kidney","heart","lung"],"sentence":"The patient underwent surgery to remove a damaged ______ from his body. The organ had stopped functioning properly due to disease.","translation":"患者進行了手術以移除他體內受損的腎臟。這個器官因疾病而停止了正常功能。","word":"kidney"}},"kin":{"createdAt":1781939439464,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"kin是名詞，指家屬或親戚，通常指血緣關係的家人成員。","options":["colleagues","kin","neighbors","competitors"],"sentence":"Sarah invited all her ______ to the family reunion, including cousins from three different states. The celebration brought together over fifty relatives who hadn't seen each other in years.","translation":"莎拉邀請所有親屬參加家庭聚會，包括來自三個不同州的表親。這次慶祝活動讓五十多位多年未見面的親戚聚集在一起。","word":"kin"}},"knock":{"createdAt":1781402539337,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"knock 是名詞，指敲打門或物體表面所發出的聲音或動作。","options":["ring","knock","whisper","footstep"],"sentence":"She heard a loud ______ on the door early in the morning. Three rapid raps startled her awake from her sleep.","translation":"她一大早聽到門上發出的大聲敲打聲。三下快速的敲打聲將她從睡眠中驚醒。","word":"knock"}},"knowledge":{"createdAt":1781362281668,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"knowledge指的是所掌握的信息、事實或技能，來自學習或經驗。","options":["opinion","knowledge","guess","belief"],"sentence":"Her extensive ______ of history made her an excellent teacher. Students appreciated how deeply she understood historical events and their significance.","translation":"她廣泛的歷史知識使她成為一位優秀的教師。學生欣賞她對歷史事件及其重要性的深刻理解。","word":"knowledge"}},"label":{"createdAt":1781622232185,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"label 作為動詞表示在物品上貼標籤或標記信息。","options":["label","ship","paint","seal"],"sentence":"The factory workers must ______ each product with the manufacturing date and batch number. This information helps customers identify when the item was produced.","translation":"工廠工人必須在每個產品上貼上製造日期和批號標籤。此信息幫助客戶確定何時生產該物品。","word":"label"}},"labor":{"createdAt":1781832089957,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"labor 作為名詞指勞工或工人，特別是指從事體力工作的人力資源","options":["materials","labor","equipment","capital"],"sentence":"The company decided to hire more ______ to meet the increased production demands. These workers would be responsible for assembling the new product line.","translation":"公司決定聘僱更多的勞工來滿足增加的生產需求。這些工人將負責組裝新產品線。","word":"labor"}},"laboratory":{"createdAt":1781565657695,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"laboratory 名詞指進行科學實驗和研究的專門場所，配備各種科學儀器和設備。","options":["classroom","laboratory","office","warehouse"],"sentence":"The scientists conducted their chemical experiments in the ______ using specialized equipment. The facility had safety protocols and ventilation systems to protect researchers from hazardous substances.","translation":"科學家在實驗室中使用專門設備進行化學實驗。該設施有安全協議和通風系統，以保護研究人員免受有害物質的傷害。","word":"laboratory"}},"laborious":{"createdAt":1781746685546,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"laborious指的是費力的、辛苦的、繁重的，用來形容需要付出大量體力或腦力的工作。","options":["laborious","essential","stadium","tolerance"],"sentence":"The task of organizing the entire library was ______ and time-consuming. Workers spent weeks cataloging thousands of books and arranging them on shelves.","translation":"整理整個圖書館的工作是費力且耗時的。工作人員花了數週對數千本書進行編目並將其放在書架上。","word":"laborious"}},"lack":{"createdAt":1781402154553,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lack表示缺少或不足，在這裡指資金和員工的短缺導致了專案的失敗。","options":["possess","lack","compel","suspect"],"sentence":"The project failed due to a ______ of funding and experienced staff. Without sufficient resources and qualified personnel, the team could not complete the work on schedule.","translation":"這個專案因為缺少資金和有經驗的員工而失敗。沒有足夠的資源和合格的人員，團隊無法按時完成工作。","word":"lack"}},"landlord":{"createdAt":1781839950959,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"landlord 是指擁有並出租房產的人,對租住房屋的維護和修繕負有責任。","options":["landlord","tenant","contractor","neighbor"],"sentence":"The ______ refused to fix the broken heating system in the apartment. Since he owns the building, he has the legal responsibility to maintain all essential utilities.","translation":"房東拒絕修理公寓裡損壞的供暖系統。既然他擁有這棟建築,他在法律上有責任維護所有基本設施。","word":"landlord"}},"landmark":{"createdAt":1781564440928,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"landmark 表示地標，指著名的建築物或地點，用來識別或記住某個位置。","options":["restaurant","landmark","street","shop"],"sentence":"The Eiffel Tower is one of the most famous ______ in the world. Millions of tourists visit this iconic structure each year to admire its architectural significance.","translation":"埃菲爾鐵塔是世界上最著名的地標之一。每年數百萬遊客參觀這個標誌性結構來欣賞其建築意義。","word":"landmark"}},"landscape":{"createdAt":1781619188937,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"landscape 指自然的風景，特別是寬闊的戶外場景，常用於藝術和攝影中。","options":["portrait","landscape","architecture","still life"],"sentence":"The painter captured the beauty of the rural ______ in her oil paintings. Rolling hills, farmlands, and wildflower meadows filled each canvas.","translation":"畫家在她的油畫中捕捉了鄉村風景的美麗。層疊起伏的山丘、農地和野花草地填滿了每一幅畫布。","word":"landscape"}},"landslide":{"createdAt":1781777331350,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"landslide作為選舉用語，特指一方候選人或政黨以懸殊差距贏得選舉的情況","options":["landslide","majority","competition","campaign"],"sentence":"The candidate won the election by a ______, receiving more votes than all her opponents combined. Her overwhelming victory surprised no one, as polls had predicted her dominance for weeks.","translation":"這位候選人以大勝贏得了選舉，獲得的選票超過她所有對手的總和。她的壓倒性勝利沒有讓任何人感到驚訝，因為民調幾週來一直預測她會大勝。","word":"landslide"}},"lane":{"createdAt":1781424157172,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lane 在游泳中特指為每個選手劃分的單獨水道。","options":["pool","lane","course","field"],"sentence":"The swimmer dove into his assigned ______ and began racing against the other competitors. Each athlete had their own separate swimming path to prevent interference.","translation":"游泳者跳入他指定的泳道，開始與其他選手競賽。每位運動員都有自己獨立的游泳路線以防止干擾。","word":"lane"}},"latter":{"createdAt":1781619188921,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"latter 指兩者中的後者，與 former 相對，用來區分先後順序。","options":["former","latter","initial","previous"],"sentence":"Between the two proposals, I prefer the ______ one because it offers better long-term benefits. The second option includes more comprehensive coverage and lower costs.","translation":"在兩個提案中，我更喜歡後面的那個，因為它提供更好的長期利益。第二個選項包括更全面的覆蓋範圍和更低的成本。","word":"latter"}},"launch":{"createdAt":1781515372607,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"launch指正式推出或發起一個新的產品、計畫或活動","options":["fulfillment","launch","force","chief"],"sentence":"The company will ______ its new product line at the international trade show next month. Marketing teams are preparing promotional materials and coordinating with distributors to ensure a successful introduction.","translation":"該公司將在下個月的國際貿易展上推出其新產品線。市場營銷團隊正在準備宣傳材料並與經銷商協調，以確保成功推出。","word":"launch"}},"lavish":{"createdAt":1781955529034,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lavish 形容豪華、奢華或花費大量金錢的事物。","options":["simple","lavish","casual","modest"],"sentence":"The celebrity hosted a ______ party at her mansion with champagne, caviar, and live entertainment. Guests were impressed by the opulent decorations and the extravagant five-course meal served throughout the evening.","translation":"這位名人在她的宅邸裡舉辦了一場奢華派對，提供香檳、魚子醬和現場娛樂。嘉賓對華麗的裝飾和整個晚上提供的奢侈五道菜大餐印象深刻。","word":"lavish"}},"lawful":{"createdAt":1781484415236,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"lawful意指符合法律規定和法律許可的，是合法的和受到法律允許的。","options":["dangerous","common","lawful","popular"],"sentence":"The police officer explained that parking in that location was not ______ without a special permit. The city ordinance clearly prohibited it, and violators would receive fines.","translation":"警察解釋說，在沒有特殊許可證的情況下在該位置停車是不合法的。市法令明確禁止這樣做，違反者將被罰款。","word":"lawful"}},"lawsuit":{"createdAt":1782018712117,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「lawsuit」指在法院進行的法律訴訟或訴案，涉及兩方當事人的法律紛爭。","options":["contract","lawsuit","advertisement","treaty"],"sentence":"The company filed a ______ against its competitor for patent infringement last month. The case is now being heard in the federal court system.","translation":"該公司上個月因專利侵權對競爭對手提起訴訟。該案件現在在聯邦法院系統中進行審理。","word":"lawsuit"}},"layout":{"createdAt":1781886743280,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Layout 指的是物品或空間的具體排列方式，強調各個元素在空間中的相對位置。","options":["design","layout","structure","blueprint"],"sentence":"The architect presented the ______ of the new office building to the client. The plan showed where each wall, door, and window would be positioned on every floor.","translation":"建築師向客戶展示了新辦公大樓的佈局。該計畫顯示了每層樓上每面牆、門和窗戶的位置。","word":"layout"}},"lead":{"createdAt":1782006215682,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「lead」作為動詞表示「領導」或「帶領」，指引導他人朝某個方向或目標前進。","options":["follow","lead","join","watch"],"sentence":"The experienced coach will ______ the team to victory in the championship match. Players trust his strategic decisions because he has successfully guided many previous squads to win titles.","translation":"資深教練將在錦標賽中帶領球隊贏得勝利。球員信任他的戰略決策，因為他曾成功地指導許多前隊伍贏得冠軍。","word":"lead"}},"leadership":{"createdAt":1781256444516,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"leadership指領導的能力和品質，包括指揮、指導和激勵他人的能力。","options":["communication","leadership","intelligence","patience"],"sentence":"The new CEO demonstrated exceptional ______ by rallying the demoralized team and implementing a clear vision for recovery. Within six months, employee morale and productivity had significantly improved.","translation":"新執行長通過鼓舞士氣低落的團隊並實施明確的復甦願景，展現出卓越的領導能力。六個月內，員工士氣和生產力都顯著提高。","word":"leadership"}},"league":{"createdAt":1781622232188,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"league 指由多個運動隊或組織組成的聯合會或聯賽組織。","options":["league","team","tournament","club"],"sentence":"The basketball player signed a contract with the national ______ to compete against the best teams in the country. He will play fifty games throughout the regular season.","translation":"籃球運動員與國家聯賽簽訂合約，與國內最好的球隊競爭。他將在常規賽中進行五十場比賽。","word":"league"}},"leak":{"createdAt":1781693484714,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"leak 表示液體或氣體無意中從容器或管道中滲出或漏出，通常是緩慢且不受控制的。","options":["spray","leak","drip","pour"],"sentence":"The old pipe started to ______ water into the basement. We called a plumber immediately because we could see puddles forming on the floor.","translation":"舊管子開始向地下室漏水。我們立即叫了水管工，因為我們可以看到地板上形成了水坑。","word":"leak"}},"leap":{"createdAt":1781775598767,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"leap作為名詞表示「跳躍」，特別是指有力的、跨越較大距離的跳躍動作。","options":["stride","tumble","leap","crawl"],"sentence":"The athlete made an incredible ______ across the long-jump pit and broke the school record. His explosive jump was so powerful that he cleared the previous distance by several inches.","translation":"運動員在跳遠池上完成了一次令人難以置信的跳躍，打破了學校紀錄。他的爆發力十足的跳躍非常強有力，他清楚地超越了之前的距離好幾英寸。","word":"leap"}},"lease":{"createdAt":1781832761707,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lease 作動詞表示租借或租用某物，通常涉及簽訂合約和定期付款。","options":["purchase","rent","demolish","inspect"],"sentence":"She decided to ______ an apartment in the city center for two years. The landlord provided her with a signed contract that outlined all the payment terms and conditions.","translation":"她決定在市中心租一間公寓兩年。房東提供了一份簽署的合約，其中列明了所有的付款條款和條件。","word":"lease"}},"lecture":{"createdAt":1781428458255,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"lecture在此指教授在課堂上進行的正式授課或演講。","options":["crisis","citation","lecture","choke"],"sentence":"The professor gave a two-hour ______ on quantum physics to the entire class. Students took notes throughout the presentation to understand the complex theories being taught.","translation":"教授為整個班級進行了一場兩小時的量子物理學講座。學生們在整個演講過程中做筆記，以理解所教授的複雜理論。","word":"lecture"}},"lecturer":{"createdAt":1781848934151,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lecturer指在大學或學院進行教學或演講的人","options":["student","lecturer","janitor","chef"],"sentence":"The visiting ______ from Oxford University gave a brilliant presentation on medieval history. The audience was captivated by her extensive knowledge and engaging delivery.","translation":"來自牛津大學的客座講師進行了關於中世紀歷史的精彩演講。觀眾被她淵博的知識和引人入勝的演講所吸引。","word":"lecturer"}},"leftover":{"createdAt":1781582939256,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"leftover 指用完飯後剩下的食物，與冷藏和重新加熱食用的敘述相符。","options":["recipe","leftover","ingredient","plate"],"sentence":"Sarah stored the ______ from yesterday's dinner in a container and placed it in the refrigerator for tomorrow's lunch. The roasted chicken and vegetables would still taste delicious when reheated.","translation":"莎拉把昨天晚餐的剩菜放進容器中，並將其放入冰箱以備明天的午餐。烤雞和蔬菜在加熱後仍然會很美味。","word":"leftover"}},"legacy":{"createdAt":1781481311491,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"legacy指的是前人留下的遺產、遺贈或深遠的影響。","options":["secret","legacy","hobby","schedule"],"sentence":"The philanthropist's ______ included millions of dollars donated to educational institutions. Her children continue her charitable work to preserve what she left behind for future generations.","translation":"這位慈善家的遺產包括捐獻給教育機構的數百萬美元。她的孩子們繼續她的慈善事業以保護她為後代留下的東西。","word":"legacy"}},"legend":{"createdAt":1781484415216,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"legend是指世代相傳的故事或傳說，通常涉及超自然或歷史人物，真偽難以驗證。","options":["contract","invoice","legend","recipe"],"sentence":"According to an ancient ______, a magical dragon once guarded the village from invaders. Nobody could prove whether this story was true or merely a myth passed down through generations.","translation":"根據古老的傳說，一條神奇的龍曾經保護村莊免受入侵者的侵害。沒有人能證明這個故事是真實的還是世代相傳的神話。","word":"legend"}},"legendary":{"createdAt":1781841505536,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"legendary 形容詞表示某人或某事因其非凡成就而在歷史上或傳統中廣為人知，具有傳奇性質。","options":["legendary","wonder","pollution","entitle"],"sentence":"The ______ musician Bob Dylan won the Nobel Prize in Literature for his outstanding contributions to music and poetry. His songs have inspired generations of artists and continue to be studied in universities around the world.","translation":"傳奇音樂家鮑勃·迪倫因其在音樂和詩歌方面的傑出貢獻而獲得諾貝爾文學獎。他的歌曲激勵了幾代藝術家，並繼續在世界各地的大學中被研究。","word":"legendary"}},"legislate":{"createdAt":1781961517450,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"legislate 指的是正式制定或通過法律的行為，強調的是立法的法律程序。","options":["enforce","legislate","discuss","propose"],"sentence":"The government voted to ______ new environmental protection laws. This process required members of parliament to debate and pass the bill through official procedures.","translation":"政府投票表決要制定新的環境保護法律。這個過程需要議會成員辯論並通過官方程序使其生效。","word":"legislate"}},"legislation":{"createdAt":1781848934153,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"legislation指由政府制定和頒布的法律或法令","options":["treaty","legislation","movie","advertisement"],"sentence":"The new ______ on environmental protection requires companies to reduce their carbon emissions by 50% within five years. Parliament passed this law to combat climate change.","translation":"新的環境保護立法要求公司在五年內將碳排放減少50%。議會通過了這項法律來應對氣候變化。","word":"legislation"}},"legislative":{"createdAt":1781832089958,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"legislative 意為與制定法律相關的，特別是指立法機構或立法活動","options":["judicial","executive","legislative","administrative"],"sentence":"The parliament passed a new ______ proposal to address climate change. The bill was debated for months before being voted on by members of congress.","translation":"議會通過了一項新的立法提案來應對氣候變化。該法案在由國會議員投票表決前已討論了數月。","word":"legislative"}},"legislator":{"createdAt":1781401803897,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"legislator是指有權制定或投票通過法律的立法委員或立法者。","options":["lawyer","lawmaker","judge","minister"],"sentence":"The new ______ proposed a bill to increase funding for public education. This elected official will vote on the law next week in parliament.","translation":"那位新的立法者提議了一項增加公共教育經費的法案。這位當選的官員下週將在議會投票表決該法律。","word":"legislator"}},"legitimate":{"createdAt":1781836375371,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"legitimate形容詞表示合法的、正當的或法律允許的。","options":["questionable","legitimate","doubtful","suspicious"],"sentence":"The court ruled that his claim to the inheritance was ______ and fully supported by law. All proper documentation and legal procedures had been followed.","translation":"法院裁定他對遺產的索賠是合法的，並得到法律充分支持。所有適當的文件和法律程序都已遵循。","word":"legitimate"}},"legitimately":{"createdAt":1781710289366,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"legitimately 是副詞，表示「合法地、依法地」或「合理地、可接受地」，用於描述符合法律或規則的行為或主張。","options":["falsely","legitimately","questionably","dubiously"],"sentence":"The company can ______ claim that its products are environmentally friendly because it has obtained all necessary environmental certifications and passed rigorous government testing. The documentation proves their manufacturing processes meet all legal standards.","translation":"這家公司可以合法地聲稱其產品環保，因為它已獲得所有必要的環保認證並通過了嚴格的政府檢測。文件證明其製造過程符合所有法律標準。","word":"legitimately"}},"leisure":{"createdAt":1781842254310,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"leisure 作為形容詞表示空閒的、用於休閒的，指不受工作或責任束縛的時間。","options":["busy","leisure","stressful","urgent"],"sentence":"After working overtime for six months, Tom finally had some ______ time to relax and pursue his hobbies. He could now enjoy reading and painting without worrying about work deadlines.","translation":"在加班六個月後，湯姆終於有了一些閒暇時間來放鬆和追求他的愛好。他現在可以享受閱讀和繪畫，而不用擔心工作截止日期。","word":"leisure"}},"lengthy":{"createdAt":1781926370994,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lengthy 意思是冗長的、漫長的，用來描述時間很長且往往令人厭倦的事物。","options":["brief","lengthy","productive","scheduled"],"sentence":"The meeting was so ______ that many employees fell asleep before it ended. It lasted for over five hours without a single break.","translation":"那場會議是如此冗長，以至於許多員工在它結束前就睡著了。它持續了五個多小時，沒有休息過。","word":"lengthy"}},"lethal":{"createdAt":1781626081102,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"lethal 作為形容詞表示能夠導致死亡或極其危險的，用於描述具有致命性質的物質或情況。","options":["harmless","beneficial","lethal","mild"],"sentence":"The poison was ______ enough to kill a person within minutes of ingestion. The medical team had no antidote available to reverse its fatal effects.","translation":"這種毒藥足以在攝入後幾分鐘內殺死一個人。醫療團隊沒有可用的解毒劑來逆轉其致命的影響。","word":"lethal"}},"liability":{"createdAt":1781951900952,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"liability在法律和財務語境中指一個人或組織的法律責任和義務，需要承擔的負債。","options":["asset","liability","profit","expense"],"sentence":"The company's legal ______ increased significantly after the factory accident harmed several workers. They would have to pay compensation and face potential lawsuits.","translation":"工廠事故傷害了多名工人後，公司的法律責任大幅增加。他們必須支付賠償金並面臨潛在的訴訟。","word":"liability"}},"liberal":{"createdAt":1781775598765,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"liberal作為形容詞表示「心胸寬闊的；開放的」，用來描述接受多元觀點和包容不同文化的人。","options":["rigid","open-minded","hostile","conservative"],"sentence":"Her ______ attitude toward different cultures made her very accepting of people from all backgrounds. She welcomed diverse perspectives and never judged others based on their beliefs or traditions.","translation":"她對不同文化的心胸寬闊態度使她對來自各種背景的人非常接納。她歡迎多元觀點，從不根據他人的信仰或傳統對其進行評判。","word":"liberal"}},"license":{"createdAt":1781836375369,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"license是許可證或執照，由官方機構頒發，允許某人從事某項活動。","options":["certificate","license","permit","diploma"],"sentence":"Before operating a taxi, the driver must obtain a ______ from the government. The document certifies that he has passed all required safety and knowledge tests.","translation":"在運營計程車前，駕駛員必須獲得政府頒發的執照。該文件証明他已通過所有必需的安全和知識測試。","word":"license"}},"lifeguard":{"createdAt":1781484415226,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lifeguard是指在游泳池、海灘等地專門負責監督和救助遇到危險的人的工作人員。","options":["teacher","lifeguard","coach","janitor"],"sentence":"The ______ jumped into the pool immediately when he noticed a child struggling in the deep end. His quick action and swimming skills saved the young swimmer's life.","translation":"當救生員注意到一個孩子在深水區掙扎時，他立即跳進了游泳池。他迅速的反應和游泳技能救了這位年輕游泳者的生命。","word":"lifeguard"}},"lighten":{"createdAt":1781840892408,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lighten表示變亮或變淡，用於描述顏色或光線逐漸變淡的過程。","options":["darken","lighten","freeze","thicken"],"sentence":"As the sun rose higher in the sky, the night sky began to ______ from dark blue to pale pink. The transition lasted about thirty minutes before dawn fully broke.","translation":"當太陽在天空升得更高時，夜空開始從深藍色變淡到淡粉紅色。這個過程持續了大約三十分鐘，直到天亮。","word":"lighten"}},"likewise":{"createdAt":1781481124699,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"likewise 表示以相同的方式或類似的方式，用於表示相似的情況。","options":["differently","oppositely","similarly","reluctantly"],"sentence":"John enjoyed playing basketball, and his brother ______ developed a passion for the same sport. They spent countless afternoons practicing together on the court.","translation":"約翰喜歡打籃球，他的兄弟同樣對這項運動充滿熱情。他們在球場上花了無數個下午一起練習。","word":"likewise"}},"limb":{"createdAt":1781775363747,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"limb 是指身體的肢體，如手臂、腿等，醫學上用來描述從肩膀到指尖的整個身體部分。","options":["muscle","arm","bone","joint"],"sentence":"The injured athlete couldn't move his right ______ after the accident. The doctor confirmed that the fracture extended from his shoulder down to his fingertips.","translation":"受傷的運動員在事故後無法移動他的右側______。醫生確認骨折從他的肩膀一直延伸到指尖。","word":"limb"}},"liquor":{"createdAt":1781798927520,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"liquor 特指含有酒精的飲料，尤其是烈酒，不包括咖啡或果汁。","options":["beverages","liquor","coffee","juice"],"sentence":"The store had a special promotion on ______ last weekend. Customers could buy whiskey, vodka, and rum at discounted prices.","translation":"上週末商店對烈酒進行特價促銷。顧客可以以折扣價購買威士忌、伏特加和朗姆酒。","word":"liquor"}},"literal":{"createdAt":1781840667146,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"literal指的是按照字面上的實際意義理解，而不是比喻或引申的意義。","options":["figurative","serious","literal","sarcastic"],"sentence":"Don't take his comment about being 'dead tired' in a ______ sense. He simply means he is very exhausted after working all day.","translation":"不要按照字面意思理解他說的「累死了」這句話。他只是在表示整天工作後感到非常疲憊。","word":"literal"}},"literally":{"createdAt":1781773623461,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"literally作為副詞表示「逐字地」或「實在地」，此處用於強調一個表達方式的字面意思，而非比喻意思。","options":["virtually","literally","practically","almost"],"sentence":"When he said the weather was so hot he could ______ fry an egg on the pavement, his friend laughed. Of course, the temperature wasn't actually high enough to cook food on the ground.","translation":"當他說天氣炎熱到他可以在人行道上煎雞蛋時，他的朋友笑了。當然，溫度實際上還不夠高到能在地上烹飪食物。","word":"literally"}},"literate":{"createdAt":1781774456602,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"literate 表示能夠識字和閱讀，具有基本的讀寫能力。","options":["wealthy","healthy","educated","employed"],"sentence":"In the developing country, only 40% of the population was ______, unable to read or write effectively. Education programs were urgently needed to improve literacy rates.","translation":"在該發展中國家，只有40%的人口識字，許多人無法有效閱讀和書寫。教育計畫迫切需要以提高識字率。","word":"literate"}},"literature":{"createdAt":1781693254756,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"literature指的是文學作品的總稱，包括各種書籍、詩歌和戲劇創作。","options":["furniture","literature","music","cuisine"],"sentence":"She spent her summer reading classic ______ from authors like Jane Austen and Charles Dickens. Her bookshelf was filled with novels, poetry collections, and dramatic works.","translation":"她花了整個夏天閱讀珍·奧斯汀和查爾斯·狄更斯等作家的經典文學作品。她的書架上擺滿了小說、詩集和戲劇作品。","word":"literature"}},"loan":{"createdAt":1781848934138,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"loan指銀行或其他機構提供的借款，通常需要利息償還","options":["gift","loan","scholarship","inheritance"],"sentence":"He went to the bank to apply for a ______ to buy a house. The bank officer reviewed his income and credit score before approving the amount.","translation":"他去銀行申請貸款購買房子。銀行職員在批准金額前審查了他的收入和信用評分。","word":"loan"}},"lobby":{"createdAt":1782018712118,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「lobby」在此指建築物的入口大廳或前廳，是公眾集合和會面的地方。","options":["rooftop","basement","lobby","kitchen"],"sentence":"Environmental groups gathered in the ______ of the parliament building to meet with legislators. They wanted to discuss their concerns about the new bill face-to-face.","translation":"環保團體在國會大廈的大廳聚集，以便與立法者會面。他們想面對面討論他們對新法案的關切。","word":"lobby"}},"location":{"createdAt":1781839703151,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"location指場所或位置，與situated in the city centre near transportation（位於市中心靠近交通）直接相符。","options":["timing","design","location","budget"],"sentence":"The ______ of the new office has been carefully selected. It is situated in the city centre near public transportation and major business hubs.","translation":"新辦公室的位置已被仔細選擇。它位於市中心，靠近公共交通和主要商業樞紐。","word":"location"}},"lodge":{"createdAt":1781961517452,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lodge 在這裡是動詞，表示某物被固定或卡入另一物體中。","options":["hide","lodge","settle","rest"],"sentence":"A small stone managed to ______ itself in the bicycle tire during the mountain ride. Despite the rider's efforts, it remained firmly stuck until they reached a repair shop.","translation":"一塊小石子在山地自行車騎行中卡在自行車輪胎裡。儘管騎手的努力，它一直牢牢卡著，直到他們到達修車店。","word":"lodge"}},"logical":{"createdAt":1781773623459,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"logical作為形容詞表示「合邏輯的」或「合理的」，指思路清晰、符合邏輯規則的。","options":["rational","logical","reasonable","smart"],"sentence":"Her argument was very ______ and easy to follow from beginning to end. She presented facts in a clear order where each point led naturally to the next conclusion.","translation":"她的論點非常合邏輯，從頭到尾都很容易理解。她以清晰的順序呈現事實，其中每一點自然導向下一個結論。","word":"logical"}},"long":{"createdAt":1781841742844,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"long 作動詞表示「渴望、極想」，通常用於表達強烈而持久的願望。","options":["dread","long","fail","refuse"],"sentence":"After years of living abroad, she ______ to return to her hometown. The thought of seeing her family again filled her with deep yearning.","translation":"在國外生活多年後，她渴望回到家鄉。想到能再次見到家人讓她充滿深深的渴望。","word":"long"}},"loosely":{"createdAt":1781667024993,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"loosely表示不緊密、鬆散的狀態，與firmly或tightly的含義相反。","options":["firmly","tightly","securely","loosely"],"sentence":"The rope was tied ______ around the package, allowing it to shift slightly during transport. The delivery company had to retie it securely to prevent damage.","translation":"繩子鬆散地捆在包裹周圍，使其在運輸過程中可以輕微移動。快遞公司必須重新牢固地綁它以防止損壞。","word":"loosely"}},"loosen":{"createdAt":1781839703154,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"loosen指鬆開或放鬆，與gradually released the tension and let descend（逐漸釋放張力和讓下降）完全相符。","options":["tighten","secure","loosen","fasten"],"sentence":"She had to ______ her grip on the rope to let the climber descend safely. The guide gradually released the tension to control the pace.","translation":"她必須鬆開抓著繩子的力度，以讓登山者安全下降。嚮導逐漸釋放張力來控制速度。","word":"loosen"}},"lotion":{"createdAt":1781738105694,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lotion 是一種液態或乳狀的皮膚護理產品，用於滋潤和保護皮膚。","options":["powder","lotion","soap","shampoo"],"sentence":"After taking a hot bath, she applied a moisturizing ______ to her dry skin to keep it soft and hydrated. The creamy product spread smoothly over her arms and legs.","translation":"洗完熱水澡後，她在乾燥的皮膚上涂了保濕乳液以保持皮膚柔軟和滋潤。這種乳狀產品在她的手臂和腿上均勻塗開。","word":"lotion"}},"lottery":{"createdAt":1781402154554,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"lottery指一種靠運氣決定贏家的遊戲或抽籤活動，通常涉及購票和獲獎。","options":["hijack","compel","lottery","stance"],"sentence":"She won the ______ and received a prize of one million dollars. After years of buying tickets every week, her luck finally changed when she matched all the winning numbers.","translation":"她贏得了彩票，獲得了一百萬美元的獎金。在多年每週購買彩票後，她終於幸運地配對了所有中獎號碼。","word":"lottery"}},"lullaby":{"createdAt":1781481124703,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"lullaby 是唱給嬰幼兒聽以幫助他們睡眠的柔和歌曲。","options":["anthem","ballad","cradle song","hymn"],"sentence":"The mother gently sang a ______ to her baby to help him fall asleep at bedtime. The soothing melody and soft lyrics gradually calmed his restless movements.","translation":"母親溫柔地唱了一首搖籃曲來幫助她的嬰兒在睡前入睡。舒緩的旋律和溫柔的歌詞逐漸平復他的躁動。","word":"lullaby"}},"lunar":{"createdAt":1781848934149,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lunar指基於月亮週期的日曆系統","options":["solar","lunar","gregorian","julian"],"sentence":"The ______ calendar is used in many Asian countries to determine important festivals. The Mid-Autumn Festival, for example, is celebrated on the 15th day of the eighth month.","translation":"陰曆在許多亞洲國家用來確定重要節日。例如，中秋節在第八個月的第15天慶祝。","word":"lunar"}},"lure":{"createdAt":1781836375374,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"lure是誘惑或吸引，指能夠吸引某人去做某事的東西。","options":["trap","lure","trick","scheme"],"sentence":"The bright lights and exciting games of the casino served as a ______ for many gamblers. The appeal of winning big money kept drawing people back repeatedly.","translation":"賭場的明亮燈光和刺激遊戲對許多賭徒起著誘惑作用。贏大錢的吸引力不斷吸引人們反覆回來。","word":"lure"}},"lyric":{"createdAt":1781481124690,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"lyric 是指歌曲中的文字內容，通常帶有情感和故事性，不是音樂的技術成分。","options":["instrument","note","word","rhythm"],"sentence":"The singer performed a beautiful song, and the audience loved every ______ of the melody. The words told a touching story about lost love and memories.","translation":"歌手演唱了一首優美的歌曲，觀眾喜歡旋律的每一個歌詞。這些詞語講述了一個關於失去的愛情和記憶的感人故事。","word":"lyric"}},"magnetic":{"createdAt":1781430348003,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"magnetic 是指具有磁力或與磁有關的，能夠吸引鐵和其他磁性物質。","options":["electric","gravitational","magnetic","thermal"],"sentence":"Iron filings instantly stick to a ______ field when placed near a strong magnet. This property allows the metal particles to be attracted and rearranged without any direct physical contact.","translation":"當鐵屑靠近強磁鐵時，它們會立即粘附到磁場上。這種特性使金屬粒子能夠被吸引和重新排列，而無需任何直接的物理接觸。","word":"magnetic"}},"magnify":{"createdAt":1781430348003,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"magnify 是指使某物看起來更大，特別是通過光學儀器如放大鏡或顯微鏡來實現。","options":["reduce","magnify","observe","collect"],"sentence":"Scientists use a microscope to ______ tiny organisms so they can be studied in detail. Without this optical device, these microorganisms would be invisible to the human eye.","translation":"科學家使用顯微鏡來放大微小的生物體，以便進行詳細研究。沒有這種光學設備，這些微生物對人眼來說是不可見的。","word":"magnify"}},"mainland":{"createdAt":1781362281652,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"mainland指的是一個國家或地區的主要陸地部分，不包括島嶼。","options":["coast","mainland","harbor","shore"],"sentence":"Many people from the island traveled to the ______ to find better job opportunities. The larger landmass offered more industries and economic growth than their home island.","translation":"許多來自島嶼的人前往大陸尋找更好的工作機會。這片更大的陸地比他們的島嶼提供了更多的產業和經濟增長。","word":"mainland"}},"maintenance":{"createdAt":1781443653219,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"maintenance指的是對設施或系統的定期保養、維護和修繕工作，以保持其正常狀態。","options":["destruction","abandonment","maintenance","demolition"],"sentence":"The apartment building required regular ______ to keep all systems functioning properly. The landlord hired contractors monthly to inspect pipes, repair electrical issues, and service the heating system.","translation":"這棟公寓需要定期維護以保持所有系統正常運作。房東每月雇用承包商檢查管道、修復電氣問題並維修供暖系統。","word":"maintenance"}},"majesty":{"createdAt":1781425104309,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"majesty 指莊嚴、威嚴或崇高的品質，也用作皇帝或王后的敬稱。","options":["tragedy","majesty","modesty","obesity"],"sentence":"The ______ of the ancient palace left all the visitors speechless. Its grand architecture and royal decoration embodied centuries of power and authority.","translation":"古老宮殿的威嚴令所有訪客嘆為觀止。其宏偉的建築和皇家裝飾體現了數百年的權力和權威。","word":"majesty"}},"major":{"createdAt":1781430953386,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"major作為動詞表示「主修某科目」，在大學教育的語境中使用。","options":["minor","major","graduate","transfer"],"sentence":"She decided to ______ in Biology at university. Her parents were pleased because she chose a field with excellent career prospects.","translation":"她決定在大學主修生物學。她的父母很高興，因為她選擇了一個有很好職業前景的領域。","word":"major"}},"majority":{"createdAt":1781425104308,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"majority 表示大多數、佔多數的人或物，與 minority（少數）相對。","options":["majority","minority","faculty","severity"],"sentence":"The ______ of students in the class prefer online learning over traditional classrooms. Only a few students actually enjoy sitting at desks all day.","translation":"班上大多數學生比起傳統教室更喜歡在線學習。只有少數學生真正喜歡整天坐在課桌前。","word":"majority"}},"mammal":{"createdAt":1781430348005,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"mammal 是指一類溫血脊椎動物，特徵是能夠產奶來餵養後代。","options":["fish","reptile","mammal","amphibian"],"sentence":"A whale is a large ______ that lives in the ocean and breathes air through a blowhole. Despite living in water, it shares the characteristic of producing milk to feed its young.","translation":"鯨魚是一種生活在海洋中並通過噴孔呼吸空氣的大型哺乳動物。儘管生活在水中，它具有產奶來餵養幼崽的特徵。","word":"mammal"}},"manageable":{"createdAt":1781950727559,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"manageable 表示易於處理、可控制或不難管理的事情。","options":["impossible","dangerous","manageable","temporary"],"sentence":"The project seemed ______ when we divided it into smaller tasks. Breaking it down into five stages made it much easier to complete.","translation":"當我們把項目分成更小的任務時，它似乎是可以處理的。把它分成五個階段使其更容易完成。","word":"manageable"}},"management":{"createdAt":1781951900953,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"management指有效地組織和控制人力、物資等資源以達成目標的過程。","options":["ignorance","management","awareness","discussion"],"sentence":"Good ______ of time and resources is essential for the success of any large project. The team leader carefully planned and organized every aspect of their work.","translation":"良好的時間和資源管理對任何大型項目的成功都至關重要。團隊領導仔細規劃和組織了工作的各個方面。","word":"management"}},"mandate":{"createdAt":1781425104310,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"mandate 表示授權、委任或人民通過選舉給予的權力和責任。","options":["mandate","debate","climate","project"],"sentence":"The government received a ______ from the people to implement new environmental policies. The election results clearly showed that voters supported these green initiatives.","translation":"政府收到人民的授權以實施新的環保政策。選舉結果清楚地表明投票者支持這些綠色倡議。","word":"mandate"}},"manifest":{"createdAt":1781860901464,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"manifest作動詞表示表現或顯現，指某種情感或特徵清楚地表露出來","options":["hide","conceal","manifest","suppress"],"sentence":"Her anger began to ______ through her facial expressions and body language. By the time she spoke, everyone could clearly see she was upset.","translation":"她的憤怒開始通過她的面部表情和肢體語言表現出來。當她說話時，每個人都清楚地看到她很不高興。","word":"manifest"}},"manifestation":{"createdAt":1781425104307,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"manifestation 指某種情感、品質或狀況的具體表現或外在顯示。","options":["concealment","manifestation","imagination","limitation"],"sentence":"The ______ of her anger was evident when she slammed the door. Her outburst showed us exactly how upset she truly felt.","translation":"她憤怒的表現在她砰地關上門時顯而易見。她的爆發讓我們看到她真正有多沮喪。","word":"manifestation"}},"manipulate":{"createdAt":1781430953388,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"manipulate表示「以不正當手段操縱或控制」，通常帶有欺騙或不誠實的含義。","options":["report","announce","manipulate","observe"],"sentence":"The corrupt politician tried to ______ the election results in his favor. He bribed election officials and tampered with voting machines to ensure his victory.","translation":"腐敗的政客試圖操縱選舉結果以對自己有利。他賄賂選舉官員並篡改投票機以確保自己的勝利。","word":"manipulate"}},"manners":{"createdAt":1781430953389,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"manners是名詞，表示「禮貌」或「舉止得體」，涉及社交行為和禮儀規範。","options":["languages","skills","manners","interests"],"sentence":"Good ______ are essential in business meetings and formal social gatherings. Children are taught to say \"please\" and \"thank you\" from an early age.","translation":"良好的禮儀在商務會議和正式社交聚會中是必不可少的。孩子們從小就被教導要說「請」和「謝謝」。","word":"manners"}},"mansion":{"createdAt":1781430953391,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"mansion是名詞，表示「大宅」或「豪宅」，指規模很大的宏偉私人住宅。","options":["apartment","cottage","mansion","studio"],"sentence":"The billionaire purchased a grand ______ overlooking the city skyline. The property featured 15 bedrooms, multiple swimming pools, and sprawling gardens on 10 acres.","translation":"這位億萬富翁購買了一座俯瞰城市天際線的豪宅。該房產有15間臥室、多個游泳池和跨越10英畝的寬敞花園。","word":"mansion"}},"manufacture":{"createdAt":1781840892405,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"manufacture意為製造或生產，與「自己生產」和「質量控制」的語境相符。","options":["distribute","manufacture","advertise","transport"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ its own products instead of outsourcing to other factories. This allowed them to maintain strict quality control over every item produced.","translation":"該公司決定自己製造產品，而不是外包給其他工廠。這讓他們能夠對每件生產的產品保持嚴格的質量控制。","word":"manufacture"}},"manuscript":{"createdAt":1781775276767,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"manuscript指作者的原始文稿或手寫文件，在提交出版前通常會有修改和批註。","options":["publication","manuscript","blueprint","diploma"],"sentence":"The author submitted her ______ to the publisher for review. The handwritten pages were filled with notes and corrections from months of editing.","translation":"作者將她的手稿提交給出版商審查。這些手寫的頁面上充滿了數月編輯工作中的註釋和修改。","word":"manuscript"}},"maple":{"createdAt":1781430953388,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"maple是名詞，指「楓樹」，以其在秋季變色的美麗葉子而聞名。","options":["oak","pine","maple","birch"],"sentence":"The park is famous for its beautiful ______ trees in the fall. Every autumn, visitors come from all over to see the brilliant red and orange leaves.","translation":"這個公園因其在秋天時美麗的楓樹而聞名。每年秋天，遊客們從四面八方來欣賞絢爛的紅色和橙色葉子。","word":"maple"}},"mar":{"createdAt":1781425094900,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"mar 表示損壞或破壞某物的外觀或完整性，通常指造成不良影響。","options":["improve","damage","polish","inspect"],"sentence":"The accident didn't ______ the car's exterior at all. However, the mechanic found deep scratches on the hood and dents on the bumper that would require extensive repairs.","translation":"那場事故根本沒有損壞汽車的外觀。然而，機修工發現引擎蓋上有深刮痕，保險槓上有凹陷，需要大量維修。","word":"mar"}},"margin":{"createdAt":1781424574162,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"margin 指頁面的邊緣或空白處，通常用於寫註記或評論。","options":["center","title","margin","conclusion"],"sentence":"The teacher wrote helpful comments in the ______ of the student's essay. The feedback was written in the empty white spaces beside the main text.","translation":"老師在學生論文的空白處寫下有用的評論。反饋寫在主要文本旁邊的空白處。","word":"margin"}},"marginal":{"createdAt":1781337343698,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"marginal意為微小的、少量的或邊緣的，用於形容數量很少或影響不大的情況。","options":["dramatic","excellent","marginal","spectacular"],"sentence":"The student's improvement in mathematics was only ______ despite attending tutoring sessions twice a week. His test scores increased by less than 3%, which was hardly significant.","translation":"儘管學生每週參加兩次補習課程，但他的數學成績提升只是微小的。他的測試成績只提高了不到3%，這幾乎不顯著。","word":"marginal"}},"marital":{"createdAt":1781425104309,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"marital 是形容詞，指與婚姻、夫妻關係相關的事物。","options":["musical","marital","martial","material"],"sentence":"The couple sought ______ counseling to improve their relationship. They wanted professional help to strengthen the bond between husband and wife.","translation":"這對夫婦尋求婚姻諮詢以改善他們的關係。他們希望獲得專業幫助來加強夫妻之間的紐帶。","word":"marital"}},"marker":{"createdAt":1781430348002,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"marker 是一種書寫工具，通常有粗筆尖和彩色墨水，用於在白板、海報等表面上做標記或寫字。","options":["pencil","marker","eraser","ruler"],"sentence":"The teacher used a red ______ to highlight the important dates on the whiteboard. Students could clearly see the bright marks because the ink was designed to be highly visible.","translation":"老師用紅色的記號筆在白板上標記重要的日期。學生們能清楚地看到這些明亮的標記，因為這種墨水的設計就是為了高度可見。","word":"marker"}},"martial":{"createdAt":1781430348004,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"martial 是指與軍事、戰爭或格鬥相關的，常見於 martial arts（武術）這個詞組。","options":["fine","performing","martial","visual"],"sentence":"The student enrolled in a ______ arts class to learn self-defense techniques and discipline. The instructor taught traditional combat methods passed down through generations of training.","translation":"這名學生報名參加了武術課程以學習自衛技巧和紀律。教練教授了代代相傳的傳統格鬥方法。","word":"martial"}},"marvel":{"createdAt":1781425104309,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"marvel 作名詞表示令人驚奇的事物或成就；也可作動詞表示感到驚奇。","options":["failure","marvel","marble","marvel"],"sentence":"The invention of electricity was a ______ of human engineering and creativity. Scientists marveled at how such a discovery could transform entire civilizations.","translation":"電的發明是人類工程和創意的奇跡。科學家們對這一發現如何能改變整個文明感到驚嘆。","word":"marvel"}},"masculine":{"createdAt":1781425104310,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"masculine 是形容詞，表示男性的、陽剛的或具有男性特徵的事物。","options":["feminine","masculine","electric","melodic"],"sentence":"He has a ______ voice that makes him sound like a radio announcer. His deep tone and bold delivery are distinctly male in character.","translation":"他有著男性化的嗓音，聽起來像廣播播音員。他深沉的音調和大膽的表達方式具有明顯的男性特徵。","word":"masculine"}},"mass":{"createdAt":1781430953390,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"mass作為名詞表示「大量」或「大眾」，通常指數量龐大的人或物。","options":["shortage","scarcity","mass","absence"],"sentence":"There was a ______ of people gathering at the concert venue before the show started. The crowd was so dense that security had difficulty controlling the flow of attendees.","translation":"演唱會開始前，有大量人群聚集在演唱會場地。人群如此密集，以至於安保部門難以控制參與者的流動。","word":"mass"}},"massage":{"createdAt":1781430953387,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"massage是名詞，表示「按摩」這種物理治療方法，通常涉及用手對身體進行操作。","options":["surgery","consultation","massage","injection"],"sentence":"After the intense workout, Tom went to get a ______ to relieve his sore muscles. The therapist spent an hour applying pressure and kneading his shoulders and back.","translation":"激烈運動後，湯姆去做按摩來緩解肌肉酸痛。治療師花了一個小時在他的肩膀和背部施加壓力和揉搓。","word":"massage"}},"massive":{"createdAt":1781430953387,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"massive表示「大規模的、巨大的」，用來形容規模或程度很大的事物。","options":["tiny","modest","massive","slight"],"sentence":"The company experienced a ______ drop in sales last quarter. The losses were so significant that they had to lay off thousands of employees.","translation":"該公司上季度經歷了大幅銷售下滑。虧損非常巨大，他們不得不裁員數千人。","word":"massive"}},"master":{"createdAt":1781871338565,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"master表示通過努力學習和練習達到完全掌握或精通的程度。","options":["attempted","learned","perfected","discovered"],"sentence":"After years of practice, the musician finally ______ the complex piano concerto. She could now perform it flawlessly from memory in concert halls worldwide.","translation":"經過多年的練習，這位音樂家終於精通了複雜的鋼琴協奏曲。她現在可以在世界各地的音樂廳中無缺陷地從記憶中表演它。","word":"master"}},"masterpiece":{"createdAt":1781950727566,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"masterpiece 指一件傑作或最優秀的作品，通常在其領域內達到最高水準。","options":["failure","masterpiece","sketch","copy"],"sentence":"The painting is considered a ______ of Renaissance art. Art historians rank it among the greatest works ever created in human history.","translation":"這幅畫被認為是文藝復興藝術的傑作。藝術史學家將其列為人類歷史上曾創作過的最偉大作品之列。","word":"masterpiece"}},"match":{"createdAt":1781849847411,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"match表示比賽或競賽，與「網球、錦標賽、球員比賽」的線索相符。","options":["conversation","match","story","song"],"sentence":"The tennis ______ was the most exciting event of the championship tournament. The two players were equally skilled and fought intensely for every point.","translation":"這場網球比賽是錦標賽中最令人興奮的事件。這兩名球員技術相當，為每一分而激烈比賽。","word":"match"}},"material":{"createdAt":1781848934146,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"material作名詞指製作東西所需的布料、原料或材料","options":["information","material","price","design"],"sentence":"The seamstress selected a soft ______ for the wedding dress. The fabric felt smooth and luxurious between her fingers.","translation":"裁縫為婚紗選擇了柔軟的布料。這種織物摸起來光滑奢華。","word":"material"}},"matter":{"createdAt":1781848934140,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"matter作動詞表示重要、有關係，指某事物具有重要性或意義","options":["dissolves","matters","disappears","changes"],"sentence":"Time ______ greatly when you're working on an important deadline. Every minute counts if you want to finish the project on schedule.","translation":"當你在處理重要截止日期時，時間很重要。如果你想按時完成項目，每一分鐘都很關鍵。","word":"matter"}},"mature":{"createdAt":1781311983484,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"mature 表示成熟的或已經充分發育的狀態，與年輕或未發育相對。","options":["presidential","timer","mature","average"],"sentence":"The ______ trees in the orchard produced more fruit than the younger saplings. These plants had developed strong root systems over several decades of growth.","translation":"果園裡成熟的樹木比年輕的樹苗產出更多水果。這些植物經過數十年的生長已經發展出強大的根系。","word":"mature"}},"maximum":{"createdAt":1781434900593,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"maximum表示能達到或允許的最高限度或最大數量。","options":["minimum","maximum","average","typical"],"sentence":"The swimming pool has a ______ capacity of 500 people for safety reasons. Authorities strictly enforce this limit to prevent overcrowding.","translation":"出於安全考慮，游泳池的最大容納人數為500人。當局嚴格執行此限制以防止過度擁擠。","word":"maximum"}},"mean":{"createdAt":1781437220553,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「Mean」作形容詞表示一個人不友善、吝嗇或缺乏同情心。","options":["generous","kind","mean","fair"],"sentence":"It was ______ of him to refuse sharing his lunch with the hungry child. He had plenty of food but chose to be stingy and unkind.","translation":"他拒絕與飢餓的孩子分享午餐是很卑鄙的。他有很多食物卻選擇吝嗇和不善待他人。","word":"mean"}},"means":{"createdAt":1781622232187,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"means 在此語境中指財富或經濟能力，即做某事所需的金錢或資源。","options":["interest","means","courage","time"],"sentence":"Sarah doesn't have the financial ______ to travel abroad this year. She is saving money and working part-time to afford a vacation in the future.","translation":"薩拉今年沒有經濟手段出國旅遊。她正在存錢並兼職工作，以便將來能負擔起度假。","word":"means"}},"mechanical":{"createdAt":1781619188926,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"mechanical 指由機械裝置組成的，通過物理機制而非電力運作。","options":["digital","mechanical","electronic","automatic"],"sentence":"The ______ clock required winding every morning to maintain accuracy. Unlike electronic devices, it relied entirely on springs and gears.","translation":"這台機械鐘每天早上需要上鏈以保持精確度。與電子設備不同，它完全依靠彈簧和齒輪。","word":"mechanical"}},"medal":{"createdAt":1781746685515,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"medal指的是獎章、獎牌、勳章，是頒發給在比賽或活動中表現優異者的獎品。","options":["duration","medal","rubbish","entertain"],"sentence":"The champion swimmer received a gold ______ at the international competition. The award was hung around her neck as recognition of her extraordinary athletic achievement.","translation":"冠軍游泳選手在國際比賽中獲得金牌。這枚獎牌掛在她的脖子上，以表彰她非凡的運動成就。","word":"medal"}},"medication":{"createdAt":1781425078612,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"藥物是指醫生處方的、藥劑師配置的物質，用於治療疾病或緩解症狀。","options":["exercise","medication","diet","therapy"],"sentence":"The doctor prescribed a strong ______ to help manage the patient's chronic pain. The pharmacist carefully prepared the prescription at the counter.","translation":"醫生開了一種強效的藥物來幫助患者控制慢性疼痛。藥劑師在櫃檯小心地配置了這個處方。","word":"medication"}},"medicinal":{"createdAt":1781836375367,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"medicinal形容詞表示與藥物或治療疾病相關的，具有醫療功效的。","options":["decorative","medicinal","culinary","poisonous"],"sentence":"The old herbalist showed us various plants with ______ properties stored in her shop. Many of these herbs had been used for centuries to treat illnesses.","translation":"老草藥商展示了她店裡存放的各種具有藥用特性的植物。許多這些草藥已被用於治療疾病數個世紀。","word":"medicinal"}},"medieval":{"createdAt":1781935654226,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"medieval 是形容詞，表示「中世紀的」，指西元5至15世紀之間的歐洲中古時代。","options":["modern","ancient","medieval","contemporary"],"sentence":"The ______ castle was built with thick stone walls and narrow windows for defensive purposes. Historians estimate it dates back to approximately the 12th century.","translation":"這座中世紀城堡建有厚重的石牆和狹窄的窗戶以供防禦之用。歷史學家估計它可以追溯到大約十二世紀。","word":"medieval"}},"meditation":{"createdAt":1781777331357,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"meditation是名詞，表示沉思、冥想或深思熟慮的精神修行活動","options":["exercise","meditation","discussion","presentation"],"sentence":"She practiced ______ every morning for thirty minutes to calm her anxious mind. This quiet, introspective practice helped her find inner peace and clarity before facing the day's challenges.","translation":"她每天早上練習冥想三十分鐘來平復焦慮的心情。這種寧靜、內省的修行幫助她在面對一天的挑戰之前找到內心的平靜與清晰。","word":"meditation"}},"melancholy":{"createdAt":1781777331349,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"melancholy是名詞，表示悲哀、憂鬱的情感狀態；也可作形容詞，描述悲傷的心境或事物","options":["joy","melancholy","excitement","confidence"],"sentence":"The poet's ______ was evident in every verse he wrote about lost love and forgotten dreams. His dark, sorrowful mood had persisted for months since his departure.","translation":"詩人在他寫的每一首關於失落的愛和被遺忘的夢想的詩句中都顯露出悲哀。他自從離開後，那種黑暗、悲傷的心情已經持續了好幾個月。","word":"melancholy"}},"membership":{"createdAt":1781311922068,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"membership 是指加入某個組織、俱樂部或機構的資格或身份，通常需要支付費用。","options":["ticket","license","membership","permit"],"sentence":"To access the gym facilities, you must purchase a ______ card first. The annual fee includes unlimited access to all equipment and fitness classes.","translation":"要使用健身房設施，你必須先購買會員資格卡。年費包括對所有設備和健身課程的無限制使用。","word":"membership"}},"mentality":{"createdAt":1781746685492,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"mentality指的是心態、思想方法，用來描述一個人的心理狀態和思維方式。","options":["rubbish","mentality","moisture","stadium"],"sentence":"The athlete's ______ before the competition was positive and confident. He spent hours visualizing success and believing he would win the gold medal.","translation":"比賽前運動員的心態是積極而自信的。他花了數小時進行心像訓練，相信自己會贏得金牌。","word":"mentality"}},"mention":{"createdAt":1781619188928,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"mention 指簡短地談及或提到某事，通常不進行詳細討論。","options":["emphasis","mention","declaration","announcement"],"sentence":"In her speech, she made only a brief ______ of her personal struggles. She chose not to elaborate on the difficulties she had faced.","translation":"在她的演講中，她只是簡要提及了她個人的困境。她選擇不詳細說明她所面臨的困難。","word":"mention"}},"merciful":{"createdAt":1781848330189,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"merciful表示仁慈、寬宏大量、願意原諒或減輕他人痛苦的品質。","options":["strict","merciful","confused","angry"],"sentence":"The judge was ______ in her sentencing despite the defendant's serious crimes. She considered his difficult background and gave him a reduced punishment rather than the maximum penalty allowed by law.","translation":"儘管被告犯了嚴重罪行，法官在量刑時表現出慈悲。她考慮了他困難的背景，給了他減輕的懲罰而不是法律允許的最高刑罰。","word":"merciful"}},"merge":{"createdAt":1781622232186,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"merge 意為使兩個或多個事物合併或融合成一個整體。","options":["separate","merge","relocate","decline"],"sentence":"The two smaller companies decided to ______ into one larger corporation to increase their market power. By combining their resources, they became a much stronger competitor.","translation":"這兩家較小的公司決定合併成一家大公司以增加市場力量。通過整合他們的資源，他們成為了一個更強大的競爭者。","word":"merge"}},"metal":{"createdAt":1781417610409,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"metal是指金屬或合金，在此指用來製造雕像的堅固金屬材料。","options":["plastic","bronze","ceramic","wood"],"sentence":"The statue was cast from a precious ______ that gleamed in the sunlight. The artisan chose this material specifically because of its durability and resistance to corrosion.","translation":"這座雕像是用在陽光下閃閃發光的貴重金屬鑄造的。工匠之所以選擇這種材料，特別是因為它的耐久性和抗腐蝕性。","word":"metal"}},"method":{"createdAt":1781836375375,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"method是方法或方式，指完成任務或實現目標的特定步驟或程序。","options":["process","method","procedure","technique"],"sentence":"The teacher introduced a new ______ for solving complex mathematical problems. Students found this systematic approach much clearer than the traditional way.","translation":"老師介紹了一種解決複雜數學問題的新方法。學生們發現這種系統方法比傳統方式清晰得多。","word":"method"}},"midst":{"createdAt":1781651261374,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"midst在此表示事物的中央或中間位置，通常用於描述某人或某物處於環境的核心區域。","options":["rod","treasury","midst","projection"],"sentence":"In the ______ of the crowded marketplace, she found her lost friend by calling his name loudly. They embraced each other surrounded by dozens of shoppers and vendors.","translation":"在擁擠市集的中間，她通過大聲呼喊他的名字找到了失散的朋友。他們被數十位購物者和小販包圍著相擁而抱。","word":"midst"}},"migrant":{"createdAt":1781582939254,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"migrant 指季節性移動工作或為了謀生而遷徙的人，與跨國工作和季節性返回的敘述相符。","options":["migrant","wealthy","elderly","local"],"sentence":"The ______ workers came from neighboring countries to find better employment opportunities during the harvest season. They would return to their home villages after the crops were collected each autumn.","translation":"移民工人來自鄰近國家，在收穫季節尋求更好的就業機會。他們在每年秋天收割完後會返回家鄉。","word":"migrant"}},"milestone":{"createdAt":1781478568771,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"milestone 指人生或歷史上具有重要意義的重大事件或階段。","options":["obstacle","milestone","distraction","setback"],"sentence":"Graduating from university was a significant ______ in her life journey. This achievement opened doors to new career opportunities and personal growth.","translation":"從大學畢業是她人生旅程中的重要里程碑。這個成就為她打開了新的職業機會和個人成長的大門。","word":"milestone"}},"millennium":{"createdAt":1781927792735,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"millennium指的是一千年的時間跨度，特別常用來指代按照基督紀年計算的每個一千年周期。","options":["century","decade","millennium","year"],"sentence":"People around the world celebrated the arrival of the new ______ with grand fireworks and festivities. The year 2000 marked the transition from the second to the third period of one thousand years in the Common Era.","translation":"世界各地的人們用盛大的煙火和慶祝活動迎接新千年的到來。公元2000年標誌著從第二個千年過渡到第三個千年。","word":"millennium"}},"mimic":{"createdAt":1781507137215,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"mimic 表示模仿或學習某人的樣子、聲音或行為，特別強調複製的能力。","options":["ignore","understand","mimic","record"],"sentence":"The young parrot learned to ______ the sounds of its trainer perfectly. Within weeks, it could reproduce every word and tone exactly as it had heard them.","translation":"年輕的鸚鵡學會了完美地模仿它的訓練者的聲音。在幾週內，它能夠完全按照聽到的方式複製每個單詞和音調。","word":"mimic"}},"minerals":{"createdAt":1781848330187,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"minerals指天然存在的無機固體物質，是人體維持正常功能所需的營養元素。","options":["vitamins","minerals","proteins","fats"],"sentence":"The supplement contains essential ______ like calcium and iron that your body needs. These inorganic substances are crucial for maintaining healthy bones and producing red blood cells.","translation":"這種補充劑含有鈣和鐵等人體所需的必要礦物質。這些無機物質對於保持骨骼健康和生成紅血球至關重要。","word":"minerals"}},"minimum":{"createdAt":1781696018687,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"minimum 意為最低限度、極小值，指可接受或必需的最低標準。","options":["maximum","requirement","minimum","suggestion"],"sentence":"The company requires a ______ of five years of experience for this senior position. Candidates with less than that threshold will not be considered for the role.","translation":"公司要求這個高級職位至少需要五年的工作經驗。經驗少於此標準的候選人將不被考慮。","word":"minimum"}},"minister":{"createdAt":1781848330188,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"minister可指政府部長、外交使節或宗教牧師，是具有重要職位或使命的人。","options":["tourist","minister","student","merchant"],"sentence":"The ______ from the neighboring country arrived in the capital to negotiate a trade agreement. As the government's official representative, he held meetings with high-ranking officials.","translation":"來自鄰國的外交使節抵達首都談判貿易協議。作為政府的官方代表，他與高級官員舉行了會議。","word":"minister"}},"minor":{"createdAt":1781311685839,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"minor作為形容詞表示較小的、次要的、不重要的，與serious或severe相反。","options":["severe","significant","small","dangerous"],"sentence":"Although the car accident seemed ______, it still required a police report to be filed. The damage was limited to a small dent on the bumper.","translation":"雖然這起車禍看起來很輕微，但仍然需要提交警方報告。損傷僅限於保險桿上的一個小凹痕。","word":"minor"}},"miracle":{"createdAt":1781746685515,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"miracle指的是奇蹟，表示一件非常不可能但卻真實發生的事件，通常超越自然法則。","options":["miracle","obedience","editorials","laborious"],"sentence":"The patient's recovery from such a serious illness seemed like a ______. Doctors had given up hope, but the patient woke up one morning completely healed.","translation":"病人從如此嚴重的疾病中恢復似乎是個奇蹟。醫生已經放棄了希望，但病人在一個早晨醒來時完全康復了。","word":"miracle"}},"mischief":{"createdAt":1781484415230,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"mischief是指調皮搗亂或淘氣的行為，通常涉及惡作劇但不一定有害。","options":["studying","prayer","mischief","sleep"],"sentence":"The children got into ______ when they thought no adults were watching them. They hid their toys, broke a vase, and blamed each other for the chaos.","translation":"當孩子們以為沒有成人在看他們時，他們開始調皮搗亂。他們藏起玩具，打破了花瓶，互相指責造成的混亂。","word":"mischief"}},"mission":{"createdAt":1781693303266,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"mission 在此指「使命」或「外交任務」，特別是指重要的正式任務，通常涉及政治或商業目的。","options":["journey","mission","vacation","assignment"],"sentence":"The diplomat was sent on a special ______ to negotiate peace between the two countries. Her objective was to meet with government officials and establish a framework for future discussions.","translation":"這位外交官被派遣執行一項特殊的使命，以協商兩國之間的和平。她的目標是與政府官員會面並建立未來討論的框架。","word":"mission"}},"missionary":{"createdAt":1781601735996,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"「missionary」是指為了宗教目的而到異地傳教的人，通常從事宗教教育和社區服務工作。","options":["missionary","scholar","merchant","diplomat"],"sentence":"The ______ traveled to remote villages to spread Christian teachings and establish schools. Local communities welcomed him because he provided education and medical assistance to their children.","translation":"傳教士前往偏遠村莊傳播基督教教義並建立學校。當地社區歡迎他，因為他為他們的孩子提供教育和醫療援助。","word":"missionary"}},"mistook":{"createdAt":1781693591739,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"mistook 是 mistake 的過去式，表示錯誤地認為某人或某物是另一個人或物體。","options":["recognized","mistook","understood","remembered"],"sentence":"I ______ my friend's twin sister for my friend when I saw her at the grocery store. Later, I realized my mistake when she introduced herself with a different name.","translation":"我在雜貨店看到我朋友的孿生妹妹時誤認為是我的朋友。後來當她自我介紹時用了不同的名字，我才意識到我的錯誤。","word":"mistook"}},"mix":{"createdAt":1781515329268,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"mix 動詞，意思是混合、混和，指將不同的物質結合在一起。","options":["separate","mix","measure","sift"],"sentence":"The recipe instructed us to ______ the flour and sugar together in a large bowl. After combining the dry ingredients, we added the eggs and butter to create the batter.","translation":"食譜要求我們在一個大碗中將麵粉和糖混合在一起。將乾性材料混合後，我們加入雞蛋和黃油製作麵糊。","word":"mix"}},"moderation":{"createdAt":1781836375368,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"moderation表示適度、溫和或不過分，強調適量而非完全禁止或過度。","options":["abundance","excess","moderation","restriction"],"sentence":"The nutritionist advised eating sweets in ______ rather than consuming large quantities daily. She emphasized that small amounts of treats could be part of a healthy lifestyle.","translation":"營養師建議適度食用甜食，而不是每天大量食用。她強調少量的零食可以成為健康生活方式的一部分。","word":"moderation"}},"moist":{"createdAt":1781481311493,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"moist是形容詞，表示有水分、潮濕的狀態。","options":["frozen","moist","hard","burning"],"sentence":"The baker preferred to work with ______ dough to ensure the bread would have a soft texture. Adding just the right amount of water made the mixture perfect for kneading and rising.","translation":"麵包師喜歡用潮濕的麵團工作，以確保麵包具有柔軟的質地。添加適量的水使混合物非常適合揉捏和發酵。","word":"moist"}},"moisture":{"createdAt":1781746685508,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"moisture指的是濕氣、水份、潮濕，是指空氣或物質中含有的水分。","options":["moisture","medal","mentality","cooperate"],"sentence":"The ______ in the air during the rainy season can damage electronic equipment. The high humidity levels made everything feel damp and sticky.","translation":"雨季空氣中的濕氣會損害電子設備。高濕度使一切都感覺潮濕和粘膩。","word":"moisture"}},"momentary":{"createdAt":1781835134545,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"momentary 表示持續時間很短，只持續一瞬間或很短的時間，與長期或持久相反。","options":["permanent","intense","momentary","sharp"],"sentence":"The pain I felt was ______ and disappeared within seconds. By the time I finished counting to ten, it was completely gone.","translation":"我感受到的疼痛是短暫的，在幾秒鐘內就消失了。當我數到十時，它已經完全消失了。","word":"momentary"}},"monetary":{"createdAt":1781749177491,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"monetary 特別指與貨幣、金錢流通和利率相關的政策和措施。","options":["fiscal","financial","trade","industrial"],"sentence":"The government announced new ______ policies to control inflation in the economy. Interest rates will be raised to reduce the amount of money circulating in the market.","translation":"政府宣布了新的金融政策以控制經濟中的通貨膨脹。利率將提高以減少市場上流通的貨幣數量。","word":"monetary"}},"morale":{"createdAt":1781696018684,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"morale 意為士氣、精神狀態，通常指群體或組織的團隊精神和信心程度。","options":["strength","morale","strategy","equipment"],"sentence":"The team's ______ dropped significantly after they lost the championship game. Coaches had to work hard to rebuild their confidence and enthusiasm for next season.","translation":"在失去冠軍賽後，球隊的士氣明顯下降。教練必須努力重建他們對下賽季的信心和熱情。","word":"morale"}},"mortgage":{"createdAt":1781481311488,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"mortgage是指銀行向購房者提供的貸款，以及對房產的抵押擔保。","options":["investment","mortgage","insurance","scholarship"],"sentence":"After saving for ten years, Maria finally qualified for a ______ to purchase her first home. The bank approved her application because she had a stable job and a substantial down payment.","translation":"在存了十年的錢後，瑪麗亞終於獲得批准買她的第一間房子。銀行批准她的申請是因為她有穩定的工作和大筆的首付款。","word":"mortgage"}},"motion":{"createdAt":1781580511757,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"motion 表示物體的移動或運行狀態","options":["sound","color","motion","weight"],"sentence":"The pendulum continued its ______ back and forth for hours. Its regular swinging pattern was hypnotic to watch.","translation":"鐘擺持續其往復的運動好幾個小時。它有規律的擺動模式看起來很催眠。","word":"motion"}},"motionless":{"createdAt":1781481072317,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"motionless 表示完全靜止不動的狀態，沒有任何動作或移動。","options":["running","alert","motionless","graceful"],"sentence":"The deer stood ______ in the forest, barely visible among the trees. Not a muscle twitched as the hunter approached cautiously.","translation":"鹿在森林裡靜止不動地站著，在樹木中幾乎看不見。當獵人小心翼翼地靠近時，它連一塊肌肉都沒有動過。","word":"motionless"}},"murder":{"createdAt":1781951900952,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"murder指故意殺害他人的犯罪行為，強調是非法的、預謀的致命傷害。","options":["accident","suicide","murder","disappearance"],"sentence":"The detective was called to investigate a ______ that had occurred in the downtown hotel. The victim had been killed intentionally, and the police needed to find the culprit.","translation":"偵探被召來調查在市中心酒店發生的謀殺案。受害者是被故意殺害的，警察需要找到兇手。","word":"murder"}},"murderer":{"createdAt":1781758494836,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"murderer 指的是犯謀殺罪的兇手，與第二句中「犯下謀殺案的人」的描述相符。","options":["victim","witness","murderer","detective"],"sentence":"The detective finally identified the ______ after analyzing DNA evidence from the crime scene. The evidence proved that this person was the one who committed the homicide.","translation":"偵探在分析犯罪現場的DNA證據後，最終確認了兇手的身份。證據證明這個人就是犯下謀殺案的人。","word":"murderer"}},"murmuring":{"createdAt":1781839703147,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"murmuring指低聲說話或低沈的聲音，與soft voices blended together（柔和的聲音融合）完美對應。","options":["silence","applause","murmuring","laughter"],"sentence":"The ______ of the audience grew louder as they waited for the concert to begin. Soft voices blended together into a gentle background hum.","translation":"當觀眾等待演唱會開始時，低聲說話聲變得更大聲。柔和的聲音融合在一起，形成了一個溫柔的背景嗡嗡聲。","word":"murmuring"}},"mustache":{"createdAt":1781403377828,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"mustache 特指長在上嘴唇上方的鬚髮，不包括下巴或兩側的鬍子。","options":["beard","eyebrows","mustache","sideburns"],"sentence":"The old gentleman carefully groomed his ______ every morning before going to work. He took great pride in the distinctive facial hair that grew above his upper lip.","translation":"這位老紳士每天早上上班前都會細心修剪他的八字鬚。他為長在上唇上方的這道獨特鬍子感到驕傲。","word":"mustache"}},"mysterious":{"createdAt":1781582619549,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"mysterious 形容某事難以理解或無法解釋，充滿謎團和未知的特質。","options":["bright","cheerful","mysterious","ordinary"],"sentence":"The old castle had a ______ atmosphere that made visitors feel uneasy and curious. No one could explain the strange sounds heard at night or the peculiar markings on the walls.","translation":"這座古老的城堡有著神秘的氣氛，使訪客感到不安和好奇。沒有人能解釋夜間聽到的奇怪聲音或牆上的奇特標記。","word":"mysterious"}},"naive":{"createdAt":1781616876966,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"naive 形容詞表示「天真的、樸素的」，指缺乏經驗或判斷力，容易被欺騙。","options":["sophisticated","cynical","naive","skeptical"],"sentence":"The young girl was too ______ to understand the politician's deceptive promises. She believed everything she heard without questioning or analyzing the claims.","translation":"那個年輕女孩太天真，無法理解政治家欺騙性的承諾。她沒有質疑或分析這些主張就相信了一切。","word":"naive"}},"naked":{"createdAt":1781616876970,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"naked 形容詞除了表示「赤裸的」，還可引申為「未經掩飾的、毫無隱瞞的」。","options":["hidden","false","naked","complicated"],"sentence":"The ______ truth about the scandal was finally revealed to the public. All the facts were presented without any embellishment or cover-up.","translation":"關於醜聞的赤裸真相終於向公眾公開。所有事實都被呈現，沒有任何美化或隱瞞。","word":"naked"}},"narrate":{"createdAt":1781950727561,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"narrate 指講述故事或提供敘述，通常是通過語音解說。","options":["paint","ignore","narrate","compose"],"sentence":"The famous actor will ______ the documentary about Antarctic wildlife. His voice will guide viewers through each scene from start to finish.","translation":"這位著名演員將為關於南極野生動物的紀錄片敘述旁白。他的聲音將指導觀眾從頭到尾穿過每一場景。","word":"narrate"}},"narrative":{"createdAt":1781616876980,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"narrative 形容詞表示「敘事的、故事的」，指以講述故事或敘述事件為主要特徵的文學作品。","options":["descriptive","narrative","poetic","dramatic"],"sentence":"The author used a ______ technique to tell the story from the main character's perspective. The entire novel was structured as a sequential account of events.","translation":"作者使用敘事技巧從主要角色的角度講述故事。整部小說的結構是事件的順序帳述。","word":"narrative"}},"narrator":{"createdAt":1781616876983,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"narrator 名詞表示「敘述者、旁白者」，指在書籍、電影或紀錄片中講述故事或提供解說的人。","options":["actor","narrator","director","editor"],"sentence":"The ______ of the documentary spoke in a calm, authoritative voice that captivated the audience. His commentary guided viewers through the complex historical events.","translation":"紀錄片的旁白者用平靜而權威的聲音吸引了觀眾。他的評論引導觀眾了解複雜的歷史事件。","word":"narrator"}},"narrow":{"createdAt":1781616876985,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"narrow 形容詞表示「狹窄的、寬度小的」，指物理空間的寬度受限。","options":["wide","narrow","spacious","open"],"sentence":"The ______ alleyway between the buildings was so tight that two people could barely pass each other. We had to walk single file to navigate it.","translation":"建築物之間的狹窄小巷非常狹擠，兩個人幾乎無法相互通過。我們必須單排行走才能通過。","word":"narrow"}},"narrowly":{"createdAt":1781616876971,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"narrowly 副詞表示「勉強地、差一點」，指僅僅避免了不好的結果。","options":["widely","narrowly","slowly","carefully"],"sentence":"He ______ avoided the accident by swerving at the last second. His quick reflexes prevented a serious collision by mere inches.","translation":"他在最後一秒轉向，差一點就避免了事故。他敏捷的反應以極小的距離阻止了嚴重碰撞。","word":"narrowly"}},"nationalism":{"createdAt":1781616876985,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"nationalism 名詞表示「民族主義、國家主義」，指強調本國利益和民族優越性的政治思想。","options":["internationalism","pacifism","nationalism","liberalism"],"sentence":"The rise of ______ in the country led citizens to prioritize their own nation's interests above international cooperation. Political leaders appealed to patriotic sentiments.","translation":"該國民族主義的上升導致公民優先考慮本國利益而不是國際合作。政治領導人訴諸愛國情感。","word":"nationalism"}},"nationality":{"createdAt":1781484415231,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"nationality是指某人所屬的國家或公民身份，表示一個人的國籍。","options":["height","nationality","occupation","religion"],"sentence":"On the passport application, he had to indicate his ______ as Canadian. The form required him to state which country he was a citizen of.","translation":"在護照申請表上，他必須將國籍註明為加拿大人。該表格要求他說明他是哪個國家的公民。","word":"nationality"}},"native":{"createdAt":1781616876986,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"native 形容詞表示「本地的、本國的」，用於描述一個人生來就具備的語言或文化。","options":["foreign","native","amateur","student"],"sentence":"She is a ______ speaker of Mandarin Chinese, having grown up in Beijing. The language came naturally to her without any formal study.","translation":"她是普通話的母語使用者，在北京長大。該語言對她來說很自然，無需任何正式學習。","word":"native"}},"natural":{"createdAt":1781616919425,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"自然的是指未經人為改造或處理的，原本就存在的樣子。","options":["artificial","natural","obvious","difficult"],"sentence":"This river follows a ______ path through the valley without any human engineering. The water flows freely and has never been diverted by dams.","translation":"這條河流經山谷時遵循自然的路徑，沒有任何人工工程。水流自由流動，從未被大壩轉向。","word":"natural"}},"naturally":{"createdAt":1781616919428,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"自然地是指按照自然規律或天性發生，不需人為干預。","options":["artificially","slowly","naturally","gradually"],"sentence":"When the sun rises, the sky brightens ______ without any artificial light. This process happens automatically every morning.","translation":"當太陽升起時，天空不需任何人工光線自然地變亮。這個過程每天早上自動發生。","word":"naturally"}},"nature":{"createdAt":1781616876967,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"nature 名詞表示「自然、天性、本質」，指事物的基本特性或內在本質。","options":["color","history","nature","beauty"],"sentence":"The ______ of water is to flow downward due to gravity. Scientists study this fundamental property to understand how ecosystems function.","translation":"水的本性是由於重力而向下流動。科學家研究這個基本性質以了解生態系統如何運作。","word":"nature"}},"nausea":{"createdAt":1781424157176,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"nausea 指的是想吐或感到不適的感覺，通常伴隨胃部不適。","options":["dizziness","fatigue","nausea","headache"],"sentence":"The patient reported experiencing severe ______ after taking the new medication on an empty stomach. He felt so queasy that he had to lie down for an hour before he could function again.","translation":"患者報告說在空腹時服用新藥後經歷了嚴重的噁心感。他感到非常難受，必須躺下一小時才能重新活動。","word":"nausea"}},"navigate":{"createdAt":1781443653217,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"navigate在這裡指的是駕駛或引導船隻通過特定路線，需要技術和知識。","options":["abandon","navigate","sink","float"],"sentence":"The captain had to carefully ______ the ship through the treacherous waters near the rocky reef. His expertise in reading nautical charts and handling the wheel was crucial to avoiding disaster.","translation":"船長必須小心翼翼地駕駛船隻通過岩礁附近的危險水域。他閱讀航海圖表和操控舵輪的專業知識對於避免災難至關重要。","word":"navigate"}},"navigation":{"createdAt":1781616876981,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"navigation 名詞表示「航海、飛行、領航」，指確定路線和方向的過程或技術。","options":["entertainment","communication","navigation","medication"],"sentence":"The ship's captain relied on advanced ______ systems to find the correct route across the ocean. GPS technology made the journey much safer than before.","translation":"船長依靠先進的導航系統在海洋中找到正確的路線。GPS技術使航程比以前安全得多。","word":"navigation"}},"navy":{"createdAt":1781616877019,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"navy 名詞表示「海軍」，指一個國家的軍事海上部隊，或深藍色（海軍藍）的顏色。","options":["army","navy","marines","coast"],"sentence":"He enlisted in the ______ after high school to serve his country at sea. His uniform displayed the insignia of the naval fleet.","translation":"他高中後參加了海軍以在海上為國服務。他的制服展示了海軍艦隊的徽章。","word":"navy"}},"nearsighted":{"createdAt":1781616876977,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"nearsighted 形容詞表示「近視的」，指無法清楚看到遠處物體的眼睛狀況。","options":["farsighted","nearsighted","blind","colorblind"],"sentence":"The ______ student had difficulty reading the information written on the classroom whiteboard. She needed glasses to see distant objects clearly.","translation":"這個近視的學生在閱讀課堂白板上的信息時遇到困難。她需要眼鏡才能清楚地看到遠處的物體。","word":"nearsighted"}},"neat":{"createdAt":1781256444518,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"neat指整潔、有序的狀態，描述一個人或地方井井有條、乾乾淨淨。","options":["colorful","cozy","neat","spacious"],"sentence":"Sarah's apartment is always ______, with every book organized on shelves and dishes promptly washed. Her friends are impressed by how she maintains such order despite her busy work schedule.","translation":"莎拉的公寓總是整潔有序的，每本書都整齊地放在書架上，盤子也立即洗淨。她的朋友對她在繁忙的工作日程中仍能保持如此秩序感到印象深刻。","word":"neat"}},"necessarily":{"createdAt":1781616876972,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"necessarily 副詞表示「必定地、必然地」，用於表達邏輯上的必然性。","options":["always","necessarily","quickly","slowly"],"sentence":"Success in business does not ______ come from working the longest hours. Some of the most successful entrepreneurs focus on efficiency and smart strategies instead.","translation":"商業上的成功不必定來自於工作時間最長。一些最成功的企業家反而專注於效率和聰明的策略。","word":"necessarily"}},"necessary":{"createdAt":1781616919428,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"必需的是指不可或缺、一定要有的、非做不可的。","options":["optional","necessary","harmful","expensive"],"sentence":"Regular exercise is ______ for maintaining good health and fitness. Without it, your body becomes weak and susceptible to diseases.","translation":"定期運動對於維持良好的健康和體能是必需的。沒有它，你的身體會變得虛弱並容易生病。","word":"necessary"}},"necessity":{"createdAt":1781616877017,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"necessity 名詞表示「必要、必需品」，指必不可少或無法避免的事物。","options":["luxury","luxury","necessity","distraction"],"sentence":"Sleep is a biological ______ that every human must fulfill. Without adequate rest, our bodies and minds cannot function properly.","translation":"睡眠是每個人都必須滿足的生理必要條件。沒有充分的休息，我們的身體和心智無法正常運作。","word":"necessity"}},"needy":{"createdAt":1781616876974,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"needy 形容詞表示「貧困的、缺乏生活必需品的」，指經濟困難的人。","options":["wealthy","needy","educated","established"],"sentence":"The charity organization provides food and shelter to ______ families in the community. These households struggle to afford basic necessities each month.","translation":"慈善機構為社區中貧困的家庭提供食物和住所。這些家庭每個月都難以負擔基本生活必需品。","word":"needy"}},"neglect":{"createdAt":1781616919425,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"忽視是指故意或無意地不注意、不照顧某事物。","options":["care","neglect","renovation","inspection"],"sentence":"The abandoned house showed clear signs of ______ over many years. No one had maintained it or paid attention to its deteriorating condition.","translation":"這棟廢棄的房子多年來顯示出明顯的忽視跡象。沒有人維護它或關注其惡化的狀況。","word":"neglect"}},"negotiate":{"createdAt":1781484415237,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"negotiate是指通過對話和討論來達成協議或解決分歧，涉及妥協和相互讓步。","options":["celebrate","surrender","negotiate","flee"],"sentence":"The two nations had to ______ for months before reaching a peace agreement. Both sides made compromises and discussed their demands until they found common ground.","translation":"兩個國家必須談判數月才能達成和平協議。雙方做出妥協並討論他們的要求，直到找到共同點。","word":"negotiate"}},"nerve":{"createdAt":1781616876977,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"nerve 名詞可表示「神經」，也可引申為「勇氣、膽量」，指敢於採取行動的勇氣。","options":["fear","doubt","nerve","weakness"],"sentence":"It took a lot of ______ for her to speak up against the unfair decision. Her courageous stand inspired others to voice their opinions.","translation":"她需要很大的勇氣才能對不公平的決定發聲。她勇敢的立場激勵了其他人表達意見。","word":"nerve"}},"nervous":{"createdAt":1781566185162,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"nervous形容人感到不安、緊張或擔憂的情感狀態，通常伴隨著生理上的反應。","options":["confident","relaxed","nervous","excited"],"sentence":"She felt ______ before her first job interview. Her hands trembled, her heart raced, and she could barely sleep the night before due to anxiety.","translation":"她在第一次工作面試前感到緊張。她的手發抖，心跳加速，由於焦慮她前一晚幾乎無法入睡。","word":"nervous"}},"neuter":{"createdAt":1781431278560,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"neuter作為語法術語，指既不是陽性也不是陰性的詞性。","options":["positive","neuter","complex","active"],"sentence":"In grammar, the word 'it' is considered ______ because it doesn't indicate whether something is masculine or feminine. Unlike pronouns such as 'he' or 'she', it applies to objects without gender.","translation":"在語法中，單詞「it」被認為是中性的，因為它不表示某物是陽性還是陰性。與「he」或「she」等代詞不同，它適用於沒有性別的對象。","word":"neuter"}},"neutral":{"createdAt":1781616877017,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"neutral 形容詞表示「中立的、不偏袒的」，指不支持任何一方或不表示個人意見。","options":["biased","neutral","partisan","hostile"],"sentence":"The mediator remained ______ throughout the dispute to ensure a fair outcome. He did not favor either side and listened to both parties equally.","translation":"調解人在整個紛爭中保持中立以確保公平的結果。他沒有偏袒任何一方，並平等地傾聽雙方的意見。","word":"neutral"}},"nobility":{"createdAt":1781268630489,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"nobility指的是高尚或崇高的品質，表示道德上的優越性和尊嚴。","options":["wealth","nobility","strength","intelligence"],"sentence":"The prince was admired for his ______ and generous spirit toward the poor. His kindness and selflessness set him apart from others.","translation":"王子因其對貧困者的高尚和慷慨精神而受到敬佩。他的善良和無私使他與眾不同。","word":"nobility"}},"noble":{"createdAt":1781616876961,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"noble 形容詞表示「高貴的、貴族的」，指具有高尚品質或來自貴族階級的人或事物。","options":["poor","noble","common","wealthy"],"sentence":"The ______ family ruled the kingdom with honor and grace. They were respected throughout the land for their dignified conduct and high moral standards.","translation":"那個貴族家族以榮譽和優雅統治王國。他們因為舉止莊重和高尚的道德標準而在全國受到尊敬。","word":"noble"}},"nominate":{"createdAt":1781616919427,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"提名是指正式推薦某人參選或擔任某個職位。","options":["elect","nominate","dismiss","interview"],"sentence":"The board will ______ three directors at the next annual meeting. The shareholders have the right to officially propose their preferred candidates.","translation":"董事會將在下次年會上提名三名董事。股東有權正式提議他們偏好的候選人。","word":"nominate"}},"nomination":{"createdAt":1781616919427,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"提名是指正式推薦或指定某人參與評選或擔任職位的行為。","options":["rejection","nomination","approval","interview"],"sentence":"The award committee announced the ______ of five candidates for the scholarship. Each person had been formally proposed by their school.","translation":"獎學金委員會宣布了五名候選人的提名。每個人都已被其學校正式提議。","word":"nomination"}},"nominator":{"createdAt":1781616877018,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"nominator 名詞表示「提名者」，指提出某人為候選人或為某人爭取職位或榮譽的人。","options":["recipient","nominator","judge","spectator"],"sentence":"The ______ submitted her name for the awards ceremony, believing she deserved recognition. Her contribution to the organization had been exceptional.","translation":"提名者為她提交了獲獎典禮的名字，認為她值得認可。她對組織的貢獻非常卓越。","word":"nominator"}},"nominee":{"createdAt":1781616919429,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"被提名者是指被正式推薦或指定參與評選的人。","options":["judge","nominee","winner","host"],"sentence":"The ______ for Best Actor will attend the awards ceremony next week. This person has been officially selected to compete for the prize.","translation":"最佳男演員的被提名者將在下週參加頒獎典禮。這個人已被正式選中參與比賽。","word":"nominee"}},"norm":{"createdAt":1781256444513,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"norm指廣泛接受的規範或標準，是社會中普遍遵循的行為準則。","options":["greeting","norm","habit","tradition"],"sentence":"In many Western countries, shaking hands is considered a social ______ when meeting someone. However, in some Asian cultures, bowing or nodding is the expected standard instead.","translation":"在許多西方國家，握手被認為是見面時的社交規範。然而，在一些亞洲文化中，鞠躬或點頭是預期的標準。","word":"norm"}},"normal":{"createdAt":1781428458258,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"normal指符合預期或通常的狀態，不異常不特殊。","options":["superstitious","normal","crisis","confidence"],"sentence":"After three weeks of heavy rain, the weather finally returned to ______ conditions. The sun came out and temperatures were back to what we usually see in this season.","translation":"經過三週的暴雨後，天氣終於恢復到正常狀況。太陽出來了，溫度回到了本季通常的水平。","word":"normal"}},"nostril":{"createdAt":1781616877018,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"nostril 名詞表示「鼻孔」，指鼻子的開口，通過它呼吸和聞氣味。","options":["ear","nostril","mouth","eye"],"sentence":"When she breathed in the spicy aroma, her ______ flared slightly in response. The scent traveled through her nasal passage.","translation":"當她吸入辛辣的香氣時，她的鼻孔略微擴張。氣味通過她的鼻腔。","word":"nostril"}},"notable":{"createdAt":1781616876984,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"notable 形容詞表示「顯著的、值得注意的」，指因為重要性或優秀品質而受到關注的人或事物。","options":["unknown","notable","amateur","inexperienced"],"sentence":"The conference featured ______ speakers from the field of environmental science. Their groundbreaking research and innovative ideas impressed the entire audience.","translation":"會議邀請了環境科學領域的杰出講者。他們的開創性研究和創新想法給全體觀眾留下了深刻印象。","word":"notable"}},"noted":{"createdAt":1781616876982,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"noted 形容詞表示「著名的、被注意到的」，指因為成就或特點而受到認可的人或事物。","options":["unknown","noted","unsuccessful","retired"],"sentence":"The ______ surgeon had performed thousands of successful operations in his career. His reputation for excellence attracted patients from around the world.","translation":"這位著名的外科醫生在他的職業生涯中進行了數千次成功的手術。他卓越的聲譽吸引了來自世界各地的患者。","word":"noted"}},"noticeable":{"createdAt":1781583174627,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"noticeable意指明顯的、容易看出的，通常指某物的改變或差異足夠大而引人注目","options":["invisible","questionable","noticeable","temporary"],"sentence":"There was a ______ improvement in Sarah's exam scores this semester. Her hard work and extra study sessions clearly paid off with results that jumped from 65% to 92%.","translation":"莎拉本學期的考試成績有____的進步。她的努力和額外學習課程顯然得到了回報，成績從65%跳升至92%。","word":"noticeable"}},"notify":{"createdAt":1781616919431,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"通知是指向某人傳達信息或告知某事的行為。","options":["ignore","notify","cancel","guarantee"],"sentence":"The airline will ______ all passengers about the flight delay immediately. A text message and email will be sent to confirm the change.","translation":"航空公司將立即通知所有乘客航班延誤。將發送文本消息和電子郵件以確認該變更。","word":"notify"}},"notion":{"createdAt":1781616919430,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"想法或概念是指心中產生的一種想像或信念。","options":["proof","notion","fact","law"],"sentence":"She had a strange ______ that talking to plants would make them grow faster. Her idea seemed illogical to most gardeners.","translation":"她有一個奇怪的想法，認為跟植物說話會讓它們長得更快。她的想法對大多數園丁來說似乎不合邏輯。","word":"notion"}},"nourish":{"createdAt":1781616876970,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"nourish 動詞表示「滋養、供養」，指通過食物或其他方式提供營養和支持。","options":["harm","nourish","weaken","injure"],"sentence":"A healthy diet can ______ your body and strengthen your immune system. Foods rich in vitamins and minerals are essential for maintaining wellness.","translation":"健康的飲食可以滋養你的身體並增強免疫系統。富含維生素和礦物質的食物對維持健康至關重要。","word":"nourish"}},"nourishing":{"createdAt":1781840030396,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"nourishing 是形容詞，表示滋養的、滋補的；與「幫助患者恢復」和「醫生推薦」的背景相配合。","options":["spoiled","nourishing","cold","spicy"],"sentence":"The ______ soup made with fresh vegetables and lean protein helped the patient recover quickly. The doctor recommended eating this type of meal every day for optimal health.","translation":"用新鮮蔬菜和瘦肉蛋白製成的滋養湯幫助患者迅速康復。醫生建議每天食用這類飲食以獲得最佳健康狀況。","word":"nourishing"}},"novel":{"createdAt":1781616919426,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"新穎的是指前所未有的、新鮮的、令人眼目一新的。","options":["traditional","complex","novel","popular"],"sentence":"The scientist presented a ______ approach to solving the climate crisis. Her innovative method had never been attempted before in the field.","translation":"這位科學家提出了解決氣候危機的新穎方法。她的創新方法在該領域以前從未被嘗試過。","word":"novel"}},"novelist":{"createdAt":1781616876973,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"novelist 名詞表示「小說家」，指專門創作小說的作家。","options":["musician","actress","novelist","chef"],"sentence":"The famous ______ spent ten years writing her award-winning novel. Her name appeared on bestseller lists for months after its publication.","translation":"這位著名小說家花了十年時間寫她獲獎的小說。出版後，她的名字在暢銷書排行榜上出現了幾個月。","word":"novelist"}},"novelty":{"createdAt":1781616919431,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"新穎或新奇是指事物初次出現時引起人們興趣和驚奇的特性。","options":["price","reliability","novelty","quality"],"sentence":"The ______ of the new smartphone wore off after a few months. Once people got used to it, they no longer found it exciting.","translation":"新智能手機的新穎性在幾個月後消退了。一旦人們習慣了它，他們就不再覺得它令人興奮。","word":"novelty"}},"novice":{"createdAt":1781616877016,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"novice 名詞表示「新手、初學者」，指剛開始學習或從事某項活動的人。","options":["champion","novice","expert","professional"],"sentence":"As a ______ in the sport, he made many mistakes during his first competition. More experienced athletes offered him advice and encouragement.","translation":"作為這項運動的初學者，他在第一次比賽中犯了許多錯誤。更有經驗的運動員向他提供了建議和鼓勵。","word":"novice"}},"nuclear":{"createdAt":1781616876976,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"nuclear 形容詞表示「核子的、原子核的」，常用來描述與核能相關的事物。","options":["solar","wind","nuclear","fossil"],"sentence":"The country invested billions in ______ energy to reduce carbon emissions. Scientists believe this power source is crucial for sustainable development.","translation":"該國投入數十億美元於核能，以減少碳排放。科學家認為這種電力來源對可持續發展至關重要。","word":"nuclear"}},"nucleus":{"createdAt":1781616919433,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"核是指原子中心的構成部分，或細胞中心含有遺傳信息的結構。","options":["shell","nucleus","electron","orbit"],"sentence":"The ______ of an atom contains protons and neutrons. Scientists use microscopes to study this tiny central structure.","translation":"原子的核由質子和中子組成。科學家使用顯微鏡研究這個微小的中心結構。","word":"nucleus"}},"nude":{"createdAt":1781616876984,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"nude 形容詞表示「裸體的、一絲不掛的」，在藝術語境中指沒有穿衣服的人體。","options":["clothed","dressed","nude","armored"],"sentence":"The artist painted the model in a ______ pose to capture the natural beauty of the human form. The classical sculpture in the museum displayed similar artistic expression.","translation":"藝術家以裸體姿勢繪製模特兒，以捕捉人類形態的自然美。博物館中的古典雕塑展現了相似的藝術表現。","word":"nude"}},"numb":{"createdAt":1781616876968,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"numb 形容詞表示「麻木的、沒感覺的」，指失去知覺或感覺遲鈍。","options":["warm","numb","painful","tense"],"sentence":"After the dentist injected anesthetic, his fingers felt completely ______. He could not feel the sensation of touch on his hand for several hours.","translation":"牙醫注射麻醉劑後，他的手指感到完全麻木。他好幾小時內無法感受到手上的觸覺。","word":"numb"}},"numerous":{"createdAt":1781616877016,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"numerous 形容詞表示「眾多的、許多的」，指數量很大的人或物。","options":["rare","numerous","occasional","minimal"],"sentence":"The city experienced ______ earthquakes throughout the year, causing concern among residents. Seismic activity was recorded almost every week.","translation":"該市全年經歷了許多地震，引起居民的擔憂。幾乎每週都錄製到地震活動。","word":"numerous"}},"nursery":{"createdAt":1781616876981,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"nursery 名詞表示「幼兒園、託兒所、育兒室」，指照顧和教育年幼孩子的地方。","options":["office","hospital","nursery","warehouse"],"sentence":"The ______ was decorated with colorful murals and soft toys for the infants. Parents left their babies there during working hours.","translation":"託兒所用彩色壁畫和軟玩具裝飾，供嬰兒使用。父母在工作時間將嬰兒留在那裡。","word":"nursery"}},"nurture":{"createdAt":1781616876969,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"nurture 名詞表示「養育、教養、培養」，指照顧和教導某人的過程。","options":["punishment","neglect","restriction","nurture"],"sentence":"Good parental ______ is essential for a child's development. Parents provide love, care, and education to help their children grow into healthy adults.","translation":"良好的父母養育對孩子的發展至關重要。父母提供愛、照顧和教育來幫助孩子成長為健康的成年人。","word":"nurture"}},"nutrient":{"createdAt":1781616919430,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"養分或營養物是指食物中對身體有益的化學物質，如維生素、礦物質等。","options":["ingredient","nutrient","poison","flavor"],"sentence":"Calcium is an essential ______ that strengthens bones and teeth. This mineral must be consumed regularly through dairy products or supplements.","translation":"鈣是一種必要的營養物質，可以強化骨骼和牙齒。這種礦物質必須通過乳製品或補充劑定期攝入。","word":"nutrient"}},"nutrition":{"createdAt":1781616919424,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"營養是指食物中對身體有益的物質，包括維生素、礦物質等養分。","options":["exercise","nutrition","entertainment","decoration"],"sentence":"A balanced diet provides essential ______ for growth and development. The vitamins, minerals, and proteins in food support our body's functions.","translation":"均衡的飲食為成長和發展提供必要的營養。食物中的維生素、礦物質和蛋白質支持我們身體的功能。","word":"nutrition"}},"nutritional":{"createdAt":1781564440930,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"nutritional 作形容詞表示營養的，指與營養價值或成分相關的。","options":["monetary","nutritional","visual","chemical"],"sentence":"The ______ value of this food is quite high with lots of vitamins and minerals. It provides essential nutrients that support good health and body development.","translation":"這種食物的營養價值相當高，含有大量的維生素和礦物質。它提供支持健康和身體發育的必要營養。","word":"nutritional"}},"nutritionist":{"createdAt":1781616876975,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"nutritionist 名詞表示「營養學家」，指研究和提供營養飲食建議的專家。","options":["trainer","nutritionist","doctor","chef"],"sentence":"The ______ advised her client to increase protein intake and reduce sugar consumption. Professional dietary guidance helped the patient achieve her weight loss goals.","translation":"營養學家建議她的客戶增加蛋白質攝入並減少糖分攝入。專業的飲食指導幫助患者實現了她的減肥目標。","word":"nutritionist"}},"nutritious":{"createdAt":1781838276304,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"nutritious作為形容詞表示食物富有營養、有益於健康。","options":["compressed","individual","nutritious","standing"],"sentence":"The doctor recommended eating more ______ foods to improve your health. She specifically suggested adding leafy greens, whole grains, and lean proteins to your daily diet.","translation":"醫生建議吃更多富有營養的食物來改善你的健康。她特別建議在你的日常飲食中增加葉菜、全穀物和瘦肉蛋白。","word":"nutritious"}},"obedience":{"createdAt":1781746685511,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"obedience指的是順從、服從，表示願意遵守規則或聽從他人的指示。","options":["rubbish","obedience","consequence","sober"],"sentence":"The dog trainer rewarded the puppy for its ______ when it followed commands. The animal consistently responded to every instruction without hesitation or resistance.","translation":"訓犬師獎勵小狗的順從，因為它遵循了命令。這隻動物始終迅速回應每個指令，沒有猶豫或抵抗。","word":"obedience"}},"obey":{"createdAt":1781773623458,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"obey作為動詞表示「服從」或「順從」，強調對權威人物或規則的遵從行為。","options":["follow","obey","listen","respect"],"sentence":"The soldiers were trained to ______ their commanding officers without question. When the general gave an order, every soldier immediately followed it without hesitation.","translation":"士兵被訓練無條件地服從他們的指揮官。當將軍下達命令時，每個士兵都立即毫不遲疑地執行。","word":"obey"}},"object":{"createdAt":1781849847401,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"object作為名詞表示物體或實物，與「可以看到和欣賞設計」的線索相符。","options":["concept","object","idea","thought"],"sentence":"The ______ on the table was made of pure silver. Everyone admired its beautiful craftsmanship and intricate design.","translation":"桌子上的物體是用純銀製成的。每個人都讚美它美麗的工藝和複雜的設計。","word":"object"}},"objection":{"createdAt":1781429810264,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"objection是指對某事的不同意或反對意見，通常在討論或決策中表達。","options":["disappearance","firecracker","objection","rite"],"sentence":"Several committee members raised an ______ to the new proposal during the meeting. Despite their concerns about cost and feasibility, the vote proceeded as scheduled.","translation":"在會議期間，幾位委員會成員對新提案提出了反對。儘管他們對成本和可行性有顧慮，投票仍按計劃進行。","word":"objection"}},"obligatory":{"createdAt":1781738392787,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「obligatory」表示必須做的、義務性的，與「mandatory」和「requires」等詞語的意思相符，指必須完成的要求。","options":["tedium","trophy","obligatory","offense"],"sentence":"Attending the mandatory safety training is ______ for all new employees. The company requires every person to complete it before starting work.","translation":"參加強制性安全培訓對所有新員工是義務的。公司要求每個人在開始工作前完成它。","word":"obligatory"}},"observant":{"createdAt":1781485266372,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"observant形容詞表示擁有敏銳的觀察力，能注意到細微的細節和變化。","options":["careless","inattentive","observant","negligent"],"sentence":"The ______ detective noticed tiny scratches on the lock that others had completely missed. His ability to spot small details made him invaluable in solving complex cases.","translation":"這位觀察敏銳的偵探注意到了其他人完全忽視的鎖上微小的刮痕。他發現細節的能力使他在解決複雜案件時無價之寶。","word":"observant"}},"observation":{"createdAt":1781709984194,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"observation 在科學語境中表示通過觀看和記錄來收集信息的過程。","options":["hypothesis","observation","theory","prediction"],"sentence":"Based on careful ______ of the experiment, the scientist noticed that temperature affected the reaction speed. She documented every detail she saw over three months.","translation":"根據對實驗的仔細觀察，科學家注意到溫度影響反應速度。她記錄了三個月內看到的每一個細節。","word":"observation"}},"observe":{"createdAt":1781364476362,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"Observe意指仔細地注視或研究某事物，通常是為了收集信息或進行科學研究。","options":["ignore","celebrate","observe","criticize"],"sentence":"The scientist decided to ______ the behavior of the penguins in their natural habitat for several weeks. She took detailed notes on how they hunted, played, and interacted with each other throughout each day.","translation":"科學家決定在企鵝的自然棲息地觀察牠們的行為，為期數週。她詳細記錄了牠們如何捕獵、嬉戲以及每天彼此互動的方式。","word":"observe"}},"observer":{"createdAt":1781664082522,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"observer 是指觀察者或觀察家，指看著某事發生但不直接參與的人。","options":["participant","observer","conductor","inventor"],"sentence":"As a keen ______, the scientist carefully watched the experiment unfold without participating. Her detailed notes recorded every change that occurred during the procedure.","translation":"作為一名敏銳的觀察者，科學家仔細觀察實驗進行，但不參與其中。她詳細的筆記記錄了過程中發生的每一項變化。","word":"observer"}},"obsessed":{"createdAt":1781849847404,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"obsessed表示對某事物執著或沉迷，與「花費大量時間和金錢」的線索相符。","options":["indifferent","obsessed","bored","uninterested"],"sentence":"He became completely ______ with collecting vintage stamps. He spent all his free time and money searching for rare editions.","translation":"他完全沉迷於收集古董郵票。他花費所有的空閒時間和金錢尋找稀有版本。","word":"obsessed"}},"obsession":{"createdAt":1781709890952,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"obsession指的是對某事物強烈而持久的執著或著迷，常常影響一個人的日常生活和決定。","options":["hesitation","obsession","implication","hazard"],"sentence":"Her ______ with collecting vintage stamps has consumed most of her free time and money. She spends every weekend at antique markets searching for rare editions to add to her collection.","translation":"她對收集古董郵票的執念佔據了她大部分的空閒時間和金錢。她每個週末都在古董市場尋找罕見版本來加入她的收藏。","word":"obsession"}},"obvious":{"createdAt":1781345746904,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"obvious 作形容詞，表示明顯的、顯而易見的，無需解釋或證明。","options":["hidden","obvious","uncertain","debatable"],"sentence":"It was ______ to everyone that the experiment had failed from the start. The data clearly showed that none of the results matched the predicted outcomes.","translation":"每個人都很明顯地看出實驗從一開始就失敗了。數據清楚地表明，沒有任何結果與預測的結果相符。","word":"obvious"}},"obviously":{"createdAt":1781664082525,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"obviously 是副詞，表示明顯地、顯然地或易於看出的。","options":["subtly","obviously","possibly","hardly"],"sentence":"The student was ______ unprepared for the final exam, as evidenced by his poor performance. He had not studied any of the material and struggled with even the simplest questions.","translation":"這名學生顯然沒有為期末考試做準備，他的糟糕表現證明了這一點。他沒有學習任何材料，甚至在最簡單的問題上也遇到了困難。","word":"obviously"}},"occasion":{"createdAt":1781864339048,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"occasion用來表示特定的時間或事件，特別是重要或特殊的場合。","options":["event","occasion","moment","chance"],"sentence":"We should dress formally for this important ______. My cousin is getting married next Saturday, and we want to look our best.","translation":"我們應該在這個重要的場合穿著正式。我的表弟下個星期六要結婚了，我們想要看起來最好。","word":"occasion"}},"occasional":{"createdAt":1781951900950,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"occasional表示不經常發生或只在某些時候發生，與「每天」的習慣相對立。","options":["constant","occasional","regular","daily"],"sentence":"My grandfather drinks coffee only on ______ mornings, not every single day. He usually prefers tea with his breakfast.","translation":"我的祖父只在偶爾的早晨喝咖啡，而不是每天都喝。他通常喜歡用茶來搭配早餐。","word":"occasional"}},"occasionally":{"createdAt":1781402539334,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"occasionally 表示不經常發生，只是在某些特殊或不規則的時間發生某事。","options":["always","occasionally","never","frequently"],"sentence":"She ______ visits her grandmother on weekends. Most weeks she stays home, but perhaps once a month she makes the trip.","translation":"她偶爾在週末拜訪她的祖母。大多數週她待在家裡，但也許一個月一次她會進行這次旅行。","word":"occasionally"}},"occupy":{"createdAt":1781774456603,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"occupy 在此意指用軍事力量佔領或控制某個地區。","options":["abandon","survey","hold","visit"],"sentence":"The army decided to ______ the strategic region to control the area militarily. Soldiers were stationed there to maintain order.","translation":"軍隊決定佔領該戰略地區以軍事控制該地區。士兵駐紮在那裡以維持秩序。","word":"occupy"}},"occur":{"createdAt":1781831848726,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"occur 是動詞，表示「發生」，通常用於描述事件或情況的發生。","options":["appears","happens","occur","exists"],"sentence":"An accident ______ on the highway yesterday evening. The police arrived within minutes to help the injured drivers.","translation":"昨晚在高速公路上發生了一場事故。警察在幾分鐘內趕到協助受傷的駕駛人。","word":"occur"}},"occurrence":{"createdAt":1781359980245,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"occurrence指某事發生、出現或遭遇的現象；強調事件或事物發生的頻率或次數。","options":["prediction","prevention","occurrence","documentation"],"sentence":"The ______ of earthquakes in this region has increased significantly over the past decade. Local authorities recorded more than twenty tremors last year alone.","translation":"這個地區地震的發生頻率在過去十年大幅增加。當地當局去年單獨記錄了二十多次震動。","word":"occurrence"}},"odd":{"createdAt":1781860901461,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"odd表示古怪的、異常的，用來形容不符合常理或出人意料的事物","options":["common","odd","expected","normal"],"sentence":"It was quite ______ that he arrived at the party wearing pajamas. Everyone else was dressed formally, making his choice seem very unusual.","translation":"他穿著睡衣來到派對是相當古怪的。每個人都穿著正式服裝，使他的選擇顯得非常不尋常。","word":"odd"}},"odor":{"createdAt":1781746848187,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"odor 表示「氣味」或「臭味」，指通過嗅覺感受到的氣體或香氣。","options":["sight","sound","odor","taste"],"sentence":"The ______ coming from the garbage bin was absolutely unbearable in the hot summer heat. The janitor quickly replaced the trash and cleaned the area thoroughly.","translation":"在炎熱的夏天，來自垃圾桶的臭味是完全無法忍受的。清潔工迅速更換了垃圾並徹底清潔了該區域。","word":"odor"}},"offended":{"createdAt":1781434900591,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"offended表示感到不快、傷害或被冒犯的狀態。","options":["pleased","offended","amused","inspired"],"sentence":"She felt ______ by his rude comments about her appearance during the meeting. His words hurt her feelings and she refused to speak to him for days.","translation":"她對他在會議上關於她外貌的粗魯評論感到被冒犯。他的言語傷害了她的感情，她拒絕與他交談了好幾天。","word":"offended"}},"offense":{"createdAt":1781738392785,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「take offense」是常見的片語，表示對某人的言論或行為感到冒犯或被冒犯，符合被傷害和受侮辱的感受。","options":["trophy","offense","tedium","obligation"],"sentence":"Taking ______ to his comments, she decided to avoid him in the future. She felt deeply hurt and insulted by what he had said about her work.","translation":"她對他的評論感到冒犯，決定以後要避開他。她對他關於她工作的言論感到深深受傷和被侮辱。","word":"offense"}},"official":{"createdAt":1781507137219,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"official 指的是來自政府或權威機構的正式、具有權威性的，而不是非正式或個人的說法。","options":["unofficial","official","personal","private"],"sentence":"The ______ statement from the government was released at noon on Tuesday. All major news outlets reported the announcement as the authoritative word from the administration.","translation":"政府的官方聲明在星期二中午發布。所有主要新聞媒體都將這份公告報導為來自政府的權威聲明。","word":"official"}},"officially":{"createdAt":1781693281409,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"officially（正式地）意指以正式、官方或經過授權的方式進行某事，而非非正式或私下進行。","options":["quietly","officially","hypothetically","accidentally"],"sentence":"The company announced the new product line ______ during a press conference yesterday. All media outlets reported on the announcement, confirming it was a formal and authorized disclosure.","translation":"公司在昨天的記者會上正式宣佈了新產品線。所有媒體都報導了這項宣佈，確認這是一次正式和授權的披露。","word":"officially"}},"offshore":{"createdAt":1781311983483,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"offshore 指在海上或離岸的，通常用於描述水域中的設施或項目。","options":["offshore","mature","expressive","presidential"],"sentence":"The company decided to build its ______ wind farms to harness renewable energy. These installations are located several miles away from the coast in the ocean.","translation":"該公司決定建造離岸風電場以利用可再生能源。這些設施位於海岸線外數英里的大洋中。","word":"offshore"}},"offspring":{"createdAt":1781580511748,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"offspring 指動物或人類的幼崽或後代，這裡指獅子的幼崽","options":["enemies","offspring","territory","prey"],"sentence":"The lion and lioness watched their ______ playing in the savanna. The young cubs would soon learn to hunt from their parents.","translation":"獅子和母獅看著他們的後代在草原上玩耍。這些年幼的幼崽很快就會學會從父母那裡狩獵。","word":"offspring"}},"olive":{"createdAt":1781424157177,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"olive 是一種小的綠色或黑色果實，來自橄欖樹，常用於烹飪和製油。","options":["grape","olive","lemon","pepper"],"sentence":"The chef added fresh ______ to the Mediterranean salad to give it an authentic Greek flavor. These small green fruits were picked from trees in the coastal region.","translation":"廚師向地中海沙拉中加入新鮮的橄欖，以賦予它真正的希臘風味。這些小綠色果實是從沿海地區的樹上採摘的。","word":"olive"}},"oppose":{"createdAt":1781843396460,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"oppose表示反對或抵抗某事，在此指公民對政策的強烈反對態度。","options":["support","approve","oppose","encourage"],"sentence":"Many citizens decided to ______ the government's new environmental policy. They organized protests and submitted formal objections to demonstrate their disagreement.","translation":"許多市民決定反對政府的新環保政策。他們組織抗議並提交正式異議以表達他們的反對。","word":"oppose"}},"opt":{"createdAt":1781424282281,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"opt表示「選擇」或「挑選」，常用於表達在多個選項中優先選擇某一個，通常搭配介詞for使用。","options":["refuse","choose","delay","postpone"],"sentence":"After reviewing all the available job offers, Sarah decided to ______ for the position at the tech startup instead of the corporate firm. She was excited because the startup offered more creative freedom and opportunities to innovate.","translation":"在審視了所有可得的工作機會後，莎拉決定選擇科技新創公司的職位，而不是企業公司的職位。她很興奮，因為新創公司提供了更多的創意自由和創新機會。","word":"opt"}},"optimism":{"createdAt":1781840030393,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"optimism 是名詞，表示樂觀、樂天的態度；在句子中與「相信事情會改善」和「積極展望」相呼應。","options":["pessimism","optimism","confusion","arrogance"],"sentence":"Despite the challenging circumstances, Sarah maintained her ______ and believed things would improve. Even when others gave up, her positive outlook never wavered.","translation":"儘管情況具有挑戰性，莎拉仍然保持樂觀態度，相信事情會改善。即使當其他人放棄時，她的積極展望從未動搖。","word":"optimism"}},"option":{"createdAt":1781693254764,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"option表示可供選擇的事物或選項，強調有多種可能性。","options":["obligation","option","complaint","reservation"],"sentence":"The restaurant offered customers multiple ______ for their main course. Diners could choose between chicken, fish, beef, or vegetarian pasta.","translation":"這家餐廳為顧客提供了多種主菜選擇。用餐者可以在雞肉、魚、牛肉或素食義大利麵之間選擇。","word":"option"}},"ordeal":{"createdAt":1781838276307,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"ordeal指嚴峻的考驗或痛苦的經歷。","options":["volume","individual","ordeal","proponent"],"sentence":"After surviving the ______ of the natural disaster, the survivors received counselling and support. They had endured weeks of hardship and uncertainty before being rescued.","translation":"在經歷自然災害的磨難後，倖存者獲得了諮詢和支持。在被救出前，他們經歷了數週的艱辛和不確定性。","word":"ordeal"}},"ordered":{"createdAt":1781849847403,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ordered表示有序的或整齊的，與「整齊排列、容易找到東西」的線索相符。","options":["chaotic","ordered","messy","scattered"],"sentence":"His bedroom was very ______ with everything arranged neatly on shelves. You could easily find anything you needed without searching.","translation":"他的臥室非常整齊，每樣東西都整齊地排列在架子上。你可以輕鬆找到任何你需要的東西，無需搜尋。","word":"ordered"}},"organism":{"createdAt":1781693269015,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"organism 指的是活的生物體或生命體，可以是微生物、植物或動物。","options":["landscape","organism","monument","technology"],"sentence":"Scientists discovered a new ______ in the deep ocean that had never been documented before. The microscopic creature has unique characteristics that distinguish it from all previously known species.","translation":"科學家在深海中發現了一個以前從未被記錄過的新的生物體。這種微小的生物具有將其與所有已知物種區分開來的獨特特徵。","word":"organism"}},"organization":{"createdAt":1781920819162,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"organization 意為「組織；團體」，指由多個成員組成、有結構和目的的集體機構。","options":["individual","charity","location","document"],"sentence":"The ______ worked tirelessly to provide disaster relief to affected communities. It consisted of thousands of volunteers coordinated through regional branches across the country.","translation":"那個慈善機構不遺餘力地為受災社區提供救災援助。它由數千名志願者組成，透過全國各地的地區分支進行協調。","word":"organization"}},"organized":{"createdAt":1781402539333,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"organized 表示有系統地安排或整理，使事物井然有序、便於使用或理解。","options":["chaotic","organized","temporary","empty"],"sentence":"The ______ office has a clear filing system and labeled drawers. Everything is easy to find because the manager spent weeks creating an efficient structure.","translation":"這個井井有條的辦公室有清晰的檔案系統和標有標籤的抽屜。一切都很容易找到，因為經理花了幾週時間創建一個高效的結構。","word":"organized"}},"originality":{"createdAt":1781424157168,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"originality 指的是創新和獨創的品質，與傳統或模仿相對。","options":["imitation","originality","technique","popularity"],"sentence":"The artist's work was praised for its ______, as no one had ever seen such a unique style before. The judges noted that every piece was completely different from traditional art movements.","translation":"這位藝術家的作品因其獨創性而受到讚揚，因為沒有人見過如此獨特的風格。評委們指出每件作品都與傳統藝術運動完全不同。","word":"originality"}},"orphan":{"createdAt":1781452134701,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"orphan名詞指因父母去世而失去親生父母照顧的兒童。","options":["teacher","immigrant","orphan","volunteer"],"sentence":"The young ______ was taken in by the charity organization after losing both parents. The social workers ensured he received proper education and emotional support at their residential facility.","translation":"失去雙親的小孤兒被慈善機構收留了。社工人員確保他在他們的居住設施中獲得適當的教育和情感支持。","word":"orphan"}},"orthodox":{"createdAt":1781424356418,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"orthodox指的是遵循既定的傳統或廣泛接受的標準做法，而不是創新或激進的方法。","options":["radical","modern","orthodox","experimental"],"sentence":"His views on education were quite ______ and aligned with traditional teaching methods. He believed in standardized curricula and conventional approaches that had been used for decades.","translation":"他對教育的看法相當正統，與傳統教學方法相一致。他相信標準化課程和已使用數十年的常規方法。","word":"orthodox"}},"outfit":{"createdAt":1781842254309,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"outfit 在此指一個組織化的團隊或集體，包括所有必要的人員和設備來完成特定的任務。","options":["outfit","building","schedule","strategy"],"sentence":"The rock band needed to purchase new stage equipment and hire additional musicians to complete their ______. The manager was responsible for assembling all the necessary members and gear for the upcoming world tour.","translation":"搖滾樂隊需要購買新的舞台設備並僱用額外的音樂家來完成他們的團隊。經理負責為即將進行的世界巡迴演唱會組合所有必要的成員和設備。","word":"outfit"}},"outing":{"createdAt":1781437435163,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"outing 指短途旅遊或遠足活動，通常是有組織的集體外出參觀。","options":["meeting","outing","lecture","interview"],"sentence":"The school organized a wonderful ______ to the botanical gardens for all students. We packed lunches and spent the entire day exploring the exotic plants and enjoying nature together.","translation":"學校為所有學生組織了一次美妙的短途旅遊到植物園。我們帶著午餐，花了整天時間探索異國植物並一起享受大自然。","word":"outing"}},"outlet":{"createdAt":1781665727111,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"outlet 在此指排放口或出口，用於讓液體、氣體或廢物流出或排出。","options":["entrance","container","outlet","barrier"],"sentence":"The factory installed a large water ______ to drain waste materials from production. The pipe extended directly into the river outside the facility.","translation":"工廠安裝了一個大型水排放孔來排放生產中的廢料。管道直接延伸到設施外的河裡。","word":"outlet"}},"outright":{"createdAt":1781920819166,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"outright 作副詞時意為「徹底地；完全地；立刻地」，表示毫不保留、絕對的態度或立即的行動。","options":["partially","completely","reluctantly","quietly"],"sentence":"The company ______ rejected the merger proposal without discussing any of its terms. The decision was made immediately and without any possibility of negotiation.","translation":"該公司徹底拒絕了合併提案，沒有討論任何條款。該決定是立刻做出的，沒有任何談判的可能性。","word":"outright"}},"outwards":{"createdAt":1781268630474,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"outwards表示向外或朝外的方向，與inwards（向內）相反。","options":["inwards","upwards","outwards","downwards"],"sentence":"The explosion sent debris ______ in all directions. The force pushed everything away from the center point.","translation":"爆炸將碎片向外發送到四面八方。這股力量將所有東西從中心點推開。","word":"outwards"}},"overcoat":{"createdAt":1781484415218,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"overcoat是指穿在其他衣服外層的長厚外套，用於保暖和防寒。","options":["shirt","overcoat","shoes","hat"],"sentence":"He put on his heavy ______ before stepping outside into the freezing winter air. The thick wool garment protected him from the biting cold and strong winds.","translation":"在步入刺骨的冬季寒冷空氣之前，他穿上了厚重的大衣。這件厚羊毛衣保護他免受刺骨的寒冷和強風的侵襲。","word":"overcoat"}},"overcome":{"createdAt":1781926464745,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"overcome 表示成功地面對並克服困難或負面情感，通常需要努力和時間。","options":["express","overcome","ignore","announce"],"sentence":"She worked hard to ______ her fear of public speaking through practice and coaching. After months of dedication, she delivered a confident presentation to two hundred people.","translation":"她通過練習和指導努力克服了她對公開演講的恐懼。經過數月的奉獻，她自信地向二百人做了一次演講。","word":"overcome"}},"overtake":{"createdAt":1781651261373,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"overtake在此表示趕上並超過他人，強調在比賽或競爭中達到領先地位。","options":["overtake","projection","physics","midst"],"sentence":"The runner's energy and speed began to ______ that of her competitors in the final lap. By crossing the finish line first, she had surpassed all the other athletes.","translation":"那位跑者在最後一圈的能量和速度開始超過她的競爭對手。她通過首先衝過終點線而超越了所有其他運動員。","word":"overtake"}},"overtaken":{"createdAt":1781580511760,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"overtaken 是 overtake 的過去分詞，表示被超越或被超車","options":["cheered","supported","photographed","overtaken"],"sentence":"The racing car was ______ by its rival on the final lap of the competition. The other vehicle had accelerated faster and passed it just before the finish line.","translation":"在比賽的最後一圈，這輛賽車被對手超越了。另一輛車加速更快，在終點線前剛好超過它。","word":"overtaken"}},"overthrow":{"createdAt":1781443653220,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"overthrow指的是用武力推翻或打倒現有政權或統治者。","options":["support","strengthen","overthrow","elect"],"sentence":"The rebel forces planned to ______ the corrupt government through armed resistance. After months of fighting, they successfully took control of the capital and established a new regime.","translation":"叛軍計畫通過武裝抵抗來推翻腐敗的政府。經過數月的戰鬥後，他們成功控制了首都並建立了新政權。","word":"overthrow"}},"oyster":{"createdAt":1781840892408,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"oyster是牡蠣，一種貝類海鮮，需要打開貝殼才能食用。","options":["steak","salmon","oyster","lobster"],"sentence":"The luxury seafood restaurant served a delicious ______ appetizer topped with caviar and lemon juice. The chef carefully shucked each shell to reveal the tender meat inside.","translation":"這家高級海鮮餐廳供應美味的牡蠣前菜，上面裝飾著魚子醬和檸檬汁。廚師仔細地打開每個貝殼，露出裡面的軟肉。","word":"oyster"}},"packet":{"createdAt":1781738105687,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"packet 指的是一個小的、輕便的包裝或容器，通常用於裝載小量的商品。","options":["barrel","packet","crate","container"],"sentence":"She bought a ______ of instant noodles from the convenience store for her lunch. The small container contained dried noodles, seasoning powder, and cooking instructions all in one unit.","translation":"她從便利店為午餐買了一小包速凍麵。這個小容器裡面包含了乾麵、調味粉和烹飪說明，全部在一個單位裡。","word":"packet"}},"panelled":{"createdAt":1781515329268,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"panelled 形容詞，意思是鑲嵌面板的、用木板裝飾的，指用板材覆蓋或裝飾的表面。","options":["painted","panelled","tiled","carpeted"],"sentence":"The mansion's dining room featured walls ______ with dark mahogany wood. The luxurious interior design gave the space an elegant and sophisticated appearance.","translation":"豪宅的餐廳的牆壁用深色桃花心木面板裝飾。奢華的室內設計賦予該空間優雅而精緻的外觀。","word":"panelled"}},"panic":{"createdAt":1781758494838,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"panic 指突然的恐懼和驚慌失措，與第二句中人們急忙逃難的行為相符。","options":["calm","joy","panic","boredom"],"sentence":"When the fire alarm suddenly went off, a wave of ______ swept through the crowded shopping mall. People ran frantically toward the exits, pushing and shoving in their desperate attempt to escape.","translation":"當火警警報突然響起時，驚恐蔓延整個擁擠的購物中心。人們瘋狂地跑向出口，推搡著試圖逃脫。","word":"panic"}},"paperback":{"createdAt":1781709984198,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"paperback 名詞指用紙質封面裝訂的書籍，通常比精裝本便宜且更輕便。","options":["hardbound","paperback","leather-bound","cloth-covered"],"sentence":"I bought a ______ version of the novel because it was less expensive than the hardcover edition. The soft cover made it easy to carry in my backpack while traveling.","translation":"我買了小說的平裝本，因為它比精裝版便宜。柔軟的封面使我在旅行時容易將其放入背包中。","word":"paperback"}},"parachute":{"createdAt":1781836375376,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"parachute是降落傘，一種用於從飛行中的飛機安全著陸的裝置。","options":["umbrella","parachute","balloon","net"],"sentence":"When the plane's engines failed, the pilot deployed his ______ and prepared to land safely. The device slowed his descent significantly as he drifted toward the ground.","translation":"當飛機引擎失效時，飛行員部署了降落傘並準備安全著陸。該裝置在他漂向地面時顯著減緩了他的下降。","word":"parachute"}},"paradox":{"createdAt":1781449095516,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"paradox意為似是而非或自相矛盾，用來描述看似不合邏輯但可能含有真理的言論或情況。","options":["truth","paradox","fact","principle"],"sentence":"The statement that \"less is more\" is a famous ______ in philosophy. It seems contradictory at first, but it actually makes sense when you think deeply about it.","translation":"「少即是多」這句話是哲學中著名的悖論。乍看之下似乎自相矛盾，但當你深入思考時，它實際上是有道理的。","word":"paradox"}},"paralyze":{"createdAt":1781693266949,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"paralyze表示使某人或某物失去行動能力或思考能力，引申為使人感到極度害怕或無能為力。","options":["energize","motivate","paralyze","encourage"],"sentence":"The accident seemed to ______ the entire community with fear. Everyone was too shocked and frightened to move or speak for several minutes.","translation":"這起事故似乎使整個社區都被恐懼所癱瘓。每個人都震驚和害怕得說不出話來，無法行動。","word":"paralyze"}},"participation":{"createdAt":1781345746906,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"participation 作名詞，指參與或加入某項活動，強調主動的投入。","options":["absence","participation","observation","distraction"],"sentence":"Active ______ in classroom discussions has significantly improved students' academic performance. Teachers noticed that engaged students who regularly contributed their ideas achieved higher grades.","translation":"在課堂討論中的積極參與大大提高了學生的學習成績。教師們注意到積極參與並經常貢獻想法的學生成績更高。","word":"participation"}},"particular":{"createdAt":1781582251998,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"particular 是形容詞，表示獨特的、特殊的或與眾不同的特質。","options":["common","generic","particular","standard"],"sentence":"This restaurant has a ______ style of cooking that you won't find anywhere else in the city. The chef uses secret family recipes passed down through three generations.","translation":"這家餐廳有一種獨特的烹飪風格，在城市的其他地方找不到。主廚使用傳承三代的祕密家傳食譜。","word":"particular"}},"particularly":{"createdAt":1781693271588,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"particularly表示特別地、尤其地，用於強調某個事物在眾多選擇中特別受歡迎或重要。","options":["generally","particularly","rarely","never"],"sentence":"The restaurant serves many delicious dishes, but I enjoy their seafood ______ whenever I visit. The ocean-based meals are my favorite items on the entire menu.","translation":"這家餐廳提供許多美味佳餚，但我特別喜歡他們的海鮮。這些海鮮餐是整個菜單上我最喜歡的項目。","word":"particularly"}},"passer_by":{"createdAt":1781926371001,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"passer-by 意思是路人、過路人，指恰好經過某地點的人，通常與該地點沒有特定的關係。","options":["resident","passer-by","police officer","driver"],"sentence":"A ______ witnessed the car accident and immediately called the emergency services. The witness provided crucial information about what happened at the intersection.","translation":"一位路人目擊了這起車禍，並立即撥打了急救服務電話。這位證人提供了關於在十字路口發生的情況的關鍵信息。","word":"passer-by"}},"pastime":{"createdAt":1781311922067,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pastime 是指用來打發時間或消遣的活動，通常是為了娛樂和享受。","options":["job","pastime","habit","chore"],"sentence":"Reading novels is my favorite ______ during long train journeys. I find that spending time with a good book helps the hours pass quickly and keeps me entertained.","translation":"在長途火車旅行中，閱讀小說是我最喜愛的消遣。我發現花時間讀一本好書能幫助時間快速流逝並保持我的娛樂。","word":"pastime"}},"patent":{"createdAt":1781842656772,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"專利權是政府授予發明人在一定時期內對其發明享有的獨占權利，用以保護創新的技術或產品。","options":["license","patent","trademark","copyright"],"sentence":"The inventor filed a ______ to protect her new invention from being copied by competitors. The government granted her exclusive rights to manufacture and sell the product for twenty years.","translation":"這位發明家申請了專利權來保護她的新發明，防止競爭對手抄襲。政府授予她在二十年內製造和銷售該產品的獨家權利。","word":"patent"}},"path":{"createdAt":1781268630480,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"path指的是小徑或小路，通常是行人或動物行走的較窄的通道。","options":["road","path","highway","bridge"],"sentence":"The hikers followed a narrow ______ through the dense forest. The trail was clearly marked with white blazes on the trees.","translation":"登山者沿著一條狹窄的小徑穿過密林。這條小路在樹上用白色標記清晰地標記。","word":"path"}},"pathetic":{"createdAt":1781693254761,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pathetic形容令人感到失望或悲慘的情況，通常帶有負面評價。","options":["excellent","pathetic","energetic","athletic"],"sentence":"The team's performance in the championship game was absolutely ______, with players making careless mistakes throughout. They lost 0-10, failing to score a single point.","translation":"球隊在錦標賽中的表現絕對悲慘，球員們始終在犯粗心大意的錯誤。他們以0比10的比分落敗，未能得到一分。","word":"pathetic"}},"patriotic":{"createdAt":1781437013477,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"patriotic 形容人對自己的國家忠誠和熱愛，願意為國家的利益而奉獻。","options":["patriotic","selfish","indifferent","cowardly"],"sentence":"The soldiers displayed their ______ spirit by volunteering to serve their country during the war. They were willing to sacrifice their safety to protect their nation's freedom and independence.","translation":"士兵們通過在戰爭期間自願為祖國服役來展現他們的愛國精神。他們願意犧牲自己的安全來保護國家的自由和獨立。","word":"patriotic"}},"patrol":{"createdAt":1781257238304,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"patrol指定期往返巡視某個區域，通常是為了維持秩序和安全。","options":["construct","patrol","decorate","abandon"],"sentence":"Police officers ______ the streets every night to maintain safety. The officers walked up and down each block checking for any signs of trouble or suspicious activity.","translation":"警察每晚巡邏街道以維護安全。警察沿著每個街區走上走下，檢查任何麻煩跡象或可疑活動。","word":"patrol"}},"peak":{"createdAt":1781481124697,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"peak 指山的最高點或事物發展的最高階段。","options":["slope","summit","base","ridge"],"sentence":"The mountain climbers finally reached the ______ after five days of exhausting trek. From this highest point, they could see valleys and clouds far below them.","translation":"登山者在經過五天的疲憊跋涉後終於到達了山頂。從這個最高點，他們可以看到遠處下方的山谷和雲層。","word":"peak"}},"pedestrian":{"createdAt":1781532967162,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pedestrian 指行人，與「過馬路」和「正在行走的人」的描述相符。","options":["driver","pedestrian","cyclist","passenger"],"sentence":"The ______ was crossing the street when the car suddenly turned the corner. The person walking had the right of way.","translation":"______(行人)正在過馬路時，汽車突然轉過街角。這個正在行走的人有優先通行權。","word":"pedestrian"}},"peek":{"createdAt":1782016805981,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"peek 是動詞，表示快速或秘密地看，通常是從隱蔽的地方窺視。","options":["peek","flee","ignore","skip"],"sentence":"The curious child tried to ______ behind the curtain to see what presents were hidden. His mother caught him with his eyes directed toward the gap in the fabric.","translation":"好奇的孩子試著偷看窗簾後面看看隱藏了什麼禮物。他的母親抓住他時，他的眼睛正指向布料的縫隙。","word":"peek"}},"pelt":{"createdAt":1781363994340,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"pelt作為名詞表示動物的皮毛，通常指去毛的獸皮，可用於製作衣物或毛皮製品。","options":["skin","arrow","voice","stone"],"sentence":"The hunter carefully removed the ______ from the animal to use as clothing. He stretched and dried the soft fur before trading it at the market.","translation":"獵人小心地從動物身上剝下獸皮來作為衣服。他在拿到市場交易之前先將柔軟的毛皮拉伸並晾乾。","word":"pelt"}},"penalty":{"createdAt":1781268630486,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"penalty指的是處罰或懲罰，特別是針對違規或犯罪行為的懲罰。","options":["reward","bonus","penalty","award"],"sentence":"The player received a ______ for fouling his opponent during the game. He was benched for the next five minutes as punishment.","translation":"球員因在比賽中犯規對手而受到處罰。作為懲罰，他被替換下場五分鐘。","word":"penalty"}},"peninsula":{"createdAt":1781926370999,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"peninsula 意思是半島，指由水體三面包圍、只有一面與陸地相連的地理區域。","options":["island","peninsula","continent","plateau"],"sentence":"Florida is a large ______ that extends into the Atlantic Ocean and Gulf of Mexico. It is surrounded by water on three sides, which shapes its climate and economy.","translation":"佛羅里達是一個伸入大西洋和墨西哥灣的大半島。它在三面被水包圍，這形成了它的氣候和經濟。","word":"peninsula"}},"per":{"createdAt":1781414884520,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"per是介詞，表示「每」或「每一」，常用於計算單位價格或比率。","options":["per","after","during","beyond"],"sentence":"The car rental company charges thirty dollars ______ day for this luxury vehicle. If you rent it for a week, the total cost would be two hundred and ten dollars.","translation":"租車公司對這輛豪華車每天收費三十美元。如果你租一週，總成本將是二百一十美元。","word":"per"}},"perception":{"createdAt":1781268630485,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"perception指的是感知或認知，是指人對事物的理解和看法，可能與事實不符。","options":["action","perception","reaction","decision"],"sentence":"His ______ of the situation was completely different from reality. He believed the meeting was a disaster when it actually went very well.","translation":"他對局勢的感知與現實完全不同。他認為會議是一場災難，而實際上進行得非常順利。","word":"perception"}},"perfectionist":{"createdAt":1781864339052,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"perfectionist指對自己或他人的工作要求極高，追求完美無缺的人。","options":["student","perfectionist","writer","scholar"],"sentence":"My sister is such a ______ that she rewrites her essays five times before submitting them. Even though her first draft is already excellent, she insists on finding every tiny flaw.","translation":"我的妹妹是個完美主義者，她在提交論文前要重寫五次。雖然她的初稿已經很優秀了，但她堅持要找到每一個小缺點。","word":"perfectionist"}},"performer":{"createdAt":1781832549170,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"performer 指在觀眾面前進行表演或展示技能的人，可以是舞者、雜技演員、音樂家等各種類型。","options":["musician","painter","performer","chef"],"sentence":"The talented ______ captivated the entire audience with her stunning acrobatic display on stage. Her years of training and practice were evident in every graceful movement she executed.","translation":"這位才華橫溢的表演者用她舞台上令人驚歎的特技表演吸引了整個觀眾。她多年的訓練和練習在她執行的每一個優雅動作中都很明顯。","word":"performer"}},"periodically":{"createdAt":1781693303267,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"periodically 表示「定期地」或「週期性地」，指按照固定的時間間隔反覆進行某項活動。","options":["occasionally","periodically","rarely","once"],"sentence":"The company checks its equipment ______ to ensure everything is functioning properly. These inspections happen every three months without fail.","translation":"公司定期檢查其設備以確保所有東西運作正常。這些檢查每三個月進行一次，風雨不改。","word":"periodically"}},"perish":{"createdAt":1781836375377,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"perish表示毀滅或死亡，特別是指生物因為缺乏必要條件而無法生存。","options":["evolve","perish","migrate","adapt"],"sentence":"Many animals will ______ if their natural habitats continue to be destroyed. Without forests or water sources, they cannot survive.","translation":"如果自然棲息地繼續被破壞，許多動物將會滅絕。沒有森林或水源，它們無法生存。","word":"perish"}},"permanent":{"createdAt":1781714871283,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"長久的是指持續很長時間，不會改變或結束的狀態。","options":["seasonal","permanent","brief","casual"],"sentence":"The company decided to hire him for a ______ position rather than a temporary contract. He would work there for many years without any expiration date.","translation":"公司決定為他提供一份長久的職位，而不是臨時合約。他將在那裡工作多年，沒有任何終止日期。","word":"permanent"}},"perseverance":{"createdAt":1781362281661,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"perseverance表示毅力和不屈不撓的精神，即堅持不懈的決心。","options":["laziness","perseverance","arrogance","confusion"],"sentence":"Her ______ through years of training eventually led to Olympic gold. She never gave up despite countless setbacks and failures.","translation":"她多年訓練中的毅力最終導致了奧運金牌。儘管遭遇無數挫折和失敗，她從未放棄。","word":"perseverance"}},"persist":{"createdAt":1781622232182,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"persist 意為堅持不懈地繼續做某事，儘管遇到困難或反對。","options":["abandon","persist","forget","doubt"],"sentence":"Despite facing rejection, she continued to ______ in her efforts to become a professional musician. Eventually, after years of dedication, she was accepted into a prestigious conservatory.","translation":"儘管面臨拒絕，她繼續堅持她成為專業音樂家的努力。最終，經過多年的奉獻，她被著名音樂學院錄取。","word":"persist"}},"personality":{"createdAt":1781431278559,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"personality指一個人的個性、人格特質和整體行為模式。","options":["appearance","personality","intelligence","schedule"],"sentence":"Her bright and cheerful ______ makes her popular with everyone at school. Classmates are drawn to her infectious enthusiasm and kind attitude toward others.","translation":"她明亮和愉快的個性使她在學校受歡迎。同學們被她具有感染力的熱情和對他人的善良態度所吸引。","word":"personality"}},"persuasive":{"createdAt":1781515372605,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"persuasive用來形容具有說服力、能讓人改變想法或接受觀點的事物","options":["violent","persuasive","domestic","chief"],"sentence":"The ______ argument convinced many voters to change their minds about the policy. His speech included compelling evidence and logical reasoning that appealed to both emotions and facts.","translation":"那個有說服力的論點說服了許多選民改變對該政策的看法。他的演講包含了令人信服的證據和合理的推理，吸引了情感和事實兩方面的共鳴。","word":"persuasive"}},"pessimistic":{"createdAt":1781774456604,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"pessimistic 形容一個人傾向於期待負面結果和事物的態度。","options":["realistic","optimistic","gloomy","balanced"],"sentence":"Despite having many opportunities, he maintained a ______ outlook on life. He always expected the worst possible outcomes.","translation":"儘管擁有許多機會，他對生活仍然持悲觀態度。他總是期待最壞的結果。","word":"pessimistic"}},"pest":{"createdAt":1781580511759,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"pest 是指危害農作物或造成麻煩的害蟲或討厭的東西","options":["blessing","helper","pest","friend"],"sentence":"The farmer discovered a ______ infestation in his crops that was destroying the harvest. He would need to use pesticide to eliminate these unwanted insects.","translation":"農民發現他的莊稼中有害蟲侵擾，正在毀壞收穫。他需要使用殺蟲劑來消滅這些不受歡迎的昆蟲。","word":"pest"}},"petrol":{"createdAt":1781871338553,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"petrol是指汽油，用於給車輛提供動力，與加油站和refuel相關。","options":["water","fuel","diesel","battery"],"sentence":"The car's ______ tank is nearly empty after the long road trip. We need to stop at the nearest gas station immediately to refuel.","translation":"這輛車在長途旅行後的油箱幾乎是空的。我們需要立即停在最近的加油站加油。","word":"petrol"}},"phenomenon":{"createdAt":1781449588288,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"phenomenon作為名詞表示「現象、特殊的或不尋常的事件」，其複數形式為phenomena。","options":["improve","glorify","phenomenon","regulate"],"sentence":"The northern lights are a spectacular natural ______ that occurs when solar particles interact with Earth's atmosphere. Scientists have studied this occurrence extensively to understand the physics behind the stunning colored displays in the sky.","translation":"北極光是一種壯觀的自然現象，當太陽粒子與地球大氣相互作用時就會發生。科學家們已經廣泛研究了這種現象，以了解天空中令人驚嘆的彩色顯示背後的物理學原理。","word":"phenomenon"}},"philosopher":{"createdAt":1781693293272,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"philosopher 是名詞，意思是「哲學家」，指從事哲學研究和思考的人。","options":["crush","executive","philosopher","plant"],"sentence":"Socrates was a renowned Greek ______ who spent his life questioning conventional wisdom. His ideas about virtue and knowledge continue to influence Western thought.","translation":"蘇格拉底是著名的希臘哲學家，他用一生時間質疑傳統智慧。他關於美德和知識的思想持續影響西方思想。","word":"philosopher"}},"philosophical":{"createdAt":1781715397124,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"philosophical 意為「哲學的、哲學相關的」，涉及抽象的思辨和對根本性問題的探討。","options":["scientific","philosophical","historical","mathematical"],"sentence":"The professor engaged her students in a ______ discussion about the nature of consciousness and free will. The students debated abstract concepts rather than focusing on practical applications.","translation":"教授與學生進行了一場哲學性的討論，涉及意識和自由意志的本質。學生們辯論的是抽象概念而非實際應用。","word":"philosophical"}},"philosophy":{"createdAt":1781961517453,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"philosophy 指的是人對生活和價值的系統化思考和信念，而不僅是單一的意見或態度。","options":["strategy","philosophy","opinion","attitude"],"sentence":"His personal ______ emphasizes the importance of hard work and perseverance in achieving success. This belief system guides all his major life decisions and values.","translation":"他個人的人生觀強調勤奮工作和堅持不懈在成功中的重要性。這個信念體系指導他所有的重大人生決定和價值觀。","word":"philosophy"}},"photography":{"createdAt":1781310338175,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"photography 是指用相機捕捉和創作影像的藝術和技術。","options":["painting","poetry","photography","sculpture"],"sentence":"She decided to pursue a career in ______ after winning several awards for her landscape images. Her portfolio of stunning nature photographs has been featured in multiple international exhibitions.","translation":"在因風景照片獲得多個獎項後，她決定從事攝影事業。她令人驚嘆的自然照片作品集已在多個國際展覽中展出。","word":"photography"}},"physician":{"createdAt":1781836375366,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"physician是內科醫生，主要治療內科疾病，而不是牙科、外科或心理治療。","options":["dentist","surgeon","physician","therapist"],"sentence":"When Sarah developed a persistent cough, she made an appointment with her ______. The doctor specialised in treating lung and heart conditions.","translation":"當莎拉出現持續咳嗽時，她預約了醫生。這位醫生專門治療肺部和心臟疾病。","word":"physician"}},"physicist":{"createdAt":1781884659833,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"physicist 是指研究物理學、物質和能量等現象的科學家，與相對論理論最相關。","options":["mathematician","physicist","chemist","astronomer"],"sentence":"Albert Einstein was a renowned ______ who revolutionized our understanding of gravity and motion. His theories of relativity changed the course of science forever.","translation":"愛因斯坦是一位著名的物理學家，他革新了我們對重力和運動的理解。他的相對論理論永遠改變了科學的進程。","word":"physicist"}},"physics":{"createdAt":1781651261375,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"physics是研究物質、能量和力的自然科學學科，涉及對物體運動和相互作用的研究。","options":["treasury","midst","rod","physics"],"sentence":"She excelled in her ______ class and won first place in the science competition. Her understanding of motion, force, and energy helped her solve complex problems about how objects move and interact.","translation":"她在物理課中表現出色，並在科學競賽中獲得第一名。她對運動、力和能量的理解幫助她解決了有關物體如何運動和相互作用的複雜問題。","word":"physics"}},"pickpocket":{"createdAt":1781532967167,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pickpocket 指扒手，與「在人群中巧妙地偷取」的描述相符。","options":["vendor","pickpocket","beggar","performer"],"sentence":"The ______ stole the man's wallet without him even noticing during the crowded festival. The thief had expertly removed it from his back pocket.","translation":"在擁擠的節日期間，______(扒手)在那個人沒有注意到的情況下偷了他的錢包。小偷巧妙地從他的後口袋裡取出了它。","word":"pickpocket"}},"pickup":{"createdAt":1781749177490,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pickup 在此指接某人的動作或時間安排，通常用於接載乘客或物品。","options":["dropoff","collection","meeting","delivery"],"sentence":"I arranged a ______ time of 3 PM outside the shopping mall entrance. Make sure you bring your luggage to the designated meeting spot.","translation":"我安排在下午3點在購物中心入口進行接人時間。確保將你的行李帶到指定的會面地點。","word":"pickup"}},"pilotage":{"createdAt":1781507137217,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pilotage 指的是領航人員引導船隻通過困難或危險的水域的行為，特別是在狹窄或複雜的航道上。","options":["cargo","pilotage","insurance","maintenance"],"sentence":"The large cargo ship required ______ to safely navigate through the narrow strait. An experienced local guide boarded the vessel to direct it through the treacherous waters.","translation":"這艘大型貨船需要領航才能安全通過狹窄的海峽。一位經驗豐富的當地嚮導登上該船，引導它通過危險的水域。","word":"pilotage"}},"pioneer":{"createdAt":1781582278975,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pioneer指的是在某個領域中最早開創或開拓的人，特別是指那些進入未知領域並為後來者鋪路的人物。","options":["critic","pioneer","follower","investor"],"sentence":"Steve Jobs was a ______ in the technology industry, introducing revolutionary products that changed how people work and communicate. His innovations came decades before competitors caught up, making him a true first-mover.","translation":"史蒂夫·賈伯斯是科技產業的開拓者，推出了革命性的產品改變了人們的工作和溝通方式。他的創新比競爭對手早了幾十年，使他成為真正的先行者。","word":"pioneer"}},"pitiful":{"createdAt":1781873027350,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pitiful 形容某事物令人感到同情或憐憫，通常因為其情況很糟糕或令人遺憾。","options":["excellent","pitiful","normal","healthy"],"sentence":"The stray dog's ______ condition, with ribs showing through its matted fur, broke everyone's heart. Donations poured in immediately after the rescue shelter posted photos of the animal.","translation":"那隻流浪狗可憫的狀況——肋骨從糾結的毛髮中露出來，讓所有人心碎。救援庇護所發佈了這隻動物的照片後，捐款立即湧入。","word":"pitiful"}},"pity":{"createdAt":1781625891342,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"pity在此指令人感到遺憾或失望的事情","options":["joy","blessing","pity","privilege"],"sentence":"It's such a ______ that you can't attend the concert tonight. I know you've been looking forward to it for months.","translation":"你今晚無法參加音樂會真是太遺憾了。我知道你已經期待它好幾個月了。","word":"pity"}},"plague":{"createdAt":1781598671058,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"plague 作名詞表示瘟疫或大災難，通常指造成大規模死亡或破壞的傳染病或災難","options":["blessing","plague","celebration","monument"],"sentence":"The ______ of locusts destroyed the entire harvest in the region. Medieval people believed that such disasters were divine punishments for their sins.","translation":"該地區的蝗蟲瘟疫摧毀了整個收成。中世紀的人們認為這樣的災難是上帝對他們罪惡的懲罰。","word":"plague"}},"planet":{"createdAt":1781961517451,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"planet 指的是繞恆星公轉的大型天體，而不是恆星、小行星或彗星。","options":["star","planet","asteroid","comet"],"sentence":"Scientists discovered a new ______ orbiting a distant star system. This celestial body has the right atmospheric conditions to potentially support life.","translation":"科學家們發現了一顆圍繞遠方星系運行的新行星。這個天體具有可能支持生命的正確大氣條件。","word":"planet"}},"plant":{"createdAt":1781693293271,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"plant 作名詞可表示「工廠」或「製造設施」，與生產和工業活動相關。","options":["philosopher","ruthless","priceless","plant"],"sentence":"The manufacturing ______ in the industrial zone produces thousands of units daily. Workers operate heavy machinery on the factory floor around the clock.","translation":"工業區的製造工廠每天生產數千件產品。工人們在工廠樓層全天候操作重型機械。","word":"plant"}},"plantation":{"createdAt":1781840659328,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"plantation 是指大規模的農業莊園，專門種植某一種商業作物。","options":["city","plantation","forest","village"],"sentence":"The vast ______ stretched across hundreds of acres of fertile land in the Caribbean. Rows of sugarcane grew under the tropical sun, harvested by workers year-round.","translation":"這片遼闊的大農場在加勒比地區佔據了數百英畝的肥沃土地。排成一列的甘蔗在熱帶陽光下生長，全年由工人收割。","word":"plantation"}},"plastic":{"createdAt":1781926370999,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"plastic 作為形容詞意思是塑膠的，指由塑膠材料製成的物品，該材料難以分解。","options":["paper","glass","plastic","metal"],"sentence":"The ______ bag dissolved in the ocean, harming marine life and contributing to environmental pollution. Marine scientists found pieces of it in the stomachs of fish and sea turtles.","translation":"塑膠袋在海洋中溶解，傷害了海洋生物並造成環保污染。海洋科學家在魚類和海龜的胃裡發現了它的碎片。","word":"plastic"}},"platform":{"createdAt":1781871338558,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"platform在此指提供發表言論或傳播信息的場所或媒介。","options":["strategy","stage","foundation","medium"],"sentence":"The political candidate used the social media ______ to share her ideas with millions of supporters. She posted three times daily to maintain engagement with her followers.","translation":"這位政治候選人利用社交媒體平臺與數百萬支持者分享她的想法。她每天發佈三次以保持與追隨者的互動。","word":"platform"}},"plea":{"createdAt":1781359980244,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"plea是指向權威人士提出的懇求或請求；在法律語境中指被告就罪名所作的供述或認罪。","options":["objection","declaration","plea","verdict"],"sentence":"The defendant made a desperate ______ for mercy before the judge announced the sentence. His lawyer begged the court to consider his difficult family situation.","translation":"被告在法官宣佈判決前對法官提出了絕望的懇求。他的律師懇求法庭考慮他困難的家庭狀況。","word":"plea"}},"pneumonia":{"createdAt":1781933311795,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pneumonia（肺炎）是影響肺部的呼吸道感染，而arthritis（關節炎）、diabetes（糖尿病）和amnesia（遺忘症）都是不同類型的疾病，不會影響肺部。","options":["arthritis","pneumonia","diabetes","amnesia"],"sentence":"The elderly patient was admitted to the hospital with a severe case of ______ that affected both lungs. The doctor prescribed antibiotics and oxygen therapy to help him recover from this respiratory infection.","translation":"這位年長患者因嚴重的肺炎入院治療，影響了兩個肺。醫生開了抗生素和氧氣療法來幫助他從這種呼吸道感染中恢復。","word":"pneumonia"}},"point":{"createdAt":1781580511758,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"point 在運動中指得分，代表比賽中計算的單位","options":["player","coach","point","strategy"],"sentence":"The team scored the winning ______ in the final seconds of the game. This single score gave them the victory they had worked so hard for.","translation":"球隊在比賽最後幾秒鐘獲得了獲勝的得分。這一分給了他們辛苦爭取的勝利。","word":"point"}},"poisonous":{"createdAt":1781336858138,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"poisonous 用來形容某物含有毒素，會對生命造成威脅或傷害。","options":["beautiful","poisonous","harmless","colorful"],"sentence":"The snake's venom is ______, so hikers must avoid contact with it. Even a small bite from this creature can cause death within hours.","translation":"這條蛇的毒液是有毒的，所以登山者必須避免與它接觸。即使被這種生物輕輕咬一口，也可能在幾小時內導致死亡。","word":"poisonous"}},"polar":{"createdAt":1781693254771,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"polar形容詞指與地球南北極有關的地區，特別是非常寒冷和冰凍的地方。","options":["tropical","urban","polar","coastal"],"sentence":"Scientists conducted extensive research in the ______ regions to study climate change and its effects on ice. Teams traveled to the Arctic and Antarctic to collect data about melting glaciers.","translation":"科學家在極地地區進行了廣泛的研究，以研究氣候變遷及其對冰的影響。團隊前往北極和南極收集關於冰川融化的數據。","word":"polar"}},"polished":{"createdAt":1781784029103,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"refined（精緻的、老練的）形容一個人的表現或風格，表示經過充分準備和專業訓練。","options":["rough","smooth","refined","unfinished"],"sentence":"Her ______ presentation impressed all the judges at the competition. She had rehearsed every word and gesture with precision, showing no nervousness or hesitation.","translation":"她精緻的演講給比賽中的所有評委留下了深刻印象。她對每一個字詞和姿態都進行了精確排練，沒有表現出任何緊張或猶豫。","word":"polished"}},"politics":{"createdAt":1781841148117,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"politics 名詞意思是政治、政治活動，指與政府、權力和公共事務管理相關的活動和討論。","options":["sports","cooking","politics","music"],"sentence":"Many university students became passionate about ______ after attending debates about election campaigns and policy reforms. They spent hours discussing how government decisions affected society and joined student political organizations.","translation":"許多大學生在參加關於選舉活動和政策改革的辯論後對政治充滿熱情。他們花了幾個小時討論政府決策如何影響社會，並加入了學生政治組織。","word":"politics"}},"pollutant":{"createdAt":1781603436398,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"pollutant是指污染環境、危害生態或人體健康的物質，通常來自工業排放或廢棄物。","options":["nutrient","resource","pollutant","product"],"sentence":"The factory's emissions released a dangerous ______ into the atmosphere that affected the air quality for miles around. Scientists identified the harmful substance as nitrogen dioxide, a chemical that damages human respiratory systems.","translation":"工廠的排放物向大氣中釋放了一種危險的污染物，影響了方圓數英里的空氣品質。科學家將這種有害物質確定為二氧化氮，這是一種會損害人體呼吸系統的化學物質。","word":"pollutant"}},"polluted":{"createdAt":1781832089958,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"polluted 表示被污染的，指環境、空氣、水等被有害物質汙染","options":["purified","polluted","clear","refreshing"],"sentence":"The river became increasingly ______ due to industrial waste dumping upstream. Fish and aquatic plants began to die as the water quality deteriorated significantly.","translation":"由於上游工業廢物傾倒，河流變得越來越污染。隨著水質明顯惡化，魚類和水生植物開始死亡。","word":"polluted"}},"pollution":{"createdAt":1781841505535,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"pollution 指的是環境中的污染物質或污染現象，會對生態和人類健康造成負面影響。","options":["entitle","healthcare","pollution","wonder"],"sentence":"The ______ in our city's air has reached dangerous levels this week due to factory emissions. Parents are keeping their children indoors because breathing the contaminated atmosphere poses serious health risks.","translation":"由於工廠排放，我們城市空氣中的污染本週已達到危險水平。父母們讓孩子待在室內，因為呼吸被污染的空氣會造成嚴重的健康風險。","word":"pollution"}},"ponder":{"createdAt":1781424157171,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"ponder 意為深思熟慮、仔細考慮某事，特別是指重大決定。","options":["ignore","dismiss","ponder","announce"],"sentence":"She sat quietly in the garden for hours to ______ the important decision about her future career. Finally, after deep reflection, she decided to pursue medicine.","translation":"她在花園裡靜靜地坐了幾個小時來沉思這個關於她未來職業的重要決定。經過深思熟慮後，她最終決定從醫。","word":"ponder"}},"popularity":{"createdAt":1781693266948,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"popularity指某人或某物受歡迎的程度，即人氣、流行度。","options":["popularity","confidence","anxiety","confusion"],"sentence":"The singer's ______ grew dramatically after her hit single was released. Fans from all over the world were listening to her music and buying concert tickets.","translation":"這位歌手的人氣在她的熱門單曲發行後急劇增長。來自世界各地的粉絲都在聽她的音樂並購買演唱會門票。","word":"popularity"}},"populated":{"createdAt":1781950727562,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"populated 指住有人口或居住著許多人的地方。","options":["decorated","populated","isolated","destroyed"],"sentence":"The downtown area is densely ______ with office buildings and shops. Thousands of people live and work there every single day.","translation":"市中心區域密集居住著辦公樓和商店。每天都有數千人在那裡生活和工作。","word":"populated"}},"porch":{"createdAt":1781481072318,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"porch 表示建築物入口處的走廊或門廊，通常在房屋外部供人休息和活動。","options":["basement","attic","porch","kitchen"],"sentence":"We sat on the ______ of the farmhouse, enjoying the cool evening breeze. The wooden chairs were arranged perfectly for viewing the sunset over the fields.","translation":"我們坐在農舍的走廊上，享受涼爽的傍晚微風。木製椅子完美地排列著，方便欣賞田野上的日落。","word":"porch"}},"portrait":{"createdAt":1781738105693,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"portrait 指的是對某人臉部或全身的繪畫、素描或攝影，通常用於表現一個人的樣子。","options":["landscape","portrait","sculpture","mural"],"sentence":"The famous painter spent three months creating a detailed ______ of the historical figure. The artwork captured not only his physical appearance but also the wisdom reflected in his eyes.","translation":"這位著名畫家花了三個月創作了這位歷史人物的詳細肖像畫。這件藝術作品不僅捕捉了他的外表，還反映了他眼中的智慧。","word":"portrait"}},"position":{"createdAt":1781345746903,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"position 作名詞，在此指職務或職位，表示在機構中的工作角色。","options":["location","position","movement","direction"],"sentence":"She was offered a senior management ______ at the international corporation. She accepted the job offer and will start work next month as the new director.","translation":"她獲得了國際公司高級管理職位的聘請。她接受了工作邀請，將於下個月作為新任總監開始工作。","word":"position"}},"possess":{"createdAt":1781402154558,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"possess表示擁有或持有某物，在這裡指律師必須持有法律執業執照。","options":["possess","lack","compel","hijack"],"sentence":"To practice law in this country, a lawyer must ______ a valid license issued by the bar association. Without this credential, it is illegal to provide legal services to clients.","translation":"在這個國家執業律師必須擁有律師協會頒發的有效執照。沒有這個證書，向客戶提供法律服務是違法的。","word":"possess"}},"postpone":{"createdAt":1781950727567,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"postpone 指延遲或推遲某事件的日期或時間。","options":["expedite","postpone","announce","cancel"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ the product launch until next quarter. They needed more time to conduct thorough market research and testing.","translation":"公司決定將產品發佈推遲到下個季度。他們需要更多時間進行全面的市場研究和測試。","word":"postpone"}},"potent":{"createdAt":1781619188931,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"potent 指強大、有力或有效力的，特別是指藥物或物質的功效。","options":["weak","potent","mild","gentle"],"sentence":"The medicine proved to be a ______ treatment for the patient's condition. Just a small dose was enough to produce significant improvement within hours.","translation":"這種藥物被證明是治療患者病症的強有力的治療方法。僅僅一小劑量就足以在幾小時內產生顯著的改善。","word":"potent"}},"poultry":{"createdAt":1781950727559,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"poultry 指家禽，特別是為了食物而飼養的雞、鴨、鵝等家禽。","options":["vegetables","cattle","poultry","fish"],"sentence":"The farm raises ______ such as chickens and ducks for their eggs and meat. These birds are kept in dedicated enclosures on the property.","translation":"農場飼養家禽，如雞和鴨，以獲取它們的蛋和肉。這些鳥類在該地產上的專用圍欄中飼養。","word":"poultry"}},"pour":{"createdAt":1781564440920,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pour 作動詞表示倒、灌，指將液體從一個容器流向另一個容器。","options":["sip","pour","freeze","collect"],"sentence":"She decided to ______ the hot water into the teapot. The steam rose up as the boiling liquid flowed inside.","translation":"她決定把熱水倒入茶壺。滾燙的液體流入時蒸氣上升。","word":"pour"}},"poverty":{"createdAt":1781709854477,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"poverty（貧窮）指缺乏金錢或資源的狀態，與struggle to afford basic necessities（難以負擔基本必需品）形成因果關係。","options":["wealth","poverty","abundance","prosperity"],"sentence":"Many families in rural areas live in ______ and struggle to afford basic necessities. The government launched a program to provide food and shelter to those without sufficient income.","translation":"許多農村地區的家庭生活在貧窮中，難以負擔基本生活必需品。政府啟動了一項計劃，為收入不足的人提供食物和住所。","word":"poverty"}},"practitioner":{"createdAt":1781478568770,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"practitioner 指在某一專業領域中執業或從事該行業工作的人。","options":["student","patient","practitioner","researcher"],"sentence":"A skilled medical ______ must complete years of education and licensing before treating patients. Dr. Chen has been practicing medicine for over twenty years.","translation":"一名技術熟練的醫療從業人員必須在治療患者之前完成多年的教育和執業執照。陳醫生已經執業二十多年了。","word":"practitioner"}},"praise":{"createdAt":1781871338568,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"praise表示對他人優點或成就的讚美和認可，與正面評論相關。","options":["criticism","compliments","feedback","accusations"],"sentence":"The student received ______ from all her teachers for her exceptional academic performance this semester. They highlighted her dedication, intelligence, and kindness in their comments.","translation":"這名學生因本學期的傑出學業表現而獲得所有老師的讚美。他們在評論中強調了她的奉獻精神、聰慧和善良。","word":"praise"}},"precise":{"createdAt":1781746848186,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"precise 表示「精確的」或「準確的」，指數據或資訊非常準確和詳細。","options":["approximate","vague","precise","rough"],"sentence":"The engineer provided ______ measurements for the construction project. Every dimension was accurate to within one millimeter.","translation":"工程師為建築專案提供了精確的測量。每個尺寸都精確到毫米以內。","word":"precise"}},"precisely":{"createdAt":1781624534652,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"precisely 意為「精確地、確切地」，強調準確無誤的程度。","options":["vaguely","carefully","precisely","quickly"],"sentence":"The scientist measured the chemical compound ______ to ensure the experiment's accuracy. Even a difference of 0.001 grams could affect the final results.","translation":"科學家精確地測量了化學化合物以確保實驗的準確性。即使相差0.001克也會影響最終結果。","word":"precisely"}},"predecessor":{"createdAt":1781738105689,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"predecessor 指的是某人之前擔任過的職位上的人，或是先前存在的版本或事物。","options":["successor","predecessor","subordinate","colleague"],"sentence":"The new manager was eager to learn from her ______ about the company's operational procedures. Her previous supervisor had worked at the firm for fifteen years before retiring last month.","translation":"新經理渴望從她的前任那裡了解公司的運營程序。她的前一位主管在上月退休前在公司工作了十五年。","word":"predecessor"}},"prediction":{"createdAt":1781401591593,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"prediction 是指基於現有信息對未來事件的預測或預言。","options":["observation","memory","prediction","description"],"sentence":"The weather forecaster made a ______ that it would rain heavily next Tuesday. Meteorologists use computer models and historical data to make such forecasts.","translation":"氣象預報員預測下週二會下大雨。氣象學家使用電腦模型和歷史數據來進行這樣的預測。","word":"prediction"}},"prefer":{"createdAt":1781437528476,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"prefer 表示較喜歡或寧願選擇某一個選項勝過另一個，常用來比較兩個事物的偏好。","options":["prefer","require","attend","schedule"],"sentence":"Most students ______ online classes over in-person lectures because they offer more flexibility. They can attend sessions at their own pace and rewatch difficult material as many times as needed.","translation":"大多數學生寧願選擇網上課程而不是面對面講座，因為它們提供了更多的靈活性。他們可以按照自己的進度參加課程，並根據需要多次重新觀看困難的內容。","word":"prefer"}},"prejudiced":{"createdAt":1781839703150,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"prejudiced指對他人有成見或偏見的，與comments showing bias about ethnicity（關於種族的帶有偏見的評論）完全相符。","options":["fair","impartial","prejudiced","objective"],"sentence":"The judge was deemed ______ and removed from the case. His comments about the defendant's ethnicity made his bias obvious to everyone.","translation":"該法官因為有偏見而被判定應該退出此案。他對被告種族的評論使他的偏見對每個人都顯而易見。","word":"prejudiced"}},"preliminary":{"createdAt":1781839703153,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"preliminary指初步的、未最終確定的，與更多comprehensive testing is needed to confirm（需要更多全面測試來確認）的語境完全相符。","options":["final","conclusive","preliminary","definitive"],"sentence":"The ______ results of the medical test suggest a potential issue. However, more comprehensive testing will be needed to confirm the diagnosis.","translation":"醫療測試的初步結果表明有潛在問題。但是需要更全面的測試來確認診斷。","word":"preliminary"}},"premature":{"createdAt":1781256444515,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"premature指過早或倉促的，暗示應該等待更多資訊才下決定。","options":["careful","premature","detailed","thorough"],"sentence":"The doctor advised against ______ conclusions about the patient's condition based on initial symptoms. More comprehensive tests would be needed before making any definitive diagnosis.","translation":"醫生建議不要根據初期症狀對患者的病情做出倉促的結論。需要進行更全面的測試才能做出明確診斷。","word":"premature"}},"premiere":{"createdAt":1781401361936,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"premiere指電影、戲劇等作品的首次公開展演或首映式，通常是一個重大的文化事件。","options":["sequel","premiere","release","screening"],"sentence":"The new Marvel movie had its ______ at the Cannes Film Festival last night. Thousands of fans gathered outside the theatre to see the actors walk the red carpet for the first public showing.","translation":"新的漫威電影昨晚在坎城影展舉行了首映。數千名粉絲聚集在劇院外，為第一場公開放映時看到演員走紅毯。","word":"premiere"}},"prescribe":{"createdAt":1781747309098,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"prescribe 是醫學術語，特指醫生正式開藥方，患者可以在藥房領取該藥物。","options":["recommend","prescribe","discuss","suggest"],"sentence":"The doctor decided to ______ antibiotics for the patient's bacterial infection. After writing the medication on a form, the patient took it to the pharmacy to fill.","translation":"醫生決定為患者的細菌感染開抗生素。醫生在表格上寫下藥物後，患者拿著處方箋到藥房配藥。","word":"prescribe"}},"prescription":{"createdAt":1781401591591,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"prescription 是指醫生開給患者的藥方或處方籤，用於在藥局購買特定藥物。","options":["diagnosis","prescription","symptom","treatment"],"sentence":"The doctor wrote a ______ for antibiotics after examining my throat infection. I took this document to the pharmacy to obtain my medication.","translation":"醫生檢查完我的喉嚨感染後，開了一張抗生素的處方籤。我拿著這份文件到藥局去拿藥。","word":"prescription"}},"presence":{"createdAt":1781837419086,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"Presence指的是一個人的存在所帶來的影響力和氣場，能夠吸引他人的注意。","options":["absence","voice","presence","smile"],"sentence":"Her calm ______ immediately put everyone at ease when she entered the room. The way she commanded attention without speaking demonstrated her powerful impact.","translation":"當她進入房間時，她的沉著讓所有人立即感到放心。她無需言語就能吸引注意力的方式展示了她強大的影響力。","word":"presence"}},"preservation":{"createdAt":1781951900949,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"preservation指維持某物的原有狀態並防止其損壞，強調的是保持而非修復或展示。","options":["destruction","restoration","preservation","exhibition"],"sentence":"The museum focuses on the ______ of ancient artifacts by keeping them in climate-controlled rooms. Without these careful protective measures, these priceless objects would crumble to dust.","translation":"博物館專注於在氣候控制的房間裡保存古代文物。如果沒有這些仔細的保護措施，這些無價之寶會化為塵埃。","word":"preservation"}},"preservative":{"createdAt":1781839950962,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"preservative 是指添加到食品中以防止腐敗並延長保存期的物質。","options":["flavoring","preservative","coloring","sweetener"],"sentence":"The food manufacturer added a ______ to extend the shelf life of the bread. Without this chemical substance, the product would spoil within just a few days.","translation":"食品製造商添加了防腐劑以延長麵包的保存期。沒有這種化學物質,產品幾天內就會變質。","word":"preservative"}},"preserve":{"createdAt":1781950727566,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"preserve 指保護或維持某物的原始狀態，防止其被破壞或消失。","options":["destroy","preserve","populate","relocate"],"sentence":"The government created a wildlife ______ to ______ the endangered species from extinction. The protected area ensures these animals can live safely without hunting interference.","translation":"政府設立了一個野生動物保護區來保護瀕危物種免於滅絕。受保護的區域確保這些動物可以安全生活，不受捕獵干擾。","word":"preserve"}},"president":{"createdAt":1781831347631,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"president 可以表示國家的總統，也可以表示大學、公司等組織的校長或總裁。","options":["janitor","president","groundskeeper","security guard"],"sentence":"The ______ of Harvard University announced new scholarship programs during the graduation ceremony. This leader oversees all academic and administrative operations across the institution's numerous colleges and schools.","translation":"哈佛大學的校長在畢業典禮上宣布了新的獎學金計畫。這位領導者監督該機構眾多學院和學校的所有學術和行政運作。","word":"president"}},"presidential":{"createdAt":1781311983485,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"presidential 指與總統或總統職位相關的，通常用來描述選舉或權力。","options":["expressive","presidential","offshore","syndrome"],"sentence":"The ______ election drew record numbers of voters to the polls across the nation. Citizens were eager to choose the next head of state and determine the direction of the country.","translation":"總統選舉在全國各地吸引了創紀錄人數的選民投票。公民渴望選擇下一任國家首腦並決定國家的方向。","word":"presidential"}},"press":{"createdAt":1781434900598,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"press指新聞媒體和出版界，特別是報紙、雜誌和新聞機構。","options":["judicial","press","religious","medical"],"sentence":"The ______ coverage of the scandal damaged the politician's reputation significantly. Newspapers and television networks reported extensively on the unfolding investigation.","translation":"新聞界對醜聞的報導大大損害了該政治家的聲譽。報紙和電視網絡廣泛報導了持續進行的調查。","word":"press"}},"pressure":{"createdAt":1781582251997,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"pressure 是名詞，表示來自外界環境、工作或期望所造成的心理或物理壓力。","options":["relief","freedom","pressure","excitement"],"sentence":"The student felt intense ______ as the exam date approached and deadlines piled up. Multiple assignments and upcoming tests created an overwhelming sense of stress.","translation":"隨著考試日期臨近和截止日期堆積，那位學生感受到強烈的壓力。多項作業和即將到來的考試造成了壓倒性的壓力感。","word":"pressure"}},"prestigious":{"createdAt":1781565657691,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"prestigious 形容詞表示享有高聲望和廣泛認可的地位，通常與教育機構、公司或組織相關。","options":["unknown","prestigious","affordable","recently-founded"],"sentence":"She earned her degree from a ______ university that is recognized worldwide for excellence. Employers actively seek graduates from this institution because of its outstanding reputation.","translation":"她從一所享有盛譽且在世界各地因卓越而聞名的大學獲得學位。雇主積極尋求該機構的畢業生，因為它有傑出的聲譽。","word":"prestigious"}},"pretentious":{"createdAt":1781582278976,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"pretentious形容試圖表現得比實際更高雅、更重要或更複雜的人或事物，通常帶有虛偽和自大的意味。","options":["affordable","traditional","pretentious","modest"],"sentence":"The restaurant's ______ menu featured dishes with unnecessarily complicated French names for simple preparations. Yet when the food arrived, diners were disappointed to discover it was ordinary cuisine presented with artificial flair.","translation":"這家餐廳自命不凡的菜單上，簡單的菜式被冠以複雜的法文名稱。然而當食物端上來時，食客失望地發現這只是用人為浮華包裝的平凡料理。","word":"pretentious"}},"prevail":{"createdAt":1781841742850,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"prevail 作動詞表示「佔優勢、盛行」，指某種思想、趨勢或情況廣泛流行並占上風。","options":["diminish","prevail","disappear","weaken"],"sentence":"Despite the opposition from traditionalists, modern values ______ throughout the younger generation. New ideas about work-life balance became the cultural norm.","translation":"儘管傳統主義者的反對，現代價值觀在年輕一代中佔據上風。關於工作與生活平衡的新想法成為了文化規範。","word":"prevail"}},"preventive":{"createdAt":1782007196628,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「預防的」用來形容在問題發生前採取的行動或政策，強調預先防止而非事後補救。","options":["curative","preventive","reactive","expensive"],"sentence":"Taking ______ measures early can save you from serious health problems later. Doctors often recommend vaccines and regular exercise as ways to stop diseases before they start.","translation":"及早採取預防措施可以讓您免於日後嚴重的健康問題。醫生通常建議接種疫苗和定期運動是在疾病開始前阻止疾病的方式。","word":"preventive"}},"previous":{"createdAt":1781746848180,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"previous 表示「以前的」或「先前的」，指過去發生過的事情。","options":["current","previous","future","ideal"],"sentence":"In her ______ job, she worked as a software engineer for five years. Now she has transitioned to become a project manager.","translation":"在她以前的工作中，她做了五年的軟體工程師。現在她轉變成了專案經理。","word":"previous"}},"prey":{"createdAt":1781951900948,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"prey指被捕食者捕獵的動物，在掠食者和被捕食者的關係中具體指被追捕的對象。","options":["enemy","prey","target","victim"],"sentence":"The eagle spotted a rabbit as its ______ and dove down from the sky to catch it. The smaller animal had no chance of escaping this powerful predator.","translation":"鷹發現一隻兔子是它的獵物，從空中俯衝而下去抓住它。這隻較小的動物無法逃脫這隻強大捕食者的追捕。","word":"prey"}},"priceless":{"createdAt":1781693293271,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"priceless 是形容詞，意思是「無價的」或「極為珍貴的」，無法用金錢衡量其價值。","options":["ruthless","priceless","executive","crush"],"sentence":"The ancient painting discovered in the museum vault is absolutely ______. Experts estimate its historical and artistic value to be beyond any monetary calculation.","translation":"在博物館金庫中發現的古代畫作絕對是無價的。專家認為其歷史和藝術價值超過任何金錢計算。","word":"priceless"}},"prime":{"createdAt":1781496369387,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"prime在此作動詞使用，表示「事先給某人提供情況，使有所準備」，強調提前告知和準備。","options":["dismiss","prime","ignore","confuse"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ its employees with detailed information before the major product launch. The briefing session ensured everyone understood their roles and responsibilities for the announcement.","translation":"公司決定在重大產品發佈前向員工提供詳細信息，做好準備。簡報會議確保每個人都了解自己在公佈會上的角色和責任。","word":"prime"}},"primitive":{"createdAt":1781774456605,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"primitive 形容早期人類或未經高度發展的文明，處於遠古或未開化的階段。","options":["modern","advanced","ancient","civilized"],"sentence":"The ______ tribe lived in caves and hunted animals for survival. Archaeological evidence showed they had minimal contact with other civilizations.","translation":"原始部落住在山洞中並靠獵捕動物維生。考古證據表明他們與其他文明接觸甚少。","word":"primitive"}},"primitives":{"createdAt":1781926370999,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"primitives 意思是原始人、未開化的人，指人類早期的祖先或文化發展水平較低的人群。","options":["modernists","scholars","primitives","inventors"],"sentence":"The anthropologist studied ______ from ancient civilizations by examining their tools and artwork. These early people had developed surprisingly sophisticated techniques despite lacking modern technology.","translation":"人類學家通過檢查他們的工具和藝術作品來研究古代文明的原始人。儘管缺乏現代技術，這些早期的人已經發展出令人驚訝地複雜的技術。","word":"primitives"}},"private":{"createdAt":1781479123532,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"private 指的是私人的、不對外公開的，與公眾無關的事務。","options":["public","casual","private","formal"],"sentence":"The CEO held a ______ meeting with the board of directors in a closed conference room. No journalists or employees were invited to attend this confidential discussion about the company's future strategy.","translation":"執行長在一間密閉的會議室裡與董事會進行私人會議。沒有記者或員工被邀請參加這次關於公司未來策略的機密討論。","word":"private"}},"procedure":{"createdAt":1781961506841,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"procedure指一系列有順序的步驟或規定步驟，通常用於正式的流程和手續。","options":["celebration","procedure","accident","decoration"],"sentence":"To apply for a passport, you must follow the government ______ carefully and complete each step in order. The official checklist outlines exactly which documents to submit first, then which agency to visit next.","translation":"申請護照時，你必須仔細遵循政府______，並依序完成每個步驟。官方檢查清單列出了確切要先提交哪些文件，然後再去哪個機構。","word":"procedure"}},"productive":{"createdAt":1781939439465,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"productive是形容詞，表示多產的、高效的、富有成果的，形容能夠產生大量成果或結果。","options":["idle","slow","productive","incomplete"],"sentence":"The research team had a very ______ year, publishing multiple studies and making significant discoveries. Their laboratory output exceeded all previous records and contributed greatly to the field.","translation":"研究團隊度過了非常多產的一年，發表了多項研究並取得了重大發現。他們實驗室的產出超過了所有以往的紀錄，對該領域的貢獻很大。","word":"productive"}},"profession":{"createdAt":1781840667145,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"profession指的是需要專業訓練和知識的職業或行業。","options":["hobby","skill","profession","passion"],"sentence":"After graduating from medical school, she entered the ______ of dentistry. She spent years training to specialize in oral health care.","translation":"從醫學院畢業後，她進入了牙科專業。她花了多年時間培訓以專精於口腔保健。","word":"profession"}},"professional":{"createdAt":1781582939254,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"professional 形容具有專業知識、技能和經驗的人或工作，與長期培訓和獲得業界認可的背景相符。","options":["amateur","young","professional","expensive"],"sentence":"The ______ photographer used high-end cameras and lighting equipment to capture the wedding photos. She had spent fifteen years studying her craft and had won multiple industry awards for her work.","translation":"這位專業攝影師使用高端相機和照明設備來拍攝婚禮照片。她花了十五年研究她的技藝，並因她的工作獲得了多個行業獎項。","word":"professional"}},"profile":{"createdAt":1781774456605,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"profile 指對人物的簡介或傳略，介紹其重要背景和特點。","options":["photograph","advertisement","biography","review"],"sentence":"The magazine published a detailed ______ of the successful entrepreneur. The article covered her background, achievements, and personal life.","translation":"該雜誌發表了對成功企業家的詳細人物簡介。文章涵蓋了她的背景、成就和個人生活。","word":"profile"}},"profound":{"createdAt":1781794866353,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"profound指深遠的、深切的，用於形容思想、感受或影響具有深刻的意義和重要性。","options":["shallow","obvious","profound","trivial"],"sentence":"The philosopher's ______ insights into human nature changed how people understood themselves. His ideas continue to influence thinkers and scholars more than a century after his death.","translation":"這位哲學家對人性的______ 洞察改變了人們對自己的理解。他的想法在他去世一個多世紀後仍繼續影響思想家和學者。","word":"profound"}},"progress":{"createdAt":1781848934154,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"progress指在某方面的改善或向前發展的過程","options":["decline","progress","failure","stagnation"],"sentence":"The student's ______ in mathematics has been remarkable this year. Her test scores have improved dramatically, and she now ranks at the top of her class.","translation":"這位學生今年在數學方面的進步非常顯著。她的考試成績大幅提高，現在在班級中排名靠前。","word":"progress"}},"progressive":{"createdAt":1781843396462,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"progressive表示不斷前進和逐步進行的，在此指組織的改變是循序漸進而非突然的。","options":["sudden","dramatic","progressive","radical"],"sentence":"The organization implemented ______ changes to modernize its operations. Each phase of the reform built upon the previous one, gradually transforming the company over five years.","translation":"該組織實施循序漸進的改革以使其業務現代化。改革的每個階段都建立在前一個基礎上，在五年內逐漸改變公司。","word":"progressive"}},"prohibition":{"createdAt":1781839950960,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"prohibition 指的是官方的禁止或禁令,具有法律效力。","options":["permission","suggestion","prohibition","advertisement"],"sentence":"The government enacted a ______ on smoking in public buildings. Violating this law could result in significant fines or penalties.","translation":"政府頒布了在公共建築物內禁止吸煙的禁令。違反這項法律可能導致罰款或處罰。","word":"prohibition"}},"projection":{"createdAt":1781651261360,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"projection在此表示基於分析而做出的預測或推測，常用於天氣、經濟等領域的未來預估。","options":["rod","projection","treasury","physics"],"sentence":"The weather forecast made a ______ that temperatures would drop significantly next week. The meteorologists based their prediction on months of collected data and climate patterns.","translation":"天氣預報做出了下週氣溫會大幅下降的推測。氣象學家根據數月收集的資料和氣候模式來做出這項預測。","word":"projection"}},"projector":{"createdAt":1781582251997,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"projector 是名詞，指的是能夠將影像投射到牆面或螢幕上的設備。","options":["speaker","projector","microphone","printer"],"sentence":"The teacher turned on the ______ to display the lesson slides on the classroom wall. The bright image was clearly visible to all students in the back row.","translation":"老師打開投影機將課程投影片顯示在教室牆上。明亮的影像對後排的所有學生都清晰可見。","word":"projector"}},"promising":{"createdAt":1781362281662,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"promising表示有前途的或大有可為的，預示著未來的成功。","options":["poor","promising","average","disappointing"],"sentence":"The young athlete showed ______ skills during the tournament. Coaches believe she has great potential to become a champion.","translation":"這位年輕運動員在比賽中表現出有前途的技能。教練認為她有成為冠軍的巨大潛力。","word":"promising"}},"promote":{"createdAt":1781775276773,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"promote指晉升或提拔員工到更高的職位，通常伴隨著更多責任和更高的報酬。","options":["demote","fire","promote","transfer"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ Sarah to manager after she demonstrated excellent leadership skills. She will now oversee the entire department and earn a higher salary.","translation":"公司決定提升莎拉為經理，因為她展示了出色的領導能力。她現在將監督整個部門並獲得更高的薪酬。","word":"promote"}},"pronounce":{"createdAt":1781693304925,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pronounce 在此意為正式宣告或宣布某項決定、判決或結論。","options":["hear","pronounce","question","debate"],"sentence":"The judge will ______ the verdict after carefully reviewing all the evidence presented during the trial. The courtroom fell silent as everyone awaited her formal declaration.","translation":"法官在仔細審查審判期間提出的所有證據後，將宣告判決。法庭陷入沉寂，所有人都在等待她的正式宣告。","word":"pronounce"}},"proper":{"createdAt":1781359980249,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"proper指適合、適當或恰當的；強調符合特定情境或標準的要求。","options":["casual","improper","proper","creative"],"sentence":"Using ______ grammar and correct spelling is essential when writing formal business letters. Your employer expects professional communication in all official correspondence.","translation":"寫正式商業信函時，使用適當的語法和正確的拼寫至關重要。你的雇主期望所有官方函件中的溝通都是專業的。","word":"proper"}},"properly":{"createdAt":1781414884517,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"properly表示適當地、恰當地、按照正確方式進行，強調符合要求和規範。","options":["quickly","properly","eagerly","loudly"],"sentence":"The student did not follow the instructions ______, so her essay format was completely incorrect. The teacher had to ask her to rewrite it according to the exact guidelines provided.","translation":"學生沒有適當地遵循說明，所以她的論文格式完全不正確。老師不得不要求她按照提供的確切指南重新撰寫。","word":"properly"}},"prophet":{"createdAt":1782022372247,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"prophet 意為「預言家、先知」，指被認為具有預知未來或傳達神聖訊息能力的人物。","options":["prophet","historian","philosopher","merchant"],"sentence":"In ancient times, people believed a ______ could foresee future events through divine inspiration. The oracle at Delphi was one of the most famous figures consulted for predictions about what would happen in the coming years.","translation":"在古代，人們相信先知可以通過神聖的靈感預見未來事件。德爾菲的神殿祭司是人們最常諮詢的著名人物，用來預測未來幾年將發生的事情。","word":"prophet"}},"proponent":{"createdAt":1781838276307,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"proponent指某個想法或計劃的支持者或倡導者。","options":["ordeal","toll","proponent","volume"],"sentence":"Dr. Chen is a leading ______ of renewable energy in our country. She has spent the last twenty years advocating for solar and wind power initiatives.","translation":"陳博士是我們國家可再生能源的主要支持者。她過去二十年一直在倡導太陽能和風能項目。","word":"proponent"}},"propose":{"createdAt":1781693266948,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"propose在此表示向某人提出結婚的建議，即求婚；也可表示提議或建議。","options":["propose","postpone","promote","provide"],"sentence":"He decided to ______ marriage to his girlfriend on Valentine's Day. He had carefully planned the romantic dinner and prepared a diamond ring.","translation":"他決定在情人節向女友求婚。他仔細計畫了浪漫的晚餐並準備了一枚鑽石戒指。","word":"propose"}},"prosecute":{"createdAt":1781848934146,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"prosecute指以法律手段對被告人進行起訴或檢舉的行為","options":["defend","prosecute","release","pardon"],"sentence":"The district attorney decided to ______ the suspect for armed robbery. The evidence collected at the crime scene was sufficient to bring charges.","translation":"地方檢察官決定起訴該嫌疑人武裝搶劫罪。在犯罪現場收集的證據足以提起訴訟。","word":"prosecute"}},"prospect":{"createdAt":1781515270335,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"prospect 在此作名詞，指探勘或勘探的地點，也可指有潛力開採的礦藏地點。","options":["investment","prospect","bucket","curious"],"sentence":"The geologist spent weeks exploring the remote area as a potential mineral ______. The company hired him specifically to search for deposits of copper and gold underground.","translation":"地質學家花了數週時間探勘一個潛在的礦物前景。該公司聘請他專門在地下尋找銅和金的礦床。","word":"prospect"}},"prosperous":{"createdAt":1781515329259,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"prosperous 形容詞，意思是昌盛的、興旺的，在這裡用來描述經濟發展良好的狀態。","options":["declining","prosperous","stagnant","fragile"],"sentence":"The ______ economy created countless job opportunities for workers. The country's GDP grew by 15% last year, attracting foreign investors from around the world.","translation":"繁榮的經濟為工人創造了無數的工作機會。該國的國內生產毛額去年增長了15%，吸引了來自世界各地的外商投資。","word":"prosperous"}},"protein":{"createdAt":1781332009083,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"protein 是名詞，指的是蛋白質，一種重要的營養物質，對肌肉和組織的構成至關重要","options":["carbohydrate","protein","fat","vitamin"],"sentence":"Athletes need to consume adequate ______ to support muscle growth and recovery. Foods like chicken, fish, and eggs are excellent sources of this essential nutrient.","translation":"運動員需要消耗足夠的蛋白質來支持肌肉生長和恢復。雞肉、魚和雞蛋等食物是這種必要營養素的極好來源。","word":"protein"}},"provide":{"createdAt":1781777331353,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"provide是動詞，表示供應、提供某物給某人或某個地方","options":["withhold","provide","deny","refuse"],"sentence":"The restaurant agreed to ______ complimentary drinks for all guests at the wedding reception. The manager wanted to ensure every attendee felt welcome and well cared for throughout the evening.","translation":"餐廳同意為婚禮招待會的所有賓客提供免費飲料。經理想確保每位出席者在整個晚上都感到受歡迎且得到妥善照顧。","word":"provide"}},"province":{"createdAt":1781583174625,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"province是指國家內部的一個行政區域，通常由中央政府管轄，具有某種程度的自治權","options":["country","province","city","district"],"sentence":"The ______ of Ontario is one of the most populated regions in Canada. It has its own government and laws that differ from other parts of the country.","translation":"安大略____是加拿大人口最密集的地區之一。它擁有自己的政府和與該國其他地區不同的法律。","word":"province"}},"provincial":{"createdAt":1781831347625,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"provincial 形容詞表示首都或大城市以外的地方，通常帶有閉塞或不開放的含義。","options":["metropolitan","rural","provincial","cosmopolitan"],"sentence":"The ______ town had no major universities or cultural institutions like those found in the capital city. Most residents had never traveled beyond their own region and were unfamiliar with urban life.","translation":"這個外省的小鎮沒有像首都那樣的主要大學或文化機構。大多數居民從未離開過自己的地區，對城市生活不熟悉。","word":"provincial"}},"provision":{"createdAt":1781832508019,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"provision 表示「供應量；預備；食糧」，指為特定目的預先準備的物品或數量。","options":["denial","provision","prohibition","reduction"],"sentence":"The government made adequate ______ of food and water for the refugees. Trucks arrived daily at the camp delivering supplies that would last several weeks.","translation":"政府為難民做出了充足的食物和水的供應。卡車每天抵達營地運送可以維持數週的物資。","word":"provision"}},"psychic":{"createdAt":1781362281725,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"psychic表示通靈的、有特異功能的，指超自然或心靈上的能力。","options":["mathematical","psychic","musical","athletic"],"sentence":"She claimed to have ______ abilities that allowed her to read minds. She said she could communicate with spirits and see the future.","translation":"她聲稱擁有通靈能力，可以讀取他人的想法。她說她可以與靈魂溝通並看到未來。","word":"psychic"}},"psychology":{"createdAt":1781532967164,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"psychology 是心理學，與「人如何思考」、「人類行為和情緒」的描述相符。","options":["biology","chemistry","psychology","physics"],"sentence":"She decided to study ______ in university because she was interested in how people think. Her focus was on understanding human behavior and emotions.","translation":"她決定在大學學習______(心理學)，因為她對人們如何思考感興趣。她的專注點是理解人類的行為和情緒。","word":"psychology"}},"publication":{"createdAt":1781345237584,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"publication指書籍、文章或其他作品的出版或發行行為及其所發行的物品。","options":["reception","publication","rejection","discussion"],"sentence":"The ______ of the research paper was delayed due to peer review corrections. The journal finally released the study online and in print this morning.","translation":"由於同行評審修正，研究論文的出版被延遲了。期刊今早終於在線和印刷版上發布了這項研究。","word":"publication"}},"pump":{"createdAt":1781359980247,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pump作為動詞有套問的意思；指通過反覆或持續的提問來從某人那裡獲取信息。","options":["extract","pump","document","broadcast"],"sentence":"The reporter tried to ______ information from the witness about what he had seen that night. Despite persistent questioning, the witness refused to reveal any details.","translation":"記者試圖從證人那裡套問他那晚看到的信息。儘管提出了持續的質詢，證人拒絕透露任何細節。","word":"pump"}},"pumps":{"createdAt":1781332009077,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pumps 是名詞，指的是無帶的高跟女鞋，通常用於正式場合","options":["boots","pumps","sandals","sneakers"],"sentence":"She wore elegant red ______ to the formal evening gala. The high-heeled shoes matched her dress perfectly and made her feel confident and stylish.","translation":"她穿著優雅的紅色高跟鞋參加了正式的晚宴。這雙高跟鞋與她的禮服完美搭配，讓她感到自信和時尚。","word":"pumps"}},"purify":{"createdAt":1781749177485,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"purify 意為使某物變得純淨，強調去除不需要或有害的物質。","options":["test","cleanse","distribute","store"],"sentence":"The water treatment plant uses advanced filters to ______ the drinking water. This process removes all harmful chemicals and bacteria from the source.","translation":"淨水廠使用先進的過濾器來淨化飲用水。這個過程會從水源中去除所有有害化學物質和細菌。","word":"purify"}},"purpose":{"createdAt":1781693270387,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"purpose指「意圖、目的、目標」，表示做某事想要達到或實現的目標。","options":["obstacle","purpose","consequence","tradition"],"sentence":"The main ______ of the new community center is to provide affordable recreational activities for local residents. The facility offers sports classes, art workshops, and meeting spaces for all ages.","translation":"新社區中心的主要目的是為當地居民提供價格合理的娛樂活動。該設施為各年齡層提供運動課程、藝術工作坊和會議空間。","word":"purpose"}},"pursuit":{"createdAt":1781939898048,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"pursuit表示追趕或追求某個目標，這裡特別指動態的追捕行為。","options":["wandering","pursuit","rendering","hesitation"],"sentence":"The detective was in ______ of the suspect through the crowded streets. He finally caught up with him near the train station after a twenty-minute chase.","translation":"偵探在擁擠的街道上追趕嫌疑人。在二十分鐘的追捕後，他終於在火車站附近逮捕了他。","word":"pursuit"}},"quake":{"createdAt":1781950727565,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"quake 指震顫或顫抖，特別是指地震或由於恐懼而發抖。","options":["settle","quake","freeze","harden"],"sentence":"The ground began to ______ when the earthquake struck the city. Buildings shook violently and people ran out into the streets in panic.","translation":"當地震襲擊城市時，地面開始震動。建築物劇烈搖晃，人們驚慌失措地跑到街上。","word":"quake"}},"qualified":{"createdAt":1781332009068,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"qualified 意為有資格的、勝任的，表示具備必要的技能或資格","options":["inexperienced","qualified","young","willing"],"sentence":"Only ______ professionals with years of training should perform this dangerous surgery. The hospital requires all surgeons to have medical degrees and board certification.","translation":"只有有資格的專業人士經過多年培訓才應執行這項危險的手術。該醫院要求所有外科醫生都要有醫學學位和委員會認證。","word":"qualified"}},"quality":{"createdAt":1781425737119,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"quality 指事物的優秀程度或品質水平，與服務標準和訓練計畫的改善相關。","options":["quantity","quality","location","price"],"sentence":"The restaurant's ______ of service has improved significantly over the past year. The manager implemented strict training programs to ensure every customer interaction meets high standards.","translation":"這家餐廳的服務品質在過去一年中大幅改善。經理實施了嚴格的培訓計畫，以確保每次客戶互動都達到高標準。","word":"quality"}},"quantity":{"createdAt":1781933311793,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"quantity（數量）指可測量的物質多少，而quality（品質）、identity（身分）和facility（設施）都不能用「一半的量」來修飾。","options":["quality","quantity","identity","facility"],"sentence":"The baker reduced the ______ of sugar in the recipe to make the cookies less sweet. She used exactly half the amount that was originally specified.","translation":"麵包師傅減少了食譜中糖的數量，使餅乾不那麼甜。她使用的量正好是原本規定量的一半。","word":"quantity"}},"quarrel":{"createdAt":1781864339053,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"quarrel表示兩個人或多個人之間的口頭爭執或吵架，通常涉及不同意見。","options":["chat","quarrel","laugh","whisper"],"sentence":"The two friends began to ______ loudly in the cafeteria about who should pay for lunch. By the time they finished shouting, everyone in the room was staring at them.","translation":"這兩個朋友在自助餐廳大聲爭吵誰應該付午餐費。當他們停止尖叫時，房間裡的每個人都在看著他們。","word":"quarrel"}},"queer":{"createdAt":1781794866350,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"queer是用來描述非異性戀或非順性別身份的現代術語，常用於LGBTQ+相關語境中。","options":["religious","queer","athletic","academic"],"sentence":"The ______ community has made significant progress in fighting for equal rights and recognition. Pride parades celebrate the diverse identities of LGBTQ+ individuals worldwide.","translation":"______ 社群在爭取平等權利和認可方面取得了重大進展。驕傲遊行慶祝全球LGBTQ+個體的多元身份。","word":"queer"}},"questionnaire":{"createdAt":1781935654222,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"questionnaire 是一份包含多個問題的書面表格，用於收集受調查者的意見或信息。","options":["interview","feedback","questionnaire","survey form"],"sentence":"Please fill out this ______ with your feedback about our customer service. We need your written responses to all twenty questions.","translation":"請填寫此問卷以提供對我們客戶服務的反饋。我們需要您對所有二十個問題的書面回答。","word":"questionnaire"}},"quilt":{"createdAt":1781484415210,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"quilt是指用多層布料和填充物製成的厚重被子，通常是手工製作的。","options":["pillow","quilt","curtain","rug"],"sentence":"She snuggled under her warm ______ on the cold winter night. The handmade blanket had been stitched together from colorful fabric patches by her grandmother.","translation":"在寒冷的冬夜，她蜷縮在溫暖的棉被下。這條手工製作的被子是由她祖母用五顏六色的布料碎片縫製而成的。","word":"quilt"}},"quota":{"createdAt":1781848330185,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"quota指規定必須達到的數量、定額或限額，通常用於銷售或生產目標。","options":["complaint","quota","tradition","vacation"],"sentence":"Each sales team must meet the monthly ______ or face consequences. The company expects every representative to sell at least fifty units by the end of the month.","translation":"每個銷售團隊必須完成月度配額，否則將面臨後果。公司期望每位代表在月底前至少銷售五十個單位。","word":"quota"}},"race":{"createdAt":1781580511756,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"race 在這裡指的是競速比賽，參與者要看誰能最先完成","options":["match","game","race","tournament"],"sentence":"The sprinter won the ______ by crossing the finish line first. All the other competitors had been running at full speed as well.","translation":"短跑運動員率先衝過終點線贏得了比賽。所有其他競爭對手也一直在全速奔跑。","word":"race"}},"racism":{"createdAt":1781935654226,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"racism 是名詞，表示「種族主義」或「種族歧視」，指基於種族差異而進行的不公正對待或歧視。","options":["diversity","racism","cooperation","integration"],"sentence":"The government launched a national campaign to combat ______ in schools and workplaces. Educational programs were designed to promote equality and respect for all ethnic groups.","translation":"政府發起了一項全國運動來對抗學校和工作場所中的種族歧視。教育計畫旨在促進所有種族的平等和尊重。","word":"racism"}},"racist":{"createdAt":1781418481459,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"racist作為名詞，指持有種族歧視觀點並根據種族差異對他人進行判斷或歧視的人。","options":["pacifist","racist","activist","realist"],"sentence":"The ______ made offensive statements based on people's ethnicity and skin color. His discriminatory views were condemned by the entire community.","translation":"那位種族主義者根據人們的種族和膚色發表了冒犯性言論。他的歧視性觀點被整個社區譴責。","word":"racist"}},"rage":{"createdAt":1781871338555,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"rage在此表示自然災害的猛烈肆虐，與火勢蔓延的激烈程度相關。","options":["beauty","spread","fury","color"],"sentence":"The ______ of the wild fire spread rapidly across the forest during the drought. The firefighters worked through the night to contain the disaster.","translation":"野火的猛烈肆虐在乾旱期間迅速蔓延到整個森林。消防員整夜工作以控制災難。","word":"rage"}},"rally":{"createdAt":1781362281649,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rally是指集會或群眾大會，人們聚集在一起表達共同的立場或支持。","options":["debate","rally","interview","broadcast"],"sentence":"The political ______ attracted thousands of supporters from across the country. Citizens gathered in the square to show their support for the candidate.","translation":"這場政治集會吸引了來自全國各地的數千名支持者。市民聚集在廣場上表示對候選人的支持。","word":"rally"}},"random":{"createdAt":1781693484714,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"random 表示沒有計畫、順序或目的，完全按照機會或巧合進行。","options":["carefully","randomly","quietly","quickly"],"sentence":"The teacher picked students ______ to answer questions in class. There was no pattern to who got called on each day.","translation":"老師隨意地挑選學生在課堂上回答問題。每天被點名的人沒有規律可循。","word":"random"}},"rapid":{"createdAt":1781332009075,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rapid 是形容詞，表示速度快的、迅速的","options":["slow","rapid","steady","stable"],"sentence":"The ______ growth of the company allowed it to expand into three new markets within a year. Investors were impressed by how quickly the business was developing.","translation":"公司的迅速增長使其在一年內擴展到三個新市場。投資者對業務發展的速度印象深刻。","word":"rapid"}},"rapidly":{"createdAt":1781332009075,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rapidly 是副詞，表示非常快速地或迅速地發生","options":["slowly","rapidly","steadily","gradually"],"sentence":"The technology company's stock price increased ______ after announcing their new product. Within a month, the value had nearly doubled due to strong investor interest.","translation":"這家科技公司在宣佈新產品後股價迅速上升。在一個月內，由於投資者的強烈興趣，股票價值幾乎翻倍。","word":"rapidly"}},"rare":{"createdAt":1781708461109,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rare在此作為形容詞，表示物品珍貴且極少見的特性。","options":["common","rare","broken","modern"],"sentence":"This ______ antique vase is worth thousands of dollars at the auction. Only three identical pieces are known to exist in the entire world.","translation":"這件珍貴的古董花瓶在拍賣會上價值數千美元。全世界只有三件相同的藝術品存在。","word":"rare"}},"rash":{"createdAt":1781840892411,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rash指皮膚上出現的疹子或皮疹，通常由過敏或感染引起。","options":["fever","rash","cough","bruise"],"sentence":"The child broke out in a red ______ after eating shellfish at dinner last night. The allergic reaction caused itching and swelling that persisted for several hours.","translation":"孩子在昨晚晚餐吃貝類後出現紅色皮疹。這種過敏反應導致瘙癢和腫脹，持續了數小時。","word":"rash"}},"ratify":{"createdAt":1781332009069,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ratify 意為正式批准或簽署，使條約或協議具有法律效力","options":["reject","ratify","ignore","debate"],"sentence":"The government must ______ the international treaty before it becomes legally binding. Parliament voted to officially approve the agreement with a strong majority.","translation":"政府必須正式批准這項國際條約，使其具有法律約束力。議會以絕對多數投票正式批准了該協議。","word":"ratify"}},"ratio":{"createdAt":1781414438947,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ratio用來表示兩個量之間的相對關係或比較，通常用分數或冒號表示","options":["percentage","ratio","average","quantity"],"sentence":"The ______ of boys to girls in the class is 3:2. This mathematical proportion helps us understand the distribution of students by gender.","translation":"班級中男生與女生的比例是3:2。這個數學比例幫助我們了解學生按性別的分布。","word":"ratio"}},"raw":{"createdAt":1781664082519,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"raw 表示食物未經烹飪、處於自然狀態或未經加工的。","options":["cooked","raw","frozen","canned"],"sentence":"She prefers to eat ______ vegetables in her salad rather than cooked ones. The fresh carrots and uncooked broccoli retain all their natural crunch.","translation":"她更喜歡在沙拉中吃生蔬菜而不是熟的。新鮮的胡蘿蔔和未煮過的花椰菜保留了所有天然的脆爽。","word":"raw"}},"reach":{"createdAt":1781664082516,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"reach 作名詞時表示可以到達的範圍或距離，特別是指伸手能夠到的距離。","options":["distance","reach","height","length"],"sentence":"The top shelf is beyond my ______, and I cannot grab the books without using a ladder. My arm is simply too short to touch that height.","translation":"頂部的架子超出了我的夠得著的範圍，沒有梯子我無法拿到書籍。我的手臂太短了，無法觸及那個高度。","word":"reach"}},"react":{"createdAt":1781784029106,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"respond（反應）指對某事做出的即時回應，與「反應」的定義相符。","options":["perform","question","respond","complain"],"sentence":"When the teacher announced a pop quiz, the students began to ______ with groans and complaints. Their immediate response showed their frustration with the unexpected test.","translation":"當老師宣佈要進行突擊測驗時，學生開始以呻吟和抱怨來反應。他們的立即反應表明他們對這次突如其來的測驗感到沮喪。","word":"react"}},"realistic":{"createdAt":1781362281724,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"realistic表示符合實際的、實際上可能的，指根據現實情況制定的計畫或目標。","options":["impossible","realistic","extreme","vague"],"sentence":"He set ______ goals for his fitness journey instead of expecting immediate results. He understood that progress would take time and consistent effort.","translation":"他為自己的健身之旅設定了現實的目標，而不是期望立竿見影的結果。他明白進步需要時間和持續的努力。","word":"realistic"}},"realization":{"createdAt":1781831848729,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"realization 作為名詞表示「領悟」或「認識」，指突然明白或理解某件事的過程。","options":["discovery","understanding","realization","decision"],"sentence":"His ______ that he had wasted years pursuing the wrong career path came too late. He finally understood his true passion when he was already in his fifties.","translation":"他領悟到自己浪費多年追求錯誤職業道路的時刻已經太晚了。當他已經五十多歲時，他才最終明白自己的真正熱情所在。","word":"realization"}},"realize":{"createdAt":1781332009078,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"realize 意為實現或達成，表示將想法或計畫變成現實","options":["abandon","realize","forget","ignore"],"sentence":"The entrepreneur didn't ______ his business dream until years of hard work and persistence. He eventually built a successful company that generated millions in revenue.","translation":"企業家在多年的辛勤工作和堅持後才實現了他的商業夢想。他最終建立了一家成功的公司，產生了數百萬的收入。","word":"realize"}},"realm":{"createdAt":1781362281658,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"realm指的是特定領域或範圍，如藝術、科學或政治等。","options":["country","realm","location","region"],"sentence":"In the ______ of sports, Michael Jordan is considered the greatest basketball player. His achievements set records that remain unmatched in his field.","translation":"在體育領域，邁克爾·喬丹被認為是最偉大的籃球運動員。他的成就創造了在他的領域中仍然無與倫比的紀錄。","word":"realm"}},"reasonable":{"createdAt":1781849622417,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"合理的是指符合常理、適當或公平的，通常用來描述價格、決定或主張是否明智且可接受。","options":["excessive","reasonable","suspicious","outrageous"],"sentence":"The price of thirty dollars for that shirt seems ______ to me. I checked several stores and found similar items in the same price range.","translation":"這件襯衫三十美元的價格對我來說似乎是合理的。我檢查了幾家商店，發現類似的商品價格範圍相同。","word":"reasonable"}},"reassure":{"createdAt":1781927792736,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"reassure指的是通過安慰、保證或提供信息來消除某人的擔憂和恐懼。","options":["threaten","reassure","confuse","ignore"],"sentence":"The doctor tried to ______ the anxious patient about the upcoming surgery. She explained the procedure in detail and shared success statistics to calm his fears.","translation":"醫生試圖讓焦慮的患者對即將進行的手術放心。她詳細解釋了手術程序並分享成功統計數據來緩解他的恐懼。","word":"reassure"}},"rebellion":{"createdAt":1781798927523,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rebellion 指對權威的武裝反抗或起義，通常涉及暴力和有組織的抗爭活動。","options":["celebration","rebellion","petition","election"],"sentence":"The peasants launched a ______ against the tyrannical government in the 18th century. They organized armed uprisings, burned government buildings, and demanded political reform.","translation":"十八世紀農民對暴虐的政府發動了叛亂。他們組織了武裝起義，焚燒政府建築，並要求政治改革。","word":"rebellion"}},"receptionist":{"createdAt":1781693538701,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"receptionist 是在辦公室、飯店或診所前台工作的接待人員，負責招待訪客和進行初步接待。","options":["manager","receptionist","janitor","accountant"],"sentence":"The ______ greeted every visitor with a warm smile and helped them sign in. She had worked at the front desk for five years and knew all the regular clients by name.","translation":"接待員用溫暖的微笑迎接每位訪客，並幫助他們簽到。她在前台工作了五年，認識所有的常客。","word":"receptionist"}},"recess":{"createdAt":1781840659328,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"recess 在政治或學校環境中指休會或休假期間，暫停正常活動。","options":["session","recess","meeting","debate"],"sentence":"Parliament announced a two-week ______ starting next Monday for all members to return to their constituencies. During this break, legislators would campaign and address local concerns.","translation":"議會宣佈從下週一開始兩週的休會期，供所有成員返回各自的選區。在此休息期間，立法者可以進行競選並解決地方問題。","word":"recess"}},"recession":{"createdAt":1781311922068,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"recession 是指經濟的衰退期，特徵是商業活動減少、失業增加和收入下降。","options":["recession","growth","boom","expansion"],"sentence":"During the ______, many businesses closed and unemployment rates increased dramatically. The economic downturn lasted for two years before the country began to recover.","translation":"在經濟衰退期間，許多企業關閉，失業率大幅上升。這次經濟衰退持續了兩年才開始恢復。","word":"recession"}},"recharge":{"createdAt":1781933311792,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"recharge（充電；放鬆休息）在此指恢復精力，而accelerate（加速）、restructure（重組）和substitute（替代）都無法在此情境下表達休息和恢復的意思。","options":["accelerate","recharge","restructure","substitute"],"sentence":"After working for twelve hours straight, the exhausted employee decided to ______ by taking a week-long vacation. This break helped him regain his physical and mental strength.","translation":"連續工作十二小時後，疲憊的員工決定通過一週長的假期來放鬆休息。這個休息幫助他恢復了身體和心理的力量。","word":"recharge"}},"recite":{"createdAt":1781582424689,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"recite意為背誦或朗誦，特別是指從記憶中說出或背出文字，這裡與from memory和without notes的語境相符。","options":["write","recite","translate","analyze"],"sentence":"The student had to ______ the entire poem from memory during the exam. She listed every line perfectly without looking at her notes.","translation":"那名學生必須在考試中憑記憶背誦整首詩。她完美地列舉了每一行，沒有查看筆記。","word":"recite"}},"reckon":{"createdAt":1781836375376,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"reckon表示認為或想，是一種相對非正式的表達方式，表達個人的看法或估計。","options":["calculate","reckon","determine","estimate"],"sentence":"Based on the weather forecast, I ______ that tomorrow will be sunny. The meteorologists predicted clear skies throughout the day.","translation":"根據天氣預報，我認為明天會是晴天。氣象學家預測全天天空晴朗。","word":"reckon"}},"recognize":{"createdAt":1781532967163,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"recognize 表示認出、辨認，與「改變很多後無法辨認但聽到名字後明白」的情境相符。","options":["forget","remember","recognize","ignore"],"sentence":"I could not ______ my old friend at the party because she had changed so much. After she told me her name, I finally understood who she was.","translation":"在派對上我無法______(認出)我的老朋友，因為她改變了很多。在她告訴我她的名字後，我終於明白她是誰了。","word":"recognize"}},"recommend":{"createdAt":1781332009082,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"recommend 意為推薦或建議，表示認為某事物很好而建議他人使用或欣賞","options":["criticize","recommend","discourage","warn"],"sentence":"The film critic highly ______ the new movie to all audiences who enjoy dramatic storytelling. She gave it five stars and called it a must-see film.","translation":"電影評論家高度推薦這部新電影給所有喜歡戲劇性故事講述的觀眾。她給了它五顆星，並稱其為必看電影。","word":"recommend"}},"recover":{"createdAt":1781939439466,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"recover作動詞表示恢復、復原或重新獲得，通常指從疾病、受傷或困難中恢復過來。","options":["worsen","ignore","develop","recover"],"sentence":"After three weeks of rest and treatment, the athlete was finally able to ______ from the serious knee injury. His doctors confirmed he could return to training and resume his competitive schedule.","translation":"經過三週的休息和治療，運動員終於能夠從嚴重的膝蓋受傷中恢復。他的醫生確認他可以恢復訓練並恢復他的競賽日程。","word":"recover"}},"recreation":{"createdAt":1781564440919,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"recreation 表示娛樂、消遣，指為了享樂和放鬆而進行的活動。","options":["exercise","recreation","employment","duty"],"sentence":"Playing video games is my favorite form of ______. I enjoy this activity after work to relax and unwind.","translation":"玩電子遊戲是我最喜歡的娛樂方式。我喜歡在工作後進行這項活動來放鬆。","word":"recreation"}},"recreational":{"createdAt":1781481311491,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"recreational是指為了消遣、娛樂和休閒目的的活動。","options":["mandatory","recreational","professional","dangerous"],"sentence":"The park offers many ______ activities for families on weekends. Children can enjoy playgrounds, sports fields, and swimming pools designed purely for leisure and entertainment.","translation":"這個公園在週末為家庭提供許多消遣活動。兒童可以享受遊樂場、運動場和游泳池，這些都是為了消遣和娛樂而設計的。","word":"recreational"}},"redefine":{"createdAt":1781767999780,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"redefine 意指從根本上改變某事物的定義或內涵，賦予它新的、更適切的意義。","options":["revise","redefine","remove","reconsider"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ its mission statement to reflect modern values and social responsibility. The new version emphasized sustainability and community engagement rather than profit alone.","translation":"公司決定重新定義其使命宣言，以反映現代價值觀和社會責任。新版本強調永續發展和社區參與，而不僅僅是利潤。","word":"redefine"}},"reduction":{"createdAt":1781948564910,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"減少是指數量或規模的下降，從第二句提到的費用從1000萬美元降至600萬美元這個具體例子可以看出，這裡明確指的是數值的下降。","options":["increase","expansion","reduction","fluctuation"],"sentence":"The company announced a significant ______ in production costs through new technology. Expenses fell from $10 million to $6 million over the fiscal year.","translation":"公司宣佈透過新技術實現成本______。開支在財政年度內從1000萬美元降至600萬美元。","word":"reduction"}},"refined":{"createdAt":1781933311794,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"refined（精煉的；優雅的）描述有禮貌、優雅的人，而crude（粗糙的）、boisterous（吵鬧的）和clumsy（笨拙的）都與精緻舉止和磨練言辭的描述相反。","options":["crude","boisterous","refined","clumsy"],"sentence":"The ______ gentleman always used proper etiquette and spoke with eloquent vocabulary at formal events. His sophisticated manners and polished speech impressed everyone in attendance.","translation":"那位優雅紳士在正式場合總是遵循適當的禮儀，並用雄辯的詞彙說話。他的精緻舉止和磨練過的言辭給在場的每個人留下了深刻印象。","word":"refined"}},"refreshment":{"createdAt":1782002325566,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"refreshment 在這裡指的是會議或活動中提供的食物和飲料，用來讓人感到精神恢復和滿足。","options":["decoration","refreshment","transportation","equipment"],"sentence":"After the long meeting, the conference organizers provided ______ for all the attendees. The cookies and juice were especially appreciated by those who had skipped lunch.","translation":"長會議後，會議組織者為所有與會者提供了點心。特別是那些沒吃午餐的人都很喜歡餅乾和果汁。","word":"refreshment"}},"refugee":{"createdAt":1781926464744,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"refugee 指因為戰爭、迫害或自然災害而逃離家園的人，必須是被迫離開的狀況。","options":["tourist","refugee","diplomat","merchant"],"sentence":"The organization provides shelter and food to ______ fleeing war zones. Many of these individuals have lost everything and are seeking safety across international borders.","translation":"該組織為逃離戰爭地帶的難民提供住所和食物。許多這些人已經失去了一切，正在尋求跨越國際邊界的安全。","word":"refugee"}},"refund":{"createdAt":1781437013473,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"refund 意為退款或退費，指商家將顧客已支付的金額返還給顧客。","options":["replacement","refund","discount","warranty"],"sentence":"The customer demanded a ______ after discovering the defective product had broken within a week. The company processed the request immediately and returned the full purchase price to her account.","translation":"顧客在發現有缺陷的產品在一週內損壞後要求退款。公司立即處理了該請求並將全部購買價格退回到她的帳戶。","word":"refund"}},"refusal":{"createdAt":1781332009076,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"refusal 是名詞，表示對要求或提議的拒絕或回絕","options":["agreement","refusal","acceptance","willingness"],"sentence":"The athlete's ______ to use performance-enhancing drugs earned him great respect from the sporting community. He consistently declined offers to cheat despite pressure from competitors.","translation":"運動員拒絕使用性能增強藥物的行為贏得了體育界的高度尊重。儘管競爭對手的施壓，他一直拒絕作弊的提議。","word":"refusal"}},"refute":{"createdAt":1781332009066,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"refute 意為駁斥或反駁某人的說法，通常帶有提供相反證據的含義","options":["support","refute","ignore","accept"],"sentence":"The scientist was able to ______ the false claims with solid evidence. The data clearly demonstrated that the original hypothesis was incorrect.","translation":"科學家能夠用確鑿的證據駁斥那些虛假的主張。數據清楚地表明原來的假設是錯誤的。","word":"refute"}},"regain":{"createdAt":1781749177487,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"regain 表示重新獲得之前失去的東西，強調恢復原有的狀態或能力。","options":["lose","strengthen","demonstrate","restore"],"sentence":"After receiving treatment, the patient was able to ______ her ability to walk. Her doctors were amazed at how quickly she recovered from the surgery.","translation":"在接受治療後，患者能夠恢復她的行走能力。她的醫生對她從手術中恢復得如此之快感到驚訝。","word":"regain"}},"regard":{"createdAt":1781848934142,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"regard作動詞表示敬重、尊敬，或者表示看待、認為的意思","options":["ignore","regard","forget","question"],"sentence":"I ______ my former teacher with great respect and admiration. She was the one who inspired me to pursue a career in education.","translation":"我非常尊敬和欽佩我的前任老師。她是激勵我從事教育事業的人。","word":"regard"}},"regardless":{"createdAt":1781515329267,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"regardless 副詞，意思是不管、不顧，表示不受某事物影響或限制。","options":["because","regardless","instead","unless"],"sentence":"The athlete decided to compete in the tournament ______ of her recent injury. She was determined to participate and give her best effort despite the pain.","translation":"儘管最近受傷，運動員仍決定參加比賽。她決心參加並不顧疼痛而盡力表現。","word":"regardless"}},"region":{"createdAt":1781515329268,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"region 名詞，意思是地區、區域，指一個特定的地理範圍。","options":["city","region","building","street"],"sentence":"The ______ experiences heavy rainfall during the monsoon season every year. Residents in this area need to prepare for flooding and landslides during those months.","translation":"該地區每年在季風季節都會經歷大量降雨。該地區的居民需要在那段時間準備應對洪水和山崩。","word":"region"}},"registration":{"createdAt":1781831347632,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"registration 名詞表示正式的登記或註冊程序，特別是在教育或行政機構中。","options":["graduation","registration","vacation","recreation"],"sentence":"Students must complete ______ before attending their first classes at the university. The process involves submitting documents, paying fees, and confirming enrollment in specific courses.","translation":"學生必須在參加大學第一堂課之前完成登記。該過程涉及提交文件、支付費用和確認特定課程的入學資格。","word":"registration"}},"regretful":{"createdAt":1781951900948,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"regretful表示為過去的行為感到後悔或遺憾，與願意改變未來行為的想法相符。","options":["happy","regretful","excited","proud"],"sentence":"After eating too much candy, the child felt ______ and wished she hadn't been so greedy. She promised her mother that she would be more careful with sweets next time.","translation":"吃了太多糖果後，孩子感到懊悔，希望自己沒有那麼貪心。她向媽媽承諾下次會更小心對待甜食。","word":"regretful"}},"regulate":{"createdAt":1781449588284,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"regulate作為動詞表示「限制、控管、調節」，指通過規則或法律來管理某事物的程度或行為。","options":["glorify","regulate","phenomenon","trillion"],"sentence":"The government decided to ______ the amount of pollution that factories could release into the environment. New laws were implemented to set strict limits on emissions and require regular monitoring of industrial activities.","translation":"政府決定限制工廠可以向環境中排放的污染量。實施了新的法律來設定嚴格的排放限制並要求對工業活動進行定期監測。","word":"regulate"}},"regulation":{"createdAt":1781515329261,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"regulation 名詞，意思是規定、管理，指具有約束力的官方或正式規則。","options":["suggestion","regulation","recommendation","tradition"],"sentence":"The new ______ required all restaurants to display their health inspection scores. Restaurant owners had to follow these mandatory guidelines or face heavy fines.","translation":"新的規定要求所有餐廳公開展示其衛生檢查評分。餐廳老闆必須遵守這些強制性的指導方針，否則將面臨高額罰款。","word":"regulation"}},"rehearsal":{"createdAt":1781434900594,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rehearsal指為準備正式表演而進行的練習或排練。","options":["vacation","rehearsal","composition","recording"],"sentence":"The orchestra spent three months in ______ before the concert performance. The conductor made the musicians repeat difficult passages over and over until they achieved perfection.","translation":"樂團在音樂會前進行了三個月的排練。指揮讓音樂家們一遍又一遍地重複困難段落，直到達到完美。","word":"rehearsal"}},"reign":{"createdAt":1781481072317,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"reign 表示「統治、當政」，指君主或統治者行使權力的時期。","options":["visit","reign","promotion","residence"],"sentence":"Queen Victoria's ______ lasted over 60 years and transformed the British Empire. During this entire period, she held absolute power and made all the major decisions for the nation.","translation":"維多利亞女王的統治持續了60多年，並改變了大英帝國。在整個時期中，她掌握絕對權力並為國家做出所有重大決定。","word":"reign"}},"relate":{"createdAt":1781798927526,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"relate 在此語境中表示詳細敘述或描述某一事件或故事的經過。","options":["ignore","relate","conceal","distort"],"sentence":"The witness carefully ______ the events of the night to the police detectives. She described how the suspect entered the building through the back door at 10 PM.","translation":"證人仔細地向警察偵探敘述了那晚發生的事件。她描述了嫌疑人如何在晚上10點從後門進入建築物。","word":"relate"}},"relationship":{"createdAt":1781776694532,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"relationship 是名詞，意思是兩個或多個人之間的連結或互動狀態。","options":["distance","relationship","competition","confusion"],"sentence":"Their ______ has grown stronger over the past five years. They now trust each other completely and share all their personal thoughts and feelings.","translation":"他們的關係在過去五年裡變得更加牢固。他們現在完全互相信任，並分享彼此的所有個人想法和感受。","word":"relationship"}},"relativity":{"createdAt":1781849622415,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"相對論是物理學中的基本理論，說明事物的性質往往取決於參考框架或觀察者的角度。","options":["absorption","relativity","density","momentum"],"sentence":"The concept of ______ in physics shows that time and space are not absolute. Einstein's theory demonstrates that measurements depend on the observer's frame of reference.","translation":"物理學中的相對論概念表明時間和空間不是絕對的。愛因斯坦的理論證明測量結果取決於觀察者的參考框架。","word":"relativity"}},"relentless":{"createdAt":1781481072315,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"relentless 表示持續不斷、堅持不懈的，通常帶有強烈的力量或嚴厲的意味，強調沒有停止或緩解。","options":["occasional","relentless","constructive","fair"],"sentence":"The ______ criticism from the media never gave the politician a moment of peace. Day after day, week after week, the attacks continued without any breaks or mercy.","translation":"媒體的持續嚴厲批評從未給這位政治家片刻的安寧。日復一日、周復一周，攻擊持續不斷，沒有任何中斷或寬恕。","word":"relentless"}},"reliable":{"createdAt":1781775276770,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"reliable指值得信任、可依賴的，與按時完成工作、被同事信任的描述相符。","options":["lazy","dishonest","reliable","careless"],"sentence":"Maria is a ______ employee who always completes her work on time and with great accuracy. Her colleagues trust her to handle the most important projects.","translation":"瑪麗亞是一位可信賴的員工，她總是按時完成工作且精確度很高。她的同事信任她來處理最重要的項目。","word":"reliable"}},"relic":{"createdAt":1781437013472,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"relic 指的是來自過去的遺物或遺跡，通常具有歷史價值，需要被保存和研究。","options":["relic","invention","document","theory"],"sentence":"The ancient ______ discovered in the archaeological dig provided valuable insights into the lost civilization. Experts carefully preserved the pottery fragments and stone tools for further study.","translation":"在考古挖掘中發現的古老遺跡為失落文明提供了寶貴的見解。專家們小心翼翼地保存了陶器碎片和石製工具以供進一步研究。","word":"relic"}},"relieve":{"createdAt":1781481124691,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"relieve 意思是減輕或消除不適、痛苦或煩惱，帶來舒適感。","options":["worsen","increase","ease","prolong"],"sentence":"The cold compress helped to ______ her headache after hours of suffering. She felt immediate comfort and relaxation once she applied it to her temples.","translation":"冷敷布幫助緩解了她經過數小時痛苦後的頭痛。她將其敷在太陽穴上後立即感到舒適和放鬆。","word":"relieve"}},"reminder":{"createdAt":1781437435165,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"reminder 是提醒物或提醒者，幫助人們記住需要完成的事情。","options":["decoration","reminder","achievement","complaint"],"sentence":"I set a phone alarm as a ______ to pay my monthly bills on time. Without this notification, I would likely forget the important deadline.","translation":"我設置了一個手機鬧鐘來提醒我按時支付月度帳單。沒有這個通知，我可能會忘記這個重要的截止日期。","word":"reminder"}},"render":{"createdAt":1781939898049,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"render用於表示使某人或某物處於某種狀態，此處表示「使...失能」。","options":["rendered","wandered","pursued","abandoned"],"sentence":"The accident ______ him unable to work for several months. Doctors said his injuries were too severe for him to return to his job anytime soon.","translation":"這場事故使他數月無法工作。醫生說他的傷勢太嚴重，他在短期內無法回到工作崗位。","word":"render"}},"renew":{"createdAt":1781709984195,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"renew 表示延長有效期或更新已過期的文件，使其重新有效。","options":["replace","renew","restore","revise"],"sentence":"I forgot to ______ my passport before my international trip next month. The government website allows citizens to complete the process online in just a few minutes.","translation":"我忘記在下個月的國際旅行前更新護照。政府網站允許公民在幾分鐘內在線完成這個過程。","word":"renew"}},"renewable":{"createdAt":1781693270388,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"renewable表示「可再生的、可恢復的」，指能夠自然地或通過人為方式補充和重新生成的資源。","options":["fossil","renewable","dangerous","outdated"],"sentence":"The government invested heavily in ______ energy sources like wind and solar power to reduce carbon emissions. These resources can be naturally replenished and will not deplete over time.","translation":"政府大力投資於風能和太陽能等可再生能源，以減少碳排放。這些資源可以自然補充，不會隨著時間而耗盡。","word":"renewable"}},"renewed":{"createdAt":1781452425259,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"renewed表示延長或更新，在這裡指合約被重新延長，員工可以繼續工作。","options":["expired","extended","terminated","broken"],"sentence":"After signing the ______ contract, Sarah will continue working at the company for another two years. The human resources department will process the paperwork this week.","translation":"在簽署延長的合約後，莎拉將在公司再工作兩年。人力資源部門將在本週處理文件。","word":"renewed"}},"renowned":{"createdAt":1781843396461,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"renowned表示享有高度名譽和廣泛認可的，通常用於描述才華出眾的人物。","options":["unknown","infamous","renowned","ordinary"],"sentence":"The ______ chef was invited to prepare the royal banquet. His restaurants had won multiple international awards and were featured in prestigious culinary magazines worldwide.","translation":"那位著名廚師被邀請為皇家宴會準備食物。他的餐廳贏得了多個國際獎項，並在世界各地享有盛譽的烹飪雜誌上刊登。","word":"renowned"}},"repair":{"createdAt":1781515329262,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"repair 名詞，意思是修理、修整，指恢復損壞物品的工作。","options":["inspection","repair","maintenance","upgrade"],"sentence":"The car required extensive ______ after the accident damaged its engine. The mechanic spent three weeks fixing all the broken components and replacing damaged parts.","translation":"事故後，汽車的引擎受損，需要進行大規模的修理。機修工花了三週時間修復所有破損的零件並更換受損的部件。","word":"repair"}},"repay":{"createdAt":1781693484716,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"repay 表示償還欠款或以實際行動回報他人的恩情和幫助。","options":["forget","deny","repay","ignore"],"sentence":"I borrowed money from my best friend last year, and now I want to ______ her kindness. She helped me when I needed it most, so I will always be grateful.","translation":"去年我向我最好的朋友借了錢，現在我想報答她的善意。她在我最需要時幫助了我，所以我將永遠感謝她。","word":"repay"}},"repentant":{"createdAt":1781653278521,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"repentant是形容詞，表示後悔的，用於描述對過去的錯誤或不當行為感到真正懊悔和遺憾的狀態。","options":["stubborn","repentant","proud","arrogant"],"sentence":"The ______ thief apologized sincerely to the store owner and returned all the stolen goods. His genuine remorse and promise to change his ways convinced everyone of his transformation.","translation":"這個______小偷真誠地向店主道歉並歸還了所有被盜的物品。他真正的悔恨和改過自新的承諾使每個人都相信他的轉變。","word":"repentant"}},"repetitive":{"createdAt":1781774456604,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"repetitive 形容事物一再重複而變得枯燥乏味的特性。","options":["creative","challenging","monotonous","varied"],"sentence":"The factory worker found the ______ nature of the job monotonous and tiresome. Performing the same task all day long became exhausting.","translation":"工廠工人覺得這份工作的重複性質很單調乏味。整天重複同樣的任務變得令人疲憊。","word":"repetitive"}},"replaceable":{"createdAt":1781843396461,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"replaceable表示可以被取代或替換的，強調該職位或物品並不是獨一無二的。","options":["irreplaceable","permanent","replaceable","unique"],"sentence":"The company emphasized that all customer service representatives are ______ by equally trained staff. This policy ensures continuous service even during employee turnover.","translation":"該公司強調所有客服代表都可以由同樣訓練有素的員工取代。這項政策確保即使員工流動也能持續提供服務。","word":"replaceable"}},"reply":{"createdAt":1781776694539,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"reply 是名詞，意思是對某人說的話或寫的信的回應或答覆。","options":["question","complaint","reply","delivery"],"sentence":"I sent her an email three days ago, but I still haven't received a ______ from her. She has not written back or acknowledged my message in any way.","translation":"我三天前給她發了一封電子郵件，但我仍然沒有收到她的回覆。她沒有寫回信或以任何方式確認我的信息。","word":"reply"}},"represent":{"createdAt":1781256547736,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Represent在此表示描寫或描繪，指藝術作品表現或呈現出某個場景或概念。","options":["ignore","represent","conceal","destroy"],"sentence":"The painting ______ a peaceful village at sunset with golden light spreading across the sky. Every detail in the artwork captures the artist's vision of rural tranquility.","translation":"這幅畫描寫了一個日落時刻的寧靜村莊，金色的光線灑滿天空。藝術品中的每一個細節都捕捉了藝術家對鄉村寧靜的想像。","word":"represent"}},"representation":{"createdAt":1781424356417,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"representation指的是以某種形式對現實事物或概念的展示或描繪。","options":["photograph","representation","contract","theory"],"sentence":"The artist created a beautiful ______ of the landscape through her oil painting. The canvas captured the essence of the mountains, valleys, and golden sunset in striking detail.","translation":"這位藝術家通過油畫創作了對風景的優美呈現。畫布以引人注目的細節捕捉了山脈、山谷和金色日落的精髓。","word":"representation"}},"representative":{"createdAt":1781848934139,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"representative指能夠代表某個類別或時代特徵的典型例子","options":["fake","representative","modern","abstract"],"sentence":"This painting is a ______ example of Renaissance art from the 15th century. Art historians often use it in textbooks to illustrate the period's characteristics.","translation":"這幅畫是15世紀文藝復興藝術的典型例子。藝術史學家經常在教科書中用它來說明該時期的特點。","word":"representative"}},"representatives":{"createdAt":1781836375378,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"representatives是代表，指被授權代表某個團體、機構或國家行動的人。","options":["ambassadors","representatives","delegates","envoys"],"sentence":"Each country sent ______ to the international conference to discuss climate change. These officials had the authority to negotiate agreements on behalf of their nations.","translation":"每個國家派遣代表參加國際會議討論氣候變化。這些官員有權代表他們的國家進行談判。","word":"representatives"}},"reproduce":{"createdAt":1781693265626,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"複製是指以相同或相似的方式製作或重新創作某物。","options":["sell","reproduce","destroy","analyze"],"sentence":"The art student was asked to ______ the famous painting using watercolors. The instructor wanted the class to practice the original artist's techniques and style.","translation":"美術學生被要求用水彩複製這幅著名畫作。講師希望全班練習原始藝術家的技巧和風格。","word":"reproduce"}},"republican":{"createdAt":1781437220554,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「Republican」形容詞表示支持共和政體制度和民主原則的人或政策。","options":["monarchist","communist","republican","anarchist"],"sentence":"The ______ candidate promised to reduce government spending and protect individual freedoms. He campaigned on principles of limited state power and free enterprise.","translation":"這位共和黨候選人承諾減少政府支出並保護個人自由。他在限制國家權力和自由企業的原則基礎上進行競選。","word":"republican"}},"request":{"createdAt":1781832508021,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"request 表示「請求；要求」，指向他人提出希望對方做某事的願望。","options":["expense","request","accident","beginning"],"sentence":"At the ______ of the students, the teacher agreed to postpone the final exam by one week. The class had submitted a formal petition explaining their need for additional study time.","translation":"應學生的要求，老師同意將期末考試推遲一週。全班提交了一份正式請願書，解釋他們需要更多的複習時間。","word":"request"}},"require":{"createdAt":1781840892411,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"require表示強制性的要求或必須有的條件，比建議或推薦更具強制力。","options":["suggest","require","recommend","prefer"],"sentence":"Most universities ______ applicants to submit standardized test scores along with their essays and transcripts. Without these documents, admissions officers cannot complete their evaluation process.","translation":"大多數大學要求申請者提交標準化考試成績以及論文和成績單。沒有這些文件，招生官員無法完成評估過程。","word":"require"}},"required":{"createdAt":1781848934142,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"required指被需要或被強制要求必須完成的事項","options":["optional","required","forbidden","suggested"],"sentence":"All students must submit a ______ essay before the end of the semester. Without it, they cannot receive credit for the course.","translation":"所有學生必須在學期末前提交一份必需的論文。沒有它，他們無法獲得課程學分。","word":"required"}},"resemblance":{"createdAt":1781481124692,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"resemblance 指事物或人之間的相似性或相像程度。","options":["difference","similarity","relationship","connection"],"sentence":"There was a striking ______ between the twin sisters, yet their personalities were completely different. People often mistook one for the other due to their identical facial features.","translation":"這對雙胞胎姐妹之間有驚人的相似之處，但她們的性格卻完全不同。由於她們相同的面部特徵，人們經常把一個誤認為另一個。","word":"resemblance"}},"resemble":{"createdAt":1781310338173,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"resemble 表示看起來相像或具有相似的特徵。","options":["ignore","resemble","criticize","change"],"sentence":"The teenage boy's facial features ______ those of his father quite remarkably. People often comment that they look like they could be twins despite their age difference.","translation":"這個青少年男孩的面部特徵與他父親的特徵非常相似。儘管年齡相差很大，人們經常評論他們看起來就像可能是雙胞胎。","word":"resemble"}},"resent":{"createdAt":1781622232189,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"resent 表示對某人或某事感到不滿、憎恨或感到受傷和冤枉。","options":["praise","resent","support","congratulate"],"sentence":"Tom began to ______ his coworker after she was promoted to a supervisory position. He felt that the promotion was unfair and that he deserved the opportunity more than she did.","translation":"在他的同事被提升為主管職位後，湯姆開始憎恨她。他認為這次晉升是不公平的，並且認為他比她更應該得到這個機會。","word":"resent"}},"reservation":{"createdAt":1781832761713,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"reservation 表示預定、預約，指提前為某服務（如餐廳、酒店等）預留位置。","options":["complaint","booking","cancellation","suggestion"],"sentence":"She made a ______ at the restaurant for eight people at 7 PM tomorrow evening. The manager confirmed the booking over the phone and wrote down all the necessary details.","translation":"她為明天晚上八個人七點的餐廳預訂了一張桌子。經理透過電話確認了預訂並記下了所有必要的細節。","word":"reservation"}},"reserved":{"createdAt":1781696018677,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"reserved 意為拘謹、有保留的，指人在社交場合中不願過多表露自己的想法和感受。","options":["outgoing","reserved","enthusiastic","talkative"],"sentence":"The CEO maintained a ______ demeanor during the public interview, speaking only when necessary. Her colleagues noted that she rarely shared personal opinions at company gatherings.","translation":"這位執行長在公開採訪中保持著矜持的舉止，只在必要時才發言。她的同事們注意到她很少在公司聚會上分享個人觀點。","word":"reserved"}},"reservoir":{"createdAt":1781693266949,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"reservoir是一個蓄水或儲存液體的大型人工結構，通常用於供水或灌溉。","options":["reservoir","factory","hospital","library"],"sentence":"The city built a large ______ to store water during the rainy season. This facility supplies drinking water to over one million residents throughout the year.","translation":"該市修建了一個大型蓄水池來在雨季儲存水。這個設施全年為超過一百萬居民供應飲用水。","word":"reservoir"}},"reside":{"createdAt":1781622232190,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"reside 意為居住或住在某個地方，通常指長期的居住。","options":["visit","reside","travel","explore"],"sentence":"The ambassador will ______ in the capital city for the duration of her diplomatic mission. She has been assigned to the country's main government district.","translation":"大使將在她的外交任務期間住在首都。她被派遣到該國的主要政府區域。","word":"reside"}},"residence":{"createdAt":1781582939253,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"residence 意指某人居住的地方或住房，在這裡與搬家和尋找房子的語境相符。","options":["job","residence","hobby","language"],"sentence":"After retiring, Mr. Chen decided to change his ______ from the bustling city to a quiet countryside village. He spent months searching for the perfect house with a garden and a peaceful view of the mountains.","translation":"退休後，陳先生決定將他的住所從熙攘的城市改至寧靜的鄉村。他花了數月尋找完美的房子，有花園和寧靜的山景。","word":"residence"}},"residual":{"createdAt":1781832508018,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"residual 表示「剩餘的；殘留的」，指留下來或保留下來的部分。","options":["new","residual","imported","synthetic"],"sentence":"The factory was ordered to clean up ______ chemicals left in the storage tanks. Environmental inspectors found traces of toxic substances that had accumulated over decades.","translation":"工廠被要求清除儲存槽中留下的殘留化學物質。環境檢查員發現了數十年來累積的有毒物質痕跡。","word":"residual"}},"resigned":{"createdAt":1781926464746,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"resigned 表示接受不幸的狀況或放棄希望的態度，通常帶有無奈和放棄的情緒。","options":["excited","resigned","promoted","ambitious"],"sentence":"After losing the promotion, he felt ______ to his current position and accepted he would not advance further. He stopped applying for better jobs and simply focused on his daily tasks.","translation":"失去晉升機會後，他對現在的職位感到認命，接受了他不會進步的事實。他停止申請更好的工作，只是專注於日常工作。","word":"resigned"}},"resist":{"createdAt":1781452425257,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"resist表示抵抗或反對某事物，在這裡指公司起初試圖反抗削減成本的壓力。","options":["surrender","oppose","accept","welcome"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ the pressure from investors to cut costs. However, they ultimately gave in and reduced their budget by 30%.","translation":"公司決定抵抗來自投資者削減成本的壓力。然而，他們最終屈服了，將預算減少了30%。","word":"resist"}},"resolution":{"createdAt":1781434900597,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"resolution指堅定的決心或計劃做某事的明確意圖。","options":["complaint","resolution","excuse","question"],"sentence":"She made a ______ to exercise every morning and eat healthier food starting January first. Her determination to change her lifestyle remained strong throughout the entire year.","translation":"她下定決心從一月一日開始每天早晨鍛煉並吃更健康的食物。她改變生活方式的決心在整個一年中保持堅定。","word":"resolution"}},"resolved":{"createdAt":1781424157174,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"resolved 作為形容詞表示堅定不移、下定決心的狀態。","options":["hesitant","uncertain","resolved","confused"],"sentence":"After months of self-doubt, Marcus felt ______ to finally start his own business venture. He had made a firm commitment and would not change his mind no matter what obstacles appeared.","translation":"經過幾個月的自我懷疑，馬庫斯感到下定決心終於開始自己的商業冒險。他已經做出堅定的承諾，無論出現什麼障礙都不會改變主意。","word":"resolved"}},"resort":{"createdAt":1781860901466,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"resort作名詞表示度假地或名勝，是供人休閒娛樂的地方","options":["fortress","resort","prison","factory"],"sentence":"The tropical ______ offered beautiful beaches, luxury hotels, and fine dining restaurants. Thousands of tourists visited this destination every year to relax and enjoy the amenities.","translation":"這個熱帶度假地提供美麗的海灘、豪華酒店和高級餐廳。每年有數千名遊客前往這個目的地放鬆和享受設施。","word":"resort"}},"resource":{"createdAt":1781926464745,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"resource 在商業語境中指公司可利用的資產、資金或財產，用於運營和發展。","options":["expense","resource","liability","debt"],"sentence":"The company carefully manages its financial ______ to ensure long-term stability. Their accountants track every dollar of capital and investment to prevent wasteful spending.","translation":"公司謹慎地管理其財務資源以確保長期穩定性。他們的會計師追蹤每一美元的資本和投資以防止浪費支出。","word":"resource"}},"respecting":{"createdAt":1781622232188,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"respecting 作為介詞表示「關於」或「就...而言」，用於引入所討論的主題。","options":["Ignoring","Respecting","Questioning","Delaying"],"sentence":"______ the new company policy, all employees must submit their reports by Friday afternoon. Management has made this requirement clear to ensure proper workflow.","translation":"關於新的公司政策，所有員工必須在星期五下午前提交報告。管理層已經明確了這一要求，以確保適當的工作流程。","word":"respecting"}},"restoration":{"createdAt":1781693295122,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"restoration 表示修復或恢復某物到原來的狀態，在這裡指藝術品的修復工作。","options":["destruction","restoration","removal","examination"],"sentence":"The old painting required careful ______ to bring back its original beauty. The art team spent months removing layers of dirt and repainting damaged sections.","translation":"這幅古老的畫作需要仔細的修復以恢復其原有的美麗。藝術團隊花費了數月時間去除汙垢層並重新繪製受損部分。","word":"restoration"}},"restrain":{"createdAt":1781777331351,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"restrain是動詞，意為阻止、制止或遏制某事物的發展或蔓延","options":["promote","distribute","restrain","encourage"],"sentence":"The government attempted to ______ the spread of misinformation during the crisis. Officials implemented strict regulations on media outlets to control what could be published.","translation":"政府試圖在危機期間阻止錯誤信息的傳播。官員們對媒體機構實施了嚴格的規定，以控制可以發表的內容。","word":"restrain"}},"restricted":{"createdAt":1781310338165,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"restricted 表示受到限制或約束，只有符合條件的人才能進入或使用。","options":["welcomed","restricted","encouraged","advertised"],"sentence":"Access to the top floor of the building is ______ to authorized personnel only. Visitors without proper identification cannot enter that area under any circumstances.","translation":"建築物頂層的通道僅限授權人員進入。沒有適當身份證明的訪客在任何情況下都無法進入該區域。","word":"restricted"}},"restriction":{"createdAt":1781871338556,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"restriction表示政府或組織對某項活動的限制性規定。","options":["permission","encouragement","limitation","requirement"],"sentence":"The government imposed a ______ on the export of certain technology to foreign countries. Companies must obtain special permits before selling these products abroad.","translation":"政府對向外國出口某些技術實施了限制。公司在向國外銷售這些產品之前必須獲得特殊許可證。","word":"restriction"}},"result":{"createdAt":1781950727567,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"result 作為動詞，指由於某原因而發生或產生某個結果。","options":["ignored","prevented","resulted","started"],"sentence":"The poor air quality ______ from industrial pollution in the region. Factories emit harmful gases that significantly damage the environment.","translation":"不良的空氣質量源於該地區的工業污染。工廠排放有害氣體，對環境造成重大損害。","word":"result"}},"resume":{"createdAt":1781749177486,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"resume 表示中斷後重新開始某項活動，這裡特別指會議在休息後繼續進行。","options":["conclude","commence","relocate","adjourn"],"sentence":"After the lunch break, the conference will ______ in the main auditorium. Attendees should expect the afternoon sessions to begin promptly at 1 PM.","translation":"午餐休息後，會議將在主禮堂重新開始。與會者應該預期下午會議將在下午1點準時開始。","word":"resume"}},"retailer":{"createdAt":1781715397125,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"retailer 意為「零售商」，指直接向消費者銷售商品的商家。","options":["manufacturer","retailer","supplier","wholesaler"],"sentence":"The local fashion ______ announced a massive sale to clear out last season's inventory from all their stores. Customers lined up before dawn to purchase discounted clothing at competitive prices.","translation":"當地服裝零售商宣佈進行大規模促銷，以清空所有門店的上季庫存。顧客在天亮前排隊，以競爭性的價格購買打折衣服。","word":"retailer"}},"retain":{"createdAt":1781777331357,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"retain是動詞，表示保留、保有或繼續擁有某人或某物","options":["dismiss","replace","retain","remove"],"sentence":"The school decided to ______ the same principal for another term due to his excellent leadership. Administrators believed his experience and vision were invaluable for the institution's continued growth.","translation":"由於這位校長的卓越領導力，學校決定保留他再任一個任期。管理人員認為他的經驗和遠景對機構的持續發展是無價的。","word":"retain"}},"revenue":{"createdAt":1781926464745,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"revenue 指政府或企業通過各種來源（如稅收、銷售）獲得的收益或歲入。","options":["expense","profit","revenue","loss"],"sentence":"The government collected significant ______ from taxes this quarter. These funds will be allocated to education, healthcare, and infrastructure projects.","translation":"政府在本季度從稅收中徵集了可觀的稅收收入。這些資金將被分配給教育、醫療和基礎設施項目。","word":"revenue"}},"reverse":{"createdAt":1781581925130,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"reverse 作為形容詞表示相反的一面或背面，指物體的另一側或相對的方向。","options":["opposite","reverse","inverse","backward"],"sentence":"The ______ side of the coin showed a different image than the front. When I flipped it over, I discovered an eagle engraved on the back.","translation":"硬幣的反面顯示的圖像與正面不同。當我翻轉它時，我發現背面刻著一隻鷹。","word":"reverse"}},"reversed":{"createdAt":1781362281725,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"reversed表示相反的、反轉的，指改變方向或返回先前的狀態。","options":["confirmed","reversed","approved","maintained"],"sentence":"The ______ decision meant they had to go back to their original plan. The previous ruling was overturned and everything returned to how it was before.","translation":"相反的決定意味著他們必須回到最初的計畫。之前的裁決被推翻，一切都回到了之前的樣子。","word":"reversed"}},"revival":{"createdAt":1781693281411,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"revival（復興）指某事物的重新興起、恢復流行或重新激發人們的興趣。","options":["decline","revival","division","survival"],"sentence":"The 1990s saw a ______ of interest in vintage fashion among young people. Thrift stores reported a significant increase in customers searching for retro clothing styles from previous decades.","translation":"1990年代見證了年輕人對復古時尚興趣的復興。舊衣店報告了尋找前幾十年復古服裝風格的顧客大幅增加。","word":"revival"}},"revive":{"createdAt":1781832761717,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"revive 表示使甦醒、使復原、使復興、使重新流行，指恢復某事物的生命力或受歡迎程度。","options":["destroyed","restored","forgotten","closed"],"sentence":"The old theater was successfully ______ after years of abandonment and restoration work. Audiences now flock to enjoy performances in the beautifully renovated venue.","translation":"經過多年的放棄和修復工作後，這家老劇院得以成功復興。觀眾現在紛紛前往在美麗翻新的場地享受表演。","word":"revive"}},"revolt":{"createdAt":1781824444628,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"revolt 動詞表示反抗權威或進行武裝起義，通常指大規模的抵抗運動。","options":["support","surrender","revolt","compromise"],"sentence":"The citizens began to ______ against the oppressive regime after decades of unfair treatment. They organized massive protests and demanded immediate political reforms throughout the country.","translation":"在數十年的不公平待遇後，市民開始反抗壓制性政權。他們組織了大規模抗議活動，並要求全國立即進行政治改革。","word":"revolt"}},"revolutionary":{"createdAt":1781832761718,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"revolutionary 是形容詞，表示革命性的、完全創新的，指帶來根本性變化的。","options":["traditional","ordinary","groundbreaking","conventional"],"sentence":"The smartphone technology was truly ______ when it first appeared on the market. It completely transformed how people communicated and accessed information in their daily lives.","translation":"智能手機技術在首次出現在市場上時確實是革命性的。它完全改變了人們在日常生活中如何溝通和獲取信息。","word":"revolutionary"}},"rib":{"createdAt":1781665727115,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rib 指人體胸腔的肋骨，是保護內臟器官的骨骼結構，共12對。","options":["shoulder","rib","ankle","finger"],"sentence":"The accident caused a severe fracture in his left ______, making it painful to breathe. The doctor recommended complete rest for six weeks to allow proper healing.","translation":"事故導致他左邊肋骨嚴重骨折，使呼吸變得痛苦。醫生建議完全休息六週以促進正確癒合。","word":"rib"}},"ridicule":{"createdAt":1781449095506,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ridicule意為嘲笑或戲弄，指用嘲諷的方式對待或評論他人。","options":["praise","ridicule","ignore","help"],"sentence":"The bully would ______ his classmate's appearance every day at school. The victim felt humiliated and hurt by these constant mocking comments.","translation":"霸凌者每天在學校嘲笑他同學的外貌。受害者因為這些不斷的嘲笑評論感到羞辱和受傷。","word":"ridicule"}},"riot":{"createdAt":1781665727113,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"riot 指暴亂或騷亂，指多人參與的暴力事件，伴隨破壞和混亂。","options":["parade","discussion","riot","seminar"],"sentence":"The protest escalated into a full-scale ______ when tensions between demonstrators and police became violent. Fires were set, windows were broken, and hundreds of people were injured.","translation":"當示威者和警察之間的衝突變成暴力事件時，抗議升級為全面的暴亂。火災被點燃，窗戶被打破，數百人受傷。","word":"riot"}},"rip":{"createdAt":1781840892407,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rip表示撕裂或撕破，描述衣物被利物割破的情況。","options":["fold","rip","iron","wash"],"sentence":"He accidentally ______ his new shirt on the sharp nail sticking out from the wall. The damage was so severe that the garment was no longer wearable.","translation":"他不小心在牆上突出的尖釘上撕破了他的新襯衫。損傷非常嚴重，以至於衣服不再可穿。","word":"rip"}},"ripe":{"createdAt":1781362281663,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ripe表示水果已經成熟，可以食用或採摘。","options":["green","ripe","frozen","sour"],"sentence":"The ______ fruit fell from the tree and was ready to eat. It had developed a sweet aroma and deep yellow color.","translation":"成熟的水果從樹上掉下來，已經可以吃了。它已經散發出甜蜜的香氣並呈現深黃色。","word":"ripe"}},"ripple":{"createdAt":1781869467058,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ripple 表示「漣漪、水面上的細浪」，指水面因外力而形成的波紋。","options":["current","wave","stream","splash"],"sentence":"When the stone dropped into the calm pond, it created a ______ that spread outward across the entire water surface. The concentric circles gradually became smaller and fainter as they moved away from the impact point.","translation":"當石頭掉入平靜的池塘時，它產生了一道漣漪，向外擴散到整個水面。當波紋遠離撞擊點時，同心圓逐漸變小變淡。","word":"ripple"}},"rise":{"createdAt":1781582424690,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"rise作為名詞表示上升或增加，與climbed higher and higher相符，fall(下降)、cycle(循環)和pattern(模式)都不符合。","options":["fall","cycle","rise","pattern"],"sentence":"The temperature showed a significant ______ over the past week. The thermometer climbed higher and higher each day.","translation":"過去一週內溫度出現了顯著的上升。溫度計每天都爬得越來越高。","word":"rise"}},"rising":{"createdAt":1781582251996,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"rising 是形容詞，表示在增加、上升或提高的趨勢。","options":["falling","stable","rising","freezing"],"sentence":"The ______ temperature in the city broke all previous records this summer. The thermometer continued to climb higher each day throughout July and August.","translation":"城市的上升溫度打破了今年夏天所有以前的記錄。整個七月和八月期間，溫度計每天都在持續上升。","word":"rising"}},"risky":{"createdAt":1781824444606,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"risky 形容詞表示某事物存在危險、損失或失敗的可能性，通常用於警告情境。","options":["safe","stable","risky","profitable"],"sentence":"Investing all your savings in a single startup is a ______ financial decision. Many experienced investors warn against putting money into unproven companies with uncertain futures.","translation":"將所有積蓄投資於單一初創公司是一個危險的財務決定。許多經驗豐富的投資者警告不要將資金投入於未經驗證且前景不確定的公司。","word":"risky"}},"rite":{"createdAt":1781429810243,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rite是指宗教或文化上的正式儀式或典禮，通常具有重要的象徵意義。","options":["detail","rite","firecracker","temperature"],"sentence":"The wedding ______ included exchanging vows and rings in front of family and friends. This sacred ceremony has been practiced in their culture for generations.","translation":"婚禮儀式包括在家人和朋友面前交換誓言和戒指。這個神聖的儀式在他們的文化中已經實踐了很多代。","word":"rite"}},"rod":{"createdAt":1781651261365,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rod在此指釣竿或其他長的杆狀物體，是一根可以拿握的硬棒形工具。","options":["treasury","rod","overtake","midst"],"sentence":"The fishing guide handed me a ______ and pointed toward the river. I held the long wooden shaft firmly and prepared to cast my line into the water.","translation":"釣魚嚮導遞給我一根竿，指向河流。我緊緊握住這根長木軸，準備將釣線投入水中。","word":"rod"}},"rotten":{"createdAt":1781625891336,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rotten表示食物或物品因腐朽、變質而不適合使用或食用","options":["fresh","rotten","sweet","firm"],"sentence":"The fruit had turned ______ and was covered in mold. We had to throw it away because it was no longer safe to eat.","translation":"水果已經腐爛並且長滿了黴菌。我們必須把它扔掉，因為它已經不安全食用了。","word":"rotten"}},"roughly":{"createdAt":1781848934137,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"roughly用來表示大概或大約，不是精確的數字","options":["exactly","roughly","legally","secretly"],"sentence":"The project will cost ______ $50,000 to complete. We might spend a bit more or less depending on unexpected expenses.","translation":"這個項目完成大約需要50,000美元。根據意外開支，我們可能花費更多或更少。","word":"roughly"}},"route":{"createdAt":1781431278557,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"route表示行進的路徑或途線，與destination（目的地）、vehicle（車輛）和schedule（時間表）不同。","options":["destination","route","vehicle","schedule"],"sentence":"The delivery driver took a different ______ to avoid traffic on the highway. He turned left at the intersection and followed the GPS directions through residential streets.","translation":"送貨司機採取了不同的路線以避免高速公路上的交通。他在十字路口向左轉，並按照GPS方向穿過住宅街道。","word":"route"}},"royal":{"createdAt":1781626081100,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"royal 作為形容詞表示與國王、皇帝或王室有關的，用於描述屬於或涉及統治階級的人物或事物。","options":["royal","common","ordinary","peasant"],"sentence":"The ______ family attended the grand ceremony in their ceremonial robes and jewels. Members of the palace, including the king and his immediate relatives, graced the event with their presence.","translation":"皇室成員穿著禮儀服飾和珠寶出席了盛大的典禮。宮殿成員，包括國王和他的直系親屬，出席了這項活動。","word":"royal"}},"rub":{"createdAt":1781661288532,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rub 是指用手或物體在表面上進行摩擦或按壓的動作","options":["ignore","rub","observe","measure"],"sentence":"The massage therapist began to ______ the client's sore shoulders with firm, circular motions. After thirty minutes of this soothing treatment, the patient's muscle tension finally started to release.","translation":"按摩治療師開始用有力的圓形動作摩擦客戶酸痛的肩膀。經過三十分鐘的舒緩治療後，患者的肌肉緊張終於開始釋放。","word":"rub"}},"rubbish":{"createdAt":1781746685497,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rubbish指的是垃圾、廢物，是日常生活中產生的不需要的物質。","options":["obedience","rubbish","miracle","tolerance"],"sentence":"The sanitation workers collected the ______ from every house on the street. They placed all the waste materials into the truck for disposal.","translation":"清潔工人從街上每棟房子收集垃圾。他們將所有廢棄物放入卡車中進行處理。","word":"rubbish"}},"rural":{"createdAt":1781832761717,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"rural 是形容詞，表示鄉村的、農村的，指與農業和開放鄉村相關的。","options":["urban","metropolitan","countryside","industrial"],"sentence":"The family moved to a ______ village far from the city to escape the hustle and bustle of urban life. They enjoyed the peaceful countryside atmosphere with farms and open fields all around.","translation":"全家遷到遠離城市的鄉村以逃離城市生活的喧囂。他們享受周圍農場和開闊田野的寧靜鄉村氛圍。","word":"rural"}},"rush":{"createdAt":1781951900954,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"rush表示倉促、急速地做某事，通常暗示不夠仔細或容易出錯，與「仔細做」相對立。","options":["complete","rush","finish","start"],"sentence":"Don't ______ through your homework; take your time to do it carefully and correctly. Hurrying often leads to silly mistakes that could have been avoided.","translation":"不要匆忙完成你的家庭作業；花時間仔細正確地做。急速完成往往會導致本可避免的愚蠢錯誤。","word":"rush"}},"ruthless":{"createdAt":1781693293272,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ruthless 是形容詞，意思是「無情的」、「冷酷的」或「殘忍的」，形容沒有同情心的人或行為。","options":["priceless","ruthless","executive","philosopher"],"sentence":"The dictator's ______ regime was responsible for countless human rights violations. Dissidents who opposed the government simply disappeared without a trace.","translation":"獨裁者的無情政權造成了無數的人權侵犯。反對政府的異議人士簡直是人間蒸發。","word":"ruthless"}},"sacrifice":{"createdAt":1781360333384,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"sacrifice 表示放棄或獻出某物以換取更重要的東西，常用於做出重大的犧牲。","options":["gain","preserve","sacrifice","enjoy"],"sentence":"The soldier was willing to ______ his life for his country. He knew that dying in battle was the ultimate price he might have to pay.","translation":"那位士兵願意為國家犧牲自己的生命。他知道在戰鬥中喪生是他可能要付出的最高代價。","word":"sacrifice"}},"sake":{"createdAt":1781360333390,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sake 表示目的、緣故或理由，常用於短語「for the sake of」表示為了某人或某事的利益。","options":["criticism","sake","amusement","debate"],"sentence":"For the ______ of his family's happiness, Mr. Chen decided to relocate to a safer neighborhood. He believed that protecting his loved ones was worth any personal inconvenience.","translation":"為了家人的幸福，陳先生決定搬到一個更安全的社區。他相信保護親人值得任何個人的不便。","word":"sake"}},"salary":{"createdAt":1781360333388,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"salary 是指員工由僱主按期支付的固定報酬，通常是按月或按年計算。","options":["gift","loan","salary","bonus"],"sentence":"The company offered John a monthly ______ of $3,500 for his new position. He was satisfied with the financial package they provided.","translation":"公司為約翰的新職位提供了每月3,500美元的薪水。他對他們提供的財務待遇感到滿意。","word":"salary"}},"salute":{"createdAt":1781794866348,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"salute在軍事環境中指敬禮，是向上級或旗幟表示尊敬的正式舉動。","options":["ignore","salute","insult","embrace"],"sentence":"The soldiers would ______ their commanding officer every morning at dawn. This gesture of respect was a mandatory military tradition that demonstrated obedience and discipline.","translation":"士兵們每天黎明時都會______ 他們的指揮官。這種尊敬的舉動是強制性的軍事傳統，表達了服從和紀律。","word":"salute"}},"salvage":{"createdAt":1781362281657,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"salvage表示搶救或搶救可用的東西，特別是從損壞或危險的情況中。","options":["damage","salvage","abandon","destroy"],"sentence":"The divers worked to ______ valuable items from the sunken ship. They managed to recover precious artifacts and cargo from the ocean floor.","translation":"潛水員努力從沉沒的船隻中搶救貴重物品。他們成功地從海底恢復了珍貴的文物和貨物。","word":"salvage"}},"sandal":{"createdAt":1781360333386,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"sandal 是一種開放式的鞋類，通常在溫暖的季節穿著，讓腳部能夠透氣。","options":["boot","sneaker","sandal","loafer"],"sentence":"On hot summer days, Tom prefers to wear a comfortable ______ instead of closed shoes. The open design allows his feet to breathe in the humid weather.","translation":"在炎熱的夏天，湯姆喜歡穿著舒適的涼鞋而不是封閉的鞋子。開放的設計使他的腳在潮濕的天氣中透氣。","word":"sandal"}},"satellite":{"createdAt":1781961466407,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"satellite 是指繞行星球運行的人造或天然天體，能夠從軌道上傳輸資料或進行觀測。","options":["satellite","telescope","rocket","drone"],"sentence":"The space agency launched a new ______ into orbit to improve weather forecasting across the region. This advanced equipment transmits data back to Earth every few minutes to monitor atmospheric conditions.","translation":"太空機構將一顆新的衛星發射到軌道上，以改進該地區的天氣預報。這套先進設備每隔幾分鐘就向地球傳輸資料以監測大氣狀況。","word":"satellite"}},"satisfaction":{"createdAt":1781360333385,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"satisfaction 是指對某事物感到滿足和高興的感受，通常來自達成目標或期望被滿足。","options":["confusion","frustration","satisfaction","exhaustion"],"sentence":"After completing her master's degree, Maria felt a sense of ______ with her academic achievements. She smiled knowing that all her hard work had finally paid off.","translation":"完成碩士學位後，瑪麗亞對自己的學術成就感到滿意。她微笑著，知道自己所有的辛苦最終得到了回報。","word":"satisfaction"}},"satisfied":{"createdAt":1781871338559,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"satisfied表示對某事物感到滿意，通常與positive的期望相反時會加上否定詞。","options":["happy","content","pleased","delighted"],"sentence":"The customer was not ______ with the quality of the product he received. He complained to the manager and requested a full refund.","translation":"客戶對他收到的產品品質不滿意。他向經理投訴並要求全額退款。","word":"satisfied"}},"satisfy":{"createdAt":1781360333391,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"satisfy 表示使人感到滿足和滿意，通常指滿足期望或需求。","options":["disappoint","annoy","satisfy","frustrate"],"sentence":"The restaurant's excellent service and delicious food helped ______ every customer who visited that evening. Many guests left positive reviews praising their overall experience.","translation":"餐廳的優質服務和美味食物使那天晚上光臨的每位顧客都感到滿足。許多客人留下了肯定的評價，讚揚他們的整體體驗。","word":"satisfy"}},"sauce":{"createdAt":1781311685840,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"sauce是一種調味液體或醬料，用來搭配食物以增加風味，不同於單純的香料或油。","options":["spice","oil","coating","seasoning"],"sentence":"She poured a delicious tomato ______ over the pasta to enhance its flavor. The condiment added a tangy and aromatic taste to the dish.","translation":"她將美味的番茄醬澆在意大利麵上以增強其風味。這種調料為這道菜增添了酸爽芳香的味道。","word":"sauce"}},"savage":{"createdAt":1781775276772,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"savage形容凶猛、野蠻、未被馴化的動物或人，符合不加警告攻擊的兇悍行為。","options":["gentle","tame","savage","friendly"],"sentence":"The ______ tiger attacked the hunter without warning or hesitation. Its wild and ferocious behavior showed no signs of domestication.","translation":"那隻兇猛的老虎毫無警告地攻擊了獵人。它野蠻兇悍的行為表明沒有被馴化的跡象。","word":"savage"}},"scarcity":{"createdAt":1781626081098,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"scarcity 指某種資源或物品供應不足、難以獲得的狀態，與 abundance、plenty、surplus 等表示充足的詞相反。","options":["abundance","plenty","scarcity","surplus"],"sentence":"The ______ of fresh water in the desert region forced residents to travel miles for drinking supplies. Without adequate rainfall for years, the local population struggled with severe shortages.","translation":"沙漠地區缺乏淡水，迫使居民要走很遠的路才能獲得飲用水。由於多年沒有充足的降雨，當地人口面臨嚴重的短缺。","word":"scarcity"}},"scenario":{"createdAt":1781849622418,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"設想場景是指一種可能發生的情況或假想的狀態，通常用於規劃、預測或分析可能的結果。","options":["achievement","scenario","document","budget"],"sentence":"In a worst-case ______, the company would lose half its revenue next year. Management discussed this possibility during the financial planning meeting to prepare contingency strategies.","translation":"在最壞的設想下，公司明年可能會失去一半的收入。管理層在財務規劃會議上討論了這種可能性以準備應急策略。","word":"scenario"}},"scent":{"createdAt":1781693266946,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"scent是指某物散發出來的氣味或香氣，也可作動詞表示嗅聞到。","options":["texture","scent","color","size"],"sentence":"The ______ of fresh roses filled the entire garden. I could smell the sweet fragrance from across the yard.","translation":"新鮮玫瑰的香味充滿了整個花園。我可以從院子的另一端聞到這股甜蜜的香氣。","word":"scent"}},"schedule":{"createdAt":1781837601401,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"schedule 作為名詞表示「時間表」，指按照順序安排的時間計畫，通常詳細列出各個活動或事件的時間。","options":["calendar","schedule","syllabus","notebook"],"sentence":"The teacher posted the class ______ on the bulletin board so students would know when each lesson starts. All the time slots were filled in clearly for the entire semester.","translation":"老師將課程時間表貼在公告欄上，以便學生知道每堂課何時開始。整個學期的所有時間段都清楚地填入了。","word":"schedule"}},"scoop":{"createdAt":1781360333389,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"scoop 表示用勺子或類似工具舀取或挖取物品的動作。","options":["pour","mix","scoop","spread"],"sentence":"Using a large wooden spoon, the chef began to ______ ice cream into bowls for the dessert course. The creamy vanilla melted slightly as it fell into each dish.","translation":"主廚用一把大木勺開始用舀的方式將冰淇淋放入碗中作為甜點。奶油狀的香草冰淇淋在掉入每個碗時略微融化。","word":"scoop"}},"scope":{"createdAt":1781848934145,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"scope指某項活動、研究或工作所涵蓋的範圍或限制","options":["cost","scope","success","criticism"],"sentence":"The ______ of this research project is limited to North American universities only. We cannot include data from European institutions due to time constraints.","translation":"這個研究項目的範圍僅限於北美大學。由於時間限制，我們無法納入來自歐洲機構的數據。","word":"scope"}},"score":{"createdAt":1781360333392,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"score 作為動詞表示在比賽中得分或獲得分數，是體育競技中的常用詞彙。","options":["lose","score","defend","catch"],"sentence":"The basketball player was thrilled to ______ thirty points in the championship game, leading his team to victory. The crowd cheered wildly as the final buzzer sounded.","translation":"籃球運動員在錦標賽比賽中得到三十分而感到高興，帶領他的隊伍贏得勝利。當最後的蜂鳴聲響起時，觀眾歡聲雷動。","word":"score"}},"scramble":{"createdAt":1781449095509,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"scramble意為急忙移動、攀爬或爭搶，通常帶有緊急或混亂的意味。","options":["walk","scramble","sit","wait"],"sentence":"When the fire alarm sounded, all the employees had to ______ out of the building quickly. Everyone rushed toward the emergency exits in panic.","translation":"當火災警報聲響起時，所有員工都必須快速爬出大樓。每個人都驚慌地衝向緊急出口。","word":"scramble"}},"scrambled":{"createdAt":1781661288530,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"scrambled 是指蛋類烹飪方法，將打散的蛋液在鍋中攪拌加熱，也可表示打亂或混亂","options":["fried","scrambled","boiled","poached"],"sentence":"The ______ eggs were served with toast and bacon for breakfast. The chef had mixed the raw eggs vigorously in the pan until they formed soft, fluffy curds.","translation":"炒蛋配吐司和培根作為早餐上桌。廚師在平底鍋中將生雞蛋用力攪拌，直到形成柔軟蓬鬆的凝塊。","word":"scrambled"}},"scrap":{"createdAt":1781955529034,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"scrap 作為動詞表示放棄、取消或廢除某個計畫、項目或想法。","options":["launch","scrap","revise","postpone"],"sentence":"After the budget cuts, the company decided to ______ the expansion project entirely. All the blueprints and preliminary designs were thrown away, and the initiative was completely abandoned.","translation":"在預算削減後，公司決定完全放棄擴展項目。所有的藍圖和初步設計都被丟棄，該計畫被徹底放棄。","word":"scrap"}},"scratch":{"createdAt":1781939439461,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"scratch作動詞表示用爪子或尖銳物體在表面留下痕跡，動物常用爪子抓撓物體。","options":["paint","scratch","polish","measure"],"sentence":"The cat began to ______ at the furniture with its sharp claws. Within minutes, deep marks appeared on the wooden armchair where it had been digging in.","translation":"貓開始用銳利的爪子抓家具。幾分鐘內，木製扶手椅上出現了深深的痕跡，那是它挖掘留下的。","word":"scratch"}},"script":{"createdAt":1781531595648,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"script 是指電影、戲劇或電視節目的原稿或台詞，演員需要根據劇本表演。","options":["schedule","script","contract","proposal"],"sentence":"The actor received the ______ from the director just before filming began. The handwritten notes in the margins showed the director's personal instructions for each scene.","translation":"演員在開始拍攝前從導演那裡收到了原稿。邊際的手寫註釋顯示了導演對每個場景的個人指導。","word":"script"}},"scroll":{"createdAt":1781360333391,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"scroll 表示向上或向下移動來查看電子屏幕上的更多內容，或展開捲軸查看內容。","options":["jump","scroll","flip","skip"],"sentence":"As Sarah continued to ______ down her social media feed, she discovered an interesting article about ancient history. Hours passed as she kept moving through endless posts.","translation":"當莎拉繼續滾動瀏覽她的社交媒體動態時，她發現了一篇有趣的古代歷史文章。當她不斷翻閱無數的帖子時，幾個小時過去了。","word":"scroll"}},"sculptor":{"createdAt":1781360333386,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"sculptor 是指專門從事雕刻或塑造作品的藝術家，通常用石頭或其他材料創作。","options":["painter","musician","sculptor","architect"],"sentence":"The famous ______ spent decades carving marble and bronze into beautiful works of art. His studio was filled with chisels, hammers, and partially completed statues.","translation":"那位著名的雕塑家花費數十年將大理石和青銅雕刻成美麗的藝術作品。他的工作室裡擺滿了鑿子、錘子和未完成的雕像。","word":"sculptor"}},"sculpture":{"createdAt":1781832508020,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sculpture 表示「雕塑；雕刻」，指用石頭、木頭、金屬等材料製成的立體藝術作品。","options":["painting","sculpture","poem","symphony"],"sentence":"The museum's newest acquisition is a bronze ______ created by a renowned artist in the 19th century. Visitors can admire the intricate details of the carved figures from multiple angles in the main gallery.","translation":"博物館最新的收藏品是由一位著名藝術家在19世紀創作的青銅雕塑。遊客可以在主畫廊中從多個角度欣賞雕刻人物的複雜細節。","word":"sculpture"}},"seal":{"createdAt":1781926464746,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"seal 作為動詞表示用材料或方法將東西密封起來，防止漏水或空氣進入。","options":["open","crack","seal","expose"],"sentence":"The contractor will ______ the roof with waterproof material before winter arrives. This protective barrier will prevent rain and snow from leaking into the building.","translation":"承包商將在冬天到來之前用防水材料密封屋頂。這層保護屏障將防止雨和雪滲入建築物。","word":"seal"}},"season":{"createdAt":1781832478023,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"season 意為「季節」，用來指一年中特定的時間段，如春、夏、秋、冬。","options":["week","holiday","season","year"],"sentence":"Winter is my favorite ______ because I love the cold weather and snow. During these months, I enjoy skiing and building snowmen with my friends.","translation":"冬天是我最喜歡的季節，因為我喜歡寒冷的天氣和雪。在這些月份裡，我喜歡和朋友滑雪和堆雪人。","word":"season"}},"section":{"createdAt":1781746685504,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"section指的是部份、區域、地域，表示某個整體中分開的一部分或特定的地區。","options":["section","consequence","miracle","laborious"],"sentence":"The library's reference ______ contains all the important dictionaries and encyclopedias. Students can find maps and atlases in that particular area of the building.","translation":"圖書館的參考書區包含所有重要的字典和百科全書。學生可以在建築的那個特定區域找到地圖和地理誌。","word":"section"}},"seek":{"createdAt":1781839703148,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"seek意為尋求、尋找，與fled their homeland和need for shelter（逃離祖國和需要庇護）的語境完全相符。","options":["abandon","reject","seek","avoid"],"sentence":"Many refugees ______ shelter and safety in neighbouring countries. They fled their homeland due to ongoing conflict and persecution.","translation":"許多難民在鄰國尋求庇護和安全。他們因持續的衝突和迫害而逃離了祖國。","word":"seek"}},"seem":{"createdAt":1781832508016,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"seem 表示「似乎；仿佛」，用來描述表面上的印象或感覺，常用於帶有轉折的語境中。","options":["appear","seem","look","sound"],"sentence":"The old house might ______ abandoned, but the owner still lives there. Upon closer inspection, we discovered furniture inside and fresh food in the kitchen.","translation":"這棟老房子似乎被遺棄了，但業主仍然住在那裡。經過仔細檢查，我們發現裡面有傢俱和新鮮食物在廚房裡。","word":"seem"}},"seemingly":{"createdAt":1781746848185,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"seemingly 表示「表面上」或「看起來」，指事物在外表上的樣子，但實際可能不同。","options":["definitely","seemingly","certainly","obviously"],"sentence":"The project appeared ______ simple at first glance. However, when the team started working on it, they discovered numerous hidden complications.","translation":"這個項目乍一看似乎很簡單。不過，當團隊開始著手時，他們發現了許多隱藏的複雜性。","word":"seemingly"}},"segment":{"createdAt":1781950727560,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"segment 表示整體中的一個部分或分割的一部分。","options":["majority","segment","company","product"],"sentence":"The market research team analyzed a specific ______ of the customer population. They focused only on female consumers aged 25 to 40 for their study.","translation":"市場研究團隊分析了客戶群體的特定部分。他們的研究只針對年齡在25至40歲的女性消費者。","word":"segment"}},"seize":{"createdAt":1781787229330,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"seize 表示迅速而用力地抓住或奪取某物，通常帶有緊急或強制的含義。","options":["ignore","examine","seize","follow"],"sentence":"The police officer managed to ______ the suspect's weapon before anyone got hurt. The quick action prevented a potential tragedy at the store.","translation":"警察在任何人受傷前成功地奪取了嫌疑人的武器。這次迅速的行動防止了商店內可能發生的悲劇。","word":"seize"}},"seizure":{"createdAt":1781869467056,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"seizure 在此表示「奪取、沒收」，指官方機構依法扣押和沒收的違禁品。","options":["loss","confiscation","discussion","prevention"],"sentence":"The customs officers made a major ______ of illegal drugs at the airport last week. The confiscated packages contained over 100 kilograms of contraband material.","translation":"海關官員上週在機場進行了一次重大毒品查獲行動。繳獲的包裹含有超過100公斤的走私物品。","word":"seizure"}},"seminar":{"createdAt":1781950727561,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"seminar 指一種教育活動，通常涉及專家和參與者之間的討論和學習。","options":["movie","concert","seminar","party"],"sentence":"She attended a ______ on digital marketing strategies last week. The workshop included interactive discussions with industry experts for two hours.","translation":"她上週參加了一個關於數位行銷策略的研討會。該研討會包括與業內專家進行兩小時的互動討論。","word":"seminar"}},"senior":{"createdAt":1781345746901,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"senior 用作形容詞，表示年資較久、地位較高的人，與 junior（資淺的）相對。","options":["junior","senior","lateral","external"],"sentence":"My ______ colleague has been working at the company for over twenty years. He mentors the newer employees and holds significant authority in our department.","translation":"我的前輩同事在公司工作已經超過二十年了。他指導新員工，在我們部門中擁有重要的權力。","word":"senior"}},"sensation":{"createdAt":1781848934136,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sensation指引起廣泛注意或引發強烈反應的事件或情況","options":["silence","sensation","disappointment","delay"],"sentence":"When the celebrity arrived at the event, their presence caused a great ______. Fans screamed and pushed forward, creating chaos everywhere.","translation":"當這位名人抵達活動時，他們的出現引起了巨大的轟動。粉絲尖叫著向前推擠，到處都是混亂。","word":"sensation"}},"sensibly":{"createdAt":1781449588287,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"sensibly作為副詞表示「明智地、合理地」，指以理性、謹慎且明智的方式行動或思考。","options":["sensibly","trillion","glorify","defensive"],"sentence":"The financial advisor recommended that her clients invest their money ______ by diversifying their portfolio across different asset classes. This prudent approach helped protect their savings from excessive risk and volatility.","translation":"理財顧問建議她的客戶通過將投資組合分散到不同資產類別來明智地投資他們的金錢。這種謹慎的方法有助於保護他們的儲蓄免受過度風險和波動性。","word":"sensibly"}},"sensitivity":{"createdAt":1781424574159,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sensitivity 在此指對他人感受的敏銳體察和善解人意的能力。","options":["ignorance","sensitivity","criticism","distance"],"sentence":"The therapist's ______ to her clients' emotional needs made her an excellent counselor. She always noticed when someone was upset and responded with compassion and understanding.","translation":"治療師對客戶情感需求的體貼使她成為一名優秀的顧問。她總是注意到有人不開心，並以同情和理解來回應。","word":"sensitivity"}},"sentiment":{"createdAt":1781869467057,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sentiment 在此表示「看法、意見」，指大眾對某件事物所持的態度或觀點。","options":["weather","opinion","distance","silence"],"sentence":"The survey revealed that public ______ toward the new policy was overwhelmingly negative. Most respondents expressed strong disapproval and concern about its potential impact.","translation":"調查顯示公眾對新政策的看法絕大多數是負面的。大多數受訪者表達了強烈的反對和對其潛在影響的擔憂。","word":"sentiment"}},"separation":{"createdAt":1781773623454,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"separation作為名詞表示「分離」或「分開」，強調原本統一或相連的事物被分開的狀態。","options":["division","separation","boundary","border"],"sentence":"The ______ between the two countries lasted for decades until they finally reunited. Both sides had built walls and borders to keep their populations apart during this period.","translation":"兩國之間的分離持續了數十年，直到他們最終重新統一。在這一時期，雙方都建造了牆壁和邊界來讓他們的人口分開。","word":"separation"}},"serenity":{"createdAt":1781738105696,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"serenity 指的是一種寧靜、平和和安詳的狀態，通常帶來心靈的平靜。","options":["chaos","serenity","excitement","tension"],"sentence":"She found ______ in the quiet garden, surrounded by blooming flowers and gentle birdsong. The peaceful atmosphere helped her forget about all her work-related stress and worries.","translation":"她在寧靜的花園中找到了平靜，四周環繞著盛開的花朵和溫柔的鳥鳴。這種平和的氛圍幫助她忘記了所有與工作相關的壓力和煩惱。","word":"serenity"}},"sergeant":{"createdAt":1781493458240,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sergeant 是軍銜，指軍隊中的士官階級，擁有領導和下達命令的權限","options":["major","sergeant","doctor","teacher"],"sentence":"The ______ barked orders at the soldiers during the morning drill. He was a military officer with years of experience leading troops in the field.","translation":"這位軍士在早上訓練時對士兵們發出命令。他是一位有多年率領部隊作戰經驗的軍事長官。","word":"sergeant"}},"serial":{"createdAt":1781619188915,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"serial 指連續的、一連串的，通常用來描述重複發生的事件或行為。","options":["isolated","serial","random","accidental"],"sentence":"The ______ killer was arrested after committing crimes across multiple cities over several years. Investigators discovered a pattern of similar offenses spanning a decade.","translation":"連環殺手在多個城市犯下多起罪行多年後被逮捕。調查人員發現了跨越十年的一系列相似犯罪模式。","word":"serial"}},"serve":{"createdAt":1781437220550,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「Serve」在此表示提供食物或飲料給客人，是餐飲業的常見用法。","options":["consume","serve","purchase","store"],"sentence":"The restaurant will ______ dinner at 6 PM every evening. The head chef personally prepares each dish to be presented to our guests.","translation":"這家餐廳每晚將在6點提供晚餐。主廚親自準備每一道菜肴呈獻給我們的客人。","word":"serve"}},"shabby":{"createdAt":1781843487265,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"shabby 是形容詞，表示衣服或物品破爛、磨損、不整潔的樣子。","options":["expensive","pristine","shabby","fashionable"],"sentence":"His ______ coat had holes in the sleeves and a missing button. He could barely afford new clothes because he had lost his job six months ago.","translation":"他破舊的外套袖子上有洞，還缺了一個鈕扣。他因為六個月前失業，幾乎買不起新衣服。","word":"shabby"}},"shade":{"createdAt":1781452425260,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"shade表示陰涼處或被遮蔽的地方，可以保護人們免受烈日照射。","options":["light","open","shelter","darkness"],"sentence":"During the hot summer day, the children played in the ______ of the large oak tree. The temperature there was at least ten degrees cooler than in the direct sunlight.","translation":"在炎熱的夏日，孩子們在大橡樹的陰涼處玩耍。那裡的溫度至少比直射陽光下低十度。","word":"shade"}},"shareholder":{"createdAt":1781424157173,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"shareholder 指的是擁有公司股票或股份的人，具有投票權和經濟利益。","options":["employee","shareholder","customer","director"],"sentence":"Each ______ of the company was invited to attend the annual meeting to vote on important business matters. The meeting included representatives from over 500 investors who owned pieces of the company.","translation":"公司的每位股東都被邀請參加年度會議以對重要的商業事項進行投票。會議包括來自超過500位擁有公司股份的投資者代表。","word":"shareholder"}},"sharp":{"createdAt":1781951900953,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sharp在這裡指刀刃銳利、鋒利，能夠進行精確切割而不會損傷食材。","options":["dull","sharp","heavy","old"],"sentence":"The chef used a ______ knife to slice the vegetables with precision and efficiency. The blade cut through the produce without any crushing or tearing.","translation":"廚師用一把鋒利的刀子精確而有效地切割蔬菜。刀片切過農產品時沒有任何壓碎或撕裂。","word":"sharp"}},"shed":{"createdAt":1781665727114,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"shed 指動物自然地脫落或掉落毛髮、皮膚或其他物質的過程。","options":["stretched","shed","stored","painted"],"sentence":"The dog ______ its thick winter coat every spring when the weather became warmer. The groomer had to brush out pounds of fur during each appointment.","translation":"每年春天天氣變暖時，狗都會脫去厚重的冬毛。美容師在每次預約時都要梳掉幾磅的毛髮。","word":"shed"}},"sheer":{"createdAt":1781449095513,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sheer意為完全的、徹底的，用來強調某種品質或程度的絕對性或極端性。","options":["partial","sheer","slight","minimal"],"sentence":"The ______ determination of the athlete helped her win the championship despite her injuries. She never gave up, no matter how difficult the competition became.","translation":"這位運動員完全的決心幫助她在受傷的情況下贏得了冠軍。無論比賽變得多麼困難，她都從未放棄。","word":"sheer"}},"shelf":{"createdAt":1781311922069,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"shelf 是指附著在牆上或家具上的水平面，用來放置物品。","options":["counter","shelf","desk","cabinet"],"sentence":"The library organized all the books on a tall wooden ______ near the entrance. Visitors could easily see the new arrivals displayed on the second level of the structure.","translation":"圖書館在入口附近的高木製架子上組織所有書籍。訪客可以輕易看到在這個結構的第二層展示的新書。","word":"shelf"}},"shelter":{"createdAt":1781484415232,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"shelter是指提供保護和避難的地方，保護人們免受惡劣環境或危險。","options":["danger","shelter","challenge","opportunity"],"sentence":"The homeless people found ______ in the old warehouse during the harsh winter storm. The building provided them with protection from the freezing wind and heavy snow.","translation":"無家可歸的人在嚴寒的冬季暴風雪中在舊倉庫裡找到了避難所。這棟建築為他們提供了免受刺骨寒風和大雪的保護。","word":"shelter"}},"shelves":{"createdAt":1781532967168,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"shelves 指擱板、架子，與「在其上放置書籍」和「五個水平面」的描述相符。","options":["cabinets","shelves","drawers","closets"],"sentence":"She organized all her books neatly on the wooden ______ in the living room. The library furniture had five levels where different collections could be displayed.","translation":"她在客廳的木製______(架子)上整齊地整理了所有的書。這個圖書館家具有五個水平面可以展示不同的收藏。","word":"shelves"}},"shift":{"createdAt":1781841742845,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"shift 作動詞表示「改變、轉移」，在此語境中指改變策略方向或優先順序。","options":["maintain","shift","ignore","reverse"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ its focus from product quantity to product quality. Management announced this strategic change at the quarterly board meeting.","translation":"該公司決定將重點從產品數量轉移到產品質量。管理層在季度董事會會議上宣佈了這一戰略改變。","word":"shift"}},"shortsighted":{"createdAt":1781926464746,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"shortsighted 形容缺乏遠見卓識，只關注眼前利益而忽視長期後果的人或政策。","options":["visionary","strategic","shortsighted","innovative"],"sentence":"The company's ______ business strategy focused only on next quarter's profits. As a result, they failed to invest in innovation and eventually lost market share to competitors.","translation":"該公司目光短淺的商業策略只關注下一季度的利潤。結果，他們未能投資於創新，最終將市場份額失給了競爭對手。","word":"shortsighted"}},"showcase":{"createdAt":1781564440923,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"showcase 作動詞表示展示、展出，指為了凸顯優點而展示某物。","options":["hide","showcase","ignore","criticize"],"sentence":"The fashion show will ______ the designer's latest collection. The models will wear all the new outfits on the runway to highlight their beauty and craftsmanship.","translation":"時裝秀將展示設計師的最新系列。模特會在跑道上穿著所有新服裝，突出它們的美感和工藝。","word":"showcase"}},"shrill":{"createdAt":1781738724025,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"shrill用來形容令人不快的尖銳刺耳的聲音，特別是高音量的聲音會讓人感到不適。","options":["melodious","shrill","gentle","muted"],"sentence":"The ______ sound of the alarm clock pierced through the quiet bedroom at 6 AM. My ears rang painfully as the high-pitched noise continued blaring without stopping.","translation":"鬧鐘刺耳的聲音在早上六點刺穿了安靜的臥室。當這個高頻率的噪音持續不停地響起時，我的耳朵疼痛地嗡嗡作響。","word":"shrill"}},"shrink":{"createdAt":1781257238302,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"shrink指物體體積或尺寸變小，常用於描述織物經過洗滌或乾燥後的變化。","options":["expand","shrink","fade","stretch"],"sentence":"The wool sweater will ______ if you wash it in hot water. After one cycle in the dryer, it became two sizes smaller and no longer fit.","translation":"如果你用熱水洗羊毛毛衣，它會縮小。在烘乾機中轉一圈後，它縮小了兩個尺碼，不再合身。","word":"shrink"}},"shrub":{"createdAt":1781693270388,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"shrub指「灌木」，是一種比樹木矮小、有多個主幹的木本植物。","options":["tree","shrub","vine","flower"],"sentence":"The gardener planted a flowering ______ along the garden pathway to add color and texture. This woody plant was perfect for the space because it stayed relatively small and required minimal pruning.","translation":"園丁沿著花園小徑種植了一株開花灌木來增添顏色和質感。這種木本植物非常適合這個空間，因為它保持相對較小的尺寸且需要最少的修剪。","word":"shrub"}},"shuttle":{"createdAt":1781532967168,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"shuttle 指穿梭運行的交通工具，與「在兩地之間往返運送」和「定時服務」的描述相符。","options":["taxi","shuttle","ambulance","truck"],"sentence":"The airport ______ service provided free transportation between the terminal and the parking lot. Passengers could ride it every fifteen minutes without paying.","translation":"機場______(接駁車)服務在航站樓和停車場之間提供免費運輸。乘客可以每十五分鐘乘坐一次，無需付費。","word":"shuttle"}},"sideways":{"createdAt":1781709984194,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sideways 是副詞，表示向一側或側向移動，身體與前進方向垂直。","options":["backward","sideways","forward","diagonally"],"sentence":"The crab moved ______ across the sandy beach toward the ocean. Its body was turned at a ninety-degree angle to its direction of travel.","translation":"螃蟹橫著身體沿著沙灘向海洋移動。它的身體與移動方向成九十度角。","word":"sideways"}},"sigh":{"createdAt":1781478568769,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sigh 表示因疲勞、失望或放鬆而發出的長呼氣聲。","options":["whisper","sigh","laugh","shout"],"sentence":"She began to ______ heavily as she reviewed the stack of unfinished work on her desk. Her exhausted expression revealed her frustration and fatigue.","translation":"當她看著桌上未完成的工作堆時，她開始重重地嘆氣。她疲憊的表情表露了她的沮喪和疲勞。","word":"sigh"}},"sign":{"createdAt":1781841742845,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"sign 作名詞表示「簽名」，指一個人的親筆簽字或姓名的手寫形式。","options":["approval","signal","signature","gesture"],"sentence":"The celebrity was asked for her ______ on the poster, which she wrote with a special pen. Fans lined up for hours just to receive her autographed memorabilia.","translation":"這位名人被要求在海報上簽名，她用特殊的筆簽下了名字。粉絲們排隊數小時只為了得到她簽名的紀念品。","word":"sign"}},"signal":{"createdAt":1781362281666,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"signal表示發出信號或信號本身，用於傳達信息或指示。","options":["ignore","signal","watch","follow"],"sentence":"The coach ______ to the player to make a substitution. The specific hand gesture communicated the desired action from the sideline.","translation":"教練向球員發出信號進行替換。這個特定的手勢從場邊傳達了所需的行動。","word":"signal"}},"signature":{"createdAt":1781481124702,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"signature 指某人親筆簽名，用於表示身份確認或同意。","options":["initials","name","seal","handwriting"],"sentence":"The contract was not valid until both parties provided their ______ at the bottom. The legal document required authentic written authorization from each representative.","translation":"合約在雙方在底部簽字之前是無效的。該法律文件需要每位代表的真實書面授權。","word":"signature"}},"signify":{"createdAt":1781449588286,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"signify作為動詞表示「表示、意指、象徵」，指通過符號、標誌或動作來表達某種意思或信息。","options":["regulate","sensibly","signify","phenomenon"],"sentence":"The red traffic light does ______ that drivers must stop their vehicles immediately. This universal symbol is recognized worldwide as a clear instruction to halt before proceeding.","translation":"紅色交通燈表示駕駛員必須立即停止他們的車輛。這個普遍的符號在世界各地都被認識為清楚的停止指令。","word":"signify"}},"silent":{"createdAt":1781848934147,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"silent指完全沒有聲音或寂靜的狀態","options":["crowded","silent","chaotic","empty"],"sentence":"The library was completely ______ during exam week. Students studied intently without making any noise or distractions.","translation":"考試週期間圖書館完全寂靜無聲。學生們集中精力學習，沒有任何噪音或干擾。","word":"silent"}},"similar":{"createdAt":1781784910908,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"similar 表示有相同或共同特徵，但不一定完全相同；這裡用 however 轉折，強調儘管時代不同，兩幅畫在藝術風格上卻相似。","options":["different","similar","identical","opposite"],"sentence":"The two paintings are ______ in style and composition. However, one was created in the 19th century while the other was painted just last year.","translation":"這兩幅畫在風格和構圖上是相似的。然而，其中一幅創作於19世紀，另一幅則是去年才完成的。","word":"similar"}},"similarity":{"createdAt":1781401591593,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"similarity 是指兩個或多個事物之間的相同或相似的特徵。","options":["difference","similarity","contrast","distance"],"sentence":"There is a striking ______ between the two paintings, even though they were created by different artists. Both artworks feature the same color palette and landscape composition.","translation":"這兩幅畫之間有著令人驚訝的相似之處，儘管它們是由不同的藝術家創作的。兩件藝術作品都採用相同的調色板和風景構圖。","word":"similarity"}},"simple":{"createdAt":1781709984196,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"simple 形容詞表示容易理解或做到的，不複雜、不繁瑣的。","options":["basic","simple","small","short"],"sentence":"The recipe is quite ______ and requires only five basic ingredients. Even children can follow the straightforward instructions without any difficulty.","translation":"這個食譜很簡單，只需要五種基本材料。甚至小孩都可以輕鬆按照直接的說明進行操作。","word":"simple"}},"simplify":{"createdAt":1781693295125,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"simplify 表示使某事變得簡單或容易，在此指教授簡化複雜的數學內容。","options":["complicate","simplify","ignore","translate"],"sentence":"The professor decided to ______ the complex mathematical formula for beginner students. She broke it down into smaller steps and provided clear examples that made the concept easier to follow.","translation":"教授決定為初學者學生簡化複雜的數學公式。她將其分解成更小的步驟，並提供了清晰的範例以使概念更容易理解。","word":"simplify"}},"singular":{"createdAt":1781653278509,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"singular是形容詞，表示單數的，與複數形式相對，用來描述只代表一個人或物的語法形式。","options":["plural","singular","possessive","abstract"],"sentence":"The teacher asked the student to identify the ______ form of the noun 'children'. The correct answer was 'child', which refers to only one person.","translation":"老師要求學生識別名詞「children」的______形式。正確答案是「child」，它指的是只有一個人。","word":"singular"}},"site":{"createdAt":1781848934145,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"site指建築或某項工程進行的地點或地理位置","options":["website","site","office","store"],"sentence":"The construction ______ is located just outside the city center. Workers have already begun drilling and preparing the land for the new shopping mall.","translation":"建築工地位於城市中心外。工人已經開始鑽孔並為新購物商場準備土地。","word":"site"}},"situated":{"createdAt":1781950727565,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"situated 表示坐落在或位於某個特定位置。","options":["built","situated","named","designed"],"sentence":"The hotel is ______ near the beach and within walking distance of downtown. Guests enjoy easy access to both nature and urban attractions.","translation":"這家酒店位於靠近海灘的地方，距離市中心步行距離內。客人可以輕鬆前往自然和城市景點。","word":"situated"}},"skeleton":{"createdAt":1781665727114,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"skeleton 指事物的基本框架或梗概，省略細節，只保留主要結構或要點。","options":["museum","skeleton","library","obstacle"],"sentence":"The project manager created a ______ of the business plan to present the main ideas clearly. It outlined only the essential steps and timelines without minor details.","translation":"項目經理為商業計劃製作了一個梗概，以清楚地呈現主要想法。它只概述了基本步驟和時間表，沒有細節。","word":"skeleton"}},"skeptical":{"createdAt":1781784910912,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"skeptical 表示持懷疑態度、不相信；第二句強調她傾向於質疑和不信任，與懷疑的態度完全吻合。","options":["excited","trusting","skeptical","optimistic"],"sentence":"She was ______ about the company's promises of guaranteed profits within a month. Her years of experience in finance had taught her to question unrealistic claims.","translation":"她對這家公司在一個月內保證獲利的承諾持懷疑態度。她多年的金融經驗教會她質疑不切實際的說法。","word":"skeptical"}},"skull":{"createdAt":1781414884516,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"skull指頭蓋骨或顱骨，是頭部骨骼結構的總稱，常在考古挖掘中被發現。","options":["skull","pottery","artifact","fossil"],"sentence":"The archaeologist carefully excavated the ancient ______ from the burial site. The bone structure revealed important information about the person who had lived thousands of years ago.","translation":"考古學家小心翼翼地從埋藏地點挖掘出古代頭蓋骨。骨骼結構揭示了數千年前生活的人的重要信息。","word":"skull"}},"slavery":{"createdAt":1781693265625,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"蓄奴是指強迫他人成為奴隸並從事無償勞動的非人道制度。","options":["agriculture","slavery","democracy","trade"],"sentence":"The abolition of ______ in the 19th century marked a turning point in human rights. Millions of people were finally freed from forced labor and cruel treatment.","translation":"十九世紀廢除奴隸制度標誌著人權的轉折點。數百萬人終於從強制勞動和殘酷待遇中解放出來。","word":"slavery"}},"slay":{"createdAt":1781443653215,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"slay是指殺死或摧毀，在這個語境中用來描述龍對村莊造成的致命傷害。","options":["protect","slay","befriend","nurture"],"sentence":"The dragon was said to ______ entire villages in ancient legends. Warriors spent years searching for the beast that had caused such terrible destruction.","translation":"傳說中那條龍在古老的傳說裡曾殘殺過整個村莊。戰士們花了數年時間尋找造成如此可怕破壞的野獸。","word":"slay"}},"slim":{"createdAt":1781767999781,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"slim 作為形容詞表示身材苗條、纖瘦，通常帶有正面的健康含義。","options":["tall","slim","strong","muscular"],"sentence":"After six months of exercise and healthy eating, Marcus achieved his goal of having a ______ physique. His doctor noted that his improved fitness levels had significantly enhanced his overall health.","translation":"經過六個月的運動和健康飲食後，馬庫斯達到了擁有苗條身材的目標。他的醫生指出他改善的體能水平大大提升了他的整體健康。","word":"slim"}},"slogan":{"createdAt":1781770031230,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"口號是指為了宣傳或推廣目的而創作的簡潔、容易記住的短語或格言。","options":["billboard","slogan","jingle","mascot"],"sentence":"The company's marketing team created a memorable ______ to promote their new product. The phrase \"Just Do It\" became so iconic that customers immediately recognized the brand.","translation":"行銷團隊創造了一個容易記住的口號來推廣他們的新產品。「Just Do It」這句話變得如此標誌性，以至於顧客立即認出了這個品牌。","word":"slogan"}},"sloppy":{"createdAt":1781824444650,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"sloppy 形容詞表示馬虎、不細心、不整潔或工作品質差。","options":["careful","precise","sloppy","organized"],"sentence":"The restaurant received a failing health inspection due to ______ food preparation and poor sanitation standards. The inspector found uncovered dishes, dirty utensils, and improper storage of raw ingredients.","translation":"該餐廳因食物準備馬虎和衛生標準差而收到健康檢查不合格。檢查員發現未蓋好的菜肴、骯髒的餐具和生食材料儲存不當。","word":"sloppy"}},"slump":{"createdAt":1781452425261,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"slump表示急劇下降或暴跌，通常用來形容價格、銷售或經濟指標的大幅下滑。","options":["rise","stabilize","soar","plummet"],"sentence":"The company's stock price began to ______ after the negative earnings report was released. Investors immediately started selling their shares, pushing the value down by 25%.","translation":"負面收益報告發佈後，公司股價開始暴跌。投資者立即開始拋售股票，將價值下跌了25%。","word":"slump"}},"smother":{"createdAt":1781840892410,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"smother在此指撲滅或扼殺，常用於描述滅火或抑制發展的行為。","options":["ignite","spread","smother","report"],"sentence":"The firefighters worked quickly to ______ the flames using foam and water from their hoses. Within minutes, the dangerous fire was completely extinguished.","translation":"消防員迅速用泡沫和從水管中噴出的水來撲滅火焰。在幾分鐘內，危險的火災被完全撲滅了。","word":"smother"}},"smuggle":{"createdAt":1781531595643,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"smuggle 表示祕密地或非法地運輸違禁品，通常是為了逃避稅收或法律。","options":["declare","smuggle","examine","transport"],"sentence":"The criminal tried to ______ diamonds across the border without paying taxes. The customs officers at the checkpoint were specifically trained to catch people attempting illegal imports.","translation":"那名罪犯試圖在未繳稅的情況下將鑽石走私過邊境。海關檢查站的官員受過專門訓練，以抓捕試圖非法進口的人。","word":"smuggle"}},"snatch":{"createdAt":1781848934134,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"snatch表示突然快速地奪走或搶走某物，通常帶有強行的含義","options":["donate","grab","return","examine"],"sentence":"The thief tried to ______ the purse from the old woman's hands. Police arrived quickly and arrested him before he could escape with it.","translation":"小偷試圖從老婦人手中奪走錢包。警察很快趕到並在他逃脫前逮捕了他。","word":"snatch"}},"snore":{"createdAt":1781961506842,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"snore指睡眠時鼻子發出的粗重呼吸聲，是一種無意識的睡眠現象。","options":["whisper","snore","laugh","sing"],"sentence":"My grandfather would ______ loudly every night, keeping everyone in the house awake. His wife finally bought him earplugs to help him breathe more easily while sleeping.","translation":"我的祖父每晚都會______很大聲，讓家裡所有人都睡不著。他的妻子最後為他買了耳塞，幫助他在睡眠時呼吸更順暢。","word":"snore"}},"soak":{"createdAt":1781603436394,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"soak是指將物體長時間浸入液體中，使其吸收液體或變軟，通常需要一段時間。","options":["boil","soak","rinse","drain"],"sentence":"You should ______ the dried beans in water overnight before cooking them. This process will soften them and reduce the cooking time significantly.","translation":"你應該在烹飪前將乾豆子在水中浸泡一整夜。這個過程會軟化它們並大幅縮短烹飪時間。","word":"soak"}},"soar":{"createdAt":1781832089956,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"soar 表示急速上升或高飛，可用於描述信心、價格等迅速增長的情況","options":["decline","soar","stabilize","fluctuate"],"sentence":"After winning the championship, the team's confidence began to ______. The stock market also ______ by 15% following the positive economic report.","translation":"贏得冠軍後，球隊的信心開始翱翔。股市在正面經濟報告後也上漲了15%。","word":"soar"}},"sober":{"createdAt":1781746685518,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"sober指的是清醒的、冷靜的，當用作動詞時表示使清醒、使冷靜或恢復正常狀態。","options":["sober","terminate","affirm","cooperate"],"sentence":"After drinking too much at the party, he needed to ______ up before driving home. He drank coffee and took a walk in the fresh air to clear his mind.","translation":"在派對上喝了太多酒後，他需要清醒一下才能開車回家。他喝了咖啡並在新鮮空氣中散步以清醒頭腦。","word":"sober"}},"socially":{"createdAt":1781693264936,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"socially 是副詞，表示「以社交的方式」或「在社交方面」，用來修飾與他人互動的方式。","options":["temporarily","valueless","socially","vanish"],"sentence":"My shy cousin doesn't enjoy attending parties and prefers to spend time alone rather than interact ______ with others. She finds large gatherings overwhelming and would rather read books at home.","translation":"我害羞的表妹不喜歡參加派對，寧願獨自度過時光而不是與他人社交互動。她發現大型聚會令人感到不適，寧願在家裡讀書。","word":"socially"}},"sole":{"createdAt":1781951900954,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"sole表示唯一的、獨享的，強調沒有其他目的或責任，與「單一使命」相符。","options":["multiple","dual","sole","primary"],"sentence":"The ______ purpose of the charity organization is to help homeless people find shelter and employment. Everything they do is dedicated to this single mission.","translation":"慈善組織的唯一目的是幫助無家可歸者找到住所和工作。他們所做的一切都致力於這個單一使命。","word":"sole"}},"solidarity":{"createdAt":1781451343281,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"團結是指人們為了共同的目標而聯合在一起，這個詞強調集體的凝聚力和互相支持的精神。","options":["competition","solidarity","indifference","confusion"],"sentence":"The workers showed ______ by refusing to work until their demands were met. All of them stood together as one unified group, demonstrating their commitment to supporting each other's cause.","translation":"工人們通過拒絕工作直到滿足他們的要求來表達團結。他們全都作為一個統一的整體站在一起，展示了他們相互支持的承諾。","word":"solidarity"}},"solitary":{"createdAt":1781402539335,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"solitary 表示獨自一人的、孤獨的或喜歡獨居的狀態，通常指不與他人互動。","options":["social","solitary","friendly","crowded"],"sentence":"The ______ hiker preferred to walk through the mountains alone. He avoided group tours and deliberately chose trails where he would not encounter other people.","translation":"這個孤獨的登山者喜歡獨自走過山脈。他避免參加團體遊覽，刻意選擇不會遇到其他人的登山道。","word":"solitary"}},"somehow":{"createdAt":1781337343697,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"somehow用於表達對某事發生方式的不確定或驚訝，意為不知怎麼的。","options":["obviously","somehow","certainly","slowly"],"sentence":"She ______ managed to finish the entire project before the deadline, despite facing numerous obstacles. Nobody understood how she did it with so many interruptions.","translation":"她不知怎麼的在截止日期前完成了整個項目，儘管面臨了許多障礙。沒有人明白她在這麼多中斷的情況下是如何做到的。","word":"somehow"}},"soothing":{"createdAt":1781452134699,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"soothing形容詞用來描述能夠安撫、舒緩或使人平靜的事物或環境。","options":["chaotic","soothing","loud","confusing"],"sentence":"The ______ music helped calm the anxious patient before surgery. The hospital specifically chose instrumental pieces known for their relaxing and comforting effects.","translation":"舒緩的音樂幫助手術前焦慮的病人平靜下來。醫院特別選擇了以其放鬆和舒適效果而聞名的器樂作品。","word":"soothing"}},"sophisticated":{"createdAt":1781403377829,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"sophisticated 形容一個人見多識廣、經驗豐富、具有高度的文化修養和世故的態度。","options":["naive","young","sophisticated","inexperienced"],"sentence":"The ______ diplomat navigated the complex international negotiations with ease and grace. After decades of experience working with world leaders, she understood the subtle protocols and unwritten rules.","translation":"這位老練的外交官輕鬆優雅地應對複雜的國際談判。經過幾十年與世界領導人合作的經驗，她深諳細微的外交禮節和不成文的規則。","word":"sophisticated"}},"sore":{"createdAt":1781784029104,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"aching（疼痛的）形容身體某部位的酸痛感覺，通常是因為運動過度或受傷而產生。","options":["tired","stiff","aching","weak"],"sentence":"After running a marathon, her legs felt incredibly ______. She could barely walk down the stairs the next morning.","translation":"跑完馬拉松後，她的腿感到難以置信地疼痛。第二天早上她幾乎無法走下樓梯。","word":"sore"}},"soulful":{"createdAt":1781431278560,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"soulful形容充滿深厚感情和靈魂的藝術表達或表現。","options":["technical","soulful","casual","brief"],"sentence":"The jazz musician's ______ performance moved everyone in the audience to tears. His deep emotional expression and passionate playing connected with the hearts of all who listened.","translation":"爵士樂音樂家充滿情感的表演使觀眾中的每個人都感動到流淚。他深刻的情感表達和充滿激情的演奏與所有傾聽者的心靈相連。","word":"soulful"}},"souvenir":{"createdAt":1781849622418,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"紀念品是指人們為了紀念特定的事件、地點或時刻而購買或保留的物品。","options":["textbook","souvenir","equipment","ingredient"],"sentence":"She bought a ______ from the museum gift shop to remember her visit. The small wooden figurine now sits on her shelf at home as a lasting memento.","translation":"她從博物館禮品店買了一個紀念品來紀念她的訪問。這個小木製雕像現在放在她家的架子上作為永久的紀念。","word":"souvenir"}},"sovereign":{"createdAt":1781961517452,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sovereign 在這裡指的是擁有至高權力的統治者或君主。","options":["minister","sovereign","ambassador","advisor"],"sentence":"The ______ of the kingdom made the final decision regarding trade agreements. As the absolute monarch, this ruler had the power to bind the entire nation to international contracts.","translation":"這個王國的元首對貿易協議做出了最終決定。作為絕對君主，這位統治者有權將整個國家與國際契約綁定。","word":"sovereign"}},"spare":{"createdAt":1781749177492,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"spare 在此意為撥出或抽出（時間、資源等）供他人使用。","options":["waste","allocate","borrow","save"],"sentence":"Could you ______ me some time this afternoon to discuss the project? I have a few important ideas I'd like to share with you before the deadline.","translation":"你今天下午能抽出一些時間和我討論這個項目嗎？在截止日期前，我想和你分享一些重要的想法。","word":"spare"}},"specialize":{"createdAt":1781345746904,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"specialize 作動詞，表示專門研究或專攻某個領域，通常需要深入的學習和經驗。","options":["generalize","specialize","graduate","practice"],"sentence":"Dr. Chen decided to ______ in pediatric cardiology after completing her general medical training. She attended advanced courses and spent years studying heart conditions in children.","translation":"陳醫生在完成普通醫學培訓後決定專門研究小兒心臟病學。她參加了高級課程，並花費多年研究兒童心臟疾病。","word":"specialize"}},"species":{"createdAt":1781362281653,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"species是指同一類型的生物，具有相同的遺傳特徵，可以相互繁殖。","options":["type","species","variety","category"],"sentence":"Scientists discovered a new ______ of butterfly in the Amazon rainforest. This previously unknown insect has unique colorful patterns never seen before.","translation":"科學家在亞馬遜雨林中發現了一種新的蝴蝶物種。這種以前未知的昆蟲有著從未見過的獨特彩色圖案。","word":"species"}},"specification":{"createdAt":1781401803898,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"specification是指對產品或項目的詳細描述和技術要求，包括尺寸、標準和性能參數。","options":["budget","schedule","blueprint","requirements"],"sentence":"The engineer carefully reviewed the ______ for the new bridge construction project. The document detailed every measurement, material, and safety requirement needed to complete the work.","translation":"工程師仔細檢查了新橋樑施工項目的規格說明書。該文件詳細說明了完成工作所需的每一項測量、材料和安全要求。","word":"specification"}},"specify":{"createdAt":1781840659326,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"specify 是指詳細說明或明確指出某些事物，在這裡表示需要清楚地陳述截止日期和具體細節。","options":["ignore","specify","delay","announce"],"sentence":"The project manager asked the team to ______ the exact deadline for the next phase. Without clear dates and milestones, everyone would be working toward different goals.","translation":"專案經理要求團隊明確指出下一階段的確切截止日期。如果沒有清楚的日期和里程碑，每個人都會朝向不同的目標工作。","word":"specify"}},"speculate":{"createdAt":1781746848182,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"speculate 表示「推測」或「投機」，指基於不完全信息進行猜測或假設。","options":["ignore","speculate","calculate","document"],"sentence":"Investors like to ______ about the stock market's future direction. However, without concrete data and analysis, such predictions are often just guesses.","translation":"投資者喜歡推測股票市場的未來方向。不過，沒有具體的數據和分析，這樣的預測往往只是猜測。","word":"speculate"}},"spell":{"createdAt":1781481311492,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"spell作名詞指的是魔法、符咒或咒語。","options":["contract","spell","proposal","agreement"],"sentence":"The magician cast a ______ and made the rabbit disappear from the stage. The audience was amazed by the mysterious incantation and magical effects that followed.","translation":"魔術師施展了一個符咒，使兔子從舞台上消失了。觀眾為神祕的咒語和隨之而來的魔法效果感到驚訝。","word":"spell"}},"spine":{"createdAt":1781693254769,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"spine指的是脊柱或脊椎，是人體中央的骨骼結構，保護脊髓。","options":["lung","spine","stomach","liver"],"sentence":"The doctor examined the patient's ______ to check for any injuries or misalignment. X-rays revealed a serious fracture in the lower vertebrae.","translation":"醫生檢查了患者的脊椎以檢查是否有任何傷害或錯位。X光片顯示下部椎骨有嚴重骨折。","word":"spine"}},"spirit":{"createdAt":1781848330190,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"spirit指人的精神狀態、士氣、心靈或內在的勇氣和決心。","options":["injury","spirit","salary","complaint"],"sentence":"Despite losing the championship game, the team maintained a strong ______ and remained optimistic about their future. Their determination and positive attitude showed they had not been defeated mentally or emotionally.","translation":"儘管輸掉了錦標賽，球隊保持著強大的精神並對未來保持樂觀。他們的決心和積極態度表明他們在精神和情感上沒有被打敗。","word":"spirit"}},"splash":{"createdAt":1781274836863,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"splash作為名詞表示液體濺起的動作或聲音，通常伴隨水四處飛濺。","options":["splash","silence","movement","dive"],"sentence":"The child made a big ______ when she jumped into the swimming pool. Water flew everywhere and soaked everyone standing nearby.","translation":"當女孩跳進游泳池時，她激起了很大的水花。水到處飛濺，浸濕了附近站著的每個人。","word":"splash"}},"splendor":{"createdAt":1781774456604,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"splendor 指事物所展現的光彩、壯麗和顯赫的特質。","options":["simplicity","darkness","plainness","brilliance"],"sentence":"The royal palace displayed its ______ through golden decorations and intricate architecture. Visitors were amazed by its magnificence and grandeur.","translation":"皇宮通過金色裝飾和複雜的建築展現了其光彩。遊客被其壯麗和雄偉所驚嘆。","word":"splendor"}},"spoilt":{"createdAt":1781842254312,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"spoilt 作為形容詞表示被寵壞的，指由於過度縱容而變得性格不好、任性或不知感恩的人。","options":["determined","humble","spoilt","disciplined"],"sentence":"The ______ teenager demanded an expensive sports car for his birthday, having been given everything he wanted since childhood. His parents had never refused him anything, which created his ungrateful and demanding attitude.","translation":"這個被寵壞的少年要求在他生日時得到一輛昂貴的跑車，因為他從小就被給予了他想要的一切。他的父母從未拒絕過他，這創造了他不感恩和苛刻的態度。","word":"spoilt"}},"sponsorship":{"createdAt":1781403377828,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sponsorship 指的是公司或個人為了獲得宣傳權而投資支持某個活動或組織。","options":["ticket","sponsorship","membership","donation"],"sentence":"The tech company secured a lucrative ______ of the international soccer tournament. Their logo appeared on every advertisement and broadcast throughout the entire event.","translation":"這家科技公司獲得了國際足球錦標賽的有利可圖的主辦權。他們的標誌出現在整個賽事的每個廣告和播放中。","word":"sponsorship"}},"spontaneous":{"createdAt":1781738724027,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"spontaneous指的是未經計劃或思考而自然而然發生的行為或反應。","options":["rehearsed","spontaneous","scheduled","deliberate"],"sentence":"Her ______ laughter erupted from the audience during the comedian's performance. No one had prepared or planned for the moment; everyone simply burst out laughing naturally at the funny joke.","translation":"在喜劇演員的表演中，她自發的笑聲從觀眾席中爆發出來。沒有人為這一刻做過準備或計劃；每個人都自然而然地對這個有趣的笑話突然大笑。","word":"spontaneous"}},"spotlight":{"createdAt":1781565657693,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"spotlight 名詞指舞台或攝影中使用的聚光燈設備，也引伸為大眾關注或媒體注意的焦點。","options":["curtain","spotlight","microphone","backdrop"],"sentence":"The theater director positioned the ______ to illuminate the lead actor on stage. The bright beam of light created a visible circle around the performer, drawing all audience attention to him.","translation":"劇院導演將聚光燈放置在舞台上來照亮主演員。這束明亮的光線在演員周圍創造了一個可見的圓圈，將所有觀眾的注意力吸引到他身上。","word":"spotlight"}},"spotlit":{"createdAt":1781582251996,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"spotlit 是形容詞，表示被聚光燈或集中光源直接照射的狀態。","options":["shadowed","spotlit","hidden","obscured"],"sentence":"The ______ actor stood alone on the dark stage, with only a single bright light illuminating his face. The rest of the theater remained in complete darkness.","translation":"那位被聚光燈照射的演員獨自站在黑暗的舞台上，只有一束明亮的光線照射著他的臉。劇院的其他部分保持完全黑暗。","word":"spotlit"}},"sprang":{"createdAt":1781849847399,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sprang是spring的過去式，表示迅速地跳或突然出現，與「快速移動」的線索相符。","options":["walked","sprang","sat","climbed"],"sentence":"The cat ______ from the windowsill without any warning. It moved so quickly that nobody saw it coming.","translation":"貓從窗台上跳躍而下，完全沒有任何警告。它移動得如此之快，以至於沒有人看到它的動作。","word":"sprang"}},"spray":{"createdAt":1781425096277,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"spray 作名詞時指細小的液體顆粒或霧狀物質被噴出；作動詞時指噴灑或噴霧，通常產生細小的水珠或液體微粒。","options":["stream","spray","puddle","wave"],"sentence":"The child ran through the garden and felt the cool ______ from the watering can on a hot summer afternoon. Each fine mist of tiny water droplets refreshed her skin as she played near the flowers.","translation":"孩子在花園裡奔跑，在炎熱的夏日午後感受到澆水罐的清涼噴霧。細小的水滴霧氣在她靠近花朵時讓她的皮膚感到清爽。","word":"spray"}},"spring":{"createdAt":1781849511877,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"春天是一年中的季節，介於冬天和夏天之間，特點是溫度上升、花草生長。","options":["summer","winter","spring","autumn"],"sentence":"Every ______, the flowers bloom and the weather becomes warmer after a long, cold winter. The season brings new life to gardens and parks around the city.","translation":"每到春天，花朵盛開，經過漫長寒冷的冬天後天氣變得溫暖。這個季節為城市周圍的花園和公園帶來新的生命。","word":"spring"}},"square":{"createdAt":1781429810253,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"square作為形容詞表示四邊相等、四個角都是直角的正方形形狀。","options":["swift","symbol","square","rite"],"sentence":"The carpenter cut the wood into a ______ shape with equal sides and right angles at each corner. This geometric form is often used in construction and design.","translation":"木匠將木頭切成正方形，邊長相等，每個角都是直角。這種幾何形狀經常用於建築和設計。","word":"square"}},"squash":{"createdAt":1781481124693,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"squash 指用力按壓或擠壓某物，使其變扁或變形。","options":["rinse","crush","separate","freeze"],"sentence":"Be careful not to ______ the fresh strawberries when you pack them into the container. Gentle handling will preserve their shape and prevent the juice from spilling everywhere.","translation":"當你把新鮮草莓裝入容器時要小心不要把它們壓扁。輕柔的處理將保持它們的形狀並防止果汁灑出來。","word":"squash"}},"squat":{"createdAt":1781950727566,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"squat 指蹲下或坐在腳跟上，身體接近地面。","options":["run","squat","jump","lie"],"sentence":"The firefighters had to ______ down to avoid the thick smoke while searching for survivors. Their low position helped them breathe fresher air near the floor.","translation":"消防員不得不蹲下以避開濃煙，同時搜尋倖存者。他們較低的位置幫助他們呼吸靠近地板的新鮮空氣。","word":"squat"}},"stability":{"createdAt":1781345237584,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"stability指事物保持穩定、平衡且不易改變的特性或狀態。","options":["chaos","stability","uncertainty","volatility"],"sentence":"Economic ______ is essential for a country's long-term growth and development. A reliable government and consistent policies help maintain this important condition.","translation":"經濟穩定性對國家的長期增長和發展至關重要。可靠的政府和一致的政策有助於維持這一重要條件。","word":"stability"}},"stadium":{"createdAt":1781746685501,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"stadium指的是露天運動場、體育場館，是舉辦各類運動比賽和大型活動的場所。","options":["stadium","duration","editorials","sober"],"sentence":"Thousands of fans gathered in the ______ to watch the championship game. The massive structure had seating for over fifty thousand spectators.","translation":"數千名球迷聚集在運動場觀看冠軍賽。這座龐大的建築可容納超過五萬名觀眾。","word":"stadium"}},"stain":{"createdAt":1781626081103,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"stain 作為動詞表示玷污、損害或留下不良印象，特別是用於描述對聲譽、名譽或品格的損害。","options":["polish","enhance","stain","improve"],"sentence":"The scandal would ______ his reputation forever in the eyes of the public. His involvement in the corruption case left a permanent mark on his career that could never be erased.","translation":"這樁醜聞將在公眾眼中永遠玷污他的聲譽。他涉及貪污案件在他的職業生涯中留下了永久的污點，永遠無法消除。","word":"stain"}},"stake":{"createdAt":1782016805982,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"stake 是名詞，在商業語境中表示投資或股份，即對企業的所有權比例。","options":["debt","stake","loss","expense"],"sentence":"He decided to increase his ______ in the business venture by investing an additional $50,000. This meant he now owned a larger percentage of the company than before.","translation":"他決定通過額外投資五萬美元來增加他在商業企業中的股份。這意味著他現在擁有該公司比以前更大的百分比。","word":"stake"}},"stall":{"createdAt":1781311922063,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"stall 是指在市場或展覽會上的臨時販賣攤位或小亭子。","options":["store","stall","warehouse","garden"],"sentence":"At the farmer's market, the elderly woman sold fresh vegetables from her ______. Customers lined up every Saturday morning to buy tomatoes and lettuce from her small booth.","translation":"在農夫市集裡，那位老婦人從她的攤位上販賣新鮮蔬菜。顧客每個星期六早上都排隊到她的小販賣處購買番茄和生菜。","word":"stall"}},"stance":{"createdAt":1781402154552,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"stance表示對某個議題的觀點或立場，在這句話中指政府對氣候變遷採取的官方立場。","options":["lottery","lack","stance","hijack"],"sentence":"The government's ______ on climate change has become much stricter in recent years. Officials have publicly declared their commitment to reducing carbon emissions by 50% within the next decade.","translation":"近年來政府在氣候變遷上的立場變得嚴格得多。官員們已公開宣布他們承諾在未來十年內減少50%的碳排放。","word":"stance"}},"stand":{"createdAt":1781838276307,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"stand作為動詞表示容忍或忍受某事。","options":["compress","claim","stand","toll"],"sentence":"I cannot ______ the bitter taste of black coffee without any sugar or cream. Every time I try to drink it, I have to add sweetener immediately.","translation":"我無法忍受黑咖啡不加糖或奶油的苦味。每次我試著喝它時，我都得立即加入甜味劑。","word":"stand"}},"staple":{"createdAt":1781832549169,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"staple 作為名詞時指某物的主要或必需的部分，特別是指日常飲食中的基本食物。","options":["luxury","staple","exotic","expensive"],"sentence":"Rice is a ______ food in many Asian countries and has been for thousands of years. In China, Japan, and Vietnam, it appears on nearly every dinner table as the main carbohydrate source.","translation":"米飯是許多亞洲國家的主要食物，已有數千年的歷史。在中國、日本和越南，它幾乎出現在每個餐桌上，作為主要的碳水化合物來源。","word":"staple"}},"starvation":{"createdAt":1781531595650,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"starvation 表示因缺乏食物而導致的嚴重飢荒狀態，甚至可能導致死亡。","options":["migration","starvation","poverty","disease"],"sentence":"The famine led to widespread ______ in the region. Thousands of people died because food supplies had completely run out.","translation":"飢荒導致該地區普遍挨餓。由於食物供應完全耗盡，數千人死亡。","word":"starvation"}},"statue":{"createdAt":1781917052436,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"statue指的是用石頭、金屬或其他材料製作的立體雕刻作品，常放置在公共場所供人欣賞。","options":["painting","statue","monument","sculpture"],"sentence":"The museum displayed a marble ______ of the famous general in the center of the hall. Visitors admired how the sculptor had captured every detail of his facial features and military uniform.","translation":"博物館在大廳中央展示了這位著名將軍的大理石雕像。遊客們讚賞雕塑家如何捕捉了他臉部特徵和軍裝的每一個細節。","word":"statue"}},"statute":{"createdAt":1782016805981,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"statute 是名詞，指由政府或立法機構正式制定的法律或法規。","options":["rumor","tradition","statute","suggestion"],"sentence":"The new traffic ______ requires all drivers to wear seatbelts on highways. The government enforced this law to reduce serious injuries and fatalities in vehicle accidents.","translation":"新的交通法令要求所有駕駛在高速公路上繫安全帶。政府制定這項法律以減少車禍中的重傷和死亡事故。","word":"statute"}},"steadily":{"createdAt":1781849847408,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"steadily表示平穩地或穩固地，與「一致的步伐、不減速」的線索相符。","options":["frantically","steadily","erratically","unevenly"],"sentence":"The runner moved ______ throughout the marathon without slowing down. Her consistent pace and endurance impressed all the spectators.","translation":"跑步者在整個馬拉松比賽中平穩地前進，沒有放慢速度。她一致的步伐和耐力給所有觀眾留下了深刻印象。","word":"steadily"}},"stem":{"createdAt":1781677018340,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"stem作名詞，表示植物的「莖」，是連接根和葉子、花朵的主要結構，提供支撐和營養輸送。","options":["root","stem","flower","leaf"],"sentence":"The plant's ______ grows upward toward the sunlight and provides support for the leaves. Without this central structure, the flower would collapse to the ground.","translation":"植物的莖向上生長朝向陽光，為葉子提供支撐。沒有這個中央結構，花朵會倒在地上。","word":"stem"}},"stepfather":{"createdAt":1781713470382,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"繼父是指與某人的母親或父親再婚的男性配偶，不是親生父親。","options":["uncle","stepfather","grandfather","cousin"],"sentence":"After my mother remarried, my ______ helped me with my homework every evening. He was not my biological father, but he had been married to my mother for five years.","translation":"我母親再婚後，我的繼父每晚幫助我做功課。他不是我的親生父親，但他已經和我母親結婚五年了。","word":"stepfather"}},"stepmother":{"createdAt":1781850347299,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"繼母是指一個人的父親或母親與某人結婚後所帶來的配偶，通常是在原配偶去世或離婚後再婚。","options":["guardian","stepmother","nanny","tutor"],"sentence":"After her father remarried, Sarah had to adjust to living with her new ______. The woman had been married to Sarah's father for three years and was raising her alongside her biological children.","translation":"在她父親再婚後，莎拉必須適應與她的繼母一起生活。這位女性已經與莎拉的父親結婚三年，並與她的親生子女一起撫養她。","word":"stepmother"}},"stereotype":{"createdAt":1781839703148,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"eliminate意為排除、消除，與work to break down outdated beliefs（努力打破過時信念）語境相符。","options":["reinforce","promote","stereotype","eliminate"],"sentence":"We must work to ______ outdated beliefs about different cultures and communities. Education and exposure to diverse perspectives are essential tools.","translation":"我們必須努力消除對不同文化和社區的過時信念。教育和接觸不同的觀點是必要的工具。","word":"stereotype"}},"stimulant":{"createdAt":1781425078613,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"興奮劑是能刺激神經系統、增強警覺性和活力但可能有負面副作用的物質。","options":["water","vitamin","stimulant","protein"],"sentence":"Many athletes avoid consuming ______ before competitions because it can cause jitteriness and elevated heart rate. The coach warned the team that such substances could affect their performance negatively.","translation":"許多運動員在比賽前避免服用興奮劑，因為它會導致發抖和心率升高。教練警告球隊這些物質可能會對他們的表現產生負面影響。","word":"stimulant"}},"stimulate":{"createdAt":1781939439465,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"stimulate作動詞表示刺激、激發或促進，使某人或某物變得更活躍或感興趣。","options":["reduce","ignore","stimulate","forget"],"sentence":"The teacher used games and interactive activities to ______ the students' interest in mathematics. By making lessons engaging and fun, she saw their participation and enthusiasm grow significantly.","translation":"老師用遊戲和互動活動刺激學生對數學的興趣。通過讓課程引人入勝且有趣，她看到他們的參與度和熱情大幅增長。","word":"stimulate"}},"stingy":{"createdAt":1781323901185,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"stingy意為「吝嗇的」或「小氣的」，用來形容不願意花錢或分享金錢的人。","options":["generous","stingy","wealthy","careless"],"sentence":"My uncle has a reputation for being ______ with his money. He refuses to leave a tip at restaurants and always finds excuses to avoid sharing expenses.","translation":"我叔叔以對金錢小氣而聞名。他拒絕在餐廳留小費，總是找藉口避免分擔費用。","word":"stingy"}},"stink":{"createdAt":1781653278518,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"stink是動詞，表示散發異味或發出難聞的氣味，通常用於描述令人不快的臭味，比一般的smell更強調不愉快的感受。","options":["smell","stink","appear","disappear"],"sentence":"The garbage in the alley began to ______ after sitting in the hot sun for several days. Neighbors complained about the horrible smell and demanded immediate cleanup.","translation":"在烈日下放置數天後，小巷中的垃圾開始______。鄰居們抱怨難聞的氣味，並要求立即清理。","word":"stink"}},"stool":{"createdAt":1781402539334,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"stool 是一種沒有靠背和扶手的簡單座位，通常用來坐著或踩踏以達到高處。","options":["ladder","stool","wall","desk"],"sentence":"The painter stood on a small ______ to reach the ceiling. He needed something portable that he could move from room to room easily.","translation":"畫家站在一個小凳子上去接觸天花板。他需要一些他可以輕易地從一個房間移到另一個房間的東西。","word":"stool"}},"storage":{"createdAt":1781884659836,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"storage 指專門用於保存和存放物品的地點或設施，在農業語境中特別適用。","options":["greenhouse","storage","barn","cellar"],"sentence":"The farmer built a large ______ to keep grain dry and protected from pests throughout the winter. This facility prevents food spoilage and ensures supplies last until the next harvest.","translation":"農民建造了一個大型儲存設施來保持穀物乾燥並在整個冬天防止害蟲。這個設施防止食物腐爛並確保供應能持續到下一個收穫季節。","word":"storage"}},"straight":{"createdAt":1781775363748,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"straight 表示筆直的，沒有彎曲的形狀，用來描述沒有彎曲的道路。","options":["narrow","straight","empty","flat"],"sentence":"The road ahead appeared ______ and clear with no curves or intersections. We could see all the way to the horizon without any obstacles blocking our view.","translation":"前面的路看起來______，沒有彎曲或十字路口。我們可以一直看到地平線，沒有任何障礙物阻擋我們的視線。","word":"straight"}},"straightforward":{"createdAt":1781449095512,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"straightforward意為率直的、坦率的，用來形容清楚直接、沒有隱瞞的表達或方式。","options":["complicated","straightforward","vague","mysterious"],"sentence":"The manager gave a ______ answer to the employee's question. There was no ambiguity or hidden meaning in what he said.","translation":"經理對員工的問題給出了率直的答案。他所說的話沒有任何歧義或隱含意思。","word":"straightforward"}},"strained":{"createdAt":1781746848180,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"strained 表示「拉傷」或「扭傷」，描述肌肉或肌腱受傷的狀態。","options":["relaxed","strong","strained","flexible"],"sentence":"After lifting the heavy box incorrectly, his back felt ______. The doctor recommended rest and physical therapy for the next few weeks.","translation":"在不正確地抬起重箱後，他的背感到拉傷。醫生建議他在接下來的幾週內休息和進行物理治療。","word":"strained"}},"strand":{"createdAt":1781566055843,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"strand 指的是線、繩或頭髮等細長物體的單一條狀部分，常用於編織或組合的語境中。","options":["bunch","strand","lock","piece"],"sentence":"She carefully braided each ______ of hair to create an intricate hairstyle. The salon stylist twisted together three separate sections from root to tip.","translation":"她小心地編織每一縷頭髮來創造一個複雜的髮型。沙龍髮型師從髮根到髮尾把三個不同的部分絞在一起。","word":"strand"}},"strap":{"createdAt":1781774456600,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"strap 是指用來綁緊或固定物品的帶子，通常有扣環或鉤子。","options":["button","belt","band","chain"],"sentence":"She tightened the leather ______ around her backpack to keep it secure. The buckle at the end made it easy to fasten.","translation":"她繫緊背包上的皮帶以保持牢固。末端的扣環使其易於繫緊。","word":"strap"}},"strategic":{"createdAt":1781664082527,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"strategic 表示與戰略、策略或計劃有關的，指經過深思熟慮的長期方向。","options":["random","strategic","tactical","routine"],"sentence":"The company's ______ plan involves acquiring smaller competitors to strengthen market position. This long-term approach aims to ensure competitive advantage for the next five years.","translation":"該公司的戰略計畫涉及收購較小的競爭對手以加強市場地位。這種長期方法旨在確保未來五年的競爭優勢。","word":"strategic"}},"strategy":{"createdAt":1781345237581,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"strategy指為達成目標而制定的周密計畫或方案。","options":["equipment","strategy","schedule","uniform"],"sentence":"The coach developed a new ______ to help the team win the championship. The plan focused on improving defense and creating more scoring opportunities in the second half.","translation":"教練制定了新的策略來幫助球隊贏得冠軍。該計畫著重於改進防守和在下半場創造更多得分機會。","word":"strategy"}},"stray":{"createdAt":1781693303268,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"stray 作為形容詞表示「走失的」或「迷路的」，用來描述沒有主人、在街上流浪的動物。","options":["trained","stray","aggressive","loyal"],"sentence":"The ______ dog wandered through the neighborhood looking for food and shelter. Without an owner or identification tag, it had been lost for several weeks.","translation":"這隻走失的狗在社區裡流浪，尋找食物和住處。沒有主人或身份標籤，它已經失蹤好幾週了。","word":"stray"}},"strengthen":{"createdAt":1781837419095,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"Strengthen表示使某物變得更強大、更有力或更堅實。","options":["weaken","stretch","strengthen","relax"],"sentence":"Regular exercise will ______ your muscles and improve your overall fitness. By consistently working out, you'll notice increased physical power and endurance.","translation":"定期運動將加強你的肌肉並改善你的整體健康狀況。通過持續鍛煉，你會注意到身體力量和耐力的增加。","word":"strengthen"}},"striking":{"createdAt":1781950727561,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"striking 指非常明顯、引人注目或給人深刻印象的。","options":["hidden","striking","expensive","small"],"sentence":"The ______ difference between the two paintings made them easy to compare. One was vibrant and colorful while the other was dull and gray.","translation":"這兩幅畫之間的顯著差異使它們易於比較。一幅色彩鮮豔，而另一幅則暗淡無光。","word":"striking"}},"string":{"createdAt":1781362281722,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"string指的是細繩、帶子，也可以表示一系列或一連串事物。","options":["rope","string","chain","belt"],"sentence":"He tied a ______ around the package to keep it securely closed. The thin cord held everything together during transport.","translation":"他用細繩在包裝周圍綁了一圈以保持其安全閉合。這根細繩在運輸過程中將所有東西連在一起。","word":"string"}},"stroke":{"createdAt":1781275226786,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"此處stroke指「中風」，一種醫學上的腦血管疾病","options":["feast","stroke","dazzle","fume"],"sentence":"He suffered a ______ that left him partially paralyzed. The doctor explained that a blood clot had blocked oxygen to his brain.","translation":"他中風了，導致身體部分癱瘓。醫生解釋說血栓阻礙了氧氣進入他的大腦。","word":"stroke"}},"structural":{"createdAt":1781664082526,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"structural 表示與結構有關的，指涉及或影響事物基本框架或組織的。","options":["minor","structural","cosmetic","temporary"],"sentence":"The building has ______ damage from the earthquake that requires immediate repair. Engineers need to reinforce the beams and walls to ensure stability.","translation":"該建築有地震造成的結構損傷，需要立即修復。工程師需要加強梁和牆以確保穩定性。","word":"structural"}},"struggle":{"createdAt":1781787229335,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"struggle 作為名詞表示艱難的努力或對抗，通常指長期的困難經歷。","options":["victory","struggle","vacation","celebration"],"sentence":"After years of ______ against poverty, the family finally achieved financial stability. Their perseverance and hard work eventually paid off.","translation":"經過多年與貧困的抗爭，這個家庭終於獲得了財務穩定。他們的毅力和辛勤工作最終得到了回報。","word":"struggle"}},"stuff":{"createdAt":1781499075059,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"填充物是用來填滿或塞進容器或物體內部的材料。","options":["fabric","thread","stuff","pattern"],"sentence":"The seamstress used soft cotton ______ to fill the pillows before sewing them shut. The material she chose was comfortable and long-lasting for customers.","translation":"女裁縫在縫製枕頭之前用柔軟的棉質填充物填充枕頭。她選擇的材料舒適耐用，適合顧客使用。","word":"stuff"}},"stunned":{"createdAt":1781311922062,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"stunned 表示被某事驚嚇或震驚到無法反應的狀態，通常伴隨著沈默和呆滯的反應。","options":["amused","stunned","bored","confused"],"sentence":"When the magician made the elephant disappear, the entire audience was ______. Everyone sat in complete silence, unable to move or speak for several minutes.","translation":"當魔術師讓大象消失時，整個觀眾席都被震驚了。每個人都靜靜地坐著，幾分鐘內無法移動或說話。","word":"stunned"}},"stunning":{"createdAt":1781311922064,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"stunning 形容某人或某物非常美麗或令人印象深刻，足以令人驚嘆。","options":["plain","ordinary","stunning","casual"],"sentence":"The bride looked absolutely ______ in her white wedding dress on her special day. Her elegant appearance left all the guests breathless and amazed.","translation":"新娘在她的特殊日子穿著潔白的婚禮服看起來絕對是驚人地美麗。她優雅的外表讓所有客人都驚嘆不已。","word":"stunning"}},"sturdy":{"createdAt":1781425096276,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sturdy 意為堅實、結實、耐用，用來形容物品或人身體強健，能夠承受長期使用或壓力而不易損壞。","options":["fragile","sturdy","decorative","antique"],"sentence":"The old wooden table was ______ enough to support the weight of the heavy books. After fifty years of daily use without any damage or wear, it remained as reliable as the day it was built.","translation":"那張老木桌足夠堅固，能夠承受重書的重量。經過五十年的日常使用而沒有任何損傷或磨損，它仍然像製造的那天一樣可靠。","word":"sturdy"}},"stylish":{"createdAt":1781939439464,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"stylish是形容詞，表示時尚的、格調優雅的、很有氣派的，通常形容衣著或設計。","options":["torn","stylish","casual","simple"],"sentence":"He wore a ______ suit to the gala that turned heads as he walked through the room. His tailored jacket and designer accessories demonstrated impeccable taste and elegance.","translation":"他穿著一套氣派的西裝參加慶典，當他走過房間時吸引了眾人的目光。他剪裁得體的夾克和名牌配飾展現了無可挑剔的品味和優雅。","word":"stylish"}},"subject":{"createdAt":1781481124703,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"subject 作為名詞指學校教授的課程科目。","options":["student","schedule","course","test"],"sentence":"The teacher introduced a new ______ in the curriculum that focused on environmental science. Students learned about ecosystems, conservation, and sustainable practices.","translation":"老師在課程中介紹了一個專注於環境科學的新科目。學生們學習了生態系統、保護和可持續實踐。","word":"subject"}},"submarine":{"createdAt":1781431278561,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"submarine是能在水下航行的軍事或探險用船隻，其主要特點是能夠潛入水下。","options":["airplane","submarine","boat","train"],"sentence":"The military ______ descended silently into the ocean depths to avoid enemy detection. The vessel's special design allowed it to operate completely underwater without surfacing.","translation":"軍事潛水艇無聲地潛入海洋深處以避免敵人發現。該船的特殊設計允許它完全在水下運作而無需浮出水面。","word":"submarine"}},"submit":{"createdAt":1781832761709,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"submit 表示提交或呈交文件、作業等給相關的人或部門。","options":["display","hand in","steal","memorize"],"sentence":"The students must ______ their research papers by Friday or they will lose marks. The professor will review all the documents once they are handed in at the deadline.","translation":"學生必須在週五前提交他們的研究論文，否則他們將失去分數。教授將在截止日期時審查所有遞交的文件。","word":"submit"}},"subscribe":{"createdAt":1781837419095,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"Subscribe指的是為了定期接收報紙、雜誌或服務而支付費用並簽署協議。","options":["ignore","subscribe","return","donate"],"sentence":"Many readers ______ to the magazine to receive it every month at their home. They paid an annual fee to access all the latest articles and exclusive content.","translation":"許多讀者訂閱該雜誌，以便每月在家中收到。他們支付年費以訪問所有最新文章和獨家內容。","word":"subscribe"}},"subsidized":{"createdAt":1781362281661,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"subsidized表示獲得政府或組織的補助或財務支持。","options":["expensive","subsidized","private","luxury"],"sentence":"The ______ housing program helps low-income families afford homes. The government provides financial support to reduce the rent burden.","translation":"這個獲得補助的住房計畫幫助低收入家庭買得起房子。政府提供財務支持以減輕租金負擔。","word":"subsidized"}},"substance":{"createdAt":1781661288526,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"substance 是指具有物質形式的東西，可以是固體、液體或氣體等具體的物質","options":["theory","substance","idea","method"],"sentence":"The chemist analyzed the unknown ______ in the laboratory. After testing, she determined it was made of hydrogen and oxygen molecules.","translation":"化學家在實驗室裡分析了這種未知物質。經過測試後，她確定它是由氫分子和氧分子組成的。","word":"substance"}},"substantial":{"createdAt":1781402539337,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"substantial 表示數量大的、相當可觀的或具有實質意義的，通常指重要或重量級的東西。","options":["minimal","substantial","light","trace"],"sentence":"The ______ amount of rain caused flooding in several neighborhoods. The weather report showed that over 200 millimeters fell in just 24 hours.","translation":"大量的降雨在幾個社區造成了洪水。天氣報告顯示在短短24小時內下降了超過200毫米。","word":"substantial"}},"subtle":{"createdAt":1781693271585,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"subtle用來形容細微、不易察覺的差異或變化，與obvious和bold等詞形成對比。","options":["obvious","subtle","dramatic","bold"],"sentence":"The artist made ______ changes to the painting that only experts could notice. Most people walked past without seeing any difference at all.","translation":"藝術家對這幅畫進行了微妙的改變，只有專家才能注意到。大多數人走過時根本看不出有什麼不同。","word":"subtle"}},"succeed":{"createdAt":1781362281642,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"succeed表示成功或達成目標，通常與努力、堅持等正面詞彙搭配使用。","options":["fail","succeed","struggle","delay"],"sentence":"If you work hard and stay focused, you will ______ in your goals. Your determination and effort will eventually lead to achieving what you set out to do.","translation":"如果你努力工作並保持專注，你將會在目標上成功。你的決心和努力最終會導致實現你的目標。","word":"succeed"}},"success":{"createdAt":1781794866349,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"success指成功、成就，用來形容達到預期目標或取得成果的情況。","options":["failure","struggle","success","loss"],"sentence":"Her ______ in the business world came after years of hard work and dedication. She started from nothing and built a multi-million dollar company through perseverance.","translation":"她在商界的______ 來自多年的努力和奉獻。她從無到有，通過堅持不懈建立了一家價值數百萬美元的公司。","word":"success"}},"successful":{"createdAt":1781625891346,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"successful表示達到預期目標或取得良好成果","options":["failed","successful","controversial","forgotten"],"sentence":"The marketing campaign proved to be ______ beyond all expectations. Sales increased by 150% within just two months.","translation":"行銷活動的效果超出了所有預期的成功。銷售額在短短兩個月內增長了150%。","word":"successful"}},"successive":{"createdAt":1781693266945,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"successive表示連續發生的、相繼的，用來描述一個接著一個發生的事件或現象。","options":["occasional","successive","previous","simultaneous"],"sentence":"The team won ______ championships in 2020, 2021, and 2022. Each victory came one right after the other without any interruption.","translation":"該隊在2020年、2021年和2022年贏得了連續的冠軍。每次勝利都一個接一個地到來，沒有任何中斷。","word":"successive"}},"successor":{"createdAt":1781515329266,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"successor 名詞，意思是接替者、繼承人，指接替某人職位或地位的人。","options":["predecessor","successor","rival","employee"],"sentence":"The retiring CEO named his ______ during the board meeting yesterday. The company announced that this experienced executive would take over as the new leader next month.","translation":"退休的首席執行官在昨天的董事會會議上任命了他的繼承人。該公司宣布這位經驗豐富的主管將於下個月成為新領導人。","word":"successor"}},"sue":{"createdAt":1781484415229,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"sue是指在法律上向某人或某組織提起訴訟，要求賠償或尋求司法救濟。","options":["praise","hire","sue","congratulate"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ the manufacturer for selling defective products. They filed a legal complaint in court seeking compensation for damages.","translation":"該公司決定起訴製造商銷售有缺陷的產品。他們在法院提出法律訴狀，尋求損害賠償。","word":"sue"}},"suffer":{"createdAt":1781832508017,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"suffer 表示「遭受；受難」，指經歷痛苦、傷害或困難，常與 from 搭配使用。","options":["recover","suffer","benefit","heal"],"sentence":"Many people continue to ______ from the effects of the natural disaster years later. The psychologists are now treating their post-traumatic stress disorder.","translation":"許多人在多年後仍然遭受自然災害的影響。心理學家現在正在治療他們的創傷後壓力症。","word":"suffer"}},"suffice":{"createdAt":1781424137069,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"suffice 意為「足夠」，用來表示某物在數量或質量上能滿足需求。","options":["complicate","suffice","enhance","spoil"],"sentence":"A simple meal will ______ for our picnic lunch today. We don't need anything fancy since we're just going to a nearby park for a few hours.","translation":"一份簡單的餐點對於我們今天的野餐午餐就夠了。我們不需要任何花俏的東西，因為我們只是去附近的公園幾個小時。","word":"suffice"}},"sufficient":{"createdAt":1781920819165,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"sufficient 意為「充足的；足夠的」，表示數量或程度足以滿足需要或要求。","options":["excessive","adequate","minimal","insufficient"],"sentence":"The amount of funding available was ______ to complete the entire research project within budget. The team confirmed they had exactly what they needed without requiring additional resources.","translation":"可用的資金充足，足以在預算內完成整個研究項目。團隊確認他們擁有所需的一切，不需要額外資源。","word":"sufficient"}},"suffocate":{"createdAt":1781837601403,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"suffocate 作為動詞表示「使窒息而死」，指因缺氧或有害氣體導致無法呼吸而喪命。","options":["trap","suffocate","separate","injure"],"sentence":"The firefighters worked quickly to rescue the trapped miners before the toxic gas could ______ them in the deep shaft. Every second counted as the oxygen levels continued to drop dangerously low.","translation":"消防隊員們迅速工作，在有毒氣體在深井中使被困的礦工窒息身亡之前將他們救出。隨著氧氣水平危險地不斷下降，每一秒都至關重要。","word":"suffocate"}},"suggest":{"createdAt":1781798927525,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"suggest 表示提出建議或想法供他人考慮，語氣較為溫和，不具強制性。","options":["demand","suggest","require","force"],"sentence":"I ______ that we go to the new Italian restaurant downtown for dinner tonight. Based on the rave reviews and five-star ratings online, it seems like an excellent choice.","translation":"我建議我們今晚去市中心的新義大利餐廳用餐。根據網上的好評和五星評級，這似乎是一個絕佳的選擇。","word":"suggest"}},"suggestion":{"createdAt":1781848934136,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"suggestion指提出來供他人考慮或接納的想法或建議","options":["complaint","threat","suggestion","joke"],"sentence":"I made a ______ to improve the company's sales strategy during the meeting. My boss thanked me for proposing such a practical idea.","translation":"我在會議中提出了改進公司銷售策略的建議。我的老闆感謝我提出了這個實用的想法。","word":"suggestion"}},"suitability":{"createdAt":1781832508019,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"suitability 表示「適合；適當」，指某事物是否符合特定目的或需求。","options":["beauty","suitability","history","popularity"],"sentence":"The architect questioned the ______ of the location for building a hospital. The site was too far from major roads and public transportation, making it impractical for emergency services.","translation":"建築師質疑該地點對於建造醫院的適合性。該地點離主要道路和公共交通太遠，對於緊急服務來說不切實際。","word":"suitability"}},"suitable":{"createdAt":1781832761716,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"suitable 表示適宜的、合適的，指適合某種情況或目的的。","options":["inappropriate","colorful","appropriate","casual"],"sentence":"The dark blue suit was very ______ for the formal business meeting scheduled for Monday. The professional appearance matched the dress code requirements perfectly.","translation":"深藍色西裝非常適合定於週一的正式商務會議。專業的外表與著裝守則要求完美相符。","word":"suitable"}},"suite":{"createdAt":1781783820685,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"suite是指由多個房間組成的一套房間，通常用於飯店或公寓，各房間相互連接。","options":["suite","floor","room","building"],"sentence":"The hotel offers a luxurious ______ with a bedroom, living room, and private bathroom. When we checked in, the receptionist explained that all the rooms were interconnected as one accommodation.","translation":"飯店提供豪華套房，包括臥室、客廳和獨立浴室。我們辦理入住時，前台人員解釋所有房間都連接在一起作為一個住宿。","word":"suite"}},"sum":{"createdAt":1781784029105,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"total（總數）表示所有項目加在一起的最終結果，與「總數」的含義完全相同。","options":["number","total","cost","bill"],"sentence":"The ______ of all the expenses for the school trip came to five thousand dollars. The principal asked each parent to contribute an equal share toward this total amount.","translation":"學校旅行所有費用的總數達到了五千美元。校長要求每位家長對這個總金額貢獻相等的份額。","word":"sum"}},"summary":{"createdAt":1781849622419,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"摘要是指對某段文本、事件或主題的簡潔概述，保留主要信息但省略細枝末節。","options":["extension","summary","criticism","analysis"],"sentence":"The professor asked students to write a brief ______ of the novel. The one-page overview should capture the main plot points and character development without including unnecessary details.","translation":"教授要求學生寫一份簡短的小說摘要。這份一頁的概述應該涵蓋主要的情節點和角色發展，而不包括不必要的細節。","word":"summary"}},"summit":{"createdAt":1781839703150,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"summit指山峰或最高點，與reached the top at 8,848 meters（到達8848米的頂部）完全相符。","options":["valley","base","foothill","summit"],"sentence":"The mountain climbers reached the ______ after eight days of arduous climbing. They stood at 8,848 meters above sea level, at the top of the world.","translation":"登山者經過八天艱苦的攀登後到達了山頂。他們站在海拔8848米處，在世界之巔。","word":"summit"}},"superb":{"createdAt":1781449095500,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"superb意為極好的、傑出的，用來形容某事物品質優異或令人印象深刻。","options":["terrible","superb","average","mediocre"],"sentence":"The restaurant received a ______ review from the food critic. He praised every aspect of the meal and gave it five stars.","translation":"這家餐廳收到美食評論家的極好評價。他稱讚了這頓飯的每一個方面，並給了它五顆星。","word":"superb"}},"superintendent":{"createdAt":1781664082517,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"superintendent 是指負責管理和維護建築物或機構的人，特別是看管大樓的工作人員。","options":["owner","superintendent","architect","tenant"],"sentence":"The building ______ manages all maintenance and repairs for the apartment complex. He is responsible for fixing broken pipes, replacing light bulbs, and ensuring security.","translation":"大樓看管人負責管理公寓大樓的所有維修和保養工作。他負責修復破損的水管、更換燈泡以及確保安全。","word":"superintendent"}},"superior":{"createdAt":1781710289366,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"superior 是形容詞，表示「上等的；較優越的」，用來描述比其他事物更好或更高質量的東西。","options":["inferior","ordinary","superior","average"],"sentence":"This new smartphone model is considered ______ because it has better processing power and a longer battery life than its competitors. The technology reviewers consistently ranked it at the top of their comparison tests.","translation":"這款新智慧型手機因為處理能力更強和電池續航時間更長而被認為是上等的。科技評論家在比較測試中一致將其列為首選。","word":"superior"}},"superstition":{"createdAt":1781832761716,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"superstition 表示迷信，指由於傳統或無知而對某事的盲目信仰。","options":["fact","proof","folk belief","discovery"],"sentence":"The old woman's belief that black cats bring bad luck was merely a ______ passed down through generations. There was no scientific evidence to support this traditional belief.","translation":"這位老婦人認為黑貓會帶來厄運的信念只是代代相傳的迷信。沒有科學證據支持這一傳統信念。","word":"superstition"}},"superstitious":{"createdAt":1781428458261,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"superstitious形容相信迷信的人，認為某些行為或對象會帶來好運或壞運。","options":["normal","superstitious","contain","lecture"],"sentence":"The ______ old woman refused to walk under ladders or open umbrellas indoors. She believed these actions would bring her bad luck and cause misfortune.","translation":"迷信的老婦人拒絕在梯子下走過或在室內打開傘。她相信這些行為會給她帶來厄運和不幸。","word":"superstitious"}},"supervise":{"createdAt":1781565657693,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"supervise 動詞表示監督或管理他人的工作，確保按照標準和指示進行。","options":["ignore","supervise","hire","promote"],"sentence":"The manager needed to ______ the new employees during their first week of work. She checked their progress daily and provided guidance to ensure they followed proper procedures.","translation":"經理需要在新員工的第一週工作期間監督他們。她每天檢查他們的進度，並提供指導以確保他們遵循適當的程序。","word":"supervise"}},"supervisor":{"createdAt":1781425122881,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"supervisor 指監督人或管理者，與定期審查工作和監督員工這個脈絡相符。","options":["inferior","colleague","supervisor","competitor"],"sentence":"My ______ reviewed my work performance every quarter and provided helpful feedback. He was responsible for monitoring all employees in our department.","translation":"我的主管每季度都會審查我的工作表現並提供有幫助的反饋。他負責監督我們部門的所有員工。","word":"supervisor"}},"suppose":{"createdAt":1781871338550,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"suppose表示根據現有資訊做出的猜想或假設，需要進一步確認。","options":["ignore","assume","remember","announce"],"sentence":"I ______ that the meeting will start at 9 AM based on the email I received. However, I should confirm this with the organizer before making any plans.","translation":"我假設會議將在上午9點開始，根據我收到的電子郵件。但是，在制定任何計劃之前，我應該與組織者確認一下。","word":"suppose"}},"supposedly":{"createdAt":1781950727566,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"supposedly 表示據說或推測某事為真，但並非確定無疑。","options":["certainly","supposedly","actually","obviously"],"sentence":"He is ______ the best player on the team, but he rarely gets playing time. The coach seems to prefer other athletes despite his reputation.","translation":"他據說是隊上最好的球員，但他很少有上場時間。儘管他名譽很高，教練似乎更喜歡其他運動員。","word":"supposedly"}},"suppress":{"createdAt":1781532967171,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"suppress 表示鎮壓、壓制，與「阻止進入、防止集聚」的描述相符。","options":["encourage","suppress","announce","support"],"sentence":"The government tried to ______ the protest by blocking access to the city center. The authorities prevented demonstrators from gathering in public spaces.","translation":"政府試圖通過阻止進入市中心來______(鎮壓)抗議活動。當局阻止示威者在公共場所集聚。","word":"suppress"}},"suppression":{"createdAt":1781775598767,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"suppression作為名詞表示「鎮壓；隱瞞；抑制」，通常指權力機構對人民自由或權利的強力限制。","options":["promotion","protection","celebration","suppression"],"sentence":"The government's ______ of free speech angered many citizens who demanded their right to express opinions freely. Journalists were arrested and media outlets were shut down without any legal justification.","translation":"政府對言論自由的鎮壓激怒了許多公民，他們要求享有自由表達意見的權利。記者被逮捕，媒體機構無故關閉。","word":"suppression"}},"surgeon":{"createdAt":1781619188928,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"surgeon 指進行手術的醫療專家，特別是進行外科手術的醫師。","options":["pharmacist","surgeon","therapist","dentist"],"sentence":"The skilled ______ spent ten hours performing the complex operation on the patient's spine. Only a specialist with years of training could handle such delicate work.","translation":"這位熟練的外科醫師花費十個小時為患者進行複雜的脊椎手術。只有經過多年培訓的專家才能進行這種精細的工作。","word":"surgeon"}},"surgical":{"createdAt":1781449095507,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"surgical意為與外科手術相關的，用來形容手術用的工具、技術或程序。","options":["dental","surgical","cooking","gardening"],"sentence":"The doctor used ______ instruments to perform the operation. These specialized tools were sterilized in preparation for the procedure.","translation":"醫生使用外科手術器械進行手術。這些專門工具在手術前進行了消毒。","word":"surgical"}},"surname":{"createdAt":1781835517796,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"surname 意為姓氏，是一個人的家族名字，通常在全名的最後。","options":["nickname","surname","title","initial"],"sentence":"My ______ is Smith, which I inherited from my father's side of the family. It appears on all my official documents and is shared with all my relatives.","translation":"我的姓是史密斯，這是我從父親那一方繼承下來的。它出現在我所有的官方文件上，並且與我所有的親戚共享。","word":"surname"}},"surpass":{"createdAt":1781832761719,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"surpass 表示超過、優於、勝過，指在某方面優於或超越他人。","options":["match","lag","exceed","equal"],"sentence":"The new student's academic performance continued to ______ that of her classmates throughout the school year. She consistently scored higher on all tests and excelled in every subject.","translation":"這位新學生的學術成績在整個學年中不斷超越她的同學。她在所有測試中的成績一致地更高，並在每個科目中都表現出色。","word":"surpass"}},"surplus":{"createdAt":1781832761710,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"surplus 表示剩餘的、多出來的，超過需要或消耗量的部分。","options":["shortage","excess","deficit","limitation"],"sentence":"The farm produced a large ______ of wheat this year due to good weather conditions. The extra grain was donated to food banks to help people in need.","translation":"由於天氣良好，農場今年生產了大量過剩的小麥。多餘的穀物被捐贈給食物銀行以幫助有需要的人。","word":"surplus"}},"surround":{"createdAt":1781693265627,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"圍繞是指在四周形成一個圓圈或邊界，將某物包圍在中心。","options":["abandon","surround","connect","attack"],"sentence":"Tall mountains ______ the small village on all sides. Visitors must travel through narrow mountain passes to reach this remote location.","translation":"高山從四面八方圍繞著這個小村莊。遊客必須通過狹窄的山口才能到達這個偏遠地點。","word":"surround"}},"surveillance":{"createdAt":1781443653222,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"surveillance指的是對人員或場所的持續監視和盯梢，通常用於安全或執法目的。","options":["entertainment","decoration","surveillance","advertisement"],"sentence":"The security team installed multiple cameras throughout the building as part of their ______ system. Every hallway and entrance was monitored continuously to detect and prevent unauthorized access.","translation":"安全團隊在整個建築物內安裝了多個攝像頭作為監視系統的一部分。每條走廊和入口都被持續監控以檢測和防止未經授權的進入。","word":"surveillance"}},"survival":{"createdAt":1781564440924,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"survival 表示倖存、生存，指在困難環境中活著和繼續生存的能力。","options":["luxury","survival","entertainment","decoration"],"sentence":"The climber brought a first aid kit as essential equipment for ______ in the harsh mountain environment. Without proper supplies, his chances of staying safe would be greatly reduced.","translation":"登山者帶了一個急救箱作為在惡劣山地環境中倖存的必要設備。沒有適當的物資，他保持安全的機會會大大降低。","word":"survival"}},"suspect":{"createdAt":1781402154555,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"suspect作為動詞表示懷疑或對某人或某事產生疑心，通常基於某些證據或跡象。","options":["lack","hijack","suspect","possess"],"sentence":"The detective began to ______ that the butler was not telling the truth about his whereabouts. Evidence from security cameras showed he was in the mansion during the time of the crime.","translation":"偵探開始懷疑管家對自己行蹤的說法並不真實。安全攝像機的證據顯示他在犯罪時間正在宅邸內。","word":"suspect"}},"suspend":{"createdAt":1781414438958,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"suspend表示暫時停止、中止某項活動或服務","options":["increase","suspend","accelerate","redirect"],"sentence":"The bridge had to ______ traffic for several hours due to emergency repairs. Workers blocked off the entire roadway to ensure public safety.","translation":"由於緊急維修，大橋必須暫停交通數小時。工人們封閉了整條道路以確保公眾安全。","word":"suspend"}},"suspicion":{"createdAt":1781798927522,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"suspicion 表示對某人或某事的懷疑和不信任，通常源於令人困惑或矛盾的證據。","options":["trust","suspicion","sympathy","admiration"],"sentence":"The police officer viewed the suspect with great ______ when he found contradictions in his story. The witness's account did not match any of the facts presented by the accused.","translation":"當警官發現嫌疑人的故事中有矛盾之處時，對他產生了極大的懷疑。證人的陳述與被告提出的任何事實都不相符。","word":"suspicion"}},"sustainable":{"createdAt":1781965320892,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"sustainable 表示能夠長期維持和保持，不會耗盡資源或造成環保問題。","options":["temporary","wasteful","sustainable","harmful"],"sentence":"The company developed a ______ farming method that protects the environment. By maintaining soil quality and using renewable resources, farmers can continue producing crops for generations.","translation":"該公司開發了一種可持續的農業方法來保護環境。通過保持土壤品質和使用可再生資源，農民可以為後代繼續生產農作物。","word":"sustainable"}},"swamp":{"createdAt":1781580511755,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"swamp 是指充滿水和泥濘的濕地或沼澤地","options":["canyon","mountain","swamp","valley"],"sentence":"The explorer had to wade through the murky ______ to reach the other side of the forest. The waterlogged ground made every step difficult and muddy.","translation":"探險家必須涉過黑暗的沼澤地才能到達森林的另一邊。浸水的地面使每一步都困難且泥濘。","word":"swamp"}},"swap":{"createdAt":1781798927518,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"swap 表示兩方互相交換物品，使得原本屬於A的東西現在屬於B，反之亦然。","options":["share","swap","steal","compare"],"sentence":"The two friends decided to ______ their lunch boxes because they both wanted to try each other's food. By the end of lunch, each person had the other's original meal.","translation":"兩個朋友決定交換他們的午餐盒，因為他們都想嘗試彼此的食物。午餐結束時，每個人都擁有了對方原本的餐點。","word":"swap"}},"sway":{"createdAt":1781713470385,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"搖擺指物體在風力或力量作用下有節奏地前後或左右運動。","options":["sway","freeze","bloom","crack"],"sentence":"The tall trees began to ______ gently in the evening breeze. Their branches moved back and forth rhythmically as the wind grew stronger.","translation":"高大的樹木開始在晚風中輕輕搖擺。隨著風勢增強，樹枝有規律地前後擺動。","word":"sway"}},"swear":{"createdAt":1781775276771,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"swear指發誓或作莊嚴的承諾，尤其是在法律或宗教背景下進行。","options":["whisper","deny","swear","ignore"],"sentence":"The witness will ______ to tell the truth in court today. He will place his hand on the Bible and make a solemn legal promise.","translation":"證人今天將在法庭上發誓說真話。他將把手放在聖經上並做出莊嚴的法律承諾。","word":"swear"}},"swell":{"createdAt":1781709984198,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"swell 動詞表示身體部位因受傷或炎症而腫起或隆起。","options":["ache","swell","hurt","throb"],"sentence":"My ankle began to ______ after I twisted it during the soccer match. By the next morning, it had doubled in size and turned purple with bruising.","translation":"我在足球比賽中扭傷腳踝後，踝部開始腫脹。到了第二天早上，它的大小增加了一倍，並因瘀傷而變成紫色。","word":"swell"}},"swift":{"createdAt":1781429810263,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"swift是指速度快、動作敏捷的，形容人或事物移動迅速。","options":["symbol","detail","swift","temperature"],"sentence":"The ______ runner crossed the finish line in record time, leaving all competitors far behind. His incredible speed made him the undisputed champion of the race.","translation":"迅速的跑步者以創紀錄的時間衝過終點線，將所有競爭對手遠遠甩在身後。他的驚人速度使他成為這場比賽的無可爭議的冠軍。","word":"swift"}},"switch":{"createdAt":1781836375367,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"switch作動詞表示突然改變或調換，特別是從一種方式改為另一種方式。","options":["adjust","switch","transfer","switch"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ from using plastic packaging to recyclable materials. This major change was implemented across all their factories worldwide.","translation":"公司決定改變策略，從使用塑膠包裝轉為可回收材料。這項重大改變在全球所有工廠實施。","word":"switch"}},"swollen":{"createdAt":1781950727563,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"swollen 表示因液體積累或腫脹而膨脹的。","options":["broken","swollen","skinny","pale"],"sentence":"After the injury, his ______ ankle made it difficult to walk. The swelling was so pronounced that his foot looked twice its normal size.","translation":"受傷後，他腫脹的腳踝使行走困難。腫脹非常明顯，以至於他的腳看起來是正常尺寸的兩倍。","word":"swollen"}},"symbol":{"createdAt":1781429810259,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"symbol是指代表特定概念或事物的標誌或象徵，具有特殊的象徵意義。","options":["rite","symbol","firecracker","trustee"],"sentence":"The dove is a universal ______ of peace and hope, appearing in artworks and literature across many cultures. Nations often use this image in their official seals and monuments.","translation":"鴿子是和平與希望的普遍象徵，在許多文化的藝術作品和文學中出現。國家經常在其官方印章和紀念碑中使用這一形象。","word":"symbol"}},"symbolic":{"createdAt":1781832761715,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"symbolic 是形容詞，表示象徵的、符號性的，用作象徵或標記某種意義。","options":["practical","literal","figurative","commercial"],"sentence":"The dove released at the ceremony had ______ meaning for the nation. It represented peace, hope, and the beginning of a new era after the conflict.","translation":"在儀式上釋放的鴿子對國家具有象徵意義。它代表和平、希望以及衝突後新時代的開始。","word":"symbolic"}},"symmetry":{"createdAt":1781848934135,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"symmetry指事物兩邊完全相同或相似的特性，具有平衡和和諧的視覺效果","options":["complexity","symmetry","height","color"],"sentence":"The building's design displays perfect ______ on both sides of its facade. Each architectural element on the left mirrors exactly what appears on the right.","translation":"建築物的設計在其正面的兩側呈現完美的對稱。左邊的每個建築元素都與右邊出現的完全相同。","word":"symmetry"}},"symphony":{"createdAt":1781337343697,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"symphony是指由多個樂章組成、為大型樂隊創作的長篇交響樂作品。","options":["poem","sandwich","symphony","painting"],"sentence":"The orchestra performed a beautiful ______ that lasted over an hour during the concert. The composer had skillfully arranged multiple instrumental sections to create a complex and harmonious piece.","translation":"樂隊在音樂會中演奏了一部持續超過一小時的美麗交響樂。作曲家巧妙地編排了多個樂器部分來創作這個複雜和諧的樂曲。","word":"symphony"}},"syndrome":{"createdAt":1781311983486,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"syndrome 指一組相關症狀的集合，在醫學上表示特定疾病的特徵表現。","options":["arena","syndrome","mature","timer"],"sentence":"The patient was diagnosed with a rare ______ that caused multiple physical and neurological symptoms. The doctor explained that this collection of symptoms typically appear together as a recognizable pattern.","translation":"患者被診斷患有一種罕見的症候群，導致多種生理和神經症狀。醫生解釋說這一系列症狀通常作為可識別的模式一起出現。","word":"syndrome"}},"synonym":{"createdAt":1781842656773,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"同義字是指意思相同或非常相似的詞彙，可以在許多情況下互相替代而不改變句子的主要意思。","options":["homonym","antonym","synonym","acronym"],"sentence":"The word \"happy\" is a ______ for \"joyful\" because they have almost the same meaning. When you replace one word with the other in a sentence, the overall message remains virtually unchanged.","translation":"「開心」是「快樂」的同義字，因為它們的意思幾乎相同。當你在句子中用其中一個詞替換另一個詞時，整體意思基本保持不變。","word":"synonym"}},"synthesis":{"createdAt":1781849622416,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"綜合是指將多個部分或元素組合在一起形成一個整體，特別是將不同的信息或想法整合成一個統一的整體。","options":["division","synthesis","criticism","isolation"],"sentence":"The researcher combined multiple studies to create a ______ of recent findings. The final report integrated data from ten different experiments into one comprehensive document.","translation":"研究人員結合多項研究來創建最近發現的綜合。最終報告將來自十個不同實驗的數據整合為一份綜合文件。","word":"synthesis"}},"synthetic":{"createdAt":1781950727560,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"synthetic 指由人工製造的合成物質，通常不是天然來源的。","options":["organic","authentic","synthetic","rare"],"sentence":"This fabric is made from ______ materials rather than natural fibers. The manufacturer uses petroleum-based chemicals in the production process.","translation":"這種織物由合成材料製成，而不是天然纖維。製造商在生產過程中使用石油基化學物質。","word":"synthetic"}},"syrup":{"createdAt":1781848330181,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"syrup是濃稠的糖水或蜂蜜類液體，常用於甜點和飲料中增加甜味。","options":["butter","syrup","cream","milk"],"sentence":"I poured thick ______ over my pancakes at breakfast this morning. The sweet, sticky liquid made every bite taste delicious and covered the entire surface of my meal.","translation":"今天早上早餐時，我在我的煎餅上倒了厚厚的糖漿。這種甜蜜、粘稠的液體讓每一口都味道美妙，覆蓋了我整餐的表面。","word":"syrup"}},"systematic":{"createdAt":1781849847406,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"systematic表示有系統的或有組織的，與「清楚分類、妥善記錄、提高效率」的線索相符。","options":["random","systematic","chaotic","haphazard"],"sentence":"Her ______ approach to organizing the files made the office much more efficient. Everything was categorized clearly and documented properly.","translation":"她對文件進行組織的有系統的方法使辦公室效率更高。所有東西都被清楚地分類並妥善記錄。","word":"systematic"}},"tangle":{"createdAt":1781311685838,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tangle指的是復雜的糾結或纏繞狀態，通常用來形容難以理清的亂麻般的情況。","options":["pile","knot","net","collection"],"sentence":"The fishing line got into a complicated ______ after being left in the box for months. It took hours to carefully unwind and separate all the knotted strands.","translation":"釣魚線在盒子裡放了幾個月後陷入了複雜的糾結。花了好幾個小時才仔細解開並分開所有纏繞的線條。","word":"tangle"}},"target":{"createdAt":1781832761712,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"target 作名詞表示靶子、目標物，即射擊或攻擊的對象。","options":["bow","ground","mark","forest"],"sentence":"The archer aimed carefully at the ______ before releasing the arrow. He had been training for months to hit the bullseye consistently from a distance.","translation":"弓箭手在放箭前仔細瞄準靶子。他已經訓練了數月，以從遠距離一致地射中靶心。","word":"target"}},"tax":{"createdAt":1781437220551,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「Tax」作動詞表示政府對收入或商品徵稅。","options":["exempt","tax","reduce","eliminate"],"sentence":"The government will ______ all income above $50,000 at a rate of 25%. Citizens must file their annual returns by April 15th to pay what they owe.","translation":"政府將對超過5萬美元的所有收入按25%的稅率徵稅。公民必須在4月15日之前提交年度申報表以支付應納稅款。","word":"tax"}},"tease":{"createdAt":1781431278557,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tease指以玩樂的方式嘲笑或戲弄某人，通常帶有友善的意圖。","options":["encourage","tease","praise","ignore"],"sentence":"The older siblings love to ______ their younger brother about his new haircut. They laugh and make jokes whenever he comes into the room, but he knows they're just playing around.","translation":"年長的兄弟姐妹喜歡因為弟弟的新髮型而嘲笑他。每當他進入房間時，他們都會大笑並開玩笑，但他知道他們只是在玩耍。","word":"tease"}},"technological":{"createdAt":1781601735994,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「technological」指與工業技術和科技相關的，常用來描述涉及機器、軟體或科學進步的事物。","options":["cultural","educational","technological","political"],"sentence":"The company invested millions in ______ advancement to stay competitive in the market. Their research team developed new software and machinery that revolutionized production efficiency.","translation":"該公司投入數百萬美元進行技術進步以保持市場競爭力。他們的研究團隊開發了革命性的新軟體和機器，改善了生產效率。","word":"technological"}},"technology":{"createdAt":1781481124704,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"technology 指應用科學原理進行實用設計和開發的技術和方法。","options":["tradition","invention","advancement","document"],"sentence":"The latest ______ in smartphone design includes advanced cameras and faster processors. These innovations allow users to perform tasks that were impossible just a few years ago.","translation":"智能手機設計的最新技術進步包括先進的攝像頭和更快的處理器。這些創新使用戶能夠執行幾年前不可能完成的任務。","word":"technology"}},"tedious":{"createdAt":1781831848727,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tedious 是形容詞，表示「乏味的」或「令人厭倦的」，強調內容或活動的單調無趣。","options":["complex","tedious","thick","lengthy"],"sentence":"Reading that ______ instruction manual made me feel exhausted and bored. I nearly fell asleep by the time I finished the third chapter.","translation":"閱讀那份乏味的說明書讓我感到疲憊和無聊。當我讀完第三章時，我幾乎要睡著了。","word":"tedious"}},"tedium":{"createdAt":1781738392787,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「tedium」指令人厭煩和沉悶的感覺，與長時間無趣的演講和與會者昏昏欲睡的狀態完全相符。","options":["obligation","offense","tedium","trophy"],"sentence":"The long meeting filled everyone with a sense of ______ as the speaker droned on endlessly. By the third hour, most attendees were struggling to stay awake.","translation":"隨著演講者沒完沒了地講話，冗長的會議使每個人都感到沉悶。到了第三個小時，大多數與會者都在努力保持清醒。","word":"tedium"}},"teller":{"createdAt":1781424356416,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"teller指的是在銀行或金融機構中直接與顧客進行交易的工作人員。","options":["manager","guard","teller","accountant"],"sentence":"The bank ______ counted the cash drawer at the end of her shift. She worked behind the counter handling customer deposits and withdrawals all day long.","translation":"銀行出納員在她班次結束時清點現金抽屜。她整天在櫃檯後面工作，處理客户的存款和取款。","word":"teller"}},"temperament":{"createdAt":1781425094901,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"temperament 指一個人的天生氣質或性格特徵，包括他們對事物的反應方式。","options":["schedule","appearance","disposition","education"],"sentence":"Her calm and patient ______ made her an excellent teacher for difficult students. Even when children acted out in class, she never lost her composure or raised her voice.","translation":"她冷靜且耐心的氣質使她成為困難學生的優秀教師。即使孩子在課堂上調皮，她也從不失去冷靜或提高嗓音。","word":"temperament"}},"temperature":{"createdAt":1781429810256,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"temperature是指物質或人體的冷熱程度，通常用攝氏度或華氏度來測量。","options":["objection","temperature","trustee","square"],"sentence":"The doctor measured the patient's ______ and found it was 39 degrees Celsius, indicating a high fever. This reading showed that the infection was serious.","translation":"醫生測量了患者的體溫，發現是攝氏39度，表示高燒。這個讀數顯示感染很嚴重。","word":"temperature"}},"temple":{"createdAt":1781337343694,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"temple是指廟宇或寺廟，是宗教信仰者進行祈禱和祭祀的地方。","options":["hospital","temple","museum","castle"],"sentence":"The ancient ______ stood on the hilltop, attracting thousands of pilgrims each year. Visitors came to pray and make offerings at this sacred religious site.","translation":"古老的廟宇聳立在山頂上，每年吸引數千名朝聖者。遊客來到這個神聖的宗教場所祈禱和獻祭。","word":"temple"}},"tempo":{"createdAt":1781832761712,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"tempo 表示音樂或動作的節奏、步調、速度，用於衡量時間流逝的快慢。","options":["volume","pitch","pace","rhythm"],"sentence":"The conductor slowed down the ______ of the orchestra during the sad section of the symphony. The musicians played more slowly and deliberately to create a melancholic atmosphere.","translation":"指揮家在交響樂悲傷段落期間放慢樂隊的節奏。音樂家們以更緩慢而刻意的方式演奏以營造憂鬱的氛圍。","word":"tempo"}},"temporarily":{"createdAt":1781693264939,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"temporarily 是副詞，表示「暫時地」或「短期地」，用來修飾某個動作或狀態是不永久的。","options":["socially","valueless","temporarily","vanish"],"sentence":"The store closed its doors ______ due to renovations and construction work. The manager announced that it would reopen in three weeks after all the improvements were completed.","translation":"這家商店因為裝修和施工工作暫時關閉。經理宣布在所有改善完成後三週內將重新開放。","word":"temporarily"}},"temporary":{"createdAt":1781704395605,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"temporary表示「暫時的」，用來形容預期會改變或被移除的事物","options":["permanent","temporary","threatening","threshold"],"sentence":"The construction company set up ______ barriers around the work site. However, they plan to remove everything by next month when the project is completed.","translation":"建築公司在工地周圍設置了暫時性的障礙物。不過，當專案在下個月完成時，他們計畫將所有東西都移除。","word":"temporary"}},"tempt":{"createdAt":1781693264938,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"tempt 是動詞，表示「誘惑」或「慫恿」，指引誘某人做出某個行為，通常帶有吸引力的承諾。","options":["vanish","temporarily","tempt","socially"],"sentence":"The advertisement tried to ______ consumers with promises of free gifts and huge discounts on luxury products. Many people were unable to resist the attractive offer and immediately made purchases.","translation":"廣告試圖以免費禮物和奢侈品大幅折扣的承諾誘惑消費者。許多人無法抗拒這個吸引人的優惠，立即進行購買。","word":"tempt"}},"temptation":{"createdAt":1781842419966,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"temptation指一種難以抗拒的欲望或引人犯錯的事物；在這裡特別指應該被抗拒的不良衝動。","options":["opportunity","temptation","motivation","permission"],"sentence":"The ______ to eat dessert was strong after dinner, but I managed to resist it. My doctor had warned me that sugar would worsen my health condition.","translation":"晚餐後吃甜點的誘惑很強，但我還是抵抗住了。我的醫生警告我說糖會惡化我的健康狀況。","word":"temptation"}},"tempting":{"createdAt":1781841742851,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"tempting 作形容詞表示「誘人的、吸引人的」，指某物令人想要嘗試或擁有。","options":["repulsive","boring","tempting","ordinary"],"sentence":"The dessert looked so ______ with its rich chocolate and fresh berries that I almost forgot my diet. I had to resist the urge to order it immediately.","translation":"那道甜點看起來誘人極了，有豐富的巧克力和新鮮的漿果，我幾乎忘記了我的飲食計劃。我不得不抗拒立即訂購它的衝動。","word":"tempting"}},"tenant":{"createdAt":1781565657694,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tenant 名詞指租賃房產的人，他們向房東支付租金以換取居住權。","options":["landlord","tenant","neighbor","contractor"],"sentence":"The ______ paid rent to the landlord every month for living in the apartment. Without this person's monthly payment, the property owner would not receive income from the unit.","translation":"租戶每個月向房東支付租金以居住在公寓中。沒有這個人的月度付款，房產所有者將無法從該單位獲得收入。","word":"tenant"}},"tendency":{"createdAt":1781950727558,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tendency 指一種經常性的傾向或習慣，用來描述某人或某事物經常發生的行為模式。","options":["achievement","tendency","location","emotion"],"sentence":"She has a ______ to arrive late to every meeting. Her colleagues have noticed this pattern happening consistently for months.","translation":"她有一種經常遲到開會的傾向。她的同事已經注意到這種模式持續了幾個月。","word":"tendency"}},"tense":{"createdAt":1781824968064,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"tense 作為形容詞表示緊張的、焦慮的或充滿壓力的氣氛或情緒狀態。","options":["relaxed","cheerful","tense","comfortable"],"sentence":"The atmosphere in the courtroom became very ______ as the judge was about to announce the verdict. Everyone held their breath waiting to hear the final decision.","translation":"當法官即將宣佈判決時，法庭裡的氣氛變得非常緊張。每個人都屏住呼吸等待聽到最終決定。","word":"tense"}},"tension":{"createdAt":1781704395611,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"tension表示「緊張」或「不安的狀態」，指人與人之間或群體內部因為衝突或分歧而產生的不和諧氣氛","options":["thesis","adoption","temporary","tension"],"sentence":"The ______ in the negotiation room grew as both parties refused to compromise on key issues. Eventually, the meeting was postponed until cooler heads could revisit the discussion.","translation":"隨著雙方在關鍵問題上拒絕妥協，談判室內的緊張局勢不斷升高。最終，會議被推遲到雙方能夠冷靜地重新討論該問題時。","word":"tension"}},"tentative":{"createdAt":1781452425258,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tentative表示暫時性的、試驗性的，用來形容還未最終確定的計劃或想法。","options":["permanent","preliminary","final","concrete"],"sentence":"The manager made a ______ plan for the project launch next month. Once we receive approval from headquarters, we will finalize all the details.","translation":"經理為下個月的項目啟動制定了試驗性的計劃。一旦我們獲得總部的批准，我們將確定所有細節。","word":"tentative"}},"tentatively":{"createdAt":1781824968060,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tentatively 表示暫時性的、保留態度的或試驗性的同意，意味著還沒有做出最終決定。","options":["firmly","tentatively","enthusiastically","immediately"],"sentence":"The company ______ agreed to the merger proposal during the initial negotiations. However, they wanted to review all the documents carefully before making a final commitment.","translation":"公司在初步談判中試驗性地同意了合併提案。然而，他們希望在做出最終承諾之前仔細審查所有文件。","word":"tentatively"}},"terminate":{"createdAt":1781746685520,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"terminate指的是終止、結束，表示使某事物停止或結束，特別是指正式或官方的結束。","options":["terminate","mentality","moisture","medal"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ the contract after discovering the vendor's poor quality work. All business relations between the two parties ended immediately.","translation":"公司在發現供應商工作質量差後決定終止合同。兩方之間的所有業務關係立即結束。","word":"terminate"}},"terms":{"createdAt":1781843207978,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"此字在法律或商業文件中指的是雙方必須遵守的條件和規定。","options":["signatures","terms","dates","names"],"sentence":"Before signing the contract, both parties must agree on all the ______. The document specifies payment amounts, deadlines, and conditions that each side must follow.","translation":"簽署合約前，雙方必須同意所有條款。該文件規定了每一方必須遵守的付款金額、截止日期和條件。","word":"terms"}},"terrace":{"createdAt":1781843207979,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"此字指的是建築物外的露天平臺或陽台，通常用於戶外活動。","options":["basement","terrace","hallway","kitchen"],"sentence":"The restaurant features a beautiful outdoor ______ where guests can dine under the stars. Tables and chairs are arranged on this elevated, flat area overlooking the city skyline.","translation":"這家餐廳有一個美麗的戶外露台，客人可以在星空下用餐。桌椅排列在這個俯瞰城市天際線的升起平臺上。","word":"terrace"}},"terrific":{"createdAt":1781843207979,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"此形容詞表示極好的、出色的，通常用於讚美某件事物的品質。","options":["boring","terrible","confusing","terrific"],"sentence":"The performance was absolutely ______, and the audience gave the actors a standing ovation. Everyone in the theater agreed it was one of the best shows they had ever seen.","translation":"這場演出絕對精彩，觀眾給了演員們起立鼓掌。劇院裡的每個人都同意這是他們看過的最好的演出之一。","word":"terrific"}},"terrify":{"createdAt":1782007196629,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「使驚恐」表示引起極端的恐懼或驚慌，通常是突然和強烈的情感反應。","options":["entertain","inspire","terrify","bore"],"sentence":"The horror movie was designed to ______ audiences with its graphic scenes and sudden jumps. When the killer appeared on screen without warning, people in the theater screamed and covered their eyes.","translation":"這部恐怖電影旨在通過其血腥的場景和突然的驚嚇來使觀眾感到驚恐。當殺手在沒有任何警告的情況下出現在螢幕上時，影院裡的人尖叫並掩住眼睛。","word":"terrify"}},"terror":{"createdAt":1781774456601,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"terror 指由暴力或威脅引起的極端恐懼和驚駭感。","options":["joy","confusion","fear","excitement"],"sentence":"The ______ caused by the bombing spread throughout the city as people fled in panic. Citizens were horrified by the sudden attack.","translation":"炸彈攻擊引起的恐怖蔓延整個城市，人們驚慌逃離。市民對突然的襲擊感到驚駭。","word":"terror"}},"testament":{"createdAt":1781849847409,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"testament表示證明或驗證，與「證明品格、說明價值觀」的線索相符。","options":["contradiction","testament","denial","refusal"],"sentence":"His dedication to charity is a ______ to his generous character. His years of volunteer work speak volumes about his values.","translation":"他對慈善事業的奉獻證明了他慷慨的品格。他多年的志願工作充分說明了他的價值觀。","word":"testament"}},"text":{"createdAt":1781402539336,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"text 指書籍、雜誌或文章中的正文內容，即主要的文字材料部分。","options":["margin","text","cover","spine"],"sentence":"The student highlighted important passages in the ______ of her history book. She focused on the words and paragraphs rather than the photographs and diagrams.","translation":"學生在她的歷史書的正文中突出顯示了重要段落。她專注於文字和段落，而不是照片和圖表。","word":"text"}},"textile":{"createdAt":1781693347905,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"textile指的是紡織品或織品，通常指用纖維製成的布料或衣物材料。","options":["wage","textile","tuition","villain"],"sentence":"The factory specializes in producing high-quality ______ such as cotton and silk fabrics. These materials are then sold to clothing manufacturers around the world.","translation":"這家工廠專門生產高品質的紡織品，如棉布和絲綢布料。這些材料隨後被賣給世界各地的服裝製造商。","word":"textile"}},"texture":{"createdAt":1781848330173,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"texture指物體表面的觸覺感受和質地，包括光滑、粗糙、柔軟等特性。","options":["color","texture","weight","smell"],"sentence":"The ______ of the silk fabric felt incredibly smooth against my skin. Running my fingers across it, I noticed it had a soft and delicate quality rather than a rough or bumpy surface.","translation":"絲綢布料的觸感對我的皮膚來說感覺異常光滑。用手指在它上面劃過時，我注意到它有柔軟精緻的特質，而不是粗糙或凹凸不平的表面。","word":"texture"}},"theology":{"createdAt":1781848934148,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"theology指研究宗教、信仰和上帝的學科","options":["biology","theology","chemistry","psychology"],"sentence":"Professor Harrison teaches ______ at the university and specializes in religious philosophy. His lectures examine the nature of God and faith across different traditions.","translation":"哈里森教授在大學教授神學並專門研究宗教哲學。他的講座探討了不同傳統中上帝的本質和信仰。","word":"theology"}},"theoretical":{"createdAt":1781839950961,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"theoretical 指的是基於理論的,與實際情況相對,強調基於原則而非實踐。","options":["practical","experimental","theoretical","accurate"],"sentence":"The professor presented ______ models of how markets should function in perfect conditions. However, real-world economics often behaves very differently due to unpredictable consumer behavior.","translation":"教授展示了市場在完美條件下應該如何運作的理論模型。然而,現實世界的經濟學通常因為無法預測的消費者行為而表現得非常不同。","word":"theoretical"}},"theoretically":{"createdAt":1781481124693,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"theoretically 表示根據理論或假說，但可能與現實情況不同。","options":["Practically","Actually","In reality","In principle"],"sentence":"______, the plan should work perfectly if all conditions are ideal and nothing goes wrong. However, in practice, unexpected problems often arise that require adjustment.","translation":"理論上，如果所有條件理想且沒有出現問題，該計畫應該完美運作。然而，在實踐中，意外問題經常出現，需要調整。","word":"theoretically"}},"thereafter":{"createdAt":1781935654223,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"thereafter 是副詞，表示「之後」或「從那時以後」，指某個時間點之後發生的事情。","options":["before","thereafter","previously","currently"],"sentence":"The company was founded in 1995, and ______ it became one of the largest manufacturers in Asia. From that point on, they never stopped growing.","translation":"這家公司成立於1995年，之後它成為亞洲最大的製造商之一。從那時起，他們從未停止增長。","word":"thereafter"}},"thesis":{"createdAt":1781704395609,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"thesis表示「論文」，指學生完成學位課程時提交的正式學術文件","options":["barrier","threshold","thesis","tension"],"sentence":"The university required each doctoral student to submit a ______ demonstrating their original research findings. The committee would carefully review it over several months before granting the degree.","translation":"大學要求每位博士學位候選人提交一份論文，展示他們的原創研究發現。委員會將在數個月內仔細審查，然後才授予學位。","word":"thesis"}},"theta":{"createdAt":1781228443754,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"Theta是希臘字母表中的第八個字母，在數學和物理學中最常用來代表角度或相位角。","options":["theta","iota","zeta","kappa"],"sentence":"The eighth letter of the Greek alphabet is ______. Engineers and mathematicians use this symbol extensively to denote angles in trigonometry and calculus problems.","translation":"希臘字母表中的第八個字母是______。工程師和數學家廣泛使用這個符號來表示三角學和微積分問題中的角度。","word":"theta"}},"thoroughly":{"createdAt":1781832761709,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"thoroughly 是副詞，表示徹底地、完全地、仔細地做某事。","options":["quickly","completely","partially","casually"],"sentence":"The detective ______ investigated the crime scene to find all possible evidence. He examined every corner, checked all surfaces, and took detailed photographs of everything.","translation":"偵探徹底調查了犯罪現場以尋找所有可能的證據。他檢查了每一個角落，檢視了所有表面，並對所有東西進行了詳細拍照。","word":"thoroughly"}},"thoughtful":{"createdAt":1781257238301,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"thoughtful形容人具有體貼、周到的品質，或者深思熟慮的態度。","options":["careless","thoughtful","lazy","rude"],"sentence":"Marcus was a ______ friend who always remembered his friends' birthdays and called to check on them. His actions showed he genuinely cared about others' feelings and wellbeing.","translation":"馬可是一位體貼的朋友，他總是記得朋友的生日，並打電話看望他們。他的行動表明他真心關心他人的感受和幸福。","word":"thoughtful"}},"threat":{"createdAt":1781704395608,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"threat表示「威脅」或「危險」，指可能造成傷害或損失的事物","options":["solution","thesis","threshold","threat"],"sentence":"The rising sea levels posed a serious ______ to coastal communities worldwide. Governments began investing in defense systems and relocation programs to protect their citizens.","translation":"海平面上升對全球沿海社區構成了嚴重的威脅。各國政府開始投資防禦系統和搬遷計畫來保護其公民。","word":"threat"}},"threatening":{"createdAt":1781704395608,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"threatening作為形容詞表示「有威脅性的」或「危險的」，用來形容看起來可能造成傷害的情況","options":["temporary","thesis","threatening","adopt"],"sentence":"The sky turned dark and ______, with heavy clouds rolling in from the west. The weather forecast warned that a severe storm would arrive within the next two hours.","translation":"天空變得黑暗且具有威脅性，濃厚的烏雲從西邊滾滾而來。氣象預報警告說，一場暴風雨將在接下來的兩小時內到達。","word":"threatening"}},"threshold":{"createdAt":1781704395612,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"threshold表示「門檻」或「起點」，指進入新階段或達到新水準的關鍵點","options":["threat","temporary","threshold","tension"],"sentence":"The athlete finally crossed the ______ into professional sports after years of training and dedication. She signed her first major contract with a leading international team.","translation":"經過多年的訓練和奉獻，運動員終於進入了職業體育的門檻。她與一支領先的國際隊簽署了她的第一份重要合約。","word":"threshold"}},"thrive":{"createdAt":1781566460880,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"thrive表示在良好條件下生長繁榮，與後句提到的植物不會枯萎形成對比。","options":["wilt","thrive","fade","shrink"],"sentence":"Plants ______ in warm sunlight and rich soil. Without proper nutrients, they would wither and die instead.","translation":"植物在溫暖的陽光和肥沃的土壤中茂盛生長。沒有適當的營養，它們會枯萎和死亡。","word":"thrive"}},"thrust":{"createdAt":1781664082520,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"thrust 是指猛烈地推、刺或插入某物，通常涉及快速有力的動作。","options":["withdrew","thrust","lifted","rotated"],"sentence":"The fencer ______ his sword forward with great force to attack his opponent. The blade pierced through the air in a quick, aggressive stabbing motion.","translation":"擊劍手用很大的力量向前推進他的劍去攻擊對手。劍刃以快速、具有侵略性的刺戳動作穿過空氣。","word":"thrust"}},"tidy":{"createdAt":1781503378968,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"tidy 表示整齊、清潔和井井有條的狀態，或整理和收拾的動作。","options":["messy","dirty","tidy","chaotic"],"sentence":"After the party ended, she spent hours making the house ______ again. Every cushion was straightened, the floor was swept, and all items were returned to their proper places.","translation":"派對結束後，她花了幾個小時使房子再次整潔。每個墊子都被整理好，地板被掃乾淨，所有物品都被放回原位。","word":"tidy"}},"tile":{"createdAt":1781564440923,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tile 作名詞表示瓷磚、瓦片，指用於鋪地或牆面的平方形陶瓷製品。","options":["brick","tile","wood","carpet"],"sentence":"The bathroom floor was covered with small ceramic ______ in a blue and white pattern. Each individual piece was carefully arranged to create an attractive mosaic design.","translation":"浴室地板上覆蓋著藍白相間圖案的小陶瓷瓷磚。每一塊都被仔細排列成有吸引力的馬賽克設計。","word":"tile"}},"tilt":{"createdAt":1781950727563,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tilt 指使某物傾斜或以角度移動。","options":["lower","tilt","spin","straighten"],"sentence":"He had to ______ his head back to see the top of the tall building. Leaning backward at an angle was the only way to view it completely.","translation":"他不得不向後傾斜頭部以看到高樓的頂部。向後傾斜是完全看到它的唯一方式。","word":"tilt"}},"tilted":{"createdAt":1781515329260,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tilted 形容詞，意思是傾斜的、歪斜的，描述物體不平直的狀態。","options":["straight","tilted","centered","aligned"],"sentence":"The picture frame hung ______ on the wall, creating an uncomfortable visual effect. We adjusted it so that the top edge was perfectly level with the ceiling.","translation":"相框在牆上掛得歪斜，產生了令人不舒適的視覺效果。我們調整它，使上邊緣與天花板完全水平。","word":"tilted"}},"timber":{"createdAt":1781362281727,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"timber指的是木材，特別是用於建築或製造的木料。","options":["metal","timber","plastic","concrete"],"sentence":"The construction company ordered high-quality ______ for the new building project. The wood was carefully selected for its strength and durability.","translation":"建築公司為新建築項目訂購了高質量的木材。木頭因其強度和耐久性而被仔細選擇。","word":"timber"}},"timer":{"createdAt":1781311983484,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"timer 是計時或定時的裝置，用來測量特定時間段的流逝。","options":["evolution","average","timer","syndrome"],"sentence":"I set the kitchen ______ to remind me when the cookies were done baking. After fifteen minutes, the device beeped loudly to alert me that time was up.","translation":"我設置廚房定時器提醒我餅乾何時烤好。十五分鐘後，該裝置發出大聲嗶聲警告我時間到了。","word":"timer"}},"timid":{"createdAt":1781503378970,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"timid 表示容易害怕、缺乏勇氣或自信，特別是在面對陌生人或新情況時。","options":["brave","bold","timid","confident"],"sentence":"The ______ child hid behind his mother when strangers approached him. He was too fearful and shy to speak to people he didn't know.","translation":"這個膽小的孩子當陌生人靠近時躲在媽媽身後。他太害怕和羞怯，不敢和陌生人說話。","word":"timid"}},"tiptoe":{"createdAt":1781950727563,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tiptoe 指用腳尖輕輕地行走，通常是為了保持安靜。","options":["wheels","tiptoe","stilts","ladders"],"sentence":"She walked on ______ through the library to avoid disturbing the other readers. Her quiet, delicate steps made no sound on the carpet.","translation":"她踮著腳尖走過圖書館，以免打擾其他讀者。她安靜而細膩的步伐在地毯上沒有發出任何聲音。","word":"tiptoe"}},"tolerance":{"createdAt":1781746685500,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tolerance指的是寬容、忍耐，表示對他人缺點或過錯的理解和接納態度。","options":["consequence","tolerance","laborious","affirm"],"sentence":"The teacher showed great ______ towards her students' mistakes during the learning process. She understood that errors were natural and important for growth.","translation":"老師在學生的學習過程中對他們的錯誤表現出很大的寬容。她明白錯誤是成長過程中自然且重要的一部分。","word":"tolerance"}},"tolerant":{"createdAt":1781503378963,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"tolerant 表示能夠忍受、接納或寬恕與自己不同的事物或觀點。","options":["judgmental","biased","tolerant","narrow-minded"],"sentence":"His ______ attitude toward different cultures made him a respected leader. He actively listened to people with opposing viewpoints and never dismissed their beliefs.","translation":"他對不同文化的寬容態度使他成為受尊敬的領導者。他積極傾聽持相反觀點的人，從不否定他們的信念。","word":"tolerant"}},"toll":{"createdAt":1781838276302,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"toll在此指因災難造成的死傷人數或損失。","options":["volume","toll","claim","ordeal"],"sentence":"The ______ of the earthquake was devastating, with thousands of lives lost. Emergency officials announced the final death count after three weeks of search and rescue operations.","translation":"地震的死傷人數是毀滅性的，有數千人喪生。急難救助官員在三週的搜救行動後宣佈了最終的死亡人數。","word":"toll"}},"tomb":{"createdAt":1781871338566,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"tomb表示埋葬死者的地方，特別是古代的墳墓，通常包含遺骸和陪葬品。","options":["temple","fortress","burial chamber","monument"],"sentence":"The archaeologists discovered an ancient Egyptian ______ buried deep beneath the sand of the desert. Inside, they found the mummified remains of a pharaoh and treasures of immense historical value.","translation":"考古學家在沙漠沙土深處發現了一個古埃及墳墓。裡面有法老的木乃伊遺骨和具有巨大歷史價值的寶藏。","word":"tomb"}},"ton":{"createdAt":1781503378957,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ton 是重量單位，1 公噸等於 1000 公斤，用於測量大型物體的重量。","options":["kilos","tons","pounds","grams"],"sentence":"The cargo ship was carrying ______ of steel across the ocean. The ship's scale indicated it had loaded exactly 500 units of weight measurement.","translation":"貨輪正在運送數噸鋼鐵穿越大洋。船的秤表顯示它裝載了正好 500 噸。","word":"ton"}},"tore":{"createdAt":1781503378958,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tore 是 tear 的過去式，表示用力撕裂或扯破某物。","options":["cut","tore","burned","folded"],"sentence":"He ______ the letter into small pieces in anger. The paper was destroyed completely, leaving no way to read what was written.","translation":"他憤怒地把信撕成小片。紙被完全破壞了，沒有辦法閱讀上面寫的內容。","word":"tore"}},"tornado":{"createdAt":1781693471557,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tornado 是指一種猛烈的旋轉風暴，具有漏斗形狀，威力極強且具有破壞性。","options":["hurricane","tornado","blizzard","flood"],"sentence":"A devastating ______ swept through the small town, destroying buildings and uprooting trees in its path. The weather service had issued a warning just minutes before the funnel cloud touched down.","translation":"一場毀滅性的龍捲風襲擊了小鎮，摧毀了建築物並連根拔起樹木。氣象部門在漏斗形雲團接觸地面前幾分鐘發出了警告。","word":"tornado"}},"torture":{"createdAt":1781424137078,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"torture 動詞意為「拷打；折磨」，指對某人造成極度身心痛苦以獲取信息或懲罰。","options":["question","convince","torture","persuade"],"sentence":"The villain threatened to ______ the hero if he didn't reveal the secret location. The cruel interrogator used various painful methods to extract information.","translation":"惡棍威脅要折磨主角，如果他不透露秘密地點的話。殘忍的審訊者用各種痛苦的方式來榨取信息。","word":"torture"}},"torturous":{"createdAt":1781843396462,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"torturous表示極其痛苦和難受的，在此指牙科治療帶來的身體和心理上的折磨。","options":["pleasant","comfortable","torturous","relaxing"],"sentence":"The patient described the dental procedure as absolutely ______. She winced throughout the entire appointment because of the intense discomfort and pain.","translation":"患者將牙科治療描述為絕對令人難受的。由於極度的不適和疼痛，她在整個治療過程中都在皺眉。","word":"torturous"}},"tournament":{"createdAt":1781425122879,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tournament 指正式的比賽或競技會，與運動員和國際競爭的脈絡相符。","options":["exhibition","tournament","discount","fiber"],"sentence":"She trained for months to prepare for the ______ next spring. The competition would feature the best athletes from twenty different countries.","translation":"她花了幾個月時間為明年春天的錦標賽做準備。這項比賽將有來自二十個不同國家的最優秀運動員參加。","word":"tournament"}},"toxic":{"createdAt":1781738724027,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"toxic意指有毒的或含有毒物質的，能夠對生命造成傷害或死亡。","options":["nutritious","toxic","fragrant","beneficial"],"sentence":"The factory's ______ waste was dumped illegally into the river. Scientists discovered that fish in the water were dying within hours of exposure to the contaminated water.","translation":"工廠的有毒廢料被非法傾倒到河裡。科學家發現河裡的魚在接觸被污染的水後數小時內就死亡了。","word":"toxic"}},"trace":{"createdAt":1781773623444,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"trace作為名詞表示「蹤跡」或「痕跡」，指留下來的少量印記或線索。","options":["clue","trace","evidence","sample"],"sentence":"The detective found a ______ of blood at the crime scene that helped solve the case. By analyzing the DNA evidence from this mark, they were able to identify the suspect.","translation":"偵探在犯罪現場發現了一絲血跡，幫助破案。通過分析這個痕跡的DNA證據，他們能夠識別出嫌疑人。","word":"trace"}},"trade":{"createdAt":1781935654224,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"trade 是名詞，表示「貿易」，指國家或地區之間買賣商品的商業活動。","options":["conflict","alliance","trade","communication"],"sentence":"International ______ between China and the United States has grown significantly over the past decade. Both nations export and import billions of dollars in goods annually.","translation":"過去十年間，中國與美國之間的貿易顯著增長。兩國每年出口和進口數十億美元的商品。","word":"trade"}},"tradition":{"createdAt":1781696018690,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"tradition 意為傳統，指代代相傳、具有歷史和文化意義的習俗和做法。","options":["rule","law","tradition","invention"],"sentence":"The ______ of exchanging gifts on Christmas has been passed down through the family for generations. Every year, relatives gather together to honor this long-standing practice.","translation":"在聖誕節交換禮物的傳統已經在家族中傳承了好幾代。每年，親戚們聚在一起來遵守這項由來已久的習俗。","word":"tradition"}},"traditional":{"createdAt":1781784029105,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"special（特別的）在這裡指根據傳統習俗特別準備的，與「傳統的」意思呼應。","options":["modern","quick","special","festive"],"sentence":"In China, families often prepare a ______ meal together during the Lunar New Year. This custom has been passed down for thousands of years without significant change.","translation":"在中國，家庭在農曆新年期間經常一起準備傳統餐點。這個習俗已經傳承了數千年，沒有發生重大改變。","word":"traditional"}},"tragedy":{"createdAt":1781661288529,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"tragedy 是指引起悲傷或不幸的重大事件，通常涉及死亡、痛苦或失敗","options":["comedy","event","tragedy","story"],"sentence":"The sinking of the ship was a terrible ______ that claimed thousands of lives. Historians still study this disaster today as one of the worst maritime catastrophes in history.","translation":"船的沉沒是一場可怕的悲劇，奪走了數千人的生命。歷史學家至今仍將其視為歷史上最嚴重的海上災難之一進行研究。","word":"tragedy"}},"tragic":{"createdAt":1781832508020,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tragic 表示「悲慘的；不幸的」，形容造成死亡、傷害或嚴重損失的事件。","options":["comedic","tragic","fortunate","amusing"],"sentence":"The ______ accident claimed the lives of an entire family traveling home for the holidays. The investigation revealed that faulty brakes had caused their vehicle to collide with an oncoming truck.","translation":"這場悲慘的事故奪去了一個準備回家度假的家庭的生命。調查顯示，制動器故障導致他們的車輛與迎面而來的卡車相撞。","word":"tragic"}},"training":{"createdAt":1781362281728,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"training指的是訓練或培訓，通過系統的教學使人獲得新的知識和技能。","options":["vacation","training","entertainment","competition"],"sentence":"The ______ program at the company helps employees develop new skills. New staff members complete several weeks of instruction before starting their roles.","translation":"公司的培訓計畫幫助員工發展新技能。新員工在開始工作前完成數週的指導。","word":"training"}},"transcribe":{"createdAt":1781775276773,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"transcribe指將口頭內容或錄音轉換成書面文字的過程。","options":["erase","transcribe","delete","lose"],"sentence":"The secretary will ______ the recording of the meeting into a written document. She will convert every spoken word into typed text for the official record.","translation":"秘書將把會議的錄音謄寫成書面文件。她將把每句話轉換成打字文本供正式記錄之用。","word":"transcribe"}},"transfer":{"createdAt":1781746848182,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"transfer 表示「調動」或「遷移」，指將某人從一個地點或職位調換到另一個地點或職位。","options":["promote","transfer","retire","dismiss"],"sentence":"The company decided to ______ him to their new branch office in Shanghai. He packed his belongings and relocated with his entire family last month.","translation":"公司決定將他調動到上海的新分公司。他上個月收拾行李並和家人一起搬遷了。","word":"transfer"}},"transform":{"createdAt":1781746848183,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"transform 表示「轉變」或「改造」，指將某物改變成完全不同的樣子。","options":["damage","transform","preserve","demolish"],"sentence":"The architect's innovative design will ______ this abandoned warehouse into a modern art gallery. The project will take two years to complete the renovation.","translation":"建築師的創新設計將把這個廢棄的倉庫改造成現代藝術館。這個項目需要兩年時間來完成翻新。","word":"transform"}},"transformation":{"createdAt":1781665727112,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"transformation 指從一種狀態、形式或外觀完全改變成另一種，強調根本性的轉變。","options":["destruction","transportation","transformation","conversation"],"sentence":"The ______ of the old warehouse into a modern art gallery took two years to complete. The rundown building was now filled with contemporary paintings and sculptures.","translation":"老倉庫改造成現代藝術畫廊花了兩年時間完成。這棟破舊的建築現在充滿了當代繪畫和雕塑。","word":"transformation"}},"translate":{"createdAt":1781693471557,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"translate 意指將一種語言的文字轉換成另一種語言，特別強調按字面意思和風格進行轉換。","options":["summarize","translate","interpret","pronounce"],"sentence":"The student must ______ the French text into English for her homework assignment. Her teacher specifically requested that she convert each paragraph while maintaining the original meaning and style.","translation":"該學生必須為她的家庭作業將法文文本翻譯成英文。她的老師特別要求她在保持原意和風格的同時轉換每個段落。","word":"translate"}},"transmit":{"createdAt":1781598671064,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"transmit 作動詞表示傳播或傳遞，特別是指傳播疾病或信息","options":["cure","transmit","eliminate","predict"],"sentence":"Mosquitoes can ______ malaria to humans through their bites. Scientists have developed new vaccines to prevent this specific pathway of infection.","translation":"蚊子可以通過叮咬將瘧疾傳播給人類。科學家已開發出新疫苗來防止這種特定的感染途徑。","word":"transmit"}},"transplant":{"createdAt":1781693347920,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"transplant在醫學中指的是將器官或組織從一個人身體移植到另一個人身體內的手術。","options":["textile","tuition","transplant","wage"],"sentence":"The patient underwent a heart ______ after waiting on the donor list for two years. The surgical procedure was performed by the hospital's top cardiac team.","translation":"這名患者在等待捐贈者名單兩年後進行了心臟移植。這個手術由醫院頂級的心臟病專家團隊進行。","word":"transplant"}},"transport":{"createdAt":1781746848183,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"transport 表示「運輸」或「運送」，指將物品或人從一個地方移動到另一個地方。","options":["store","transport","display","recycle"],"sentence":"The company uses large trucks to ______ goods from the warehouse to retail stores across the country. This logistics network ensures products reach customers within one week.","translation":"該公司用大型卡車將貨物從倉庫運送到全國各地的零售店。這個物流網絡確保產品在一週內送達客戶。","word":"transport"}},"treasury":{"createdAt":1781651261374,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"treasury在此表示珍貴物品的收藏地或寶庫，引申為珍貴事物的集合。","options":["projection","overtake","treasury","rod"],"sentence":"The museum's ______ contained priceless artifacts dating back thousands of years. Each item in the collection was carefully preserved and considered invaluable to historians.","translation":"博物館的寶庫裡收藏著可追溯至數千年前的無價文物。收藏品中的每件物品都被小心保存，被歷史學家認為無價之寶。","word":"treasury"}},"tremendous":{"createdAt":1781664082523,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tremendous 表示非常大的、驚人的或令人印象深刻的，通常用於表達強烈程度。","options":["quiet","tremendous","scattered","brief"],"sentence":"The athletes received a ______ ovation from the crowd after winning the championship. The audience stood and cheered loudly for several minutes in celebration.","translation":"運動員在贏得冠軍後獲得了觀眾的巨大掌聲。觀眾站起來並為慶祝大聲歡呼了幾分鐘。","word":"tremendous"}},"trend":{"createdAt":1781401361943,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"trend指在短期內廣泛流行的風潮或傾向，通常是暫時性的而非長期固定的習慣。","options":["habit","tradition","trend","rule"],"sentence":"Social media influencers often start a new ______ that millions of people follow online. Right now, everyone is dancing to that viral song challenge that took off just two weeks ago.","translation":"社群媒體網紅經常開始一種新的趨勢，數百萬人在線上追隨。現在，每個人都在跳那個兩週前爆紅的病毒舞蹈挑戰。","word":"trend"}},"trial":{"createdAt":1781935654227,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"trial 是名詞，在此指「試用」或「試驗期」，允許用戶在購買之前測試產品。","options":["purchase","demonstration","trial","warranty"],"sentence":"The company offered a free two-week ______ of their new software before requiring customers to purchase a subscription. Users could test all features without paying any money.","translation":"該公司在要求客戶購買訂閱之前，提供新軟體免費兩週的試用期。用戶可以在不付款的情況下測試所有功能。","word":"trial"}},"tribe":{"createdAt":1781503378960,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tribe 指的是由共同血統、文化或領導人統治的小型社區或民族群體。","options":["nation","tribe","kingdom","empire"],"sentence":"The ______ lived in the remote forest for thousands of years. The indigenous group had its own unique language, customs, and governance system.","translation":"這個部落在偏遠的森林裡生活了數千年。這個土著民族有自己獨特的語言、習俗和治理制度。","word":"tribe"}},"tricky":{"createdAt":1782007196630,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「狡猾的；微妙的」用來形容不容易處理或容易使人誤解的事物，需要特別注意細節。","options":["easy","straightforward","tricky","obvious"],"sentence":"The math problem seemed simple at first, but it was actually quite ______ and required careful thinking. Many students made mistakes because they didn't read all the conditions in the fine print.","translation":"這道數學題乍一看很簡單，但實際上相當微妙，需要仔細思考。許多學生犯了錯誤，因為他們沒有仔細閱讀小字部分的所有條件。","word":"tricky"}},"trifle":{"createdAt":1781784283024,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"trifle是名詞，指微不足道的瑣事或浪費時間的事情；句子強調了這件事情的微不足道性質和時間的浪費。","options":["achievement","trifle","concern","responsibility"],"sentence":"He spent the entire afternoon on such a ______, arguing about something completely unimportant. His friends were amazed that he wasted so much energy on such a minor matter.","translation":"他整個下午都花在這樣一件______ 上，爭論一些完全不重要的事情。他的朋友們對他在這樣一件小事上浪費這麼多精力感到驚訝。","word":"trifle"}},"trigger":{"createdAt":1781452134703,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"trigger動詞表示引起、誘發或激發某種反應、事件或情況。","options":["prevent","soothe","trigger","eliminate"],"sentence":"Certain loud noises can ______ anxiety attacks in people with PTSD. Understanding these specific sounds helps therapists develop better treatment strategies for their patients.","translation":"某些大聲的噪音可能會引發患有創傷後壓力症候群的人的焦慮發作。了解這些特定聲音幫助治療師為患者制定更好的治療策略。","word":"trigger"}},"trillion":{"createdAt":1781449588285,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"trillion作為名詞表示「兆、萬億」，是一個極大的數字單位，等於一百萬個百萬。","options":["phenomenon","sensibly","trillion","improve"],"sentence":"The national debt has exceeded one ______ dollars, making it one of the largest financial obligations in the world. This astronomical figure represents a thousand billion dollars, which is difficult for most people to comprehend.","translation":"國家債務已超過一兆美元，使其成為世界上最大的財務債務之一。這個天文數字代表一千億美元，大多數人很難理解。","word":"trillion"}},"triple":{"createdAt":1781362281655,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"triple表示三倍的，即原數量乘以三。","options":["double","triple","half","quarter"],"sentence":"The ______ amount of revenue means the business grew significantly this year. What was earned last year is now multiplied by three.","translation":"三倍的收入意味著今年業務大幅增長。去年賺取的金額現在乘以三。","word":"triple"}},"triumph":{"createdAt":1781478568770,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"triumph 表示重大的勝利或成功。","options":["defeat","struggle","triumph","attempt"],"sentence":"Their ______ in the championship game was celebrated by thousands of cheering fans. The team's hard work and dedication had finally paid off.","translation":"他們在冠軍賽中的勝利受到數千名歡呼球迷的慶祝。球隊的努力和奉獻終於有了回報。","word":"triumph"}},"troops":{"createdAt":1781595752102,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"troops 指軍隊或部隊，通常指大量的士兵組成的軍事單位。","options":["supplies","troops","vehicles","equipment"],"sentence":"The military ______ marched through the city streets in formation. Thousands of soldiers wearing uniforms moved together as one organized unit.","translation":"軍隊在城市街道上排隊行進。成千上萬穿著制服的士兵作為一個有組織的單位一起行動。","word":"troops"}},"trophy":{"createdAt":1781738392786,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「trophy」指的是獲勝或成就的象徵物，通常是獎盃或獎品，與刻有名字的金杯完全符合。","options":["tedium","trophy","offense","obligation"],"sentence":"The winning team proudly displayed their ______ in the school's main hall. The gold cup had their names engraved on it as a permanent record of their championship victory.","translation":"獲勝的球隊在學校的大廳裡驕傲地展示他們的獎盃。金杯上刻著他們的名字，作為他們獲得冠軍勝利的永久記錄。","word":"trophy"}},"tropical":{"createdAt":1781449095513,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tropical意為熱帶的，用來形容靠近赤道、溫暖潮濕的地理區域或氣候。","options":["arctic","tropical","temperate","desert"],"sentence":"The ______ climate of Thailand makes it very hot and humid throughout the year. The weather there is typical of regions near the equator.","translation":"泰國的熱帶氣候使其全年都非常炎熱潮濕。那裡的天氣是赤道附近地區的典型特徵。","word":"tropical"}},"trout":{"createdAt":1781842000006,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"鱒魚是一種生活在冷水中的淡水魚，以難以捕捉和美味而聞名。","options":["salmon","trout","pike","bass"],"sentence":"The fisherman caught a large ______ in the cold mountain stream. He was excited because this freshwater fish is known for being difficult to catch and is prized for its delicate flavor.","translation":"漁夫在冷山溪中捕獲了一條大的______。他很興奮，因為這種淡水魚以難以捕捉和其細膩的味道而聞名。","word":"trout"}},"trustee":{"createdAt":1781429810261,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"trustee是指被委托管理他人財產或事務的人，需要承擔法律責任。","options":["firecracker","disappearance","trustee","swift"],"sentence":"The bank appointed a ______ to manage the estate funds and make financial decisions on behalf of the beneficiaries. This person is legally responsible for protecting the assets.","translation":"銀行任命了一名受託人來管理房產基金並代表受益人做出財務決定。這個人在法律上有責任保護資產。","word":"trustee"}},"tuition":{"createdAt":1781693347919,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"tuition指的是上學或接受教育所需支付的費用，通常特指大學或學校的學費。","options":["villain","wage","transplant","tuition"],"sentence":"She needed to save money for her child's university ______ which costs thousands of dollars each year. The school's education fees represent a significant financial burden for the family.","translation":"她需要為孩子的大學學費存錢，每年要花費數千美元。學校的教育費用對這個家庭來說是一筆巨大的經濟負擔。","word":"tuition"}},"tumble":{"createdAt":1781515329261,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"tumble 動詞，在這裡意思是價值暴跌、驟降，形容股票或物價迅速下降。","options":["rise","tumble","stabilize","fluctuate"],"sentence":"Stock prices began to ______ after the scandal was revealed to the public. Within weeks, the company's market value dropped by 40%, alarming all shareholders.","translation":"醜聞被公開後，股票價格開始暴跌。在幾週內，該公司的市值下降了40%，使所有股東感到震驚。","word":"tumble"}},"tumor":{"createdAt":1781832761717,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"tumor 表示腫瘤，指人體組織中異常增生形成的病理性增生物。","options":["muscle","bone","growth","vessel"],"sentence":"The doctor discovered a ______ in the patient's brain during the medical imaging scan. The abnormal growth required immediate surgical intervention to prevent complications.","translation":"醫生在醫學影像掃描期間在患者的腦中發現了一個腫瘤。這個異常生長需要立即進行手術幹預以防止併發症。","word":"tumor"}},"tumour":{"createdAt":1781770031234,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"腫瘤是指身體組織中不正常生長的細胞塊，可以是良性或惡性的。","options":["fracture","infection","tumour","scar"],"sentence":"The doctor discovered a ______ in the patient's lung during the routine medical examination. The biopsy results showed that it was benign and did not require immediate surgical intervention.","translation":"醫生在例行健康檢查中發現患者肺部有一個腫瘤。活檢結果顯示它是良性的，不需要立即進行手術治療。","word":"tumour"}},"twilight":{"createdAt":1781966009084,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"twilight 作為名詞除了表示黃昏時刻，還引申表示人生的晚年時期或事物走向衰落的階段。","options":["morning","twilight","summer","childhood"],"sentence":"The old man spent his ______ years sitting on the porch, reflecting on a lifetime of memories. He was in the final period of his existence, no longer young or working.","translation":"這位老人在他的晚年坐在門廊上，反思著一生的記憶。他正處於生命的最後時期，不再年輕或工作。","word":"twilight"}},"ultimate":{"createdAt":1781478568765,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ultimate 表示最終的、最後的、最高的目標或結果。","options":["preliminary","ultimate","secondary","temporary"],"sentence":"After years of training and competition, winning an Olympic gold medal was his ______ goal. He had worked toward this achievement since childhood.","translation":"經過多年的訓練和比賽後，贏得奧運金牌是他最終的目標。他自童年以來就為這個成就而努力。","word":"ultimate"}},"unanimous":{"createdAt":1781359980247,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"unanimous指全體一致、意見完全相同的；強調所有參與者都同意某個決定或觀點。","options":["narrow","unanimous","preliminary","delayed"],"sentence":"The committee reached a ______ decision to approve the new project without any opposing votes. All twelve members voted in favour of the proposal.","translation":"委員會一致決定批准這個新項目，沒有任何反對票。所有十二名成員都投票贊成該提案。","word":"unanimous"}},"unbiased":{"createdAt":1781693265626,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"公正是指沒有偏見或偏袒，能夠公平對待所有相關方。","options":["confused","unbiased","tired","suspicious"],"sentence":"The jury must remain ______ when evaluating evidence in the courtroom. Both the prosecution and defense teams are monitored to ensure fair treatment of the case.","translation":"陪審團在評估法庭證據時必須保持公正。控方和辯方團隊都受到監督以確保對案件進行公平處理。","word":"unbiased"}},"undergo":{"createdAt":1781481072316,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"undergo 表示「接受、經歷」，特別是指經歷醫療手術或治療的過程。","options":["observe","undergo","postpone","avoid"],"sentence":"The patient will ______ surgery next week to repair the damaged knee ligament. The doctor explained that this procedure is necessary to restore full mobility.","translation":"患者下週將接受手術以修復受損的膝蓋韌帶。醫生解釋說這個手術是恢復完全活動能力所必需的。","word":"undergo"}},"underline":{"createdAt":1781708461108,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"underline作為動詞，表示在詞語下面畫線，同時也引申為強調或突出某事物的重要性。","options":["circle","underline","erase","translate"],"sentence":"The teacher asked students to ______ the key vocabulary words in their textbooks. This technique helps readers focus on the most important concepts for the exam.","translation":"老師要求學生在教科書中重要的詞彙下面畫線。這種技巧幫助讀者專注於考試中最重要的概念。","word":"underline"}},"underneath":{"createdAt":1781431278562,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"underneath表示在某物的下方或下面，是一個表示空間位置的介詞。","options":["above","underneath","beside","within"],"sentence":"The cat was hiding ______ the bed where it felt safe and secure. When we looked down at the floor, we could see its eyes glowing in the darkness under the furniture.","translation":"貓躲在床下，那裡它感到安全和有保障。當我們向下看時，我們可以看到它的眼睛在家具下的黑暗中閃閃發光。","word":"underneath"}},"understandably":{"createdAt":1781693295124,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"understandably 是副詞，表示可以理解地或合乎情理地，修飾形容詞 stressed。","options":["mysteriously","understandably","fortunately","carelessly"],"sentence":"The students were ______ stressed about their final exams after months of intensive studying. Many of them had sleepless nights leading up to the test dates.","translation":"經過數月的密集學習後，學生們對期末考試感到可以理解的緊張。許多人在考試日期前都經歷了許多不眠之夜。","word":"understandably"}},"underwent":{"createdAt":1781345746902,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"underwent 是 undergo 的過去式，表示經歷或承受某事，在此指承受手術治療。","options":["avoided","underwent","postponed","cancelled"],"sentence":"The patient ______ a serious surgical procedure last month. The doctors successfully repaired the damage, and she is now recovering well.","translation":"患者上個月經歷了一次嚴重的手術。醫生成功修復了損傷，她現在正在康復中。","word":"underwent"}},"unemployed":{"createdAt":1781481124692,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"unemployed 指沒有工作或沒有被僱用的狀態。","options":["retired","wealthy","jobless","promoted"],"sentence":"After the factory closed, many workers became ______ and struggled to find new jobs. The government provided temporary benefits to help them during this difficult transition period.","translation":"工廠關閉後，許多工人失業，並努力尋找新工作。政府提供了臨時福利以幫助他們度過這個困難的過渡期。","word":"unemployed"}},"unemployment":{"createdAt":1781832508021,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"unemployment 表示「失業；失業人數」，指失去工作或無法找到工作的狀況。","options":["employment","unemployment","inflation","investment"],"sentence":"The economic crisis caused ______ to rise dramatically across the country last year. Statistics showed that over two million workers had lost their jobs within a six-month period.","translation":"經濟危機導致去年全國失業人數急劇上升。統計數據顯示，在六個月內有超過兩百萬名工人失業。","word":"unemployment"}},"unfold":{"createdAt":1781425094902,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"unfold 指故事、事件或信息逐漸展開、發展或被揭示的過程。","options":["collapse","disappear","develop","freeze"],"sentence":"As the mystery ______ throughout the novel, readers discovered shocking revelations about the protagonist's past. By the final chapter, every clue had been explained and all questions were answered.","translation":"當謎團在小說中發展時，讀者發現了關於主人公過去的驚人揭露。到了最後一章，每個線索都得到了解釋，所有問題都得到了回答。","word":"unfold"}},"unify":{"createdAt":1781503378961,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"unify 表示使分散的事物合併或連接成一個整體或統一體。","options":["separate","divide","unify","fragment"],"sentence":"The president's goal was to ______ the divided country under one vision. By promoting shared values and working toward common goals, he successfully brought the separated regions together.","translation":"總統的目標是在一個願景下統一分裂的國家。通過推動共同的價值觀並朝著共同目標努力，他成功地將分離的地區團結在一起。","word":"unify"}},"union":{"createdAt":1781503378962,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"union 表示兩個或更多事物的結合或聯合，形成一個統一的整體。","options":["separation","division","union","split"],"sentence":"The ______ of the two companies created a stronger business entity. After the merger was completed, they combined their resources and operations into one organization.","translation":"這兩家公司的結合創造了一個更強大的商業實體。合併完成後，他們將資源和業務合併為一個組織。","word":"union"}},"unique":{"createdAt":1781582424690,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"unique表示獨一無二的或特殊的，強調與眾不同，與unlike anything和no other artist相對應。","options":["popular","unique","traditional","colorful"],"sentence":"Her painting style was completely ______ and unlike anything anyone had ever seen before. No other artist in the world created work quite like hers.","translation":"她的繪畫風格完全獨一無二，與任何人之前見過的都不同。世界上沒有其他藝術家創作出像她那樣的作品。","word":"unique"}},"universal":{"createdAt":1781484415209,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"universal意指普遍存在於所有地方或所有人身上，不限於特定的群體或地區。","options":["rare","unique","universal","personal"],"sentence":"The desire to be loved and accepted is a ______ human experience. People from every culture and country throughout history have felt this same need.","translation":"被愛和接納的慾望是普遍的人類體驗。來自世界各地的人們在歷史上都感受到了這種相同的需要。","word":"universal"}},"universally":{"createdAt":1781862799294,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"「universally」表示在所有地方或對所有人都普遍適用，強調某事物具有廣泛的、無處不在的適用性或接受度。","options":["occasionally","universally","rarely","theoretically"],"sentence":"The principle of gravity is ______ accepted by scientists across all countries and cultures. Even in remote villages without modern education, people observe objects falling down, confirming this law works everywhere on Earth.","translation":"重力原理被世界各地的科學家普遍接受。即使在沒有現代教育的偏遠村莊，人們也觀察到物體向下墜落，證實這個定律在地球上到處都有效。","word":"universally"}},"university":{"createdAt":1781693295127,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"university 是名詞，表示高等教育機構，學生在此進行大學程度的學習。","options":["kindergarten","university","restaurant","hospital"],"sentence":"She was accepted to a prestigious ______ with a full scholarship to study engineering. The institution is ranked among the top 10 in the world and offers world-class research facilities.","translation":"她憑全額獎學金被一所著名大學錄取以學習工程學。該機構在全球排名前10，並提供世界一流的研究設施。","word":"university"}},"unprecedented":{"createdAt":1781481124698,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"unprecedented 指從未發生過或沒有先例的事情。","options":["common","remarkable","unique","expected"],"sentence":"The economic growth in that country was ______ in the region's history. No previous year had ever achieved such high levels of development and prosperity.","translation":"那個國家的經濟增長在該地區的歷史上是前所未有的。以前沒有任何一年曾達到過這樣高的發展和繁榮水平。","word":"unprecedented"}},"unrealistic":{"createdAt":1781869467057,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"unrealistic 表示「不符合現實、不可行的」，用來形容一個計畫或期望不符合實際情況。","options":["generous","impractical","flexible","detailed"],"sentence":"His plan to complete the entire project in one week seems ______ given the current resources and timeline. Even the most experienced team would need at least two months to finish such complex work.","translation":"考慮到目前的資源和時間表，他在一週內完成整個專案的計畫似乎不切實際。即使是最有經驗的團隊也需要至少兩個月才能完成這樣複雜的工作。","word":"unrealistic"}},"unstable":{"createdAt":1781345237585,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"unstable作形容詞表示容易改變、不穩定或可能危險的狀態。","options":["solid","unstable","permanent","secure"],"sentence":"The chemical mixture became ______ when exposed to high temperatures. Scientists had to work quickly to prevent an explosive reaction.","translation":"當暴露在高溫下時，化學混合物變得不穩定。科學家必須快速行動以防止爆炸性反應。","word":"unstable"}},"untangle":{"createdAt":1781345564014,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"untangle 表示解開、鬆開或整理複雜纏繞的物品，強調耐心地逐步分離糾結的東西。","options":["braid","untangle","curl","trim"],"sentence":"She spent an hour trying to ______ the knot in her daughter's hair. By carefully working through it section by section, she finally managed to free the strands without cutting them.","translation":"她花了一個小時試圖解開女兒頭髮中的結。通過小心地逐段處理，她最終設法在不剪斷髮絲的情況下鬆開了它們。","word":"untangle"}},"unusual":{"createdAt":1781503378960,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"unusual 表示不同尋常、罕見或與通常情況不同的事物。","options":["normal","usual","unusual","common"],"sentence":"The weather this winter has been ______ for our region. We have experienced temperatures far below our historical average and record-breaking snowfall.","translation":"今年冬天我們地區的天氣非同尋常。我們經歷了遠低於歷史平均值的溫度和創紀錄的降雪。","word":"unusual"}},"unveil":{"createdAt":1781848934139,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"unveil指正式向公眾展示或公開某個新事物或真相","options":["hide","unveil","delay","cancel"],"sentence":"The company will ______ its new product line at the annual conference next week. Hundreds of journalists are expected to attend and report on the announcement.","translation":"公司將在下週的年度會議上揭露其新產品線。預計有數百名記者將出席並報導該公告。","word":"unveil"}},"up_to_date":{"createdAt":1781775276769,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"up-to-date指保持在最新狀態，與立即安裝最新補丁和更新的做法相符。","options":["obsolete","broken","up-to-date","outdated"],"sentence":"Our company keeps all software ______ to ensure we have the latest security features. We install every new patch and update as soon as it becomes available.","translation":"我們的公司保持所有軟體最新，以確保我們擁有最新的安全功能。我們在每個新補丁和更新可用時立即安裝。","word":"up-to-date"}},"upgrade":{"createdAt":1781515634902,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"「upgrade」表示將某物改善或提升到更高的標準或版本。","options":["maintain","downgrade","upgrade","repair"],"sentence":"We decided to ______ our old computer system to improve efficiency at work. The new software and hardware will be installed next week.","translation":"我們決定升級舊的電腦系統以提高工作效率。新的軟體和硬體將在下週安裝。","word":"upgrade"}},"upright":{"createdAt":1781437435164,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"upright 表示直立的、挺直的姿態，與垂直或水平對齊的位置有關。","options":["crooked","fallen","upright","tilted"],"sentence":"The old oak tree stood ______ in the garden despite the strong winds that night. Its trunk never bent or leaned, maintaining a perfectly vertical position.","translation":"儘管那晚有強風，那棵老橡樹在花園裡挺直地站著。它的樹幹從不彎曲或傾斜，保持完全垂直的位置。","word":"upright"}},"uprising":{"createdAt":1781565657698,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"uprising 名詞指人民反抗政府或權力機構的暴動或起義，通常涉及大規模的公開抗爭。","options":["celebration","uprising","election","conference"],"sentence":"The ______ against the oppressive government began when citizens took to the streets demanding change. Thousands of people participated in protests and demonstrations that lasted for several weeks.","translation":"反對壓制性政府的起義開始於公民走上街頭要求改變之時。數千人參加了持續數週的抗議和示威活動。","word":"uprising"}},"urban":{"createdAt":1781337343699,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"urban意為城市的或與城市相關的，用於形容城市地區及其特徵。","options":["rural","agricultural","urban","natural"],"sentence":"The ______ development project transformed the rural farmland into a bustling city center with skyscrapers and shopping malls. The construction dramatically changed the landscape of the once-quiet countryside.","translation":"城市發展項目將農村農田改造為擁有摩天大樓和購物商場的繁華市中心。這項建設大幅改變了曾經寧靜鄉村的面貌。","word":"urban"}},"urge":{"createdAt":1781775363749,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"urge 是指內在的衝動或強烈的欲望，驅使一個人立即採取行動。","options":["obligation","urge","reason","plan"],"sentence":"He felt a strong ______ to call his mother and tell her the good news. Despite being late at night, he couldn't resist the impulse any longer.","translation":"他感到一種強烈的______想要打電話給他的媽媽並告訴她這個好消息。儘管已經很晚了，他再也無法抗拒這個衝動。","word":"urge"}},"urgent":{"createdAt":1781431278561,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"urgent表示需要立即關注和行動的緊迫情況。","options":["routine","urgent","weekly","scheduled"],"sentence":"The hospital received an ______ call about a patient in critical condition needing immediate surgery. The medical team dropped everything they were doing and rushed to the operating room.","translation":"醫院收到了一個緊急電話，告知一名患者情況危急，需要立即進行手術。醫療團隊放下手頭的工作，匆忙趕往手術室。","word":"urgent"}},"urine":{"createdAt":1781503378965,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"urine 是由腎臟產生並排出體外的液態廢物，含有水和代謝產物。","options":["blood","saliva","urine","sweat"],"sentence":"The doctor requested a ______ sample for the medical test. The laboratory would analyze this bodily fluid to check for any abnormalities or infections.","translation":"醫生要求提供尿液樣本進行醫療檢查。實驗室將分析這種體液以檢查是否有任何異常或感染。","word":"urine"}},"utterly":{"createdAt":1781693271586,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"utterly是副詞，用來強調程度是完全的、絕對的，比somewhat和slightly等程度副詞表達更強的intensity。","options":["somewhat","utterly","slightly","mildly"],"sentence":"After hearing the terrible news, Sarah felt ______ devastated and couldn't stop crying. Her emotional state was complete and absolute with no room for hope.","translation":"聽到這個可怕的消息後，莎拉感到完全崩潰，無法停止哭泣。她的情緒狀態是完全和絕對的，沒有一絲希望。","word":"utterly"}},"vacancy":{"createdAt":1781503378969,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"vacancy 表示空位或空房間，指可用或未被佔據的位置。","options":["guest","booking","vacancy","reservation"],"sentence":"The hotel had one ______ available for the weekend. The front desk clerk confirmed that only one room remained unoccupied for guests seeking accommodation.","translation":"酒店週末有一個空房間。前台職員確認只有一個房間仍未被占用，可供客人入住。","word":"vacancy"}},"vacant":{"createdAt":1781449095515,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"vacant意為空的或無人居住的，用來形容沒有人使用或未被佔據的空間。","options":["occupied","vacant","furnished","renovated"],"sentence":"The apartment had been ______ for several months before a new tenant moved in. The landlord finally found someone to rent the empty space.","translation":"在新房客搬進來之前，這間公寓已經空置了好幾個月。房東終於找到了一個租賃這個空房間的人。","word":"vacant"}},"vaccinate":{"createdAt":1781503378966,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"vaccinate 表示給人注射疫苗以激發免疫系統產生對特定疾病的抵抗力。","options":["infect","treat","vaccinate","isolate"],"sentence":"The health campaign decided to ______ all children against measles before school started. The vaccination program aimed to prevent disease outbreaks in the community.","translation":"健康運動決定在開學前為所有兒童接種麻疹疫苗。疫苗接種計劃旨在預防社區中的疾病爆發。","word":"vaccinate"}},"vaccinated":{"createdAt":1781479123531,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"vaccinated 表示已經接種過疫苗的狀態，醫療機構會根據接種情況決定防護措施。","options":["vaccinated","frustrated","educated","isolated"],"sentence":"The ______ patients were allowed to enter the hospital without wearing a mask. The medical staff verified their vaccination records before admitting them to the ward.","translation":"已接種疫苗的患者被允許不戴口罩進入醫院。醫療人員在將他們錄入病房前驗證了他們的疫苗接種記錄。","word":"vaccinated"}},"vaccine":{"createdAt":1781864339054,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"vaccine是預防性的醫學製劑，通過注射或口服來幫助身體建立對特定疾病的免疫力。","options":["medicine","vaccine","treatment","cure"],"sentence":"Everyone in our school received a ______ against the flu virus this year. The nurse gave us injections to protect us from getting sick during the winter season.","translation":"今年我們學校的每個人都接受了流感病毒的疫苗接種。護士給我們注射疫苗，以保護我們在冬季不會生病。","word":"vaccine"}},"vacuum":{"createdAt":1781933311792,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"vacuum（真空吸塵器）是能發出巨大噪音並用於清理地板的電動機器，而掃帚、拖把和海綿都是無聲的手動工具。","options":["broom","mop","vacuum","sponge"],"sentence":"After the party ended, Sarah used a ______ to clean up all the crumbs and dust from the living room floor. The loud noise from the machine echoed throughout the house.","translation":"派對結束後，莎拉用真空吸塵器清理客廳地板上的所有麵包屑和灰塵。機器發出的巨大噪音在整棟房子裡迴盪。","word":"vacuum"}},"vague":{"createdAt":1781653278516,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"vague是形容詞，表示模糊的、不清楚的，與具體和明確的意思相反，常用於描述不明確的說法或指示。","options":["clear","vague","detailed","precise"],"sentence":"His ______ instructions confused the team members about what to do. When he finally provided specific details and clear deadlines, everyone understood the project perfectly.","translation":"他的______指示讓團隊成員對該做什麼感到困惑。當他最後提供具體的細節和明確的截止日期時，每個人都完美地理解了這個項目。","word":"vague"}},"vain":{"createdAt":1781935654225,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"vain 是形容詞，表示「自負的」或「虛榮的」，指過分關注自己的外表或自我形象的人。","options":["humble","vain","quiet","friendly"],"sentence":"He spent hours in front of the mirror admiring his appearance because of his ______ nature. His constant need for compliments annoyed everyone around him.","translation":"由於他自負的性格，他花了好幾個小時在鏡子前欣賞自己的外表。他不斷尋求讚美的需求惹惱了周圍的人。","word":"vain"}},"valid":{"createdAt":1782021524331,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"valid 表示某事物在法律上或邏輯上站得住腳、合理且有約束力。","options":["valid","broken","signed","printed"],"sentence":"The contract is not ______ because it was signed without the witness's consent. The lawyer explained that the missing signature makes it legally unenforceable.","translation":"這份合約無效，因為它是在沒有證人同意的情況下簽署的。律師解釋說，缺少簽名使其在法律上無法執行。","word":"valid"}},"value":{"createdAt":1781503378964,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"value 作為動詞表示認為某事物很重要或有價值，高度尊重或珍惜它。","options":["ignore","neglect","value","despise"],"sentence":"She ______ her family above all else in her life. Their love and support meant more to her than any amount of money or possessions.","translation":"她在生活中最重視她的家人。他們的愛和支持對她來說比任何金錢或財產都重要。","word":"value"}},"valueless":{"createdAt":1781693264937,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"valueless 是形容詞，表示「沒有價值的」或「毫無用處的」，用來描述物品或事物的價值狀態。","options":["vanish","valueless","tempt","temporarily"],"sentence":"The old coins appeared to have no worth and seemed ______ at first glance. However, after the appraiser examined them, she discovered they were actually rare collectibles worth thousands of dollars.","translation":"這些舊硬幣乍看之下似乎沒有價值，顯得一文不值。然而，在鑑定師檢查後，她發現它們實際上是價值數千美元的稀有收藏品。","word":"valueless"}},"vanilla":{"createdAt":1781403377829,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"vanilla 可作為形容詞表示「普通的、基本的、沒有特色的」，除了指香草精的風味外，也用於描述簡單或平凡的事物。","options":["chocolate","exotic","vanilla","spiced"],"sentence":"She didn't want anything fancy for her birthday party, just a ______ cake with simple white frosting. Her preference for basic, uncomplicated flavors reflected her understated style.","translation":"她不想在生日派對上要任何花俏的東西，只是想要一個普通的香草蛋糕配簡單的白色糖霜。她對基本、單純口味的偏好反映了她低調的風格。","word":"vanilla"}},"vanish":{"createdAt":1781693264938,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"vanish 是動詞，表示「消失」或「突然不見了」，通常用來描述物體或人突然從視野中消失。","options":["tempt","socially","temporarily","vanish"],"sentence":"The magician performed an incredible trick where the rabbit seemed to ______ into thin air. The audience gasped in amazement as the animal completely disappeared from the locked box within seconds.","translation":"魔術師表演了一個不可思議的魔術，兔子似乎憑空消失。當動物在幾秒鐘內從鎖著的盒子裡完全消失時，觀眾們驚呼不已。","word":"vanish"}},"vanity":{"createdAt":1781849847405,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"vanity表示虛榮或過度關注外表，與「常看鏡子、注重外表」的線索相符。","options":["humility","vanity","modesty","simplicity"],"sentence":"His ______ was evident in the way he constantly admired his reflection in every mirror. He seemed more concerned with appearance than substance.","translation":"他的虛榮心在他不斷在每面鏡子前欣賞自己的倒影的方式中表現得很明顯。他似乎更關心外表而不是內涵。","word":"vanity"}},"vapor":{"createdAt":1781966009083,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"vapor 是物質從液體或固體狀態轉化為氣態時所產生的氣體或霧氣，通常在加熱時出現。","options":["liquid","vapor","solid","frost"],"sentence":"The hot water turned into ______ and rose into the air. We could see the invisible gas floating above the boiling pot.","translation":"熱水變成了蒸氣並上升到空中。我們可以看到在沸騰的鍋上方漂浮的無形氣體。","word":"vapor"}},"variable":{"createdAt":1781424356417,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"variable用來形容容易改變或不穩定的事物，特別是在不同時間或情況下表現不同。","options":["consistent","warm","variable","humid"],"sentence":"The weather in spring is quite ______ and unpredictable. One day it might be sunny and warm, but the next day could bring rain and cold temperatures.","translation":"春天的天氣相當多變和難以預測。某一天可能晴朗溫暖，但第二天卻可能帶來雨水和寒冷溫度。","word":"variable"}},"variance":{"createdAt":1781425094901,"q":{"answer":3,"explanation":"variance 指兩個或多個事物之間的差異或變異程度，在統計學中也表示數據的離散程度。","options":["agreement","similarity","connection","difference"],"sentence":"The ______ between the two survey results was significant and unexpected. When we analyzed the data carefully, we discovered that one group had been measured in centimeters while the other in inches.","translation":"這兩份調查結果之間的差異非常顯著且出乎意料。當我們仔細分析數據時，我們發現一組以厘米測量，而另一組以英寸測量。","word":"variance"}},"variant":{"createdAt":1781564440929,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"variant 作名詞表示變體、變種，指同一事物的不同版本或形式。","options":["origin","variant","cure","symptom"],"sentence":"The scientist discovered a new ______ of the virus that had different characteristics. This mutated form showed resistance to certain medications.","translation":"科學家發現了病毒的一個新變體，具有不同的特徵。這種變異形式對某些藥物表現出耐藥性。","word":"variant"}},"variation":{"createdAt":1781840667144,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"variation指的是對原物的改變或變化版本，在音樂中特指根據主題進行的變奏。","options":["repetition","melody","variation","arrangement"],"sentence":"The composer created a beautiful ______ on the original melody. He kept the same basic theme but changed the rhythm, tempo, and instrumentation.","translation":"作曲家根據原始旋律創作了一個美妙的變奏曲。他保留了相同的基本主題，但改變了節奏、速度和樂器編排。","word":"variation"}},"varied":{"createdAt":1781926464746,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"varied 表示多樣化的、種類繁多的，強調有許多不同種類或類型的事物。","options":["limited","varied","identical","boring"],"sentence":"The restaurant offers a ______ menu with options from different cuisines around the world. Customers can choose from Italian, Thai, Mexican, Japanese, and Indian dishes.","translation":"這家餐廳提供各種各樣的菜單，包括來自世界各地不同菜系的選項。顧客可以選擇義大利、泰國、墨西哥、日本和印度菜肴。","word":"varied"}},"variety":{"createdAt":1781693591740,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"variety 意為多樣化或多種選擇，強調不同種類或品種的豐富性。","options":["scarcity","selection","variety","limitation"],"sentence":"The restaurant menu offers a wide ______ of dishes from different cuisines around the world. You can find Italian pasta, Japanese sushi, Thai curry, and Mexican tacos all in one place.","translation":"餐廳菜單提供來自世界各地不同菜系的多種菜餚。你可以在一個地方找到義大利麵、日本壽司、泰國咖哩和墨西哥塔可。","word":"variety"}},"various":{"createdAt":1781401361944,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"various表示多種多樣、種類繁多，用來描述具有差異性和多樣性的事物。","options":["similar","various","ancient","rare"],"sentence":"The museum's collection includes ______ paintings from different countries and time periods. You can see works by Italian Renaissance masters, Japanese ukiyo-e artists, and contemporary African painters all in one building.","translation":"博物館的收藏包括來自不同國家和時期的各種繪畫。你可以在同一棟建築內看到義大利文藝復興大師、日本浮世繪藝術家和當代非洲畫家的作品。","word":"various"}},"vast":{"createdAt":1782021522931,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"vast 表示面積、範圍或規模極其龐大，通常用來形容無法一眼看盡的寬闊空間。","options":["tiny","vast","narrow","shallow"],"sentence":"The Amazon rainforest covers a ______ area of South America. Scientists estimate it spans over 5.5 million square kilometers, making it nearly impossible to explore in a lifetime.","translation":"亞馬遜雨林覆蓋了南美洲的廣大地區。科學家估計它跨越超過550萬平方公里，使得在一生中幾乎不可能完全探索。","word":"vast"}},"vegetarian":{"createdAt":1781775276775,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"vegetarian指不食用肉類但可能食用奶製品或雞蛋的飲食方式和遵循此飲食的人。","options":["carnivorous","omnivorous","vegetarian","vegan"],"sentence":"Tom follows a ______ diet and refuses to eat any meat products. He gets his protein from beans, nuts, tofu, and other plant-based sources instead.","translation":"湯姆遵循素食飲食，拒絕食用任何肉類產品。他從豆類、堅果、豆腐和其他植物性來源獲取蛋白質。","word":"vegetarian"}},"veil":{"createdAt":1781619188930,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"veil 指透明或半透明的面罩或布料，常用於婚禮或宗教場合。","options":["crown","veil","tiara","headpiece"],"sentence":"The bride wore a delicate ______ decorated with pearls and lace. It covered her face until the moment the groom lifted it during the ceremony.","translation":"新娘戴著一條用珍珠和蕾絲裝飾的精緻面紗。在儀式中新郎掀起面紗的那一刻之前，它一直覆蓋著她的臉。","word":"veil"}},"vein":{"createdAt":1782021524831,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"vein 是指將血液運回心臟的血管，通常在皮膚下呈現藍色或紫色，用於醫療抽血。","options":["artery","vein","muscle","bone"],"sentence":"The doctor used an ultrasound to locate the patient's ______ before drawing blood. The medical technician inserted the needle into the blue line running along the patient's arm.","translation":"醫生在抽血前用超音波定位患者的靜脈。醫療技術員將針頭插入沿著患者手臂延伸的藍色管線中。","word":"vein"}},"venture":{"createdAt":1781424356418,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"venture指的是具有風險或不確定性的商業活動或冒險嘗試。","options":["hobby","vacation","venture","tradition"],"sentence":"Starting a new business is a risky ______ that requires careful planning and investment. Many entrepreneurs lose money on their first startup because they underestimate the challenges involved.","translation":"開設新企業是一項需要仔細規劃和投資的冒險事業。許多企業家在他們的第一次創業中虧損，因為他們低估了所涉及的挑戰。","word":"venture"}},"verbal":{"createdAt":1781871338566,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"verbal表示通過言語或口頭進行的，與口頭承諾和會議中的確認相關。","options":["written","visual","oral","digital"],"sentence":"The contract includes both written and ______ agreements between the two parties. The CEO confirmed these spoken promises during the meeting last week.","translation":"合同包含雙方之間的書面和口頭協議。首席執行官在上週的會議中確認了這些口頭承諾。","word":"verbal"}},"verbally":{"createdAt":1781425122881,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"verbally 指用言語或口頭方式，與不是書面形式和員工記筆記的脈絡相符。","options":["physically","visually","verbally","digitally"],"sentence":"The boss gave instructions ______ during the morning meeting rather than in writing. Employees had to take notes carefully to remember all the details.","translation":"老闆在早會上口頭給出指示，而不是書面形式。員工必須仔細記筆記以記住所有細節。","word":"verbally"}},"verge":{"createdAt":1781824968061,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"verge 作為名詞表示「邊緣」，通常用在「on the verge of」這個片語中，表示即將發生某事。","options":["peak","edge","verge","center"],"sentence":"The patient was on the ______ of losing consciousness as his blood pressure continued to drop dangerously. The doctors rushed to stabilize him before it was too late.","translation":"隨著血壓持續危險地下降，患者接近於失去意識。醫生們急忙穩定他的狀況以免太遲。","word":"verge"}},"versatility":{"createdAt":1781840892406,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"versatility指事物的多用途和多功能特性，能夠適應多種用途。","options":["durability","versatility","simplicity","fragility"],"sentence":"The ______ of this smartphone makes it an excellent choice for both work and entertainment. Users can seamlessly switch between professional applications, gaming, photography, and streaming without any lag.","translation":"這款智慧型手機的多功能性使其成為工作和娛樂的絕佳選擇。用戶可以在專業應用、遊戲、攝影和串流之間無縫切換，毫無延遲。","word":"versatility"}},"verse":{"createdAt":1781774456603,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"verse 指押韻且有韻律的詩歌形式，與 poetry 同義。","options":["prose","letters","poetry","articles"],"sentence":"The poet wrote beautiful ______ that rhymed perfectly and expressed deep emotions. Each stanza contained lines of rhythmic language.","translation":"詩人創作了優美的詩歌，完美押韻並表達了深刻的情感。每個詩節都包含有節奏感的語言。","word":"verse"}},"version":{"createdAt":1781503378963,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"version 表示某物的不同形式、變體或詮釋，特別是在內容或形式上有所改變。","options":["copy","duplicate","version","clone"],"sentence":"The director released a new ______ of the classic film with improved special effects. This updated adaptation was filmed using modern technology and techniques.","translation":"導演發布了經典電影的新版本，改進了特效。這個更新的改編版本使用現代技術和技巧拍攝。","word":"version"}},"versus":{"createdAt":1781847052507,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"versus用來表示兩個對手之間的對比或對抗，常用於體育比賽或法律訴訟中表示雙方對陣。","options":["alongside","versus","within","beyond"],"sentence":"The championship game will feature Team A ______ Team B in an exciting matchup. Both teams have won all their previous games this season, making this competition especially fierce.","translation":"冠軍賽將以A隊對陣B隊，這是一場令人興奮的比賽。兩隊在本賽季都贏得了所有先前的比賽，使得這場比賽特別激烈。","word":"versus"}},"vessel":{"createdAt":1782006620282,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"vessel是指「船」或「船隻」，第二句中提到「wooden ship」（木製船隻）和航海經歷，完全對應vessel的定義。","options":["merchant","crew","vessel","explorer"],"sentence":"The ancient ______ sailed across the Atlantic Ocean with a crew of fifty sailors searching for new trade routes. The wooden ship was built in the 1600s and had to withstand massive storms and rough seas during its long voyage.","translation":"這艘古老的船隻帶著五十名水手跨越大西洋，尋找新的貿易路線。這艘木製船隻建於17世紀，必須在漫長的航程中承受巨大風暴和洶涌的大海。","word":"vessel"}},"veto":{"createdAt":1781478568766,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"veto 是指有權力的人或機構對提案的否決或禁止。","options":["veto","approval","amendment","revision"],"sentence":"The president used his ______ power to block the controversial legislation. Congress was unable to override his decision.","translation":"總統使用他的否決權來阻止這項有爭議的立法。國會無法推翻他的決定。","word":"veto"}},"viable":{"createdAt":1781832761712,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"viable 表示可實行的、可行的、有生存能力的，指某事物在實踐上是可能的。","options":["impossible","feasible","foolish","risky"],"sentence":"After analyzing the market, the business consultant determined that the startup's plan was ______ and worth pursuing. The financial projections showed realistic revenue growth with manageable costs.","translation":"在分析市場後，業務顧問確定該初創公司的計畫是可行的且值得追求。財務預測顯示現實的收入增長與可管理的成本。","word":"viable"}},"victim":{"createdAt":1781503378952,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"victim 指的是遭受傷害或損失的人，在這個句子中指的是被車撞傷的人。","options":["survivor","victim","witness","driver"],"sentence":"The ______ of the accident was rushed to the hospital immediately. The injured person had been hit by a car while crossing the street.","translation":"車禍的受害者被立即送往醫院。那個受傷的人在過馬路時被汽車撞到。","word":"victim"}},"vigorous":{"createdAt":1781839950957,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"vigorous 表示充滿精力和力量的,通常用來形容活動或運動的強度很高。","options":["lazy","vigorous","theoretical","relaxing"],"sentence":"The athletes performed a ______ exercise routine that left them exhausted. They maintained high intensity throughout the entire two-hour training session without stopping.","translation":"運動員進行了一項精力充沛的運動訓練,讓他們筋疲力盡。他們在整個兩小時的訓練課程中保持高強度,沒有停止過。","word":"vigorous"}},"villain":{"createdAt":1781693347920,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"villain指的是故事或現實中的壞人、惡棍或反派角色，通常與邪惡或犯罪行為有關。","options":["tuition","villain","wage","textile"],"sentence":"The ______ in the movie kidnapped the princess and stole the royal treasure. The antagonist was eventually defeated by the hero in the final battle.","translation":"電影中的惡棍綁架了公主並偷走了皇家寶藏。這個反派角色最終在最後的戰鬥中被英雄擊敗。","word":"villain"}},"violate":{"createdAt":1781798927526,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"violate 表示違反、違背或破壞法律、規則或協議。","options":["support","violate","promote","ignore"],"sentence":"The company was fined heavily for ______ environmental protection laws. They had been illegally dumping toxic waste into the river for several months.","translation":"該公司因違反環境保護法而被罰款巨大。他們已經非法傾倒有毒廢物到河裡好幾個月了。","word":"violate"}},"violation":{"createdAt":1781824444585,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"violation 表示對法律、規則或協議的違背或侵犯，通常帶有負面的法律含義。","options":["compliance","violation","agreement","cooperation"],"sentence":"The company faced serious legal penalties for its ______ of environmental protection laws. The government discovered they had been illegally dumping toxic waste into the river for months.","translation":"該公司因違反環境保護法律而面臨嚴厲的法律處罰。政府發現他們數個月來一直在向河流中非法傾倒有毒廢物。","word":"violation"}},"violence":{"createdAt":1781961517451,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"violence 指的是具體的暴力行為和身體傷害，而不僅僅是混亂或不安。","options":["chaos","violence","disorder","unrest"],"sentence":"The protest escalated into ______ when angry crowds began throwing objects at police. Authorities had to deploy riot control measures to prevent further injuries.","translation":"當憤怒的群眾開始向警察扔物體時，抗議升級為暴力。當局不得不部署防暴措施來防止進一步的傷害。","word":"violence"}},"virtually":{"createdAt":1781693591740,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"virtually 是副詞，表示「幾乎」或「實質上地」，用來強調某事物已經發生了根本性的轉變。","options":["slightly","marginally","virtually","partially"],"sentence":"The new technology has ______ changed the way we communicate with each other. Almost everyone now uses smartphones and social media platforms daily instead of traditional mail.","translation":"新技術幾乎改變了我們相互溝通的方式。幾乎每個人現在都每天使用智慧型手機和社群媒體平台，而不是傳統郵件。","word":"virtually"}},"visualize":{"createdAt":1781414438957,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"visualize指在腦海中形成心像或圖像，想像看到某物的樣子","options":["forget","visualize","criticize","minimize"],"sentence":"Before starting the project, the architect asked the team to ______ the final building design in their minds. They closed their eyes and imagined what the completed structure would look like.","translation":"在開始專案之前，建築師要求團隊在腦海中想像最終的建築設計。他們閉上眼睛，想像完成後的建築物會是什麼樣子。","word":"visualize"}},"vocalize":{"createdAt":1781693269014,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"vocalize 意思是用聲音表達或發聲，在這個句子中指的是通過唱歌來表達情感。","options":["hide","vocalize","write","ignore"],"sentence":"The singer will ______ her emotions through a powerful performance. She plans to express her feelings by singing a heartfelt ballad at the concert.","translation":"這位歌手將透過強有力的表演來發聲表達她的情感。她計劃在演唱會上唱一首深情的民謠來表達她的感受。","word":"vocalize"}},"volume":{"createdAt":1781838276305,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"volume在此指聲音的大小或響度。","options":["toll","proponent","volume","ordeal"],"sentence":"Please turn down the ______ on the television; it is too loud for everyone in the room. My elderly grandmother can barely hear the dialogue at lower levels.","translation":"請把電視的音量調小；對房間裡的每個人來說都太大聲了。我年邁的祖母在較低音量時幾乎聽不到對白。","word":"volume"}},"voyage":{"createdAt":1781661288532,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"voyage 是指長途的船舶或太空旅行，強調航海或太空中的旅程","options":["walk","voyage","flight","drive"],"sentence":"The explorer embarked on a long ______ across the Atlantic Ocean in the 1800s. The journey took several months as the ship battled storms and unpredictable weather at sea.","translation":"這位探險家在1800年代開始了一次跨越大西洋的漫長航行。這次旅行花了數個月，船隻在海上與暴風雨和不可預測的天氣搏鬥。","word":"voyage"}},"wage":{"createdAt":1781693347919,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"wage是指定期支付給員工的薪資或工資，特別是按小時或日計算的報酬。","options":["transplant","tuition","wage","textile"],"sentence":"The workers demanded a higher ______ to support their families and pay for living expenses. The factory owner refused to increase their hourly pay rate.","translation":"工人要求提高薪資以養家糊口並支付生活開支。工廠老闆拒絕增加他們的時薪。","word":"wage"}},"wander":{"createdAt":1781939898050,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"wander指沒有目的或方向地走動，強調漫遊和沒有具體目標。","options":["pursue","render","wander","target"],"sentence":"After the concert ended, the lost tourists began to ______ aimlessly through the unfamiliar city streets. They had no map and no destination in mind, just walking randomly wherever their feet took them.","translation":"音樂會結束後，迷路的遊客開始在陌生的城市街道上漫無目的地徘徊。他們沒有地圖，也沒有目的地，只是隨意地走著。","word":"wander"}},"wandering":{"createdAt":1781332009067,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"wandering 作為形容詞表示蜿蜒的、曲折的，通常用來描述路線或水流的形狀","options":["straight","wandering","fast","deep"],"sentence":"The ______ river creates a beautiful and scenic landscape as it flows through the valley. The water meanders back and forth rather than flowing in a straight line.","translation":"蜿蜒的河流在流經山谷時創造了美麗的景觀。水流來回迂迴流動，而不是直線流動。","word":"wandering"}},"ward":{"createdAt":1781401803899,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"ward off表示「避開、防禦或抵擋」某種不想要的事物或攻擊。","options":["invite","deflect","attract","welcome"],"sentence":"The goalkeeper managed to ______ off the opposing team's attacking shots in the final minutes of the match. His quick reflexes and positioning prevented multiple goals from being scored.","translation":"守門員在比賽最後幾分鐘成功擋開了對隊的進攻射門。他敏捷的反應和位置感阻止了多個進球。","word":"ward"}},"wardrobe":{"createdAt":1781955529032,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"wardrobe 指的是一個人擁有的所有衣服和相關服飾的總稱。","options":["apartment","wardrobe","bedroom","closet"],"sentence":"Sarah spent thousands of dollars updating her ______ with designer clothes and accessories. She now has an entire room dedicated to storing her extensive collection of outfits for every occasion.","translation":"莎拉花了數千美元用設計師服裝和配飾更新她的衣櫃。她現在有一整個房間專門用來存放她為各種場合準備的廣泛服裝收藏。","word":"wardrobe"}},"wary":{"createdAt":1781966009083,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"wary 表示謹慎小心或警惕，通常指對潛在危險保持警覺態度。","options":["happy","tired","wary","curious"],"sentence":"The dog became ______ when the stranger approached the gate. It barked loudly and kept its distance, clearly distrusting the unfamiliar person.","translation":"當陌生人靠近大門時，狗變得警惕。它大聲吠叫並保持距離，明顯不信任這個不熟悉的人。","word":"wary"}},"wasteland":{"createdAt":1781926370998,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"wasteland 意思是荒地、荒蕪之地，指被破壞或長期未開發的土地。","options":["garden","wasteland","sanctuary","reserve"],"sentence":"After the factory closed down, the surrounding area became a barren ______ with no signs of life. Nothing could grow there because the soil had been heavily polluted by decades of industrial waste.","translation":"工廠關閉後，周圍地區變成了荒蕪的荒地，沒有生命跡象。因為土壤被幾十年的工業廢料嚴重污染，所以什麼都不能在那裡生長。","word":"wasteland"}},"waterproof":{"createdAt":1781847052511,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"waterproof是形容詞，用來描述物品能夠防止水進入或滲透，特別是在衣服、容器或其他產品上。","options":["comfortable","waterproof","fashionable","lightweight"],"sentence":"I bought a new ______ jacket for my hiking trip next week. Since I'll be trekking through a rainy mountain area, I need clothing that won't let water seep through the fabric.","translation":"我為下週的登山旅行買了一件新的防水夾克。因為我將在多雨的山區徒步旅行，我需要衣服不會讓水滲透布料。","word":"waterproof"}},"wax":{"createdAt":1781926464744,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"wax 作為動詞或名詞，表示月亮逐漸變滿，與 waning（虧缺）相反。","options":["waning","wax","eclipse","orbit"],"sentence":"The moon enters its ______ phase when it grows larger each night. Astronomers can predict these cycles precisely because they follow predictable patterns.","translation":"當月球每晚變得越來越大時，它進入了蠟（漸盈）階段。天文學家能夠精確預測這些週期，因為它們遵循可預測的規律。","word":"wax"}},"weakness":{"createdAt":1781767999782,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"weakness 指的是個人的缺點或弱點，通常在自我評估或職業發展的背景下討論。","options":["strength","weakness","achievement","quality"],"sentence":"During the job interview, the candidate was asked to discuss her greatest ______ in the workplace. She honestly explained that she sometimes struggled with time management but had been taking courses to improve.","translation":"在工作面試中，候選人被要求討論她在職場中最大的弱點。她誠實地解釋說她有時在時間管理上有困難，但一直在上課以改進。","word":"weakness"}},"weary":{"createdAt":1781746848183,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"weary 表示「疲倦」或「疲憊」，描述身體或精神上的極度疲勞狀態。","options":["energetic","weary","excited","motivated"],"sentence":"After hiking for eight hours in the mountains, the entire group felt ______. They all collapsed on their beds immediately upon returning to the lodge.","translation":"在山裡徒步八小時後，整個小組都感到疲倦。他們回到小屋後立即倒在床上。","word":"weary"}},"weight":{"createdAt":1781747745753,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"weight 指的是物體或人的重量，通常用磅或公斤來測量，可以通過運動和飲食改變。","options":["height","weight","age","temperature"],"sentence":"The doctor told me to monitor my ______ by stepping on the scale every morning. Since I started exercising regularly, the number has decreased by ten pounds.","translation":"醫生告訴我要通過每天早上站在體重計上來監測我的體重。自從我開始定期運動以來，這個數字已經減少了十磅。","word":"weight"}},"weird":{"createdAt":1781935654226,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"weird 是形容詞，表示「怪異的」或「不尋常的」，指令人感到陌生、奇怪或超自然的事物。","options":["normal","pleasant","weird","familiar"],"sentence":"The ______ sound coming from the old mansion at midnight frightened all the neighborhood children. Nobody could explain the mysterious origin of these unexplainable noises.","translation":"午夜時分從舊宅邸傳來的怪異聲音嚇到了所有鄰近的孩子。沒有人能解釋這些無法解釋的噪音的神秘來源。","word":"weird"}},"whenever":{"createdAt":1782006620281,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"whenever用來表示「每當...時」，表示一個反覆發生的時間關係，適合搭配「many times」這類表示重複的語境。","options":["Although","Whenever","Unless","Because"],"sentence":"______ it rains heavily, the local river overflows and floods the nearby villages. The residents have learned to evacuate immediately because this pattern has occurred many times over the past decade.","translation":"每當下大雨時，當地河流就會氾濫並淹沒附近的村莊。居民已經學會立即撤離，因為這種情況在過去十年中已經發生過很多次。","word":"whenever"}},"whereas":{"createdAt":1781693269015,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"whereas 是連接詞，用來表示兩件事物之間的對比或相反的情況。","options":["because","whenever","whereas","unless"],"sentence":"Tom enjoys spending time indoors playing video games, ______ his brother prefers outdoor activities like hiking and camping. This contrast shows how different their personalities and interests truly are.","translation":"湯姆喜歡在室內玩電子遊戲，然而他的哥哥卻更喜歡登山和露營等戶外活動。這個對比顯示了他們的性格和興趣有多麼不同。","word":"whereas"}},"whine":{"createdAt":1781927792730,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"whine指的是一種帶有抱怨或不滿情緒的尖銳聲音，特別是用來表達不開心或乞求什麼。","options":["bark","whine","growl","howl"],"sentence":"The puppy started to ______ whenever its owner left the house. The continuous high-pitched complaint lasted for hours until someone returned home.","translation":"當主人離開房子時，小狗開始發牢騷。這種持續的尖銳抱怨一直持續到有人回家為止。","word":"whine"}},"whisper":{"createdAt":1781425094902,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"whisper 指非常輕柔和隱密的說話方式，通常是為了不被他人聽見。","options":["shout","announcement","murmur","speech"],"sentence":"He leaned close to her ear and spoke in a soft ______ so no one else could hear their conversation. The other guests at the party continued talking loudly, completely unaware of their secret exchange.","translation":"他靠近她的耳朵，用輕柔的低語說話，這樣別人就聽不到他們的對話。派對上的其他客人繼續大聲談話，完全沒有意識到他們的秘密交流。","word":"whisper"}},"whistle":{"createdAt":1781503378961,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"whistle 表示通過嘴唇發出高音調的聲音，通常是吹出的曲調。","options":["sing","hum","whistle","shout"],"sentence":"The old man loved to ______ while he walked through the park. His cheerful tune filled the morning air and made passersby smile.","translation":"老人喜歡在公園散步時吹口哨。他歡快的曲調充滿了清晨的空氣，讓路人微笑。","word":"whistle"}},"wholesale":{"createdAt":1781503378969,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"wholesale 表示以批發方式銷售或購買大量商品，通常價格比零售便宜。","options":["retail","expensive","wholesale","premium"],"sentence":"The company purchased office supplies at ______ prices from the distributor. They bought large quantities of items in bulk to reduce costs significantly.","translation":"該公司從經銷商以批發價格購買辦公用品。他們大量購買商品以顯著降低成本。","word":"wholesale"}},"will":{"createdAt":1781696018692,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"will 作名詞意為意志、決心，指克服困難和實現目標的精神力量。","options":["luck","wealth","will","genetics"],"sentence":"Through sheer ______ and determination, the athlete overcame every obstacle on her path to becoming an Olympic champion. Her mental strength was as important as her physical abilities.","translation":"通過純粹的意志和決心，這位運動員克服了成為奧運冠軍道路上的每一個障礙。她的心理素質與體能一樣重要。","word":"will"}},"willing":{"createdAt":1781566055842,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"willing 表示一個人樂意或同意做某事，反映了個人的主動態度和接受度。","options":["unwilling","able","willing","hesitant"],"sentence":"He was ______ to help his friend move to a new apartment on Sunday. However, he made it clear he could only stay for two hours due to other commitments.","translation":"他願意在星期天幫助他的朋友搬到新公寓。然而，他明確表示由於其他承諾，他只能待兩個小時。","word":"willing"}},"wisdom":{"createdAt":1781565657696,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"wisdom 名詞指深刻的知識和判斷力，通常通過經驗和深思熟慮而獲得。","options":["fortune","wisdom","education","luck"],"sentence":"Her ______ came from decades of experience and careful reflection on life's challenges. The elderly mentor shared insights that helped younger colleagues avoid making the same mistakes she had made.","translation":"她的智慧來自數十年的經驗和對人生挑戰的仔細反思。這位年長的導師分享了洞察力，幫助年輕同事避免犯她曾經犯過的同樣錯誤。","word":"wisdom"}},"wise":{"createdAt":1781738105691,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"wise 表示具有智慧、判斷力強和經驗豐富，能夠給出好的建議。","options":["foolish","wise","inexperienced","hasty"],"sentence":"The elderly teacher was known as ______ for her thoughtful advice and deep understanding of human nature. Her students often sought her guidance when facing difficult personal decisions.","translation":"這位老教師以她的深思熟慮的建議和對人性的深刻理解而聞名為聰慧的人。她的學生在面臨困難的個人決定時經常尋求她的指導。","word":"wise"}},"wit":{"createdAt":1781840659329,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"wit 指機智、聰慧的言語表達能力，特別是能夠快速、巧妙地說出有趣的話。","options":["strength","wit","patience","knowledge"],"sentence":"The comedian impressed the audience with his quick ______ and clever jokes. His ability to make sharp, funny remarks kept everyone laughing throughout the show.","translation":"這位喜劇演員以他的機智和聰明笑話給觀眾留下了深刻印象。他快速做出尖銳、有趣評論的能力讓大家全程歡笑。","word":"wit"}},"witness":{"createdAt":1781661288534,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"witness 是指目睹了某件事發生的人，可以提供目擊證詞或作為證人","options":["suspect","victim","witness","officer"],"sentence":"The only ______ to the accident was a woman who was waiting at the bus stop. She provided detailed information to the police about what she saw happen between the two vehicles.","translation":"這起事故唯一的目擊者是一名在公車站等車的女性。她向警察提供了關於她看到兩輛車之間發生事故的詳細信息。","word":"witness"}},"witty":{"createdAt":1781424574163,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"witty 形容說話或寫作充滿機智、風趣和聰慧的幽默。","options":["boring","witty","rude","confusing"],"sentence":"The comedian's ______ remarks had the entire audience laughing throughout the show. His clever wordplay and humorous observations were perfectly timed.","translation":"喜劇演員機智的評論讓整個觀眾在整場演出中笑聲不斷。他聰明的文字遊戲和幽默的觀察完美契合時機。","word":"witty"}},"woe":{"createdAt":1781414884516,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"woe是指深深的悲傷和不幸，通常用來形容因災難或重大失業而帶來的痛苦。","options":["wealth","woe","joy","anger"],"sentence":"The refugee family faced endless ______ after losing their home in the earthquake. Their pain and suffering continued for months as they struggled to rebuild their lives.","translation":"難民家庭在地震中失去家園後面臨無盡的悲哀。他們的痛苦和苦難持續了數月，因為他們努力重建生活。","word":"woe"}},"wonder":{"createdAt":1781841505536,"q":{"answer":0,"explanation":"wonder 作為名詞可指奇觀或令人驚嘆的事物，也可表示極其傑出或不可思議的人或事。","options":["wonder","pollution","entitle","healthcare"],"sentence":"The Great Wall of China is considered one of the world's greatest ______ due to its massive scale and architectural brilliance. Engineers and historians still marvel at how ancient civilizations managed to build such a magnificent structure without modern technology.","translation":"由於其龐大的規模和建築的精湛，中國長城被認為是世界上最偉大的奇觀之一。工程師和歷史學家仍然對古代文明如何在沒有現代技術的情況下建造如此宏偉的建築物感到驚嘆。","word":"wonder"}},"woodpecker":{"createdAt":1781709984198,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"woodpecker 名詞指的是以啄食樹皮中的昆蟲為生的鳥類，以其啄木的聲音而聞名。","options":["sparrow","woodpecker","robin","finch"],"sentence":"A ______ was tapping loudly on the old oak tree in my backyard every morning. The distinctive sound of its rapid pecking echoed through the quiet neighborhood at dawn.","translation":"每天早上，一隻啄木鳥在我後院的老橡樹上大聲敲擊。它快速啄木的獨特聲音在黎明時分迴盪在安靜的社區。","word":"woodpecker"}},"workforce":{"createdAt":1781661288533,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"workforce 是指一個公司或組織的全體員工或勞動力，代表組織的人力資源總和","options":["budget","productivity","workforce","revenue"],"sentence":"The company's ______ has grown significantly over the past five years. They now employ over 5,000 people across their factories and offices in multiple countries.","translation":"該公司在過去五年中的勞動力大幅增長。他們現在在多個國家的工廠和辦公室僱用了5,000多人。","word":"workforce"}},"workout":{"createdAt":1781917052440,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"workout指的是一段時間內的體育鍛煉或訓練活動，目的是增強體能或保持健康。","options":["conversation","workout","meeting","argument"],"sentence":"Sarah completed an intense ______ at the gym this morning, lifting weights and running on the treadmill. Her muscles were sore and she felt exhausted but energized by the physical exertion.","translation":"莎拉今早在健身房完成了一次激烈的鍛煉，舉重並在跑步機上跑步。她的肌肉酸痛，因為體力消耗感到疲憊但精力充沛。","word":"workout"}},"worthwhile":{"createdAt":1781619188933,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"worthwhile 指值得花時間和精力去做的，具有價值和意義的。","options":["tedious","worthwhile","pointless","exhausting"],"sentence":"Despite the initial challenges, the volunteer project proved to be ______ and deeply fulfilling. The team members reported that helping the community made all their efforts worthwhile.","translation":"儘管最初面臨挑戰，這個志願者項目被證明是值得做的，也很有意義。團隊成員表示，幫助社區使他們的所有努力都值得。","word":"worthwhile"}},"woven":{"createdAt":1781503378971,"q":{"answer":2,"explanation":"woven 是 weave 的過去分詞，表示通過交織纖維或線條製成的織物。","options":["carved","painted","woven","carved"],"sentence":"The ______ basket was made from colorful strands of natural fibers. Each strand had been carefully interlaced to create a durable and beautiful pattern.","translation":"這個編織的籃子是由彩色的天然纖維製成的。每條纖維都被仔細交織在一起，以創造一個耐用而美麗的圖案。","word":"woven"}},"wrinkle":{"createdAt":1781425078612,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"皺褶是布料或皮膚上形成的褶痕，可以通過熨燙或拉扯來消除。","options":["stain","wrinkle","hem","button"],"sentence":"When she washed the shirt, it developed a deep ______ down the front that needed to be ironed out. She placed it on the board and used the hot iron to smooth it flat.","translation":"當她洗襯衫時，前面產生了一道深深的皺褶，需要燙平。她把它放在燙衣板上，用熱熨斗把它燙平整。","word":"wrinkle"}},"yoga":{"createdAt":1781622232184,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"yoga 是一種源自印度的身心修練方式，包括姿勢、呼吸和冥想。","options":["pottery","yoga","cooking","swimming"],"sentence":"Every morning, Michael practices ______ to improve his flexibility and reduce stress. He spends an hour performing various poses and breathing exercises on his mat.","translation":"每天早上，邁克爾練習瑜伽來改善他的柔韌性並減輕壓力。他在墊子上花一小時進行各種姿勢和呼吸練習。","word":"yoga"}},"youth":{"createdAt":1781582424688,"q":{"answer":1,"explanation":"youth指的是青春期或年輕時代，通常指青少年時期，與childhood(童